battle.line: I don't know what I'm doing, but I'm doing it, buli!

detail.line: Buli? Buli? Where are we? What are we gonna do here?

drop_descrip.line: Universal Bulin. Can be used to limit break all ships of Elite rarity or below.

expedition.line: Buli! The girls are back!

feeling1.line: Wahh~! Commander is a big, big dummy!

feeling2.line: My big sis can apparently only strengthen one color. I can strengthen a bunch! Which means... that I'm more powerful than her? Wow! I'm stronger than her, buli!

feeling3.line: Bulin is happy that she can help everyone get stronger, but she enjoys playing with you too, Commander! Bulin can help strengthen you... Aww, why not?

feeling4.line: I'm not meant for combat, yet you use me anyway, so being the more sensible Bulin, I need to thank you! I guess it's just because we're too cute...? *Kyah~* I might be in love~!

feeling5.line: My heart races whenever I see you, Commander! I could dismantle the entire dock for you! Could this be... my inner fire? Buli!

home.line: Buli! Look, I'm full of energy!

login.line: If I swing this wrench hard enough, I could poke a hole in the office floor, buli!

lose.line: Huh? Am I... no good in battle, buli?

mail.line: Something strange just popped outta me, buli...

main1.line: Us Bulins are pretty awesome, buli!

main2.line: Is there nothing for Bulin to do? Really? Then let's go play! Wheee!

main3.line: Commander, let's go dig for some treasure, buli~!

mission.line: Buli? What's the mission?

mission_complete.line: Rewards... Can I eat them, buli?

profile.line: They say I'm just like my sister, but we're actually in charge of different colors... What's a color? Sounds yummy!

propose.line: Bulin has been caught~ Ahh, I'm blushing so much! What will I do! Let's buy some new toys and celebrate!

skill.line: My wrench is the wrench that will pierce the earth!

touch.line: Buli? Do you want to be bulified?

touch2.line: Buli? ... ... Buli?

unlock.line: Buli? Seems like I can help make your fleet stronger, buli!

upgrade.line: [Cannot be enhanced]

win_mvp.line: Buli? Could it be that... I'm super strong?!

battle.line: Witness the power of my new rigging, bulin!

detail.line: That green cat said something about this new equipment being "experimental," bulin. Not sure what that means, but since it looks like my sis, it must be super strong!

drop_descrip.line: Bulin? Did I just get an upgrade?! Now I can fight too, bulin!

home.line: Are you not letting me sortie because I'm too OP, bulin?

hp_warning.line: Bulin?! I'm in trouble, bulin!

login.line: I want to try out some experimental equipment here in your office, bulin!

lose.line: Ehh? I thought I was supposed to be stronger, bulin?

main1.line: This bulibulin has become even strongerer, bulin!

main2.line: Even though I look a bit like my sis now, she's still the only one in charge of super rares, bulin~

main3.line: I never get tired! But, Commander, you seem to get tired all the time... does that mean you're weak, bulin?

skill.line: Within my equipment is the power to end all creation!

touch.line: Bulin? Commander, did you wanna learn how to bulin?

touch2.line: Bulin! I'm about to activate my skill all over you!

unlock.line: Bulin? Did I just get an upgrade? Now, I can fight too, bulin!

upgrade.line: (I can't believe it... Even with my newfound powers, there's no way to undergo enhancement...)

win_mvp.line: Bulin! I've successfully buli buli'd the enemies!

battle.line: Purin~! Don't stop until they kneel and cry!

detail.line: Staring at me all day won't turn you into an expert!

drop_descrip.line: Prototype Bulin MKII. Can be used to limit break all Super Rare ships.

expedition.line: Yaaaay~! Commander! The girls who went out on a commission have come back! Let's drill something to celebrate!

feeling1.line: You're pretty amazing to have gotten on my bad side! But I won't get angry just to appease you! Haha! Enjoy your emptiness!

feeling2.line: My sister is so dumb. When people talk about our colors, it's not about our hair, it's about ra... rari... ah, now I remember! Reality TV!

feeling3.line: I'll let you in on a little secret. My little sister keeps telling people that she's smarter than me. But truth is, she's dumber! I try to be nice and let her feel good about herself, like a big sister should. Ha!

feeling4.line: Whee~! I'm flying! So~ high! Hey, don't move! You'll have to catch me if I fall!

feeling5.line: You're not an average commander if you managed to conquer my heart. But I won't be shy or blush! Instead I'll give you a growl! Graaaah!

home.line: Let's run around and relax! Purin~!

login.line: Righty tighty, Lefty loosey, Stay calm and Purin on!

lose.line: So why am I on the battlefield anyway, purin?!

mail.line: Purin! Secret skill: Drill Translation!

main1.line: Purin~! It's so big in here! There's so much room to run around!

main2.line: Oh right, it's not my job to just run around, is it? Purin~!

main3.line: Purin~? I'm too loud? Hmph, who cares what you think!

mission.line: Purin~! The next mission has been chosen for you!

mission_complete.line: I'm just heading out to fetch your rewards, purin! I promise I won't break them!

profile.line: Hahaha! It's your lucky day now that you've met me! We can purin together from this day forward! What for? To make everyone stronger, obviously! How do you purin? Like this! Purin~! Purin~!

propose.line: As a simple Bulin, I'm meant to just help strengthen your other ships... But you gave me this ring... You're a strange one! I like you! Come, let's raise our hands together and say purin~ purin~!

skill.line: My drill is the drill that will pierce the heavens!

touch.line: Purin~ You can't catch me!

touch2.line: Purin~ purin~! (Prototype Bulin MKII continues to spin faster)

unlock.line: Purin~! The herald of good fortune has arrived! Are you ready? Raise your hands and follow me... Purin~ purin~!

upgrade.line: [Cannot be enhanced]

win_mvp.line: Purin~! I'm the strongest!

battle.line: I'm fully charged, bulin! Let's show them what a real bulin's made of!

detail.line: If ever in doubt, just tell me to bonk it with my hammer, bulin!

drop_descrip.line: Specialized Bulin Custom MKIII. Can be used to Limit Break all Ultra Rare ships.

expedition.line: Bulin! The commission team has returned with boatloads of rewards!

feeling1.line: You've lost your way, but don't give up! Pull yourself together, bulin!

feeling2.line: The other bulins are only one color, but I'm the whole rainbow! Which can only mean one thing: that I'm the strongest of the bunch, bulin!

feeling3.line: As thanks for always hanging with me, I'll let you borrow my Kitty Kabam Hammer for an hour, bulin! But don't use it for any mean stuff, okay?

feeling4.line: Are you sure you aren't hanging out with me too much, Commander? If this keeps up, the port will be in ruins soon, bulin!

feeling5.line: I was made to upgrade fleets, nothing more, and yet you're being so kind to me... I love you, Commander! Let me give you a special type of bonk, bulin! Hm? You'd rather not?

home.line: Bulin? My gear and I both need to recharge, bulin!

hp_warning.line: Oh heck! My health bar is glowing red, bulin!

login.line: Commander, it's hammer time! You'll get super strong, bulin!

lose.line: My batteries are out... My Kitty Kabam Hammer was never made for battle, bulin!

mail.line: Is it true that more mail comes in when I go "bulin"?

main1.line: Sleepy, bulin? Then I'll charge you right up! I just need to plug in my... What? That doesn't work, bulin?

main2.line: You might get a surprise when you collect 1 of each bulin! But I dunno what the surprise would even be!

main3.line: My Kitty Kabam Hammer goes glimmer-glammer, sparkely sparkle, whooshy-kablam! Check it out, bulin!

mission.line: A new mission? A good bonk with my hammer should finish it, bulin!

mission_complete.line: Look here! Smash that Collect All button, bulin!

profile.line: A wrench, a drill, and a hammer... Wait a sec! Is there some kind of pattern here, bulin?!

propose.line: Woohoo! This shiny ring is proof of our love bond, bulin! Watch this! I'm gonna whack it to infinity with my hammer! ...Never, ever whack the ring? Okay then, bulin!

skill.line: My hammer is the hammer that will bring down the stars, bulin!

touch.line: This bad boy is my "raison d'etre"! Be careful with it, or you'll get hurt, bulin!

touch2.line: Oh nooooooo! I'm gonna overload, bulin!

unlock.line: Bulin~! Aren't you amazed? Standing before you is the legendary secret unlockable character of the Bulin family, none other than me! Rejoice, for you have been blessed with supremely good RNG, bulin!

upgrade.line: Glad you asked, but I can't be enhanced, bulin!

win_mvp.line: My Kitty Kabam Hammer is the strongest around, bulin!

battle.line: I'll do the best I can for everyone's sake!

detail.line: Is there something on your mind, Commander? Something you need my help for...?

drop_descrip.line: Farragut-class destroyer – Dewey, Hull Number DD-349.

expedition.line: The commission team has returned! They've brought with them exactly what we needed, so let's put it to good use!

feeling1.line: You're scarier than any storm, Commander...

feeling2.line: Are you hungry, Commander? Then would you like me to cook some curry and rice for you? Just so you know, I can't guarantee you'll like it.

feeling3.line: Commander, I cleaned your office earlier. Wouldn't you say it looks more orderly now? I could clean your bedroom too, if you'd like!

feeling4.line: Did you lose something, Commander? Then I'll search your room and try to find it!

feeling5.line: Commander, does your freshly dried futon feel comfy? Keeping your living environment clean is good for your health. But I'll look after you if you should ever fall sick, so don't worry about that!

home.line: Well done on the last mission! Allow me to take care of the after-combat report, and you can get some rest in the meanwhile.

hp_warning.line: I've taken significant damage... but I'm still in the fight!

login.line: Welcome back, Commander. Could we inspect the port's emergency relief supplies? You never know when disaster might strike.

lose.line: I-I messed up...

mail.line: Commander, please check your new intel regularly. By staying up-to-date, you can prevent disaster from striking.

main1.line: I love listening to music. My favorite song is made by Lexington!

main2.line: Eep! S-Sorry, Commander! Typhoons and thunder are just too scary for me...

main3.line: The caring Yorktown, the cool Enterprise, the peppy Saratoga... The Eagle Union has good people left and right.

mission.line: If missions feel like a chore to you, let me take care of them!

mission_complete.line: Isn't it wasteful to simply leave the mission rewards sitting there?

profile.line: I'm the Farragut-class destroyer, Dewey. I took part in many carrier convoys and support missions. I pride myself on my service history! Although... I sadly couldn't save two of my sister ships who were in trouble... Typhoons can be frighteningly strong...

propose.line: Is this... for me? Am I really your most beloved...? Okay! I can't promise I'll be perfect, but I will support you in any way I can, be it at work or in private!

touch.line: My hair is a little messy? Oh, thank you for pointing it out! Please let me return the favor by giving you a massage later!

touch2.line: Hm...? My chest doesn't hurt, so why'd you do that?

unlock.line: I'm Dewey, I'm a destroyer. If there's anything I can help with, please just say the word. Whatever I'm tasked with, I'll give it my all!

upgrade.line: No matter how tough the going gets, I will not let anyone down!

win_mvp.line: I did only what was expected of me. Everyone else deserves the rewards!

detail.line: What's in this notebook? Well, um... It's a story about a girl chasing after the person she longs for the most in her dream... Y-you want to read it? Fine... Ah, um! Please promise to keep it a secret from Miss Lexington!

drop_descrip.line: Saratoga went over there, and Lexington is... Oh, Commander, good morning! Are you here to play with us, or were you just out for some fresh air...?

home.line: Commander, if you're tired, let me give you a massage.

login.line: According to the weather forecast, it's gonna be real sunny today.

mail.line: There's a new announcement. Hopefully it's not a storm warning...!

main1.line: If you want to know where Saratoga is, I think I saw her playing beach volleyball with the others?

main2.line: I seem to be a bit too tired to swim... so I'll just enjoy the feeling of rocking around in this floaty ring...

main3.line: Does anyone need any help? ...Thank goodness, looks like everyone is doing well...

touch.line: C-Commander, please don't play with my floaty ring. You're going to get my notebook wet...

touch2.line: Eek?! I-I'm gonna flip over...!

unlock.line: Saratoga went over there, and Lexington is... Oh, Commander, good morning! Are you here to play with us, or were you just out for some fresh air...?

detail.line: I'd like to give Lexington a very special present for Christmas... What would you suggest, Commander?

drop_descrip.line: Lexington gave me this Christmas costume as a thank-you for always supporting her. Commander, do you think I look... pretty in it?

home.line: Commander, have you bought Christmas presents yet? I'm just making sure...

login.line: Merry Christmas, Commander. Umm, may you have a happy holy night.

main1.line: The star at the top of the Christmas tree... I wonder what it could mean?

main2.line: Commander, don't forget to greet everyone on Christmas. Everyone's looking forward to seeing you.

main3.line: Gridley took lots of pictures of Lexington for me. I ought to thank her later.

touch.line: E-Ever since I put on this costume, Benson has been really staring me down...

touch2.line: Pl-Please don't play around with the bells!

unlock.line: Lexington gave me this Christmas costume as a thank-you for always supporting her. Commander, do you think I look... pretty in it?

battle.line: Well... you're keeping me from my time off... I need to teach you some manners!

detail.line: I don't have anything you'd be interested in...

drop_descrip.line: Mahan-class destroyer - Cassin, Hull Number DD-372!

expedition.line: Work is finished...

feeling1.line: Can't you just let me sleep for a while?

feeling2.line: What is it, Commander? If you wanna have a chat with me then I doubt you'll have anything interesting to say...

feeling3.line: Hmm, how should I say this... If you're free, would you like to take a nap together?

feeling4.line: Commander, you don't seem like you've been sleeping well recently... Huh? It's because I keep moving over to your side of the bed?

feeling5.line: You're a real gentleman, Commander... but it's actually making me a little angry. Am I really... that unattractive to you?

home.line: My sister said I'd die from boredom if I always stay in my room... But we all die eventually anyway, so what's the big deal?

login.line: Even you can't make me leave my room, Commander...

lose.line: What a pain... Might as well head back.

mail.line: New mail... Aren't you going to take a look?

main1.line: Don't you have anything to say? I'm not great at starting conversations...

main2.line: Oh, you want to know about my eyes? One of them is fake... Can you guess which?

main3.line: Everyone is back! That's good...

mission.line: Hm... We have some uncompleted missions, is that really fine?

mission_complete.line: Rewards have arrived... Looks like we did well...

profile.line: Mahan-class destroyer, Cassin. I get picked on for being top heavy and not being great at defending the skies... My left eye has nothing to do with the Solomon Islands, alright? Just leave it.

propose.line: Commander, you've been preparing this in secret this whole time? I'd have been fine with any kind of gift, but... thank you. I'm as happy as I can be.

touch.line: Mmm... I don't hate this feeling...

touch2.line: Are you interested in shut-in girls?

unlock.line: How do you do? I'm Cassin... If you have no business with me, I'd like to stay in the docks...

upgrade.line: Even if I get stronger... I'd rather stay in my room...

win_mvp.line: What? That was it?

detail.line: Huh? Is there something... weird about me sitting in the shopping cart?

drop_descrip.line: I know I said we'd go shopping after school, but walking is so exhausting... I'll just hitch a ride in this cart. Looks sturdy enough...

home.line: Anything interesting happen late– Aahh! For the love of... Watch it where you put those ice-cold drinks!

login.line: I'm beat. Don't wanna move a muscle... Hey, Commander? Could you push the cart around?

main1.line: Do you drink a lot of coffee, Commander? I don't. Staying up all night is not my thing...

main2.line: I think Downes works here part-time. Just hope she doesn't kerplode anything...

main3.line: You could stock up on instant noodles so you won't have to go shopping for food for a good while. I think it's a good idea.

touch.line: Yeah? What? I'm not exactly hogging the entire cart to myself, am I?

touch2.line: There's security cams in here, you know...

unlock.line: I know I said we'd go shopping after school, but walking is so exhausting... I'll just hitch a ride in this cart. Looks sturdy enough...

detail.line: Fwaah... Commander, I need to take another nap, so I'm leaving the rest to you...

drop_descrip.line: Commander... I've been cocoooned up in my room for so long that I've started to metamorphize... Eh? It's because of the retrofit? Phew... thank goodness. Well then, guess it's time to go back to my room.

main1.line: Mmh... just staying together quietly like this... might be pretty nice too.

main2.line: Wear my clothes properly? Eh...? Don't wanna~ More importantly, care for an Oxy Cola, Commander?

unlock.line: Commander... I've been cocoooned up in my room for so long that I've started to metamorphize... Eh? It's because of the retrofit? Phew... thank goodness. Well then, guess it's time to go back to my room.

battle.line: Let's go, girls! Show them what we've got!

detail.line: Oh? Do you fancy girls with a bit of muscle? Girls like me?

drop_descrip.line: Mahan-class destroyer - Downes, Hull Number DD-375!

expedition.line: A commission has been completed... Hey, are there any commissions where we can blow stuff up?

feeling1.line: There's nothing I hate more than the listless!

feeling2.line: Hey, Commander, don't be such a slouch! How about going blast fishing with me?

feeling3.line: My body? Don't pay it any attention. I've only had half of it replaced. I can still eat and sleep just fine. Nothing's wrong!

feeling4.line: Although I really shouldn't care... I still worry if my love will accept me like this... Huh?! Commander! When did you get here? No, it's nothing. I was just... t-t... talking to myself!

feeling5.line: Commander, um... what should I say... I... my body may... be full of holes... but my heart is whole... and I give it all... to you...

home.line: Everyone is back! When are we taking off again?

login.line: Yo~! Commander, the wind is nice today. Want to go with me and feed our enemies some torpedoes?

lose.line: Ow ow ow... My magazine's been...

mail.line: Yo! You've got mail!

main1.line: Tsk! I'm so bored~ I wanna blow something up!

main2.line: My magazine's too easy to hit? It's fine, one day or another it'll blow up anyway!

main3.line: Oh, Commander, what do you think of the phrase, "I'm only half the person I used to be"? Sounds kinda philosophical, doesn't it?

mission.line: Looks like you've got some unfinished missions!

mission_complete.line: Alright, let's go fetch those rewards!

profile.line: Yahoo! I'm the Mahan-class destroyer Downes! I've had to undergo some pretty serious repairs, and have had to replace half my body! I'm stronger than I ever was now! I promise, you won't be disappointed!

propose.line: ...... I never thought I would see the day when I would receive this from you... It's not that I don't believe in you, Commander, it's that I don't believe... in myself. But now I can live without worries! Thank you, Commander!

touch.line: Ah, that's the spot, right there~

touch2.line: You looking to get bitten?

unlock.line: Hey! Are you the commander? I'm Downes. Nice meeting you!

upgrade.line: Hey, I really want to make something violently explode right now!

win_mvp.line: Weaklings, do you know Downes' power now?

detail.line: Hahahah! Whaddya think of my little creation here? Oh, and don't tell Akashi about it!

drop_descrip.line: I heard another person was coming to help out at the store, but I never thought it'd be you, Commander! What am I doing here? Ahaha, well uh, I had a little bit of free time on my hands... right~♪

home.line: And this bottle goes ri– Oh crap! ...Phew! Nice catch, Commander! That was a real close one...

login.line: Yo! Talk about being early! C'mere and gimme a hand stocking these shelves.

main1.line: Hey, Commander, pass me that triangular can! Cool, thanks!

main2.line: I reckon I can make an explosive out of stuff lying around the store! ...Look, I'm just saying it's possible!

main3.line: This fella's almost past its expiration date... Heheh. Should we ask Akashi for permission to do an inventory sweep?

touch.line: What'd I tell you – two heads are more productive than one!

unlock.line: I heard another person was coming to help out at the store, but I never thought it'd be you, Commander! What am I doing here? Ahaha, well uh, I had a little bit of free time on my hands... right~♪

drop_descrip.line: Roar! I'm the tiger, Downes! Hehe, Commander, how do you like me now? I feel super fired up right now, so hurry up and let me at 'em!

home.line: Commander, let me give you a massage! I promise, I'll make all your all your fatigue go away, hehe~

login.line: Yo! Commander, let's work hard today as well! If you get tired, I'll raise your spirits with a bang!

main1.line: Shall we go light things up on the seas? Well, just when you're free, Commander. I'm not that bored yet~

unlock.line: Roar! I'm the tiger, Downes! Hehe, Commander, how do you like me now? I feel super fired up right now, so hurry up and let me at 'em!

battle.line: You over there! Strike a pose! I'm about to shoot~!

detail.line: Wow, look at that cutie! No, not me! The one over there!

drop_descrip.line: Gridley-class destroyer - Gridley, Hull Number DD-380!

expedition.line: The girls who went out on a commission are back. I wonder how the photos I asked for turned out?

feeling1.line: You don't get to look at pictures of Sara anymore!

feeling2.line: So, Commander, don't you wanna see some awesome photos of Saratoga? Fine, fine, I'll show you! Aren't I nice~

feeling3.line: Commander, didn't you promise we'd go see Sara together? What are we waiting for? Let's go!

feeling4.line: Look at this one. It's great, right? This one, too. I'm confident about this one. ...Commander, why are you looking at me instead of the photos?

feeling5.line: Ah... You don't want to hear about Sara? You want... to know more about... me? Eh... um.... Ah! This is so embarrassing!

home.line: I need to develop these photos~

login.line: Hey, Commander~ So listen, Sara's just soooo cute!

lose.line: Dammit~ I lost focus!

mail.line: Commander~ You've got mail~!

main1.line: I've got plenty of pictures of Sara. 800 bucks a print!

main2.line: Mississippi will bring me back home just fine if I get lost!

main3.line: Commander, have you seen Sara? I want to try my new camera!

mission.line: The mission area is so pretty~ C'mon, let's go take some photos!

mission_complete.line: The rewards are here~! Now we can buy new some film!

profile.line: I'm the first ship of the Gridley-class, and I was very active in the Pacific theater. But never mind that now, Commander. Want to look at photos of Sara?

propose.line: Commander, Commander! Strike a pose! 1... 2... 3! Cheese! ...That was a great shot! We'll get a copy each after we develop the film~

touch.line: Aaah, that tickles~! I can't keep the camera straight~

touch2.line: Commander! If you do that again, I'll photograph it and report it to the police~

unlock.line: Nice to meet you, Commander! I'm Gridley. I once escorted Saratoga~ She's such a cutie!

upgrade.line: Now I can snap even more photos of Sara!

win_mvp.line: Ten out of ten! Commander, Commander! Take a photo of me too!

drop_descrip.line: Commander, Merry Christmas! Guhehe~ Won't you attend my "Super Special Sexy Sara (tentative)" photoshoot event?

main1.line: Christmas special edition Saratoga photos, one thousand dollars each! Guhehe~ my fangirl power level increases during the holiday season!

main2.line: Commander, can you take some photos of me with Saratoga?

main3.line: Thanks for the waterproof camera, Commander! I'll be sure to take good care of it!

touch.line: What's in this bag? Guhehe~ an album of premium Saratoga photos! As long as I have this, she will always be at my side!

touch2.line: Uwaah! Don't take any pictures!

unlock.line: Commander, Merry Christmas! Guhehe~ Won't you attend my "Super Special Sexy Sara (tentative)" photoshoot event?

battle.line: C'mon, everyone~ Let's fight with all we've got today~☆!

detail.line: Ahh~ Commander! D-don't get so close all of a sudden!

drop_descrip.line: Gridley-class destroyer - Craven, Hull Number DD-382!

expedition.line: No matter where they go, I'll always be my sisters' chealeader! C'mon, Commander! Lets go and greet them!

feeling1.line: I'll go cheer someone else on instead. I might not be coming back today!

feeling2.line: Cheering, outside of work? I don't... quite understand what you mean...

feeling3.line: You don't look very energetic, Commander. Should I pat you on the head to cheer you up?

feeling4.line: If you ever want me to, Commander, I-I would love to come and cheer you on any time...

feeling5.line: You. Can. Do. It. Co-man-der! L! O! V! E! Co-man-der! L! O! V! E! Did my cheers of love reach your heart?

home.line: Perfect! We've earned a flawless curtain call today!

login.line: Leave today's halftime cheering to me, Commander!

lose.line: Oh no... My cheering must not have worked...

mail.line: You've got new mail! Any inspirational messages to share?

main1.line: Even if it's time to rest, we've got to keep fighting and dancing. Never give up!

main2.line: Northampton thinks she can take me down? Hmph!

main3.line: Fight~ Come on~ Eagle Union~ ☆!

mission.line: We've still got unfinished missions, Commander!

mission_complete.line: I've got your rewards, Commander. Surely they must include some sort of surprise?

profile.line: I'm Craven, second ship of the Gridley-class, at your command. As a high speed torpedo destroyer, I was active in the Pacific theater with my little sisters, mainly tasked with night battle support.

propose.line: Commander, now we need to make a cheerleading team just for you. Hm? Of course I'll be the coach! Nobody else has feelings for you like I do!

touch.line: Commander, I can feel your encouragement. I'll work even harder!

touch2.line: E-even if you're just trying to encourage me, there's... there's this thing called being too passionate!

unlock.line: Second ship of the Gridley-class, Craven, reporting in. Leave the halftime cheering to me!

upgrade.line: Now I'll be able to cheer on everyone even harder!

win_mvp.line: Huh, I was just cheering everyone on... Oh well, this works too~

drop_descrip.line: I much rather cheer for my Commander than go to class...but no matter where I go, I will definitely give it my all! Commander, wait for me to come back as the top student of this school year.

main1.line: When you are overwhelmed by all this learning, go for a jog to relax yourself!

main2.line: If you're struggling with the material, then find a tutor. If that doesn't work, get special training...nothing can’t be solved through special training!

main3.line: The Commander has always been the best in my heart, so I have to be in his heart, too!

touch.line: These courses are too hard...Commander, can you tutor me?

touch2.line: I'm on fire!

unlock.line: I much rather cheer for my Commander than go to class...but no matter where I go, I will definitely give it my all! Commander, wait for me to come back as the top student of this school year.

battle.line: We have to fight? Guess I couldn't avoid it forever...

detail.line: Sorry, can we keep it brief? I need a new popsicle.

drop_descrip.line: Gridley-class destroyer - McCall, Hull Number DD-400!

expedition.line: ...Oh, everyone's back. I'll go get some popsicles.

feeling1.line: (McCall continues licking her popsicle and acts like she didn't notice you.)

feeling2.line: I heard those Sakura Empire girls sit around and drink tea all afternoon. I'd like to try that some day!

feeling3.line: Tips for daydreaming? Empty your mind and don't think about anything. Don't forget about your popsicle before it melts, though...

feeling4.line: Want a taste of my popsicle, Commander? Ah, yeah, it'd be like an indirect kiss, but that's fine... Anyway, can I daydream for a bit and lean on your back?

feeling5.line: I used to hope that my days of just eating popsicles and daydreaming would go on forever. But after meeting you, Commander, I think I might have been wrong...

home.line: It's kinda hot in here, got anything to help me cool down?

login.line: Commander, can't I just sit around here for today instead?

lose.line: Whoa, I got so scared I dropped my popsicle...

mail.line: *Sigh* There's no end to all this mail...

main1.line: We all get along around here, don't you think? Care for a popsicle?

main2.line: Ahh... Hawaii was so hot. I felt like I was melting...

main3.line: ... Ah! Oh no! My popsicle melted.

mission.line: Missions, huh? Whatever happens, happens.

mission_complete.line: Help me pack up these rewards... Hey, can we have them sent to my house?

profile.line: I'm McCall, third ship of the Gridley-class. There isn't much special about me, except that I've lived as long as my big sisters. I'm just relieved know that they're doing well.

propose.line: My life's changed ever since I met you, Commander... I'm sure we'll get to do many new things together. But there's one thing I hope won't ever change: that I'll be together with you...

skill.line: Let's finish this before my popsicle melts!

touch.line: ... Are you trying to encourage me?

touch2.line: Ah, it's so hot...

unlock.line: Hello, Commander. Just call me McCall. I like to sleep, daydream, and eat popsicles. Please assign me somewhere peaceful, will you?

upgrade.line: Hm... It's nothing special.

win_mvp.line: "Slay the enemy while your blade is still warm"... Is that true for popsicles as well? Oh, it melted...

battle.line: Lets finish this quick before I get hungry!

detail.line: Umm... Why are you always watching me do my warm-ups? Do you like watching me sweat?

drop_descrip.line:
Gridley-class destroyer, Maury, Hull Number DD-401
<color=#ffde38>Unlock build after receiving</color>

expedition.line: I need to get some exercise... Commander, a commission just got completed, so could you send me out on the next one?

feeling1.line: Sorry, I've got some training to do, so I gotta go!

feeling2.line: Commander, is it really okay for you to sit around all day? Get outside and do some sports!

feeling3.line: Want me to teach you how to run faster, Commander? There's quite a lot to it, actually.

feeling4.line: I feel like I can run even farther when I'm next to you, Commander. What an incredible feeling!

feeling5.line: Commander, how about going on a jog with me? I want to share the beautiful scenery I find with you.

home.line: Rest now so that we can sprint faster later!

login.line: Commander, want to do some warm-ups with me?

lose.line: ... I need to get back before everyone starts worrying about me.

mail.line: You've got new mail. It's about that celebratory party, isn't it?

main1.line: Commander, want to work out a bit? Sitting for so long is terrible for your body!

main2.line: I thought we were going for some long distance trip at Wake Island again.

main3.line: I swear it wasn't my tummy making that noise!

mission.line: You've still got some missions to finish up, Commander! Put your back into it, it's the final stretch!

mission_complete.line: Phew~ I'm exhausted... Save some Oxy-cola for me when the rewards arrive!

profile.line: I'm Maury, the fourth ship of the Gridley-class destroyer squadron. Although I'm the youngest of my class, I'm also the fastest short-distance Union ship! I'm prone to getting hungry a lot? Well, they say that light meals make you live longer, don't they?

propose.line: No matter how fast I run, I can't escape my feelings for you, Commander...

touch.line: Are you helping me recover? ... Thank you...

touch2.line: ...!! Hey! There's a line you shouldn't cross when giving massages.

unlock.line: You can just call me Maury. As a track athlete, I hold the Union's speed record, reaching a maximum speed of 42.8 knots. Just don't make me run a marathon...

upgrade.line: Not enough... I can still go faster...!

win_mvp.line: Like I said, those guys can't keep up with me!

battle.line: There's only a handful of enemies. Let's beat them with sheer numbers!

detail.line: I can move quickly, so I probably won't get hit. Well... even if I do, I'll... probably be fine.

drop_descrip.line: Fletcher-class destroyer - Fletcher, Hull Number DD-445!

expedition.line: A commission has been completed! Let's see what's next... Wow, there's so many! Almost one for each of my little sisters...

feeling1.line: S-sorry, I have to go check up on my little sisters...

feeling2.line: Whew... I need to take care of my sisters so much that I don't really have time to think about anything else...

feeling3.line: Commander, can you help me a little bit? Thank you... You're stronger than me, after all... I'm a little jealous.

feeling4.line: Out of all of us in the fleet... Who do you personally like the most, Commander? ... Counting me as well?

feeling5.line: Hm? You want to help me take care of my little sisters? There's a lot of them, and I could use the help, but... Are you really, REALLY sure? In that case... Can I think about it for a bit first...?

home.line: I'm back~ Wait, huh? Did another one of my little sisters join the fleet while I was gone?

login.line: Can you recognize me today, Commander? My sisters don't look like this!

lose.line: *Sob*... You bullies... My sisters will hurt you if they find out about this!

mail.line: Who has been writing so many letters to you, Commander? I'm a bit curious...

main1.line: Last time someone tried to impersonate me, one of my little sisters told them to name EVERY Fletcher-class ship. That's when they gave up the act~

main2.line: When I look at my little sisters, it makes me wonder... Maybe our parents were rabbits?

main3.line: ... Commander? Really... Are you thinking about one of my sisters again?

mission.line: I can go on missions with my sisters again. Give the order whenever you're ready, Commander!

mission_complete.line: I wonder if all my sisters can get an equal share of the rewards...

profile.line: I'm Fletcher, the big sister of all 175 Fletcher-class destroyers! As the main force of the destroyer fleet, I participated in all the important naval battles~

propose.line: A family, huh? ... I already have so many sisters, but you're special to me after all, Commander!

touch.line: My little sisters would probably like doing this too. Huh? Your hand would get sore from it?

touch2.line: C-Commander, please stop! What if my sisters see this...

unlock.line: Hm? You think we've met before? I get it... You know, I have over 100 sisters who look like me! I'll be following your orders from now on, Commander.

upgrade.line: Now I can take better care of my sisters!

win_mvp.line: I've heard that if you collect fifteen stars then one of your wishes will come true~!

battle.line: Little Beavers, full speed ahead at 31 knots! Keep an eye on your sides!

detail.line: Weapons and gear are the iron fists of justice!

drop_descrip.line: Fletcher-class destroyer - Charles Ausburne, Hull Number DD-570!

expedition.line: A commission of justice has just been completed!

feeling1.line: You're the embodiment of evil itself, Commander!

feeling2.line: Commander, there's still much injustice in this world, so we can't just stand around and do nothing!

feeling3.line: Being partners in justice is never easy. But you've got Ausburne by your side, so I'm sure we'll be fine!

feeling4.line: The path of justice is a lonely one. It's rare to have a partner on such a difficult path... What I mean is... I... D-do you want to read some stories about justice with me?

feeling5.line: In the stories I read, the hero always goes back to his normal life after defeating evil with his partners. I have to say, I feel a bit sad reading an ending like this...

home.line: Good work, everyone!

hp_warning.line: Justice will prevail!

login.line: Good day, Commander. Charles Ausburne, Captain of the Little Beavers, reporting in! Are there any naughty kids who need to be disciplined today?

lose.line: I'll be back! Justice will prevail! *Sob*...

mail.line: Your mail? Of course! We need help from others if we want to make this world a just one. Reply as soon as you can!

main1.line: Become a friend of justice with me!

main2.line: Justice is justice~!

main3.line: My sonar shows... it looks like your heart is beating extra fast, Commander!

mission.line: Commander, let's finish it in one go! Now is the chance to deliver swift justice!

mission_complete.line: Your rewards have arrived. It's always nice to be rewarded for your hard work, don't you think?

profile.line: I'm Charles Ausburne of the Fletcher-class, and the world famous Captain of the Little Beavers! I showed my true colors at the Cape of St. George. Want to be my partner in justice, Commander?

propose.line: ... Are you sure you want to give this... to me? You've really chosen me? Then I'll follow you until the end!

skill.line: Accept your punishment in the name of justice!

touch.line: Mmm, I feel the justice coming from you!

touch2.line: !!... Uh oh... You're evil, Commander!

unlock.line: Nice to meet you, Commander! I'm Charles Ausburne, Captain of the Little Beavers. Whoever picks on the hopeless and defenseless will receive their punishment in due time!

upgrade.line: This is the power of justice!

win_mvp.line: See? This is the real strength of the Little Beavers!

detail.line: Cannons and riggings make up the fist of justice. Honesty and bravery make up the beating heart of justice!

drop_descrip.line: Captain Ausburne of the Little Beavers, upgraded and ready to go! Heh heh, my new-and-improved justice isn't just for show! Evildoers are gonna be in for a bad time!

home.line: Good work, everyone! Hehe, even justice needs to rest~

hp_warning.line: Justice won't be defeated so easily!

login.line: Commander, Ausburne is ready to go at any time! I'll always be there to rush to the aid of people in need!

main1.line: Our allies of justice become more and more numerous! But, don't get overconfident just because we're getting stronger!

main2.line: Commander, don't be fooled by those evildoers who pretend to be righteous! With your heart of justice, you'll be able to see right through them!

main3.line: Woah, is this the "Superhero of Justice's Armaments" that Reno was talking about? It's freakin' cool!

touch.line: Haah! I'll transfer my power of justice to you, Commander!

touch2.line: *gasp*!! ...As a disciple of justice, how could you have such evil thoughts?!

unlock.line: Captain Ausburne of the Little Beavers, upgraded and ready to go! Heh heh, my new-and-improved justice isn't just for show! Evildoers are gonna be in for a bad time!

battle.line: I missed the Turkey Shoot last time, but this battle is mine!

detail.line: Don't touch my radar! It's our most effective weapon against the enemy during the night!

drop_descrip.line: Fletcher-class destroyer - Thatcher, Hull Number DD-514!

expedition.line: Another commission complete! I sure hope the girls didn't run into any kamikazes.

feeling1.line: You're so boring now, Commander...

feeling2.line: You're still upset about that prank? You're no fun!

feeling3.line: Commander, I want to always be able to play tricks on you, but... Do you hate me for that?

feeling4.line: What would you do if I told you I liked you? Hehe, I'm just joking~!

feeling5.line: Close your eyes, Commander~... *Kiss* Did you feel that? That wasn't me... Okay, it was!

home.line: Good work, Commander! Want me to help you relax? Don't worry, I won't play any tricks on you~!

login.line: What tricks should we play on the other girls today, Commander? Heehee~!

lose.line: Damn it! My prank failed! Ahh, Spence, get outta the way, I'll end up bumping into you!

mail.line: You've got new mail! I-I'm not hiding it this time!

main1.line: Commander, don't just stand there, come play with me!

main2.line: Hahaha, look! Spence's reactions are so hilarious!

main3.line: Since I don't know when I'll do something wrong, I'll just go ahead and apologize now.

mission.line: The game isn't over yet. Don't be lazy!

mission_complete.line: I'll take these rewards off your hands if you don't want them, Commander!

profile.line: I'm Thatcher from the Little Beavers. I'm named after Rear Admiral Henry K. Thatcher. Awesome, right? Aren't you surprised?

propose.line: Just so you know: you're totally wrong if you think my pranks will end just because I got this ring! My pranks are an expression of love. So, I'm expecting you to take~ good~ care~ of~ me~!

touch.line: I know what it is you really want to touch, weirdo!

touch2.line: Hoho? You wanna touch me there again?

unlock.line: Hi there, Commander! I'm Thatcher. Want to play a game with me?

upgrade.line: Aha! I came up with a new prank!

win_mvp.line: Pranking Tactics: super effective!

battle.line: Sssh, be quiet! We need to coordinate with our sisters preparing to flank the enemy.

detail.line: Don't forget to keep your gear in working order, Commander!

drop_descrip.line: Fletcher-class destroyer - Aulick, Hull Number DD-569!

expedition.line: The girls are back from their adventure!

feeling1.line: You think it's funny to call me by the wrong name?

feeling2.line: Want to take a walk together, Commander?

feeling3.line: ... After being called sweet for so long, I think I'm starting to get used to it. ... You call me sweet because that's what girls are? I-is that a compliment?

feeling4.line: Like a cookie - twist, lick, and dunk. D-do you want to give it a try, Commander?

feeling5.line: Commander... H-how sweet am I?

home.line: This place is great, Commander~ I've grown to like it more and more!

login.line: Yaaay! Welcome back, Commander!

lose.line: Why does everything have to hit me in the face?!

mail.line: You've got mail, Commander!

main1.line: Commander, won't you take Aulick out to play~?

main2.line: Aulick loves hanging out with all the other Little Beavers!

main3.line: Ah, Aulick likes the Commander too, of course!

mission.line: Commander, you've still got unfinished missions! You're being lazy, aren't you?

mission_complete.line: Reporting in! Mission rewards have been delivered!

profile.line: I'm Aulick of the Little Beavers! I was mainly tasked with air rescues. I'm not as strong as the captain, but I'll be more than satisfied as long as you let me fight till the end!

propose.line: My Little Beaver sisters are for sure going to envy me now.

skill.line: It's Aulick, I'm telling you! A-u-lick!

touch.line: Aren't I so soft and squishy?

touch2.line: C-Commander...! You're naughty!

unlock.line: Yaaay! It's so great to meet you, Commander! Just call me Aulick! ... What was that? I said Aulick! My name is Aulick!

upgrade.line: I hope it'll come in use to you, Commander...

win_mvp.line: I'd never let you down, Commander!

battle.line: You want me to be the flagship? That's too much work...

detail.line: Come on, hurry up. It's exhausting to hold this pose!

drop_descrip.line: Fletcher-class destroyer - Foote, Hull Number DD-511!

expedition.line: I love not having to go out on commissions... but it's annoying that I have to report back to you every time one of the girls come back...

feeling1.line: *Tsk* Could you just stop bothering me?

feeling2.line: Who would ever be interested in me... You're a real pain in the neck...

feeling3.line: You're being surprisingly quiet, Commander. I'll keep you company for a while longer then.

feeling4.line: Isn't it annoying to have to call me over all the time? I think I'll just move into your room instead...

feeling5.line: I feel like... I want to help you with stuff... Even though that's a bother... I'm so annoyed...

home.line: Being your secretary is so bothersome... I'm getting tired... Zzz...

login.line: It's so annoying having to greet you every day...

lose.line: *Tsk* Too much trouble. I don't wanna play with these guys anymore.

mail.line: Mail's here. There, I told you.

main1.line: *Tsk* Is the food ready yet?

main2.line: Commander... this doesn't go... oh forget it. It's too much trouble to fix.

main3.line: Thatcher and Spence are always fighting. Can't they just quiet down?

mission.line: Can't you just finish these missions already?

mission_complete.line: *Sigh* Do I really need to remind you every time you need to collect your rewards?

profile.line: I'm Foote, one of the Fletcher-class Little Beavers. You think you have family issues? Try remembering the names of your thirty older sisters and nearly a hundred younger sisters...

propose.line: This is annoying... But if it's for your sake then I have no choice...

touch.line: C-Commander... Could you stop touching me for a while?! I'm getting sore...

touch2.line: Being shy... is also pretty annoying...

unlock.line: *Tsk* Greetings... I hate greetings. But I suppose it's a formality... Hello, Commander. I'm Foote...

upgrade.line: I'm stronger now...? How annoying...

win_mvp.line: You don't need to praise me for something this easy.

battle.line: Commander... I'll work hard not to disappoint you!

detail.line: Ah! D-don't touch me anywhere weird, okay...

drop_descrip.line: Fletcher-class destroyer - Spence, Hull Number DD-512!

expedition.line: The girls are back! I'm so jealous of how awesome they all are!

feeling1.line: You're a bit scary, Commander...

feeling2.line: Woah! Commander... You scared me...

feeling3.line: My big sister said... that I can trust you, Commander...

feeling4.line: C-C-Commander, can I come stay with you when it's storming outside? I'm terrified of thunder!

feeling5.line: C-C-Commander... I just watched a film in which two people really liked each other... but they couldn't be together in the end... We'll be together forever, right?

home.line: You're back in one piece, Commander... Thank the lord!

login.line: C-Commander... N-no, I wasn't waiting that long!

lose.line: I-I'm so scared!

mail.line: C-Commander... You've got mail...

main1.line: Commander, it's so warm here! I think I can relax like this...

main2.line: Thatcher's over there! She's making me anxious~!

main3.line: Ausburne isn't like Thatcher at all... She actually helps me when I need it!

mission.line: Commander... You haven't finished all of your missions...

mission_complete.line: Remember to claim... that... reward...

profile.line: I'm... Spence from the Little Beavers. I took part in the Great Marianas Turkey Shoot with my younger sisters. Oh no! A h-h-hurricane is coming... Sorry, Commander, I forget everything when I get nervous!

propose.line: So you like me too, Commander? W-w-w-what will I do now... I'm so happy that I can't stop crying...!

touch.line: I'm sorry that I don't live up to your expectations, Commander...

touch2.line: Eeek~! Um... W-what am I supposed to...

unlock.line: Huh...? C-C-C-Commander... Hello... Spence h-has been wanting to talk to you... b-but didn't have the courage to...

upgrade.line: U-u-umm... I'll try to work harder now!

win_mvp.line: Whew, that wasn't easy...

battle.line: It won't be as simple as going back to the title screen if we get a game over~

detail.line: Stop touching my ears! I told you already, they're real! I-I'll bite you!

drop_descrip.line: Benson-class Destroyer - Benson, Hull Number DD-421!

expedition.line: Commander, the commission's been completed! I'm going to have to punish you if you forget about those girls!

feeling1.line: Oh evil being who conspires against cuties... in the name of the moon, I will punish you!

feeling2.line: Ahah! What's that tasty-looking snack you've got there?

feeling3.line: I am cuteness, and cuteness is me. Don't you agree, Commander? Yay!

feeling4.line: Commander, you keep telling me I'm stupid, but you actually like me, don't you?

feeling5.line: Commander! Cutie Benson has come again! I've been stopping by too often lately? That's because you haven't been paying this super duper cutie Benson a visit, so you left me no choice~ I'm not lonely at all, I swear!

home.line: Were you thinking about how badly you wanted to come back and meet me~? Come here, I'll give a positively explosive hug! ... Hm? Fine... I'm sorry, I'll put away the dynamite... J-just hold on a minute~

login.line: Let's hear your excuse for making the strongest and cutest cutie in the world wait for so long, Commander!

lose.line: Oh nooo! You didn't see anything, Commander! Got it?! *Sob*... I failed...

mail.line: Mail for you, Commander! I didn't want to anyone else to peek, so I went ahead and took a look myself first!

main1.line: I'm so cute! The cutest in the universe!

main2.line: I'm telling you, Commander, Fletcher's house next door is full of people! Us girls need to help her out every now and then~.

main3.line: If you don't talk to me enough then I'll stop being a bunny! Woof woof!

mission.line: A mission? No problem! Easy peasy! Bring it on, whatever it may be!

mission_complete.line: Come on, come on! Give me a reward!

profile.line: Here comes Benson! I'm way cooler than Anderson. I'm a capital destroyer, and can move at speeds up to 35 knots! My anti-air defenses are just as impressive. I can't wait for you to see me in battle!

propose.line: Hehe, so you've finally noticed how important I am? Have you? Do you understand that I'm irreplaceable and that just a glance of me makes your heart skip a beat? ... Commander, why are you touching my forehead?

touch.line: Whoa! I actually fell asleep! Could this be because of that fabled super hypnosis thing?!

touch2.line: Ah, I feel so hot... I'm burning inside!

unlock.line: Yahoo! Commander! Aren't you charmed by how cute and risqué I am? Huh? W-who am I? ... Hahaha... My name is Benson... It's a pleasure to meet you...

upgrade.line: My cuteness level has gone up even higher!

win_mvp.line: Hoho! Even the most cunning fox couldn't best a rabbit like me!

detail.line: One swing from my amazing magic pumpkin wand will blow all the monsters to kingdom come! ...O-of course, I'm just joking... Ahahaha...

drop_descrip.line: Fighting for love and peace this Halloween night, it's none other than the pumpkin-style Planet Bunny cutie pie, Benson!

home.line: Raven eggs and golem clay, make the beasties go away! There, now no monster's gonna bother you anymore!

login.line: You're late, Commander. Come on, let's go on a Halloween monster mashing quest!

main1.line: Show yourselves, Halloween beasties! Queen of cuties Benson has a bone to pick with you!

main2.line: Commander! If you don't start giving me attention soon, I'm gonna bonk you on the head with my wand!

main3.line: It's Halloween, soooo... Trick or treat! Well duh, of course I know what it means! I'm not a little kid like Bailey.

touch.line: Woohoo! Top me off with some pumpkin power!

touch2.line: Eep! I-I've used up all my pumpkin power...

unlock.line: Fighting for love and peace this Halloween night, it's none other than the pumpkin-style Planet Bunny cutie pie, Benson!

battle.line: Deactivating self-imposed limiter...

detail.line: Will you still come see me even if I grow out of this body?

drop_descrip.line: Benson-class destroyer - Laffey, Hull Number DD-459!

expedition.line: I was actually wondering whether you'd remember it or not, but a commission has been completed, Commander.

feeling1.line: Zzzzzzz...

feeling2.line: *Yawns* Commander, want to take a nap with me?

feeling3.line: I thought you were a bit boring at first, Commander... But now that I've been thinking about it, I'm not really motivated about anything other than fighting, so we might be a decent match...

feeling4.line: I'm used to being alone... But I think I like it better when you're with me, Commander... Mmm... Zzzzzz...

feeling5.line: I've been thinking... If you'd been there back then, I might have been able to take down {namecode:71}... But if she comes after you now, then this time I won't let her go...

headtouch.line: Mmh... Stop shaking me, Commander...

home.line: I've returned from the mission. Regrouping with original unit.

hp_warning.line: This isn't good enough... I used to be much better...

login.line: Did you have a good rest, Commander? I'm full of energy. Probably.

lose.line: Mmm... We lost... They weren't so easy were they?

mail.line: Commander, your mail...

main1.line: Commander, don't you think we should plant some flowers?

main2.line: Since you're ignoring me, I might as well... *yawns*... get some sleep.

main3.line: Yes? This is what I look like when I'm happy.

main4.line: I'm not trying to make you pay attention to me. Nope, not at all...

main5.line: I'm not trying to get you to play with me. Nope, probably not...

mission.line: Looks like we've still got a few missions to do...

mission_complete.line: Mhm, we got some rewards.

profile.line: I'm the much anticipated Benson-class destroyer, Laffey, who performed excellently during the Third Battle of the Solomon Sea. Battleship? What's that?

propose.line: I thought I wouldn't mind becoming a demon again if it was for you, Commander… But since you've taken such good care of me, I guess my chance for that is gone… Have I disappointed you, Commander?

touch.line: Are you tired, Commander?

touch2.line: Are you... a pervert, Commander...?

unlock.line: Benson-class destroyer, Laffey, awaiting your orders... Commander, these ears aren't real... you don't need to stare at them...

upgrade.line: Mm... Back to sleep for me...

win_mvp.line: Mm... That was okay.

battle.line: It's hard to move around...

detail.line: Don't drag me around... I'm tired after my walk with the dog, Commander...

drop_descrip.line: Mmph... The waistline is too high... and a little too tight... The sleeves are too breezy cause they're so big... It's not like I wanted to change clothes, but... what do you think, Commander?

login.line: I look cute in it? Then I guess... I'll keep it on a little longer.

main1.line: Want a candied apple, Commander? I got it from Ayanami. Here.

main2.line: I hope... I'll have lots of good naps... this whole year.

main3.line: Commander, my friends are calling for me... so I'm gonna go play with them.

touch.line: Winter... makes me so sleepy...

touch2.line: Commander, you pervert...

unlock.line: Mmph... The waistline is too high... and a little too tight... The sleeves are too breezy cause they're so big... It's not like I wanted to change clothes, but... what do you think, Commander?

detail.line: New Year... and Lunar New Year... are different? I don't really get it... Although, any day with good food and lots of sleep... is a good day. Mhm.

drop_descrip.line: "Have a happy New Year. Let's pray for everyone's good luck"... Is that enough...? *Yawn*, I'm tired... Can I go home now and take a nap...?

home.line: You know the crackles and pops firecrackers make after you light the fuse... *Ughh*... Those are so noisy...

login.line: The Commander's still not back. I might just fall asleep here... Zzzzz...

main1.line: I'm wearing limited-edition Lunar New Year bunny ears and bunny slippers... do you like them? I like them.

main2.line: I think Zed is interested in old Lunar New Year folklore...

main3.line: Sitting on top of this tree makes me feel like I'm going to blossom, too...

touch.line: I totally don't feel like leaning against your shoulder, Commander. Nope, not at all...

touch2.line: This strange sensation... Could it be EM waves from Planet Bunny...?

unlock.line: Can you see the ghost next to me? Hehehe— the black witch from Planet Bunny is none other than me, Bailey!

detail.line: Commander, why don't you be a Bunny Santa, too? It's really fun to give out gifts to all the good boys and girls!

drop_descrip.line: Your Bunny Santa has arrived! That's right – not regular ol' Santa, but Bunny Santa! The real Santa's busy, so Bailey from Planet Bunny is here to help out!

home.line: Now that you're back, it's time to get back to delivering presents! Don't worry; the cold is nothing to Bunny Santa!

login.line: There you are, Commander. Get over here and help me out! There are way too many presents here for one bunny to carry...

main1.line: Santa is real! Planet Bunny has Santa, so this planet has to have one, too! Heehee!

main2.line: Kalk, you can't give people chili peppers for Christmas! And Hobby, the Commander's helping me out right now, so you can play reindeer later!

main3.line: Cutie and Lucky, did you deliver the presents like I asked? Aww, thank you!

touch.line: Can you carry the heavy stuff for me? Thank you! Bunny Santa rates you nice this year!

touch2.line: Brr, that's chilly... Uh, but that isn't the only problem here!

unlock.line: Your Bunny Santa has arrived! That's right – not regular ol' Santa, but Bunny Santa! The real Santa's busy, so Bailey from Planet Bunny is here to help out!

battle.line: Bunny magic is suuuuper strong!

detail.line: Cutie, Lucky, I'm leaving the equipment to you two~!

drop_descrip.line: This long-awaited day has finally come. My bunnies, are you all ready? Bailey's debut shall now begin! Commander, my sisters, let's all come see Bailey's bunny magic!

home.line: Good work! Bailey shall use her brighest smile to soothe Commander's heart!

mail.line: Commander, there's mail! Is there any fanmail for Bailey?

main1.line: Bailey will always be shining brighter in the next moment~!

main2.line: Commander, Commander! Is Bailey cute? Ehehe... you can praise Bailey some more~!

unlock.line: This day has finally arrived~ Are you ready, Rabbits? Bailey’s new debut is about to begin. Commander, sisters, come and witness Bailey’s rabbit magic!

win_mvp.line: It's Bailey from Planet Bunny! Everyone, please give me your support~

battle.line: No need to thank me! Good things are meant to be shared. I'm not gonna hog all of my candy!

detail.line: Commander, do you appreciate something sweet every now and then? Here, take whatever you like.

drop_descrip.line: Fletcher-class Destroyer - Radford, Hull Number DD-446!

expedition.line: Hey, Commander! How about we exchange all our commission rewards for candy instead?

feeling1.line: I'm never giving you any more candy ever again!

feeling2.line: I feel like my famous sisters always make me seem a bit... insignificant. Oh well, I guess there's nothing wrong with that.

feeling3.line: Hey, Commander, that candy you gave me the other day was really good. Where'd you get it?

feeling4.line: Have you ever tried making your own candy? It's fun! Here, try some of mine!

feeling5.line: I made some chocolate just for you, Commander! Will you take it?

home.line: C-Commander! Did you manage to snatch any candy from the enemies? ... They didn't have any?!

login.line: If my hunch is right, Commander's candy should be... Huh? Hey! There's nothing here!

lose.line: My... my sweets...

mail.line: New mail! It's not another pamphlet about how sugar is bad for your health, is it?

main1.line: You really can't take the Sakura Empire's destroyer squadrons lightly!

main2.line: If only everyone had lifetime supplies of candy, there wouldn't ever be another war!

main3.line: Commander, why don't we fire candy at the enemy instead of explosives?

mission.line: Now is not the time for candy... Ha! I'd never say that!

mission_complete.line: This will get rid of some of the shame from Kolombangara... (Munch)

profile.line: I'm Radford, DD-446, part of the Fletcher-class! Hmm... and... even though I didn't do that well in the Kula Gulf and Kolombangara, I tried my best! Anyways, the only thing that matters at the end of the day is candy!

propose.line: Does this mean I'm the sweetest candy in the world to you, Commander? ... Okay, so... I guess that means I'll be your lollipop from now on?

touch.line: (Munches)... Hmm, what's up?

touch2.line: Hmpf! If you keep this up then I won't let you come to my room and eat candy anymore!

unlock.line: I'm Radford, a Fletcher-class destroyer. Want a lollipop, Commander?

upgrade.line: Don't worry, my teeth are perfect!

win_mvp.line: The taste of victory... Hmph, it's not as sweet as candy!

detail.line: You know what'd be some really sweet magic? Being able to turn all the ammunition in this world into candy! Everyone would be too busy enjoying candy, and there'd be world peace!

drop_descrip.line: Commander, the sweet magic within my tome lets me turn things into candy! Hehe, that sounds pretty convincing— ...Eh, Commander? Wh-when'd you get here?!

home.line: Commander, want some bubblegum? I've got strawberry, orange, and grape!

login.line: Halloween is the time of year to stuff yourself silly with candy! Eh? That's wrong?

main1.line: Nicholas, stop sleeping already. If you're that sleepy, why not eat some candy for a nice sugar rush?

main2.line: This piece of candy right here will make you braver! Jenkins, step right up and test your courage!

main3.line: Commander, you're going to get pranked if you don't have enough candy to give out! Fine, looks like I'll have to give you some of mine!

touch.line: I've still got plenty of candy here, Commander. Don't be shy, just ask if you want me to give you some more!

touch2.line: Hmph! As punishment, I'm withholding half of your candy supply today!

unlock.line: Commander, the sweet magic within my tome lets me turn things into candy! Hehe, that sounds pretty convincing— ...Eh, Commander? Wh-when'd you get here?!

battle.line: Now is not the time for me to be scared... L-let's give them a beating!

detail.line: I-is there anything we can do together, Commander...?

drop_descrip.line: Fletcher-class destroyer - Jenkins, Hull Number DD-447!

expedition.line: That supply fleet... Isn't the enemy this time around, right...?

feeling1.line: U-um... Please stop staring at me...!

feeling2.line: I'm a bit of a scaredy cat... and I'm always afraid to tell people what I really think...

feeling3.line: C-Commander... I'm feeling a little troubled...

feeling4.line: How about we have some tea together after lunch... N-n-not like a date or anything like that...!

feeling5.line: C-Commander, I want to tell you something... U-um, if you hold me in your arms, then I could say it... C-could you do that for me?

home.line: Good work, Commander. Is there anything I can help you with? Huh? There isn't...?

login.line: D-do remember the secret word? ... P-phew... Then it's really you, Commander...

lose.line: *Pant*... *Pant*... T-the enemy hasn't caught up yet, have they?!

mail.line: Commander, you've got new mail. Would you like me to check it for you?

main1.line: There are actually some obvious differences between us Fletcher sisters.

main2.line: M-my heart beats so quickly... whenever I'm in front of you, Commander...

main3.line: It really is a wonder... that all of us who ended up spread across the world could reunite here...

mission.line: Commander, I-I think you still have a few unfinished missions.

mission_complete.line: Commander, I-I think you still have a few rewards you haven't collected yet.

profile.line: I-I'm Jenkins, DD-447, one of the earliest Fletcher-class ships built. Truth be told, I'm actually not good at combat at all... I barely helped out at Kula Gulf or Kolombangara... Anyways... That's my story~!

propose.line: You want to be with me forever and ever? As long as you're okay with it... then of course I'll be with you! D-do you... f-feel the same, Commander?

skill.line: I-if you don't run away now then I'll have to get serious!

touch.line: C-Commander, would you like to... um... have lunch together sometime?

touch2.line: C-Commander?! U-um, I-I-I don't believe you should be doing this...

unlock.line: Y-you're the commander?... Hello, I'm Jenkins, a Fletcher-class destroyer... U-um, could you take me back with you?

upgrade.line: If only I was a little more brave...

win_mvp.line: Whew... I was so nervous I thought my heart was going to burst... H-hooray for victory!

battle.line: I won't hand these important presents over... Hah!

detail.line: I wonder if Radford would be happy to wake up to an apple in her present box... M-Maybe I should give her some candy, after all...?

drop_descrip.line: Commander, g-good evening...? Right now, I'm bringing presents to Radford and the others...? Could you give me a hand? Th-thank you... Um, your present.. this apple, do you want it?

home.line: You're working so hard even though it's Christmas Eve... Commander... You all... Good job...!

login.line: The code word... do you remember it? I'm so glad... Commander, Merry Christmas!

main1.line: Santa would be wearing a Santa hat and a beard like I am, right?

main2.line: Nicholas is acting just the same as she would on any other day, even though it's Christmas...

main3.line: It's a shooting star! If you make a wish upon it before it disappears...! Uh, you want to know what I wished for...? I-It's a secret!

touch.line: You know... It's okay to come a b-bit closer...?

touch2.line: C--Commander... N-Not in the dark like this... Ah...

unlock.line: Commander, g-good evening...? Right now, I'm bringing presents to Radford and the others...? Could you give me a hand? Th-thank you... Um, your present.. this apple, do you want it?

battle.line: ... We came here to win... right?

detail.line: Zzzz... Oh, C-Commander? Are you gonna say that I've been slacking off too much and now I have to sortie?!

drop_descrip.line: Fletcher-class destroyer – Nicholas, Hull Number DD-449!

expedition.line: The commission team is back... I'm heading back now too...

feeling1.line: I'm never leaving my room... Never!

feeling2.line: I'm not sleepy... I just can't open my eyes.

feeling3.line: C-Commander, if you're free, then how about coming to my room and playing some games...?

feeling4.line: If I always stay in my room then I won't get to see you much, Commander... Hmm, what should I do...

feeling5.line: *Yawns*... Well, if I stay in your room, I can look at you and sleep at the same time, Commander...

home.line: W-welcome back, Commander! ... Hey, listen, can I leave already?

login.line: I'm different from you, Commander. I'd prefer to just stay here and not go anywhere else...

lose.line: I-I really should've never left the base...

mail.line: We invented email for a reason...

main1.line: Sakura Empire torpedoes... that's scary stuff...

main2.line: Commander, how about you learn from Helena and just leave me to my own devices?

main3.line: I really don't feel like training... not at all...

mission.line: It's not like we HAVE to finish our missions... right?

mission_complete.line: Commander, since we're done for now, do you think I could...

profile.line: I'm Nicholas, DD-449... Although my hull number is at the bottom of the list, I was actually the first Fletcher-class to be commissioned and launched... I mainly provided fire support, and... I contributed to the sinking of Jintsuu and the rescue of Helena, but I don't have much else noteworthy to my name... If there is nothing else you want to know, can I go back?

propose.line: *Groans*... How long is this ceremony going to last... I want to go back and sleep... Don't you agree, Commander?

touch.line: I'm not sleeping... Zzzz...

touch2.line: S-stop it...

unlock.line: I'm Nicholas, the first Fletcher-class ship to be launched... I'd rather stay at the base than head out to battle... You don't mind, right?

upgrade.line: Woooow...

win_mvp.line: Guess I'm the MVP... That's unusual.

detail.line: I need to control my sleepiness when treating people on the battlefield. *Yawn*... I'm working on it...

drop_descrip.line: I love doing relief missions as a nurse... I don't need to go outside or take part in any training, I just need to look after injured people... What about treating them? No worries, they just need to rest and they'll get better.

login.line: Medical staff are valuable and should stay in the back... Frontline duty? That stuff is Vestal's job...

mail.line: Here's your health record, Commander...

main1.line: This syringe contains Radford's sweetie candy... It won't hurt... You won't feel a thing...

main2.line: You don't feel so good, do you? Don't worry about me, just stay in bed and rest...

main3.line: Some of my patients can be pretty problematic... That's when I just dump them on Vestal...

touch.line: Do you want an "injection"...?

touch2.line: You must have suddenly gotten very sick...

unlock.line: I love doing relief missions as a nurse... I don't need to go outside or take part in any training, I just need to look after injured people... What about treating them? No worries, they just need to rest and they'll get better.

detail.line: Huh? I don't get the day off on Christmas? ... Fine, give me five more minutes... Just five more minutes... Zzzzz...

drop_descrip.line: Merry Christmas, Commander... I'm your present, probably... Would you mind closing the lid for me so I can sleep a bit more... Zzz...

feeling5.line: I didn't intend to doze off in here, but seeing your face first thing in the morning is pretty nice... Merry Christmas, Commander...

home.line: You tired, Commander? Here, borrow half my pillow...

login.line: ... *Yawn*... Good morning, Commander...

main1.line: What I want for Christmas...? Don't really care, as long as I can get enough sleep...

main2.line: Going out on an errand? Have fun... You want me to come with you? I don't wanna...

main3.line: Helena, wanna take a nap together? It's really snug inside this box...

mission_complete.line: Commander, come check which one of these boxes contains the mission rewards... I forgot which it was...

touch.line: Don't shake me, Commander... Zzzzz...

unlock.line: Merry Christmas, Commander... I'm your present, probably... Would you mind closing the lid for me so I can sleep a bit more... Zzz...

detail.line: This swimsuit is a bit tight... Speaking of which, why am I even wearing a swimsuit anyway? I don't plan on swimming... Oh well. Too late now.

drop_descrip.line: Commander, did you also come to play in the pool? ...Me? Fletcher said I have to help clean up because I was slacking off... Mm, watch your step~

feeling5.line: It's too hot to do anything in the summer... Huh? You'd like to go somewhere? ...Well, in that case, maybe I can consider it...

home.line: Commander, you're all sweaty. Want to take a shower then relax in the pool?

login.line: The beach is too far... The pool's good enough.

main1.line: There are too many of us in the Fletcher class. Fletcher even made groups to stagger when we come to the pool... Not that it matters to me. I just plop on a sofa and sleep...

main2.line: I really want to finish here so I can go back to sleep... *yawn*...

main3.line: Hmm, since I can't go back to sleep... How about this, Commander, why don't we float around like we're dead?

touch.line: My hairstyle? It's too hot, so I asked Helena to tie it up into a bun for me... What, do you like it?

unlock.line: Commander, did you also come to play in the pool? ...Me? Fletcher said I have to help clean up because I was slacking off... Mm, watch your step~

detail.line: Not only does she sell chocolate, she even wraps it up... Akashi's shop sure is convenient...

drop_descrip.line: Commander, because you kept your promise and came... here's some chocolate, and a letter for you. Please read it later. No, it's not that big of a deal... Just a little embarrassing...

home.line: Commander... stay with me a bit longer~

login.line: Just the two of us, all alone... Mm, we can talk about anything you'd like.

main1.line: Sleepy... Gonna put the desks together to make a bed...

main2.line: Commander, since you accepted my chocolate, can I expect a reward...?

main3.line: I also brought the chocolate that Helena prepared for you. Make sure to treasure it, okay?

touch.line: Commander, stop moving around... Let me get a little closer... Zzzzz...

unlock.line: Commander, because you kept your promise and came... here's some chocolate, and a letter for you. Please read it later. No, it's not that big of a deal... Just a little embarrassing...

detail.line: You can let me handle all the work you don't have to go outdoors for...

drop_descrip.line: Commander, what month is it...? I think I overslept a bit... am I taller than I was before? *Yawn*... Gotta be because I slept the whole time...

main1.line: These torpedoes... could work as a half-decent pillow replacement.

main2.line: It's not like I sleep all day EVERY day... But that's not to say I like moving around when awake...

main3.line: Nicholas has a dream... A dream of becoming a statue...

touch.line: S-s-s-still awake, okay?!

touch2.line: Y-you jerk...

unlock.line: Commander, what month is it...? I think I overslept a bit... am I taller than I was before? *Yawn*... Gotta be because I slept the whole time...

battle.line: I'll fight with all I've got!

detail.line: What is it? Do you want something from me?

drop_descrip.line: Fletcher-class destroyer – Bush, Hull Number DD-529.

expedition.line: Oh, it's time to go welcome the commission team back!

feeling1.line: You need to learn to smile, Commander...

feeling2.line: Whuah! A-a plane came flying towards me! ... What? Th-that was just a beetle...?

feeling3.line: You know, I'm actually quite athletic! Check it out, I could hop side to side all day! ... *Pant*, *pant*... This is exhausting... I can't hop anymore...

feeling4.line: Gotcha! ... Well, how do you like the prank Thatcher taught me, Commander? ... Huh? But I thought you liked pranks, or at least Thatcher said that you do...

feeling5.line: For whatever reason, I don't feel that scared of planes anymore. It's got to be because we love each other, Commander! ... At least that's what Thatcher told me. She's not wrong, is she?

home.line: Whoa! Everyone's back home!

hp_warning.line: I-I'm not giving up yet!

login.line: Umm... What are we doing today, again?

lose.line: Nooo! Get those planes away from meee!

mail.line: I've brought your mail along! What does it say?

main1.line: If I stay out of sight, the Commander probably won't notice I'm neglecting my work...

main2.line: Uughh... Following a schedule is so boooring! I say we do stuff when we see it needs doing! ... What? That's not gonna fly?

main3.line: I've got a bunch of sisters, both younger and older than me! I forget their names all the time, though...

mission.line: You've got some missions left to do. Commander, you're not... slacking off again, are you?

mission_complete.line: Mission complete! ... Did I do it right?

profile.line: I'm the Fletcher-class destroyer Bush. Like my sisters, I fought in the Pacific Ocean and took on tons of missions! ... Planes? I-I don't wanna talk about those scary things!

propose.line: Does this mean you love me more than anyone else? If so, will you do anything I ask you to? Okay! I want some snacks from that store that just opened, so let's go there right now!

touch.line: Yep, what is it?

touch2.line: It's not okay to touch me like that!

unlock.line: I'm Bush, from the Fletcher class! I'll be staying here from now on!

upgrade.line: Huh? Will this make me stronger?

win_mvp.line: Hehehe! That was super easy!

detail.line: North Carolina asked me to paint a portrait of Washington smiling, but Washington didn't really wanna do it... I think I know why! Maybe smiling is embarrassing for her?

drop_descrip.line: Tadaaah! All done! How does it look? I think I'm pretty talented as an artist!

home.line: *gasp*! You spooked me... You almost made my hand slip and mess up my painting!

login.line: Aww, do we really have to work? I'm not done painting yet...

main1.line: Just give me a minute! I'm just finishing up my painting!

main2.line: This is my sketchbook I use for drawing practice! And no looking inside, okay?

main3.line: I'm gonna draw portraits of everyone at the port! Heehee!

touch.line: Hm? Do you want me to paint something for you, Commander?

touch2.line: Oh no! I got paint on my clothes because of that!

unlock.line: Tadaaah! All done! How does it look? I think I'm pretty talented as an artist!

battle.line: All righty! Let's set sail, everyone!

detail.line: Phew! That feels great! The warm sunshine feels amazing today!

drop_descrip.line: Fletcher-class destroyer – Hazelwood, Hull Number DD-531.

expedition.line: A commission has finished? I'll be right back!

feeling1.line: Everyone's saying to stay away from the commander... I wonder why?

feeling2.line: There are lots of girls here who like to run fast. That's why I'd like to race them!

feeling3.line: There's nothing more relaxing than soaking in the sunlight! Commander, you come with me too~!

feeling4.line: The sun isn't coming out today... But no matter, hehe! As long as I stick with you, I won't get mopey at all~!

feeling5.line: I see you, Commander! Heheh~♪ Are you gonna get in trouble if I cling to you too much? But it feels so good... so can I keep doing it a bit more? Yaay~!

home.line: Are you tired? Should I help you get comfortable?

hp_warning.line: I... I'm not scared!

login.line: Right on time~! I just finished warming up~ Let's get going!

lose.line: I can't hold out any longer!

mail.line: Whaddya think? Nobody gets the mail faster than me, right!

main1.line: These sunburns are battle scars from my active lifestyle!

main2.line: Hey Bush, stop loafing around and come jog with me!

main3.line: If only we could host a port-wide sports meet... I know I'd be the fastest one out of all my sisters!

mission.line: Don't back down, no matter how intimidating your pile of work looks!

mission_complete.line: Woo! That's one more checked off the list! Way to go, Commander!

profile.line: I have a lot of experience on the battlefield, so I guess I'm a bit of a veteran! Oh right, I also served as a "reserve aviation command ship" for a while! What's that, you ask? Well, that'd be a ship that helps carriers guide their planes! Something like that~

propose.line: From now on, I'll cling to you even more, Commander! ...Hehe, Commander, you're nice and warm... rub against me more~

touch.line: How about it? I've got a super healthy tan, right? Commander, show me ours~

touch2.line: Eek! Don't go peeking under there!

unlock.line: Gotcha! Hehe, I'm Hazelwood, from the Fletcher class! Pleased to meet you!

upgrade.line: Faster, stronger!

win_mvp.line: I'm number one? Now that's what I call unexpected, ehehe...

battle.line: You suckers think you can defeat me? That's funny!

detail.line: Hah hah hah! Is it my time to sortie?

drop_descrip.line: Fletcher-class destroyer – Bache, Hull Number DD-470.

expedition.line: Commander, someone's back! Remember how it's part of the job to greet the commission team? Yeah, don't forget it!

feeling1.line: I'm the only one on the planet who'd look after someone as sorry as you~ Poor little thing~
