feeling2.line: Hm? Hurt my leg? Nope! The bandaid is just for decoration~! Nothin' for you to worry your little mind about! Heheh☆

feeling3.line: Hoho? You digging my jacket, Commander? Y'know, your style might just improve if you wear something like it! Hahahahah!

feeling4.line: Your style is so last century, Commander! Take a seat and I'll give you a fashion crash course!

feeling5.line: Y'know, your fashion sense has really improved; you don't look so lame anymore! Keep it up and I might fall for you~ Pfft, yeah right☆

headtouch.line: You might be weaksauce, but you're really good at patting heads!

home.line: You look awfully mopey, Commander. I can't stand it! Take a sip of my special honey-infused energy drink! Don't argue, just do it!

hp_warning.line: Not bad! But I'm badder and stronger than you! Hahaha!

login.line: Drink this energizing coffee! We can't have you run outta gas, can we!

lose.line: I'll be back to smack the crap outta you dolts, just you waaaaaait!

mail.line: Heh heh! You've got mail! Since you're such a busy bee and I'm so considerate, I'll read it out for ya!

main1.line: It's windy as all hell today... and when it gets too windy, bad things happen. You get me, Commander?

main2.line: This outfit is what's in vogue! Do you seriously not know fashion when you see it?

main3.line: If the other Fletchers were as flashy as me then maybe I could actually remember their names!

mission.line: If you can't finish your missions then magnanimous me's gonna have to step up to the plate!

mission_complete.line: I really have to babysit you, don't I? Don't forget about collecting the mission rewards!

profile.line: Ahah! I'm the numero uno coolest Fletcher-class destroyer, Bache! My fire support in the Surigao Strait was no big deal! Also, no other destroyer has experienced the glory of resting beside the Colossus of Rhodes as much as I have! Hahahahah!

propose.line: Guess I'll always need to babysit you, no matter how stylish you get~ But that's okay! I'll look after you till the end of time! Hehehe, hope you're ready for me!

touch.line: Don't come begging for my help later if you're this easily distracted and can't finish your work!

touch2.line: You really like my getup, don'tcha, Commander? You absolute degenerate~

unlock.line: Yoohoo~! You the Commander? You look kinda weaksauce, though~! Name's Bache! I'm joining this fleet, starting today! I'll take good care of you, so just kick back and get ready for my greatness!

upgrade.line: Suh-weet! Let's try out my new powers!

win_mvp.line: So weeeak! What a buncha losers! Hahahaha!

detail.line: When it comes to bikes... I don't know squat! So I just got my Royal Navy pal to help out! I've gotta thank her later!

drop_descrip.line: Ahaha~! Are you seeing this, Commander? This sturdiness, this gorgeous paint job, and these special accessories hand-picked by yours truly! Muahaha! I am the true speed-star of this port!

home.line: Speed-star, engine at full throttle! Let's roll! ... Teehee~ I came up with that sweet catchphrase long ago!

login.line: Hmm? Hmmmmmm? Man, you look miserable, Commander! Sit here and I'll take you on a wild ride! Ahahahaha!

main1.line: Still looking brand new? Well yeah, thanks to my daily pro-level maintenance!

main2.line: You wanna ride my bike? Of course you... can't! Think what'd happen if you crash it!

main3.line: If there's somewhere you wanna go, if you ask me really nicely with a cherry on top, I just might let you hop on~

touch.line: Aha! You're digging my bike and style, aren't you, Commander? Aren't you jelly? Since I'm so nice, I'll let you stare until you're satisfied!

touch2.line: Seizing the chance to feel me up, huh~? You dirty perv~

unlock.line: Ahaha~! Are you seeing this, Commander? This sturdiness, this gorgeous paint job, and these special accessories hand-picked by yours truly! Muahaha! I am the true speed-star of this port!

detail.line: I've gotta come up with a sweet victory pose... It doesn't concern weaksauce like you, but you can brainstorm with me if you want!

drop_descrip.line: Tada! Your favorite tennis superstar, Bache, is right here! ...Hey Commander, you're supposed to cheer for me like you're one of my fans in the stands!

home.line: I'm practicing my serves right now! Be a nice weaksauce Commander and fetch my ball!

login.line: Commander, come here and help me practice! If I win the championship, you'll get a special reward♪

main1.line: They said I'm a wild card... Does that mean I'm super talented?!

main2.line: Hey! Wait a sec! You're throwing too fast for me to return the ball...!

main3.line: You tired, Commander? Guess what, I anticipated that you would be~! Heheh, have a taste of my deluxe honey drink! This stuff will get you back in the game, no matter how drained you are!

touch.line: Has my tennis outfit got you crazy for me~?

touch2.line: No weaksauce commander in the world can touch me now~! Whuah?!

unlock.line: Tada! Your favorite tennis superstar, Bache, is right here! ...Hey Commander, you're supposed to cheer for me like you're one of my fans in the stands!

battle.line: The one and only Hobby will be the flagship of course.

detail.line: Hobby is ready with her POSE! Commander, did you take a good photo?

drop_descrip.line: Benson class Destroyer— Hobby, hull number DD-610.

expedition.line: The commission has been completed, Commander, won’t you go check it out?

feeling1.line: Commander is stupid, Commander is stupid! (makes face, wiggles tongue)

feeling2.line: Commander, if you want my help then just say so~

feeling3.line: Commander, as a child star,the sense of lens is very important. I am also very cute today,right?

feeling4.line: Hobby and the Commander are happiest together~ hehe. Wearing this headband makes me have huge rabbit ears? Hobby, wants to be a cute little bunny for the Commander!

feeling5.line: Commander, can you give me a piggyback, just for today, please. You agreed! Don’t turn back on a promise! Haha, yeeha~

headtouch.line: Hehe, feels good? Well, you can pet me for a while longer.

home.line: Finally, the battle is over. Come play with Hobby for a while~

hp_warning.line: Impossible, Hobby will not forgive you!

login.line: Welcome back Commander! Did you come back because you missed Hobby?

lose.line: This is just a little setback that’s all...

mail.line: Mail is here...come take a look!

main1.line: It’s no big deal that Destroyers can be normal, Hobby, lives a happy lifestyle~

main2.line: Whether it’s her name or characteristics, Hobby is truly unique~

main3.line: Commander, if you don’t have a camera with you, just use your hand to mimic a frame for cute little Hobby.

mission.line: There are still many tasks to complete? Hobby can also help you, Commander.

mission_complete.line: Hmm? Mission complete...great job everyone...

profile.line: Eagle Union Destroyer DD610, Hobby has arrived! Usually, Hobby is too busy to have an outstanding battle record. Also, Hobby used to be a child star who also starred in movies~ Surprised?

propose.line: Oh, finally you’ve arrived Commander~ Hobby just can’t wait anymore! Next, we’ll take lots of pictures of cute little Hobby, and you’ll always be Hobby’s dashing prince charming! Promises promises~

skill.line: The one and only Hobby, full of enthusiasm~

touch.line: Do you need my help? Just say so, maybe Hobby will even become the Commander’s savior~

touch2.line: Commander, you’re really bold… then let us skip ABCD and go directly to EFG tonight… haha, blushes, just kidding! (Wiggles tongue).

unlock.line: The one and only Hobby has arrived! Commander, Commander! Are you ready to be impressed by my charm? Hehe~

upgrade.line: Hehe, I seem to be getting stronger~ Thank you, Commander!

win_mvp.line: Hehe, Hobby is the best~

battle.line: Even though there’s still tons of stuff to learn, but Hobby is not afraid of it~

detail.line: Are you taking a closer look at all of Hobby’s changes? Hey! Commander, ready your camera, take as many pics as you like!

drop_descrip.line: Here comes the debut of school uniform Hobby~ Commander, how do I look? Hobby is all grown up~

feeling5.line: Oh? Commander is completely mesmerized by Hobby’s cute charm? Haha~ Hobby is ready! Does the Commander want to touch Hobby's head or give her a hug?

home.line: Welcome back Commander! Hobby just finished class today, do you want to go take a stroll together?

login.line: Commander, HELLO! Accompany Hobby to class today~ Relax, we still got plenty of time for the road~

main1.line: My backpack has a little Kalk puppet? Yes~ She is my close friend. Even though she likes to play pranks, but you should get along with her Commander~

main2.line: If Hobby becomes the “mind” of the fleet, then will Commander like her more?

main3.line: Commander, Commander~ Let’s go together. Is Hobby as cute as ever today?

touch.line: Hobby is the best at sharing the workload of the Commander, on call at anytime~

touch2.line: Commander, if it goes on like this, then Mr. torpedo will not let you go—— haha, don’t be afraid Commander, I’m just kidding~

unlock.line: Here comes the debut of school uniform Hobby~ Commander, how do I look? Hobby is all grown up~

battle.line: The battle has started, I have to behave myself~

detail.line: You need to give me good equipments~ This way, those mean aircrafts won’t hurt me anymore.

drop_descrip.line: Benson class Destroyer— Kalk, hull number DD-611.

expedition.line: Commander, come get the spoils of war~

feeling1.line: Commander, don’t you like the ice cream I made with hot sauce... such a meanie.

feeling2.line: I’ve been to many places, seen a lot, do you want to listen to my tales, Commander?

feeling3.line: Come come~ There’s a rabbit hidden in my sleeves. Commander, do you want to see a magic trick? Wow... how did Mr. Rabbit suddenly slip away?

feeling4.line: Commander Commander, seeing you this happy has also made me very happy!

feeling5.line: I want to stay longer at port, Commander don’t leave me, ok? ...（flick sleeves）.

home.line: Commander, even if a typhoon is blowing our way, I will still accompany you all the way to safety!

hp_warning.line: It doesn’t matter, I am very lucky. We should... should be able to survive!

login.line: Commander Commander, while you were away I secretly drizzled hot sauce on everyone’s food. But how come only my food is especially spicy... oh no... don’t knock me on the head...

lose.line: Sigh... I hate it when I get injured, so annoying...

mail.line: Hurry up and check your mail!

main1.line: Compared to running errands, it’s definitely better to stick together with Commander.

main2.line: Hehe, I am full of luck as long as the Commander holds my hand~

main3.line: Commander, do you want me to put insects in your bed?

mission.line: Commander, here comes another mission!

mission_complete.line: The mission has been successfully completed, Commander you’ve worked hard out there.

profile.line: I am Benson class Destroyer, Kalk, hull number DD611. I run many errands for the Eagle Union, and I’ve been to many places as such. Although, I don’t really like all this running around… (whispers)

propose.line: Commander, reach your hands into my sleeves… hurry hurry, grab my hands, hold them. This will bring us luck. Hehe, I will always be happy with you in the days to come!

skill.line: Let’s charge ahead against the roaring wind——

touch.line: Huh? Are you praising me for switching everyone’s breakfast into homemade Italian spicy-sauce noodles~ Thank you Commander!

touch2.line: ...Does this make you happy, Commander? (Tilts head)

unlock.line: Kalk, reporting in (flick sleeves) Commander, will you give me a high-five. As long as we high-five, we’re friends.

upgrade.line: My body is heating up, I’m getting stronger! (flick sleeves) I feel so agile now~

win_mvp.line: Kalk is very lucky today!

detail.line: Cute little bunny~ Hehe, Commander, I like to hang out with cute little animals.

drop_descrip.line: Kalk, reporting in once again, now with a new outfit! Hehe... Commander, will you walk me to school?

feeling5.line: Commander, you've worked so hard out there, so let's get you a fresh change of clothes. Let me massage your shoulders and make some warm cider for you~ (Shakes head) No, there's no hot sauce this time. Just lots and lots of sugar, hehe~

home.line: Commander, take a break. I already made a snowman. Now, let's have a snowball fight~

login.line: Commander, I've been waiting for you! Uuu.... just look, I've been standing here for so long that my cannon and torpedoes have turned into ice pops~

main1.line: It's snowing pretty hard outside. Commander, want a nice warm cup of cider before you head out?

main2.line: Hobby is so cute, isn't she? I'd love to be as outgoing as her.

main3.line: It's really cold outside, Commander, so you should take care to stay warm. Here, I poured your cider into hot sauce so it will keep you warm better~

touch.line: Want to come with me? Mhm, let's head to school together then!

touch2.line: Commander? So you're also a prankster...

unlock.line: Kalk, reporting in once again, now with a new outfit! Hehe... Commander, will you walk me to school?

win_mvp.line: MVP? Hehe, thanks for everyone’s support.

battle.line: Prepare to meet the enemies.

detail.line: Just what are you looking at? You ought to hurry up and return to your post.

drop_descrip.line: Fletcher-class Destroyer - Kimberly (DD-521)

expedition.line: Commander, a commission has finished.

feeling1.line: The incompetent will be weeded out by time. You are no exception.

feeling2.line: As long as we keep on winning, will we be able to bring an end to the war? Rather than searching for the answer to that question, it would be more practical to focus on winning the battles ahead of us.

feeling3.line: "What do I plan to do after the war is over?" Hmm... I've never given this much thought, nor have I wanted to. However, why did you bring it up all of a sudden?

feeling4.line: Recently, I had a strange dream. I dreamt that I wasn't on the battlefield, but instead taking a walk along the port, hand-in-hand with someone close to me... Wh-what's so funny?

feeling5.line: After discussing things with my sisters a bit, I realized that if the war actually ended, I wouldn't know how to do anything else... Eh, you'd stay with me and teach me yourself... so there would be no problem? E-ehhh?

headtouch.line: What is... the meaning of this?

home.line: I see you've returned at the scheduled time, Commander. However, you can't afford to take it easy just yet.

hp_warning.line: Damage confirmed, continuing combat.

login.line: Being punctual is a good habit to have, so please keep it up.

lose.line: Strategic retreat...

mail.line: Commander, there's mail for you.

main1.line: If you are tired, please take a break. If you were to collapse, the command chain would follow suit.

main2.line: For me, no matter where I am, or what I am called, I will continue to fight on as long as I live.

main3.line: I was born for battle and died for peace. Other than this fact, I won't dwell on anything else.

mission.line: As a commander, it is only fitting that you complete these tasks.

mission_complete.line: Mission complete. However, your work doesn't end there.

profile.line: I am the Fletcher-class destroyer Kimberly. I am normally tasked with escort and anti-submarine duties, so should the need arise, please do not hesitate to deploy me.

propose.line: S-so this is a promise ring... Really, I never could have imagined that this would happen to me... However, I'm truly, truly happy, from the bottom of my heart. Is this... the "love" that my sisters were talking about? Hey... don't laugh!

skill.line: Let's put this needless battle to an end!

touch.line: What tasks are there?

touch2.line: Do you want to pay a visit to the court martial?

unlock.line: I am the Fletcher-class destroyer, Kimberly. From today onward, I will be one of your subordinates. Pleased to meet you.

upgrade.line: Strengthening combat effectiveness is also an important link when it comes to battle.

win_mvp.line: This is a fine example of tactical synergy. Let's keep it up.

detail.line: There are many differences between the Eagle Union and the Dragon Empery, but the one thing that doesn't change no matter where you are is everyone's desire for a better future.

drop_descrip.line: While wearing clothes from the Dragon Empery, I can't help but reminisce about those days... Hehe, Commander, do you prefer me in Empery-style clothes, or Union-style clothes?

feeling5.line: When I'm with you, I feel energized and my productivity goes through the roof. Perhaps... this is your magic spell? Hehe~

headtouch.line: C-Commander, the buns are going to get messed up...

home.line: Every time I return to port, I feel a wave of relief wash over me. Is this what "home" is?

login.line: There is a proverb from the Dragon Empery: "A day's plans begin in the morning." Even if it's not the morning though, don't you think it's important to start off on the right foot, Commander?

main1.line: My friends from the Dragon Empery told me about a lot of fascinating legends! Commander, do you want to hear them too?

main2.line: Recently, I tried to learn the bamboo flute. Commander, want to give it a listen?

main3.line: Ugh... calligraphy is really difficult...

mission.line: If you put things off for tomorrow, you'll find that there's always another tomorrow. That's why you shouldn't put off today's missions for tomorrow.

mission_complete.line: Mission complete. Commander, want to take a break?

touch.line: There's still a lot of work left to do... but don't worry, Commander! Let's knock it out together!

touch2.line: Commander... you could go to jail for this, you know?

unlock.line: When I change into clothes from the Dragon Empery, I can't help but to reminisce about the time I spent there... Commander, which style of clothes do you prefer - Union, or Empery?

battle.line: I have to work hard for Commander today as well~

detail.line: Commander, please let me know if there's anything you need me for.

drop_descrip.line: Fletcher-class Destroyer - Mullany (DD-528)

expedition.line: Commander, a commission has been finished!

feeling1.line: Cooking for someone you don't like is suffering...

feeling2.line: Commander, what are your interests? My hobby is cooking - though sometimes weird stuff come out, it usually tastes pretty good anyway. Mhm!

feeling3.line: My cooking would be perfect if I stopped trying to study weird things? Well, that's a darn shame! If you ask me, the element of surprise is the most important spice!

feeling4.line: Commander, are you keeping up with your schedule? If you feel like you can't manage everything alone, please let me handle your domestic affairs~

feeling5.line: You feel bad for always imposing on me? It's fine, it's fine! I'm happiest when I can be of use to the one I care about~ so feel free to rely on me even more from now on!

headtouch.line: Being treated like a kid... feels a bit weird... ahaha...

home.line: Commander, good work~ Would you like to have a meal? I kept your food warm.

hp_warning.line: Oh no...

login.line: Commander, have you eaten? Should I prepare something for you?

lose.line: Commander, I'm sorry...

mail.line: Commander, there's mail for you. Don't forget to read it!

main1.line: Aww... I thought I followed the recipe perfectly, so how did it turn out like this...?

main2.line: Commander, make sure to strike the right balance between work and leisure! It's not good to be lazy or overworked~

main3.line: Commander, do your best! Believe in yourself, you're the greatest!

mission.line: Work hard to finish your missions, Commander~

mission_complete.line: Mission rewards, huh... Should I also prepare something for you, Commander?

profile.line: The Fletcher-class is pretty big, so it's not strange that you haven't heard of me. Though I had my fair share of dangerous moments, I managed to return peacefully. Right after that, I even went to live the Dragon Empery for a while! Is that why you think I look a bit bigger? Who knows~

propose.line: Commander, would you like me to keep cooking for you every day, even after a long, long time? Hm, you'd like there to be fewer weird dishes? Hehe, I guess I can manage that~

touch.line: Uhh... the black smoke coming from that side of the kitchen? Ahaha... ha... I have no idea what you're talking about~

touch2.line: C-Commander... so you're also interested in the racy stuff...

unlock.line: Hello Commander, I am the Fletcher-class destroyer, Mullany. From today onwards, we'll be spending a lot of time together. Please take good care of me!

upgrade.line: Ah! An inspiration for my new recipe!

win_mvp.line: I'm number one? Um... as long as I can be of help to you, I'll be happy...

detail.line: After studying abroad in the Dragon Empery and being exposed to their history and culture, I've learned to be a bit calmer. However, I'm still the same person as before... as you can probably tell from my cooking...

drop_descrip.line: What's with the weird look, Commander? Ah, I got this outfit while studying abroad in the Dragon Empery. Umm... does it suit me?

feeling5.line: Cooking for someone else... is a whole different experience. Cooking for you? Hm, I'd say that's a bit of a heart-racing sensation, hehe~

headtouch.line: Commander, are you... interested in my new hairstyle?

login.line: Would you like to have some soup dumplings?

main1.line: nil

main2.line: nil

main3.line: nil

mission.line: Today's business is best done today, Commander.

touch.line: The elegance of ladies from the Empery, walking with their parasols opened, is a sight to behold. So, I picked up a few things from them - want to see?

touch2.line: C-Commander, some self-restraint, please...

unlock.line: What's with the weird look, Commander? Ah, I got this outfit while studying abroad in the Dragon Empery. Umm... does it suit me?

win_mvp.line: The things I learned in the Dragon Empery came in handy.

battle.line: Everyone, let's give it our all!

detail.line: Commander, who do you like more - Lexington, or Saratoga? Or... perhaps some other girl has caught your eye?

drop_descrip.line: Farragut-class destroyer – Aylwin, Hull Number DD-355.

expedition.line: The military commission has been completed. Commander, why don't we head down together to welcome everyone back?

feeling1.line: Commander, listen up. If this continues on, I'll be keeping my distance from you...

feeling2.line: Commander, you're not too busy right now, are you? Umm, I'd like to... here, I have a little bit of candy for you~♪ Some sugar is good for the brain!

feeling3.line: Compared to Dewey, I'm only a tiny bit more... H-huh? I'm not chubby! Jeez, Commander, I'm not talking to you anymore!

feeling4.line: Commander, you're the type who likes it when there's a bit more to love, right? ... I'll drink plenty of milk and eat lots of candy every day so that I can be your ideal type~

feeling5.line: Commander, what's different about me today? Have you noticed yet? ...You still haven't noticed it? Hurry, hurry, hurry up and notice it, okay?

home.line: Commander, you're finally back~! Did you bring back some some delicious treats for us? Thank you so much! I'll be helping myself~♪

hp_warning.line: I'm... I'm still okay... probably...

login.line: Commander, welcome back. It's the start of a bright new day!

lose.line: Oops, guess I lost... Commander, can you give me some candy to cheer me up...?

mail.line: Hm? There seems to be some new mail... Hrmm... Ah! Now, this seems like some good news!

main1.line: I had a dream that I would one day share the stage with Lexington. If I could sing and dance just like her, which one of us would you support?

main2.line: *pouts* Another training exercise? You keep saying next time... I want to sortie and go on real missions with everyone else!

main3.line: Dewey really looks after me. Maybe she's also one of Lexington's fans, hehe~!

mission.line: New missions have been posted~ Let's hurry up and set sail! Just kidding, we still have plenty of time right now.

mission_complete.line: Mission complete! It's a pretty good haul isn't it, Commander~

profile.line: I am Aylwin, from the Eagle Union. During the war, I carried out many operations as well as training exercises, and had some ties with both the Royal Navy and Iris Libre. I admire elegant, mature women like Lexington. Commander, I look forward to working with you!

propose.line: Commander, I don't mind if you have a thing for Lexington. But you have to swear that you absolutely love me, okay? I try my best every single day to be your ideal girl, so don't take your eyes off me, okay?

skill.line: Looks like it's time for Aylwin to get serious!

touch.line: Commander, do you need something~?

touch2.line: Jeez, Commander... That's a foul, you know?

unlock.line: Greetings, my name is Aylwin. I'm actually quite talented at nautical navigation, so please allow me to be your guide.

upgrade.line: Hmm... I don't particularly feel any different. Whatever, a gain is a gain~

win_mvp.line: Yay, I'm the MVP! Surely a wonderful commander like you would have something nice for me, right~

battle.line: What I saw just now could prove useful for anti-submarine operations...

detail.line: I'm feeling a little peckish... Umm, cookies, candy, and... Ah, I musn't... I have to leave enough for Commander...

drop_descrip.line: So this is an aquarium... What a novel experience! Oh, also, I won't be your guide today as it's your turn to escort me around, Commander. Please don't get us lost, okay? Ehehe~

login.line: How do you do, Commander? How's that? I learned how to curtsy from the Royal Navy maids~

main1.line: Even though I spent a lot of time training with the submarines, it's a totally different experience to enjoy the sight underwater.

main2.line: This outfit was chosen painstakingly, you know? Commander, what do you think...?

main3.line: Want to go see Lexington's performance together next time? I'll even get your ticket for you if you'd like.

touch2.line: Commander, did you get some perverted ideas...?

unlock.line: So this is an aquarium... What a novel experience! Oh, also, I won't be your guide today as it's your turn to escort me around, Commander. Please don't get us lost, okay? Ehehe~

win_mvp.line: A most graceful and elegant victory. Ehehe, thank you for your praise~

battle.line: Combat mode, activate! Set sail!

detail.line: What are you staring at? I'm not going to transform...

drop_descrip.line: Fletcher-class destroyer - Stanly , Hull Number DD-478.

expedition.line: Next time you're sending a commission, let Stanly handle the escort duty!

feeling1.line: Stanly is now operating in disappointment mode! Hmph!

feeling2.line: Stanly's in happy mode today – I can take on any task with a spring in my step!

feeling3.line: The other members of the Little Beaver Squad are fun to hang out with, but I still have the best time when I'm with you, Commander!

feeling4.line: As long as I'm with you, my happiness gauge will continue to fill up! So, Commander, please stay and play with me for a while.

feeling5.line: Warning, Stanly has entered the "will self-destruct if not within a 3-meter radius of Commander" mode... I-I'm serious! So, I'm going to make sure I'm never separated from you, heehee~

home.line: Yo... When'd you get back, Commander? Stanly's rest mode still needs a while to run its course.

hp_warning.line: C-convert to defense mode!

login.line: Stanly has entered work mode! By the way, it doesn't last very long.

lose.line: Crap, gotta switch to retreat mode pronto!

mail.line: There's a news update! Don't say I didn't tell you!

main1.line: Commander, join me in becoming a hero of justice... Bahaha! Just kidding!

main2.line: Commander, are you still in work mode? Jeez, don't keep me waiting much longer...

main3.line: Commander, your hair sure is funny! Let's give it a good twirl~!

mission.line: I wish I had some mode that would let me skip the daily grind...

mission_complete.line: Whoa! The rewards are here! Commander, let's go take a look!

profile.line: In the past, I've escorted many of my allies, and served in the Battle of Empress Augusta Bay as a member of the Little Beaver Squadron. As long as I'm in my serious mode, I'm really reliable in both day and night battles.

propose.line: Commander, your hand, please... Good, connection complete! From now on, we will be able to communicate telepathically! Heehee, do you feel how happy I am?

touch.line: Self-defense mode activating... Bahaha, you should've seen your face!

touch2.line: Sorry to disappoint, but I don't have a hot and bothered mode.

unlock.line: Good morning, Commander. I'm Stanly, a destroyer from the Eagle Union. I will follow your every order to bring you victory... Pffft! Bahaha! S-Sorry, this whole "serious introduction" thing totally cramps my style, haha!

upgrade.line: Strengthening complete! I'm gonna reward myself to a little rest and relaxation!

win_mvp.line: Heheh! MVP belongs to me!

battle.line: Let's get warmed up!

detail.line: Baltimore...? Oh, Commander... I didn't notice you because I was training.

drop_descrip.line: Fletcher-class destroyer – Smalley , Hull Number DD-565.

expedition.line: The commission fleet has returned. Commander, want to race me to the piers?

feeling1.line: Do whatever you want. I'm going back to training. See you.

feeling2.line: Commander, how about getting some exercise?

feeling3.line: Commander, want to go buy some workout equipment on our next day off? Using it properly will get you better results!

feeling4.line: Commander, I see you also appreciate the feeling of making gains. Mhm, we really do understand each other.

feeling5.line: It'd be fun to have someone who looks out after you and helps you out... Commander, let's get stronger together!

home.line: Here's a towel. Use it to wipe off your sweat.

hp_warning.line: Should've worked out harder...

login.line: Commander, can I train in your office?

lose.line: Well, that's awkward...

mail.line: New mail? I'll get it for you. Give me 10, no, 8 seconds.

main1.line: Commander, I'll show you some exercises. You can even do these while sitting down. Not moving around is bad for your health.

main2.line: There are very few restrictions to what you can do in kickboxing. However, it's not very useful in naval combat... so that's why it's just a hobby.

main3.line: I want to spar with the battleships. They all seem strong.

mission.line: Using missions to test your worth? I like that idea.

mission_complete.line: The feeling of testing my abilities is far better than any reward.

profile.line: Fletcher-class destroyer, Smalley. I did radar pickets, patrols, rescues, diplomatic functions, and basically a bit of everything. My hobbies...? Do I really have to repeat what I said before?

propose.line: Don't worry, Commander. We've worked hard together all this time, so I can guess what you're thinking. I understand your feelings... but I'm not sure how I should respond... Um, of course! If you're fine with me, I'd love to!

touch.line: Commander, want me to show you the ropes? It's good for self-defense.

touch2.line: Eat my... roundhouse kick!

unlock.line: Destroyer Smalley, reporting in. Interests: kickboxing.

upgrade.line: Thank you. My body feels lighter.

win_mvp.line: Hmm, not bad.

detail.line: I can help everyone out and get some training in at the same time. This is the kind of work that I like.

drop_descrip.line: I am the courier of the night. In other words, it's my job to bring stuff straight to you, Commander. Here you go, this jack-o-lantern is for you.

home.line: Candy? Forget it, eating too much of that junk will just erase all your gains... Fine, just one...

login.line: Let's use this jack-o-lantern to decorate your office. I'm putting it right here.

main1.line: Rumors of wasabi-flavored candy? Never heard of it. I'm just the delivery witch.

main2.line: Ghosts and monsters? If they exist, line 'em up and I'll knock 'em down.

main3.line: My broom? Who needs to fly when you can just run faster.

touch.line: Is there anything you'd like me to deliver?

touch2.line: ...! Witch uppercut!

unlock.line: I am the courier of the night. In other words, it's my job to bring stuff straight to you, Commander. Here you go, this jack-o-lantern is for you.

battle.line: I, Halsey Powell, shall lead this fleet to victory!

detail.line: Ehehe~ See, Commander, you're totally into me after all, aren't you~?

drop_descrip.line: Fletcher-class destroyer – Halsey Powell, Hull Number DD-686.

expedition.line: The commission fleet is returning? I'll go greet them! ...That's right, the more you put yourself out there, the quicker you can make a name for yourself!

feeling1.line: Just you wait! When I become the most famous person at the port...!

feeling2.line: All right! I'm going to put my best foot forward for everyone to see!

feeling3.line: It might be hard to stand out from the rest of the Fletchers, but... Commander, I know you'll be able to come up with something!

feeling4.line: It's going to be hard to capture everyone's attention here, but... but... Yeah, I'll start by making sure I have your undivided attention!

feeling5.line: I like it when you shower me with attention, Commander~ Ehehe... However! At this rate, I'm going to end up as some simple-minded girl who can throw away her dreams as long as she gets to cling to you! ...Though that doesn't sound half bad... But, forget it! Ehehe!

home.line: Gah! Commander, I bet you took advantage of the fact that I wouldn't be around to go somewhere fun!

hp_warning.line: Am I really in a pinch...?

login.line: Staaaaaare... Commander doesn't look any different today!

lose.line: Awww... P-please don't look at meeee...

mail.line: Don't you forget, I'm the one who brought you the mail!

main1.line: Bad little submarines, come out, come out, wherever you are~

main2.line: I'm a bit jealous of the Little Beavers... If only I had the same legendary feats as them...

main3.line: Jeez, Commander, you have such a cute and capable Destroyer right next to you, but you're so absorbed in your work!

mission.line: Commander, it seems like you'll need a capable assistant after all... Ehehe, you need my talents, don't you~!

mission_complete.line: Don't forget that I helped you with that mission! Ehehe, vanilla ice cream is waiting for me~!

profile.line: There are a lot of us Fletchers, but nobody's done a better job of supporting than Halsey Powell! Whether it's anti-air or anti-sub, nobody out there can match me!

propose.line: With this ring, I'm totally going to capture everyone's attention! Hehe... my dreams are finally coming true... Huh? Commander, you want me to only capture your attention? Why's that?

touch.line: Commander, are you in a pickle? Do you need my help? Hehe, I'd be glad to give you a hand, but the cute little Halsey Powell won't work for free... Hmm, if you treat me to lots of tasty snacks, we have a deal!

touch2.line: Y-You can't do that...!

unlock.line: There you are, Commander! Ehehe~ Huh? You've never heard of me? Jeez, I'm Halsey Powell! Don't you forget it!

upgrade.line: I have to get stronger, and shine even brighter!

win_mvp.line: Mhmhm! Do bask in the heroic visage of your MVP, Halsey Powell!

detail.line: The Dragon Empery's lucky star is an old geezer? I see... W-wait! I don't want to be the lucky star anymore!

drop_descrip.line: Halsey Powell is making her debut as your lucky star for the Spring Festival! Commander, if you show me a fun time, you'll be blessed with good luck this year!

home.line: I've finished hanging up all the paper lanterns around the port! Hehe, now when everyone sees them, they'll praise the hardworking maiden who put them up - that's right, me!

login.line: Commander, Happy Spring Festival! Um, hey, where's my red envelope?

main1.line: I want to eat something sweet and fluffy...

main2.line: The Zodiac is really neat! But... why is there a dog and a rat on there but no cat?

main3.line: Commander, why don't we make a huge paper lantern? One that stands out from the rest!

touch.line: If you're ever in trouble, just leave it to your lucky star, Halsey Powell!

touch2.line: Commander, bad luck unto you!

unlock.line: Halsey Powell is making her debut as your lucky star for the Spring Festival! Commander, if you show me a fun time, you'll be blessed with good luck this year!

battle.line: Cast off! Let's go!

detail.line: I have an incredible power inside me that will burst forth to save everyone at that critical moment... Yeah! That would be badass!

drop_descrip.line: Allen M. Sumner-class destroyer – Cooper, Hull Number DD-695.

expedition.line: Go greet the team coming back from commission? Easy peasy! Just watch me~

feeling1.line: Even if Commander is my enemy, I won't go soft!

feeling2.line: Whenever you're in trouble, just call my name! Then you can bet Cooper will be there to bail you out, Commander!

feeling3.line: Commander! Did I hear my name? Hah hah hah, just point me at the enemy and... You need me to deliver these documents? I'm not your errand girl!

feeling4.line: Sorry, Commander. I know you were looking for me, but I got held up with this black kitty cat. I hope you didn't worry about me... B-but, like, who could resist playing with a kitty cat...?

feeling5.line: Commander! From now on I'm staying here with you, whether you call for me or not. So you won't have to worry about a thing...! Huh? You think I'm the one who's gonna get in trouble? Nng, yeah, maybe... But that still means I gotta stay with you, Commander!

home.line: Commander, I took care of a whole bunch of things while you were gone! See these reports? I wrote them all wrong? What the...

hp_warning.line: I won't be afraid! Now more than ever, they need me!

login.line: It's nice to see your smiling face, Commander! Heh heh!

lose.line: One little setback won't get me down!

mail.line: A new message? Could it be a distress signal...? My Danger Antenna is tingling!

main1.line: Paperwork? How does that help in a fight?

main2.line: Aaahhh~ I just lose it whenever I see a kitty cat. Commander, let's keep one in the office, a black one!

main3.line: Hey... how long are we gonna stay in the office? I'm so bored...

mission.line: We won't be able to help anyone if you leave your missions unfinished!

mission_complete.line: Mission accomplished! We're definitely making a difference!

profile.line: I'm an Allen M. Sumner-class destroyer, Cooper! I fought alongside Allen M. Sumner and Moale at Ormoc Bay, but I guess I didn't try hard enough... Nnng, damn it! How was I supposed to pick out anything like those oxygen torpedoes!

propose.line: Commander, who knew I was so important to you... I'm so happy! As long as I'm with you, then tomorrow... and the next day, and the day after that, I know I'll be able to do anything!

touch.line: Hey! Ready to move anytime!

touch2.line: Commander, do you understand what you're doing here?

unlock.line: Hey Commander, I'm Cooper! Let's join forces and fight for the future of the world! Booyah!

upgrade.line: Getting stronger is how I help more people!

win_mvp.line: Phew... What a nice feeling. Feels like victory.

detail.line: I never thought a game of afternoon tennis would be so exhausting... Huh? What's up, Commander?

drop_descrip.line: Break point!

home.line: Wait up! Hold on! Gotta catch my breath...! Phew, whew...

hp_warning.line: Deuce! This ain't over!

login.line: Watch me beat this Sakura girl... then it's you and me, Commander!

main1.line: Ace shot! Yaaaaaah!

main2.line: This is for me? Alright...! Glug glug... Haah!

main3.line: A black kitty cat! Where is it...?! Hey now, don't distract me!

touch.line: Y-you probably shouldn't touch me. I'm all sweaty right now.

unlock.line: 30 to 15... Next match will be mine, you hear! Oh, Commander, are you here to play a round of tennis?

detail.line: Whew! It's freezing cold outside, but warm and cozy in here! Nothing beats an open fireplace in the winter~

drop_descrip.line: Hm? I'm just wrapping up some presents! Can't just present them as-is, and all that. Hehe~ I could sure use a little help, Commander!

expedition.line: I think the commission team's back. Let's invite them in here and we can all have a cozy Christmas together!

home.line: I'm not sure who'll end up getting this snowglobe, but I am sure they'll love it!

login.line: I get excited thinking about what kind of presents I might get! What stuff did you wish for, Commander?

mail.line: New mail, huh? You think it might be someone's Christmas wishlist?

main1.line: You'd be surprised how easy wrapping presents is! You just put it like this... take some wrapping paper... then a ribbon... aaand done!

main2.line: Man, I wish I could ride anywhere in a cool snowmobile like Minneapolis. "It's too dangerous for a kid to ride"? Hey! It's not like I'm a little baby or anything!

main3.line: I'm getting kinda bored... Hey, Commander, wanna play word association? With a Christmas theme, obviously!

touch.line: Are you feeling chilly? Come a little closer if you wanna warm up, then~

touch2.line: Hrmph... You're not fooling me with any "just wanted to warm my hands up" excuses!

unlock.line: Hm? I'm just wrapping up some presents! Can't just present them as-is, and all that. Hehe~ I could sure use a little help, Commander!

battle.line: Let's do this thing!

detail.line: So Commander, do you like being the one cuddling, or the one being cuddled? Just wonderin'!

drop_descrip.line: Allen M. Sumner-class destroyer – Allen M. Sumner, Hull Number DD-692.

expedition.line: Commission completezo! Check it out, I categorized the rewards with some stickers!

feeling1.line: Okay, okay, calm yourself and I'll indulge you with a nice, heartwarming hug.

feeling2.line: My rigging's in tip-top condition! Counting on you to keep it that way, Commander! Hehe!

feeling3.line: I've finished all my combat drills, so I'm gonna use my break time to run down to the store! Oh, before I forget, here's a special sticker for you! It's all good if you wanna trade it with someone later.

feeling4.line: So, you doing anything special on your next day off? No? Perfect! Then mark that date your calendar. I'll bring the vidya and we can game all day!

feeling5.line: Zzz... Hmm? Commander? *yawn*... Guess I dozed off, whoops. Could you gimme a ride to the couch? ...No? Aww, why not?! We're buds, so what's the big deal? Zzz...

headtouch.line: Hmm?

home.line: Whoa! Hel-looo! The couch is all yours if you want it.

hp_warning.line: Owch! I'm not outta the game yet, though!

login.line: You're still in dreamland, huh? Hm... *blows*... Oh, hey! So you are awake!

lose.line: Oh crap, I really whiffed this one... Thank god for that near miss back there... Umm, I'll do better next time.

mail.line: New mail's come in! Gonna read it later? Gotcha, I'll put a sticker on it then.

main1.line: Okay, hear me out! Why don't we spruce up the office with some stickers? These here would look great on the walls and your desk!

main2.line: Man, it's crazy how much Fletcher cares for her sisters. Who, me? I, uhh, prefer a hands-off approach with my sisters!

main3.line: So this is what you do all day... You don't think I could become a commander too if I studied enough? Yeeeah, me neither. Heheh. Feel a little less tense now?

main4.line: You just yawned, didn't you, Commander? Just be honest and admit it~

mission.line: Beep boop, this is an automated deadpan mission reminder. Uncompleted missions detected. Do your job. Beep boop.

mission_complete.line: Mission completed! ...Wait a sec, this thing says I had zero involvement in it!

profile.line: I'm Allen M. Sumner, nameship of the class that succeeded the Fletcher class. We may not be as numerous as the Fletchers, but we've got a teensy edge over 'em in firepower and AA! Hell, I think it's no exaggeration to say we were the Eagle Union's strongest destroyers back in the war!

propose.line: One mystery remains: did I charm you, or did you charm me? Meh, don't really matter... All that's important is now we'll live happily ever after! Hehe~ I love you so much, Commander♡

touch.line: What's that? You cuddle with me? Go on, try it!

touch2.line: Hahaahh! Too slippery for you! Can't catch me!

unlock.line: I'm Eagle Union destroyer Allen M. Sumner! Just call me Allen! It's a pleasure, Commander! Anyway, I've heard you've got yummy food and cushy work here at this port. That true?

upgrade.line: Sweet! Burst of energy like this make me wanna do stretches!

win_mvp.line: Easy-breezy! That's another star on my record!

detail.line: Thanks for popping in! By the way... I'll pay you back for the OJ later.

drop_descrip.line: Welcome, Commander! I would fetch you our menu, but I've had a teensy accident here... Don't worry, I'll fix this somehow!

home.line: Hey, Commander, order a glass of OJ! ...No, it's for me! Staff can't just order drinks for themselves, y'know? That's weird.

login.line: Welcome, Commander! Uh, watch your step!

main1.line: Turns out North Carolina is like, a bunny girl expert! I never knew that.

main2.line: No, Cooper! No adult drinks, got it? Ask the commander to order you some juice instead! Hehehe~

main3.line: Sooo... You like bunny girls, Commander? Asking for a friend.

touch.line: You know what, it's comfier to sit and take it easy, so I'm gonna stay put for now.

touch2.line: Hey! You can't grope a staff member!

unlock.line: Welcome, Commander! I would fetch you our menu, but I've had a teensy accident here... Don't worry, I'll fix this somehow!

battle.line: All right, since I've gotta take this flagship thing seriously... Let 'em have it, girls!

detail.line: Here to chillax and hang out, eh, Commander?

drop_descrip.line: Fletcher-class destroyer – Stephen Potter, Hull Number DD-538.

expedition.line: A commission's been completed. Just throwing that out there before I forget.

feeling1.line: Yeah, no, I'll find someplace less boring to hang out. Hit me up only if you've got business with me.

feeling2.line: You need help with something? I've got a bazillion sisters, why not try asking them first?

feeling3.line: Hm? Why do I always just sit and stare when you take me in as the secretary? Becaaaause... you never explicitly ask for help? If you need something done, just like, tell me? I'm not the most attentive person in the universe, so sorry for that.

feeling4.line: It's getting harder and harder to tune you out of my mind... No, I don't mean that in reference to like, work, my free time, or whatever... I mean you, Commander. I'll just keep my eyes on you for now.

feeling5.line: Well yeah, I've thought about love before? It's not alien to me. Although thinking about it drains too much brainpower and just makes me sleepy in the end. I'd rather just be with you, Commander, and figure it out over time.

headtouch.line: Okay, now I think I get why some girls have headpat addictions.

home.line: Hum-hmmhm~♪ Oh, welcome back.

hp_warning.line: All right, no more messing around...

login.line: Welcome to the circle of hell known as "the office." Relax, I'll lend a hand if the cauldron gets too hot for you.

lose.line: Crap. I went too easy on 'em...

mail.line: Kind of curious who sent that unread letter on your desk.

main1.line: Dang, you caught me spacing out at work. ...Oh? Maybe you didn't after all? Cool. I'll just get back to doing it then.

main2.line: Hey, how about a bit of jazz? Chill, I'm just getting up to put a song on. I'm not gonna bail on you or anything.

main3.line: Mind if I borrow your coat, Commander? Thanks. This will work great as a blanket.

mission.line: Hey, a new mission! Oh, whoops... I guess we've both gotta actually do work now that I've said that.

mission_complete.line: Finished a mission, huh? Cool, then let's take ten to veg out.

profile.line: My record's got the usual destroyer stuff. You know, did anti-air duty, hunted a submarine, and went on the odd rescue mission. So basically, I can do anything a destroyer should be able to, just don't expect me to singlehandedly save the day like some superhero.

propose.line: It's gonna be so tiring, dealing with the responsibilities that come with getting hitched... Just saying, that's all. Hehe, I can handle a bit of fatigue as long as I've got you, sweetheart.

touch.line: You want some gum? 'Kay. Mint or orange flavor?

touch2.line: Whoa! Talk about a blunt-ass approach...

unlock.line: Fletcher-class Stephen Potter here. You've probably met a million of my sisters already, so I'll spare you my life story. See you around.

upgrade.line: Welp, guess the Slacker Council has to disband for the day.

win_mvp.line: Cool beans. I wasn't trying to style on 'em, but I'll take any commendations I'll get.

detail.line: I've got bunny pajamas on top of a bunny girl costume. That's double the bunny right there.

drop_descrip.line: Welcome to my private retreat, where you can skip work and veg out all you want. And by "skip work" I mean "enjoy your regularly scheduled day off." Anyway, make yourself at home, Commander.

headtouch.line: It's only human to want to touch the bun, I guess.

home.line: Oh, there's that collector's edition I ordered. What to do with these stickers... Guess I'll put 'em somewhere.

login.line: Heya. Wanna play a game? Mobile, console, or tabletop?

mail.line: Oh, new mail. Let's see here... Figures. This one's for you, Commander.

main1.line: Meowfficer plushes, Manjuu hand puppets... I never realized how much weird stuff I've amassed over the years.

main2.line: I invited Laffey over, thinking she'd be fun to chill with. Turns out she's just a sleep junkie, like Nicholas.

main3.line: Yeah, the place is a mess, but I'm used to it. It's way too much work to tidy up, so let's not.

touch.line: You want a bubblegum kiss? Sure. I've got plenty of flavors you can choose from.

touch2.line: I'm starting to think this outfit is a bit too inviting...

unlock.line: Welcome to my private retreat, where you can skip work and veg out all you want. And by "skip work" I mean "enjoy your regularly scheduled day off." Anyway, make yourself at home, Commander.

battle.line: N-not another battle...

detail.line: This little guy is my friend, Mr. Bear. Umm... he's equipped with a lot of equipment. Take this right hand, for example... Wait, you can't aim at the Commander!

drop_descrip.line: Fletcher-class destroyer – Morrison, Hull Number DD-560.

expedition.line: A commission has been completed. Umm, if you need any help, I don't mind...

feeling1.line: Just like I thought, things are better without me around...

feeling2.line: Commander, umm... to tell the truth, there's something I... i-it's nothing... forget I said anything...

feeling3.line: Commander, are you curious about Mr. Bear? T-Then, I'll introduce him to you.

feeling4.line: Commander, um, could I have a bit of your time...? I wanted to get your input on what kinds of things I could do to improve upon Mr. Bear's specs...

feeling5.line: Commander, am I helpful to you? I'm not a bother, am I? ...Mm, every time I hear your words of reassurance, I can relax a bit... Thank you very much, Commander.

headtouch.line: Mr. Bear...? Oh, Commander... I don't think Mr. Bear meant to hit you, Commander...

home.line: Commander, umm... I don't know if these will be of any use, but... (Morrison hands you some files)

hp_warning.line: Mr. Bear, save me...!

login.line: Commander, ah, um, n-never mind...

lose.line: Oww... Ugh, I want to go back to port...

mail.line: Mr. Bear, bring the mail over to the Commander.

main1.line: I'd really like to get my hands on a few sets of the Iron Blood's rigging... Heh, hehehe...

main2.line: Y-yes, you called? ...You didn't...? I'm sorry...

main3.line: It's sunny out today... Though, it's not like sunny days are always good either.

mission.line: Commander, if you need any help completing the missions, I don't mind...

mission_complete.line: You completed the missions? That means that I'm free for the time being, right?

profile.line: I'm the Fletcher-class destroyer, Morrison. I participated in anti-submarine warfare and rescue missions with my allies... If there's anything you want me to do... I-I should be able to do it.

propose.line: Phew... I've worked hard to prepare myself for this moment, so it's okay. Commander, if it's you, I'm okay with it...! Breathe in... Breathe out... C-C-Commander, u-u-um, I-I-I've finished preparing my heart! I-I'll be in your care!

touch.line: Mr. Bear, why don't you greet the Commander? Yes, normally, just like this... P-please keep your paws to yourself!

touch2.line: M-Mr. Bear is on a rampage?!

unlock.line: Phew... Finally got here in one piece... Ah, um, are you the commander? My name is Morrison. Yes, the Fletcher-class Morrison with way too many sisters...

upgrade.line: I really don't think you need to go that far for someone like me...

win_mvp.line: Whew... That should give me a bit of leeway...

detail.line: Benson told me all about the ins and outs of Planet Bunny... Huh? Is something amiss?

drop_descrip.line: Zzz... Commander? S-sorry, I fell asleep for a bit... Uh, umm, what would you like me to do...?

headtouch.line: M-my ears are going to fall off...

home.line: Commander, would you like some tea...?

login.line: It's a bit embarrassing, but... it's surprisingly comfortable...

mail.line: Mr. Bear, take the mail to the Commander... Oh, Mr. Bear isn't here right now...

main1.line: I wonder if I should take Stanly's advice and turn Mr. Bear into "Rabbit Mode"...

main2.line: I'm so jealous of all the people that get to wear cute clothes... Y-you think I'm cute, too...?

main3.line: I-it's spicy? Was it Thatcher? No, it could have been Kalk...

touch.line: C-can I take a nap yet...?

touch2.line: Commander, um, please show some self-restraint...

unlock.line: Zzz... Commander? S-sorry, I fell asleep for a bit... Uh, umm, what would you like me to do...?

battle.line: Full module calibration complete. I'm loaded and ready for battle!

detail.line: Breaking stuff is easy. Making stuff is not.

drop_descrip.line: Allen M. Sumner-class destroyer – Ingraham, Hull Number DD-694.

expedition.line: Commission complete. Any parts you don't need? Send 'em my way.

feeling1.line: I'd love to unscrew your thick skull and have a look at what's inside.

feeling2.line: Even minor flaws impact the quality of a product. You want high-end equipment? Make sure it's perfectly calibrated.

feeling3.line: Hey, Cooper, I finished that "morph item" you asked about... No, Allen! Stop plastering stickers all over my stuff!

feeling4.line: Yo, Commander, I scrounged up some spare parts and made you this steel medal on my day off. C'mere, I'll attach it to your uniform... Pfft! Looks pretty good on you!

feeling5.line: Listen, if you ever need something, just hit me up. Scratch that, uhh... You can hit me up anytime, for any reason. I just feel kinda lonely without you, you know? Ahem... Anyway!

headtouch.line: This hairpin? It's made from a repurposed binder clip. Is that so weird?

home.line: My hunch was right – this thing really is a millimeter off... Oh, hey there, Commander. Just who I was looking for. Could you have a look at this?

hp_warning.line: Oh, crap! That's gonna be a pain to repair!

login.line: You're late, Commander. I oughta build you an alarm clock that keeps ringing no matter what you do.

lose.line: I've gotta do thorough rigging maintenance when I get back!

mail.line: Mail, eh... I could give your mailbox a makeover, if you want.

main1.line: Yo, Commander, you mind if I do some tinkering in here? Don't wanna disturb you, is all... All righty, I'll take that as a "yes."

main2.line: Why am I wearing just one stocking? Uhh, because I forgot to put the other one on. What does it matter, anyway? Clothes are just a bother.

main3.line: There's a loose screw under the bookcase... No biggie, I'll get it myself. And don't you dare try to sneak a dirty peek in while I'm doing it.

mission.line: New missions, huh? Ugh. I don't wanna get off my butt...

mission_complete.line: Need a pen to write the mission complete papers? Here, you can borrow mine.

profile.line: Thought about it some more, but I really don't have much else to tell you. On another note, wanna see the Allen M. Sumner-class miniature I made? Main battery, AA guns, even depth charges, it's all there. See?

propose.line: Here I thought you were dense, but I guess I was wrong. Oh yeah, I made this ring for you. It's no promise ring, but I still want you to have it... This thing's special to me, so don't even think about having me remake it for you.

touch.line: Keep the touching to a minimum, thanks.

touch2.line: This is your dirty-deeds-hand, huh? I'm gonna keep you armlocked until you say you're sorry.

unlock.line: I'm Ingraham, Eagle Union destroyer. Not much else to tell you, honestly... Anyhoo, good to meet you.

upgrade.line: Rigging upgrades, huh? Keep them coming, thanks.

win_mvp.line: Sweet! My rigging's perfectly tuned!

detail.line: Your job's simple. All you need to do is drink what I serve you and give feedback on the taste, mouthfeel, et cetera.

drop_descrip.line: Hmm... Could use a little more sweetness, and a splash of the secret ingredient... Oh, you're here? Great. I appoint you as my first dedicated taste-tester, Commander. We're gonna come up with some novel and fresh drinks, you and I!

expedition.line: Commission complete. Let's see if they brought back anything I can use...

home.line: Once I've perfected this recipe, I'll give you a gold taste-tester medal for your efforts.

login.line: You're on time for once! That means you're due for a reward. I'll make your drink doubly sweet.

main1.line: All I asked Allen for was some label paper, and instead she dumped a billion different stickers on me...

main2.line: No, Cooper, that stuff's got alcohol in it. Put it back where you found it.

main3.line: Yeah, Allen made me wear this getup when she found out I'll be handling the bar counter... That said, I guess I don't really mind it.

touch2.line: Hey! Wow... Hope you like your lemonade with 30 times more lemon juice.

unlock.line: Hmm... Could use a little more sweetness, and a splash of the secret ingredient... Oh, you're here? Great. I appoint you as my first dedicated taste-tester, Commander. We're gonna come up with some novel and fresh drinks, you and I!

battle.line: Bristol Investigation Team, setting off!

detail.line: Curious about my little helper? Hehehe. Well, Ingraham built it to assist me in exploration. Its name is Data 857!

drop_descrip.line: Allen M. Sumner-class destroyer – Bristol, Hull Number DD-857.

expedition.line: A commission's been completed! Data 857, go see if the girls brought back any strange goodies. And watch out for k-kelp!

feeling1.line: Hmph... Our adventure went so badly all because you went and got the kelp curse put on you!

feeling2.line: The Dragon Empery's a land teeming with folklore and myths... Next time I see my Empery friends, I wanna hear all about them!

feeling3.line: If that'll be all, do you mind if I go for a stroll around port? ...Awesome! Come along, Data 857!

feeling4.line: Are you scared of the dark, Commander? Then just stick close to me, and my lantern will shoo the dark away! You've nothing to fear – I've trained for this!

feeling5.line: There are more mysteries in the world than Data 857 and I can ever hope to solve... It's a good thing I have you, Commander! We might never solve EVERY mystery, but together, we can solve a lot more!

headtouch.line: Sure, praise me for my investigator skills all you want~

home.line: Now's the perfect opportunity to look into the Commander, one of the port's many myster– Oh! Welcome back! Err, I'm not up to anything at all! Not yet, at least!

hp_warning.line: Zoinks! Don't put out my light!

login.line: Weapons check complete – I'm ready to go on an adventure! Get your mystery-solving gear on, Commander!

lose.line: Fiddlesticks! Agghh... No regrets...

mail.line: New mail? Could it be... a request to look into a paranormal case?

main1.line: Show the Commander what an awesome robot you are, Data 857! Let's start with your best feature – replay mode! List the results of our last investigation!

main2.line: I was told your desk can transform and your bookshelf has a secret mechanism... I'm disappointed neither of those are true.

main3.line: The forecast saaays... Awesome! It'll be sunny tomorrow! Can't go mystery-solving in the rain, you know!

mission.line: New missions are in, Commander! Maybe one of them involves investigating something!

mission_complete.line: Mission complete! I'll write up a report of my findings right away!

profile.line: My history? Eh, it's honestly pretty unremarkable... Anyway, lemme tell you a story! Deep under the sea, there once lived a legendary monster that was as long as several school buses. When a ship sailed over it, the monster would open its jaws and swallow it whole...

propose.line: Hehehe! Now we're mystery-solving partners! We'll go wherever there are clues to be found, be they at sea, in the skies, or on land!

skill.line: Your biggest mistake was underestimating this investigator!

touch.line: My uniform looks pretty, doesn't it?

touch2.line: Are you possessed by an evil entity?! Then I have no choice... I've got to subdue you for everyone's safety!

unlock.line: The name is Bristol, Eagle Union destroyer! Well met, Commander! This port must be home to many mysteries... I will make it my duty to solve each and every one! Heheheh!

upgrade.line: Firepower upgrade complete! New depths to explore are now within my reach!

win_mvp.line: Crushing victory! Heheh! Now we can keep investigating in peace!

detail.line: Sorry for dropping in unannounced, Tai Yuan. I was just wondering, could I borrow some books from you again? Cool, thanks a bunch!

drop_descrip.line: Happy Lunar New Year, Commander! The time's finally come to look into the age-old legends from the Dragon Empery! The truth behind these legends is bound to be as fascinating as the legends themselves!

home.line: Cooper, I could use more soap liquid! ...Thanks! Come blow bubbles with me! Hehehe~

login.line: Investigator task for today: gather anecdotes about Dragon Empery legends and folklore! But that's for after I've enjoyed the festivities.

main1.line: Assuming a legend is a story embellished by people from many generations ago, then what is the kernel of truth that inspired it all?

main2.line: Where's Data 857? Ingraham's doing maintenance on it. The little bot deserves a break too once in a while.

main3.line: If the legends are true, then that makes this fish – the Kun – the biggest aquatic monster to ever exist!

touch.line: Allen picked these clothes out for me! Hehehe~ How do I look in them?

touch2.line: Whoa! Hey! Don't startle me like that!

unlock.line: Happy Lunar New Year, Commander! The time's finally come to look into the age-old legends from the Dragon Empery! The truth behind these legends is bound to be as fascinating as the legends themselves!

battle.line: Hmph! Witness my newly obtained power!

detail.line: Wh-why have you been staring at me for so long?! Could it be that you're actually a perv—Oh, you're just examining my rigging? I-I don't believe you!

drop_descrip.line: Edsall-class destroyer escort – Hammann II, Hull Number DE-131.

expedition.line: Go and greet the girls who just got back from their commission! And... Make sure you come back quick!

feeling1.line: Hmph! I don't even care anymore!

feeling2.line: Yorktown might trust you, but you won't win me over that easily! Hmph! ...You say you'll try to work on your worst qualities? W-well, either way, I'm watching you, bub!

feeling3.line: You wanna know why I'm staring at you now? Does it really matter?! Oh, I get it - you think I'm a stalker, right?! I'm just worried that you're gonna do something weird if I don't keep my eye on you!

feeling4.line: H-hmph! Since you've been good recently, I'll show my appreciation with a rare compliment! ...Th-that doesn't mean I've totally accepted you, though!

feeling5.line: Hmph! Every time I look away, you glue your eyes to some other girl... Hyah?! Wh-what's gotten into you?! O-okay, now your face is way too close to mine! I get what you're trying to say, alright?! Geez… That was seriously not the time for that.

headtouch.line: I've never understood why some girls at the port get so excited when you pat them on the head... That didn't mean I want you to touch me!

home.line: Why isn't the Commander back yet... Eep?! D-don't just sneak over without saying anything!

hp_warning.line: I can't stand this...!

login.line: Hmph! I don't care whether you're here or not, okay?!

lose.line: Aww, now the Commander is gonna lecture me... H-hey, you didn't hear anything from me!

mail.line: Commander! I brought your mail in for you!

main1.line: Stupid Commander, are you just gonna work all of our time away? ...I-I didn't say anything! You just do your own thing!

main2.line: How am I adjusting to my new rigging? Hmph, I'm just fine! Worry about me when it actually matters!

main3.line: Heheheh, now I can really show I-168 who's boss... Y-Yorktown, wait! I'm just trying to make friends with her, I swear!

mission.line: Stupid Commander! You're forgetting all these missions you haven't finished!

mission_complete.line: Excuse me! You've got something waiting for you to pick it up! ...I mean the mission rewards, idiot!

profile.line: Hmph. No matter what, I'm still me. Now I've told you all about Yorktown, there is nothing else you need to say. I-if you really wanna do anything for me... Err, I take that back!

propose.line: D-don't say a word, and just hug me, okay? But don't look at my face! And stop laughing! So this is what I get for being brave and baring my emotions to the person I like...

touch.line: Ack?! Don't touch me out of nowhere! You scared me!

touch2.line: Pervert! Degenerate! I'm gonna tell Yorktown... I-if Yorktown doesn't get mad at you, then I still have ways to get back at you!

unlock.line: Wh-what do you think you're looking at, pervert?! You say it's irresistible...? And you think I'm going to believe that?! Here I was thinking I'd introduce myself properly... I'm gonna remember this!

upgrade.line: Ugh, I can't say no to you...

win_mvp.line: I won! ...Wh-what?! Just so you know, your compliments don't make me happy at all!

detail.line: How long are you gonna stare? Do you l-like my swimsuit that much? ...Why am I not calling you a pervert? C-come on, you have to be teasing me now!

drop_descrip.line: Hmph! I only promised to come to the beach because I was worried you'd be lonely! There's no deeper meaning—w-wait! What are you doing?! Stooop!

home.line: If you're tired, then I guess you can come here... H-hey, I'm saying you can sit NEXT to me! Dummy! U-ugh, forget it.

login.line: You're the one who invited me out, so why are you late?! ...Hmph!

main1.line: Beach volleyball? Eh, I'll pass... Wh-what? If you wanna play that bad, then go. See if I care! Hmph!

main2.line: You're giving me a drink? Look, buttering me up won't get you—Th-thank... you...

main3.line: Sims, wait! I am NOT on a date with the Commander! ...Darn it, Commander, back me up!

touch.line: Hyah?! W-was that on purpose?!

touch2.line: Pervert! Lecher! I'm never going to forgive you for that!

unlock.line: Hmph! I only promised to come to the beach because I was worried you'd be lonely! There's no deeper meaning—w-wait! What are you doing?! Stooop!

battle.line: I'm invincible now that I'm full! You can't stop me from fighting until I'm totally exhausted!

detail.line: M-my belly isn't fat at all, Commander! Ah, don't look at it!

drop_descrip.line: Omaha-class light cruiser – Omaha, Hull Number CL-4!

expedition.line: Don't look at me like that, Commander. I'd take on commissions too if they gave snacks as rewards!

feeling1.line: Something to eat? I'm actually full right now. No thanks, Commander.

feeling2.line: Hmm? I only like commanders who can actually cook!

feeling3.line: Mmph... C-come on, surely you like your girls with a little more meat on them!

feeling4.line: Maybe I should lose some weight... What, isn't it normal to try and look good for the person you like? Besides, it's not like I'm really fat or anything!

feeling5.line: Commander, from now on, if I don't lose weight, then that's your fault! You have to take responsibility! How? By taking care of me for the rest of your life, of course!

home.line: Commander! What should we have first? Breakfast? Or lunch? Or maybe dinner~?

login.line: Commander~ Any fun things you want Omaha to do today?

lose.line: Wait until I come back with a full belly!

mail.line: You've got mail, Commander! Maybe it's the snacks I ordered yesterday?

main1.line: Ahh... I'm so hungry...

main2.line: You don't eat snacks, Commander? How dull your life must be!

main3.line: Have you eaten yet, Commander? Cause you don't look too great...

mission.line: Huh? A mission? Let me just finish these chips first...

mission_complete.line: Feed me, feed me! We'll talk about losing weight tomorrow!

profile.line: Omaha has arrived! I was born after the first World War, but as a reconnaissance ship, I've got a lifetime's worth of intel in my brain!

propose.line: Now we have a promise, Commander. You take care of the cooking, and I'll take care of the ea... housework! That way I can eat and still lose weight! I'm so smart!

skill.line: Oh no! I loaded my guns with snacks instead!

touch.line: Hm... I'm getting a bit chubby? No! I'll never give up my search for the most delicious food!

touch2.line: You're not "checking if I've gained weight" at all! You're just a big old pervert, Commander~!

unlock.line: Omaha-class cruiser - Omaha! Greetings, Commander! You could say that I'm a fleet veteran~!  Hehe~! So, since this is the first time we meet, shouldn't you celebrate by giving me some sort of gift?

upgrade.line: I got stronger, but I also got hungrier at the same time!

win_mvp.line: Oh yeah! There's no armor my guns can't penetrate!

battle.line: Please pay attention, everyone! This is a good chance to get some real combat experience~

detail.line: Make sure you ask me any questions if you're lost before we head out!

drop_descrip.line: Omaha-class light cruiser – Raleigh, Hull Number CL-7!

expedition.line: It's almost time, Commander. I'll go ahead and welcome the girls back from their commission.

feeling1.line: I'm not a kid, okay!

feeling2.line: Commander, mature people like you need to pay attention on the job.

feeling3.line: You want to know more about me? Hmm... you may be the first person to treat me like an equal. I'm happy about that, I suppose.

feeling4.line: You've been taking it pretty easy recently, Commander... *Sigh*... I guess some of the blame is mine to share... It's hard to be strict with someone I like...

feeling5.line: You're calling me 'professor' in such an... interesting way when we're alone. Are you expecting to receive private lessons? You're just like a little kid, Commander...

home.line: You did quite well, Commander!

login.line: Hello, Commander. I've been waiting for you. Oh my, look at the time! Shouldn't we start the training now?

lose.line: Phew... That was close... I nearly...

mail.line: Your mail has been sorted. Remember to read your messages thoroughly, please!

main1.line: Shall we begin our training, Commander?

main2.line: For a beginner, every bit of training is very important~!

main3.line: My name is Raleigh, not... that! Also, don't forget the "Ms."!

mission.line: Commander, please don't forget about your unfinished missions!

mission_complete.line: Please don't forget to claim your mission rewards.

profile.line: I'm the training officer of the Omaha-class fleet - Raleigh. I'm going to be very strict with anyone who won't listen to what I say!

propose.line: To receive something so precious from a student... I should be ashamed to call myself a professional mentor... But you make me...

skill.line: Let me show you some textbook maneuvers.

touch.line: Please don't tug me like that... I'm not a kid!

touch2.line: I'm not immune to getting angry, you know... Co-man-der!

unlock.line: I'm Raleigh, the Omaha-class light cruiser. Please sign this contract here... There we go. I'm hoping we'll make a good team from now on, Commander.

upgrade.line: Now I can properly mentor you, Commander.

win_mvp.line: You can't use the same trick on me twice!

battle.line: Fire at will! I have you covered!

detail.line: This information is confidential, so please keep it a closely guarded secret.

drop_descrip.line: Brooklyn-class Light Cruiser – Brooklyn, Hull Number CL-40!

expedition.line: Though it may be tough for everyone, completing commissions like this will help raise our reputation. Let's start another one as soon as possible.

feeling1.line: Commander, I'm thinking of resigning because you just don't seem like you're worth the effort.

feeling2.line: Commander, my responsibility is to ensure that you have the upper hand in foreign affairs. Rest assured, I am an expert in that area.

feeling3.line: It feels like I've been managing your personal affairs more than foreign affairs lately, Commander... Surely this isn't on purpose, is it?

feeling4.line: Commander, a diplomat doesn't usually take on the role of a secretary... but I personally wish to deepen my relationship with you.

feeling5.line: I wish to fight only for you, to give you the upper hand... Maybe I am no longer suited to be the entire fleet's diplomat.

home.line: Good work, Commander. I will make sure that the results of your last battle come to good use.

login.line: You came just in time. A few files need your signature.

lose.line: Now we won't have an advantage during the negotiations...

mail.line: There's mail for you, Commander... Hm? Where was this sent from?

main1.line: It's important to communicate with other nations.

main2.line: Please don't stare at me in such a weird way.

main3.line: I may be a diplomat, but don't even think about underestimating my power.

mission.line: Completing missions is a good way to demonstrate our capabilities. Please take a look at some of the new missions.

mission_complete.line: Here is a summary of the rewards. Your confirmation, please, Commander.

profile.line: As the representative of the then newly constructed pre-war cruisers, I was put in charge of foreign diplomacy. That said, my firepower is never to be underestimated, so please put your mind at ease.

propose.line: Thank you, now I have more confidence in managing the fleet's affairs. Hm? I may act on your behalf for a little? What a pleasant joke. ... At any rate, I will not let you down.

skill.line: Deterrence is also a part of diplomacy...

touch.line: Are you interested in my tanned skin, Commander?

touch2.line: A diplomat is not the same thing as a secretary... Please, restrain yourself, Commander!

unlock.line: I am Brooklyn. I am an elite cruiser, so you may let me handle all foreign diplomacy matters.

upgrade.line: Power is the foundation of gunboat diplomacies. Thank you.

win_mvp.line: Now then, let us talk about reparations.

battle.line: Look to the east! It's burning red!

detail.line: What's the matter, Commander? You look kinda emotionless.

drop_descrip.line: Brooklyn-class light cruiser – Phoenix, Hull Number CL-46!

expedition.line: Commission completed... Hey, isn't it about time you let me head out on one?

feeling1.line: Get outta here, coward!

feeling2.line: Only those who aren't afraid of death deserve to live! Ahh, don't be afraid Commander, I don't mean that literally! What I meant to say is that it's not about living or dying, it's about what mindset you have!

feeling3.line: What's the matter? If you're okay with me then I can give you some advice!

feeling4.line: Although I respect that man, you're still you, Commander. As long as you're with me, I'm invincible!

feeling5.line: I see. It's no wonder that whenever I'm with you, I'm in such high spirits! I feel like my heart is on fire! This is it, this is love... I've never experienced this before...

home.line: Looks like we made it back safe and sound as usual today!

hp_warning.line: My hand is calling out to me to seize victory!

login.line: Hey, Commander! I'll protect you, like I always do!

lose.line: Tsk, I'll get you for this!

mail.line: Hey! Commander! Your mail is here!

main1.line: My motto is: "be the best at everything"!

main2.line: Is the sun bigger in Argentina?

main3.line: There's nothing more thrilling than coming back from the verge of death!

mission.line: How could you fall behind on something as simple as missions?

mission_complete.line: Looks like our well-deserved rewards have been delivered.

profile.line: I'm Phoenix. I once escorted a certain important person. Just like a phoenix, no matter what happens to me, I'll always come back from death! Throw all the dangerous missions you've got at me, I won't let you down!

propose.line: ... Thank you. I'll accept it. Also, um... I don't really know how to talk all sweet or flirt or anything like that, but now that you've chosen me, I promise I won't let you down!

touch.line: It's here, it's here! Want to head out now?

touch2.line: Hey~! Be a gentleman!

unlock.line: Are you the commander? I'm Phoenix. That's right, the legendary phoenix! Do you have what it takes to lead me?

upgrade.line: Alright! I've gotten stronger!

win_mvp.line: Hahah! Aren't there any strong enemies left for me to fight?

battle.line: The enemy can't hide from me.

detail.line: I can't rely on this thing alone...

drop_descrip.line: Brooklyn-class Light Cruiser – Helena, Hull Number CL-50!

expedition.line: Hey, Commander, could I lend my SG radar to my sisters this time?

feeling1.line: SG, protect me...

feeling2.line: If only my recon could help the others...

feeling3.line: My expression? Ah... it's because I left while we were on the losing end of the war... I might just not be so used to peace and happiness. But don't worry, I'll be fine!

feeling4.line: I think I've been more at ease lately... No, I was just too tense up until now. It's all thanks to the courage you've given me by being beside me.

feeling5.line: I believe that you will bring us hope, Commander. This time, I'll fight to the end... Just the thought of saying goodbye to the person I love makes me feel like my heart will tear in half...

home.line: Did everyone make it back safe and sound? Good. But there's spare parts lying around in the docks now... I wonder why...

hp_warning.line: SG, lock on the enemy position!

login.line: ... Ah, welcome back, Commander. Sorry, I was just brooding over something.

lose.line: ... Please, save me... Ignore the enemy, just let them go...

mail.line: You've got new mail. It's important to stay in touch with your loved ones.

main1.line: Are you trying to hide, Commander? No matter where you hide, I know where you are.

main2.line: Commander, what should we do after the war?

main3.line: If only my guns could be as strong as my radar...

mission.line: Bit by bit we'll build the foundation for victory. We'll start by doing missions.

mission_complete.line: Resources are no good if they just pile up. We should make use of them.

profile.line: I was designed to be on par with heavy cruisers, but just my power alone isn't enough to save everyone... Commander, can you help me?

propose.line: A promise... from you, Commander? I see... I'm so happy...

touch.line: Hm? I'm fine. I'm just... a little distracted.

touch2.line: If this makes you feel good, then... I'm fine with it.
