unlock.line: Nice to meet you, Commander. I'm Helena. My strong suit is enemy reconnaissance. Please... guide us towards victory.

upgrade.line: I'll use this power to protect everyone!

win_mvp.line: ... We actually won?

battle.line: I... want to win!

detail.line: St. Louis must've had a lot of fun making me try out so many clothes... Do you really think I look cute this way, Commander?

drop_descrip.line: I... want to be part of the new year festivities too. Oh, you don't have to worry about me. I'm no longer the fledgling I once was.

feeling5.line: Commander? You don't have to worry about me. I was just thinking about how I now have friends and a sweetheart who I can celebrate the new year together with, and how unbelievably happy it makes me.

home.line: Let me be part of the mission, Commander. My SG would surely be good to have.

login.line: It seems the New Year's spirit has swept over the entire fleet.

lose.line: It's okay, there's always the next time...!

main1.line: My New Year's wish is... that I'll be more courageous and positive, and that no harm will come to any of my friends...

main2.line: For this year's shrine visit, the whole Brooklyn-class, Cleveland, and her Knights of The Sea all went there together as one big family.

main3.line: It's snowing... I never realized how peaceful and beautiful snow can be.

touch.line: Huh? I was just thinking about what I should do during New Year's... There are so many things I want to do.

touch2.line: C-Commander, please stop...

unlock.line: I... want to be part of the new year festivities too. Oh, you don't have to worry about me. I'm no longer the fledgling I once was.

win_mvp.line: That's right...! You did a great job, me!

battle.line: I... want to win!

detail.line: In preparation for today, I got St. Louis to teach me how to dance. She laughed a lot at me, telling me I'm "such a klutz"... Ahah.

drop_descrip.line: Um, Commander, could we... share a dance? I have things I want to tell you...

expedition.line: Commander, let's extend an invitation to the commission team to join us for the party.

feeling5.line: You and my friends have always taken care of, looked after, and protected me. But that can't go on forever. I want to stand beside you and become someone people can count on... So, could you wait for me just a little longer... please?

home.line: Commander, before we leave for the party, do you have any unfinished business?

login.line: Commander, the party is about to start.

lose.line: It's okay, there's always next time...!

mail.line: It seems you've got an invitation to another dance party... Hahah, you really are a superstar, Commander.

main1.line: Commander, you know something? It's thanks to you that I've become as cheerful as I am now. Ahah~

main2.line: I'm not going to be scared or hesitate ever again because you and my friends are always with me.

main3.line: My dance partner will be... No, it'll just be you, Commander. I have so many things I want to tell you.

mission.line: Commander, please go complete your missions. Don't worry, I'll be here waiting for you.

mission_complete.line: You really are incredible, Commander.

touch.line: I'm all ready, Commander. Shall we dance?

touch2.line: Eek?! ... Ah, sorry, did I step on your foot, Commander?

unlock.line: Um, Commander, could we... share a dance? I have things I want to tell you...

win_mvp.line: Yeah, that's right...! You're awesome, Helena!

battle.line: Keep calm and focus, Helena!

detail.line: I'm okay with wearing a swimsuit – we all wear them on the beach, after all. It's only when you look at me that I get all shy... It's a weird feeling.

drop_descrip.line: Commander, what do you think... umm... about this swimsuit? Actually, umm, never mind. If I were to hear your impressions directly, I'd be too embarrassed to stand in front of you... So, would you mind, umm... secretly whispering it to me?

expedition.line: The commission team is back. No, it wasn't my SG that told me, but a friend. As for who... that's a secret.

feeling5.line: Be confident, Helena. It's okay to fawn on the Commander. You started this when you mustered your courage, remember? So just... H-hey! Commander, would you mind... taking the lead for our date?

headtouch.line: Heehee... *blushes*

home.line: Welcome back, Commander. If you, uh, have a moment, we could go for a swim... I know you just got back from the ocean, but... still?

login.line: Whew... This breeze is lovely... Hey, Commander, for just a brief moment, I was thinking I could... be more daring around you...

lose.line: Commander, over here! I'll keep you safe!

mail.line: A letter has arrived. Do you want to read it now?

main1.line: SG, track the Commander's exact location. If we meet before I've mentally prepared myself for it, I might just freak out...

main2.line: I like "you're pretty" over "you're cute" as a compliment... Oh, that doesn't mean you can't say I'm cute or anything... It's obviously up to you to decide how to compliment me, Commander, you can even use both, so... *whimper*...

main3.line: Just tell me if anything feels wrong. It's my... No, it's all our job to ensure you don't have anything to worry about.

mission.line: Commander, please go complete your missions. Don't worry, I'll be here waiting for you.

mission_complete.line: You really are incredible, Commander.

touch.line: Mhm, I'm all ears. What is it, Commander?

touch2.line: Umm, I... *blushes*

unlock.line: Commander, what do you think... umm... about this swimsuit? Actually, umm, never mind. If I were to hear your impressions directly, I'd be too embarrassed to stand in front of you... So, would you mind, umm... secretly whispering it to me?

win_mvp.line: Thank you, SG. You help me push myself.

battle.line: I'm... going to win!

detail.line: I used to feel constant anxiety over if I'm capable or not, but nowadays... that anxiety's been overtaken by confidence, knowing all will be fine when you're with me. Heehee.

drop_descrip.line: Wh-what do you think, Commander? Does it suit me? ...I never could've imagined getting to wear this even in my dreams, let alone experience the bliss I feel now... Thank you so, so much.

expedition.line: The commission team has come back. That's at least some weight off my mind.

feeling5.line: When I'm with you, I keep hoping you'll rely on me, but instead I'm the one who relies on you... It's sort of backwards, isn't it? Heehee... I'm so, so happy to be your wife, Commander.

login.line: Welcome back, Commander. My SG told me that you were on your way, but I had to see you with my own eyes.

lose.line: It's okay, Helena. There's always next time...!

main1.line: I'll cook dinner tonight! And breakfast tomorrow, and dinner after that, and breakfast the day after– Oops! I blurted all that without thinking...

main2.line: Having experienced such bliss for a while now, I've started wishing for an even more blissful future... It's sort of selfish of me, but you don't mind, do you?

main3.line: I can't be reliant on my SG forever... Huh? So I should turn to you for help instead? ...Okay! I'll try to, at least...

touch.line: I should be fine if you, um, hold my hand for just another minute...

touch2.line: W-wait, I need time to prepare myself...

unlock.line: Wh-what do you think, Commander? Does it suit me? ...I never could've imagined getting to wear this even in my dreams, let alone experience the bliss I feel now... Thank you so, so much.

win_mvp.line: Don't get complacent, Helena... You've got to get even stronger!

battle.line: I'm... going to win!

detail.line: St. Louis always praises me like, "my, how you've grown" whenever I do anything... It's kind of embarrassing...

drop_descrip.line: This new equipment... might take some time to get used to... N-no, I'm sure I can handle it now! Commander, Helena will... meet your expectations!

expedition.line: SG receiving message... A commission team has returned to port.

feeling5.line: I feel a bit more confident in myself when I'm with you, Commander. But I want more; I want to be the girl you rely on so I can be the center of your attention... It might be selfish to ask, but... will you love me?

login.line: Welcome back, Commander. Let's get to work and do our best.

lose.line: It's okay, Helena. There's always next time...!

main1.line: You want to know what my new and improved SG is capable of? All right... Find a place to hide that nobody knows about. Hehehe~

main2.line: I think everyone would be better off living in the present without regrets than spend every day anxious about the future.

main3.line: It's not enough to focus only on improving my equipment. I need to become stronger to use it properly, too.

touch2.line: You really can't go around doing this, Commander!

unlock.line: This new equipment... might take some time to get used to... N-no, I'm sure I can handle it now! Commander, Helena will... meet your expectations!

win_mvp.line: Don't get complacent, Helena... You've got to get even stronger!

battle.line: I'll show you what the tons-of-guns doctrine is really worth!

detail.line: Ah, Commander's looking... I have to behave like a big sister!

drop_descrip.line: Atlanta-class light cruiser – Atlanta, Hull Number CL-51!

expedition.line: Commander, the commission's done. Are we gonna go welcome the girls back?

feeling1.line: Sometimes I'm happy that I'm not actually your big sister...

feeling2.line: Being a big sister isn't just about looking like one, you need to have the personality of one as well. That's why you can depend on me all you want~!

feeling3.line: The bigger the better, don't you think? ...Hey! What are you staring at?! Gee, sorry for not being big enough, I guess!

feeling4.line: Are you fond of assertive big sister type characters? That is to say... someone like me...

feeling5.line: ... Huh? You want me to take the initiative? O-o-o-o-of course, I don't mind! I-I mean, I'm your big sister after all, so it's my job to guide you!

home.line: That's the Commander I know. No problem for you at all, right?

login.line: Commander, if you ever run into a problem, please tell me!

lose.line: Argh, this is bad... My big sister image is ruined...

mail.line: You've got new mail! I wonder if any of the messages are from my sisters...

main1.line: Not being a flagship sure is more peaceful...

main2.line: San Francisco was terrible to me! Just once is tolerable for accidental friendly fire, but she shot me well over ten times!

main3.line: Shooting down aircraft is my specialty. Want me to teach you how to do it, Commander?

mission.line: So, does this mean you're leaving all your unfinished missions to me, Commander?

mission_complete.line: Our mission rewards have arrived. I'll give my share of the rewards to my little sisters.

profile.line: I'm the anti-aircraft cruiser Atlanta... I was the flagship of the 10th and 11th Atlantic cruising fleet and I've taken part in nearly every military operation in the Pacific. Even the President has given me praise!

propose.line: Thank you... From now on I'll... What? You'd prefer it if I took the initiative and gave it to you instead? Y-you have a point... Okay then, should we do it again from the start?

touch.line: Mgh, don't touch me like that... My big sister image would be ruined!

touch2.line: *Eek* W-what are you doing?!

unlock.line: I'm the anti-aircraft cruiser Atlanta. Kept you waiting, huh, Commander? But from now on you can rest easy and let me handle everything!

upgrade.line: Let me handle things from now on!

win_mvp.line: All targets eliminated. Requesting new mission!

battle.line: Everyone... look after yourselves... and watch out for those mean submarines...

detail.line: The... old injury to my foot? Well... my foot's still a bit stiff, but I won't ever let myself drag everyone else down...!

drop_descrip.line: Atlanta-class light cruiser – Juneau, Hull Number CL-52!

expedition.line: Umm... Commander... there's a commission that's been completed...

feeling1.line: Don't come near me! ...Sorry, I think you're a little scary, Commander...

feeling2.line: I... often have nightmares about five brothers whose faces are all blurred, and they tell me to come with them... It's really scary...

feeling3.line: Commander, can I go to bed with you again tonight? ... I feel very safe when I sleep next to you...

feeling4.line: I'm not afraid of having nightmares anymore... b-but can I still sleep together with you, Commander...?

feeling5.line: Now when I dream about those five brothers... I can see their faces clearly, and they bless me with their smiles... But somehow it was so sad it almost made me cry... *Tearful sobbing*... Can I really live happily together with you, Commander? It's not just a dream, right...?

home.line: I'm really hoping this war will end soon... Once it's over, let's all go someplace together...

login.line: C-Commander... I'll always be w-waiting for you here...

lose.line: That hurts! ... I can't feel my left foot... Someone come save me....!

mail.line: Commander... excuse me... here's your mail...

main1.line: *Eek* Commander?! Y-you scared me...

main2.line: I want to be brave... But it's really hard...

main3.line: Commander, have I annoyed you in any way...?

mission.line: What? A mission? I don't mind as long as we aren't fighting submarines...

mission_complete.line: I don't need any rewards... just being here with everyone is enough for me...

profile.line: I-I'm Juneau, an Atlanta-class anti-aircraft cruiser... Because I have high anti-air capabilities, I was assigned to a Task Force, but I'm actually scared of getting shot... Unfortunately I couldn't make it back home from Espiritu Santo...

propose.line: ...Mhm, I have faith in you, Commander... I told the people in my dreams that I've found happiness and would do my best to live on for their sake as well... I'm truly... truly happy right now...

skill.line: Me too! I-I'll give it my best shot!

touch.line: Pl... please be gentle... I'm very susceptible to pain...

touch2.line: Mmh... *Whimper*...

unlock.line: I-I'm Juneau... I'm a cruiser... I'm scared of pain... *Sob* And I'm scared of you, Commander...!

upgrade.line: I'll... try to work harder...!

win_mvp.line: Phew... I almost got hit... *Sob*... I don't care about being the MVP... I'm just trying my best so I can come home in one piece...

battle.line: I'll do everything I can to make these peaceful days last forever...!

detail.line: Oh, the sun's reflection in that lake looks amazing! Commander, can we go have a closer– Eek! ...Ugh, sorry for that. I almost tripped there because I'm not used to walking in a dress. Thank you for catching me...!

drop_descrip.line: This swan is so soft and pettable... Heehee, it even let me put a ribbon on it. Now we have matching looks... Huh? You could take a picture of us? I-if it's not too much work then please, by all means!

expedition.line: Oops, I got completely distracted by the scenery... Commander, a commission just got completed!

home.line: You could rest on the bench if your feet are sore, Commander. I'll figure out where we should go next in the meanwhile!

login.line: I've heard the scenery out back is stunning too. Commander, I-I'd love to snap some pictures of it with you, if you don't mind.

main1.line: Having seen your gentle side and petted these swans, it feels like my scaredy-cat self is no longer, you know? Heehee.

main2.line: Thank you for telling me I look good in this! San Juan really deserves credit for helping me get through my anxiety preparing for this date, including picking out this dress.

main3.line: Not only do I get the date of my dreams, but I also get to be in a picture just with you... I'm an extremely lucky person, aren't I? Aw gosh...

mission.line: Excuse me, Commander, I think you have new missions. I'll try to do my part in them!

mission_complete.line: That's quite a lot of mission rewards! This should be enough to buy gifts for San Diego and my friends.

touch.line: Aren't these frills pretty? I really like them too...

touch2.line: Oh... Oh gosh...

unlock.line: This swan is so soft and pettable... Heehee, it even let me put a ribbon on it. Now we have matching looks... Huh? You could take a picture of us? I-if it's not too much work then please, by all means!

win_mvp.line: Heehee. The swan is happy for us.

battle.line: I'll probably be fine, even if submarines show up...

detail.line: I'll need some getting used to my improved gear... but I swear I won't be a liability!

drop_descrip.line: After all that painstaking work, I've f-finally managed to complete my retrofit! Even though I'm still afraid of getting hurt, I'll try to be brave for you, Commander!

expedition.line: E-excuse me, Commander... A commission was just completed...

home.line: Great work out there, Commander... Won't you please take me with you next time? I want to fight side-by-side with everyone else...

login.line: Good morning, Commander... I'd be happy to do anything I can to help.

main1.line: What can I do to make this war end sooner... Oh, Commander? Wh-what are you doing here?

main2.line: Seeing how the rest of the fleet fights gives me goosebumps... I hope I can be like them one day...!

main3.line: San Diego is leagues better than me, despite being my little sister... No, I can't think that way! I have to keep working at it!

touch.line: Is this a reward for the work I've done? Aww, thank you!

touch2.line: Eep! P-please be gentle with me...

unlock.line: After all that painstaking work, I've f-finally managed to complete my retrofit! Even though I'm still afraid of getting hurt, I'll try to be brave for you, Commander!

upgrade.line: I owe it all to you, Commander!

win_mvp.line: This is entirely thanks to you, Commander! I'm happy to be the MVP, but I'm just more relieved that the battle's over...

battle.line: Full speed ahead! ... Ah, that was close... I almost tripped...

detail.line: What's so interesting about this stuff? Let's go play instead~!

drop_descrip.line: Atlanta-class Light Cruiser – San Diego, Hull Number CL-53!

expedition.line: Commander, Commander! I think a commission's been completed!

feeling1.line: Don't come near me! Your stupidity is contagious!

feeling2.line: C'mon, Commander! Don't think too much, let's play!

feeling3.line: C'mon, Commander, let's have a race! Winner treats the loser to a snack!

feeling4.line: You often say mean stuff about me, but in reality you're actually having fun, aren't you~?

feeling5.line: I used to not really think about anything, but now all I can think about is you, Commander! ... Not that much has changed, though!

home.line: Commander, let's go get something duh-licious to eat!

hp_warning.line: They're actually trying to fight us?!

login.line: Hey, Commander, let's have an exciting water gun fight!

lose.line: Huh? Who's this? Where am I...? How did I lose?!

mail.line: Commander, new mail for you! Creases? N-no, I totally wasn't making paper planes out of your mail, okay?!

main1.line: Apparently people come looking for me after they've planted apple seeds... am I some kind of harvest god or something?!

main2.line: Battle stars? Are they really that amazing? I thought everyone had some?

main3.line: Come on, get motivated, now! Sit around like this and you'll go dumb!

mission.line: Bring on the missions, no matter how many there are!

mission_complete.line: Co-man-der! Look, look! We got some rewards!

profile.line: I'm San Diego! I've heard I'm second only to Enterprise for the most stars earned! ... I don't really know what a "star" is, but it sounds cool! What is it, Commander? ... A-merry-car? Is that some kind of secret code?

propose.line: Commander, I'm not dumb, I can tell that one's a fake! ...Huh? It's real?! Then does that mean... you're serious about this...?

skill.line: I'm not sure what's going on, but let's do it~!

touch.line: Hey, what are you looking for?

touch2.line: Hey, not so fast you pervert!

unlock.line: Hello~! I'm San Diego, the cruiser who earned the most stars in World War 2! Hehe, that's it for my introduction! I'm just too good!

upgrade.line: It feels like I got a little smarter!

win_mvp.line: I was just getting warmed up... Why are they surrendering already?

drop_descrip.line: Merry Christmas! Super idol San Diego, making her dazzling debut! Commander, you must come to my performance! ...Venue?! What's that?

main1.line: That's strange, why's the microphone cord getting shorter and shorter?

main2.line: I don't really get it, but if I work hard, it'll be A-O-K!

main3.line: Commander, wanna sing a few songs as well? Ehehe, here, here! Wooaahh! (CRASH) W-who tripped me?

touch.line: The smartest person is the one who is the happiest! Ehehe, that's why San Diego is the smartest!

unlock.line: Merry Christmas! Super idol San Diego, making her dazzling debut! Commander, you must come to my performance! ...Venue?! What's that?

battle.line: San Diego, moving out! Go, go, go!

detail.line: Is my June bride look just the bestest or what!

drop_descrip.line: Commander, with the power of your love, San Diego is sure to become number one in this port! ...Number one in what? I'm not really sure myself, but I'll definitely make it happen!

feeling5.line: It's kinda weird, but I get this feeling like thinking of you makes me grow stronger, Commander! Wait, doesn't that mean I'm gonna change eventually? Nope! 'Cause I'm gonna be your number one!

home.line: Welcome back, Commander! Your sweetie San Diego's been waiting for you!

login.line: I've already finished today's work and did it all in a flash! Now c'mon, it's time to have fun!

main1.line: So, Commander! You mind having tonight's dinner microwaved? Is the bath at 50 degrees all cool with you? Don't answer, 'cause San Diego went and did it all already!

main2.line: Man, San Juan's such a worrywart~ I'll be just fine, 'cause I've got you, Commander! Everything's gonna be right as rain!

main3.line: I'll cheerlead for you, Commander! Hip, hip, hooray! One, two, three! Whoop-de-doo!

touch.line: Feel my Commander-smartifying sparkly beam!

touch2.line: Whoa, whoa, whoa!

unlock.line: Commander, with the power of your love, San Diego is sure to become number one in this port! ...Number one in what? I'm not really sure myself, but I'll definitely make it happen!

win_mvp.line: Woohoo! San Diego's number one!

drop_descrip.line: Heheh~☆ I have no idea what just happened, but I feel like I've gotten super strong! Commander, can you see my sparkly aura~?

home.line: Hokay, let's do this, Commander! ... Huh? You just got done?!

login.line: Hey, Commander! Let Super-Smart Sandy handle all your work for today! It'll be done before you can say "no thanks"!

main1.line: Let's have a race, Commander! I'll be both your opponent and the referee!

main2.line: Lalala la la~! Sing along with me, Sara!

main3.line: You look bummed out, Commander~ How about we turn that frown right upside down?

touch.line: Can you feel my smartifying sparkly aura too, Commander~?

unlock.line: Heheh~☆ I have no idea what just happened, but I feel like I've gotten super strong! Commander, can you see my sparkly aura~?

battle.line: I'm in a hurry... just come at me all at once, alright?

detail.line: I'm confident in myself!

drop_descrip.line: Cleveland-class Light Cruiser – Cleveland, Hull Number CL-55!

expedition.line: Hehe, it's about time we reap the rewards of that commission, Commander!

feeling1.line: Sorry, my sisters are waiting for me. I don't have time to deal with you.

feeling2.line: What is, Commander? Something troubling you? I've got lots of little sisters, so I'm used to giving them my shoulder to lean on. So if anything's got you down, just tell me.

feeling3.line: Mm... I'm not trying to make myself look stronger than I am or anything, but honestly, I think there aren't many people like you who I can speak to like an equal...

feeling4.line: Before I realized it, I'm the one who's leaning on your shoulder instead... but hey, that's fine. We can always just rely on each other.

feeling5.line: I feel like I've told you everything about myself... Time sure flies, doesn't it... I doubt someone who understands me the way you do will ever show up again. That's why I've...

home.line: Ah, Commander, let me give you a massage... Just bear with me!

login.line: Hey, Commander! You seem to be in a good mood today!

lose.line: Ahaha... this isn't so good...

mail.line: Some new mail just arrived. You sure are popular, Commander!

main1.line: Never regret the choices you make!

main2.line: Why do you call me "Clevebro"?! I'm a girl, just like the others!

main3.line: You know, I like trees. Let's grow a bonsai, Commander!

mission.line: We've got a new mission! Let's finish it in one go!

mission_complete.line: Nice! We got some mission rewards!

profile.line: I'm the big sister of the Cleveland-class... but I guess that's obvious from my name alone. I fought through the Battle of Renelle Island, the Battle of Empress Augusta Bay, plus many others, and I earned around 13 battle stars, so I'm pretty strong!

propose.line: Heh, I had a feeling this would happen! From now on, you can tell me anything. I'll take excellent care of you!

touch.line: Wanna exercise for a bit?

touch2.line: You can't do this sorta stuff in public, Commander...

unlock.line: Pleasure meeting you, Commander! I'm Cleveland, a knight of the sea! Come on, time is money! We can't afford to take a break!

upgrade.line: Hehe, that feels good!

win_mvp.line: Hehe, now this is what I'd call the fruits of my hard labor!

drop_descrip.line: There's room for two on this pumpkin. C'mon, hurry and get on... Ah, that reminds me! I've got some pumpkin pie as well. Wanna try some, Commander?

main1.line: Heheh~ Gimme some candy!

main2.line: Time is money, Commander! ... Or so I would say, but even I want to spend some of it every now and then.

main3.line: If we the plow the fields now and add some fertilizer... then by next year's Halloween we can eat some homegrown pumpkins! Let's do it!

touch.line: Do you wanna try some of the pumpkin pie that Helena made?

touch2.line: Well made, don't you think? Heh, I've heard this thing can even harvest souls.

unlock.line: There's room for two on this pumpkin. C'mon, hurry and get on... Ah, that reminds me! I've got some pumpkin pie as well. Wanna try some, Commander?

battle.line: Let's finish this in a flash!

detail.line: Ah, don't you worry, Commander. Your invitation's got top priority to me.

drop_descrip.line: Why am I stuck with this tuxedo when everyone else is wearing a dress?! ... Though it does feel slick, so I guess it's pretty nice. So, weren't we gonna go to the party, Commander? Then it's about time we head out!

feeling5.line: Honestly, what with how people treat me when I wear this tuxedo, for a moment I considered acting more like a boy... But nah! In the end, it's obvious nothing beats being with you, Commander!

home.line: Let me join for the next sortie, Commander. It's not my style to just sit on my butt and wait around!

login.line: Ready yet, Commander? It's time to go to the party!

mail.line: Hm? You brought the Commander's mail, Knight? Aren't you a clever dog! Good boy!

main1.line: You wanna come to the party too, Knight? All right... you're coming, too!

main2.line: Quite a few people have asked me for a dance, but I'm not a great dancer... Commander, could ya help me learn the basics of dancing?

main3.line: *Phew*... You wanna go for something to eat when the party's over, Commander? I'll treat you, so don't be shy! I mean come on, we're friends~

mission.line: Commander, let's wrap up those missions pronto before the party starts!

skill.line: Here's a present for you party poopers!

touch.line: What's up, Knight? ... A rose...? Just what I needed! Here, Commander. A little gift from me to you, darling.

unlock.line: Why am I stuck with this tuxedo when everyone else is wearing a dress?! ... Though it does feel slick, so I guess it's pretty nice. So, weren't we gonna go to the party, Commander? Then it's about time we head out!

detail.line: What kind of music do you like, Commander? I've gotta have the stuff that gets you pumped up.

drop_descrip.line: Good timing! I was just about to take my little buddy here out for a road trip! Commander, there's room for two if you want to come!

home.line: Let's go outside and get some stretching in, Commander~

login.line: Ready to go, Commander? We're about to go chase the wind!

main1.line: I did this guy's paint job myself. Pretty sweet, huh? Hehe~

main2.line: Don't let the size fool you. This little guy has some serious kick!

main3.line: Even when we're out for a spin, we have to observe the traffic rules. Safety first, after all~

touch.line: Commander, you should pick out a bike too! Just leave the paint job to me, hehe!

unlock.line: Good timing! I was just about to take my little buddy here out for a road trip! Commander, there's room for two if you want to come!

detail.line: Woahh... In the Sakura Empire, if you lose at a game of hanetsuki, they draw all over your face with a marker... Never knew that...

drop_descrip.line: Happy New Year's, Commander! I heard everyone from the Sakura Empire was dressing like this, so... Hehehe, think this looks good on me? I thought I'd ask for your impression first, Commander.

home.line: Ahh, Denver, wait up! Didn't we agree that the loser has to do the winner's bidding...?!

login.line: Hehe, Commander, how about a hanetsuki match?

main1.line: Next time, I won't lose to the Sendai sisters! That's why, hehe... Commander, glad you're going to be my practice partner!

main2.line: The bonsai tree I planted last year doesn't seem to have grown much... I'll have to tend to it better this year.

main3.line: It's hard to move around in this outfit... how do the Sakura girls make it look so effortless?

touch.line: Helena was the one who drew the design on this paddle. Hehe, isn't it sweet?

touch2.line: C-Commander... even if it's the New Year's, people are going to stare...

unlock.line: Happy New Year's, Commander! I heard everyone from the Sakura Empire was dressing like this, so... Hehehe, think this looks good on me? I thought I'd ask for your impression first, Commander.

detail.line: What things influence your decision on where to travel, Commander? For me, it's the opportunity to see spectacular sights and exotic plants!

drop_descrip.line: Isn't it real exciting visiting a place you don't normally get to go? We don't often get opportunities to travel like this, so let's go look for delicious food and spectacular scenery!

home.line: Nice job, Commander! Sit down and have a break while I sort through photos to upload to my Juustagram! I can't wait to see how all my followers react~

login.line: Yo! Commander! Get over here! We don't have all day. If we wanna see as many things as possible, we gotta make the most of our time!

main1.line: The coral reefs and the huge rock formations are easily the highlights so far. They really make you appreciate the beauty of Mother Nature!

main2.line: Koalas, kangaroos, quokkas... Hm? Why'd they name this bandicoot "Crash"?

main3.line: Mmm, this place makes killer steaks! Better not post this on Juustagram though, or Yuudachi will get jealous and complain 'cause she doesn't get any.

touch.line: Here's your bus ticket, Commander. Let's hop on and go to the next sightseeing spot!

touch2.line: The mood is there, but there's onlookers around, so... yeah.

unlock.line: Isn't it real exciting visiting a place you don't normally get to go? We don't often get opportunities to travel like this, so let's go look for delicious food and spectacular scenery!

detail.line: Facing the full ensemble gets me feeling kinda nervous... Then again, I guess I have it easier than them, 'cause they have to face the audience for the whole performance.

drop_descrip.line: Ahem... I, Cleveland, am your conductor for tonight! Whoa, the echo really IS faint! How did I not know we had such a fancy concert hall at the port? ...Oh, you wanna shout something too, Commander?

home.line: Whew... Oh, you'll gimme a massage? My shoulders ARE pretty stiff after all that baton waving, so... Yeah, go on ahead! Heehee~

login.line: Came to watch me practice? Heh, alright, you can be part of my orchestra. Just take a seat right in front of me!

main1.line: One, two, three, four... Nice! I think I've got quadruple meter pinned down. Now triple meter... Something like this?

main2.line: Some conductors get so in the zone that their gestures get all crazy. Don't think I'd do that, though. Ahahahah...

main3.line: If I wanted to make an orchestra out of the whole Cleveland class... Nahhh, there's not enough of us. If we add the Fletcher class in the mix... Then we'd get the opposite problem.

touch.line: You wanna feel how it's like to stand at the podium?

touch2.line: Whoa, Commander! Stop frickin' distracting me!

unlock.line: Ahem... I, Cleveland, am your conductor for tonight! Whoa, the echo really IS faint! How did I not know we had such a fancy concert hall at the port? ...Oh, you wanna shout something too, Commander?

battle.line: This time, I fight for the commander!

detail.line: Anything I worry about? Nothing at all. ...Actually, I shouldn't keep things secret from you! Not that I could even if I wanted to. Hahahah!

drop_descrip.line: Man, this is so embarrassing... C-Commander, w-w-what do you, umm, like, think of my d-d-d-dress...?

feeling5.line: To think I'd ever get to put on these clothes and spend my joyful time with the person I love... (Hug) I guess being a girl really is pretty sweet. Hehehe~

home.line: Okay, just leave everything to me! I know just how much force to put into my grip to make you feel good!

login.line: I was just thinking you'd be back soon, and here you are! Maybe we share a telepathic link through our hearts! Hehehe~♪

mail.line: Here's your mail. Give it a look later.

main1.line: Anything you wanna do, or anything on your mind? You can tell me anything♪

main2.line: How happy you make me feel? Hmm, I feel as happy as the ocean feels big, I guess? Hehehe~

main3.line: You're worried about people meddling with us? Hehe, there's no point worrying about that stuff when we have each other!

touch.line: I've never cuddled with someone like this before... It might take some getting used to, but I still like it. Hehehe~

touch2.line: N-no probs! I'm ready for this! So just go ahead and, umm, y-you know...

unlock.line: Man, this is so embarrassing... C-Commander, w-w-what do you, umm, like, think of my d-d-d-dress...?

battle.line: Dang, guess I've got no choice! I'll show you the might of us Southerners!

detail.line: You wanna get to know me? Sure thing. Inspect me to your heart's content.

drop_descrip.line: Cleveland-class light cruiser – Columbia, hull number CL-56.

expedition.line: The commission team's back! Aren't you gonna go thank them?

feeling1.line: *Sigh*... So that's all, huh. I was wrong to get my hopes up.

feeling2.line: Commander, it's sunny outside, so why don't we go for a walk? It's unhealthy to stay indoors all the time!

feeling3.line: Hm? You'd never have guessed that I'd be into ballet? ... What's that supposed to mean?! Laugh one more time and I'll punch you!

feeling4.line: Why do I wear only one sock? That's a secret! If you're so curious, try taking it off~ Hehehe♪

feeling5.line: When I can't see you on my days off, I feel kinda lonely... Geez, look at you, making a girl say stuff like this! A-aren't you ashamed of yourself?! Jerk!

home.line: You're back~! I've been chewing on this gum so long it's lost all its taste.

hp_warning.line: It won't end like this!

login.line: Another day of calm weather! Nice!

lose.line: Darn it... Reckless bunch of...

mail.line: Aren't you gonna check your mail? There might be something nice in there.

main1.line: What tunes do I listen to? Good question. See if you can guess! ... Rock 'n' roll? Bzzzt, wrong!

main2.line: Bleh, my sis snatched my sunglasses again...

main3.line: Once this war is over, maybe I should give Eagle Union football a try...

mission.line: I only just started chewing this gum, and we've already got a new mission...?

mission_complete.line: Today's missions were a breeze! Total walk in the park!

profile.line: Hiii! It's me, the girl who scooted through the Pacific and earned 10 battle stars: Columbia! Hey, now, no need to sing my praises, go see Cleveland and sing hers instead! Need anything else? Alright, then I'll get back to patrolling.

propose.line: Yeah... thanks. Even when we're not on the battlefield, we'll always be together... No, wait, cheesy lines like this are totally out of character for me! Anyhow, right now, I feel so happy!

skill.line: Don't blame me if you get hit!

touch.line: Gee, thanks! You made my bubble pop!

touch2.line: Commander, is it this star on my shirt you like? Or is it... what's underneath it~?

unlock.line: Cleveland-class light cruiser number 2, Columbia! That's me~! Not the Columbia in D.C., the one in South Carolina! Geez, listen to me! Not the Columbia with Bogotá as its capital!

upgrade.line: Uh-huh, feelin' pretty good!

win_mvp.line: That was nothing special~ I do it all the time~

detail.line: I wonder why Cleve suddenly started to make chocolate for everyone this year... Well, knowing her, I'm sure it's just her way of looking out after us.

drop_descrip.line: Commander, here, I made some chocolate for you~ Come on, hurry up and take it already! Holding this pose makes me look like I'm waiting for some knight in shining armor, and it's super embarrassing.

home.line: Commander, how much chocolate did you get today? ...Oh, you don't have to answer that. I was just curious.

login.line: The ever-popular commander must be busy today, right? After all, this day only comes around once a year~ Anyway, best of luck out there~

main1.line: What, this sketch? Just a little doodle I made during class. What do you think? Looks like her, doesn't it?

main2.line: There's a rule at my school that you're not allowed to chew gum during class. I get it and all, but isn't that a total drag?

main3.line: I'm actually wearing two socks today? ...You pay attention to the weirdest stuff~

touch.line: I'm looking forward to what you'll give me on White Day~

touch2.line: Commander, are you that interested in my school badge~? Or~ perhaps~ something~ else~?

unlock.line: Commander, here, I made some chocolate for you~ Come on, hurry up and take it already! Holding this pose makes me look like I'm waiting for some knight in shining armor, and it's super embarrassing.

battle.line: Feast your eyes! This is the power of a Cleveland-class cruiser!

detail.line: Wonder what Cleve's up to right now... No doubt she's doing just great, but still, wish I could see her for myself.

drop_descrip.line: ...Mm, that's good enough for today's journal entry. Wonder what Cleve's gonna think after reading this~ What do you think, Commander? Wait... Commander? Jeez, don't wander off when I'm all focused on my writing...

home.line: Welcome back. I went and made some soup with the ingredients you foraged. Wanna taste it?

login.line: There you are, Commander. I've been looking everywhere for you! ...You were out foraging for food? Oh, thanks...

main1.line: As someone who's been all over the Pacific, I'm having the time of my life exploring the open prairie! Especially with you along for the ride~

main2.line: Crap, my gum reserves are almost empty! ...You brought extra just for me? Aww, thanks a ton, buddy!

main3.line: Y'know what a prairie at night is perfect for? Stargazing! Come nighttime, you wanna lie with me in the grass and look through the telescope?

touch.line: What am I writing about? It's a secret, so you'll just have to guess~

touch2.line: Are you getting all touchy-feely 'cause I'm wearing socks on both feet today? Or is it... something else~?

unlock.line: ...Mm, that's good enough for today's journal entry. Wonder what Cleve's gonna think after reading this~ What do you think, Commander? Wait... Commander? Jeez, don't wander off when I'm all focused on my writing...

win_mvp.line: That was easy! Didn't even break a sweat.

battle.line: Alrighty, let's do some warm-ups!

detail.line: Commander, do you need anything? You can always chat with me if you're free.

drop_descrip.line: Omaha-class light cruiser - Richmond, Hull Number CL-9!

expedition.line: Commander, you can stare at me all day if you want, but just know that a commission has been completed.

feeling1.line: Seems like I have to find another place...

feeling2.line: I've been to a lot of places, but this is the first time I've ever seen a fleet with girls from all around the world. This is so interesting!

feeling3.line: Commander~ I only just joined this fleet and there's still plenty I don't know yet. So, could I ask you to accompany me on a short walk?

feeling4.line: This fleet is great! And you're awesome too, Commander! Let me tell you about myself... First thing: after that World War just before this one, I was...

feeling5.line: Commander, I've seen a lot during my time in this world, but there's still one thing I haven't experienced yet since I don't have a partner...

home.line: You look so cool coming right off the battlefield, Commander!

login.line: Commander, did you do anything interesting while you were away for so long? You should bring me along next time~!

lose.line: Oh no, we lost... Well that sucks~

mail.line: Commander, I checked the mail box and brought your mail along with my own~

main1.line: Commander, you've got something on your lips... Got it!

main2.line: I'd love to be able to see everyone from all over the world~!

main3.line: Lots of my sisters have survived through this war. Impressive, right?

mission.line: ♪Mission here, mission there♪ Being a commander is so much work. Let me help you!

mission_complete.line: Teehee~ Our rewards have arrived, Commander! ... Or would you rather get a passionate hug from me instead?

profile.line: I'm Richmond of the Omaha-class. Because I'm an old model, I was mainly tasked with things like escorts and transport. Although my performance is nothing to brag about, you can say that I've seen a lot of action! Feel free to ask me anything whenever you have questions~!

propose.line: That's right, I was talking about love! ... And the things that follow! I've never met a suitable candidate, at least until I met you~! When I accept this, it'll mean you agree to be my partner as well, right~?

skill.line: Let me show you what a difference experience makes!

touch.line: Do you like getting physical too, Commander?

touch2.line: Com~man~der~

unlock.line: Hi! Are you the commander? That's great~! I'm Richmond. Hit me up whenever you feel like~!

upgrade.line: Teehee~ This feels good~

win_mvp.line: Teamwork makes the dream work! Yay!

battle.line: All I need to do is get rid of these guys, right?

detail.line: Maintenance? Fine, as long as you don't do anything weird...

drop_descrip.line: Brooklyn-class Light Cruiser – Honolulu, Hull Number CL-48!

expedition.line: What are you waiting for... A commission's been completed!

feeling1.line: So that's who you are, huh, Commander?

feeling2.line: Do I really need to chat with you...? But I guess I don't have anything else to do, so I'll keep you company for a while.

feeling3.line: I think people are jealous of me because mine are bigger than theirs… But personally I wish they were smaller. When they're big, you know, it's pretty inconvenient...

feeling4.line: I don't really have anything going for me outside of my body, but you're still being so nice to me... Do you like my body THAT much? Even if you don't, it's not like I... No, I'll stop myself right there, because otherwise you'll just get carried away.

feeling5.line: ... Didn't I tell you they're not this big just because I wanted them to be? Well, if you like them that much... then maybe they're not so bad...

home.line: Good work. What, are you not satisfied until I say something mean?

login.line: Why do I have to wait for you here...

lose.line: I don't want to go to Mare Island again...

mail.line: Here, mail for you. What? I can at least do something this simple for you...

main1.line: I don't seem very Hawaiian even though my name is Honolulu? Well gee, my bad...

main2.line: Helena's always acting so gloomy... You should think of ways to make her smile too, Commander.

main3.line: I was born with this personality. I don't hate you or anything like that...

mission.line: If you have the time to stare at me, how about you go finish your remaining missions?

mission_complete.line: What, you don't even want your rewards?

profile.line: I'm Honolulu of the Brooklyn-class. I've basically only ever served in the Pacific. I was damaged pretty bad once, but somehow I managed to make it... At least I was luckier than Helena...

propose.line: This is really embarrassing, so could we just get this over with... Y-you can do whatever you want when it's just the two of us...

skill.line: This time things should go well...!

touch.line: Do you just go around touching everyone you see? Do you need anything?

touch2.line: *Sigh*... If you're gonna be this direct then I don't even feel like getting mad at you...

unlock.line: Brooklyn-class, Honolulu, reporting in. Hey, listen... could you stop staring at me like that? It's not like they're this big because I wanted them to be...

upgrade.line: I didn't really ask you for this...

win_mvp.line: Is that enough for you?

detail.line: Y-you want to eat lunch together? Really? I bet you're just teasing me. Or are you... just hoping to get a taste of Helena's cooking?

drop_descrip.line: If everyone's focusing on the teacher, they probably won't stare at me from up front... As for the umbrella, it's... I know it makes me stand out, but I don't want people to stare at me from behind either...

home.line: Don't say you'll "see me after school"... O-or else I'll just stay behind...

main1.line: I made a friend at school. He's brown, cuddly, and doesn't say a word, though...

main2.line: There's nobody who's like you at school. Nobody who sometimes makes me laugh, sometimes makes me cry, and sometimes... Gosh, what am I saying...

main3.line: nil

touch.line: It's small, but it's the only umbrella I could find. S-so, when 2 people are sharing it... i-it's only natural they'd have to stand so close together...

touch2.line: I-I don't have anything going for me besides my bust anyway...

unlock.line: If everyone's focusing on the teacher, they probably won't stare at me from up front... As for the umbrella, it's... I know it makes me stand out, but I don't want people to stare at me from behind either...

battle.line: If I get rid of everyone who saw me... then I won't have anything to be embarrassed about!

detail.line: Commander, you're the one who messed with my cannons, didn't you? A-admit it! Admit it while you still have the chance...

drop_descrip.line: Aaaahh! My sundae! What's up with this stupid hose?! Commander, don't just stand there, help me!

home.line: C-Commander, umm, do you wanna take a cold shower...?

main1.line: *Gasp*! Where the heck is all this water coming from?!

main2.line: Commander, you don't sound convincing at all when you tell me my swimsuit is cute while you're laughing!

main3.line: *Sob*... Everyone's going to laugh at me...

touch.line: You called over Helena?! This is NOT the way I want to make her laugh!

touch2.line: How could you, Commander... I'll hose you till you're as soaked as I am!

unlock.line: Aaaahh! My sundae! What's up with this stupid hose?! Commander, don't just stand there, help me!

win_mvp.line: Today was your unlucky day... because I'm in a REALLY bad mood!

detail.line: "Special Christmas lingerie"... I never should've listened to Louis! I need to put on this whole costume quick, before someone sees me...!

drop_descrip.line: Stupid Louis... "If you dress up as a reindeer for Christmas, you'll have an easy time talking to Helena"... You think I'm stupid enough to believe that...?! *Eeeeeek*?! C-Commander?! Get out, right now!

feeling5.line: *Sigh*... "Go visit the Commander and say 'I'm your present~!'"... That's ridiculous, the Commander would never like this stupid costu... D-did you just hear that?!

home.line: Commander?! You sure chose an awfully convenient time to come back!

login.line: C-Commander! You did that on purpose, didn't you?!

lose.line: They're staring at me... They're staring at me...!

mail.line: Your mail? Oh no... I forgot which box I put it in...

main1.line: *Sigh*... Just thinking about that idiot standing behind me with a straight face makes all my motivation go away...

main2.line: I-I tripped just a moment ago, and these ribbons got all tangled up around me... Ahahaha, I'm such a klutz... What are the ribbons for...? U-uhh...

main3.line: That's a wonderful Christmas tree...? T-thanks... Hey, hold on, don't you have anything else to say?!

touch.line: My plans for Christmas? Um, let's see... Hey, hold on, why are you asking that with a straight face to someone who's dressed like this?!

touch2.line: *Eek*?! Commander, when did you get here...?!

unlock.line: Stupid Louis... "If you dress up as a reindeer for Christmas, you'll have an easier time talking to Helena"... You think I'm stupid enough to believe someth...? *Eeeeeek*?! C-Commander?! Get out, right now!

battle.line: Let's get this over with quick, I wanna go back to the festival...!

detail.line: Wh-what are you staring at me for... Is it weird to have fun at a festival now...?

drop_descrip.line: Come on, Louis, the goldfish stall is this way! ... W-why are you giving me that weird look like th– Wait... Eeeek! C-Commander?! When did you get here?!

feeling5.line: *Sigh*, why can't I ever keep my composure in front of you... "What am I murmuring about"...? N-nothing! I didn't say a word...! Dummy...!

home.line: Do you want this...? Here, take it...

login.line: I'll say this now: I don't like festivals in any... Ah, you know what, never mind! Just come with me, okay?!

lose.line: After all that trouble putting this on... This sucks...

main1.line: Stupid Louis... She just went "I'd rather not be kicked by a horse" and walked off... Let's just forget about her... Commander, do you want... some fried squid?

main2.line: Y-you saw how flustered I was just now, didn't you... I don't hate you or anything like that, you know...

main3.line: Goldfish scooping is pretty hard... Could you lend me a hand, Commander? I want one to give to Helena...!

touch.line: Seems there'll be a fireworks display by the harbor... Commander, how about we go there on our walk?

touch2.line: Don't make excuses... I know you did that on purpose...!

unlock.line: Come on, Louis, the goldfish stall is this way! ... W-why are you giving me that weird look like th– Wait... Eeeek! C-Commander?! When did you get here?!

win_mvp.line: Can we go back now, Commander?

battle.line: Did you hear that? That was the sound of the Winds of Fortune!

detail.line: Unlike those Sakura Empire ships, I don't bring any misfortune to my allies. Probably… I hope…

drop_descrip.line: Brooklyn-class Light Cruiser – St. Louis, Hull Number CL-49!

expedition.line: Hmm... Okay, I'll go greet the returning commission team with these clothes.

feeling1.line: At least spare Helena...

feeling2.line: Things might have gone differently at Kolombangara, had Helena been there...

feeling3.line: Want me to help you clean your office, Commander? ... You don't!?

feeling4.line: Hehe~ I know about all the secret things you have hidden in your room, Commander~!

feeling5.line: Whew… Cleaning is always such a pain… Hey, why don't we go on a date somewhere, Commander?

home.line: Always remember: "the feud chair is unpredictable"… Hmm, I heard that from someone, but who…?

hp_warning.line: Hehe... my luck is second to none!

login.line: Luck never stays with one person for too long, Commander. We should make the best use of it while we still have it.

lose.line: Today is not my lucky day…

mail.line: New mail? It must be good news!

main1.line: What are you looking at, Commander?

main2.line: Helena, your SG radar can't detect underwater threats.

main3.line: Arizona, even if you'll never forget what happened that day, you shouldn't let it wear you down so much.

mission.line: Hey, Commander, you should prepare yourself for a real surprise.

mission_complete.line: Hehe... You're so spoiled, Commander... Okay, before you go and collect those rewards, you can stay here for a while and rest if you want.

profile.line: I'm St. Louis, Helena's big sister. I got my nickname, Lucky Lou, from getting through the attack on Pearl Harbor unscathed. After that, however, my missions didn't go all that well. I guess luck really does come and go after all...

propose.line: Oh dear, why are you giving me a present all of a sudden... Ah, I see, it's one of these... Okay, could I ask you to put it on my finger for me, Commander?

touch.line: You get good luck if you touch me? I've never heard of that before.

touch2.line: This isn't something you should do outside, Co-man-der~

unlock.line: Hello, I'm St. Louis, but I'm called Lucky Lou. Hey, Commander, don't you think it's your lucky day, finding me like this?

upgrade.line: Luck comes and goes. You can't depend on in it forever.

win_mvp.line: Hehe~ That wasn't all thanks to luck.

drop_descrip.line: What do you think of this foreign dress, Commander? *Giggle* ...Perhaps it's rekindled something within you?

main1.line: How I wish I could bring this chair with me on sorties... Helena, could you help upgrade my rigging?

main2.line: I am Lucky Lou. I may not look like it, but I actually have experience with fortune-telling.

main3.line: Brr... It's actually a bit cold... Commander, could you come a little closer and... share your body heat with me?

touch2.line: Oh, do you mean I've put it on wrong? Have I really...?

unlock.line: What do you think of this foreign dress, Commander? *Giggle* ...Perhaps it's rekindled something within you?

drop_descrip.line: The Sakura Empire's clothes are just so refined. Ahaha... Aren't you cold standing out there, Commander? Sit down with me and have a drink.

feeling5.line: Hmm... seems it'll keep snowing for a while. Why don't you stay for the night, Commander? ...Oh? I was thinking we could share some drinks, but perhaps you had something else in mind? Ahahah♡

home.line: Welcome back. I've put on the heater for you. Oh, me? I'd like to stay here and enjoy the snow a little longer.

login.line: You should drink a little something to warm yourself up before getting to work.

main1.line: A "hatsumode," huh... Do you have any wishes to make, Commander? It so happens I don't, so you can have my wish.

main2.line: Not to say the Eagle Union's new year celebrations are lonesome, but the Sakura Empire's and Dragon Empery definitely celebrate New Year's with more festivity. And I like festivities.

main3.line: Oh, Commander, if you're hoping to get me drunk... well, it depends on how much you yourself can drink. Ahahah~

touch.line: Are we heading out? Ahah, then let me get out my umbrella. Hey, come closer, otherwise you'll get snow on your clothes.

unlock.line: The Sakura Empire's clothes are just so refined. Ahaha... Aren't you cold standing out there, Commander? Sit down with me and have a drink.

detail.line: Hehehe, you thought I'd drive in these high heels? It's certainly not impossible, but I'd rather use the other pair of shoes I have inside.

drop_descrip.line: Oh my, what a good little commander you've been, waiting here all this time for me. Hop in~ Did you think you would be driving? Hehe, you shouldn't underestimate me~

feeling5.line: As much as I like parties, I like being alone with you even more, Commander... Maybe we could sneak out and go for a drive together? But probably not~ Hehehe~

home.line: Do you have everything, Commander? We're not driving back if you forgot to bring something.

login.line: The view here is lovely~ Let's pull over for a moment to take in the winds of good luck.

mail.line: Helena messaged me, saying the party's starting soon. Check your mail, then let's hurry on back to the venue.

main1.line: Oh dear, was that... Jamaica? Hehehe... Fasten your seatbelt, Commander. This'll be a bit of a wild ride.

main2.line: You want to use my car? You can, of course, but promise me one thing in return: take Honolulu on a nice trip.

main3.line: Whew... Finally we've arrived at the party. Now, Commander, wait here for thirty minutes while I reapply my makeup. Relax, I'm just joking! Hehehe~

mission.line: You have an urgent mission? I'll wait another five minutes for you, then.

mission_complete.line: Oh, you went and claimed those mission rewards? You could've taken your time if you wanted. Hehehe~

touch.line: Let's see here... Ah, thanks, Commander. Hehehe, you're getting quite good at this.

unlock.line: Oh my, what a good little commander you've been, waiting here all this time for me. Hop in~ Did you think you would be driving? Hehe, you shouldn't underestimate me~

battle.line: Knights of the Sea, onwards!

detail.line: Big sis! ... Oh, it's you. Need something?

drop_descrip.line: Cleveland-class light cruiser – Montpelier, hull number CL-57.

expedition.line: A commission's done. Aren't you gonna welcome the team back?

feeling1.line: Guess my big sis can't tell good and bad people apart...

feeling2.line: I don't get why my big sis chose you. But I trust her intuition.

feeling3.line: My big sis is... strong, cool, has a golden smile, and she could probably beat anyone in a fight... I want to be like her one day.

feeling4.line: I used to think commanding was just about giving orders from a comfy room while sounding like a bigshot... But after seeing it for myself, now I understand. You have a tough job, Commander.

feeling5.line: I don't just blindly listen to everything my big sis says. I listen because she's always right... And I finally get why she chose you. It's because you're outstanding.

home.line: Well done. You should get some rest.

hp_warning.line: Big sis told me... to never give up!

login.line: So, you're back. I'll take my leave, then. It's too crowded in here for me.

lose.line: Big sis... I'm sorry... I've stained the reputation of the Knights of the Sea...

mail.line: I left your mail over here.

main1.line: How can I be more like Cleveland... "Smile"? ... That might not be possible...

main2.line: I don't get along with anyone but my sisters. As for you, Commander... I'll try.

main3.line: Commander, I'm curious: when my sister's doing secretary work, what's she like?

mission.line: Commander, we've got a mission. Time's money... get going already.

mission_complete.line: Rewards, eh... Guess this is part of my job. I'll go get them.

profile.line: Listen, the Cleveland-class were the most powerful cruisers the Eagle Union had in the war. You should show more respect for my big sis. ... Me? I was in the battles of Midway, Augusta Bay, and a few others. I guess I did okay.

propose.line: Big sis told me to follow my heart. Which is why I'm here: to follow my heart. Are you following yours, Commander?

touch.line: ... Huh? If you've no need of me, don't call for me.

touch2.line: G-gotta put up with it... This is obviously a test of the trust I have for my big sis...!

unlock.line: You're a commander? You don't... look reliable. But my big sis works for you... I've no choice, then. Montpelier, reporting for duty. I don't really care whether you give me orders or not.

upgrade.line: I'm one step closer to my big sis...!

win_mvp.line: This is how victory feels... Not bad.

detail.line: The Sakura Empire's New Year's celebration is... a bit different from my expectations.

drop_descrip.line: So this is Sakura-style New Year's attire... If Cleve was also interested in this... Hm? Commander, were you watching? Um, well, Happy New Year's.

feeling5.line: Spending the end of the year with you isn't so bad... You really still want to see me dance in this outfit? Hmm... I'm probably a bit rusty, but let's just consider it a rehearsal for when I'm doing this for Cleve.

main1.line: The sleeves on this outfit are long and heavy... and this, uh... dress? It's really hard to move around in. Don't they find this cumbersome?

main2.line: If Cleve was to wear this outfit... Hmm, I can't picture it after all.

main3.line: My New Year's wish...? I'd like to get a bit closer with Cleve, I suppose...

touch.line: ...You'd like to see me dance in this outfit? Commander, you're as prone to flights of fancy as always.

touch2.line: Everyone is hard at work preparing for New Year's... but what in the world is going on inside that head of yours?

unlock.line: So this is Sakura-style New Year's attire... If Cleve was also interested in this... Hm? Commander, were you watching? Um, well, Happy New Year's.

detail.line: This set really is expertly made. It shocked me when I first laid eyes on it.

drop_descrip.line: As unreliable as you are, I didn't think you'd be too scared to approach a movie prop... You're just "admiring it from a distance?" ...Fair enough.

home.line: Time to go back to the party? All right. Give me a moment to come down.

login.line: "Welcome back, darling." ...This feels wrong. Doesn't fit the scene.

main1.line: I'm only wearing this dress because big sis told me to. It's the total opposite of the clothes I'm used to wearing... Hm? That's not the point of this all?

main2.line: Change my pose? Okay. How's this? ...I have no clue what you think is so funny about this. Guess it doesn't matter as long as big sis is enjoying herself...

main3.line: Wanna sit next to me? This thing is built to handle several people.

touch.line: No thanks. I can get down on my own. The set isn't a hard climb or anything, I'm just not used to wearing this dress.

touch2.line: Are you that keen to taste the power of darkness?

unlock.line: As unreliable as you are, I didn't think you'd be too scared to approach a movie prop... You're just "admiring it from a distance?" ...Fair enough.

win_mvp.line: "Kneel to the power of darkness!" ...Is it cooler to recite this line from the script?

battle.line: All the stars in the sky are our enemies! Everyone, fiiiiire!

detail.line: Commander, what do you do for your own training? Why don't you come join us down here every now and then?

drop_descrip.line: Cleveland-class light cruiser - Denver (CL-58)

expedition.line: Let's load up some extra supplies. In a battle of attrition, we can't let supplies run out before our spirits do.

feeling1.line: Commander, where's your dignity!?

feeling2.line: Before I met you, Commander, I felt like I was always trapped within Cleveland's shadow.

feeling3.line: I've relentlessly honed my skills in order to defeat all our enemies, but... is that really all there is to life?

feeling4.line: Even though I don't think I can ever truly grasp the kind of future that you are envisioning, if it is something that you can stand by firmly, it must be very dazzling and beautiful.

feeling5.line: Commander, you are the one who I admire and look up to the most... so if one day, you ever decide to turn your back on the person you are now, I will make sure... to drag you back!

home.line: Welcome back! I prepared some refreshments, but... Sorry, this isn't exactly my forte.

hp_warning.line: Scars are the only battle honors I need!

login.line: Welcome back, Commander! Today's a fine day to sortie!

lose.line: I'm still not... mature enough?

mail.line: Commander, check your mail!

main1.line: I want to fight alongside my sisters again, just like at Augusta Bay.

main2.line: I want to be able to dominate the battlefield with swagger, just like Cleveland.

main3.line: Even though many of my younger sisters were converted into light aircraft carriers, I'm not jealous of them at all. After all, it's best to be yourself.

mission.line: Rain or shine, hell or high water, I'm always ready to sortie!

mission_complete.line: We were able to complete our mission without a hitch because of everyone's superb teamwork!

profile.line: I am Denver, fourth ship of the Cleveland-class light cruisers. I fought hard alongside my sisters in the Battle of Empress Augusta Bay. Though I still lack experience, I won't let you down, Commander!

propose.line: Commander, your ideals and morals are loftier and purer than anyone else's... From now on, can I have the privilege of being your sword so that I may cut aside everything barring you from your future?

touch.line: How strange, Commander, you're also a fan of the "bro fist?" I thought we were the only ones who used that greeting.

touch2.line: Commander, what are you trying to feel for?

unlock.line: Hello! I'm Denver, 4th Cleveland-class cruiser and Knight of the sea! Before I officially start working for you, I've got one question: what is the future you want to see?

upgrade.line: I'll make sure to put this power to good use!

win_mvp.line: Let's seize the day! And the next!

battle.line: Let's go! I want to see everyone at their best!

detail.line: If you intend to keep me by your side, you'd better carefully observe my every move!

drop_descrip.line: Omaha-class light cruiser – Memphis, Hull Number CL-13.

expedition.line: The commission fleet has returned. Don't forget to check the performance records later.

feeling1.line: Hmph. If it's about me ignoring you, you brought this upon yourself!

feeling2.line: Next, I'll handle the paperwork and review the training plans. Commander, make sure to check my work properly. Don't slow me down, got it?

feeling3.line: Who can blame you for being so captivated by me? Very well, I'll allow you to gawk a bit longer.

feeling4.line: Sidling up to me this closely... Are you trying to smell my hair? Hehe, how is it? Does it remind you of the sea breeze?

feeling5.line: You feel uneasy when I'm not around? Don't worry, I'll always be here to escort you. As a matter of fact, you should make sure to always be around me.

home.line: Hehe, not bad. But don't get too cocky. There are still many trials ahead of us.

hp_warning.line: We can't afford to be careless!

login.line: Commander, you sure took your time getting here. Come on, let's set sail. Can you keep up with me?

lose.line: To think that I would lose... how unsightly!

mail.line: Please go get the mail. I expect some good news.

main1.line: Capturing everyone's attention with my brilliant performance at Naval Reviews - that's the way I like to do things.

main2.line: Because of my hectic schedule, I never got much time to relax back in port... But that's fine, someone like me ought to be busy, wouldn't you agree~?

main3.line: You want me to bring you back a souvenir next time? Should you really be asking that while you still have work to do?

mission.line: If there are any missions left, take care of them right away. Don't procrastinate... Hey, I'm talking to you, Commander!

mission_complete.line: You've earned these rewards. Take a look when you have time.

profile.line: I am the Omaha-class light cruiser, Memphis. I've hosted some very famous people, as well as served as flagship of the fleet in the Royal front. Make sure you carefully observe my every move!

propose.line: Do you feel honored? You've managed to earn my recognition. From here on out, I'll have high expectations for you, so don't let me down~

skill.line: Leave the escort duties to me!

touch.line: Hm? You'd like to see me while I'm training? Very well... you'd better burn this into your eyes!

touch2.line: If you don't unhand me this instant, I'll make you regret it~

unlock.line: Hmm, so you're the commander here? Don't worry, I'll carry out my duties as an escort ship. But first, you'll have to meet my standards!

upgrade.line: I wonder if I'll be even better at my escort duties now?

win_mvp.line: Hmph! Did you witness that? That's the glory that only I can bring to bear~

drop_descrip.line: Oh my, do I really look so unusual in this outfit? I want to be able to enjoy my day off as well, you know? Hehe, don't you think it feels nice to just sit back and take in the ocean breeze?

home.line: The view here is gorgeous! Oh, you're back, Commander? The picture I just took? Heheh, I'll show you later.

login.line: Morning. There's a nice wind blowing today. Perfect for a cruise, wouldn't you say?

main1.line: Phew... Let's hope this will be a relaxing day... Hey, Commander, you know what "work hard, play hard" means, right?

main2.line: My pictures? I wouldn't say I put the pros to shame, but I am experienced. Don't go underestimating my ability.

main3.line: Brooklyn and I sometimes go out on day trips. Unlike me though, she just refuses to relax even on vacation days... Or rather, we each relax in very different ways, I suppose.

touch.line: Training? Hello, do you not understand what it means to be on vacation?

touch2.line: Eek! Wh-what was that for?!

unlock.line: Oh my, do I really look so unusual in this outfit? I want to be able to enjoy my day off as well, you know? Hehe, don't you think it feels nice to just sit back and take in the ocean breeze?

battle.line: Have a taste of a witch's power!

detail.line: Commander, are you here to trick-or-treat? Here, I got this candy from Abercrombie.

drop_descrip.line: We have to work hard if we want to play hard, isn't that right, Commander? Are you ready for our happy Halloween?

home.line: Everyone has a different way of enjoying Halloween. Hehe, that's how it should be~

login.line: Commander, you came at just the right time~! Shall we go carve the jack-o'-lanterns together? Just make sure you keep up with my high standards!

main1.line: I'll let you handle giving candy out to the trick-or-treaters, Commander~ Me? Hehe, of course I'm going to go bring back more candy~

main2.line: I'm a witch now, so if you're not on your best behavior, I'll turn you into a critter~ Hehe, just kidding!

main3.line: Look, a witch and her broomstick are always paired together. I won't hear your objections!

touch.line: Commander, you'd like to sit on the broom with me? I suppose you can... but it's not my problem if you fall off, okay?

touch2.line: ... I should just boot you off the broomstick and be done with it!

unlock.line: We have to work hard if we want to play hard, isn't that right, Commander? Are you ready for our happy Halloween?

detail.line: This? Just a doodle, nothing of note... Please, would you stop trying to peek?

drop_descrip.line: Oh, what a wonderful breeze. Maybe the windows ought always to be open during class... Commander? What are you standing around for? There's a vacant seat right here for you.

home.line: Come on, get up, Marblehead! Ugh... I told her not to pull an all-nighter to conduct experiments, and she does it anyway.

login.line: Fashionably late, I see. Had you turned up a moment later, I would've gone home for the day.

main1.line: Omaha! Don't you think the amount of snacks in your desk drawers is a little excessive?

main2.line: Let's see what's new on Juustagram... Concord's posted a new sweets review. That's worth a read.

main3.line: I love sitting by the window. You get a great view of the schoolyard, and have ready access to a cool breeze.

touch.line: You'd like to see my notes? Sure thing, just– H-hey! I didn't say you could flip through it as you see fit!

touch2.line: Go to the faculty office to receive your due punishment. Now!

unlock.line: Oh, what a wonderful breeze. Maybe the windows ought always to be open during class... Commander? What are you standing around for? There's a vacant seat right here for you.

battle.line: Heeheehee, how exactly should I “love” you?~

detail.line: Do your best, Commander, if you perform well then there’ll be lollipops waiting for you~

drop_descrip.line: Omaha-class light cruiser— Concord, hull number CL-10.

expedition.line: The commission fleet has returned~ I hope they brought back new flavored ice cream with them.

feeling1.line: I’m not tired, don’t touch my feet. Touch it again and I’ll kick you!

feeling2.line: Help me grab these desserts! Then follow me around and help carry these things for me~

feeling3.line: Just stay beside me like this, ok? Take a good look at me, and don’t doze off!

feeling4.line: Since I’m on sugar crash, how are you going to sway me over? What, you’re going to reward me with dark chocolate? I certainly can’t wait!~

feeling5.line: My whole body is on a sugar rush, would you like me to show you? Hehe~ Give me your face… (pinch) How does it feel? Sweet, huh~

home.line: You’re finally back~ Do you want to taste the new flavored ice cream cone in my hand?

hp_warning.line: Hmm~... Isn’t it too risky always rushing towards the front lines...

login.line: It’s nice to see you again, Commander~ Did you bring me any yummy candy?

lose.line: A total loss… I can’t lift myself up…

mail.line: There’s new mail~ Not sure if it's notification for new desserts?

main1.line: Hmm, I’m getting tired from all this walking… it seems you got time on your hands, come and give me a feet rub~?

main2.line: I always want to go to the town of my namesake~ If we get a chance can we go?

main3.line: I am a very helpful individual~ Can’t you tell? Hehe, looks like we’ll need more time to understand one another~

mission.line: There’s still missions to do? Don’t just stand there daydreaming while looking at my feet, c’mon~

mission_complete.line: If you don’t hurry up and collect your rewards, then I’ll do it for you~ And then all these rewards will belong to me!

profile.line: I am an Omaha-class light Cruiser, Concord, of the Eagle Union~ After many weapon modifications, you can certainly count on me~ probably? Hehe.

propose.line: Wow, we’re finally at this step Commander~ From today onwards, you’ll rub my feet. Of course, I’ll also share with you all my candy~ I simply cannot wait!

touch.line: Do you also like candy? If you ask me nicely, perhaps I’ll share some of mine? Teehee.

touch2.line: Commander, if you touch me here again, then I’ll have to send you flying with a high kick~

unlock.line: Light cruiser Concord, reporting in. Do I like lollipops and ice cream—— huh? Does the Commander always like to gaze at people’s feet? Hehe.

upgrade.line: This feels awesome~

win_mvp.line: Oh, getting MVP isn’t such a difficult feat~

drop_descrip.line: Apple candy, Taiyaki, and fried noodles~ The Sakura Empire’s Temple Fair really is something~ Hehe Commander, do you also want to take a bite of my apple candy? Here you go~

login.line: The night-time events at the Temple Fair is starting soon, shall we go take a look?

main1.line: Hmm… with my hair up like this, I can’t properly wear my headphones~ Commander, do you want to give it a try~? Perhaps it’ll be very suitable on you.

main2.line: Hmm… walking around this temple is very tiring, hehe, can you give me a piggyback ride Commander?~

main3.line: On occasion, it’s nice to try out more exotic dresses. What do you think Commander, does this suit me?

touch.line: Even though lollipops are a must-have, but apple candy also have a distinct apple flavor. Sigh… it’s so hard to choose~

touch2.line: Commander~? You can either be kicked or stepped on by me, please choose?

unlock.line: Apple candy, Taiyaki, and fried noodles~ The Sakura Empire’s Temple Fair really is something~ Hehe Commander, do you also want to take a bite of my apple candy? Here you go~

detail.line: It's really cold here during the winter~ In times like these, you gotta give yourself the extra calories to make it through! I've been give the gift of not being able to gain weight, so I have to put it to use~!

drop_descrip.line: Merry Sweetsmas, Commander! Today, I get to eat as many sweets as I want without anyone saying things about it~♪ Hmm, I already eat this much every day? I guess so~

login.line: Commander~ let's sweeten things up together!

main1.line: I'm not tired of Dunkerque's desserts at all, but I'm equal opportunity when it comes to sugar. Premium or bargain, I want it all as long as it's sweet~

main2.line: Memphis really has it rough... I want to help her, but what should I do...?

main3.line: That's gingerbread, huh...? You can even make it look like that...?

touch.line: Amazing~ ♪  Commander, you should try a bite too!

touch2.line: Hehe~ Did you think I wouldn't be able to punt you across the room from this position~?

unlock.line: Merry Sweetsmas, Commander! Today, I get to eat as many sweets as I want without anyone saying things about it~♪ Hmm, I already eat this much every day? I guess so~

win_mvp.line: You'd better give all the Christmas sweets to me~!

battle.line: You won't get away!

detail.line: My dream is to one day be as pretty as my sis, St. Louis!

drop_descrip.line: Brooklyn-class light cruiser – Helena (CL-50)

expedition.line: Commander, big sis told me before that nobody likes tardy people.

feeling1.line: Commander, it's no fun being with you... I-I'm leaving!

feeling2.line: Jeez, Commander, how many times have I told you not to just barge into a girl's room?! ... Huh?

feeling3.line: Commander, this hairstyle is really popular right now. Um, I still think I prefer this other one though better though... Which do you prefer?

feeling4.line: Before, it was always big sis who helped me style my hair and put on makeup. But now, you're here to help me too! Ehehe, thank you, Commander~♪

feeling5.line: I wonder why... my heart always flutters when you help me do my hair... It's totally different from when big sis does it... Hopefully, I'm not sick or something...

home.line: Commander, do you have time to help comb my hair?

hp_warning.line: Wh-what should I do, what should I do?!

login.line: C-Commander... I haven't decided on how to do my hair yet, so please don't come barging in...

lose.line: *sniffle* Waaah... Commander, they're bullying me...

mail.line: Huh... there's new mail? Commander, would you mind getting it yourself? I'm... having a bit of a bad hair day...

main1.line: Big sis is just like a model, always changing into all kinds of clothes... B-but, if everyone thinks her clothes are cute, it's probably not too bad...

main2.line: Huh? Who's that blonde-haired boy always surrounded by everyone? Um, I... I'm not particularly interested or anything...

main3.line: Commander, do I look cute today?

mission.line: Commander, what do you think about the idea of wearing this hairstyle out to a mission?

mission_complete.line: The mission rewards are here? Good job, Commander!

profile.line: I'm the Brooklyn-class light cruiser, Helena. I'm good at anti-air, and I like dressing up. Even though I seem to have come to a weird place, my big sis, St. Louis, taught me that a proper lady must remain calm at all times. You don't seem to be a shady person, so I guess I'll be your care.

propose.line: Big sis always told me that an "Oath" was the proof of a deep bond... In other words, Commander and I are going to always get along and be together forever, right? Ehehe, I'm so glad~!

touch.line: Commander, um... look, a bunny~

touch2.line: Commander, all the girls will hate you if you do stuff like this!

unlock.line: How should I do my hair today~? Huh? Wh-who are you? Why are you in my room? Huh? This isn't my room...? Eh? Ehhhh...?!

upgrade.line: Commander, I'll help rub your back~!

win_mvp.line: Heehee, I am the cutest after all~

battle.line: I'll take you all on! I ain't scared!

detail.line: I eat so much every day, but I'm not growing at all... Why...?

drop_descrip.line: Cleveland-class light cruiser – Cleveland (CL-55)

expedition.line: Race you to the pier, Commander! Winner gets a prize!
