feeling1.line: Everybody's waiting for me! See ya, Commander!

feeling2.line: Hey, Commander, me and some of the girls are forming a Port Explorers' Team! You wanna come with us?

feeling3.line: I know how busy you are, Commander, and you still make time to come along with us... All right, from this day forward, I'm making the Commander an honorary member of our Explorers' Team!

feeling4.line: C-Commander, lemme ask you something. Helena said if I eat too much chocolate, I'll get fat and you won't wanna be with me anymore ... Is... is that true?

feeling5.line: Heh... I was right to ask you, Commander! You always help me out. That's why I love you! From now on, I'm gonna come to you anytime I don't understand something. Sound good?

home.line: Need a little pick-me-up, Commander? I got all kinds of snacks on me!

hp_warning.line: Don't stop now!

login.line: Morning, Commander! How about a chocolate bar?

lose.line: Commander, this is looking kinda bad...?

mail.line: New mail's here. Hey, you're as popular as me, Commander!

main1.line: I've got lots of little sisters, and I love each and every one of 'em! Lemme introduce you someday!

main2.line: Hey, Commander, is there a blue-haired girl in the fleet, about yea big, always staring at herself in the mirror? You mind if I go play with her?

main3.line: Being this small is kind of inconvenient sometimes. ... Like when? Like when I'm trying to help somebody with something...?

mission.line: Commander, go bang out that mission!

mission_complete.line: Hey, the rewards are here! I got lots of tasty snacks to trade. Whaddya say, Commander?

profile.line: I'm the big sister of the Cleveland-class... but I guess that's obvious from my name alone. I may be a light cruiser, but I can match a heavy cruiser no problem! I am gonna dominate the seas, after all!

propose.line: This means we're best friends forever? I'll take good care of it! Hehee, if you ever get into trouble, Commander, just let me know. I'll take good care of you!

touch.line: It's important to keep your energy up, Commander! Here, have a chocolate bar!

touch2.line: Huh? You wanna rub my belly?

unlock.line: Hello, my name is Cleveland! My dream is to one day join the Solomon Knights! I'm working hard towards that goal every day!

upgrade.line: Hehe, that feels good!

win_mvp.line: Hahaa! I train every day!

battle.line: We're headed for the ocean! Chaaaaarge!!

detail.line: The skies don't just belong to the planes, but to clouds and stars as well!

drop_descrip.line: Atlanta-class light cruiser – San Diego (CL-53)

expedition.line: ...?! Commander, my Sandy Senses are tingling! There's someone waiting at the port!

feeling1.line: Don't feel bad, Commander, it's not your fault that you're dumber than San Diego.

feeling2.line: The key to happiness is to not worry about the stuff you don't get. Isn't that right, Commander?

feeling3.line: What should I do if there's stuff that I can't stop worrying about though...? Ah! Got it! That's what Commander is there for!

feeling4.line: No matter what kind of stuff I ask you, you always have an answer... Commander, are you actually pretty smart?!

feeling5.line: As long as you're here, Commander, I'll know where to turn to whenever I have any problems! Hehe, I love how you know everything, Commander!

home.line: Commander, were you trying to play hide-and-seek with me?

hp_warning.line: Hey, guys, why so serious??

login.line: Yo, Commander! There's a lot of paper lying around here, so let's fold some paper airplanes and see whose fly the farthest!

lose.line: Huhhh? Isn't that the way back home?

mail.line: Commander, you always get so much mail... Next time, I'll write you a letter too!

main1.line: My sisters always told me to ask if there's anything I don't understand. But, what if I still don't get it?

main2.line: Hrmmm... Is there some way to get everyone to know about how awesome I am?

main3.line: Ehhh? Commander, doesn't it get boring sitting there all day?

mission.line: I'm gonna finish up all these missions in one fell swoop!

mission_complete.line: Sooooo many rewards! Well? I'm pretty helpful, aren't I?

profile.line: I'm the third ship of the Atlanta-class light cruisers, San Diego! I'm aiming to become the fleet's number one Super☆Star!

propose.line: What's this shiny, loopy thing? I'm supposed to put it on my finger? Ooh, it's so pretty! Hehe, I guess I'll keep it on then!

skill.line: Got it! It's about time we get serious~!

touch.line: Awright! It's my turn to be it! One, two, skip a few... Ninety-nine, a hundred! Here I come, Commander!

touch2.line: Commander, you jerk!

unlock.line: San Diego, making her shining debut! She shoots, she scores~ Yaay! Hehe, only a genius like me could come up with a one-of-a-kind intro like that!

upgrade.line: Eehhh? Is this stuff really going to be useful?

win_mvp.line: Did you see that? Just now?! I'm freakin' awesome!

battle.line: I'll keep the skies clear for you! Everyone, forward!

detail.line: I set the trap just like the book said, but why haven't I caught anything yet? That's strange...

drop_descrip.line: Atlanta-class light cruiser – San Juan, Hull Number CL-54.

expedition.line: The resources from the commission have been delivered. Commander, why don't you... Umm, I'll go check on them.

feeling1.line: I thought this might happen, but... I won't give up!

feeling2.line: The fleet is gonna lose faith in you if you keep spacing out like that. Commander, get your head in the game!

feeling3.line: Um, I know I can be a little hard on you, Commander. But you get what I mean, don't you? ... Commander?

feeling4.line: Commander, I always thought you wouldn't like me... and I'm glad that isn't true! B-but, how do we take our relationship to the next level? Wh-what are we supposed to do? I... I don't know about these things...

feeling5.line: Um, I was thinking, if you have time, could we go out on a da... date? I know it's my fault for being so hard on you all the time, so I'm trying to make it up to you... Whatever I need to do to take us to the next level, I'll do it... Okay!?

home.line: Welcome back, Commander! ... D-did it go okay?

hp_warning.line: I-it's just a scratch! I can keep going...!

login.line: Clock's ticking! We gotta get to work— Oh, come on! Here, let me straighten your collar. You're a mess!

lose.line: Agh...! Go! I'll cover your retreat!

mail.line: I got your mail for you. Don't forget to check it.

main1.line: Commander... are you daydreaming again?

main2.line: Supporting a carrier group is just watching the skies all day. I wish supporting you was as easy...

main3.line: My sisters haven't been causing you any trouble, have they? Oh, thank goodness...

mission.line: How do you still have unfinished missions? Well, since you're hopeless without me, I suppose I can help you out...

mission_complete.line: Mission complete! Feels pretty nice to be done, huh?

profile.line: I am San Juan, Atlanta-class anti-aircraft cruiser number four. I escorted many carrier groups: Enterprise, Saratoga, several of the Essex-class. I fought alongside them all. Let's just say I have a lot of experience in aircraft carrier support combat!

propose.line: L-look, Commander... I'm only doing this because you're easier to deal with than my sisters. I only have enough patience to take care of one more person, so thank your lucky stars that it's you! I wouldn't do this for anyone else, got it?!

touch.line: I know you're tired, Commander, but you don't have to whine about it. ... Okay, once you finish your work, how about I give you a massage?

touch2.line: W-w-w-watch your hands!!

unlock.line: I am San Juan, Atlanta-class anti-aircraft cruiser number four. I've served as a support unit for the Eagle Union's carrier fleets. You seem like a person up to your ears in work, Commander... so I now offer to support you!

upgrade.line: Now I can escort those carriers even better!

win_mvp.line: Victory is just a result of the effort we put into the fight. It's nothing to be especially proud of.

battle.line: I'll send 'em packing, you know it!

detail.line: That's right! My sisters can take care of themselves for once! My only focus today will be enjoying myself at the party! ...Oh, who am I kidding, they can't go without supervision...

drop_descrip.line: All right, dress looking good. Now just to check my makeup... Need to be thorough, so I don't embarrass myself in front of– What?! C-Commander?!

expedition.line: The goods have come in from the last commission. Commander, mind if I take a peek?

feeling5.line: S-so, what do you think of my dress? It's definitely different from the rest of my wardrobe, a-and I just hope you don't think it's a letdown... Y-you don't? Th-that's great then! Really great!

login.line: Hmm... Hope my lipstick looks fine... Commander? You're here already? O-okay, I'm coming!

mail.line: I left your mail where I always do. Give it a read sometime later.

main1.line: Commander? If you wanna slack off, now's the time to do it! ...Oh god, I can't believe I just said that!

main2.line: Whew... Remember, Commander: overworking is bad for you. Though having that said, we're both guilty of that...

main3.line: nil

touch.line: I'm beat. Saying hi to everyone isn't as easy as I expected... Oh right, makeup... Do I look okay, Commander?

touch2.line: Aah! Wh-what was that?!

unlock.line: All right, dress looking good. Now just to check my makeup... Need to be thorough, so I don't embarrass myself in front of– What?! C-Commander?!

win_mvp.line: I can get away with showing off just for today... I-I am number 1!

battle.line: Time is money, so let's strike quickly! I will lead the way!

detail.line: Someday I hope to see the sea return to its peaceful former state...

drop_descrip.line: Cleveland-class light cruiser – Birmingham, Hull Number CL-62.

expedition.line: Every little bit counts in the end. The worth of this commission will become clear one day.

feeling1.line: Commander, you should reflect on your actions thoroughly.

feeling2.line: Being a light cruiser, I can't markedly affect the war... However, I firmly believe that the power to protect the sea rests within me.

feeling3.line: You think I'm overly stoic...? True, but I must be in order to repel the darkness that envelops the sea.

feeling4.line: Commander, it feels as though you have the peculiar power of calming people. Just like a peaceful sea would...

feeling5.line: A smile? Like this? That is an unusual order to issue. That is not to say I dislike it... *Giggle*

home.line: It is good to see you unscathed. I suggest taking a break.

hp_warning.line: They have superior firepower! This may be bad...!

login.line: Sortie preparations complete. Your orders, Commander?

lose.line: What could I have done differently...

mail.line: Mail for you. My intuition tells me it's good news. If it's bad news, I will help you digest it.

main1.line: Princeton... please be okay. If I had fought harder back then, things wouldn't have...

main2.line: Sometimes people ridicule me for being unlucky, but having survived that hellish battle, I feel quite lucky.

main3.line: I feel at ease when I'm with Cleve and my sisters. I believe this is what's known as a "bond."

mission.line: New mission from HQ. Let's complete it right at once, Commander.

mission_complete.line: Mission rewards have arrived. Perhaps there is ice cream in... Oh, um, never mind that.

profile.line: I am Birmingham, the eighth Cleveland-class light cruiser. Born during the war, I fought to its end alongside my many sisters and earned 9 battle stars. As a Knight of the Sea, my duty continues, and I will now fight for the sea's future.

propose.line: This must be an oath... Have we already spent this much time together, Commander...? No, I'm not displeased at all. It's just... in this case, it's... *Ahem*! Now, then... Commander, will you watch the sunrise over the horizon of the sea together with me?

touch.line: What is it, Commander? Was that your sortie order?

touch2.line: Is this amusing to you?

unlock.line: Starting today, Cleveland-class light cruiser Birmingham is on active duty. I will not rest until the future of the sea is secure. Commander, grant me your guidance and support.

upgrade.line: This enhancement was necessary for me to keep advancing.

win_mvp.line: The next battleground awaits. I will stay on my guard.

detail.line: A bicycle must be maintained regularly, so I asked U-47 for advice and help. One day I need to offer her a favor in return.

drop_descrip.line: Good morning, Commander. Unfortunately, this bicycle only seats one person, but I could dismount and lead it along as we walk together.

login.line: Is it time to sortie? Please wait. I must park my ride somewhere first.

main1.line: It seems the academy has no bicycling club... Perhaps I should petition to create one... Hmm...

main2.line: A new dessert shop opened, and their specialty is ice cream...? ... C-Commander, do you mind if I leave for a moment?

main3.line: U-47, how about we go on a bicycling trip the next time you're off duty?

touch.line: Bicycling is an excellent way to train the body. Prepare your bicycle and we can go for a ride, Commander.

unlock.line: Good morning, Commander. Unfortunately, this bicycle only seats one person, but I could dismount and lead it along as we walk together.

detail.line: When snow falls over the farmlands, it kills off crop-eating insects and keeps the soil at a stable temperature. Then when the snow melts, it waters the earth... Now I can see why they call it "fruitful snow."

drop_descrip.line: Happy Lunar New Year, Commander. I'm trying out Dragon Empery fashion for a change, though this dress will some getting used to. Hey, uh, do you want to join me under the umbrella? For cover against the snowfall, I mean.

home.line: Apparently tying your hair up into buns like this is the norm in the Dragon Empery... Huh? It's not?

login.line: Welcome back, Commander. There's snow on my umbrella? Oh, darn it. I got so absorbed in the wintry landscape that I forgot to shake the snow off.

main1.line: Princeton, I'm pretty sure that aerial maneuver you learned from Saratoga is only good for pranking people...

main2.line: Ice cream doesn't melt so easily when the temperature drops. Is it weird to talk about ice cream in the middle of winter? ...Oh. Now I know...

main3.line: The family all gathering to make dumplings while they chit-chat... I like the sound of this Dragon Empery tradition. It warms the heart.

touch.line: You want to... hold hands? My hands are a bit chilly, but if you don't mind that, then sure.

unlock.line: Happy Lunar New Year, Commander. I'm trying out Dragon Empery fashion for a change, though this dress will some getting used to. Hey, uh, do you want to join me under the umbrella? For cover against the snowfall, I mean.

detail.line: The windsurfing speed record is apparently over a hundred kilometers an hour. It's wild that you can go that fast from just riding the wind... Hmm, I don't think Cleve has ever experienced that before.

drop_descrip.line: The wind and the waves are great today. You wanna try windsurfing after this, Commander? It's a lot of fun and I can teach you the... Hang on, there's a good wind coming and I've got to catch it!

expedition.line: That's the commission team! Commander, change course!

home.line: I saw you coming into the port. Great job out there, now get some rest. Your surfing lesson can wait.

login.line: Since you love learning, let's get right into it. We'll start on the beach. Don't worry, I wouldn't just throw you into the ocean from the start.

lose.line: Must've been because I lost my balance, huh... Looks like I still have a lot to learn.

mail.line: A letter? We'll check it later. Let's hope it's good news.

main1.line: When you want to change course, move to a different position on the surfboard and... Crap! Are you okay, Commander?

main2.line: Wish Biloxi and her gals would give this a shot... Actually, no, they've got their own hobbies. The reason I chose this one is because I'm true to myself!

main3.line: Watersports at the academy don't seem particularly big, but that's probably because we see enough water as shipgirls. Or, I just don't know about it...

mission.line: A new mission? I think we'll– Oh crap! ...Thanks for the save, Commander.

mission_complete.line: Mission rewards have arrived? Sweet. Nothing beats ice cream on a hot summer day.

touch.line: That's it, keep the sail leaned. You're getting the hang of this.

touch2.line: Do you really expect you'll maintain your balance while doing this?

unlock.line: The wind and the waves are great today. You wanna try windsurfing after this, Commander? It's a lot of fun and I can teach you the... Hang on, there's a good wind coming and I've got to catch it!

win_mvp.line: Pfah! That felt awesome! I... Err, Commander, do me a favor and pretend you didn't see that.

battle.line: Lights, on! Let's get this battle started!

detail.line: What's important for concerts is having confidence! If you believe you're a star, then you are! Really! Hey, that actually sounded like a pretty cool one-liner.

drop_descrip.line: Light cruiser Cleveland, right here! I'm new to this whole idol biz, but I'll go with the flow and give it my all! Oh, and I'm counting on your support, Commander!

expedition.line: Commission complete! Don't forget everyone's got a schedule to follow, all right?

feeling1.line: Sorry, I've got more important stuff to do. I don't have time for you.

feeling2.line: I'm Cleveland, one of the fleet's idols! Nice meeting you, Commander!

feeling3.line: Maybe saying I grow bonsai as a hobby sounds too basic... Maybe it is... Gah, I'm at my wit's end! Commander, what do I write to make a decent self-introduction?

feeling4.line: Dammit, Columbia... She's an expert at this stuff so I asked her to help. I'm shocked she wrote a bio for me that's half lies... Thank goodness you fixed it, Commander, or else I would've died of shame on stage...

feeling5.line: Whew... You've really helped me out tons, Commander... I'm not the greatest when it comes to this stuff, and I never thought I could be a star on stage like you've made me... We really were meant to be together, Commander!

home.line: Oh, you tired? The dressing room is free right now. You could use that if it's too exhausting to walk to the office.

hp_warning.line: I will keep drumming till the end!

login.line: Hey! You all having a good time? ...All right, that should do it! Oh, hey, Commander! Heheh, I was just doing some practice!

lose.line: I can't show myself to my sisters like this...

mail.line: New mail's come in! I've already told you: it's for you, not for me! Come on already!

main1.line: Hehe~ It's time to break it down! Can you keep up? Just kidding~ Downes is a bit of a class act, isn't she?

main2.line: Well, I'm not nervous at all because I've had a few chances to sing in front of everyone. Also, it helps that I'm not the lead vocalist, hehe.

main3.line: Montpelier, Denver, what the heck are you wearing? That's embarrassing...! And Birmingham, you don't have to go waving that thing around!

mission.line: We've got job offers... I mean, commissions! Let's get 'em done!

mission_complete.line: Mission complete! Phew... We oughta start looking over our job offers.

profile.line: I'm Cleveland, the light cruiser. My sisters and I took part in the World War and... Well, let's just say we did pretty good for ourselves. This time around I'm wearing this special uniform, and I'm gonna fight with the power of song!

propose.line: I heard that in some places, idols aren't allowed to be in relationships. Well, I'm sure we'll be fine! Anyway, Commander... Hehe, please continue to take good care of me!

touch.line: I've gotta train for the handshake meet-and-greet. Think you could "give me a hand," Commander?

touch2.line: Commander?! I'm trying to get by as an idol here! Th-Think of my image...

unlock.line: Light cruiser Cleveland, right here! I'm new to this whole idol biz, but I'll go with the flow and give it my all! Oh, and I'm counting on your support, Commander!

upgrade.line: All those lessons are paying off!

win_mvp.line: Whew! So who's our next target?

battle.line: Victory will come to us nice and easy!

detail.line: Yeah? If you need any help, just say the word. My schedule's pretty packed too, but I can always squeeze in some time to take on your orders.

drop_descrip.line: Cleveland-class light cruiser – Biloxi, Hull Number CL-80.

expedition.line: Those commission team girls are back. Let's go check what rewards they've brought. They might have a surprise for us.

feeling1.line: Look, if you wanna do nothing all day, do it without involving me.

feeling2.line: Whew... I'm still gonna be busy for a long time, but right now I need a break. You up for chatting about stuff, Commander?

feeling3.line: I sometimes enjoy talking with people about what we do on our off days... What? What's so weird about me bringing up people's hobbies? When I have time off, I enjoy myself. I'm no workaholic, you hear?

feeling4.line: Guess it's just the two of us again. Heheh, let's forget about work and have a fun chat. You know, just relax. You wanna get some drinks and snacks? It's on me.

feeling5.line: Zooming around from sea to sea can even get me feeling tired sometimes. But lately I've been having this thought... This thought that here, where you are, is my home.

home.line: Well done on that sortie. From this point on, I'm gonna assume you'll always return triumphant.

hp_warning.line: Tsk... This is nothing!

login.line: Mission status: all green. Eyes on the progress, Commander.

lose.line: Argh... This isn't over yet, you hear?!

mail.line: You've got mail, Commander. Better check it ASAP. Might be good news, after all!

main1.line: "Big sis"? Who, me? Ahh, you mean the lead ship. I respect Cleve just as a sister ship. Hahahah!

main2.line: We *are* an improved model, but we didn't end up as carriers like Bataan, and our improvements aren't extensive enough to call us part of a subclass. The differences are more obvious through our looks and personalities, though.

main3.line: A friend always deserves help, even if you yourself are in a tough spot. That's what "no man left behind" is all about. Ain't that right?

mission.line: These missions just keep piling up. Laziness will not be tolerated, Commander.

mission_complete.line: Reward recovery complete. Time to see what fruits you've earned for your labor, Commander.

profile.line: I'm Eagle Union light cruiser Biloxi. I fought in heaps of battles and carried out many carrier escort missions. Sure, the Cleveland class has its hallmark anti-air fire, but everyone's gotta work together to win. So let's do just that, Commander.

propose.line: I used to think prestige meant dashing gallantly onto the battlefield... But now I see how being by your side is just as... No, it's *more* prestigious than that idea.

skill.line: No aircraft shall evade my sights!

touch.line: Check out my gear. Nobody's got better AA than I do. You bet your butt it'll shoot down bogeys like back in the Turkey Shoot.

touch2.line: One without manners is one garnering contempt. Is that really how you wanna be, Commander?

unlock.line: I'm Biloxi. I hope we can work together and seize victory as fellow fleet members. Anyway, that's all for introductions. Nice meeting you.

upgrade.line: With great power comes great responsibility. That couldn't be more true.

win_mvp.line: Thanks for the backup, guys.

detail.line: A friend told me this look would totally steal your heart. So, has it? Are you head over heels for me? Hahahah! I'm just kidding with you.

drop_descrip.line: We're celebrating an overseas holiday, hence my not-so-casual outfit today. Heheh, what do you think? Looking slick?

feeling5.line: I came up with something that could make our trip more interesting. How about we give the Manjuu a break and *you* pull the cart to our next destination? Hahahah! I'm just joking around.

login.line: Where do you wanna go today, Commander? Don't worry, we don't have to rush it. I've got plenty of time to spare.

main1.line: These Dragon Empery signs are really unique, in a good way. I think they're fascinating.

main2.line: The seat on this Manjuu cart is pretty small. I'd offer to share if there was more room.

main3.line: I was just about to go procure some souvenirs. What would you buy if you were me, Commander?

touch.line: Getting tired? Then let's catch a breather. Oh yeah, could you pour me some wine? Let's have a toast. To a wonderful day!

unlock.line: We're celebrating an overseas holiday, hence my not-so-casual outfit today. Heheh, what do you think? Looking slick?

detail.line: My feelings for you haven't changed, but yeah, these clothes make me act really intimidating... Maybe I'm getting into my role too much.

drop_descrip.line: "Hehe... Now that you've finally fallen into my hands, why don't we take the day to get to know each other real well, Commander?" Oh my, was my acting a bit too realistic~?

feeling5.line: I came here intent on enjoying the party, but I wound up slipping into acting instead... Although, there's fun to be had in that, too. Listen, Commander, I'm sorry to ask, but I wanna know: are you... enjoying yourself?

login.line: How's it going, Commander? It might be unprofessional of me to ask, but... Is something up?

lose.line: Argh! Interesting...!

main1.line: Let's take a ride to the party. Don't worry about the Manjuu, I've seen how well he can drive... What, that wasn't your concern?

main2.line: You oughta take today off at the very least. No need to be a busy bee and work day in, day out.

main3.line: Mental clarity is the key to keeping your cool on the battlefield. My sisters, they all have the fortitude it takes.

touch2.line: "Looks like someone here doesn't know proper manners."

unlock.line: "Hehe... Now that you've finally fallen into my hands, why don't we take the day to get to know each other real well, Commander?" Oh my, was my acting a bit too realistic~?

win_mvp.line: "Clear out the rest of these fools, will you?" Hahah, guess there'll be no need for that.

detail.line: Beauty is fleeting. Look away for one moment, and you'll miss it forever... It's not exclusive to fireworks, either. When you see a thing of beauty, keep your eyes on it, Commander.

drop_descrip.line: I heard that this place is famous for its festivals with beautiful fireworks, so I made sure to come dressed for the occasion... What do you think? ...I'm even more beautiful? Well, I couldn't let the fireworks be the only things leaving an impression upo

login.line: There you are, Commander! They're putting on a fireworks display tonight. Come with me and we'll check it out.

main1.line: Even in the cold winter, the thrill of watching fireworks with your friends warms you up. Ahahahah!

main2.line: Being here with my sisters, us all watching the fireworks together... It's actually pretty nice.

main3.line: Seeing these stunning fireworks makes me hope next year will go smoothly. Fingers crossed, Commander!

touch.line: Fancy my dress? You can have a closer look at it all you want later.

touch2.line: ...You wanna make like a firework and go bang, or what?

unlock.line: I heard that this place is famous for its festivals with beautiful fireworks, so I made sure to come dressed for the occasion... What do you think? ...I'm even more beautiful? Well, I couldn't let the fireworks be the only things leaving an impression upon you tonight! Ahaha, just kidding~

detail.line: You can't tell whether I'm playing the male or the female lead? Well, I've not decided on that yet, so I've read both their scripts. And don't worry, I can dress the part if I go for the male role. Hahahah!

drop_descrip.line: The cast is all here. So, what do we rehearse first? The part where we elope and live happily ever after? Hahahah!

home.line: Welcome back, Commander. While coming home is a trying experience in certain love stories, I'm guessing everything went fine for you? That's good.

login.line: What's the mask for? It's a prop used in musicals. Speaking of which, could you help me practice my part, Commander? All right, let's get to it... "Let us soar above a common bound~"

mail.line: There's a letter for you. Be sure to read it. Who knows, it could be from someone dear to you.

main1.line: "O Commander, Commander, wherefore art thou the Commander?" ...Surprised? See, this line actually has a tragic story to it...

main2.line: "What light through yonder window breaks? It is the east, and the Commander is the sun!" ...I'm just reciting lines here. Don't take it at face value, all right?

main3.line: Hmm. I think I can pull off either role... Commander, which do you think suits me best? I was thinking I'd let Cleve play whichever one I don't take in the end.

touch.line: Why are you holding my hand? Are you asking me for a dance? Sure, let's do it.

unlock.line: The cast is all here. So, what do we rehearse first? The part where we elope and live happily ever after? Hahahah!

battle.line: Just leave the planes to me!

detail.line: Commander, I'm in a bit of a pickle... I can't get any of the parts for my costume at Akashi's shop... I guess I'll just have to make them myself... Hrm...

drop_descrip.line: Atlanta-class light cruiser – Reno, Hull Number CL-96.

expedition.line: The commission came back. You want to go out and see them?

feeling1.line: They say you should never meet your heroes. Now I know why... Sigh...

feeling2.line: Commander, you're looking at my superhero gadgets! This is my Ibranium shield, this is my Chiropterang, and this here's my Worpher Belt... Cool, huh? You name it, I've got it, Commander.

feeling3.line: There was a time when I was training really hard to become a superhero... But these huge things got in the way of my dreams... the flat girls don't know how good they have it...

feeling4.line: I may have given up my training, but I still love watching sports. Oh, but even more than sports, I love watching superhero shows...! But now that my real hero is here, Commander, maybe I'm good on that front.

feeling5.line: They say "with great power comes great responsibility," but superheroes need some downtime too, just like warships. Sometimes I just gotta be a regular girl, and you're no different. Let's do something fun sometime.

home.line: Good fight out there, Commander. Here's a towel and a drink... Hm? Isn't this what a sidekick does?

hp_warning.line: I could do this all day!

login.line: Commander, today we do our best to save the world. like always!

lose.line: They say it's always darkest before the dawn... Mm. We'll try harder next time.

mail.line: Mail for you, Commander. Is it a fan letter?

main1.line: You looking at my gear, Commander? If you press this here, it shoots out a light like bzzzzew! And if you press this one, it goes like kshaw ksshhew. And then this one's like...

main2.line: Commander, I'm in a bind... Well, I guess it's not really that big a deal. It's just, I wasn't able to get this premium figure I've been wanting...

main3.line: Woooww.... Hm? Oh, was I bothering you? I was just basking in the amazing feeling of a sidekick watching her hero work up close~

mission.line: We got a lot to do... But I'm sure you can knock it out easy peasy, Commander!

mission_complete.line: That's my Commander! You always get the best rewards!

profile.line: I'm Reno, an Atlanta-class cruiser of the later Oakland subclass. We've got souped up anti-air power compared to the regular Atlanta-class. We only saw the last bits of the war, but we still fought hard. But I feel really bad about Princeton... Nnng, it's fine! We can do it!

propose.line: So like, from now on I'm more than just your sidekick. I gotta learn how to be a partner to you too, for the rest of your life... I don't really know how to do that ♪ so you'll just have to speak up and tell me what to do~

touch.line: I'm doing good work...? Oooh! My hero complimented me! Of course my face is gonna turn bright red!

touch2.line: You think they're big too? They really get in the way...

unlock.line: You're the Commander? Ahh, I've always wanted to meet you! I mean, aren't people like you basically heroes trying to save the world? Which kind of makes me your sidekick, right? Oh, I'm Reno, part of the Oakland class! It's a pleasure!

upgrade.line: Hah ha! I'm the Commander's sidekick!

win_mvp.line: Yeah! The good guys always win!

detail.line: Craven was supposed to be cheer squad leader on account of she's older, but she ended up asking me to do it... I can't let her down. I gotta cheer hard!

drop_descrip.line: This really is a huge clash of all the biggest names from all the factions. It's one exciting match after another! I gotta cheer my hardest too. Eagle Union, go get 'em!

home.line: Commander, you're just in time. The next match is about to start~

login.line: Commander, I got a great view of the games from here. Come watch with me~

main1.line: Ah, it's half time. That means we better get out there and cheer! Everybody ready? Let's get their blood pumping!

main2.line: None of the other factions have serious cheerleaders like me or Craven. But I won't underestimate the ones they came up with either... I can't let them beat me~

main3.line: Look at them out there on the field, shining like superheroes as they fight for victory... being a cheerleader sure is amazing!

mission_complete.line: Commander, it's time to get your rewards, everyone's waiting for you to attend the ceremony~

touch.line: Huh, you brought me water, Commander? Woaaahhh, no way...! Nng, my hero brought me water... I couldn't be happier...

touch2.line: Commander, people can see...

unlock.line: This really is a huge clash of all the biggest names from all the factions. It's one exciting match after another! I gotta cheer my hardest too. Eagle Union, go get 'em!

detail.line: It was really hard to find a swimsuit that would fit my bust... Luckily, I was able to find this swimsuit at the last minute! It fits my chest perfectly, but... my poor hips are chafing... Ow...

drop_descrip.line: "Superhero spin-off! The superhero who saved the world is enjoying a hard-earned vacation on the afternoon beach with the sidekick!" ... Hehe, Commander, a tagline like that sounds pretty cool, doesn't it?

home.line: Commander, are you in Sleep Mode? Then please, rest well! ...You don't have to worry about me. I've already rested for a bit, and I was thinking about heading out to make my rounds anyway!

login.line: *Click!* Welcome back, Commander! Heehee~ I couldn't stop myself from taking a picture of my beloved hero enjoying the beach!

main1.line: Looks like everyone's pumped up for the beach volleyball tournament! If only my... weren't so big. They make it hard to move around...

main2.line: Oh yeah. How dashing does My Hero look when swimming? Do you zoom by others while going at 100 miles per hour? Hehehe~

main3.line: If you compete in the tournament, I'll cheer you on with all I've got! Go! Go! Come on! You can do it! M-Y-H-E-R-O!

touch.line: If it isn't coconut milk! Is it okay to accept such a precious gift? ...Hehe. I'm absolutely elated to receive a precious present from my hero!

touch2.line: Woah?! I-If you touch it like that, it's going to snap!!

unlock.line: "Superhero spin-off! The superhero who saved the world is enjoying a hard-earned vacation on the afternoon beach with the sidekick!" ... Hehe, Commander, a tagline like that sounds pretty cool, doesn't it?

detail.line: Reno, tired of seeing her commander fighting all alone, assumed an alter ego and joined the commander in the battle against the forces of evil! Pretty cool origin story, wouldn't you say?

drop_descrip.line: Come on in, Commander! Don't you recognize me? I'm Reno Bunnino – cutesy bunny girl by day, villain-vanquishing superhero by night! Pretty neat concept, am I right?

home.line: When Reno Bunnino's beloved commander comes home to roost, that's her time to shine.

login.line: What can I get you, Commander?

main1.line: So I was telling everyone about Reno Bunnino, and for whatever reason, North Carolina was super keen to hear it... Not like that's a bad thing. More friends is always good!

main2.line: Hungry, Commander? Vestal taught me a handful of recipes. I could cook something up for you.

main3.line: Y'know, I think this Reno Bunnino's thing really gonna take off. I'm counting on you to facilitate that, Commander.

touch.line: This gauntlet I'm always wearing? Oh, uh, I've not made my Reno Bunnino tool belt just yet, so I'm making do with this for now.

touch2.line: If you're doing what I think you are... Yeah, sorry, there aren't many clothes my size.

unlock.line: Come on in, Commander! Don't you recognize me? I'm Reno Bunnino – cutesy bunny girl by day, villain-vanquishing superhero by night! Pretty neat concept, am I right?

detail.line: "An unforeseen accident causes panic at the festival! That's when our plain-clothed superhero rises up to the task!" That'd be such a fun scenario! Although, obviously we'd all much prefer to have a peaceful holiday.

drop_descrip.line: Check this out, Commander! Hehehe, I added a little firework launcher to my superhero gadgets. Cool, huh? ...Your interest lies more in my new look? But... the firework...

home.line: I've got a red envelope for you, Commander! Here you are! ...Hm? This is backwards? Usually you're the one giving these out?

login.line: Happy Spring Festival, Commander! The port looks great with all these paper lanterns decorating it! They give it this novel, cultured vibe. You know what I mean?

main1.line: Hehe, check this out! Doesn't this outfit... kinda make me look like one of the Dragon Empery's wandering recluses?

main2.line: Want me to show you my micro-firework again? Hehe, I'd be right happy to♪

main3.line: Sorry, Ayanami. All my gadgets can do is shoot these little sparks. They can't fire real fireworks, lasers, or anything like that.

touch.line: You wanna hold hands? Sure thing! Ah, wait, this one's still a bit hot! The other one!

touch2.line: Whaaa?! You're not supposed to lift this flap!

unlock.line: Check this out, Commander! Hehehe, I added a little firework launcher to my superhero gadgets. Cool, huh? ...Your interest lies more in my new look? But... the firework...

battle.line: Tiiiime to get serial!

detail.line: Why follow the stupidly serial boss-and-subordinate template, am I right? Hehehe, let's just hang out and be friends!

drop_descrip.line: Omaha-class light cruiser – Marblehead, Hull Number CL-12.

expedition.line: Commander, I figure a commission should be done by now. Hm? Nah, I've just got a good mental clock~

feeling1.line: You're uncool as heck, Commander. I'mma hit up Concord and hang with her instead...

feeling2.line: This here picture I've got? Ah, that average-looking girl used to be me. Whatevs, let's put that aside and go have some fun~!

feeling3.line: I'm not really shy about my past as an ordinary girl. What's then is then, what's now is now, y'know? I think my new look better expresses who I am~ So anyway, as I was saying...

feeling4.line: I guess it's like, you lose sight of what's fun when you go super-serial all-work-and-no-play, you get me? I'm having tons of fun now, and wouldn't go back to my dorky self even if you told me to.

feeling5.line: I dunno if you're into girls like me, but *I'm* into commanders like *you*, so~ What do you say we get closer each other? Let's get the ball rolling with a date~

home.line: Commander, you feelin' hungry? I got some cake, fresh outta the oven.

hp_warning.line: Guess I've gotta crank up the serial factor...!

login.line: Libra's horoscope for today promises... super good luck.

lose.line: I have to investigate into what went wrong this battle... Oh, uh, never mind I said anything!

mail.line: Guess this is new mail or something... Right, I'll just pretend I never saw it.

main1.line: Yo, Commander, I promised Memphis I'd color her nails in 2 hours! That's gonna take about an hour to do, so if you've got work for me then you might wanna give it now.

main2.line: Let's see... Hey, Commander~ See this? I don't really get what this part says, but somethin' about it looks off.

main3.line: Put the seal there, check the numbers, make a report... Hm? Oh, I'm not up to anything special! You're just imagining things, probably!

mission.line: Once this mission's done, could you go get the milk tea I ordered? And not too much sugar, thanks.

mission_complete.line: You, uh, one of those super-achievers, Commander? I'm... I-I'm kinda sorta into people like that.

profile.line: I'm Marblehead, your average Omaha-class girl. I went like, all over the globe during the war, and stuff like that. Anyhoo, let's be buds and just chill, 'kay?

propose.line: I totally knew it, we're like, made for each other~ I looked into your personal preferences ages ago, so yeah~ All right, you wanna come with me and have some fun again today?

touch.line: Commander, I'm trying to take a selfie here, so could you move?

touch2.line: Whuah?! Commander, that's *really* creepy, okay?

unlock.line: Sup. Name's Marblehead. Are you the Commander? Ahah☆ I dig your style. Hehehe, let's hang out sometime!

upgrade.line: Huh. You fancy a girl like me?

win_mvp.line: Smile for the camera, Commander~ I need a selfie to preserve this moment~

detail.line: I started reading up on building muscle for future reference, and man there's a lot to learn~

drop_descrip.line: After trying out a whole bunch of activities, I settled on joinin' the boxing club in the end. Everyone wants to exercise now and then, right? Come along, Commander, and we'll have a fun workout together~

feeling5.line: We could have a workout date someday~ Like a "let your fists do the talking" kinda thing, or something like that~ Be a darling, Commander, and take my loving blows~

home.line: Good going out there. You want a sip of my electrolyte-rich sports drink?

login.line: All right, Commander, let's start with some warmups~

main1.line: Let's leave our boring work and social troubles behind and focus only on workin' out~

main2.line: I need a break... All right, time to check out the MME tournament on TV~

main3.line: Commander, you seen Omaha 'round here? I bet she's off gorging herself on snacks in secret. Don't let her get away with it~!

touch.line: Sooo, Commander, when we're working out... who're your eyes on~?

touch2.line: Using the fat around your chest for softening impacts... kinda actually works?!

unlock.line: After trying out a whole bunch of activities, I settled on joinin' the boxing club in the end. Everyone wants to exercise now and then, right? Come along, Commander, and we'll have a fun workout together~

detail.line: Hmm... The snow's falling at a rate of 3cm per second, so assuming no wind, tomorrow's forecast should be something like... Oh, Commander? Just talkin' to myself!

drop_descrip.line: Whoa! Talk about a stunning view! You like, totally all the best spots in the city, Commander~ Hehe, okay, so... Merry Christmas!

expedition.line: The commission gals are back~ You wanna go out and meet up with 'em, or...?

home.line: Sup, Commander. Oof, real chilly out there, huh? Then c'mere and I'll warm you up~

login.line: Hey Commander, you ready to get? "To get what"? To get to work, man! Hehehe~

main1.line: You think Santa Claus is real, Commander? Me, I think he's like, basically real. Because, y'know, there's all these people wearing legit Santa costumes in stores and stuff. Hahaha.

main2.line: If Miss Raleigh were in my shoes here, she'd totes be blushing to her ears.

main3.line: Wanna draw something with me, Commander? Y'know, like, exhaling on the window and making shapes with your finger~

touch.line: Feeling chilly? You can come closer if you wanna~

touch2.line: Winter makes you wanna snuggle up, doesn't it~?

unlock.line: Whoa! Talk about a stunning view! You like, totally know all the best spots in the city, Commander~ Hehe, okay, so... Merry Christmas!

win_mvp.line: This victory's almost as lit as this view!

detail.line: Why am I wearing Dragon Empery clothes? Because there's a Dragon Empery celebration today, duh~ Now if you don't mind, I'm gonna have myself a mooncake.

drop_descrip.line: The annual moon gazing festival's upon us again~ Ah, so you know a thing or two about the Mid-Autumn Festival, Commander? Then I reckon you know what we're doing tonight, right~? ♡

home.line: Thanks for this sweet gift you brought back~ I'm gonna go show it to Memphis~

login.line: Let's see the prediction for Leos born today... Hmm, clearly something's wrong with my calculations here...

main1.line: Yo, this mooncake bussin'! Concord would love this little sugar bomb! I'll grab one and bring– Hm? This one's extra salty?

main2.line: You know the myth about rabbits on the moon? Bet those rabbits can jump, like, a mile up in zero-gravity.

main3.line: I don't mind you gawkin' at me, but you'll wanna gawk at the sky too. Full moons only come once a month, you know!

touch.line: Man, this view is awesome~

touch2.line: Whoa! Careful, or I might fall, Commander!

unlock.line: The annual moon gazing festival's upon us again~ Ah, so you know a thing or two about the Mid-Autumn Festival, Commander? Then I reckon you know what we're doing tonight, right~? ♡

detail.line: The shirt and sweater I can deal with, but my tights are like glue... Dunno where to put 'em after I take 'em off. Got any ideas, Commander?

drop_descrip.line: Phew... Should be in the clear now. Oh, hey, Commander. Whatcha doing here? Waiting for a cutie to show up or something? Surely it can't be a coincidence... right?

feeling5.line: High school romance is like, pretty done to death~ You wanna shake things up a bit? 'Kay, then how about... There's something I wanna tell ya. Can we go... to an empty classroom?

home.line: Weren't we gonna do the umbrella-sharing thing on our walk back to your office? ...Hahaha! I'm just messing with you~

login.line: Maaan, it's raining cats and dogs! My uniform's soaked through... Haha♡ D'ya like it that way, Commander?

lose.line: Crap, I'm all wet again... This wasn't part of the plan.

mail.line: Whoa, we got a message. Think it's a letter for you, Commander.

main1.line: Be your personal teacher? I'm down~ Which subjects, and for how long are we talkin'? Need to know for return-favor purposes♪

main2.line: Memphis?! Crap, my bad... Wouldn't've gotten THIS drenched if I'd warned ya ten seconds sooner... Err, forget I said anything!

main3.line: If you wanna check me out, n-now's the time... You can't ogle me once I've gotten changed... So yeah.

mission.line: Missions? ...Dang, I'll try again when the Commander's free...

mission_complete.line: Mission complete~ You wanna get something warm to drink? It's on me.

touch.line: A towel? Aww, you're too nice... Huh? Err, if you wanna dry me off, sure I guess...

touch2.line: Whoa! You don't want me to get changed first?

unlock.line: Phew... Should be in the clear now. Oh, hey, Commander. Whatcha doing here? Waiting for a cutie to show up or something? Surely it can't be a coincidence... right?

battle.line: Take a deep breath. The battle is starting...!

detail.line: I can go underwater, but... I'm no submarine. I can't stay submerged for long...

feeling1.line: Commander, I don't get you at all...

hp_warning.line: Minimize... the damage...!

mail.line: Commander, there's new mail waiting for you. Please don't forget to read it...

main1.line: July 9th... It's an important date for me.

main2.line: Huff... Puff... Huff... Puff... Yes, let's try to relax...

main3.line: Phoenix is a really hot-blooded girl, isn't she...? Compared to her... I might be pretty cold...

mission.line: Commander, there are still missions to finish. It'd be best to not forget about them...

propose.line: Whether through my battles or my everyday duties, I always want to do something extra for you... If y-you're fine with that side of me, then... Huff... Puff... Y-yes! Commander, I'll be in your care!

touch.line: Mm... I'm listening.

touch2.line: What exactly... is this...?

upgrade.line: Strengthening complete. Preliminary inspection in progress...

win_mvp.line: Battle completed. Safely.

detail.line: Huff...... Puff...... (It looks like Boise has fallen asleep)

drop_descrip.line: Huff... Puff... Deep breaths... I, I'll never get used to wearing this outfit in front of others... I think...

headtouch.line: Is something wrong... with my rabbit ears...?

home.line: Commander, would you like something to drink...? If you don't want something alcoholic, how about some of the juice that New Jersey recommended...?

login.line: Huff... I guess I'll be able to relax for the time being–– Huh? C-Commander?!

main1.line: Honolulu, you don't like standing out either...? T-then, how about relaxing over here with me?

main2.line: I'm not very good at singing... sorry, Commander...

main3.line: The music is a bit too loud for me...

touch.line: My handkerchief? Ah, umm, thank you...

touch2.line: I, I don't think you should be doing this... *blush*

unlock.line: Huff... Puff... Deep breaths... I'll never get used to wearing this outfit in front of others... I think...

headtouch.line: What do you think... about this witch's hat...?

home.line: W-was that a will-o'-wisp just now...?

login.line: Huff... Puff... Commander, these pumpkin lanterns are so nice and warm... Would you like to come sit by me...?

main1.line: Witches won't stand out much compared to zombies and Frankenstein's monsters... or so I thought.

main2.line: Phoenix, um... I'm planning on watching the parade from here, so I can't really participate in it with you...

main3.line: Commander, why don't you try putting on this pumpkin mask? Pfft... I-I'm sorry... I just couldn't hold it in...

touch.line: Commander, would you like to try trick-or-treating? I've still got a fair bit of candy left, if you'd like...

touch2.line: (Huff... Puff... Huff... Puff...) Y-You scared me...!

unlock.line: Um, I decided to try on a costume, since it's Halloween and all... Do you think I got that witchy look down...?

battle.line: Take a deep breath. The battle is starting...!

detail.line: Huff... Puff... (Boise seems to be fanning herself with her hands to try to cool down.)

drop_descrip.line: Huff... Puff... These Dragon Empery clothes look good on me? It's rather revealing and breezy, and makes me feel self-conscious... but if you like it, I suppose it's fine...

expedition.line: Here are the results from the commission... Please look over them.

feeling1.line: Commander, I don't get you at all...

feeling2.line: There's nothing in particular that needs doing right now. Commander... why don't you relax for a bit...?

hp_warning.line: Minimize... the damage...!

lose.line: We'll be fine... Commander, we'll be able to withdraw soon.

mail.line: Commander, there's new mail waiting for you. Please don't forget to read it...

main1.line: Hiding one's face behind a fan is an established custom here... Huff...

main2.line: I didn't expect Marblehead to be so familiar with Dragon Empery customs... She really knows her stuff... H-huh, she's just trying to sound smart?

main3.line: Huff... Puff... The food sure smells amazing... Man, I'm totally starving... Oh, um, it's n-nothing!

mission.line: Commander, there are still missions to finish. It'd be best to not forget about them...

mission_complete.line: Umm, Commander, I reminded you earlier, but... please collect the mission rewards at some point.

profile.line: You'd like to learn more about what I did during that war? Well, I provided support for many landing invasions... The most memorable one? That'd be the one at Cape Esperance... Helena saved me back then.

propose.line: Whether through my battles or my everyday duties, I always want to do something extra for you... If y-you're fine with that side of me, then... Huff... Puff... Y-yes! Commander, I'll be in your care!

touch.line: Commander, are you also running a bit hot...?

touch2.line: Nn... Mmgh...

unlock.line: Huff... Puff... These Dragon Empery clothes look good on me? It's rather revealing and breezy, and makes me feel self-conscious... but if you like it, I suppose it's fine...

win_mvp.line: Phew... I-is the battle over now...?

battle.line: I'm in top form... Let's start today's work!

detail.line: Like they say, knowledge is power—and I'm just overflowing with power right now. Commander, I'm ready to exceed expectations any time!

drop_descrip.line: Cleveland-class light cruiser – Houston II, Hull Number CL-81.

expedition.line: Mister Rocket and Mister Plane are friends~... Commander, were you listening?! U-umm! The commission is done, so you'd better go check it out!

feeling1.line: Am I misremembering? You used to be more, uh...

feeling2.line: It's been so long since we played, Commander~ And it's even more fun than I remember! Heheh!♪

feeling3.line: *whispering* N-no, Houston, you can't hang around the Commander all day every... Huh? N-nothing, Commander! So, how about we take a walk together?

feeling4.line: Why do I look troubled? Listen close! ...D-do you hear my heartbeat, Commander? It's thumping and pounding all because of you...

feeling5.line: Commander, do you remember what I said to you long ago? It's okay if you don't. Either way, I'm going to confess again... *exhale*... L-listen carefully, please!

headtouch.line: That feels good... Pat me more, Commander...

home.line: Heheh! Another huge combat mission victory for Houston!

hp_warning.line: May our return to the port be a safe one...

login.line: Welcome back! Now, let's get to today's work... Huh? Where should we hang out after? But we haven't even started... Focus, Commander!

lose.line: I lost... I'd better review my mistakes carefully...

mail.line: Commander, you have a letter. Oh, do you want me to bring it to you?

main1.line: Yahoo? Kinda takes you back, huh... How long has it been since I last said that? If you wanna hear it again... Y-yahoo~☆

main2.line: Which Houston is your type, Commander? The energetic, happy-go-lucky one? Or the cool and calm one? ...Both? Heheheh~

main3.line: You can't master something overnight. Time and effort are key... Keep an eye on me while I do my best, okay, Commander?

mission.line: Commander, you have unfinished missions. Let's take care of them together!

mission_complete.line: I'll go check for any missed rewards just in case.

profile.line: ...You think I seem a lot more stable now? Heheh, thanks for the compliment! I think I come off that way because of how composed I've become.

propose.line: Th-that's weird... I wanted to answer normally, but now that it's really happening, I'm so happy that I don't know what to say... *inhale*... *exhale*... For realsies?! I love you, too, Commander!☆

touch.line: Commander? Something wrong?

touch2.line: You just never stop being a perv, huh?

unlock.line: Commander, I return to you in a whole new style. ...I look like a different person altogether? Heehee, that's what they call growth, isn't it?

upgrade.line: I'm so strong now, I bet I could hit escape velocity with ease!

win_mvp.line: Thanks for the praise! Heheh...

battle.line: Against enemies like these it's OK to just use half your strength!

detail.line: Maintenance? OK, tell me if you notice anything weird.

drop_descrip.line: Pensacola-class Heavy Cruiser – Pensacola, Hull Number CA-24!

expedition.line: Hey, a commission's been completed! ... It's not OK to just ignore those hardworking girls, you hear?

feeling1.line: Hey, Commander, this isn't OK at all.

feeling2.line: If you have a problem, let me handle it and it'll be OK! I can help you whenever you need it!

feeling3.line: Are we going out? OK, I'll let you decide where we're going. I'm fine with going anywhere, so just pick whatever you want!

feeling4.line: Are you tired? OK, come over here and lie down. I'll wake you up in an hour! Good night~

feeling5.line: You want to try my homemade cooking? OK, don't be shy, request anything you want and I'll make it for you!

home.line: How about a massage, Commander? ... OK, just sit down and relax!

login.line: Anything you need help with, Commander? I'm OK with helping you out any time!

lose.line: Damn... This isn't OK at all...

mail.line: I've got your mail... here! Here you go, Commander.

main1.line: I've got the same nickname as Enterprise... Pretty cool, huh?

main2.line: If you're tired, get some rest! Don't push yourself. If you ever want help, don't be shy to ask!

main3.line: Though I may look like this, I've seen quite a few battles. Wanna hear about them? OK, then let's start from the beginning...

mission.line: We have a new mission? OK, let's get it done together!

mission_complete.line: Commander? Don't forget about those rewards!

profile.line: OKOK, self-introduction time, right? I'm Pensacola, I have a little sister named Salt Lake City… Uh, what else do I even say when introducing myself? I helped out Hornet and Yorktown, but there's not much to say about that… Oh well, anyway, let me handle everything and it'll be OK!

propose.line: Is this for me? O... wait, hold on a sec! Are you serious? No no, no way in… What I mean is, OK means OK, but… Ahh, screw it! If it's from you then it's totally OK, that's obvious!

skill.line: Main guns: OK! Armor: OK! We're doing this!

touch.line: I'm always OK with heading out on a sortie~

touch2.line: H-hey, that's not at all what this gesture means!

unlock.line: Are you the commander of this fleet? Why, I'd say you look pretty reliable! … OKOK, I'm Pensacola, from now on I'll follow your orders. Nice to meet you!

upgrade.line: Now it's my turn? OK~

win_mvp.line: Easy peasy lemon squeezy~

battle.line: Those aren't allies up ahead. Ready all weapons!

detail.line: Sometimes good things happen when you're just coasting across the sea.

drop_descrip.line: Pensacola-class Heavy Cruiser – Salt Lake City, Hull Number CA-25!

expedition.line: Whew, those girls went out on a commission in this blazing heat? They even completed it, too. Must be awful out there~

feeling1.line: Commander, that look in your eyes kinda creeps me out...

feeling2.line: Helena, could you go find something interesting with that radar of yours? Wait... that's San Diego? Great, let's go play in the water together!

feeling3.line: Commander, don't you ever get bored of lying around on the beach? Why don't we play some beach volleyball? Sun burn? No worries, Pensacola has already rubbed me down with sunscreen.

feeling4.line: You can always rest on my lap if you get tired, Commander. Don't worry, I won't play any tricks on you. ... Hm? I've always been this kind to you!

feeling5.line: Welcome back, Commander! I was just about to finish drying your laundry. I cleaned up the books and other stuff that was lying around. How's it look? The tidiest it's ever been, right? And dinner will be... Hm? Why am I doing all this? Well, you know... just preparing for what comes later!

headtouch.line: Your hand feels just like Pensacola's...

home.line: Oh man, my skin is on fire... Sorry, Vestal, think I could ask for a spa treatment from you?

login.line: Commander, want to go swimming together?

lose.line: Wuah! I'm out of armor-piercing shells... damn!

mail.line: New mail for you. Oh my, is this a love letter? ... Hmm... Okay, now where's the trashcan?

main1.line: If you don't know how to swim then I can teach you, Commander.

main2.line: Shell Kiska Island? Ahaha... that'd be a new experience for me.

main3.line: Enterprise is too strict. Please don't be like her, Commander.

mission.line: Who cares about missions, let's party!

mission_complete.line: Can we go join the party now?

profile.line: I'm Salt Lake City, second ship of the Pensacola-class. That's right, I'm a genuine heavy cruiser. My armor's thin because of that treaty thing, but my firepower holds up. Although, I participated in lots of battles in the Pacific and survived to the end of it, so maybe armor isn't that important. The battle of Attu Island? Luck is a power of sorts too, you know? ... No, no, I'm not arguing. Anyway, do you really want me to wear as much as Laffey does?

propose.line: It's a promise, Commander! Every day from now on you'll hang out with me and do the stuff I enjoy. Like surfing, beach volleyball, and... scuba diving, I guess? Of course, I'll hang out with you and do all the stuff you enjoy, too~!

skill.line: The best defense is a good offense!

touch.line: Oh, it's you, Commander. I thought it was Pensacola...

touch2.line: Hey, don't do the same stuff Pensacola does...

unlock.line: Commander, I'm Salt Lake City, a heavy cruiser! You think I'm exposing too much? Well, I gotta keep a close eye on my waist, you know?

upgrade.line: Us pretty girls need to take care to maintain our good looks.

win_mvp.line: This time it wasn't just all luck!

battle.line: The battle horn has sounded! C'mon, let's go!

detail.line: My armor's gotten thicker, but it feels like I'm more exposed than before...

drop_descrip.line: Northampton-class Heavy Cruiser – Northampton, Hull Number CA-26!

expedition.line: Hey, you have a commission that's been completed.

feeling1.line: I'm getting distracted here, so do you think you could be quiet for a bit?

feeling2.line: I'm not really the talkative type, but if you're still willing to be my friend, then maybe...

feeling3.line: I have a buddy who's a bit noisy and little sisters who are pretty rowdy, so having a friend like you who's rather quiet feels pretty unusual...

feeling4.line: Smiling? I guess it's true that I rarely smile... I'm a pretty stubborn girl, and I don't have many friends... Hm... If you like girls who smile, then I'll try to do that every now and then...

feeling5.line: ... Someone I love, huh? Well, there is someone, but I don't think I can say their name just like that... Hey, Commander, aren't you a lot like me? Hornet always tells me I'm not good at adapting to new things, and neither are you...

home.line: Nobody got left behind, right? Then the fleet's safely made it back.

login.line: With proper training, I think we could make quite the team, Commander.

lose.line: I knew we couldn't win that easily...

mail.line: Commander, I've left your mail on the desk.

main1.line: You'll start to calm down if you just sit and listen to the waves...

main2.line: Houston, you're too loud! Pipe the hell down!

main3.line: Hold on, I'm thinking about something...

mission.line: Looks like that mission hasn't been completed yet. Let me handle it!

mission_complete.line: Rewards have arrived. You should check them out.

profile.line: I'm Northampton, a Washington Treaty cruiser. I participated in the Doolittle Raid and the Battle of Midway, and I've earned 6 battle stars. I regret not being able to bring Hornet back home in one piece...

propose.line: You finally realized it, didn't you, you dense man... But to be fair, I never had the courage to put it into words either... A-anyway, from now on, let's work together as dense partners in love, shall we?

touch.line: Um, I'm a... little ticklish right there...

unlock.line: Hm? Oh hey, Commander. If you can accurately predict where I'm gonna show up, then maybe we're in sync with each other... If only Hornet and I could be like that... *Sigh*...

upgrade.line: Thank you. I'll have you rewarded for this later.

win_mvp.line: I never thought I'd be able to do something like this...

battle.line: What a pleasant breeze~

detail.line: Don't just stare at boring numbers all day... how about staring at something with more meat to it for a change?

drop_descrip.line: Northampton-class Heavy Cruiser – Chicago, Hull Number CA-29!

expedition.line: Looks like the girls who went out on a commission have returned. How about we do something fun before we go greet them?

feeling1.line: You still have a lot to learn about women, Commander...

feeling2.line: The night is still young, Commander. Why don't we have some adult fun together? ... Just kidding~!

feeling3.line: Most people aren't very good at dealing with me. You have a peculiar taste in women, Commander...

feeling4.line: I've been a little more moderate lately? Indeed. That's because, for the first time in my life, I've met someone dear to me. That's why I need to behave myself~

feeling5.line: Oh dear, you don't look too good. Too much pent-up stress, perhaps? ... Then let me do the cooking. I have some responsibility of you too, after all~!

home.line: Well done out there. Come here and use my body to recover your energy~

login.line: Don't get too into ignoring me, okay, Commander~?

lose.line: Oh no, my clothes are torn~!

mail.line: You've got new mail, but it seems to be stuck here... Come~ take~ it~!

main1.line: Women can change as quickly as the wind in Chicago, Commander~

main2.line: At this distance, nobody else can hear us~

main3.line: Your shoulders are so stiff. How about a massage to help you relax?

mission.line: I put your new missions in order... Even I can actually do my job sometimes.

mission_complete.line: Our rewards are here. You're always out there pulling off great stunts, aren't you, Commander?

profile.line: I'm Chicago, fourth ship of the Northampton-class. I've never really done anything noteworthy in battle, and I've never been particularly lucky. But I'll do my best for you, Commander. So be nice to me~ *Kiss*

propose.line: I've restrained myself for so long waiting for you to give me this. But now that I have it, there's no need for self-restraint, is there? That being the case... you should brace yourself, Commander. Cause you won't be getting away from me~

skill.line: Oh my, you're not getting away from me!

touch.line: I'll show you how to have a good time~

touch2.line: Aahh~ You're a naughty boy, Commander~

unlock.line: So you're the commander? You're looking at me almost like you want me to feel you up. Things will get fun starting tomorrow.

upgrade.line: People are counting on me, so I'll need to work hard too~

win_mvp.line: I'm expecting some juicy rewards when we get back~

battle.line: Tadah! Another day, another energy-packed departure!

detail.line: Am I a light cruiser or a heavy cruiser? You sure like to ponder over weird stuff, Commander~

drop_descrip.line: Northampton-class Heavy Cruiser – Houston, Hull Number CA-30!

expedition.line: Mister rocket and mister plane are friends yet again~... Hm? Commander, a commission's been completed!

feeling1.line: You're no fun at all, Commander...

feeling2.line: Exeter is a good person at heart, but all she talks about is glory and royalty and stuff. Boooring!

feeling3.line: Bang! Ratatatata! ... Whew, today's been a lot of fun! I really love playing with you, Commander~

feeling4.line: Houston, you've got a problem... Commander, whenever I see you, I get so anxious I can't even speak properly... What should I do...

feeling5.line: Commander, how about we just relax today instead of going out to play? I... I have something I want to tell you, so listen up, okay?

home.line: Hehe~ Fighting's what a soldier does, right!

hp_warning.line: Oh no, our score is falling behind...

login.line: I get to play with the commander again today! Yahoo~!

lose.line: Ooow... My head's spinning... I think I bumped into something even harder than me...

mail.line: Commander, Commander! There's mail for you!

main1.line: Commander, sometimes you're a little preachy, so just chill out~

main2.line: I had such an exciting time in Surabaya!

main3.line: Come on, Commander, let's play!

mission.line: Co~man~der~! You've still got some unfinished missions!

mission_complete.line: Don't forget to claim your rewards!

profile.line: Hiya! I'm Houston, fifth ship of the Northampton-class! I received a Medal of Honor from the President for facing off against an entire Sakura Empire squadron in the Battle of the Java Sea and the Battle of Sunda Strait, all on my own! I'm really proud of it~!

propose.line: Thank you, Commander~ I love you~! Hehe, you don't need to be so serious about! Come on, let's go somewhere and play!

touch.line: Ah, my brain's stopped working...

touch2.line: Gosh, Commander... you're a real weirdo... aren't you!

unlock.line: Hiya! I'm Houston, fifth ship of the Northampton-class. I single-handedly took on Sakura Empire reinforcements in the Battle of the Sunda Strait! I hope I'll get to play with you every day from now on! Yahoo~!

upgrade.line: Whoosh! Houston's breaking through the first escape velocity!

win_mvp.line: Yaaay! C'mon, praise me!

battle.line: ... Indy... Ah, that's not it... Everyone, follow me!

detail.line: Hey, Commander, please hear me out! My little sister is super duper cute!

drop_descrip.line: Portland-class Heavy Cruiser – Portland, Hull Number CA-33!

expedition.line: Commander, can I pair up with Indy for the next commission? I'll show you some cute pictures of her later!

feeling1.line: Don't interrupt me when I'm fantasizing about Indy!

feeling2.line: Indy's soooooo cute!

feeling3.line: Commander, do you want to see some photos of Indy when she was little? I'll show them to you even if you say no!

feeling4.line: Commander, where's that photo of Indy eating a watermelon? Ah, thank you! And the one where she's hugging a body pillow? Ah, that's where it was, thank you~! Before I knew it, you've actually gotten more familiar with my Indy collection than I have~

feeling5.line: ... Kids? Let me think... I want them to look like Indy, and... I want ten! Let's say ten to start with! ... Huh?! Aahh! Just what are you making me say~?!

home.line: Commander, I left an Indy plushie here, have you seen it?

login.line: Hey, Commander, please hear me out! My little sister is super cute!

lose.line: Dammit... I can't let my little sister see me like this!

mail.line: I brought your mail, Commander~! What? Even I can do my job right every now and then!

main1.line: Come on, Commander, let's head out already. Indy doesn't like people who slack around!

main2.line: My little sister is just so lovely~

main3.line: Would you like to see my special Indy mags?

mission.line: If I don't do these missions properly then I can't show myself to my little sister.

mission_complete.line: Commander, can I use the rewards to buy snacks for Indy?

profile.line:
I'm Portland, Indy's big sister~! Do it again, properly this time? Aww... If only they'd have called us the Indianapolis-class, rather than the Portland-class... 
I have 16 battle stars and I've participated in a few big operations too, but who cares about me? Why don't we just talk about my little sister instead?

propose.line: It seems you and I are always appreciating just how cute Indy is, Commander... But to me, Indy still always comes first! This is the one thing I'm not giving up!

skill.line: Aahh, Indy is sooo cute... Hey, could you stop interrupting me?

touch.line: Commander, Commander, please hear me out! Indy's like, sooo soft! Want to touch her together with me?

touch2.line: Whoa! ... Not even Indy has touched me like that before!

unlock.line: Nice to meet you, Commander. I'm Portland, Indy's big sister. I've participated in the battles of the Coral Sea, Midway, Guadalcanal and Santa Cruz Islands. Hm? Who's Indy? Why, it's a nickname for my dear little sister, Indianapolis!

upgrade.line: Now I can do some more of this and some more of that to Indy!

win_mvp.line: My cute little Indy~ Look! Aren't I amazing~?

drop_descrip.line: Commander, look, look! This is my handmade Indy plushie! Isn't it utterly adorable?! It's the magnum opus of my work in the Arts & Crafts Club!

home.line: When Indy's dyed rose red from the setting sun on the way back from school... ahhh, she's so cuuuuuute! Don't you want to see how she looks too, Commander?!

login.line: Oh, Commander, have you seen Indy? I want to dress her in some super adorable clothes I made~ Guhehehe~

main1.line: Commander, why don't we go for lunch? Of course, my dear Indy will be there too!

main2.line: Whether on the way to school, in class, or heading home, I'm always with Indy... School life is the best thing EVER!

main3.line: I bet you'd make a good teacher, Commander... So, please, take pictures of Indy from every angle during class! Later, I'll trade you for regular pictures of her!

touch.line: You think Indy's suuuuper cute too, right? She really is! If you want, I'll let you cuddle with my Indy plushie just a bit!

touch2.line: Eek?! Be careful, Commander! I nearly pricked myself with my needle!

unlock.line: Commander, look, look! This is my handmade Indy plushie! Isn't it utterly adorable?! It's the magnum opus of my work in the Arts & Crafts Club!

detail.line: Commander, did you know? Indy is thiiiiiiis cute!

drop_descrip.line: Nice to meet you, I'm Indianaportland! ... Hm? Who's Indy? She's my precious little sister, and my most beloved...

main1.line: Commander, you're not getting away anymore! Come here, I'm gonna tell you all about my special Indy mags! Today's the day that I'll fully drill Indy's appeal into your head!

unlock.line: School life... It's nice as long as you and my sister are here... I think...

unlock.line: Oh. Good evening, Commander. Do you want some steak? It goes great with wine.

touch.line: What's up? What is it?

win_mvp.line: Hehe, I'm pretty capable, aren't I~

feeling3.line: Hurting others is more painful than being hurt yourself... Huh? Doesn't everyone feel that way?

login.line: What took you so long, Commander?

main1.line: What are you looking at? You want a drink, huh? Why didn't you just say so right away?

main2.line: Trick-or-treaters? It's your job to deal with those. Wouldn't want to risk petrifying any children with my terrific costume.

main3.line: Raising the brim of my witch hat to reveal my razor-sharp fangs – now that's what I'm talking about!

touch.line: Come, familiar. Get up on the pumpkin and take in the Halloween spirit.

touch2.line: Desperate to once more taste the sting of my whip, are we?

unlock.line: Tonight I am not a renowned naval general, I am a feared commander of witches! And you... Yes, you're not my lieutenant, you are my arcane familiar!

feeling1.line: You're like a little kid, Commander.

feeling2.line: Weapons are extensions of our own bodies. They need regular care, too.

feeling3.line: What do I do off-duty? Hmm. I hang out with my sisters, I go fishing, I take naps... Things like that.

main3.line: My sisters are all very eccentric. Hehe, rest assured, they're good people all the same.

touch.line: Whether you want close contact, or hand-to-hand combat, I'll oblige.

touch2.line: Hehehe. You wouldn't stand a chance against me in a real fight.

unlock.line: Heavy cruiser New Orleans, reporting in. Hehe, you'll be sure to receive a medal for finding me. Anyway... Do you have any urgent tasks for me?

upgrade.line: You think I can handle this power? Thank you. I'll trust you.

win_mvp.line: War is about always thinking two or three steps ahead of the enemy.

detail.line: I could've sworn that stuffed toy's eyes flashed red just now... Hmm... Maybe I've had too much.

drop_descrip.line: To your prestige, and to your continued victories, Commander. Hehe, I do find myself in the mood for rum tonight. Care to keep me company for a while?

home.line: Ah, welcome back. I was just drinking and watching TV while you were out. I might get more than just tipsy tonight... Hehehe~

main1.line: Thank you, Javelin. Deliver this bottle to Wichita. It's very valuable. Hehe~

main2.line: On a random note, why does San Francisco call you "pudding"? Is it because you're so sweet, perhaps? Hehehe~

main3.line: Lexington is indeed a very good friend to me, though her sister can be a piece of work... Ahahaha.

touch.line: Don't worry, I would never spike your drink~

touch2.line: Commander... You're unexpectedly needy, aren't you?

win_mvp.line: Hehe, a victory sweetens the taste.

battle.line: Who will be my next prey?

home.line: Welcome back, Commander! Gimme a big hug before I update my Juustagram~ Ahaha♪

login.line: Welcome back, Commander! Just gonna update my Juustagram status to "With the Commander"...

main1.line: I'm surprised how easy to wear this is. Maybe I'll do something physical while wearing it... like playing tennis. Ahahah! Just kidding♪

main3.line: *click!* You look so cute in this pic! I'm so saving this... You're wondering if I'll post it to Juustagram? Heheh, nah, this one's for me to look back on fondly. My followers don't get to see it♪

touch.line: Hm? Do ya wanna hold the bouquet too? I mean, I guess you can...

touch2.line: So, do you like what you see? Oh, and whisper me your answer♪

drop_descrip.line: The name's Baltimore, Eagle Union heavy cruiser. Whoops, right, I'm not just a soldier anymore, but an idol as well. I agreed to do it, and I'm gonna do it as best I can. We'll be counting on your support, Commander.

expedition.line: Commission complete! What do you say we welcome them back with a small performance?

feeling1.line: A control freak like you isn't fit to instruct us. Loosen up a bit, then try again.

feeling2.line: Your job is to plan our schedule, and our job is to follow it. So business as usual, I guess, huh? Hahahah!

feeling3.line: How do I look, Commander? This outfit's more revealing than what I'm used to... D-does it really make me look cuter?

feeling4.line: "Thanks for supporting me!" ...Yeah, Bremerton's right, my delivery is just a bit off... Hey, Commander, do I fit in with the other members? Am I really... cute?
