home.line: Oh, you're back. Hope everyone else made it safe and sound too. An idol needs an audience, after all.

hp_warning.line: A small screwup isn't gonna stop me!

login.line: What's on our schedule today, Commander? Same as always, I'm counting on you.

lose.line: Looks like we need to rehearse it from the top...

mail.line: Thanks, Dido, I really appreciate it. Got a letter for you here, Commander.

main1.line: There's tons of idol business to tend to, so I've not had much time to help people. Think you pick up the mantle for a while, Commander? Thanks, you're a hero! Hahahah!

main2.line: These moves might be too hard for the Royal Navy girls... What do you think, Commander?

main3.line: Th-this whole "cute" thing isn't exactly my thing... N-not that I hate it, and YOU seem to like it, I guess... Ughh...

mission.line: Mission time, eh... You're really not in an enviable position, having to keep doing those while we work as idols.

mission_complete.line: Got some mission rewards here. Oh, and I got rid of that trap Albacore set.

profile.line: Heavy cruiser Baltimore, currently serving as an idol to test the Muse System. I'm giving it my all to put on the best performance you'll ever see.

propose.line: This I promise you, Commander: we'll all work together to bring you the best performance ever! In return I ask for one thing: that you witness it, and witness me, at my cutest.

skill.line: Far and near! Hear our song loud and clear!

touch.line: How's this for a signature pose? Good?

touch2.line: Eep! What was that for?!

unlock.line: The name's Baltimore, Eagle Union heavy cruiser. Whoops, right, I'm not just a soldier anymore, but an idol as well. I agreed to do it, and I'm gonna do it as best I can. We'll be counting on your support, Commander.

upgrade.line: Thanks a bunch. Guess I should say: look forward to our next performance!

win_mvp.line: Picking me was the right choice, am I right? I'm never gonna let you down.

battle.line: No need to think too hard... Just head out!

detail.line: Hmm? What's up? Are you that curious about my new look?

drop_descrip.line: Oregon City-class heavy cruiser – Northampton II, Hull Number CA-125.

expedition.line: Commission complete. Let's go welcome our friends back.

feeling1.line: I guess we aren't two peas in a pod, after all...

feeling2.line: Even though I used to not talk that much, I feel like I've started to change. Though, it's still hard to think up topics to talk about...

feeling3.line: Commander, today, uhh... um... How's your work going? Oh, I'm not keeping tabs on you, I just wanted to say hello... I guess I couldn't strike up a conversation again...

feeling4.line: I don't need to come up with anything specifically and should just try to be natural? I see, I'll give it a try. Umm... Oh, sorry. I-I end up getting nervous as soon as I see your face...

feeling5.line: You want me to be with you for a bit... and I don't need to do anything but just be there with you? Then, I won't have to try so hard to think up a topic...? I see. Then I'll be here by your side until you feel satisfied.

home.line: I've confirmed that everyone has returned safely. Good work, Commander.

hp_warning.line: Things aren't looking so good.

login.line: Commander, I'll be counting on you for today's training as always.

lose.line: Sorry. It wasn't supposed to go this way...

mail.line: It's a letter for you. Yes... Should I leave it on your desk?

main1.line: Houston... Hornet... I wonder if it's because I've spent so much time with them, but it seems that I've changed a bit as well. Umm, for example... I don't hate busy places anymore...

main2.line: Commander, it's nice out. Umm... Ah, um, sorry, I just wanted to come up with a topic to talk about...

main3.line: It got quiet all of a sudden. I suppose it's fine... to focus on your work.

mission.line: A new mission? Want me to help?

mission_complete.line: Mission complete. Don't forget to collect your rewards.

profile.line: I've said before that I truly regretted not being able to bring Hornet back safely... but I never thought we'd both have a chance to ride the waves together again. For this journey ahead of us, I'll be there to witness the scenery with you!

propose.line: I'm truly thankful that you started up the conversation on your own. Knowing me, I don't know how long it would've taken for me to open up. Ahaha... As members of the overcoming-awkwardness alliance, let us work hard together.

touch.line: Oh. Sorry, I'm a bit ticklish...

touch2.line: Ugh! What's with you...

unlock.line: We meet again, Commander. It's me, Northampton. For you to know exactly where I'd show up again, I guess we really are two peas in a pod. So... Are you pleased with how I turned out?

upgrade.line: Want me to test out my new armaments?

win_mvp.line: There's nothing better than returning home safely with sweet victory in your hands.

detail.line: The submarine girls love playing at the bottom of the pool. They even brought along little toy torpedoes. I'm kind of envious of them... but also worried at the same time...

drop_descrip.line: Whew. How many laps have I done since my last break...? Oh. Commander, are you here to hone your swimming skills too?

home.line: Houston, wait up... Sigh... How many times have I told her not to run off randomly...

login.line: What wonderful weather to go for a swim. Mm, I'm sure everyone who's come to this pool has thought the same thing.

main1.line: I've heard that you're the port's best-kept secret when it comes to athletic prowess. I'd like to see it for myself.

main2.line: Unlike when I'm wearing my rigging, I get to stretch my body when I go swimming. In that sense, it's a kind of relaxation, isn't it?

main3.line: Hornet? I've heard that she prefers the beach to the pool. You might run into her if you head on over.

touch.line: Ahahaha... I told you I'm ticklish...

touch2.line: S-stop that...! *blushes*

unlock.line: Whew. How many laps have I done since my last break...? Oh. Commander, are you here to hone your swimming skills too?

battle.line: How lively! Allow me to join in the fun!

detail.line: At times like these, I tend to like your mindfulness...

drop_descrip.line: Nevada-class battleship – Nevada, Hull Number BB-36!

expedition.line: Commander, the commissions have returned without issue. Make sure to comlement them for their efforts!

feeling1.line: I'm a bit disappointed in you...

feeling2.line: I'm quite confident in my own luck. Want to gamble a bit?

feeling3.line: Commander, Oklahoma told me about a nice shop around here. Wanna have a look? ... Hey, stop standing there like a pole! Let's go

feeling4.line: If you like someone, just say it up front. What use is there to hide it? ...It's just not like you at all, Commander!

feeling5.line: The idea behind priority defenses? That is to protect our most important areas... What, you want to know how important they are? W-well, if it's you...

home.line: If you're tired, you can always rest on my shoulders. Don't be embarrassed. Come on!

login.line: Hey, get your spirits up!

lose.line: Tsk, wait and see how I take you on next time!

mail.line: Yo~ Commander! A message!

main1.line: Gambling? I'm not usually interested, but I'll give it a shot with you if you're up for it!

main2.line: Commander, go do what you want while you're still young!

main3.line: Bantry Bay Squadron? I just missed my chance, you see...

mission.line: As soldiers, completing missions is our divine duty.

mission_complete.line: Mission rewards have been delivered!

propose.line: Oh you... what are you doing, getting so bold at a time like this? Have you never considered the time and place for such an important thing? Hmph. yeah yeah. I'm not saying no, so bring it.

touch.line: Who knew you were a people person?

touch2.line: Are you that interested in my 'priority defenses'?

upgrade.line: Mmm, not a bad feeling!

win_mvp.line: Ha, you think you can beat me with such weak firepower and defences?

battle.line: Let's give 'em a good whoopin'!

unlock.line: Howdy, young'un! Aren't you tired from goin' around greetin' fancy people? Come over here and relax with me and some good food.

main1.line: That Oklahoma, she's ain't so wet behind the ears anymore. Soon she's gonna be all independent.

unlock.line: Heh, with this, I won't be outperformed by those fancy greenhorn battleships. Young'un, from now on, just leave everything to Nevada here!

detail.line: Huh? What are you looking at? Is there something on my face?

drop_descrip.line: Nevada-class battleship – Oklahoma, Hull Number BB-37!

expedition.line: The commissions have been completed. It would be nice if this brings peace.

feeling1.line: I wonder if my eyes are lying...

feeling2.line: Is the Commander looking at me? Ehehe, I'm so happy!

feeling3.line: Commander, want to go on a date with me? I know a lot of good shops around~

login.line: Commander~ Please work hard with me today as well~

lose.line: *Cries*... I need to work even harder!

main2.line: In two years... no, one year, I will surpass my sister for sure!

main3.line: Commander, I will always listen to your troubles if you have any, you hear?

mission.line: Let's finish the missions like a speedy swifty!

mission_complete.line: Don't forget to claim your rewards!

profile.line: I'm Oklahoma of the Nevada class. I served in both the Atlantic and Pacific fleets... I even bore the duty of engaging in 'friendly' diplomacy!

propose.line: Ehehe~ Commander, let's go and report to big sis about us right now~

touch.line: Commander, your hand feels comforting to me...

touch2.line: Whaa?! Geez... My heart wasn't ready for this...

unlock.line: Commander... eh, ah... I'm sorry! I was stunned just by looking at you... Ah, no, no... Nice to meet you! I'm Oklahoma!

upgrade.line: Commander, is there any way i can help you with this?

win_mvp.line: With this, big sis won't have to worry about me! I think.

login.line: Haah... Commander looks so dreamy today as well... Oh, uh, forget you heard anything!

main1.line: Naughty Manjuus who try to pull hijinks in front of the Commander will be punished by three minutes inside the cannon barrel instead of the time-out room!

main2.line: I paid extra attention to all sorts of details, from the feathers in my hat to the tassels on my clothes! I'm really glad you noticed them!

main3.line: I actually made this little Manjuu eyepatch myself. If there are any doodads you want me to make for you, just hit me up!

touch.line: Alrighty, let's put our best foot forward today as well!

touch2.line: Eep?! Wh-what's gotten into you?!

win_mvp.line: Commander, I won! Hehe~!

drop_descrip.line: Thanks a ton, Commander. With my new strength, do you think I've managed to catch up to my sister a little? Ehehe, for your sake, I'll work even harder!

home.line: I've already become more independent, so my sister told me that I'll be able to take care of you now! Ehehe~

login.line: Howdy, Commander~ Are you doin' well?

main1.line: Commander, how about we hold a Fleet Problem? I'm pretty good at those~

main2.line: Commander, wanna go riding with me? We can both ride the same horse, hehe~

main3.line: Hey Commander, you gotta hear this! I just scored a win against my sister! Yaaay~!

touch.line: Hmm? What's up, Commander? Do you need my help? Sure~ just leave it to me!

unlock.line: Thanks a ton, Commander. With my new strength, do you think I've managed to catch up to my sister a little? Ehehe, for your sake, I'll work even harder!

win_mvp.line: Commander, it's our victory! V~!

detail.line: Thanks. This is the first time someone has really cared about me...

expedition.line: Commission completed... Not bad. Everyone seems to be growing stronger.

feeling1.line: You're such a coward...

feeling2.line: You and Arizona can hide behind me. I'll protect you.

feeling3.line: You want to stand next to me?... Think carefully now. That is a very hard thing to do.

feeling4.line: It's alright if you don't want to push yourself further. You've worked very hard. I thought you were joking, but... How do I say this... I'm used to protecting others... But to meet someone who cares about me really is something else.

feeling5.line: Mmm, you've worked so hard. I didn't think that you'd be able to catch up with me... You want a reward? How about a kiss? Or an unforgettable evening? Both are fine with me~!

home.line: Having a drink after battle is something else. You want some?

login.line: Commander, you know you can always share any thoughts you have with me.

lose.line: I was a fool to have any expectations of your commanding abilities.

mail.line: Here, I got your mail. Will ya make sure to reply soon?

main1.line: Your eyes... Why do they look like those of an abandoned puppy?

main2.line: Can you please not look at me with those hungry eyes?

main3.line: You don't have the best imagination, do you?

mission.line: I say, have you forgotten a mission?

mission_complete.line: I left your rewards over there. Don't forget to collect them!

profile.line: I'm Pennsylvania, lead ship of an improved Nevada class. You can call me "Sister Penn." I really shouldn't brag, but I've sortied on countless successful missions. You can definitely depend on me!

propose.line: This fleet has turned into a place I can call home... The people I want to protect, and the person who protects me despite being unable to kill a bug, and then the 'me' who becomes so giddy for that person are all here... You idiot *blush*...

skill.line: Is that the best you've got?

touch.line: You dont have to get worked up over tiny things, Commander.

touch2.line: ...!! Hold up, are you alright in the head?

unlock.line: I'm Pennsylvania, lead ship of an improved Nevada class. You can call me "Sister Penn." I've sortied on countless successful missions, so you can be confident in my ability.

upgrade.line: You can depend on me.

win_mvp.line: Tsk...Winning like this is so dull...

battle.line: I shall trample our enemies underfoot!

detail.line: You brought lunch? Appreciate it. Be sure to give Arizona something as well.

drop_descrip.line: Halt! Who are you?! ...Oh, it's you, Commander. I briefly mistook you for a spy there. Why are you here? To spectate? Or, God forbid, to gather intel on my army?

expedition.line: Commission completed. It's vital to keep your troops and horses fed and equipped.

login.line: All right, so... Are we good? Phew... Scenes on horseback are always so draining.

main1.line: You falter not even in the presence of a general on her horse... Very good – you'll make an excellent soldier. Together, we will make great conquests!

main2.line: Are my looks really that exotic to you? Hahah! Your imagination is terribly limited.

main3.line: While I'm not as good at riding as Chapayev, I'm fairly capable on horseback... You think I'm outstanding, even? Really?

touch.line: How can Sister Penn help?

touch2.line: Unfortunately for you, this armor is the real deal.

unlock.line: Halt! Who are you?! ...Oh, it's you, Commander. I briefly mistook you for a spy there. Why are you here? To spectate? Or, God forbid, to gather intel on my army?

win_mvp.line: By my spear, the enemy is sundered!

battle.line: This time, I will protect all that I want...!

detail.line: Even me? ... Thank you very much!

drop_descrip.line: Pennsylvania-class Battleship –  Arizona, Hull Number BB-39!

expedition.line: The wind... A sign of the girls' return

feeling1.line: I wonder where I truly belong?

feeling2.line: Ahh... Apologies. I was thinking about something sad again...

feeling3.line: ...Thank you for always listening to me... I've been feeling much better now...

feeling4.line: I feel safe around you, Commander... I feel as if I'm not afraid to look ahead after thinking about what happened back then...

feeling5.line: I'm sorry... Ah, no, I'm just a little afraid... 'What if Commander doesn't come back after this mission?'... I can't stop my tears just thinking about it...

home.line: It's great to be back, safe and sound.

hp_warning.line: I can't cry!... I have to cry for happy times...!

login.line: Commander, do you understand my feelings for wanting to protect my friends?

lose.line: No more... Just this once, please let me have it my way...

mail.line: Commander, there's a mail for you. Interpersonal relationships are important.

main1.line: As long as I'm in Commander's memory, I'll never be alone

main2.line: In order to not forget about them... they... have always been with me

main3.line: Commander, did my facial expression bother you? I'm sorry...

mission.line: Commander... the... the missions. They're not done, you know?

mission_complete.line: Here's the list, but... Are the physical rewards really that important...?

profile.line:
I am the second ship of the Pennsylvania class battleships, born during summer, Arizona. 
Yes... the 'Tears of Arizona' is referring to me, but it's a little sad to call them tears... you see...

propose.line: I won't let that day happen again' you say? ...Thank you. Those are the words that resonated with my heart the most in my life... I believe in you!

touch.line: I've become calmer now...

touch2.line: Uh- Let's pretend that it didn't happen, alright?

unlock.line: I am the second ship of the Pennsylvania class, born during summer, Arizona. This time, I won't let that tragedy repeat itself...

upgrade.line: I will protect everyone...!

win_mvp.line: This feels great... It would be good if the nightmares go away at this rate...

battle.line: I'll give it my best shot...!

detail.line: Both in the past and present, being able to help your friends in various ways outside of battle is something to be happy about. Hm? You feel happy just from being with me...?

expedition.line: The girls seem to be back from their commissions. Good tidings arrive on the wind.

feeling5.line: I left the handkerchief I use to wipe my tears back at home. ...I had some trouble finding a good place to stow it away, and moreover, I don't feel like I'll be crying all that much. There's no need for you to worry, Commander.

headtouch.line: Pennsylvania? Oh, it's...

login.line: My desire to protect my friends... has been made possible here. Hehe, of course I'll continue to give it my all.

lose.line: Time to evacuate? Understood!

main1.line: If wearing this outfit means I can help my friends make wonderful memories, I don't mind doing it.

main2.line: Do you think I should try to learn some dance steps from a real dancer? Would it be okay if I asked California for help?

main3.line: Oh, Commander... there's something on your cheek. Let me wipe it off... and done.

mission_complete.line: The mission rewards have arrived. It's always nice to have extra supplies.

touch.line: Stay calm, Arizona...

touch2.line: Please keep this a secret from my sister...

unlock.line: I heard these clothes are from the Dragon Empery, but they're a bit... Umm, it's not that I dislike them, but the thought of you seeing me in them is rather embarrassing... B-but it's not like I'm going to start crying...

win_mvp.line: Dancing might not be my strong suit, but I know how to fight!

battle.line: March through the gates of hell! May our image be burned into the eyes of our enemies!

detail.line: You can look all you want. Just don't forget about your job.

drop_descrip.line: Tennessee-class battleship –  Tennessee, Hull Number BB-43!

expedition.line: The commission team is back? Allow me to show how they should really be handled.

feeling1.line: You really are helpless...

feeling2.line: My motto is, 'survival of the fittest'

feeling3.line: Commander, you are still too weak. Come and train with me, and I will turn you into a proper Commander!

feeling4.line: You're looking good these days. Hmm? Ah, not to worry. I've always stuck around with you. I don't want all the training to be in vain, after all.

login.line: Commander, it's time to roll!

lose.line: Yes. Yes! This is the kind of challenge I'm looking for!

mail.line: Commander, you've got new mail

main1.line: Commander! If you don't sortie, I'll bring the girls and head to new waters myself!

main2.line: I totally cannot comprehend why you're so easygoing...

main3.line: The secret to getting a better figure?... Cease with such jokes.

mission.line: Hurry and take care of the missions, will you?

mission_complete.line: Your rewards are here, Commander.

profile.line: I am the new type of battleship, Tennessee. In terms of combat, my waterline protection and hull armor have been upgraded, and my fire control systems have improved my fighting capabilities further. Commander, your orders?

propose.line: If I take this, it means I'm yours forever? Fine, but on one condition; I want none of that 'You'll get hurt if you're in the battlefield' crap. I need some action every now and then!

touch.line: Mm... 'Cute' doesn't quite fit me.

touch2.line: I'm not a 'Clear' target like in a game!

unlock.line: You're the Commander? Hmm... Looks like you have potential. I'm motivated enough to help with your dreams. Ah, that reminds me, I am Tennessee. Got it memorized?

upgrade.line: Like a full score and then some... Not bad.

win_mvp.line: This kind of battle is quite good

battle.line: Don't panic...Calm down... Let's go!

detail.line: Commander, I will do my best to meet everyone's expectations

drop_descrip.line: Tennessee-class battleship –  California, Hull Number BB-44!

expedition.line: Commander, the girls from the commissions have returned. Let me do one next time, please~

feeling1.line: Commander, I'll go play on my own now~

feeling2.line: You don't know if you can be friends with someone unless you tried to make them. Commander, wanna hang out together?

feeling3.line: *humming* Ah, Commander~ Just who I was looking for. I was thinking about taking you some place to have fun!

feeling4.line: We've already had fun throughout the docks. How about we go some place farther? Just the two of us... Heh heh heh...

feeling5.line: Tennesee said to me, 'You must be careful who you choose as a partner.' 'Once you do, tell me', she also said. Well, if it's you, Commander, she won't say a word, I think...

home.line: You looked great just now, Commander!

login.line: Weather, check. Wind, check. A fine sailing day, Commander.

lose.line: Oof... Big sis will lecture me for sure!

mail.line: It's new mail. Wanna open it up right away?

main1.line: I feel different from big sister? That's not true. She might not look it but she's actually kind

main2.line: Ah~ Big sis didn't say much today... Wha! N-nothing at all!

main3.line: Ah, where did my undies go? Eheh

mission.line: Commander, don't forget to do your missions!

mission_complete.line: Hahaha, this is good!

profile.line: Hello. I am the second of the Tennessee class battleships, California. I was once the flagship of the Pacific fleet, and was part of the Atlantic fleet as well. How about it? Bet you didn't expect that I was a popular one, did you? Hehe~

propose.line: Commander, where are we going to play today? ...WHA! ...Seriously, I don't... I'm happy and all, but please don't pull this again. You surprised me...

touch.line: This is comfy. Every time big sis scolds me, she comforts me with this afterwards as well.

touch2.line: Wait-... Commander! Where are you touching? Big sis wouldn't do this!

unlock.line: Hello, Commander. I am California. It's not good to brag, but I'm quite strong you know. Do look forward to it~

upgrade.line: Now I can reach for further waters~

win_mvp.line: Aaah... that was a great workout

battle.line: I will not allow you to misbehave anymore... All guns, ready to fire a volley!

detail.line: Commander... Can you take your eyes off me?

drop_descrip.line: Colorado class battleship— Colorado, hull number BB-45

expedition.line: A lot of oil and supplies have been shipped in. Looks like we got plenty of both for the next mission.

feeling1.line: Commander, please… don’t come any closer.

feeling2.line: I’m proud of my BIG SEVEN title. Unfortunately the battleship era is closing, and a new wave of ships are arriving...

feeling3.line: Commander, why do you care about me so much? Many people are afraid of me and keep their distance from me. Perhaps I've been too used to this. But recently, I’ve suddenly felt... so lonely.

feeling4.line: The Commander is willing to talk to someone as bad-tempered as me. Such a weirdo... I don't hate talking to the Commander, though.

feeling5.line: The Commander's compliment after the end of each battle is something which I crave for. Commander, can you... praise me a little more?

home.line: Making sure everyone returns home safely is also one of my duties.

hp_warning.line: The bridge was hit? Damage control, now!

login.line: Commander, you’ve rested long enough. When shall we weigh anchor?

lose.line: This is not the end of the line...

mail.line: You’ve got new mail. There may be news from my sisters...

main1.line: Commander, although aircraft carriers are really powerful, but battleships are not obsolete. They are indispensable!

main2.line: Amelia... She was a great woman, though she still cannot be found. Perhaps she is flying freely in another world...

main3.line: My poor sisters were hurt on that humiliating day. One day, I will have those invaders pay for what they have done!

mission.line: Whether you need fire support or fleet battle, please give the order Commander.

mission_complete.line: Commander, mission reward has been delivered.

profile.line: I'm the lead ship of the Colorado class. In order to gain an advantage in the decisive battle, I'm the first ship to be equipped with 406mm guns. BIG SEVEN... is the most honored title for us battleships.

propose.line: Unknowingly I’ve slowly become more dependent on you, Commander. With the power of the BIG SEVEN, I shall protect you until my dying breath.

skill.line: It's time to show you the true power of the BIG SEVEN!

touch.line: Commander, please don't touch the main gun that I was just using, you will affect my shooting accuracy.

touch2.line: Shall I load the Commander into a 406mm gun and fire him?

unlock.line: Are you the one calling me? Well, I've been waiting for this day for a long time. In the name of the BIG SEVEN, Eagle Union battleship Colorado, reporting in.

upgrade.line: Emm, as one of the BIG SEVEN, my powers are unquestionable. Although, timely enhancements are still a necessity.

win_mvp.line: Huh? Am I the MVP? Such a piece of cake for one of the BIG SEVEN.

battle.line: I can't let you get caught up in the battle... Shoo, hurry away!

detail.line: Commander, um... your gaze is making me a bit uncomfortable. My sisters might be different, but I'm not really used to having people look at me...

drop_descrip.line: Hmm-hum-hum... So very cute~♪ ...Commander? Um, about that... Please do me a favor and forget you heard anything.

feeling5.line: Hm-hmm~♪ It's in pretty good condition today, just as you said. Um... would you mind if I played you one more song?

headtouch.line: ...Hehehe.

home.line: I want to perform for people, not a crowd of trees in the barren wilderness. I'll keep fighting in order to keep it that way... together with my sisters.

login.line: (If the Commander wasn't waiting for me, I'd have liked to stay like this for a bit longer...)

mail.line: So there's new mail. Maryland's as fast to act as always.

main1.line: The Big Five... Yet another name that we were proud to be called.

main2.line: I'm not sure what I'll do if there ever comes a time when I can take off my rigging, along the title of the Big Seven... I'm sure that that girl from the Sakura Empire is thinking the same thing.

main3.line: Where would I like to go? Well... if it's not too much to ask... that place where you can pet cats.

mission.line: Commander, there are still some missions left... Make sure you check on them later.

touch.line: It's already been tuned, Commander. Leave it be. It's as delicate as my main guns are.

touch2.line: Don't I feel... cold to the touch?

unlock.line: Hmm-hum-hum... So very cute~♪ ...Commander? Um, about that... Please do me a favor and forget you heard anything.

win_mvp.line: The fact that I can still be helpful to people makes me happy.

battle.line: Dear opponents, do NOT disappoint me!

detail.line: Celebration? Honor? Nothing else except for battles will draw my attention.

drop_descrip.line: Colorado class battleship— Maryland, hull number BB-46

expedition.line: Even though commissions are an important part of the war, but I'm just not interested in them.

feeling1.line: A saying that I recently heard from my sister, “Never protest your loyalty to the weak”.

feeling2.line: I don't know who granted us the title of BIG SEVEN. But if those two keep mentioning it non-stop, then the title should have some special meaning to it.

feeling3.line: The war cannot be won by a single person. Without true sisters fighting alongside you and a reliable backline supporting you, no matter how strong you are, your defeat is inevitable!

feeling4.line: Not all problems can be solved by fighting? Well, I don't really believe that... but you always seem to find a way to solve things. After all, you are my favorite Commander.

feeling5.line: Look into my eyes, as my most trusted companions, is it even necessary to use words to express the feelings I have for you in my heart?

home.line: Sigh, staying in port is so boring...

hp_warning.line: Now, this is a fun battle!

login.line: I think I smell gunpowder, has the battle started already? Pfft... turns out it was only Vestal cooking.

lose.line: If only Oklahoma was here...

mail.line: When writing a reply back, should I carry an anti-aircraft gun with me...

main1.line: Fighting beside my sisters is the happiest thing in the world!

main2.line: I hate foul play, only fair duels are real battles!

main3.line: Working? ...I don’t know much about that, I’ll just do whatever you tell me to do.

mission.line: If I don’t complete the mission, then I can’t get a battle star.

mission_complete.line: Mission rewards... Darn, what a waste of time.

profile.line: Eagle Union Colorado class battleship, ship no. 2 “Maryland”. As one of the BIG SEVEN, I often attended various celebrations. I escaped the attack on Pearl Harbor from behind Oklahoma. After undergoing retrofit, I successfully completed counter strike attacks on the Sakura Empire Navy. I participated in Operation Magic Carpet and received a total of seven battle stars. Commander, I just saw gunfire over there...oh, nevermind it was the sunset.

propose.line: You really treasure these strange rings, do you? ...But since it's your decision, I'll go with it! From now on, I will protect you!

skill.line: No matter how many times it takes, I will sink you again!

touch.line: Commander, are we going into battle?

touch2.line: Commander, our fighting power is not in that area of expertise.

unlock.line: I am Maryland, a member of the BIG SEVEN. “Fighting Mary”, yes, that's what they call me! I heard there are many battles ahead. I look forward to them all!

upgrade.line: I really wanna try to shoot a volley from my main gun right now…

win_mvp.line: Haha! This is just the appetizer before the main course!

battle.line: The humiliation I once suffered... I'll repay you double!

detail.line: Do not doubt my combat performance, Commander.

drop_descrip.line: Colorado class battleship— West Virginia, hull number BB-48.

expedition.line: The commission fleet is really efficient. I hope the Commander can learn a thing or two about efficiency.

feeling1.line: Commander's laziness is almost beyond my bottom line.

feeling2.line: I was once seriously injured, but then I was greatly enhanced during the process for my repairs…

feeling3.line: I’m proud of my BIG SEVEN title. But aircraft carriers seem to be replacing us battleships in naval battles. I am losing myself in all this confusion: this strength that I possess... what is it for?

feeling4.line: After joining your fleet, the answer to my question has been gradually answered... This power of mine is destined to protect everyone including you, Commander. My strength still has its value, even if I'm no longer the heroine of the battlefield.

feeling5.line: Commander, you have become someone who can completely take charge on the battlefield. At last, my powers have found a worthy partner... What? A love confession? Don't you trick me to say that, you fool——

home.line: What a peaceful port, it reminds me of Hawaii before the war.

hp_warning.line: Getting hit by a torpedo... it feels bad.

login.line: You’re late... the exercise has already begun, hurry!

lose.line: I don't want to recall the humiliation I suffered on that day...!

mail.line: Could these be letters from my sisters?

main1.line: The combat exercise didn’t go well… Is the Commander being lazy again?

main2.line: I will never forget the humiliation I suffered on that day.

main3.line: On the night of the Surigao Strait, I witnessed the last moments of the Sakura Empire fleet... They truly are a worthy opponent...

mission.line: Carrying out missions is an important part of enhancing the strength of the fleet.

mission_complete.line: The mission was nicely executed, good one.

profile.line: During a "Naval Holiday", my sisters and I were honored amongst the world's strongest battleships. We were granted the high-profile title of - BIG SEVEN. Although times are changing, the three of us still have the strength to fight any enemy fleet in a decisive battle, please don't forget that.

propose.line: You’ve decided to perform a pledge ritual with me? Commander really made a bold decision... In that case, I will not let your expectation down. I'll guard you until the very end.

skill.line: Have a taste of my 406mm guns!

touch.line: This should be... a friendly gesture I suppose.

touch2.line: Commander, it seems you’re rather close to getting lectured by me.

unlock.line: It’s finally my time to show my strength... Under the guidance of fate, the third ship of Colorado class, West Virginia, reporting in.

upgrade.line: It seems the Spokane Cup this year will still be mine.

win_mvp.line: Have you seen this? This is the inevitably tragic ending of those who dare challenge the BIG SEVEN.

battle.line: Sink or swim. Let's go.

drop_descrip.line: Colorado, Maryland, you two ready to rock? Keep your cool! Commander, and everyone in the audience, get ready for the Big Seven's big performance!

expedition.line: The commission team's back. Hope they'll make it in time for our last song.

home.line: We've already started, but you've shown up at the perfect time. You're gonna like this next song, Commander.

login.line: Whew... You feeling the heat, Commander? Er, not the weather, I was talking about the performance... Alright, awesome.

lose.line: Guh... We almost had it...

main1.line: Mic test, mic test. Can you hear me clearly, Commander? What about you, Colorado and Maryland?

main2.line: While I usually play slightly more chill, calm tunes when I'm alone, this case obviously calls for something explosive.

main3.line: I always thought the ladies of the Royal Navy hated this genre... But as Rodney and more have shown, presumptions do you no good.

touch.line: A song request? Colorado, Maryland, we're playing the Commander's fave next.

touch2.line: I wasn't trying to tempt you into this...

unlock.line: Colorado, Maryland, you two ready to rock? Keep your cool! Commander, and everyone in the audience, get ready for the Big Seven's big performance!

win_mvp.line: Do not mess around with a Big Seven. Ever.

battle.line: It's time to face off!

drop_descrip.line: West Virginia, completing retrofit. Back when I joined the fleet, I said I'd show you my strength – now, after you've made me this much stronger, I feel humbled. Once more, Commander, my strength is yours.

expedition.line: It's unhealthy to overwork yourself, Commander. Let the rest of us greet the commission team.

headtouch.line: Look, I'm not Colorado...

home.line: You like it when the port is bustling? Fair enough. I don't mind either way as long as there's no fighting.

login.line: Still a while to go until the wargame starts... Hey, Commander. I've been waiting for you.

mail.line: It's about damn time Maryland learned how to file paperwork... Oh, Commander, there's a letter for you.

main1.line: Although I don't try to appear frail, it does work at tricking the enemy into thinking so. Just like that Sakura Empire Big Seven... Or am I wrong?

main2.line: "Wee Vee?" Ahahah. You're free to call be my whatever nickname you want.

main3.line: So, Commander, about that private training we talked about a while ago... You were thinking the same thing? Okay... Should we go, then?

touch.line: I accept your affection.

touch2.line: I hope you're ready to face the consequences. Now then... *blushes*

unlock.line: West Virginia, completing retrofit. Back when I joined the fleet, I said I'd show you my strength – now, after you've made me this much stronger, I feel humbled. Once more, Commander, my strength is yours.

battle.line: Don’t be overconfident, and try not to be so nervous while focusing on winning~

detail.line: Being stared like that makes me a bit shy...

drop_descrip.line: North Carolina class battleship— North Carolina, hull number BB-55.

expedition.line: The commission is over, they should be back soon~

feeling1.line: Commander, I'm gonna get angry.

feeling2.line: Commander remembers me~ Not that I’m boasting or anything, but I still have confidence in my low sense of existence. (smiles wryly)

feeling3.line: If you’re only going by appearances, every child in this fleet looks cute. But in terms of personality, they all have their unique quirks. To be honest, I am a bit envious of them. (strokes chin).

feeling4.line: I always believe there is nothing wrong with being ordinary. But after meeting you Commander, I want to change myself a little... after all, my sisters are all so charismatic~ Well.. Commander, are you fond of bunny girls?~

feeling5.line: Do you want to eat something later Commander? And then you can accompany me to go shopping, if you want to get something then let’s go together. Then... hehe... let’s take a walk in the park? Commander, everywhere I go as long as I’m with you will be just fine~

home.line: Ah, hold on, your collar is all messed up. Stand still while I fix it... there you go~ (waves).

hp_warning.line: Sisters, hold on!

login.line: Welcome back~

lose.line: Not so successful... let's try again next time.

mail.line: You’ve got new mail~

main1.line: What do I wear inside? It's not something that’s so significant

main2.line: If I think about it, I certainly have been to many places... seen many landscapes, and also parted ways with many people.

main3.line: Sometimes I get so envious of my younger sister Washington and how she’s so energetic all the time.

mission.line: It’s not good to leave tasks unfinished.

mission_complete.line: The mission rewards were sent out, are you not going to pick it up?

profile.line: I am North Carolina class ship no.1. I can be considered the big sister battleship of the Eagle Union~ I don’t particularly like or dislike anything, so to speak. Even though I have fought in all kinds of engagements, I have not gained any fame... I am a little bit troubled by this.

propose.line: Well, your trust deserves to be rewarded... umm... Commander, do you like bunny girls?~

touch.line: Do you need help with something?

touch2.line: Not good...

unlock.line: North Carolina here, awaiting your dispatch. Although I may seem to have a bland personality compared to my sisters. But as the saying goes, no personality is still a personality, hehe. Anyways, awaiting your orders, sir.

upgrade.line: I'll try to work a bit harder~

win_mvp.line: If the Commander gives me a few praises, then I will be very happy~

detail.line: "Do I wear this all the time"? Maybe, maybe not. I'll leave the answer up to your imagination.

drop_descrip.line: Commander? Oh, umm, this is just, err, equipment changing practice... Also, I recall you saying you like bunny girls. You still do, right?

expedition.line: Maybe I should keep this outfit on and give the commission team a real surprise when they return... Hehehe~ I'm just joking.

feeling5.line: Commander, are you free today? We could go on a date somewhere. Not in this outfit, of course, just my regular one. Thank you for understanding. Hehehe~

headtouch.line: It's true – you need the ears, or you can't call yourself a bunny girl. Hehehe~

home.line: Could you help out with my ribbon? It's a bit too close for my liking... Ah, thank you.

login.line: Welcome back, dear! Is there anything you need a hand with?

main1.line: Whew. This feels so liberating! ...And not in any indecent sense, or anything.

main2.line: Did Washington manage a proper smile today? She's got features as sharp as a knife, so it's easy to misinterpret her expression.

main3.line: I am genuinely interested in bunny girl things, but it's quite awkward to actually tell people about them...

touch2.line: I'll take that to mean you really like this outfit, am I right? Hehehe~

unlock.line: Commander? Oh, umm, this is just, err, equipment changing practice... Also, I recall you saying you like bunny girls. You still do, right?

win_mvp.line: Victory isn't the result of individuality. It's the result of good teamwork. Hehehe~

battle.line: Ok, let’s work out. (Snickers)

detail.line: Hmm, you want to know how well I fight?

drop_descrip.line: North Carolina class battleship— Washington, hull number BB-56.

expedition.line: Your memory can’t be worse than mine, right? The commission fleet has returned, won’t you go greet them?

feeling1.line: You are too weak, it’s no fun playing with you, go practice some more.

feeling2.line: What must I do to possess a good smile... think about the things I like? If so, I feel very happy even at the thought of winning against South Dakota... muahahaha...

feeling3.line: No, no, that’s not right. If we do it this way, won’t it end much the same like in the past? … Don’t try so hard? You sometimes say stuff like that… Hmm? That was a good smile from me just now?

feeling4.line: Lately, my smile has become more natural? Emm, huh (scratches head), I was recently trying to find a new hobby. While I was searching, I realized that being with you is not so bad… (whispers)

feeling5.line: I couldn’t help but smile when I saw you, this is the first time that I’m feeling this way... although, I also have other feelings rushing towards me. I suddenly want to see your expression when you are bullied by me—— Commander, stay with me for a while. (Laughs)

home.line: I’m glad that you didn’t get hurt—— What?! I don’t have feelings for you!

hp_warning.line: I won't let go of victories to my enemies!

login.line: Welcome back... how does my smile look? (Forcibly smiles)

lose.line: Oh, I will not forget you!

mail.line: Hey, your mail.

main1.line: My smile looks beautiful? You jerk... oops, keep smiling, keep smiling. Thank you for your compliments.

main2.line: Hey, that rigid South Dakota is still the same. Commander, you see, I am cuter than her.

main3.line: A true measurement of friendship is their actions and not their words, I don’t like people who are rhetorical in nature.

mission.line: A new mission? Haha, now my blood is boiling.

mission_complete.line: Go grab the reward yourself, I’m not interested.

profile.line: North Carolina class ship no. 2. I am Washington! The thing I like to do the most is to destroy my enemies. Recently, I am practicing on my smile. —— Battle record? I don’t really show off with such things, all in all, how’s my smile?

propose.line: Wait wait! We’re doing “that”, right? Is this your new way of teasing me!... Damn, you bastard, I’m not sure if I should cry or laugh about this...

skill.line: Out of my way. I'm ready to fight!

touch.line: Don’t touch me as if you’re trying to be intimate with me.

touch2.line: ...You wish to die? (Smiles)

unlock.line: Hello, Commander, I am Washington... my sister told me that I cannot be so rough once I join the fleet, so I am practicing my smile. Darn, why must I listen to her...

upgrade.line: It feels so good to become stronger.

win_mvp.line: Sure enough, I am happiest when all the foes are annihilated~

battle.line: We've got this in the bag, easily.

detail.line: Huh. Guess I can't help but crack a smile after having some good grub and a bit of liquor... Meaning, I don't gotta practice smiling anymore!

drop_descrip.line: Sup, Commander? ...Looking good? I don't think this outfit's anything special... You better not be trying to cozy up to me, or I'll knock your teeth out!

expedition.line: Crap, the commission team must be... Oh, you remembered? Full marks, Commander.

feeling5.line: Heheh, so then South Dakota and I just... Hang on, I feel like I'm talking to myself here! C'mon, tell me a funny story or something! I've smiled like you asked me to, so keep up your end of the deal...

home.line: Back safe and sound. Thank goodness... Uh, no? I-I wasn't... talking about you...

login.line: Wipe that stupid grin off your face. I know exactly what you're thinking! I am NOT gonna dress up like my sister today!

main1.line: W-welcome back, dear♪ ...Doesn't hit the same. How does North Carolina do it?

main2.line: South Dakota's on the piano, huh. I ain't got her level of finesse, so don't go comparing me to her... Wish I could play like that.

main3.line: Remember our deal, Commander – I'm coming along when you go around greeting people, got it?

mission.line: We've got a new mission. It'll do nicely as an after-dinner workout.

mission_complete.line: You claimed the rewards yet? ...Oh please, like I give a damn about that!

touch.line: Breaktime already? All right, take a load off.

touch2.line: What the–?! Are you drunk out of your mind?!

unlock.line: Sup, Commander? ...Looking good? I don't think this outfit's anything special... You better not be trying to cozy up to me, or I'll knock your teeth out!

win_mvp.line: Now this is something worth celebrating! Am I right?

battle.line: Come at me with all you got!

detail.line: South Dakota, standing by 24/7, Commander.

drop_descrip.line: South Dakota-class battleship –  South Dakota, Hull Number BB-57!

expedition.line: The commission teams are back... If it is necessary, send me off as well.

feeling1.line: ... I shall follow your orders.

feeling2.line: Your will is my command, Commander.

feeling3.line: I exist to help you achieve your goals, Commander. Other than that, I have no real value... A skirt? I've never worn something so fluffy before.

feeling4.line: Another way to live other than fighting? I... do not know what to do, Commander. I have always lived like this... Can you teach me?

feeling5.line: So this is your perspective, Commander... I choose how I live, was what you said... This time, I fight not for my duty, but for the sake of your smile, Commander.

home.line: Good fight out there, Commander.

hp_warning.line: I won't hold back now...!

login.line: Commander, your orders please.

lose.line: I am sorry, Commander... It's a shame...!

mail.line: There's new mail, Commander.

main1.line: In the darkness, my will was tempered. I fear nothing.

main2.line: As long as I am of use to Commander, I am fine with handing my credit over to others.

main3.line: Those who stand as Commander's enemies, are enemies all the same.

mission.line: Commander, please do not forget about completing the missions.

mission_complete.line: Commander, the mission rewards have arrived.

profile.line: Battleship of Eagle Union, South Dakota. When it comes to battlefields, I wish for you to not leave my side. I will protect you, Commander. 'The Strongest Shield'? Vain titles are worthless. There's meaning only in being useful.

propose.line: I feel warm when you're by my side, Commander. Your goals bring me the drive to fight. I become happy when I hear your words... I once offered you my shields. From now on... I give you my heart.

touch.line: I'm ready to move out anytime.

touch2.line: If this is what you want to do...

unlock.line: I am South Dakota, Commander. I shall become your shield and protect you from all cannon fire.

upgrade.line: My shields have become stronger

win_mvp.line: Partial victories aren't worth celebrating, Commander.

detail.line: Aurora asked me to perform with her... I guess it can't hurt to try.

drop_descrip.line: Massachusetts suggested I learn something useful that's unrelated to combat, so I started playing the piano... It seemed impossible at first, but after actually trying it, I've developed a pretty good feel for it.

feeling5.line: Without you, I doubt I would've ever come to understand what splendor this world holds, or started playing the piano either... Commander, I'd like to play you a song that's important to me.

home.line: Everyone's back safe and sound. Now I can resume practicing with peace of mind.

login.line: What song should I play for you today...

main1.line: I can't get used to this flimsy dress. I'd rather wear my regular clothes...

main2.line: My cat goes for the keyboard when I'm not playing... Do you want to practice the piano too, kitty?

main3.line: We can express so much through music. I suppose that's fitting for someone bad at expressing their feelings like I am.

mission.line: Music and instruments are simply hobbies. We ought to prioritize our missions, Commander.

unlock.line: Massachusetts suggested I learn something useful that's unrelated to combat, so I started playing the piano... It seemed impossible at first, but after actually trying it, I've developed a pretty good feel for it.

battle.line: Everyone, Level 1 combat readiness! Set sail!

detail.line: Thanks for finishing the equipment inspection. All systems nominal! ...Oh my, you seem to be unable to take your eyes off me~ Not that it bothers me though? Besides, don'tcha like this sort of stuff?

drop_descrip.line: Iowa-class battleship – New Jersey, Hull Number BB-62.

feeling1.line: Ah, so you're the kind of person who makes girls cry. Yeah, you'd better feel bad about it.

feeling2.line: We'll only get in each other's way if we keep an ambivalent relationship. Say, don'tcha think getting touchy-feely might help break the ice? ...Just kidding~ See, you're already not as nervous~ Hehehe~♪

feeling3.line: Look at that, you're already starting to chat me up. So, what's on your mind today? Something a bit more technical? Small talk about daily life? ...Oh, you want me to choose?

feeling4.line: My my, look who's all run down today... I knew it, you've been overworking yourself. C'mere, lie down here and let me take care of you. Yeah, my thighs make for a pretty good pillow substitute huh? Don'tcha just love this kind of stuff~?

feeling5.line: Commander, would you prefer I take the lead, or would you rather do it? Hold up~ I'll see for myself when the time is right, so there's no need for you to answer in words. After all, don'tcha just love being toyed with~?

headtouch.line: Done having your fun yet? Hehe, now it's my turn~♪ Take a seat!

hp_warning.line: I know just the thing to turn this situation around!

login.line: Glad you made it. Do you already have a plan for what you wanna do? And how do I factor into those plans?

lose.line: Unbelievable... I'm actually getting cornered?! ...I'm not gonna be able to sleep 'til I figure out how to set things straight!

mail.line: You've got new mail. Heh, dont'cha just love the anticipation~?

main1.line: Iowa versus Yamato, huh? A real classic. Don'tcha just love that kind of stuff?

main2.line: I go for the fruity stuff~ green apple, orange, and soda water. As for coffee... Not my favorite, I guess?

main3.line: How much stuff should I be doing as your secretary? ...Lemme think, how does 40% sound? If I did everything, wouldn't that make me the commander? Heh.

main5.line: It's now the age of carriers? ...Dunno about that. If carriers are able to evolve, what's to say that battleships can't also evolve?

main6.line: They call me Big J or the Black Dragon of the Eagle Union! ...What, got a problem with talking myself up a bit?

mission.line: Did you already accept this mission? Sounds good, let's take care of it together.

mission_complete.line: Since we already got the hard stuff out of the way, why not take a little break? It's gonna be pretty easy to prioritize whatever is left~

profile.line: I am battleship New Jersey, the indomitable Black Dragon of the Eagle Union. When I say "indomitable," I'm not just tooting my own horn, hehe~♪ If you knew more about me, you'd know exactly what I'm talking about.

propose.line: Commander, I can already hear everything you're thinking. As long as you're fine with it, I don't have any objections~ After all, I still owe you a proper confession, don't I? Hehe, don'tcha think that's what mutual love is supposed to look like?

skill.line: Fire control, I'm counting on you!

touch.line: I'll take any work-related requests, but anything outside of that... won't come cheap. Just kidding~♪

touch2.line: Commander, don'tcha just love being put on the defensive? In more ways than one~♪

unlock.line: The indomitable Black Dragon of the Eagle Union is none other than me, New Jersey! You're about to witness true power! Haha, just messing~♪ Don'tcha just love flashy introductions?

upgrade.line: Some say that the age of battleships is over. They haven't met the Iowa class.

win_mvp.line: Course: steady! Objective: completed! Enemies who can stop us: none! Heheh, don'tcha love it when things go smoothly?

detail.line: Can't take your eyes off me, huh? Nothing wrong with that though~ Just who do you think I am? Ahaha~♪

drop_descrip.line: One, two, jump! Woah, think I nailed it this time~♪ So, how many points would you give me for that? Naturally, a perfect 100, right? Don'tcha just love it when things go smoothly?

home.line: Shouldn't you be staring at those reports instead of at me? Alright, fine by me. Take a good look at this jump and spin. Oh, you liked that a whole lot, huh?

main1.line: Hey, you over there, you're blocking the view! Jeez, I was hoping to treat you to the best seats in the house, Commander.

main2.line: nil

main3.line: Keep the spotlight on me! That's right, keep your eyes on the red-hot dance of the Black Dragon, New Jersey!

main4.line: Being a superstar sure is exciting, isn't it? After all... I didn't come all the way from Planet Bunny for nothing! ...Err, that didn't come across right...

main5.line: Of course, this dance is something I'd only show you and my closest friends, hehe~

touch.line: Your honest feedback, please! Tell me what you really think, okay?

touch2.line: I never said you couldn't touch, but... try to mind the time and place, yeah?

unlock.line: One, two, jump! Woah, think I nailed it this time~♪ So, how many points would you give me for that? Naturally, a perfect 100, right? Don'tcha just love it when things go smoothly?

battle.line: I won't let my honey shed a single tear!

drop_descrip.line: Sooo hot... Are you alright, honey? You're not heat-exhausted, are you? I'll share my drink with you if you're thirsty, but in return, I'll need you to put my sunscreen on for me. Heheh, that's just what you like to do, right, honey~?

expedition.line: Commission team's here! ...You're still putting on your sunscreen? Come ooon.

feeling5.line: Once we're done, I'll spread stuff on you! That chilly, slick, sticky stuff, nice and slow... Hahah! I thought you might like me doing this. Do you?

home.line: Good work out there! Oh, honey, you look a little burned. Hahaha, I'm kidding! Here, I'll get you a drink. Take it easy♪

login.line: It's a scorcher out there... Midsummer sunlight is rough no matter where you go. Honey, did you put on sunscreen? We'd better get some on you~ Hahaha♪

main1.line: Aloe works as sunscreen, too? Then get to putting it on me! ...Whoa, it's all slippery and sticky... Hyah?!

main2.line: Mm... I want ice cream now... Okay! Want one, honey? Don't worry– all of us Eagle Union ships brought ice cream.

main3.line: Wanna go see Ticonderoga with me later? Tanning is fun and all, but I'd love to lie down in a cool place. You decide, honey.

touch.line: I'm counting on you, honey!

touch2.line: Hyah?! Geez, honey. I know you like this stuff, but c'mon... *blushes*

unlock.line: Sooo hot... Are you alright, honey? You're not heat-exhausted, are you? I'll share my drink with you if you're thirsty, but in return, I'll need you to put my sunscreen on for me. Heheh, that's just what you like to do, right, honey~?

battle.line: Coming right at ya, double time!

detail.line: Mm~♪ Hmm, what am I staring at so intently? You, of course~ Honey, even though you're always gazing so passionately at me, am I not allowed to return the favor? Ehehe~♡

drop_descrip.line: The indomitable Black Dragon... I mean, the adorable New Jersey makes her bridal appearance! Hehe~ Stunned, arent'cha? Of course you are, honey~♪ How wouldn't you be?

expedition.line: The commission fleet's back. Will you be coming with me, honey?

feeling5.line: Regardless of which one of us makes the first move, you'll always be the honey I know and love♪ That~ is~ why~ today, I'll show you a different side of me that'll have you falling head-over-heels for me again! Ahaha!

login.line: Welcome back, honey~♪ Let's put our best foot forward today as well!

lose.line: My honey won't lose faith in me over something like this...!

main2.line: Think we should have Ty bring some ice cream over? I think I'm in the mood for strawberry. You okay with that, honey?

main3.line: You've been working real hard? Who's smart, handsome, and totally awesome~ Yes, you are~ Now, onto the next job, right?

main4.line: nil

mission.line: Work, work... honey, what's our next mission?

mission_complete.line: Mission complete~♪ I'll handle the rewards, so you can to take a break! ...It's not time for that yet? Ahaha...

skill.line: Honey, keep your eyes on me♪

touch.line: What's the matter, honey? Oh, did you perhaps want me to give you a good head-patting?

touch2.line: I already know. You totally love this kind of stuff, dont'cha? ––Ahaha~♪

unlock.line: The indomitable Black Dragon... I mean, the adorable New Jersey makes her bridal appearance! Hehe~ Stunned, arent'cha? Of course you are, honey~♪ How wouldn't you be?

win_mvp.line: A bouquet-toss for victory~♪ Ahaha, I've been wanting to try that for a while now~

battle.line: Pretty tough, aren't you? You won't cry if I hit you, will you?

detail.line: Tell me when you're done inspecting.

drop_descrip.line: South Dakota-class battleship – Massachusetts, Hull Number BB-59.

feeling1.line: Your body is weak, Commander. Are you eating properly?

feeling2.line: How to get stronger? Uhh, do some push-ups? ... Not working for you?

feeling3.line: Seeing you challenging yourself with things you can't do is... interesting. It makes me want to explore my own limits, too.

feeling4.line: I like how cool you look when you're pushing yourself hard... but overdoing it isn't good. I'll force you to rest if I have to.

feeling5.line: I don't have any dreams. But I have the power to grant them. Commander, do you have a dream for me to grant one day?

hp_warning.line: ... So you want me to get serious?

login.line: For lunch, I'll make... Oh, Commander, are you going for a stroll?

lose.line: Sorry, I got distracted...

mail.line: I'll leave your letter here. Check it later.

main1.line: ... You know, I actually like this hair color. It's like that of a bald eagle, isn't it?

main2.line: You think my jacket is strange? This way I can feel the breeze hit my skin when out at sea, though... I love it.

main3.line: People that impressed me? Umm... when I was in Casablanca, I fought a battleship who held out a long time even with just a single turret... I'd like to fight her again in her finished state.

mission.line: So many missions waiting on us...

mission_complete.line: Ah, the rewards have arrived... Seems we can afford beef for dinner tonight.

propose.line: Umm, yeah... I already know what you want to do and want to say... Because I love you too, Commander.

touch.line: You want someone to pamper you? ... You want ME to?

touch2.line: ... If you'd move your body more, you'd have fewer weird thoughts.

upgrade.line: I feel a bit different...

login.line: My... plans for the party? We could go listen to Dakota play the piano.

main1.line: Where's Jean Bart gone? I wanted to show her how I look.

main2.line: Seems everyone's enjoying the party. Hope Dakota and Alabama are too. Me? I'm having tons of fun.

main3.line: You want something, Commander? I'm gonna go get a drink. I could get one for you too if you want.

mission_complete.line: Oh, rewards have come in. Good stuff.

touch.line: I shouldn't lift this flap? Why not?

touch2.line: Are you getting more weird thoughts because of my outfit?

unlock.line: Hey... Is this outfit that strange to you? Thought it looks just like what my sister's wearing... so what are you staring at? I don't get you at all...

drop_descrip.line: South Dakota-class battleship – Alabama, Hull Number BB-60.

feeling1.line: ......Who the hell are you?

lose.line: Time to retreat? Fine...

main2.line: I'd like to have a Turkey Shoot. Makes me wish I could fly...

main3.line: Sure is nice outside. Commander, wanna go lie in the grass under the sun? I could stay like that all day...

mission_complete.line: Commander, I'll go fetch the mission rewards. I'm big and strong, after all!

profile.line: I'm Alabama, fourth ship of the South Dakota-class, also known as Lucky A... What else? Uhh... I received some honors while fighting in Norway, the Marshall Islands, and the Marianas. Then, there was Leyte and the trip to the Sakura Empire... Since then, I've just been taking it easy in the Mobile Bay.

skill.line: Don't die on me just yet!

touch.line: You're interested in my abs? Go ahead and feel 'em.

touch2.line: Huh......? Commander, the hell are you doing?

main1.line: Havin' snowball fights, lightin' firecrackers, eatin' baozi... It's all a ton of fun. Especially with friends.

main3.line: Two beef baozi, one veggie baozi, and some shaomai... Comin' right up. Manjuus, bring this note to the kitchen.

battle.line: Ehehe, let's party~ I'm gonna scare you to the point you're spilling fuel!

home.line: Com~man~der~ No one has returned yet~

login.line: Roooaar! ... Hehehe, were you shocked? I'm like a ghost that's going to haunt you every day!

lose.line: No... No way... Could they possibly have seen me?!

main1.line: Russian roulette~ candy time~ Pick the one~ with wasabi inside~

main3.line: Commander~ Do my sleeves~ look like those of a ghost~?

win_mvp.line: Hehehe~ Look at them! They don't even know what hit them!

feeling2.line: You found out my secret, Commander... Oh well! Please don't tell anyone else, ok?

feeling3.line: Are you free, Commander? Wanna play a game then? We can make plastic models too if you want.

feeling4.line: Commander, my room is not a game store~ Oh, you just want to play with me? F...Fine! I just bought a newly launched title. Wanna play it together?

feeling5.line: We need more co-op games, as well as tools... Eeeh, I don't wanna go outside~ Commander, for the sake of the future of the adorable Long Island~ Please buy this list up!

home.line: Good work out there, Commander. Time to relax~ Here you go, you're now Player 2

lose.line: Ah, Long Island has become... Tired Island...

main1.line: Commander, don’t bother me, I’m really busy right now. Busy with what? Games! All of these stuipid friggin backlogged games!

main2.line: Commander, I brought a bunch of snacks~ Should I give you some?

main3.line: Commander, do you like High Grade or Magical Grade stuff? I even got Powerful Grade stuff too!

unlock.line: Everyone's favorite and talked-about Long Island, actually has another hidden secret...

lose.line: Oh no, my viewership is going down!

main2.line: Someone's at the door? Commandeeeer! Grab some of the snacks by the bed and give them to whoever's knocking~

touch2.line: Y-you're gonna get me demonetized!

main2.line: Ehehe~ Commander, are you looking for your gaming handheld?

unlock.line: Commander~ I am Long Island~ I've changed? Ghosts don't cha... Huh? I seemed to have become a little more alive!

battle.line: Go, curveball!

detail.line: Please keep my stats in mind!

drop_descrip.line: Bogue-class escort carrier — Bogue, Hull Number CVE-9!

expedition.line: Curveball~! Oh crap I broke the window... Ah, Commander, the commission squad is back!

feeling1.line: Can you really make me stronger, Commander? ...I'm really worried...

feeling2.line: Someday, I hope to stand on the podium of the sea with your lead!

feeling3.line: You always give me the right ideas, Commander! As expected of a great coach! I, Bogue the pitcher, will follow you for life!

feeling5.line: Co-Commander. If I win in the next league, I- I'll tell you something important! S- So please wait for it! I will become stronger. Stronger than anyone!

login.line: The best pitchers are always training. Yep!

lose.line: Is this the end of the tournament...?

mail.line: Commander, it's a mail! Which championship is it from?

main1.line: With this ball, I can sink a submarine!

main2.line: Commander, can you polish the B-25s?

main3.line: Boring... You look tired anyway, Commander, so let's go and sink some subs?

mission.line: A new goal? I will not back down!

mission_complete.line: It's satisfying to be rewarded for achieving the objective! Commander, check out the rewards!

propose.line: ...Now I understand! You noticed my feelings, Commander, and you want me to continue my journey without regrets! I, Bogue, am truly happy to have met you!

touch.line: What's this? Training to resist against attacks?

touch2.line: Waah!! Commander, that's mean!

unlock.line: *inhale*...HAA! Nice one... Oh, apologies. You're the Commander, I see. Fast pitcher, Bogue, here for duty!

upgrade.line: My balls have become even faster!

win_mvp.line: Hmhmm~ As I thought, I am the best pitcher.

drop_descrip.line: Commander, there's no need to be so afraid. There are only two things my balls hit-- Enemies, and victory! Ah, sometimes they do hit the windows too, ahaha...

main1.line: My goal is the Major Le... I mean, submarine fighting, a three strike finish!

main2.line: Rest assured, Commander! While I'm doing escort duty, no ships sink under my watch!

main3.line: I am here today because of Yorkie and Lady Lex. I have to give them my thanks!

touch.line: Yes! Thanks for getting my ball!

touch2.line: Haha, I'm used to this type of interference now!

unlock.line: Commander, there's no need to be so afraid. There are only two things my balls hit-- Enemies, and victory! Ah, sometimes they do hit the windows too, ahaha...

battle.line: A head-on battle, huh... All right, leave the air support to me!

feeling1.line: So... you were the greatest obstacle to the development of the fleet...

main1.line: Commander, shall I help assess the state of the fleet's logistics?

main2.line: Commander, where would you rather be, the thrilling, constantly-shifting front lines, or the humble, but critically important rear lines?

main3.line: If possible, I'd like to hear about what happened at the Battle of Casablanca from Massachusetts.

mission.line: You will surely be rewarded for your hard work. Please do your best, Commander!

mission_complete.line: Mission complete! All right, with these supplies, your fleet operations should be even smoother.

profile.line: Back then, roughly fifty other Casablanca-class sisters entered service over the course of just over a year. Although most of us saw our missions come to an end shortly after the war, I will do my best to fulfill my duties to this fleet, whether as an escort, air support, or a transport. It's a pleasure to work with you, Commander.

propose.line: Although love stories, with all their twists and turns, have a unique appeal, I personally would rather live a life of simple happiness. Do you think the same way, Commander? Then let us join in an embrace after you put the ring on my finger.

skill.line: I will do everything in my power to protect everyone!

touch.line: Commander, what's the matter... Oh, is my necktie crooked?

touch2.line: Eek?! I... I've never read about stuff like this in my books before...!

unlock.line: Good morning to you. Escort carrier Casablanca, reporting in. I shall support the fleet to the best of my abilities, so you may rest assured.

upgrade.line: Thank you very much, Commander!

win_mvp.line: First place... me? Hmph. Fighting on the front lines might be easier than I expected.

detail.line: Getting the choreography down isn't the hard part. It's being able to cheer so enthusiastically like Reno... It's a bit too embarrassing if you ask me...

drop_descrip.line: Phew... Can't train hard if you don't stay hydrated! Oh, Commander, good day! Did you come to watch us practice?

home.line: The actual meet is coming up... I've got to practice even harder!

login.line: Cheerleaders raise the morale of the players. It doesn't seem much different from the role of an escort carrier, supporting those who are working hard on the battlefield.

main1.line: Captain Reno, I think your enthusiasm is nothing but commendable, but wouldn't it be better to take a break now to conserve our energy?

main2.line: Commander, I brought some water and sports drinks. Feel free to take whatever you want.

main3.line: Even though this squad was thrown together last minute, thanks to the support of you and Craven, I don't want to lose to the other factions!

touch.line: Is this towel for me? Ah, thank you very much, Commander.

touch2.line: Commander, you seem to be quite good at taking advantage of these situations...

unlock.line: Phew... Can't train hard if you don't stay hydrated! Oh, Commander, good day! Did you come to watch us practice?

battle.line: This is the chance to show me what you learned. Do it properly!

detail.line: Commander, you're staring at me... Are you ready to answer my questions?

drop_descrip.line: Langley-class aicraft carrier ー Langley, Hull Number CV-1!

expedition.line: The girls on the commission field trip have returned. Now, go and check their progress.

feeling1.line: I never thought that there would be a student I cannot teach... It seems better for me to quit...

feeling2.line: What are you doing, sleeping in the job?! Take you tutoring seriously!

feeling3.line: You seem to be getting better at this- Eh? It's thanks to me? Ah, well... y-you're welcome...

feeling4.line: There's nothing more for me to teach you-- What? Teach you about myself? Y-You idiot!... Ugh

feeling5.line: I, Ms. Langley, do not mix personal and work lives! If you think that I'll give you special treatment just because of our relationship, you are sorely mistaken! ... B-but in private, I'm fine with that!

home.line: Commander, where are you heading? It's time for a reflection meeting

login.line: Commander, I'll assist you with your work the best I can!

lose.line: *sobs* ... I'm not qualified as a teacher... Maybe I should go back to transporting coal...

mail.line: Check your mail periodically. It's a good habit!

main1.line: Commander! ~Hey, you could've done better than this. Why are you not serious about this...?

main2.line: At this rate nothing about the fleet will change! Get yourself together, Commander!

main3.line: Commander? Are you listening? I'm gonna throw the chalk at you~! I hate people who don't listen to me! Hmph!

mission.line: Erhmm... Have you finished your homework today?

mission_complete.line: The reward for diligence has been delivered. Keep it up for next time!

profile.line: Ahem! I am the Eagle Union's first, I repeat, the first aircraft carrier, Langley! I do not think highly of my own fighting ability, but I've put out numerous outstanding pilots! The Eagle Union's aircraft carrier begins with me, I say!

propose.line: I was concerned about whether Commander takes good care of himself before...so from now on, teacher Langley will also correct issues of your personal life; Don't even think about running away, Commander~

skill.line: Commander, pay close attention to my moves!

touch.line: Please do not treat me like a child~! I am a teacher! TEA-CHER!

touch2.line: *phone call* Hello, is this the military police? Yes, it's the same place and the same person...

unlock.line: I've been newly assigned to assist you. Name's Langley. You listening? I am going to fix what's wrong with you, and put you on the right track to running a fleet.

upgrade.line: Even when you become stronger, never forget about why you had to in the first place.

win_mvp.line: Got it, everyone? Maintain this pace, alright?

detail.line: Commander, if you run into a mental problem, you have to solve it on your own. Staring at me won't help you.

drop_descrip.line: Listen carefully or I'll step on you!

main1.line: If we make a little progress each day, we'll be sure to achieve great results one day

main2.line: This fleet feels different from when I first came. With your hard work, Commander, we can do anything.

main3.line: We have to punish naughty children. Don't you agree, Commander?

touch.line: I will answer any question you have for me. However, is that really alright for you, Commander?

unlock.line: Listen to what I say, or I'll have to step on you!

battle.line: Everyone! Let's claim victory for our Commander!

detail.line: Aww, your frown has curled your brows. You have your share of hard work too, Commander...

drop_descrip.line: Lexington-class aircraft carrier ー Lexington, Hull Number CV-2!

expedition.line: Oh my~ The girls of the commission team have returned

feeling1.line: Oh dear, you are mistaken if you think I'm going to accept everything you do.

feeling2.line: Being an idol is a job that brings smiles to everyone. Of course, that includes you too, Commander. *giggles*

feeling3.line: Recently, whenever I dream about the Coral Sea, you are there, Commander. It somehow makes me feel safe. I wonder why~

feeling4.line: Commander, wanna try becoming my manager? You're capable and you know me, and I can't think of you as anything short of dependable~

feeling5.line: A solo live show? Oh, I haven't had plans for that yet. But if someone were to give me a ring as a present, maybe I'll host that kind of show every day. And the audience is only a single person, you see~

home.line: Oh, something's on your face. I'll wipe it off, so don't move~

hp_warning.line: Maybe it's time to cheer everyone up with my song~

login.line: Oh my~ Where are you heading, Commander? Don't worry. As long as I'm around, even the high flying crane won't get away

lose.line: Oh my~ we can't keep up with their pace. Should we retreat for now?

mail.line: A new mail has arrived. If your hands are full then perhaps I should reply it for you~

main1.line: I'm not as lively as my younger sister, though I'm confident in my own charms. What do you think~

main2.line: Oh my, where is Saratoga hiding? She's such a handful...

main3.line: My eyes are gorgeous? Well, for an idol, my eyes have to look like this~

mission.line: Oh Commander, there are still missions that have yet to be completed~

mission_complete.line: Carrier planes, bring the mission rewards to the Commander

profile.line:
Oh my~ I am aircraft carrier Lexington. 
I'm gentle? That's because I'm everyone's older sister~ That means you are a cute junior too! 
I feel assured since I've seen Saratoga working hard. Please give some attention to her as well

propose.line: Oh, oh my oh my~ I was wondering how long I would have to wait for you, Commander~ *giggles* Well then, the private live show ticket has been sold out~ The show goes-- forever~

touch.line: Commander, you seem like a hapless little brother~

touch2.line: Oh goodness, are you unsatisfied with being the younger brother?

unlock.line: Good day, Mr. Commander~ I am Lexington. I heard that my name was from the first battlefield of the War for Independance. As an idol, I think I need to have a big heart. Don't you agree?

upgrade.line: *giggles* I suddenly feel like singing. Wanna listen?

win_mvp.line: *giggles* Lady Lex is not really a title of mine~

main1.line: An idol will change her outfits and dresses several times during a performance, each one bringing forth a different character... As long as I can bring smiles to everyone's faces, I will be happy.

main2.line: nil

main3.line: Wearing this outfit seems to have gotten the children all fired up~ Hehe, Commander, don't you think this outfit brings out my domestic side?

touch.line: Commander, do you like my dress that much? Should we ask the Empery girls to tailor an outfit for you as well?

unlock.line: Hehe… sometimes you can completely change the way people see you with just a simple change in attire. Don't you agree, Commander~? Don’t worry, I'm still your Lexington~

win_mvp.line: Hehe, new outfits do bring new joys with them after all~

detail.line: If you keep on peeping where you shouldn't, even kids will not be talking to you~

drop_descrip.line: Lexington-class aircraft carrier ー Saratoga, Hull Number CV-3!

expedition.line: Commander, my patrol planes told me the girls out for commission have returned~

feeling1.line: Pranks? I already stopped pulling them on you~ You're no fun for those

feeling2.line: Who should I prank today~?

feeling3.line: Commander, what's the greatest difference between me and my big sister? The answer, is my 'color' today!

feeling4.line: Commander, I have something I want to tell you. I'm gonna write it on the back of your hand~ and done... Did you think I'm gonna write 'I like you'? Silly Commander~

feeling5.line: Commander, you dropped something~~ *kiss* ...Hehe, it was my heart♡. Here, you can keep it!

home.line: We~ are back~

hp_warning.line: Wah! I'm in a pinch!

login.line: Oh my~ Sorry Commander. I didn't mean to launch planes at you on purpose~

lose.line: Oh dang~ I'll go back for repairs, and then have a good rest while I'm at it~

mail.line: You didn't see the mail? --Then should I read it?

main1.line: Boo! Hehe, did I susprise you?  Commander, you're slow, aren't you?!

main2.line: Commander, don't confuse me with my big sister!

main3.line: Eh? Call you 'big bro'? There's no way that's happening~

mission.line: Commander, can't you complete even a mission?

mission_complete.line: This is bad, Commander! The mission rewards are missing! --Darn, you caught me.

profile.line:
I am aircraft carrier Lexington's little sister, Saratoga! Hmm... I like to play pranks! But you already knew that, Commander~ 
Pioneer of aviation tactics? If my sister hadn't passed away so soon, that title would've definitely been hers.

propose.line: Ah, Commander. Please wait for a bit~ The Eagle Union carriers are all gathering~ Eh? This is a once in a lifetime occassion! Despite my appearance I am a veteran. I'm well respected!

skill.line: Where are you looking? I'm right over here~

touch.line: My stature may be small, but I've yet to grow past that fact!

touch2.line: ...wha!

unlock.line: Hey there, and good day, Commander! I am Lexington...'s little sister, Saratoga~ If there's nothing important, I'm leaving now

upgrade.line: Saratoga-chan loves you a lot~!

win_mvp.line: Ooh la la~ Big sis is busy, so it's fine that I get to come by once a while~
