drop_descrip.line: Even if we don't get to relax on holiday, it's always good to have a swimsuit! Ok, let's go! Are you ready to swim?

expedition.line: The girls out for commission have returned. I made some shaved ice with my planes. Commander, want some syrup on top?

home.line: We~ are back~ Phew~ it's so hot!

login.line: Commander, let's head to the beach today! I want to eat chilled watermelon!

main1.line: When you talk about a sport to play on the beach, it has to be this!

main2.line: Commander, how about we get into the sea? I'll borrow you my lifesaver!

main3.line: W-Wales? Why are you hugging me suddenly... I've grown 'bigger'? Really? That's right! I have grown bigger after all!

mission.line: Eat the ice cream, and go complete the mission! I'll prepare a fireworks show for tonight!

mission_complete.line: Commander, are you done with the mission? I'm tired from volleyball practice as well. Phew... It's so hot I'm too worn to prank...

touch.line: In beach volleyball...I l-lost to destroyers... my sister isn't here... Commander, can I cry on your shoulder for a while?

touch2.line: Commander! Saratoga won! Come and see! I beat Honolulu! She can't believe it!

unlock.line: Even in a day off, I'm not loosening up! Phew... Swimsuit, check. All preparations complete! Launch time! I'll show you Sister Sara's power!

upgrade.line: If I evolve once more, I'm gonna show the Royals what I'm made of!

win_mvp.line: Summertime Saratoga has no weakspots! ☆

login.line: Welcome back, Commander~! The prank this time... is a perfectly ordinary and prank-free greeting~!

main1.line: Sure enough, a black ribbon suits Sister sara the best!

main2.line: As a special service for the hardworking commander... Sister Sara's smile will wash away your fatigue! How do you feel? Teehee~

main3.line: Commander, what are you fantasizing about right now? C'mon, you can tell me!

touch.line: Commander, I hope your attention isn't focused on some place weird?

touch2.line: Woah! Commander, what are you trying to do to your cute little Sara?

unlock.line: Hey everyone~! This time, Sister Sara has brought you fashion from a faraway land! Commander, what do you think of it?

battle.line: I'll show you what a virtual idol is capable of!

feeling1.line: Fakkyu! Fakkyufakkyu! Fakk! Yu!

feeling5.line: Commander, when I'm in this outfit, it feels as if I'm literally "tied" to you~! Sister Sara loves being tightly connected with you♡

login.line: Welcome back, Commander! I'm about to go watch Kizuna AI rehearse the lyrics for her next performance! It's a rare opportunity, so you should come along too!

lose.line: Sorry, Commander... I lost the game...

main1.line: Since I don't usually get this opportunity, maybe I should try to record a song for an anime~♪

main2.line: A new opportunity? An idol only shines because of her courage! We can't be afraid to try new things!

main3.line: Heh heh, the enemy's wide open! Pyoko Pyoko, go get 'em~!

touch.line: Since I've finally become a virtual idol, maybe I should release some new songs~

touch2.line: Uwah...! Commander, where are you touching?! Eh? This is the only way to determine if I'm the real deal...? Not like this...

unlock.line: HAI DOMO~! I’m the virtual idol, Saratoga! Well, Commander, what do you think? I asked Kizuna AI to make this dress specifically for me, modeled after her outfit!

win_mvp.line: #WINNING~! Expect no less of Sister Sara!

battle.line: Sister Sara won't forgive those who would destroy the peace of the seas! Go forth~!

drop_descrip.line: Friends of the blue sea and sky, your guardian angel and idol Sara has arrived! Ehehe~ Commander, join me in protecting the beauty of the blue seas!

login.line: Whoosh! Ehehe~ Did you like our passionate welcoming fanfare?

main1.line: It feels great to pet these cuties! Don't you wanna give it a try as well, Commander?

main2.line: The sea is colored navy blue, and in this moment, Sara is a true marine idol! Heheh♪

main3.line: Oh yeah, I saw a seal while on patrol the other day! You should come see it with me next time, Commander!

touch2.line: Waaah?! ... Heh, hehehe... You just gave me a great excuse to test out my new gear...

unlock.line: Friends of the blue sea and sky, your guardian angel and idol Sara has arrived! Ehehe~ Commander, join me in protecting the beauty of the blue seas!

detail.line: This is my special present just for you, Commander! Here~ ...This isn't the setup for a prank, I promise!

login.line: You're so late, Commander! ...Not really, just kidding! Anyhoo, lead the way and I'll follow!

main1.line: Commander! You can borrow my mittens if your hands get cold!

main2.line: Do you think Santa Claus is real, Commander? Me, I think he does, at least as someone who brings joy to people even without ever being seen!

main3.line: The whole city has been swept up in the holiday mood! Isn't Christmas just the best~?

touch.line: Wearing this winter outfit lets me blend into crowds! For, well, multiple reasons...

unlock.line: Merry Christmas! Here comes Christmas Sara, shining like a star in the silent night! Hehehe, how's that for a holiday greeting? So, have you decided where we're gonna spend our Christmas Eve yet?

drop_descrip.line: Tadaaah! Happy Lunar New Year, Commander! How do you like this fresh new spring look that Sara's rocking? Hope you haven't forgotten our promise to check out the port's spring festival together~ Ready, then? Let's go!

main1.line: Look at this panda ornament Ping gave me! Isn't it just adorable?

main2.line: A New Year's gift? For Sara? Hrmm... You know, Instructor Sara would rather be giving than receiving, but regular Sara won't turn down a gift from you!

main3.line: Let me just test my fan... Whoosh! Hehehe~ Nice breeze, right?

touch.line: Could you hold on to my handbag for a bit, Commander? Remember, no peeking inside!

unlock.line: Tadaaah! Happy Lunar New Year, Commander! How do you like this fresh new spring look that Sara's rocking? Hope you haven't forgotten our promise to check out the port's spring festival together~ Ready, then? Let's go!

detail.line: Actually, I didn't throw together this picnic all by myself. My new friend helped a whole bunch~

drop_descrip.line: Tada! Welcome to Sister Sara's special picnic! Look at all the delicious food I brought~ See, Commander, I told you it wasn't just another prank~♪

home.line: C-Commander! There's a caterpillar on your shoulder! Just kidding~ Did I spook ya?

login.line: Hehe, you're right on time! And that earns you a prize! Come and have a slice of Sister's whole-grain toast! Get it while it's still hot~

main1.line: Tomato and veggie sandwiches with whole-grain bread! Today's lunch menu is super healthy!

main2.line: Ah, hold on, you have to wash your hands before eating! Commander, you too!

main3.line: You're welcome to lie down over there and take a nap, but~ I can't guarantee that you won't have circles and squiggles drawn all over your face when you wake up~ Heehee~

touch.line: Hey, you've got food stuck on your cheek, Commander. Come over here and I'll wipe it off for you.

touch2.line: Woooah! ...I'm confiscating your food! You've made Sister Sara very angry! Hmph!

unlock.line: Tada! Welcome to Sister Sara's special picnic! Look at all the delicious food I brought~ See, Commander, I told you it wasn't just another prank~♪

detail.line: Make sure Sister Sara is the center of your universe! Ehehe, even if you don't do that, I'll use every trick up my sleeves to make sure that you can't take your eyes off me, or stop thinking about me~♪

drop_descrip.line: You ready, Commander? ...Come on, don't give me a "just one moment" right before the finish line~ It's time to imprint my adorable dress into your memory forever~♡

feeling5.line: Since we've already come this far together, I won't sneak around playing pranks on you anymore. Sister Sara will prove it to the world–– Turn your face this way, Commander~ Mmwah~♡

home.line: Commander, good job out there~ C'mere and let Sister Sara give you a shoulder rub~♪

login.line: Wheee~! Ehehe, it always feels like my day's missing a little "oomph" unless I play a prank on you, Commander~♪

lose.line: Sorry, sorry! It's okay, Sister Sara is totally fine!

mail.line: We've got mail. Wonder if there's any juicy news inside~♪

main2.line: Pop quiz time! Would you rather go on a date with Sister Sara, or get pranked~?

main3.line: Sister Sara will handle the dinner prep tonight! I'll show you everything that my sis taught me~♪

touch.line: Don't underestimate me just because I'm small! ...And, I meant that in more ways than one!

touch2.line: Even Sister Sara can get embarrassed, you know?!

unlock.line: You ready, Commander? ...Come on, don't give me a "just one moment" right before the finish line~ It's time to imprint my adorable dress into your memory forever~♡

win_mvp.line: The power of love knows no limits~♪

home.line: Welcome back~ Feel free to hang your coat on my planes or something~♪

login.line: Whoosh! Commander, what do you think of Sister Sara's welcoming flight formation?

main1.line: Commander, how about we make all the younger Eagle Union carriers into magical girls as well~? Hehehe~

main2.line: It's time for Magical Sister Saratoga's invincible catch phrase - even if you can't see the light, it'll definitely be all right! ...Opinions?

main3.line: There's nothing better than sharing Sister Sara's smiles and energy with the world!

touch.line: Commander, my wand would probably feel great when used like a baseball bat or a crowbar... Wanna let me try~?

touch2.line: Aww, Sister Sara's not fit to be a bride anymore~

unlock.line: Sister Sara is leaving her nest and going in a new direction! I'm now making my official debut as Saratoga: The Little Witch Idol! I'm leaving my PR to you, Commander~

battle.line: Everyone, the one with the lowest results will get extra lessons~~

detail.line:
D-don't look at me inappropriatly! And do your work properly! 
--Y-Y-You were just looking at my bridge?! ...Ahaha...

drop_descrip.line: Ranger-class aircraft carrier ー Ranger, Hull Number CV-4!

expedition.line: Mr. Commander~ You forgot to check the results. You might see the girls become angry at you.

feeling1.line: Maybe I should quit teaching...

feeling2.line: Why are kids today thinking about weird things all the time...!

feeling3.line: Commander, you are a capable child if you are put into action. I feel a little happy.

feeling4.line: T-T-Teacher-student relationships?!! I've never thought about such things; I've never even read those kinds of books before. I totally, totally never look forward to that!

feeling5.line: Commander, you're really helpless without me. S-so... I-I'm... I'm holding you back for another year!

home.line: Have you finished your homework? Alright. Then as promised, I'll give you a reward~

login.line: Can I conduct combat operations since the weather is so nice today, Commander?

lose.line: I can't let you see me like this, Commander.....

main1.line: What I teach besides fighting is human se... I-I mean... physical education!

main2.line: The Sakura Empire? ...Uh, Uhhh... I- I don't know enough to teach you about that!

main3.line: If you don't listen to what I say, I'll punish you!

mission.line: Finish your missions properly. Otherwise, there will be catch up lessons!

mission_complete.line: The compensation... is nothing major, but it's not good to neglect it either.

profile.line: I'm Ranger, the first purpose-built aircraft carrier of the Eagle Union. During my service in the Atlantic, I was part of various missions functioning as the largest carrier in the area. While I'm a carrier... please don't have weird expectations of me! For your sake, I don't want to disappoint you!

propose.line: *cries*... Receiving such a precious thing from a student, and getting so happy to the point of shedding tears... I, Ranger, am a failure as an educator...

touch.line: Hwaa!? Commander... S...Stop... is what you want me to say?!

touch2.line: D-don't tell anyone about this! You'll embarrass me!

unlock.line: I'm the Eagle Union's first purpose-built carrier, Ranger! I was stationed in the Atlantic, where I mainly served as an escort to convoys and aircraft carriers. Specialty teaching? T-that's not what I was sent here for, b-but… if you insist…  --I can do it...

upgrade.line: I, Ms. Ranger, am going to teach you some more things

win_mvp.line: Commander, you must not become worn out quickly like the enemy-- Oh no... not like that!

battle.line: Everyone, it's time to put what you learned to use!

detail.line: C-Commander?! I-I-Is my bridge, really that beautiful?

drop_descrip.line: I didn't realize I could still become more powerful! I'll work harder from here on out to teach everyone how to fight!

home.line: Commander, you've grown but you haven't changed much. Alright, here's your reward~

login.line: This child seems fine... This one is recovering well... Ah, welcome back, Commander!

main2.line: I've only improved a few times before, and they were just small enhancements. Now that everyone is stronger, I can start getting some work done.

main3.line: Commander? I believe in you, so I'm letting you study on your own while I work on my planes. I'll get angry if you avoid your study this time, alright?

touch.line: Yeah yeah, Commander is totally not good without a Teacher here... Yup, can't help it~

touch2.line: Commander, can you help a teacher out here a little?... Eeek! ....Really?...

unlock.line: The modernization that had never happened has finally been completed! From now on, I, Ms. Ranger, will continue to teach as well~

win_mvp.line: If you engage in some special training with me, you'll withstand fatigue for a longer time, Commander! ...Eh? Why are you looking at me like that?

battle.line: Let's search for the light!

detail.line: It's alright if you don't remember me...

drop_descrip.line: Yorktown-class aircraft carrier ー Yorktown, Hull Number CV-5!

expedition.line: What's wrong, little eagle? So, the commission team has returned? Commander, let us greet them.

feeling1.line: So you truly will leave me one day...

feeling2.line: I want to maintain the current superior-subordinate relationship, Commander... Don't mind me...

feeling3.line: Commander, you're weird... Even though I don't want to experience more painful departures, you keep stepping into my heart...

feeling4.line: Can I believe in you, Commander...? I mean, can I believe in myself this time...? I want... to try...

feeling5.line: Yes. I believe in you, Commander, as well as myself and the present day... The light beyond the darkness... I think I've finally found it

home.line: You're not hurt... That's good

hp_warning.line: The light is still far away...

login.line: Greetings, Commander. If there's a problem, please leave it to me.

lose.line: Please retreat first, Commander.

mail.line: My eagle got the mail. Please read it carefully.

main1.line: This eagle really likes being with me, but is it alright for me to feed it...?

main2.line: Commander, please do not confuse 42 with 24, no matter what

main3.line: If there's time, maybe you should spend it with my younger sisters... I'm fine on my own

mission.line: Your new missions have been organized, Commander.

mission_complete.line: The mission rewards have been delivered. Please check them.

profile.line:
Lead ship of the Yorktown class aircraft carriers, Yorktown. 
Abandoned...? It wasn't their fault, but I do not have the courage to reach out for light from that darkness. Will you leave me, Commander? Or will you guide me by my hand...?

propose.line: I had fallen into the darkness. It was you, Commander who gave me light and a helping hand which pulled me out of it. That's why this time, I, Yorktown, will give you my name. The name that shoulders the burden of liberty and peace...

touch.line: Commander, what happened?

touch2.line: Are you truly prepared to leave your mark on someone like me?

unlock.line: I am the lead ship of Yorktown class aircraft carriers, Yorktown. My name comes from the Siege of Yorktown... You know? In the Revolutionary War. Neutrality...? That's just a pre-war courtesy.

upgrade.line: Thanks...

win_mvp.line: If victory can bring peace, then I...!

battle.line: Uhhh, where am I?

detail.line: Come to think of it, Enterprise did tell me not to drink the blue stuff like A MILLION TIMES. But like, what's the dig beal, Commander?

drop_descrip.line: Hey, Commander, are you lost? How about a drink? ... Huh? Drunk? Me? Oh, Commander, you're such a card. This is just grape juice... isn't it?

expedition.line: You wanna sneak off to the harbor? Ugh, I TOLD you already, Commander, I'm *hic* not as think as you drunk I am!

feeling5.line: I mean, it's only natural for a good couple to be a little clingy, right? After all I've been through, I'm WAY too shy to make the first move. So that means YOU have to do it. Got it?

home.line: I'm not letting you leave until YOU have a drink with me, Commander.

hp_warning.line: Urk. I feel... a little sick...

login.line: You're late, Commander. You know what THAT means. One penalty drink!

lose.line: I, I have a feeling... like all the clout I had as a big sister is COMPLETELY GONE... after tonight...

mail.line: You can't go off with someone else until you finish drinking with ME, Commander!

main1.line: Enterprise is a good girl. So's Hornet. And Hammann. They all found their PLACE in this fleet. But me? The big sister? I'm HAPPY for them. And a teeeensy bit lonely.

main2.line: You know, Commander, looking back, I have some regrets. Like if I knew you were THIS good? I'd've been more HONEST with myself.

main3.line: Oh! Is that my cute little Hammann?! When did you get so BIG?! ...Oh, you're the Commander, aren't you? Have you seen Hammann?

mission.line: Now now, Commander, I'll be mad at you if you ditch these assignments.

mission_complete.line: Here's to a mission accomplished! CHEERS!

touch.line: Hey, Commander, you wanna hear some EMBARRASSING stories about Enterprise and Hornet? Oh, you'd rather hear mine? Hehe, THAT can be arranged.

touch2.line: OH! Commander, at least buy me a drink first!

unlock.line: Hey, Commander, are you lost? How about a drink? ... Huh? Drunk? Me? Oh, Commander, you're such a card. This is just grape juice... isn't it?

win_mvp.line: OOPSIE! What was that I just said in front of EVERYONE...?

battle.line: For our ideals...!

detail.line: The cathedral, the Holy Well, and... Commander, where's the next spot again?

drop_descrip.line: Across seven steps, in a tower atop a hill, you'll find the king's resting place... Hehe. Will you come with me to Utopia, Commander? I'm joking, of course, but I am very glad we could make this journey together.

expedition.line: What's the matter, my friend? I see, the commission team has returned? I'll let Hornet know.

feeling5.line: My true utopia... is the port that Enterprise and the others can call home. If there's ever a place that can bring me eternal peace... I'd think that it would be by your side, Commander.

login.line: Commander, how about taking a photo right here?

lose.line: Freedom... will never be extinguished...!

main1.line: What kind of souvenir do you think Hammann would like? ...A warding stone...?

main2.line: George is quite knowledgeable isn't she? Quite befitting of a Royal Knight, I'd say. Commander, why don't you tell me a bit about this place too?

main3.line: I quite like it here. All the places we visit have quite a unique atmosphere, whether in Iris Libre or in the Eagle Union... Hehe.

mission.line: New mission notifications? Why don't you let Hood handle it?

mission_complete.line: The mission rewards have arrived. I'm excited to see what we got.

touch2.line: Am I... good enough for you?

unlock.line: Across seven steps, in a tower atop a hill, you'll find the king's resting place... Hehe. Will you come with me to Utopia, Commander? I'm joking, of course, but I am very glad we could make this journey together.

win_mvp.line: The purpose of my wings are to guide us towards peace––

battle.line: Please be careful, Commander.

detail.line: The sound of my pounding heart seems to be riding the breeze of happiness across this lake, all the way until it reaches your ears... No, what I should be saying is, I want you to hear it, Commander. Can you feel... my love for you?

drop_descrip.line: This wedding dress, brimming with light, flutters like a feather in the wind... I'm sure that I'm still in a long, deep, slumber... That's right, Commander. The two of us are surely sharing a blissful dream together, heehee.

expedition.line: The girls in the commission team have come back. Let's go greet... Ah, umm... M-maybe I shouldn't go in this outfit after all...?

feeling5.line: I, Yorktown, will always remain by your side. Through the moment when true peace finally arrives, through the bright and joyous days that follow after that, forever and ever...

headtouch.line: I'm not sure I did anything to deserve this reward... Heehee, just kidding~

home.line: Shall we do a quick debriefing first? We can save the celebratory toast... for when the two of us have some alone time, okay?

login.line: Good day, Commander. For today's agenda... Umm, did you perhaps need a change of pace? Heehee. In that case, allow me to accompany you.

lose.line: Don't worry, I'll be fine. Commander, let's try to keep a clear head, okay?

mail.line: Commander, new mail has arrived. Shall we go through it together?

main1.line: I've already prepared a drink for you, so just go ahead and lie down over there. I don't mind lending you my lap either should you need it~ Heehee.

main2.line: Just as you saved me, Commander, I'm sure you'll also lead the other girls into the light. For your sake – for the person who I cherish so dearly, I wish to become your strength.

main3.line: The wind seems to be picking up... Oh, Commander, shall we head back inside shortly? We'll have plenty of time to chat afterwards~ Heehee.

mission.line: ...Eagle? Mm, we have work, don't we? I need to strike while the iron is hot, before the Commander can get away~♪

mission_complete.line: What's wrong, Eagle? ...Hmm? The rewards are here? Heehee, I see~ It seems that you and Commander understand each other better now.

touch.line: What do you think about the texture of my clothes? Smooth and soft? ...Ah, um... I think that's my skin you're feeling there, not my clothes... *blushes*...

touch2.line: Do you hear that throbbing? It's the sound of my heartbeat, intertwining with yours–

unlock.line: This wedding dress, brimming with light, flutters like a feather in the wind... I'm sure that I'm still in a long, deep, slumber... That's right, Commander. The two of us are surely sharing a blissful dream together, heehee.

win_mvp.line: MVP? Hmm, I wonder what kind of reward I should ask for... Maybe I'll have the Commander pat me on the head as if I was a kid? Heehee~

battle.line: Venture forth!

detail.line: Want to look at my medal collection?

drop_descrip.line: Yorktown-class aircraft carrier ー Enterprise, Hull Number CV-6!

expedition.line: I've been on the battlefield for a long time, so I know about the importance of logistics. Commander, let's greet the girls who work hard behind the scenes.

feeling1.line: ...Commander, you don't seem to have enough courage

feeling2.line: It is my wish to live honestly and sincerely. That's why I'll speak my mind if I have something to say. You too should do the same without holding back.

feeling3.line: All the lights in the sky are stars, just as all the lights on the seas are enemies... Commander, will there be a day where there's no more fighting?

feeling4.line: There's no meaning in being peerless. As long as you are here, Commander, I can draw upon all of my strength. Let us end this war.

feeling5.line: What do you want to do after the war? --Me? I'll probably stick with you. I feel the safest out of battle when I'm with you. Will you... take me along with you?

home.line: It's one battle after another, huh...

hp_warning.line: Interesting...!

login.line: You've come. If it's fighting, I'm ready for it any time.

lose.line: I've lost after giving my all. I'm not regretting this...

mail.line: Commander, it's a new mail.

main1.line: Is it you, Commander? ...Recently, I'm thinking about whether or not I can engage in anti-submarine actions...

main2.line: Luck is also a part of strength? Then if possible, I'd like to impart some of it to my older sister.

main3.line: So long as we live, there are things that will never go our way. When we die, it must happen in a way that carries no regrets.

mission.line: Commander, your missions are not yet completed.  Hurry up and set off!

mission_complete.line: Commander, the rewards are here.

profile.line: I am the Yorktown class aircraft carrier, Enterprise. "Grey Ghost" is one of the many nicknames I have. My smoke-covered and bloodstained battle record is a reminder of my mission. I will continue to be victorious until the war ends.

propose.line: I carry with me the hopes and wills of the countless battlefields and goodbyes that I have experienced. Commander, are you prepared to shoulder them all? …I see. Then let us walk together until the end of our lives.

touch.line: What is it? Sortie time?

touch2.line: What the...?!

unlock.line: Second ship of the Yorktown class, Enterprise, reporting for duty. I will neither sympathize nor hold back with my enemies, and instead, I go all out. Such is my way.

upgrade.line: I will show you... what lies at the end of power

win_mvp.line: Commander, tell me. How many more do I have to sink?

detail.line: Be thankful for the past, have dreams for the future, and live life in the present!

drop_descrip.line: Merry Christmas, Commander! I shall be Santa Claus tonight, so make sure to hang up your stockings on the fireplace before going to sleep!

main1.line: Merry Christmas! Is there anything you'd like as a present?

main2.line: Of course Santa Claus is real. Hmm? Right in front of you.

main3.line: A white Christmas, how beautiful... Eh? W-wait, Vestal, don't drag me back in! I'm not cold... I swear, I'm really not cold!

touch.line: Celebrate to your heart's content! These wonderful memories shall light your way during the darkest battles.

unlock.line: Merry Christmas, Commander! I shall be Santa Claus tonight, so make sure to hang up your stockings on the fireplace before going to sleep!

detail.line: Being able to enjoy this peaceful, festive holiday atmosphere is only possible because of everyone's continued hard work... Right, Commander?

drop_descrip.line: So this is the traditional attire of the Dragon Empery? Hmm... it fits quite well. Oh? Custom-made bow and arrows… Interesting, let's see how far these arrows can fly.

home.line: There's no harm in taking a little break before the next battle, Commander.

login.line: Lanterns... should be hung up like this, right? Ah, Commander, you're here. I heard that they hang lanterns up to celebrate Lunar New Year in the Dragon Empery, so I gave it a try... You think it's fine? Festive, isn't it?

main1.line: My flight deck is also decorated with a theme from the Dragon Empery. Its colors represent joy and happiness. Not bad, huh.

main2.line: According to legend, a mythical beast called the "Nian" comes out during the Lunar New Year. It can be warded off by setting off a lot of firecrackers.

main3.line: I heard that it's customary in the Dragon Empery to hand out "red envelopes" during the New Year. Should I prepare some for the Union girls?

touch.line: Commander, it seems that this coat is big enough to accommodate two people. It's super warm - want to see for yourself?

unlock.line: So this is the traditional attire of the Dragon Empery? Hmm... it fits quite well. Oh? Custom-made bow and arrows… Interesting, let's see how far these arrows can fly.

battle.line: Enterprise, engage!

detail.line: Commander, are you doing well? Live long and prosper!

drop_descrip.line: Happy Anniversary! Commander, celebrate to your heart's content today! I'll be praying for our continued victories!

feeling1.line: Maybe I should just hit the road and never look back...

feeling5.line: Would you like to come with me, Commander? We can go anywhere in the world. Think of all the new people and cultures we could discover together on our trek!

home.line: Good work out there! Go ahead and take a break while the others are being inspected.

login.line: Ah, you're here. I'm ready to go whenever you are. Oh, can't be forgetting my helmet!

lose.line: Sometimes there really is a no-win scenario...

mail.line: Commander, there's an incoming message from fleet command.

main1.line: Commander? Recently... I've been thinking about how it would feel to be able to soar through the skies and stars... but that's not really possible. Sorry for making you listen to my idle thoughts.

main2.line: Vacation, huh... To be honest, I've been deployed in so many places during my lengthy service that sometimes even vacations feel like yet another mission...

main3.line: Recently, Essex has picked up biking as well. It'd be great to go out with everyone else next time.

touch.line: Would you also like to see my trusty steed?

unlock.line: Happy Anniversary! Commander, celebrate to your heart's content today! I'll be praying for our continued victories!

win_mvp.line: For the sake of freedom and the Azur Lane, I'll keep on winning!

battle.line: Enterprise, sallying forth! Let us crush our enemies!

detail.line: I do not believe that it is correct to wantonly resort to violence, even in the name of justice.

drop_descrip.line: There is no doubt in my mind that I was born to fight. For the azure lanes of liberty, Enterprise, engaging!

expedition.line: Would you like to greet the commission fleet? It's a good idea to get some exercise. Otherwise, Hornet's going to make fun of you.

home.line: Commander, thank you for your hard work. Let's get ready for the next operation.

login.line: Good day, Commander. There's still some time until the strategy meeting, so you should rest up while you still have the opportunity to.

lose.line: So I've... overstepped my limits...?

main1.line: I'm quite impressed by the Royal Maids. Aside from their combat prowess, they're also very good at a wide variety of other things.

main2.line: Vestal, what's the matter? ...No, I've been making sure to eat! Commander has been making all sorts... I mean, I cook from time to time as well!

main3.line: My eagle is quite attached to you, Commander. We should all get along just like you two. Hehe.

mission.line: We still have missions that haven't been completed. You should check on their progress.

touch.line: Commander, do you need me for something?

touch2.line: You wouldn't do this to Yorktown, would you...

unlock.line: There is no doubt in my mind that I was born to fight. For the azure lanes of liberty, Enterprise, engaging!

win_mvp.line: Our slight advantage seems to have given us the victory here.

detail.line: Right, I didn't get to ask you earlier since you were in a hurry, but what do you think about my outfit? I value your input just as much as I value that of Hornet and the others.

drop_descrip.line: My ballgown? I don't normally get to wear clothes like these, so it took me a while to change. Ah, let's hurry to the venue. We shouldn't keep everyone else waiting.

expedition.line: The girls in the commission fleet have returned? The formalities will have to wait then. I'll go welcome them back first.

home.line: Commander, you shouldn't overexert yourself... Hm, you should be the one saying that to me? I understand.

login.line: I'm Enterprise of the Eagle Union. Let's proceed to the event venue.

main1.line: I see, so this is how it's done. Next time, I'll have to learn how to make... Hm? Ahh, I was talking about ice cream. Do you want some, Commander?

main2.line: I'm used to emergency sorties. Even if I'm at a banquet, just give me the order and I'll scramble my planes.

main3.line: What about Independence? Ahh, she's a nice and adorable girl, just like Eagle. Good friends who heal my heart from the weariness of battle.

unlock.line: My ballgown? I don't normally get to wear clothes like these, so it took me a while to change. Ah, let's hurry to the venue. We shouldn't keep everyone else waiting.

win_mvp.line: May this victory serve as the ornament to a fine celebration.

battle.line: Come, spread your wings and fly!

detail.line: Ah, Commander, there's something I wanted to ask you about... What do you think about this pose? I want to do what I can so I don't sully your reputation.

drop_descrip.line: Commander, did you come to watch the race? You know... I'd rather be down there competing than standing around over here. That feeling of being able to seize the wind... Don't you think that racing and sailing share the same essence?

expedition.line: The commission fleet has returned. Sorry, but could you welcome them back in my place?

home.line: Good work, Commander. Go ahead and take a break, I'll handle the follow-up work for the others.

login.line: Let's do our best today. I'll be cheering you on.

main1.line: Is that... Zuikaku? That's a pretty showy outfit... though I'm not exactly in a position to talk myself.

main2.line: Essex, be careful when you're charging ahead! ...Oh, um, I didn't mean to patronize, I just can't help but get a bit worried...

main3.line: You'd like to help me with the maintenance? Sure. To be honest, you might be better suited for this job. Ahaha~

touch.line: A photo op? Sure, but what kind of pose should I make?

touch2.line: That's against the rules, Commander.

unlock.line: Commander, did you come to watch the race? You know... I'd rather be down there competing than standing around over here. That feeling of being able to seize the wind... Don't you think that racing and sailing share the same essence?

win_mvp.line: First place, huh? Normally not much of a reason to celebrate, but since we're at a race, let's uncork the champagne.

battle.line: No matter where my foes appear, I'll take them down all the same!

detail.line: Thank you for letting me experience the stillness you can only find away from the battlefield, Commander. It's shown me... what's really worth protecting.

drop_descrip.line: It feels odd taking an extended leave just to go on vacation... but I guess you need breaks to stay on top of your game. With that in mind, let's make every minute count, Commander!

expedition.line: Commission team's come back. Let's go say hi and give them some souvenirs while we're at it.

feeling5.line: I've been all over the world on missions before, but this is my first time visiting another country as a tourist. Everything just feels so novel... I think now I get the appeal of vacationing. Here's hoping we'll see many more new places and people in future journeys to come, Commander!

home.line: Solid performance, Commander. You can go lie down for a bit while I work out our next plan.

login.line: There you are. I'm good to go whenever you are.

lose.line: This is why you never pop the champagne early...

main1.line: With so many museums and iconic buildings, it's no wonder this city is called the Capital of Art. I'd love to come here again with you at some later point.

main2.line: I asked Vestal about places to visit, and she suggested this village where lavenders bloom en masse. Said we "should definitely check it out."

main3.line: After visiting all these places with you, I've realized something – the sights themselves aren't super important to me, what matters is seeing them together with someone dear to me.

mission.line: Commander, be sure to check your mission progress before we head to the next tourist destination.

mission_complete.line: Can we check out a gift shop now that you've claimed these rewards? I want to get something for my sisters that'll really make them smile.

touch.line: What's up? Our tickets are all in order, if that's what you're wondering.

unlock.line: It feels odd taking an extended leave just to go on vacation... but I guess you need breaks to stay on top of your game. With that in mind, let's make every minute count, Commander!

win_mvp.line: Guess we're celebrating this victory with a full course dinner. I can't wait.

detail.line: As long as you are around, no matter how tough a battle I endure or how great the pain I suffer from being separated from you, I’ll go on with hope that I’ll finally be with you.

drop_descrip.line: How, how does it look? Do I look a bit strange... no, of course I like it. I'd say every girl dreams about this day, just that...

main1.line: Would you like to try my cooking tonight? Vestal said that I've already mastered her cooking skills...I am not that kind of girl who solely exists on the battlefield

main2.line: nil

main3.line: Because of you, I started to believe that one day this war will past and people will smile happily again.

touch.line: Hmm, I like you the same way that you like me.

unlock.line: How, how does it look? Do I look a bit strange... no, of course I like it. I'd say every girl dreams about this day, just that...

battle.line: Relax. I have fast hands!

detail.line: Hmm? Commander, you always look at me. Is there something you want to say to me?

drop_descrip.line: Yorktown-class aircraft carrier ー Hornet, Hull Number CV-8!

expedition.line: Commander, I'm a little sleepy~ Eh, comissions? Ah, that's right! Ehehe, let's go welcome them back, shall we?

feeling1.line: Northampton, where are you~? (Hornet doesn't seem to notice you)

feeling2.line: Eat well, sleep well, play well! Those are my goals~

feeling3.line: I'm a twintailed blonde but not a tsundere? Well sorry about that! That's because I, Hornet, am not a stereotypocal woman!

feeling4.line: Hey, Commander, are you really not treating me differently because of my sisters? Is that so...? No, I mean, I believe you!

feeling5.line: You see, I'm not as bothersome as my older sisters. The Hornet you see before you will say that she likes something if she likes it. That's why I'll say this directly: I like you, Commander! How about you?

home.line: Commander, you were awesome back there~!

hp_warning.line: I can't fall here!

login.line: Nice weather, Commander. Wanna go somewhere?

lose.line: Will I meet a new me?

mail.line: Secret technique - Doolittle Style Mail Delivery!

main1.line: Commander, if you space out again I'm gonna hit you with a wooden stick~!

main2.line: Wanna hear about my older sisters? Hmmhmm, now which of them are you smitten by?

main3.line: Northampton? Well, she's a bit rigid, but she's not a bad girl~

mission.line: Nice weather~ It's a fine day for missions, Commander!

mission_complete.line: Hahaha, the mission rewards are here!

profile.line: I am the Yorktown class' youngest, Hornet! Hmm? Yep, Northampton is my friend! But I don't get what she's thinking. I'm not like my sisters, but I'm strong as well!

propose.line: Is this your answer, Commander? ... Hehe, umm, well... I'm gonna go outside and run a couple of laps first!

skill.line: Let's finish this in a jiffy!

touch.line: I am confident in my own self!

touch2.line: Even I can get embarassed...

unlock.line: Yo! I'm Hornet! Ah.... I don't want to impose, but don't call me Big Wasp and we'll be fine~ My sisters are both legendary, but just wait and see what I can do!

upgrade.line: Yeah! Now I'm feeling really great!

win_mvp.line: Ahahaha! That felt good!

battle.line: Check me out!

detail.line: It's a party, you gotta eat a lot! What if you eat too much? "No problem, just work out and sweat it off later!" How's my Enty impression?

drop_descrip.line: Congratulations! You did it, Commander! Now let's pop the champagne and celebrate! It's party time!

login.line: Heyyy♪ Commander, I'm looking pretty hot tonight, huh?

main1.line: This one's Enty's, this one's Yorktown's, this one's Northampton's, this one's... oh, it's yours, Commander! Exactly one bottle. Pretty nice, huh?

main2.line: So I have to dress up like this for the party? Aren't you worried I'm gonna be a fish out of water in there?

main3.line: I'm not expecting anyone to call me the belle of the ball tonight. Not while everyone else is dressed up all pretty-like. What? You think I give up too easily?

touch.line: Is this dress gonna make you fall in love with me all over again? Ahahaha!

touch2.line: Turns out I'm pretty different from my sisters, huh...?

unlock.line: Congratulations! You did it, Commander! Now let's pop the champagne and celebrate! It's party time!

battle.line: You're gonna regret looking down on Hornet big time!

detail.line: Cheese sure is good stuff~ By the way, Commander, do you like Sardegna-style pizza or Eagle Union-style pizza better? ...Me? It's all good to me, hahaha!

drop_descrip.line: Mmmmm... Nothing beats pizza straight outta the oven! Here, Commander, wanna give it a try? We're gonna have to recommend this to Enty next time!

expedition.line: I also ordered some for the girls who'll be coming back from their commission. I'll swing by the dorms later, so you help out as well, Commander!

home.line: Here, have some cola! I helped myself to a few bottles from Georgia's stash~ She's got plenty, she won't even notice they're gone!

login.line: If you can't decide what to order, get a bit of everything! Just kiddin'~♪

main1.line: Want something to drink? Cola? Or maybe some oolong tea? What'll it be?

main2.line: Hey, Hammann, don't just waste food like that! I, I'll help you out! ...Commander, I'm gonna need another stomach over here!

main3.line: That Zuikaku, only ordering boneless wings... Eh? Bring the green chili sauce? ...Ah! Not a bad idea...!

touch.line: Hey, say "ahh"~ Just kidding, ahaha~♪

touch2.line: W-wait... Whah?!

unlock.line: Mmmmm... Nothing beats pizza straight outta the oven! Here, Commander, wanna give it a try? We're gonna have to recommend this to Enty next time!

detail.line: You've been ogling me all day~ Have ya fallen in love with me all over again? Look, I'm gonna make this simple for you. You got two choices, Yes or Yes?

drop_descrip.line: Let's keep it up, everyone! One more point, and we can make a comeback!!! ...Hah... *gulp gulp*... Whew~! Thanks a billion for the drink, Commander! And thanks for watching over us as well!

expedition.line: I'll go greet the commission team before heading over to the next match to cheer. Leave it to me!

home.line: Have a round of applause for your gracious return! You were really, really cool out there~♪

login.line: Shall I come cheer for you myself? Ahaha, don't worry, I know you can do just fine even without my support!

lose.line: Just watch, I won't stay down for long!

main1.line: Come on~! Let's go! White eagle Enty~☆ and Essex too! Do your best! Make sure you go get'em~!!!

main2.line: You don't have to force yourself to compete, you know? You're more like a coach than a player today... Well, that's not quite it. Maybe something more like the shipgirls' guardian?

main3.line: Hey you! Helpers aren't allowed to interfere in the game! ...Jeez, what in the world does Baltimore think she's doing... Commander, I'm going to call the ref over, so take over the cheerleading for me!

mission.line: Commander, it's thanks to you completing all those missions that we're allowed to hold these kinds of events! Keep at it!

mission_complete.line: The mission bonus has arrived~! Commander, great work!

unlock.line: Let's keep it up, everyone! One more point, and we can make a comeback!!! ...Hah... *gulp gulp*... Whew~! Thanks a billion for the drink, Commander! And thanks for watching over us as well!

win_mvp.line: I can't keep relying on Enty to get things done!

battle.line: Let me give you a taste of my Wasp battle style!

detail.line: Limbs... cams... stabilisers... hmm? Commander, do you require something? I'm quite busy with the inspection, so do as you like~

drop_descrip.line: Wasp class aircraft carrier- Wasp, hull number CV-7.

expedition.line: The commission fleet has returned, that’s good to hear. I also want to head out... Co-man-der~

feeling1.line: If you don’t want to get shot by me, then just stay away...

feeling2.line: I like natural but in actuality use a compound bow? Commander, you are stereotyping, this is called going with the times! And the use of a compound bow actually has a long history to it. You can listen to me tell you it all, in ancient times...

feeling3.line: Someone saw a ghost on the roof last night? Hahaha, that was probably me practicing outdoors~ It’s very comfortable at night, no one bothers you, and you’re surrounded by stars. Commander, you want to come try?

feeling4.line: Commander, let me teach you archery. At night, we can practice together. If you get tired, then we can stargaze. How does that sound?

feeling5.line: Archery, combat techniques, and… that sea of stars night, this is all I have. Commander, are you willing to accept me as who I am?

home.line: Commander, what do you think, the outdoors is more comfortable, right?

login.line: Commander, remember to knock before you open the door next time. Otherwise, I can’t guarantee that I won’t accidentally shoot you...

lose.line: Umm... it seems that today’s status is not very good...

mail.line: Commander, did you get the letter I just shot to you from outside?

main1.line: Commander, where are you looking at, I am above you. Hahaha, indoor climbing is quite interesting~

main2.line: It’s said that the archers of Sakura Empire is totally different from mine. So I really want to see it.

main3.line: Commander, if there’s nothing I can help with then I’ll go out and exercise?

mission.line: Commander, we have a new mission. You can give me an errand or a target. But please no paperwork~

mission_complete.line: Commander, come over here and take your rewards from the mission~ It’s too heavy for me to shoot it at you...

profile.line: I am Wasp class carrier, Wasp~! The first thing I did was go on missions in the Atlantic, and I also supported the Royal Navy. Later on, when in the thick of things in the Pacific theater, I was sent to support my Yorktown sisters. But in the end, I didn’t help quite as much. After all, I was most afraid of torpedoes...

propose.line: Is this your answer, Commander? … hehehe, I am so very happy! Then—— “I am willing to give everything to you, my dearest Commander”—— Wow, I’m so shy,  i-isn’t this awkward?

skill.line: Who said a wasp can only sting once?

touch.line: Zipper? Hehe, please don’t mind me. This is just more convenient for me to move around~

touch2.line: Commander, say the word, where do you NOT want to get shot at? I’ll try to avoid it~

unlock.line: Hmm? So you are the so-called Commander? Ok... if there is enough room in your fleet, then is it alright for me join you~

upgrade.line: Oh, my physical strength has grown stronger, it's time to customize my bow.

win_mvp.line: Hehe, I am very good, right?

battle.line: All carrier-based aircraft in position, anti-air defense preparations complete. All forces, full speed ahead!

detail.line: What would you like to know, Commander? I'll answer to the best of my abilities.

drop_descrip.line: Essex-class aircraft carrier – Essex, Hull Number CV-9.

expedition.line: The birth of the Essex-class would not have been possible without the hard work of the logistics teams. I have to show my gratitude to everyone.

feeling1.line: I wonder how Enterprise puts up with someone like you...

feeling2.line: I witnessed the end of the era of battleships with my own eyes. Will carriers share the same fate some day...?

feeling3.line: Jealousy? No, that's not the case. Enterprise is a true hero worthy of all the respect she gets. However, compared to her dazzling aura, I'm just...

feeling4.line: I won't lose to anyone, not even to Enterprise. But how do I get everyone to acknowledge this? Commander, if you were in my shoes, what would you do?

feeling5.line: I might never be able to become a hero like Enterprise... But when I'm with you, I feel like I can do so much more than just that...

home.line: The fleet has safely returned. Commander, I've prepared the battle report for you. Time is of the essence, so please review it right away.

login.line: There you are. I've already finished preparing everything. Commander, give us your orders!

lose.line: I won't let it end like this... I swear it!

mail.line: There's new mail for you. Here you go.

main1.line: Everyone knows that the Essex class is strong, but still, Enterprise is all they ever talk about... *sigh*...

main2.line: There are a lot of ships in my class. As the nameship, I have to do everything I can to be a good role model...

main3.line: Musashi and Yamato? They were... yes, formidable rivals worthy of respect. I hope I can meet them again one day.

mission.line: There are still unfinished missions? Mind letting me handle things this time...?

mission_complete.line: The mission rewards have arrived. Are you sure you don't need me to go get it?

profile.line: I am the nameship of the Essex-class carriers. Although I was built with great expectations, I was always overshadowed by Enterprise's success. If only I could have been deployed sooner...

propose.line: Once you've experienced the happiness of two people supporting each other, it becomes something you can't live without. Thank you, Commander. I no longer have to walk alone in my quest to prove my worth. I promise to always be at your side, wherever you go.

touch.line: Time to sortie?! Just leave it to me! Oh... you just wanted to chat...?

touch2.line: Wh-what is this?! I, I...

unlock.line: So this is where Enterprise is... A-ahem! I am Essex, one of the Union's state-of-the-art aircraft carriers. Commander, you can expect great things from me! I swear that I won't disappoint you!

upgrade.line: When will I be able to get jets...

win_mvp.line: Enterprise, did you see my feat?

detail.line: Even being able to see a small portion of these 2448 miles has been an eye-opening experience. Though I wasn't able to ride from sea to shining sea, what an unforgettable journey it's been!

drop_descrip.line: I'm not trying to go anywhere in particular; I just want to enjoy the scenery along the way. Commander, let's go experience the thrills of the road together.

home.line: Did you want to rest for a bit? That's fine, take your time.

login.line: Commander, have you put on your helmet yet? We're about to get going!

main1.line: Enterprise advised me to pursue some hobbies that aren't related to combat... This should count as one of those.

main2.line: Combat is something that must be done at full throttle. It'd be dangerous to do that while riding though...

main3.line: You followed us the entire way? What an incredible eagle!

touch.line: Phew... Hm? This bottle of water is for me? Thank you very much! I'll help myself then.

touch2.line: Commander, could you be... too tired to know what you're doing? I knew we should have stopped to rest...

unlock.line: I'm not trying to go anywhere in particular; I just want to enjoy the scenery along the way. Commander, let's go experience the thrills of the road together.

detail.line: By the way, Commander, there's nobody else around, right? *sigh*... Thank god... If Enterprise or Shangri-La saw me like this, I'd die of— ...Eh?! Shangri-La?! Wait, no, stop! Please, no photossssss!!

drop_descrip.line: Commander?! Ah, um, no, I'm not drunk! ...I, uh, just had a bit too much to drink... just a bit! Please don't tell the others though!

expedition.line: Wh-why is a commission fleet coming back now of all times? ...Commander, I'll— *hic*...! I don't think I should go like this after all...

feeling5.line: The princess and the prince snuggled up to one another and sailed into the sea of stars above the castle~ ...Did you hear that?! Ah, forget it... Just write it off as me being drunk... and let me cling to you already! Hehe, ehehehe...

home.line: Everyone was greeting me one after another at the party, and there I was basking in their attention, so... I started toasting everyone, and... Ugh! Why am I so childish...?!

login.line: Sorry, Commander, but could you give me a hand? ...Ugh, why is the hem of this dress so long...

main1.line: I even got Mr. Eagle here all decked out~ Looks pretty sharp and spiffy, right?

main2.line: Hey... Commander, um... Yeah, so... have you ever seen Enterprise get drunk before? Ah, no, I was just asking out of curiosity... I mean, it's almost impossible to picture that happening to her, right?

main3.line: Commander, don't worry about me. Don't you think you should head back to the venue before the others start to wonder where you went?

mission.line: We've got new work? Um, I really hope my head clears up soon... Ugh, everything's still spinning...

mission_complete.line: Did the mission rewards already get here? Th-thank god...

touch.line: One more cup... Just one more! Commander, here! Cheers! Thanks for everything you're always doing for us. This is... a token of gratitude from me... *hic*!

touch2.line: Commander! Jeez, what are you doing... Did you also have a bit too much to drink? What am I going to do...

unlock.line: Commander?! Ah, um, no, I'm not drunk! ...I, uh, just had a bit too much to drink... just a bit! Please don't tell the others though!

battle.line: Attack squadron, ready to scramble! Just like an eagle soaring through the sky!

detail.line: One, don't be blinded by the pursuit of perfection; two, seek harmony in the spacing between ink and paper... Hmm... Does this look right? No, there's something off still... Man, this is hard...

drop_descrip.line: The Dragon Empery's attire and tools of calligraphy... I see, just wearing this outfit makes me feel more scholarly and artistic! I shall put forth my best effort to prepare for the port's Spring Festival!

expedition.line: The longer the transport distance, the greater the logistical difficulty. I must extend my gratitude to everyone who works so hard to maintain our supply lines.

login.line: Happy Lunar New Year! I'll be waiting for your orders!

main1.line: This is a special technique to maneuver the flight deck... Fantastic! At this rate, I'll catch up to Enterprise in no time!

main2.line: What are those girls doing... Eh? Is that how big brushes normally are?!

main3.line: Intrepid, see that star right there? That's Mercury, but the Dragon Empery used to call it the "Chenxing." Heheh~

touch.line: Am I supposed to add another stroke here? I understand. Um... right... here?

touch2.line: Am I supposed to add another stroke here? ...Eek?! Commander?!

unlock.line: The Dragon Empery's attire and tools of calligraphy... I see, just wearing this outfit makes me feel more scholarly and artistic! I shall put forth my best effort to prepare for the port's Spring Festival!

win_mvp.line: How'd you like that! Commander, Enterprise, see that?

battle.line: Open up! Detective-Carrier Essex is on the case!

detail.line: "I am Detective-Carrier Essex, unraveller of mysteries, revealer of truths!" ...Alright, that's a good-enough catchphrase... Gotta look cool in front of Intrepid and all.

drop_descrip.line: My eagle has gone missing... Just as Enterprise said, there's something strange going on in this port–– Wait, I definitely smell a case in the making! Commander, let's get to the bottom of this together!

expedition.line: The commission team is back! Jamaica, sorry, but I'm going to borrow your bike for a sec! I need to greet– err, talk to the eyewitnesses!

home.line: Don't let your guard down when toasting in celebration. Remember your limits, and act accordingly...

login.line: I hope my eagle didn't get eaten... But now's not the time to worry about that. Gotta focus on the investigation first!

main1.line: This piece of evidence is... the drink Enterprise left behind? And there's... a lemon here too? Oh, uhh, forget I said anything!

main2.line: This piece of evidence is... the witness's photograph, but I have to glue it back together – speaking of which, where'd the glue go?

main3.line: This piece of evidence is... The Manjuus that interrogated Cheshire seemed to mention something about an organization called the "Republic of Essex"... How strange, I'll have to look into this the next time I catch her.

main4.line: This piece of evidence is... Wait, isn't this Bunker Hill?! Why were you so fired up to get a shot like THIS?

main5.line: Let's go over the evidence we have... What?! You already managed to get conclusive proof? I knew I could count on you, Commander!

mission.line: It's a great day for an investigation, Commander!

mission_complete.line: I just picked up the mission rewards. What the heck is up with this Matryoshka doll...? Pfft, ahaha, what a weird face~♪

touch.line: Let's let Shangri-La analyze the photographs. We're more cut out for field work!

touch2.line: Y-you're trying to pass down the WHAT...?

unlock.line: My eagle has gone missing... Just as Enterprise said, there's something strange going on in this port–– Wait, I definitely smell a case in the making! Commander, let's get to the bottom of this together!

win_mvp.line: "Don't assume someone's literally irrelevant just because of how they really look" ...So that's what it means!

battle.line: Eagle Union's own Tempesta... Ack, that's not what I meant!

detail.line: Uuurgh, my head hurts... I feel like I did something crazy yesterday... Do you have any idea, Commander?

drop_descrip.line: "Anchors aweigh! Arr, pirate aircraft carrier Essex be ready for battle! Nothing in the seven seas will escape my grasp!" Hic... Hehehe... I wanna be a piraaate...

expedition.line: Shangri-La, please, put that down! Huh? You're just using it to let me know the commission team is back...?

feeling5.line: You've got it rough, Commander... If I was gonna be stuck doing this every day, I'd run away and become a pirate... I'm kidding! If it means reducing your burden, I can handle it! Heheh.

home.line: Commander! Welcome baaack~

login.line: Commandeeer? Pssh, no, I'm not drunk! I just had two, MAYBE three beers during my break~

lose.line: Just imagining all the paperwork that's going to come from this defeat... Uuurgh!

mail.line: The new mail? Where did I leave it, again...?

main1.line: Mmm, the acidity of lemon works just right. I feel great! Now, let me get Enterprise to... Ah. You heard nothing!

main2.line: Endless office work... So this is your everyday struggle, Commander. I underestimated you...!

main3.line: Did you see that?! I, aircraft carrier Essex, have obtained the greatest treasure of all! I've overcome my elders—Shangri-La?! Hold it, hold it, hold it! I'll apologize! I'm sorry, I'm sorry!

mission.line: New missions... That means there's more office work to go with them... Ack!

mission_complete.line: Mission rewards... Now this is what I need to motivate myself to work!

touch.line: Commander, wanna ride my ship? Huh? That'd make you the captain, wouldn't it? Then I'd be...?

touch2.line: Hey, Commander?!

unlock.line: "Anchors aweigh! Arr, pirate aircraft carrier Essex be ready for battle! Nothing in the seven seas will escape my grasp!" Hic... Hehehe... I wanna be a piraaate...

win_mvp.line: I'm better at fighting than I am at office work!

battle.line: Essex, taking off!

detail.line: It's so hot... Just like the heated support from everyone. However, I must remain sharp at all times during a race. Heehee, then again, I've fought many battles before, so this is nothing I can't handle.

drop_descrip.line: Cooldown lap completed! Did you see me on the racetrack, Commander? Heehee. Thanks for everything, from setting up the race to assigning racers and supporters!

expedition.line: I'm sweaty all of a sudden... Oh, the commission team is back? Okay! Let's give them a warm welcome after the race is over!

home.line: Excellent work! Shall we go to the pit after a quick break? Everyone from the R&D department is there.

login.line: Everyone performed great on the track today. Maybe it was because you were watching, Commander? Ahahahah.

mail.line: Ty brought us this new letter. Are you going to read it?

main1.line: Enterprise is rooting for me?! From where? It's really motivating, but at the same time, I feel a ton of pressure on me now...

main2.line: I won't go easy on someone just because they're a friend! I'm going for the gold in my next race!

main3.line: You don't want me drinking too much during the victory party? Of course I won't! ...(Weird. Why am I the only one being told that?)

mission.line: New missions! Is there any way I can help with them? I've got time while my bike is being worked on!

mission_complete.line: Mission rewards have arrived! Maybe there are some replacement parts in there?

touch.line: Can't this get a little lower? Damn... Hm? Commander?! Oh, I was just... I didn't mean it the way you think!

touch2.line: Wh-whoa! Uhh...

unlock.line: Cooldown lap completed! Did you see me on the racetrack, Commander? Heehee. Thanks for everything, from setting up the race to assigning racers and supporters!

win_mvp.line: I managed to keep the lead by some miracle... Next!

battle.line: For freedom and victory!

detail.line: Though diplomacy may be a show of etiquette before the war, it also is the only way to put an end to war. I'm sure that means you'll have your work cut out for you though...

drop_descrip.line: Essex-class aircraft carrier – Yorktown II, Hull Number CV-10.

expedition.line: The commission team has returned safe and sound. It's not good to keep them waiting, okay?

feeling1.line: This must be a trial... to see if I am able to stand on my own legs... That must be it, right?

feeling2.line: Commander, you showed me the light of dawn and offered me salvation. I've long stopped seeing our relationship as one between superior and subordinate... Instead, you're more like... Um, oh my, this is rather embarrassing...

feeling3.line: Um, ahem... Oh, no, I'm in perfectly fine physical shape. I'm just not sure how I should act around you now that I'm in this form... I'm really alright.

feeling4.line: It's not just you, but also Enterprise, Hornet, and Hammann. They're all looking after me as well. Commander, you're the one who has made my blissful life at this port possible, and the person I dedicate my entire life to.

feeling5.line: As the light of the dawn of happiness, what should I do for the Commander who reached out to take my hand? Heehee, we'll live happily ever after, right? I understand now – that is how we can share this joy with everyone.

headtouch.line: Maybe I should try getting you to pamper me like a little child~?

home.line: Let us raise a glass to our Commander's triumphant return. Don't worry, it's just one glass. I'm glad you're worrying for my sake, but... Hehe, don't you think you're taking after Enterprise?

hp_warning.line: I can't let something like this keep me down!

login.line: Good day, Commander. What's first on the agenda today? Don't worry, all of us have your back.

lose.line: The dawn that the Commander brought us... must not be lost here!

mail.line: This is... a delivery from Hornet? I see. That means it's your mail.

main1.line: Hammann? You look totally different... Oh, now that I think about it, I wonder if I've changed as well... Hmm...

main2.line: I appreciate your concern, I truly do. But, I also don't understand why you're paying so much attention to me alone. Your time is valuable, Commander, so please make sure to look after our friends as well.

main3.line: I see, so this is how you use this rigging... Thank you, Essex. We're all a part of the same class now, so there's no need for so much deference.

main4.line: Lexington, when's your next performance? I'll bring Enterprise and Hornet along to cheer for you~

main5.line: Just as how we are not here only to fight, Commander, you are not here only to work. If you're not making progress, take a break and come back refreshed later.

mission.line: My, what's wrong, little eagle? I see, the mission has been completed... I will let the Commander know.

mission_complete.line: Thank you, little eagle, I see that the mission rewards have arrived. Oh, I can't actually understand what it's saying, but I do get the gist of it~

profile.line: I am the resurrected Fighting Lady, Essex-class aircraft carrier, Yorktown. ...Heehee, I'm actually still the same Yorktown you've always known. To allow me to fight alongside my friends in this new form, you're just as amazing as ever, Commander. Hehehe.

propose.line: I swear upon the freedom and peace borne within the name of Yorktown, upon the life of happiness that I so desire, and upon my pure love... That the warmth of my lips now belongs to you–

skill.line: With this power, I'll open a path to the future!

touch.line: Enterprise, I hope you're doing alright...

touch2.line: The mark you've carved into me will always be here.

unlock.line: The second ship of the Essex class, "The Fighting Lady" Yorktown, has returned to your side. Even the darkest night must always give way to the resplendent dawn of happiness. Commander, let us step into the future together!

upgrade.line: Strengthening complete. I'm becoming more and more used to this power.

win_mvp.line: Oh– Sorry, I wasn't watching my step... Thank you, Commander. I'll consider your embrace just now as reward for my MVP.

battle.line: My outfit has no impact on my fighting ability!

detail.line: Everyone's gathered on the beach. When we finish the shoot, let's go and join them. The beach is more fun with everyone around.

drop_descrip.line: How does this look? ...Ah, it's nothing to worry about. Do you think I should adjust the string a bit...? Hmm... Eek!!! I'm so sorry, Commander... A-are you alright...?

home.line: Oh my, I lost track of the time while gazing at the scenery... You picked out a fantastic location for the set, Commander.

main1.line: If Hammann saw me like this, she'd probably get the wrong idea... Wh-what if Enterprise does too... Oh no, what should I do...?

main2.line: I usually don't see them in their swimsuits, but it seems that most of them are wearing some daring ones. I see, that's why Hornet... Hehehe, that has to be it.

main3.line: Sigh... Oh, don't worry about me. I was just at a loss, since this outfit is so different from what I usually wear. Not only that, but the one who chose it was Hornet... Umm, how about we continue...?

touch.line: The next pose... goes like this?

touch2.line: R-right... I should be more frank with my feelings as well...

unlock.line: How does this look? ...Ah, it's nothing to worry about. Do you think I should adjust the string a bit...? Hmm... Eek!!! I'm so sorry, Commander... A-are you alright...?

battle.line: Flight preparations complete! Attack squadrons, roll out!

detail.line: One should always go all out, no matter the enemy... Having that said, there are various practical reasons why that isn't always possible...

drop_descrip.line: Essex-class aircraft carrier – Intrepid, Hull Number CV-11.

expedition.line: Commission completed, resources received~! Hehe, way to go, Commander. You know exactly how important logistics are to our fleet operations!

feeling1.line: Commander, the way you're acting now makes you no different from a coward!

feeling2.line: The great symbol of fearlessness is none other than I – Intrepid! Don't you forget that!

feeling3.line: Oh, Commander! This– yeowwwch! Who decided it was a good idea to leave a trolley here?! Jeez, why does this always happen to me...Ah, um, nevermind, I'm fine! More importantly, when do I get to sortie?

feeling4.line: During my free time, I like to read, watch movies, or stargaze. Oh, by the way, I got a movie ticket from Casablanca. Why don't we go watch it?

feeling5.line: The stars in the night sky are distant. So distant that even with all the courage in the world, the effort it would take to reach them is unfathomable... However, all it takes to catch the commander in front of me is.... this! Hehe, isn't that right?

headtouch.line: Wooahh?! You're messing up my hair?!

home.line: Phew, I'm back! Oh, you need a battle report, repair and resupply overviews, and a mission debriefing? Sure, five minutes should be enough, right? After that, send me back out there!

hp_warning.line: Crap, I didn't think there'd be so many of them...

login.line: Am I slated to sortie today? If not, hurry up and fix that!

lose.line: I have to go to the docks again...? Damnit, why is it always me... Y-you didn't hear anything!

mail.line: There's new mail... do we have new orders?

main1.line: Commander, do you like stargazing? Ahaha, it's fine if you aren't really into astronomy. If you're ever interested, just let me know.

main2.line: Submarines are... quite strong. But I think I might be able to go toe-to-toe with them.

main3.line: Despite the fact that there are many Essex-class carriers, we all have our good spots, you say? ...Uhh, you're not talking about our ship performance? I've never given much thought to those bothersome things...

mission.line: Having trouble with your missions? If you're stumped, why don't you let me try my hand?

mission_complete.line: Mission accomplished! See, there's nothing you can't do if you put your mind to it!

profile.line: I'm the third ship of the Essex class, Intrepid! Although my poor luck during the war earned me quite a few unflattering nicknames... Heheh, that's all behind me now! Commander, under your command, I'll show you just how powerful I am!

propose.line: I didn't expect you to be the one to take the initiative... but I suppose that's fine too. Commander, guess I'll continue to be in your care then! As long as I am with you, I want you to push forward and face the future fearlessly!

touch.line: Want something to drink? Then, how about a martini – shaken, not stirred? Just kidding!

touch2.line: You... *sigh*...I'm way more inclined to beat you to a pulp than to praise you for your bravery.

unlock.line: "The Fighting I" of the Essex-class, Intrepid, is here! Commander, leave the combat missions to me! I'll bring home victory and glory!

upgrade.line: I feel like I can always keep improving! For example, how 'bout giving me a dozen jets?

win_mvp.line: The crown of victory goes to me, the one who knows no fear!

detail.line: Nice catch! You've got skill! How about becoming my catcher?

drop_descrip.line: There's been a lot of inter-port meets recently... But before I can join a team with my other Eagle Union colleagues, I've got to up my game first! So, Commander, mind training with me?

home.line: Phew, time for a break! Commander, thanks for coming out with me! Feel free to use the equipment however you'd like!

login.line: It's not enough to just be a pitcher. I've gotta be a good batter as well! Oh, Bluegill's also out there training. Let's grab her for our practice!

lose.line: Gah, I gave up a run...

main1.line: A ponytail really does get in the way, huh... Next time, maybe I'll try putting it up...

main2.line: Gah! I threw the ball full power and lost control of it... My bad, my bad!

main3.line: All righty! This one's headed towards the ends of the universe! Wait, how's the catcher gonna get it then...

touch.line: Woah! I just thought of a new kind of pitch! Commander, let's go try it out!

touch2.line: Even if you brought protection, getting hit by my fastball is gonna hurt like hell~

unlock.line: There's been a lot of inter-port meets recently... But before I can join a team with my other Eagle Union colleagues, I've got to up my game first! So, Commander, mind training with me?

win_mvp.line: Nobody can return one of my pitches!

battle.line: Battle station connection established, attack formation ready to go – All ships, let's slug this one out!

detail.line: Ahaha, have you fallen in love with the new and improved me all over again? No need to be ashamed about it; it was written all over your face~

drop_descrip.line: Essex-class aircraft carrier – Hornet II, Hull Number CV-12.

expedition.line: *yaaawn*... Shoot, can't be dozing off now... Uhh, our commission buddies are already back?

feeling1.line: Say, Commander, are you really that dumb, or just playing? I really can't tell sometimes...

feeling2.line: I've prepared some home cooking for my beloved Commander! Dig right in~♪ Look, it's totally different from what Enty and Yorktown make, right?

feeling3.line: Hmm? You prefer it better when I'm pouty versus when I'm lovey-dovey? Well, that's too bad. Because... it all depends on who I'm dealing with. Yup~

feeling4.line: Leaving Enty aside, I wouldn't mind if you went out with Yorktown. I'd be totally fine with Zuikaku, Ty, or Northampton too... Nope, don't mind at all. Me? Being surly? Why, I'd never.

feeling5.line: Well, there's no point being hung up on it, and it's not like I can control who you see. All that matters is that I'm your Hornet, and that's enough for me. Eeeyup! And I'll always love you, no matter what!

home.line: Whew~♪ Commander, you looked spiffy out there as always! Here's an ice-cold one for ya... Woah! Are you okay there?

hp_warning.line: This ain't over! I'm just getting ready to make my comeback!

login.line: The new and improved Hornet has arrived at the office! Hahaha, that's a good mornin' to ya, Commander!

lose.line: The new and improved Hornet... ain't gonna fall here!

mail.line: Perfect! It's the Magic Carpet Delivery System! ...Hmm, I don't know how to feel about that name...

main1.line: I'm not worried about catchin' up to Enty's shadow anymore – I'm now thinkin' about how to become stronger and faster than her! After all, I can't be playing second fiddle to her forever~

main2.line: Is that... Northampton? Hey, Northampton! ...Ahaha, stubborn as always~ Or is she just shy around you?

main3.line: Even if you're confident, you're still going to lose if you don't assess the situation carefully. The victor is decided before the battle even begins.

mission.line: The weather's great and I'm raring to go. It's a perfect day for tackling some missions!

mission_complete.line: Your mission rewards are in! Make sure none of 'em leaked out first though.

profile.line: It's me, the mighty, new-and-improved Hornet, now an Essex-class aircraft carrier! Well, to be honest, besides the history, the outfit, and the combat power, I'm still pretty much the same girl inside! ...Hey, just because I look a little different doesn't mean I'm not real grateful to you~

propose.line: Hoo... Haah... Alright, I'm ready! C'mon, Commander, are you ready to put a ring on it? Even if nothing is really gonna change, the ceremony is sometimes what matters!

touch.line: Need me to lend a hand?

touch2.line: E-even I'll get embarrassed if you touch me like that...

unlock.line: "The Grey Ghost" Hornet that everyone's talking about is me! Haha, maybe it's time for everyone to start calling me Ma'am! Anyway, let's keep getting things done, Commander!

upgrade.line: I've powered up~!

win_mvp.line: That win was a pretty good workout! How 'bout you, Commander? Work up a good sweat?

battle.line: Rigging energy supply connected, all systems go! Time to send 'em flying!

detail.line: Heheh~ Has my bewitching, swimsuit-clad figure stolen your heart? No need to be shy about it. That was my aim from the start, after all... Just kidding~♪

drop_descrip.line: The title of fastest in the port is miiiine, hahaha! Commandeer, did you see how badass I was just now? There's a whole lot more I'd like to show you, but it'll hafta wait 'til the next race... Well, I'll let you ride with me later, so look forward to it~♪

expedition.line: The girls are back from their commission~ I'll go on ahead to greet them~!

home.line: Whew... Worked up a good sweat... You want one as well, Commander? A nice can of Oxy-Cola after exercise... Nothing beats ice-cold pop after a workout~

login.line: Oh, Commander~! Ahahaha, sorry! Did I get you all wet? Well, just think of it as having had a big wave crash down on you~!

main1.line: Isn't Yorktown's swimsuit simply breathtaking? You know, I was the one who picked it out. If it knocked the wind right out of your lungs, it's all thanks to me, hehe!

main2.line: I've finally come to the beach to have some fun, so it's time to enjoy the day to the fullest!

main3.line: The beach is loads better than the pool. This wind, this feeling of freedom~! Whew~ It just feels so darn good~!

touch.line: Want a ride, Commander? I'll cheer you on~

touch2.line: C'mere, grab on tight from behind... Wha, wha?! Commander?!!

unlock.line: The title of fastest in the port is miiiine, hahaha! Commandeer, did you see how badass I was just now? There's a whole lot more I'd like to show you, but it'll hafta wait 'til the next race... Well, I'll let you ride with me later, so look forward to it~♪

win_mvp.line: Just means you were no match for Hornet, conquerer of waves!

battle.line: Stick to the plan!

detail.line: Sigh... The last exercise revealed a lot of problems... Commander?! Please, could you please knock before entering a lady's room?

drop_descrip.line: Essex-class aircraft carrier – Ticonderoga, Hull Number CV-14.

expedition.line: The commissions team is back. We should go and greet them right away.

feeling1.line: It seems I won't be able to save the Commander with my efforts alone...

feeling2.line: You're going to head out on patrol? Then... wrap your arm around mine, just like this~ Oh, do you dislike me, Commander? Or... are you worried about the other girls' reactions?

feeling3.line: There are many excellent allies here at the port. I... I'll have to work hard, won't I~♪

feeling4.line: For some reason, it seems there are some strange rumors about the two of us floating about... Just as planned? ...Commander!

feeling5.line: I'm not particularly noteworthy as a warship, and it might be a while until I can truly stand by your side as your equal... Even so, are you really fine with me? Can I really stay at your side?

home.line: Good work on the operation, Commander. Give me your arm... Good, there we go. Hehe, doesn't it feel nice? Let all the fatigue dissipate, just like that!

hp_warning.line: Hard to port! Watch out for fire!

login.line: Oh my, you don't look that great... How about I do something special for you? What, you ask? Hehe, why don't you try imagining what it might be?

lose.line: Where did we go wrong...

mail.line: There's some mail for you, Commander. You should check them as soon as possible. After all, it'd be a disaster if you overlooked something.

main1.line: What's on the moon, you wonder? A rabbit? Aliens? Hehe. Whatever it is, I'd like to see it for myself one day.

main2.line: If you're tired, you can snuggle up to me and rest for a bit. Oh, would you rather have a lap pillow instead? Well, if someone walks in on us, I'll leave the explanations to you~ Hehe.

main3.line: The files are organized, and the Commander's schedule is ready... Phew... I should be fine.

mission.line: You still haven't completed the new missions? Hmm... Well, it's fine for now. Just take care of them at your own pace.

mission_complete.line: Great job completing those missions! You're quite something, Commander!

profile.line: The sixth ship in the Essex-class, and the first in the class to have a long hull. I was once called "Hancock," but in the end, I was renamed to "Ticonderoga" in commemoration of the great war. That's about it.

propose.line: Huh?! Uh, umm... What am I supposed to say in response to your proposal...? Uhh... You're really giving this to me? Ahh, I'm sorry, I'm just so happy that my heart is about to explode and I don't know what to do and ahh...

skill.line: Let's show off the fruits of our labor!
