touch.line: You shouldn't slack off, Commander. Oh my, am I the distracting you from your work? Heheh, just kidding~♪

touch2.line: My, are you sure you want to be doing this? I think I saw Aoba or someone passing by with a camera earlier.

unlock.line: Hi there~ I'm Ticonderoga, the newest arrival at your port. Hmm, you look just as friendly as they said you'd be~ Thank goodness. So, how about a hug to start us off on the right foot? Hehe~

upgrade.line: I've gotten even stronger... Great!

win_mvp.line: Oh, we won. It's because you were by our side, Commander.

detail.line: No matter how many times I practice, when it comes time for the performance, I can't help but get nervous... Maybe I'm not really cut out for this...

drop_descrip.line: It's showtime! The stage is all set for the performance! Let's enjoy this perfect evening together, Commander~!

login.line: Are you down in the dumps? Well, how about I cheer you up with a little show? ...A magic trick, perhaps?

lose.line: I guess we didn't rehearse enough...

main1.line: Forget about work for the time being and keep your eyes on the excitement, Commander~♪

main2.line: And the lucky volunteer is... the Commander! Here, no need to feel embarrassed! Come up onstage and join in on the fun~♪

main3.line: Next up, the Essex's air show! Feast your eyes on the performance!

touch.line: Commander, did you want to come up on stage as well?

touch2.line: Oh? Commander, everyone's looking at us, you know?

unlock.line: It's showtime! The stage is all set for the performance! Let's enjoy this perfect evening together, Commander~!

win_mvp.line: I hope you'll all come back for more! ...Hehe, just kidding~♪

detail.line: The sun is strong on the beach, so sunglasses are a must... But y'know, Commander, you might be even more dazzling. Heheh, was that smooth, or what?

drop_descrip.line: Hi! Thoughts on my swimsuit, Commander? Does it suit your tastes? Heheh, thanks! If you had to leave a comment, what would you say? ...Where did you learn how to tease people so well?

expedition.line: The commission team is back. Let's go out to the beach to greet them with gifts!

feeling5.line: Eye candy or not, it's pretty easy to get shy surrounded by so many people in bathing suits... Makes you wanna go on a little faux-date, just the two of us... Geez, what am I saying? It could be a real date, right...?

home.line: Oh, Commander, you look tired. Wanna take a break here with me? The ice cream and fruits here are cold and tasty.

login.line: Commander, you're late. I was about to melt out here waiting for you. What's that? You didn't promise to meet me here? Then why are you here, exactly? Heheh♪

main1.line: I was thinking of riding some waves for a while later. Wanna come, Commander? I bet you'll have fun.

main2.line: Hm? You're interested in Saratoga's swimsuit? I see... Probably suits Bunker Hill or Essex more than me...

main3.line: Georgia, the lace on your rash guard is so pretty. Huh? Seattle picked it for you? That's a surprise...

touch.line: Essex and I don't really burn much. It's a shame we never get a good excuse to wear tanning oil.

touch2.line: What? You wanna put suntan lotion on me? Heheh, then how about we take things behind that tree over there...?

unlock.line: Hi! Thoughts on my swimsuit, Commander? Does it suit your tastes? Heheh, thanks! If you had to leave a comment, what would you say? ...Where did you learn how to tease people so well?

win_mvp.line: Phew... Cheers to victory! Right?

battle.line: Why did they choose to become our enemy...?!

detail.line: Commander, why are you staring at me...?

drop_descrip.line: Essex-class aircraft carrier – Bunker Hill, Hull Number CV-17.

expedition.line: Pardon, but I'll go greet the girls who are coming back from their commission. Just wait here until I report back.

feeling1.line: I'd rather not talk to you right now.

feeling2.line: There is no beauty in warfare. There is only ugliness in the suffering and loss of life we inflict upon each other.

feeling3.line: Don't think I'm upset just because I have little to say. If anything, I'm probably thinking about something, or about how to express myself.

feeling4.line: Something strange has been going on with my thoughts recently. Whenever I start thinking about things, your face pops up in my head and makes it hard for me to stay calm...

feeling5.line: We were born as weapons of warfare, and I thought that is all we would ever be. But having spent time with you, I'm beginning to think... that there's more to our lives than war.

home.line: You've returned? ...Very well. Why don't we prepare for the next sortie?

hp_warning.line: Why now of all times...?!

login.line: We're in a state of emergency. Be prepared to run the Holiday Express, even if it's a holiday.

lose.line: Their power... surpasses even the "Dragon's Jaws"...?

mail.line: The mail's here... Wonder if there's any new intel?

main1.line: Right now, another place out there is being engulfed by the flames of war...

main2.line: Eldridge's ability? I'm not exactly sure, but... I feel like I've seen it somewhere...

main3.line: All resistance is meaningless before the Essex-class's attack formation.

mission.line: Missions... should best be completed in a timely manner.

mission_complete.line: There are a ton of rewards? Of course.

profile.line: Essex-class, Bunker Hill. My name comes from a battlefield in the Revolutionary War. I've seen my fair share of battles... and know that war brings nothing but sorrow and pain. Let's not talk about it any more.

propose.line: Sorry... My mind has gone completely blank... I'm lost for words... Oh, that's right! "I pledge loyalty and love to you until the end of time." ...How does that sound?

touch.line: ...Don't think I'm upset just because I have little to say. Just let me know if you need anything.

touch2.line: By the looks of things, you won't learn your lesson without some harder-hitting "experience."

unlock.line: Bunker Hill, one of the Essex-class carriers, is joining the fleet under your command. Don't worry, you'll see the extent of my abilities soon enough.

upgrade.line: I grow stronger... yet again...

win_mvp.line: So this is the end that you all chose...

detail.line: Just completed another game. Might be time to go ask the ghost for more recommendations.

drop_descrip.line: Mission complete. Next up, a new recommendation from Long Island... Oh, Commander? Come make yourself comfortable.

expedition.line: The commission team's back? I'll see to them in a minute. I need to get to a save point first.

home.line: Dammit... I'd better wrap this up...

login.line: Relax, Commander. The Holiday Express is always ready to depart, no matter the time or occasion.

main1.line: Calm down, Intrepid! You'll break the controller!

main2.line: Ugh, so many achievements left... This game has too many damn things to do!

main3.line: Nothing complements a gaming session like a refreshing Oxy-cola. Georgia was right all along.

touch.line: You wanna play? The other controller's over there. You go first, and if you can't beat the boss, I'll help.

unlock.line: Mission complete. Next up, a new recommendation from Long Island... Oh, Commander? Come make yourself comfortable.

win_mvp.line: This is the end you yourselves chose...

battle.line: Stay focused and be on your guard!

detail.line: I'm prepared to battle at nighttime, if necessary.

drop_descrip.line: Independence-class light aircraft carrier – Independence, Hull Number CVL-22.

expedition.line: The goods from that commission have arrived. Saves us time having to carry it by hand.

feeling1.line: Allow me to be blunt: what the hell is wrong with you?

feeling2.line: You're curious how nighttime carrier battles look? Got it. I'll inform you next time there's one on the exercise schedule.

feeling3.line: A CVL might never rival an ordinary CV in terms of sheer power, but... I just want you to recognize what I'm capable of.

feeling4.line: Isn't there something you want to tell me? Be it combat-related, or anything else. Why do I ask? Because I want to know what sort of place I have in your heart.

feeling5.line: "There are some things you can't express through words"...? I don't follow. If you don't tell people how you feel, how would they know? For instance, how would you be able to guess that I love you if I didn't say it directly?

home.line: Should we draft a plan for the next operation?

hp_warning.line: How many... How many chances at victory do we have left?

login.line: Today's training and routine missions are progressing smoothly, Commander. You can rest easy.

lose.line: Retreating is a legitimate tactic...

mail.line: I've brought your mail. Give it a read.

main1.line: Should I call Cleveland... "Cleve"? Or do I keep it simple?

main2.line: I will take on that task you assigned me with the highest priority, Commander.

main3.line: I'm apparently terrible at reading between the lines... So please, Commander: whenever you have something to say, tell it to me straight.

mission.line: A new mission has come in. Let's get it done ASAP.

mission_complete.line: We've got to stay diligent even after all our missions are complete.

profile.line: I was initially to be the fifth Cleveland-class cruiser, but got remodeled into a light aircraft carrier due to the skyrocketing need for additional carriers. Thanks to the new capabilities this gave me, I flourished in battle and achieved victory together with my allies.

propose.line: It's thanks to our fateful encounter at the crossroads of life that I found the place where I belong... Was that... a weird way to put it? Umm, well, you know what I mean. I just can't find the right words... In any case, I'm happy to be together with you!

touch.line: Yes? Do you need something?

touch2.line: Go to the Admiralty and explain yourself. Right now.

unlock.line: I'm Independence, light carrier. Don't worry about that "light" part, and just hand those missions over to me.

upgrade.line: How about we set up a naval exercise right away?

win_mvp.line: Never underestimate a CVL's capabilities.

detail.line: Yeah, it should be fine to leave my pet in the dorm... I think?

drop_descrip.line: So this is my new school, huh? Hmm... gotta put my stuff down first before checking in with the teacher.

home.line: Now, what's our next subject?

login.line: Living in a dorm means I don't have to worry about being late for school.

main1.line: Join a club? Maybe I should... Hmm... Actually, I'm good.

main2.line: Both studies and missions require your full, undivided attention.

main3.line: Ugh... This collar is too tight... Why are you staring, Commander?

touch.line: Do you not get what this paragraph means? Let me have a look.

touch2.line: ...Go to the staff room and explain yourself.

unlock.line: So this is my new school, huh? Hmm... gotta put my stuff down first before checking in with the teacher.

win_mvp.line: I won by making use of the things I learned. That's all there's to it!

detail.line: Forcing you to help me make all these decisions is a little embarrassing... but thanks for bearing with me. You've been a great help.

drop_descrip.line: Hmm... Isn't this one a bit too garish? Mm... What if we pair it with a necklace or some sort of purse? ...Commander, your thoughts? C'mon, don't just stare at me, give me something to work with here...

home.line: Oh, Commander, did you pick something out for tonight's ball yet? If not, why don't we stop by one of the shops en route?

login.line: There are a lot of really stunning goods here, but the price tags on some of these are also very "stunning"... Wh-why don't we start by looking through the more cost-effective stuff first...

main1.line: I also chose a getup for my partner here... Hehe, doesn't it give off "gentlemanly" vibes?

main2.line: Ahaha, seems like this store also sells wigs. Commander, want to try some on?

main3.line: Makeup? Uh, I'm not well-versed in that stuff, so I guess I'll pick up a little bit of everything. I'll try asking around for help after we get back!

touch.line: You want me to try these shoes on? Um, s-sure. Just give me a moment.

unlock.line: Hmm... Isn't this one a bit too garish? Mm... What if we pair it with a necklace or some sort of purse? ...Commander, your thoughts? C'mon, don't just stare at me, give me something to work with here...

detail.line: Saratoga and Lexington do stretches on the regular, giving them great dexterity for aircraft carriers. They really live up to their rep as idols. Good examples of hard work paying off, too.

drop_descrip.line: Whew... A bit of stretching helps keep the body flexible. Hm? I'm in loungewear, what about it? I'd appreciate it if you wouldn't stare too much, though...

home.line: Feel like doing some stretches with me? I could use a hand with a couple of moves, like the forward bend for instance.

login.line: Your health suffers if you don't move your muscles enough. Keep an eye on your posture in the office so you don't develop a hunchback, Commander.

main1.line: Who's the most dexterous among the Cleveland class? If I had to guess... Columbia. She does ballet, you know.

main2.line: Even the most basic of stretches qualify as exercise. Though I'll admit, it's not very rigorous exercise.

main3.line: Long Island claims mastering yoga gives you the power to breathe fire and extend your arms. I don't buy that idea, though.

touch.line: Yeah, that's it. Push on my back and hold it like that.

touch2.line: I appreciate your help with the pushes, but now you're just pushing your luck.

unlock.line: Whew... A bit of stretching helps keep the body flexible. Hm? I'm in loungewear, what about it? I'd appreciate it if you wouldn't stare too much, though...

detail.line: Who put this crane game here? "Supplied by Akashi, nya"...? That's what it says on the back?

drop_descrip.line: Just need to feed it a coin, then operate the crane with the joystick... Oh! I got one! That was easier than I expected.

home.line: I got a prize on my first try, so I tried it a few more times... but the crane wouldn't move like I wanted it to, and loosened up as soon as it grabbed something. What a failure. I thought I'd try again, only to find out I was all out of coins.

login.line: Commander, do you want to take a shot at this manjuu crane game?

main1.line: By the way, have you seen my pet eagle? Do you think he flew off somewhere? ...Wait, he's not in the crane game, is he?!

main2.line: Apparently, if you bang on a machine hard enough, you might get lucky and get a prize for free. Though it's more likely to get you in trouble than anything else.

main3.line: I've heard there's a café run by the Sakura Empire nearby. Why don't we stop by there later for a drink?

touch.line: Here, have some coins. Good luck, Commander!

touch2.line: You ought to get some fresh air to cool that hot head of yours...

unlock.line: Just need to feed it a coin, then operate the crane with the joystick... Oh! I got one! That was easier than I expected.

detail.line: I am fully accustomed to my new weaponry. My next battles will be legendary in naval history. Okay, maybe not to that extent.

drop_descrip.line: Light carrier Independence reporting. Retrofitting complete. I'm ready to take on harder, more vital missions. Leave anything like that to me.

expedition.line: Commission goods have arrived. I'll help transport them, of course.

home.line: You conducted that battle masterfully, Commander. Let's take a moment to roost, then get to work on the post-battle report.

login.line: I'm in top condition and ready as always, Commander. Rest easy.

main1.line: I should probably hang out with my own sisters as much as I hang out with Cleveland...

main2.line: I've finished all the work you assigned me. Proofread it at your leisure.

main3.line: Even I, someone who's terrible at inferring people's feelings, can clearly see how passionately Princeton is about her goals.

touch.line: Are we sortieing? Or is there administrative work to do around the port? Either way, leave it to me.

touch2.line: What the–?!

unlock.line: Light carrier Independence reporting. Retrofitting complete. I'm ready to take on harder, more vital missions. Leave anything like that to me.

win_mvp.line: Nothing can stand between my wings and the skies!

battle.line: Go forth... No. Let's put the lessons we've learned into practice!

detail.line: Did you need something? Oh, it's fine. I wasn't doing anything special, just sorta letting my mind wander.

drop_descrip.line: Independence-class light aircraft carrier – Princeton (CVL-23.)

expedition.line: Heading out to greet the commission team? I'll go with you.

feeling1.line: Honestly, I'd rather have Saratoga be the one giving me directions.

feeling2.line: You wanted to have a chat over some tea? Pl-please, just a moment... Umm, I need to tidy up the room a bit, so I'd appreciate it if you could give me half an hour or so...

feeling3.line: Ahem! So you were asking about my hobbies? I like to read books and... study Saratoga's battle style. In terms of combat prowess, I sincerely believe that Saratoga is in a class of her own, and wouldn't lose even to Enterprise herself.

feeling4.line: Do you understand what I mean? Even though Saratoga's usually a perky, high-spirited kind of girl, she's always looking out for others, even in battle. I've personally been saved by her many times. There's also how... Commander? Oh no, you fell asleep...

feeling5.line: Commander, why do you have a picture of Saratoga? You picked it up from the floor?! Nooo! I can't believe I've screwed up so royally... You see, this is from my collection... Please keep this a secret from everyone else, I beg you!

home.line: You look pretty tired. Here's a towel.

hp_warning.line: I won't let history repeat itself!

login.line: You're finally here. Did you rest well?

lose.line: Still out of Saratoga's league...

mail.line: Your mail? I'll go get it, so just stay there and focus on your work.

main1.line: Sara? ...S-Saratoga is someone I admire very much. I wouldn't dare call her by her nickname.

main2.line: Montpelier is a close friend of mine. It's not because we were both members of the Cleveland class, but because we both have someone we really look up to in our lives.

main3.line: Feel free to give me as much work as you need. It's part of a secretary ship's duties, so don't fret it.

mission.line: We've been assigned new missions? Let's give them a look.

mission_complete.line: Mission rewards... My heart's dancing with glee.

profile.line: Second ship of the Independence class, Princeton, at your service. I was originally laid down as the seventh ship in the Cleveland class, Tallahassee. I fought a lot alongside Saratoga in the war, and though I was able to learn much from her, I wasn't able to make it through the Battle of Leyte Gulf... It'd be an honor to fight by her side once again.

propose.line: I'm so lackluster compared to Saratoga, so why would you...? Err, not that I'm turning you down! If anything, I'd be willing to go through thick and thin with you, as long as you're fine with someone like me... Yes, let's be together!

touch.line: What, do you think I'm too inexpressive? I was wondering if that's why it's like you're always trying to make me laugh.

touch2.line: Have you never tried a knuckle sandwich before? How about a taste of mine... Hyah!

unlock.line: I'm Princeton, Independence class. Tallahassee? I don't mind if you want to call me that.

upgrade.line: Not bad at all. Appreciate it, Commander.

win_mvp.line: Looking good. Let's press on.

detail.line: I got this collector's edition of "Saratoga: Beautiful Summer Days" from Gridley. Looking at Saratoga enjoying the summer with everyone else makes me wish I could join her...

drop_descrip.line: Commander, are you also here to swim? ...Ah, this here? I brought it with me to the ocean to get some practice in.

home.line: If you stay out while the sun's blazing... you're going to get heatstroke. Make sure not to let the sun cook you for too long.

login.line: Have you done your stretches yet? You don't want to get cramps because you rushed into the ocean unprepared.

main1.line: Hehehe. With this, I'll be able to improve my sense of balance and my physical strength at the same time. Would you like to give this a try as well?

main2.line: ...It really will be a problem if my hair gets all messy from this. Um, Commander... do you think you could tie it down for me?

main3.line: Independence and the others are calling for me? ...All right, I'll go.

touch.line: You want to get on? I-it's not that I don't want you to, but...

touch2.line: W-wait a second! If you move too suddenly, it'll capsize... Wah?!

unlock.line: Commander, are you also here to swim? ...Ah, this here? I brought it with me to the ocean to get some practice in.

detail.line: According to Saratoga, what I should be doing in this situation is... Wah?! Commander?!! I wasn't up to anything at all!

drop_descrip.line: You're finally here? ...Ah, well, I only just got here as well, so don't worry about it. Anyway, shall we get going?

home.line: Commander, where have you been all this... a premium Saratoga plushie?! W-Where in the world did you find this masterpiece!!!

login.line: I heard there's a famous candy store around these parts. W-Why don't we stop by there first?

main1.line: Commander, what's your favorite flavor of ice cream? ...Oh, umm, it's just for reference...

main2.line: Saratoga told me this outfit looks fine on me, but I wonder I really do look presentable in such cute clothing...

main3.line: A shooting game? Alright, I'll show you how much I've improved thanks to Saratoga's special training sessions! Oh... it's a bit embarrassing to get all pumped up by myself...

touch.line: You want... to hold hands? ...W-Well, that's not a bad idea... Even though this isn't a big deal, why is my heart pounding so furiously...

touch2.line: Y-You did that on purpose, didn't you?!

unlock.line: You're finally here? ...Ah, well, I only just got here as well, so don't worry about it. Anyway, shall we get going?

detail.line: Of course I've prepared a present for Saratoga, I do so every year. Saratoga didn't seem all too pleased though... What could be the issue?

drop_descrip.line: I'm done changing... Is this supposed to be a "reindeer" costume? It feels a bit too risqué... Oh, Commander, since you're already here, come get your Christmas present.

home.line: W-wait, Commander, watch out! I-I'm sorry, Commander... I wanted to try flying my presents over with my planes like Saratoga does... But you arrived just as I was about to test it out...

login.line: Merry Christmas, Commander. Let us enjoy a joyful Christmas together.

mail.line: Check the mailbox? I'll do that when I go send out the presents.

main1.line: I heard someone at the port accidentally tied herself up while making some ribbons. I have to learn from those mistakes.

main2.line: You want me to tell some Santa stories to the destroyer girls... I did promise Saratoga I would help her out, but I'm not much of a storyteller...

main3.line: Commander, I've finished wrapping up my presents. Would you help me carry them over to the Christmas tree?

touch.line: If you love my smile so much... I-I suppose I could smile a bit longer for you.

touch2.line: H-hold up! The ribbon's going to come loose–!

unlock.line: I'm done changing... Is this supposed to be a "reindeer" costume? It feels a bit too risqué... Oh, Commander, since you're already here, come get your Christmas present.

battle.line: Students who refuse to listen... need a proper lecturing.

detail.line: I can't help but notice that you're staring at me. Do you have a question for Ms. Langley?

drop_descrip.line: Independence-class light aircraft carrier – Langley II, Hull Number CVL-27.

expedition.line: The girls from the commission team are back. I hope they remember my pointers...

feeling1.line: Is it just me, or are you intentionally trying to upset me?

feeling2.line: How is your work going? Remember, spending time with the girls is just as important as your paperwork... Goodness. There are so many things I still have to teach you!

feeling3.line: Good, good! You're doing great work today. So, have you noticed that Ms. Langley's instruction has helped you progress in your studies?

feeling4.line: A date... with me? Ack, what am I saying?! Of course not. Students shouldn't try to grow up so fast! N-not that... I'm entirely against it...

feeling5.line: You may have earned Ms. Langley's favor, but don't think you can get away with just anything. Though... I will allow you to take it a little easier when we're alone.

home.line: Congratulations on your latest victory. Now, where do you think you're going? The lecture's only just begun!

hp_warning.line: Oh, you mischievous students...

login.line: Welcome back. Hard at work, I see. I, Langley, am here to support you to the fullest as always! Just make sure you're ready.

lose.line: Urk... Does this mean I've been teaching them all wrong?

mail.line: Leaving mail in your mailbox forever won't solve any of your problems!

main1.line: Tighten up, Commander! Learning the rules is important; they've come from a long history of lessons.

main2.line: Instead of praying when you're in trouble, you must prudently prepare for everything, Commander!

main3.line: Commander, you must perpetually be a good example for the sake of all shipgirls' growth—Wait a second. Are you daydreaming again?! Goodness...

mission.line: I've already sent you a new homework assignment, Commander. Make sure you get it done on time!

mission_complete.line: There you go! Good work. I expect that same effort next time, Commander.

profile.line: Say hello to the new and improved Eagle Union aircraft carrier, Langley! My fighting and instruction have been perfected. Just you wait and see, Commander. Heheh!

propose.line: I've taught you so much already, but Commander, there are still plenty of places where you need to apply yourself. In other words... Ms. Langley has much more teaching to do! Expect this class to go on... f-forever!

touch.line: Commander, is this your way of telling me that you want one-on-one lessons?

touch2.line: Ahem, hello? Have I reached the military police? Yes, it's happened again... I trust you know who I'm referring to.

unlock.line: Ahem! I am the new and improved Langley. How do I look? Perhaps more refined than before? Better prepared to receive more demanding orders, even? Hehe... I hope you're excited to see what I can do, Commander!

upgrade.line: Hmm... A welcome improvement.

win_mvp.line: Okay, I'll just add this victory to the next edition of my textbook...

battle.line: I, Ms. Langley, will not allow you to disturb my precious time off from work!

detail.line: Taking adequate breaks is important. This is a rare vacation, so why don't we talk about studies another time?

drop_descrip.line: Pheeew... Being able to kick back and relax on such a sunny day is just the best! Oh, Commander! If you'd like to come chill with me, I have watermelon and cold drinks!

home.line: Where have you been? ...What's so wrong with your teacher worrying about you, exactly?

login.line: The sunlight is so warm! Ahh... Commander, why don't we relax somewhere comfortable?

main1.line: Phew, that gentle breeze just makes me want to go swimming in the ocean. B-but I'm not a child, you got that? You really look like you want to tell me, your teacher, to be careful in the water.

main2.line: I chose this swimsuit myself. Even I like to change things up once in a while, you know? But mature and sexy just don't mesh with me...

main3.line: Commander, why don't we swim over there? You're always exhausted, which is exactly why you need to kick back once in a while.

touch.line: Mm? You don't have to fuss over me, you know. But I understand... Some students need a more watchful eye on them, don't they?

touch2.line: This teacher's about to get really, REALLY mad!

unlock.line: Pheeew... Being able to kick back and relax on such a sunny day is just the best! Oh, Commander! If you'd like to come chill with me, I have watermelon and cold drinks!

battle.line: Onward without fear! For I stand behind you with all my might!

detail.line: Commander, such perfect timing. I was just performing some maintenance on this little one. Would you mind lending a hand?

drop_descrip.line: Independence-class light aircraft carrier – Bataan, Hull Number CVL-29.

expedition.line: The ships you sent out on commission have returned. Shall we go greet them?

feeling1.line: No one respects a worthless commander. You need to shape up! Come, I'll help you.

feeling2.line: Perfect. Our work goes exactly according to plan... Yes, now on to next month's plan...

feeling3.line: How will I spend my day off? I suppose I'll just lounge around by myself. That's how I like to relax, after all. It's not like I have any particular hobbies or anything... Aha, ahaha...

feeling4.line: It seems we've been spending a lot more alone time together lately, Commander... It's okay if we get even more intimate... is it? Well, then... If I sit a little closer... even cuddle up a bit... is that... okay too?

feeling5.line: Whether I'm happy or sad, you're always here with me, Commander... I, why I might just be the luckiest girl in the world... Hehehe.

home.line: Welcome back, Commander. You certainly fought hard. If you have need of me, I would be happy to accompany you on the next sortie.

hp_warning.line: We mustn't... retreat yet!

login.line: At last, you've made your return, Commander. Now, let us begin the day's labors, shall we?

lose.line: Hm... I must carry this lesson on to the next battle...

mail.line: The mail is here. Take a look, please, Commander.

main1.line: To make a beautiful plan and then watch it come together – is there any better way to get one's work done? Commander, why not give my way a try?

main2.line: This little one is a Hellcat, endlessly useful in so many battles. Hehe.

main3.line: Maybe there's nothing really special about me, I'm not the type to stand out in a crowd, but I... as long as I can do things my way, and be helpful to everyone, that's good enough for me. Hehehe.

mission.line: If you don't complete your missions, you won't get any stronger. Come, Commander, just a little bit more effort and we'll clear those missions off the board.

mission_complete.line: Mission rewards. How delightful. Hehe.

profile.line: I am the Independence-class light aircraft carrier Bataan of the Eagle Union. I participated in numerous battles during the world war. I will resolutely provide all necessary aid and support to all the ships of this fleet, as is my duty.

propose.line: To be here with you, Commander, celebrating a day like this... I can't fathom how lucky I am. I can't even begin to know what to say... Commander, umm, do you think you could close your eyes for me for a second...?

skill.line: Now it's your turn, little planes. Be sa~fe!

touch.line: I have a lovely smile? Um, well... ehehe... I'm glad my smile cheers you up, Commander.

touch2.line: My, Commander, you can be such a child sometimes...

unlock.line: Bataan of the Eagle Union's Independence-class, at your service. If you don't mind, when forming a fleet for a sortie... please consider including me! I may not be flawless, but I should be able to handle a combat mission or two!

upgrade.line: Now I can be so much more useful to everyone. Thank you very much, Commander.

win_mvp.line: Am I... the MVP? Ahahaha... this victory belongs to all of us together.

detail.line: It's a little embarrassing, but I do always sleep with this little one here...

drop_descrip.line: Yaaaaawn... Huh!? Commander!? You scared me... I was just going to lie down and... Um, yes, with little Hellcat here... Goodnight...

feeling5.line: Whether I'm hard at work or resting comfortably, you're always here, Commander... And I wouldn't trade it for the world. Hehe. Commander, would you like to hold the little one?

home.line: Welcome back, Commander... Why don't you take a rest? I can lend you my pillow...

login.line: Good morning... Sorry, Commander, do you mind if I wash my face first...?

main1.line: Good sleep is very important to your work. Commander, do make sure you're getting enough rest.

main2.line: Sorry, Commander, I'm fading again... Zzz...

main3.line: A pajama party...? I want to go... I wonder if Independence would be interested...

touch.line: These are my favorite pajamas... They aren't too childish? ... They suit me? Ahahaha... Th-thanks...

unlock.line: Yaaaaawn... Huh!? Commander!? You scared me... I was just going to lie down and... Um, yes, with little Hellcat here... Goodnight...

battle.line: Turn bow to the wind! We shall teach them the importance of freedom!

detail.line: I strictly follow the principle of divulging nothing to outsiders, but giving full disclosure to my superior officers.

drop_descrip.line: Essex-class aircraft carrier – Shangri-La, Hull Number CV-38.

expedition.line: A commission has been completed. Shall go and we receive the returning team?

feeling1.line: You've been added to my confidential informee blacklist, Commander. Do keep that in mind.

feeling2.line: Starting today, I will take notes on everything related to you, Commander.

feeling3.line: Commander, no matter how pressed for time you may be, eating junk food will only impact your health negatively. Please, I urge you to have this more healthy sandwich I made.

feeling4.line: *sigh*, I've asked you time and time again to be more health-conscious... Please, have this cup of saffron tea. It's good for you.

feeling5.line: Did you know that the saffron flower symbolizes joy in floriography? To me, writing your biography, fighting by your side, and personally looking after you... That is the greatest joy of my life.

headtouch.line: My hair ornaments? They're a gift from Yat Sen; she said they go well with my name.

home.line: The fleet has returned to port. Let us hold a tactical debriefing once everyone has had some time to rest.

hp_warning.line: Put out the fire! Please, hurry!

login.line: Welcome back, Commander. I recorded all the noteworthy events that took place while you were gone. Would you care to read about them?

lose.line: This wasn't... supposed to happen!

mail.line: You've received new mail. If you're short on time, you could consider having me read it out for you.

main1.line: Are you curious about these butterflies? Bugwatching is one of my hobbies, actually. I brought these darlings with me from Panama.

main2.line: Anti-sub warfare? I'd love to try my hand at it, should the opportunity arise. Who knows, I may be surprisingly talented!

main3.line: Ensuring you stay in good health is part of my job, Commander. I sincerely urge you to be careful so as to not overwork yourself.

mission.line: We've received a mission from headquarters. I made note of it in our task list.

mission_complete.line: A mission has been completed. I wonder what our reward will be. Perhaps an unmanned recon aircraft?

profile.line: My name, Shangri-La, has its origins in a famous operation from the war. Being an Essex-class, I've been all over the world and got to record a myriad of things and events in my notebook. This, to me, is my source of pride.

propose.line: I'd love to write down my feelings without a moment's delay, but a more important task is at hand: holding you in a close embrace. I, Shangri-La, will forever be with you, following you to the mystical land at the end of your journey.

skill.line: Weather the storm and fight with all your might!

touch.line: Which story would you like to hear, Commander? The one about the undiscovered haven, or the wonderland beyond the horizon?

touch2.line: Did you just perform a health examination on me?

unlock.line: CV-38, Shangri-La, has arrived. I'd like to share the stories in this notebook with you someday... but first, let's concentrate on the task at hand.

upgrade.line: Thank you. I will repay your generosity with greater glory in battle.

win_mvp.line: Shangri-La will forever be out of reach to the likes of you.

detail.line: This shawl you gave me is really cozy. Hehe, let's huddle up like this... There, now we share the warmth.

drop_descrip.line: Commander, welcome to my "Utopia." Here, you can find my prized collection. Now, where should we start our detailed tour?

feeling5.line: *yawn*... Oh, was I dozing off just now? Sorry for that, Commander. I just feel so relaxed when I'm with you... But thanks for lending me your shoulder to rest on. Hehehe~

home.line: Did you come across a new specimen I could add to my collection, Commander? Hehehe~

login.line: Welcome back, Commander. Let's warm you up with a nice, hot drink. Would you like coffee or hot cocoa?

main1.line: If the opportunity presents itself, I might just host my own exhibit. Perhaps I could call it... "Caracal"?

main2.line: I wouldn't mind sharing some of my prized specimens with you, Commander. You'd take good care of them, wouldn't you?

main3.line: *click*! Nice, a fine new addition to my photo collection. I name it... "Fleet Commander, in Profile." Hehehe~

touch.line: Would you like to learn how to pin a specimen, Commander?

touch2.line: Both specimens and girls alike must be treated delicately. Understood, Commander?

unlock.line: Commander, welcome to my "Utopia." Here, you can find my prized collection. Now, where should we start our detailed tour?

detail.line: One needs knowledge to write a story. Knowledge on ships, on people, and on the world as a whole. Say, Commander, has anyone ever told you, "Read a book or two"? Hehehe~

drop_descrip.line: This specimen looks to be fairly ancient... You could watch from behind me, or you could join me for an up-close examination; we can enjoy our time here however you wish.

home.line: What are your thoughts on this specimen, Commander? Hehe, would you say it befits your glory?

main1.line: It seems I can only make notes and sketches as there's no photography allowed here... I'm a little annoyed by that.

main2.line: Wait, Intrepid! Don't run around recklessly! Good grief... Could you please go help her out, Commander?

main3.line: Though not as old as these fossils, there have been relics found that indicate saffron was being cultivated during the Bronze Age. Incidentally, would you care for some tea if you're thirsty, Commander?

touch.line: Ah, I believe a theory recently surfaced, claiming that dinosaurs were feathery, not scaly. But what do you think, Commander?

touch2.line: Should I respond like a dinosaur and go, "Graaawr!" for you? Hehehe~

unlock.line: This specimen looks to be fairly ancient... You could watch from behind me, or you could join me for an up-close examination; we can enjoy our time here however you wish.

battle.line: Enterprise, engaging! ...Woah! My hat...!

detail.line: Vestal gets way too worked up when I get even the tiniest of scratches... It's really not that big of a deal...

drop_descrip.line: Yorktown-class aircraft carrier – Enterprise, Hull Number CV-6.

expedition.line: Commission complete! If we get enough supplies, the fight on the front lines will get that much easier!

feeling1.line: Perhaps... You're the one who requires more learning, Commander...?

feeling2.line: Commander, please help me train today as well! Remember what I said last time, no going easy on me!

feeling3.line: Why do I want to become the strongest shipgirl? So that I can protect my friends, defeat our enemies, and put an end to this war. That's why!

feeling4.line: Yorktown, Vestal, and Saratoga are all very nice to me... Wait, that's no good! What am I going to do if everyone tries to coddle me? Commander, you alone have to be strict with me!

feeling5.line: The hero in the story who protected everyone... ended up lonely and forgotten, right? But I have you, Commander, so everything will be okay! Someday... even if my mission has come to an end, will you still be there by my side? Will we still be able to play together?

headtouch.line: Okay, that's enough! If you pat my head any more, I'm not going to grow any taller!

home.line: Commander, how was my performance just now? Is there anything, anything I could do better?

hp_warning.line: This... is nothing I can't handle!

login.line: Commander, what will you teach me today?

lose.line: I lost... S-so frustrating...!

mail.line: Commander, I brought the mail!

main1.line: "Grey Ghost?" ...That's supposed to be me...? That sounds pretty awesome!

main2.line: Yorktown, Hornet, and me... I just know we'll become great carriers for the Eagle Union!

main3.line: I'm working hard in all sorts of things outside of battle! ...B-but lemons are out of the question!

mission.line: A new mission? Yes, let's get ready... Huh? It's just for you?

mission_complete.line: Mission complete! It's an honor to be of help to you, Commander!

profile.line: No matter how strong the enemy is, no matter how bad things get, fight with everything you have, and seize victory - that's the motto I strive for! As long as I keep working to get stronger, I know I'll be able to do it!

propose.line: Does this mean... you're proud of my achievements? ...But, I still have so much to learn... Until I become a true hero, you have to stay by my side!

touch.line: D-did you have advice for me? Ah, please share it with me!

touch2.line: Huh...? I'm not sure I understand this order, Commander...

unlock.line: Hello, Commander. I am Enterprise, aircraft carrier from the Eagle Union. I want to learn as much as I can here to be a stronger warrior... Commander, will you help me?

upgrade.line: One step closer to becoming the strongest!

win_mvp.line: Yay, I got number one again!

battle.line: Torpedoes locked, loaded, and ready to go~!

detail.line: The gleam of the metal, the coolness to the touch, the distinctive splash, and of course, the explosion... Ahh, Commander, torpedoes are simply the best!

drop_descrip.line: Gato-class submarine - Dace (SS-247)

expedition.line: The commission fleet has returned! How nice, I'd love to go out and shoot some... Ah, no no, this is commissions that we're talking about! Commander? Heey~ Commander!

feeling1.line: You're banned from the Torpedo Lovers Club!

feeling2.line: Today's a good day to shoot a bunch of torpedoes!

feeling3.line: Maya really packs a punch... I suppose she just got careless that time. Well, it is the job of a submarine to catch people off guard.

feeling4.line: Commander, won't you come see my torpedo show next time? If you're not there, I can't get hyped at all... so, promise you'll be there!

feeling5.line: Hmm... if I had to choose between Commander and my torpedoes... Urgh, there are a lot of torpedoes out there but only one Commander, so I suppose I'll pick Commander! Mmhmm, that's right!

home.line: Good work out there, Commander! Here's a torpedo for you! Huh, what's it for? For hugging of course - it'll help you sleep comfortably when you're tired!

hp_warning.line: Um... did they find our hiding place...?

login.line: Ah, Commander, good timing! Mind helping me pick up those torpedoes next to your feet~?

lose.line: Let... Lemme shoot off a few more at least!

mail.line: Commander! Mail's here! Check if my torpedoes are here~!

main1.line: "Dace's Torpedo Circus." It's always been a dream of mine to make that happen one day!

main2.line: Commander, I'm going to give you a crash course on torpedoes! Trust me, you'll be fascinated!

main3.line: Commander, wanna have some torpedo chocolate or torpedo bread? Here, have some, I made 'em myself!

mission.line: Commander! Ah, um, do you have any missions that require some serious torpedo launching?

mission_complete.line: Mission rewards-attached torpedoes, laaaaunch~! Commander, I'm not sure you'll be able to catch this one~!

profile.line: The name's Dace! My three favorite things are torpedoes, torpedo launchers, and uh, more torpedoes! My class? Oh right, I'm a Gato-class... If I remember properly, one of my achievements included taking out that Maya fellow... wonder if she's around.

propose.line: This is for me? Really? Ehehe~ I'm so happy! Commander, it's a promise, okay? In return, I promise that if you order me to shoot a torpedo in one direction, I won't also shoot them in every other direction!

touch.line: Commander, have you ever seen a dozen torpedoes go off at once? Don't you think it'd make for an awesome light show?

touch2.line: Torpedo volley! Locked on to Commander~!

unlock.line: Hi~ are you my new commander? I'm Dace from the Eagle Union, reporting for duty. I believe in shooting torpedoes first, and asking questions later~

upgrade.line: Commander, did you remember to prioritize upgrading the torpedoes first?

win_mvp.line: Heheh~ how do ya like them torpedoes!

battle.line: Who's it gonna be next~? Teehee♪

detail.line: Hohoh, I must've caught your attention~ Let me guess... you like 'em young, don't you, Commander?

drop_descrip.line: Gato-class submarine – Albacore, Hull Number SS-218.

expedition.line: Commission complete! C'mon, let's go! We can't just sit here and keep 'em waiting forever!

feeling1.line: Jeeeeeeerk!

feeling2.line: You wonder what'd happen if you tick me off? I'd host something like a public exhibit of your greatest blunders!

feeling3.line: My shoulders are so stiff after a long day of swimming... Oh, I have an idea! If a certain someone gives me a massage, I might just forget that really embarrassing thing they did!

feeling4.line: It's mean to mess with you all the time, so today, you'll get a nice, relaxing massage! ... *Phew*... Hey, you feeling something inside your ears? It's your fault for blindly trusting me like that!

feeling5.line: H-hey, listen... If some day I don't come back from the battlefield, would you... Ahahaha! Like that's ever happening! C'mere! I'm gonna tickle you senseless!

home.line: Weeelcome back! ... Why's the paperwork been stacked into a pyramid? Gee, a strong wind must've done it~!

hp_warning.line: Huh? Have they spotted me or something?

login.line: The Commander's back? Sweet, today's gonna be jam-packed with mischie... Err, I mean, time for work!

lose.line: Time to get outta heeeere!

mail.line: You've got mail! Say "pretty please" and I'll give it to you~

main1.line: So, who are you into, Commander? Come on, tell me~ It'll be a secret between us... At least for a while!

main2.line: I'm SOOOOOO tireeeeed~! Lemme sit on your lap, Commander! ... Sweet! Thanks, friendo!

main3.line: This? This is how I've always looked. Do ya like it? Let me guess... you're having naughty thoughts, aren'tcha~?

mission.line: Give me a massage and I'll keep quiet about that time you slacked off~

mission_complete.line: Sweet mission rewards! So, when am I getting my share?

profile.line: My achievements? Let's see... Oh, right! I sank Taihou! She shouldn't have sunk so easily, though... Actually, why DID she sink?

propose.line: Just claiming my ring. If that's all then I'm gonna get going now... What? You're not gonna stop me? I-I'm telling ya, I really will walk outta here! ... Fiiiine, you win! I admit it, I just can't be without you anymore!

touch.line: Oh, my! Not even submarines are safe from the Commander's evil clutches!

touch2.line: I wonder what'd happen to you if I were to scream for help right now... Wanna find out? Heheheh~

unlock.line: Tadaaah! I'm Albacore, from the Eagle Union! Oh, did I jump out and scare you? Sorry 'bout that~! I'll be a member of the fleet from now on, so let's get along!

upgrade.line: Ooh! That's good!

win_mvp.line: Hah hah! Easy peasy!

detail.line: You wanna warn people about my firecrackers? Hehehe~ By all means, go ahead~ But how exactly are you gonna explain knowing that I had 'em hidden under my dress~? You get where I'm going with this, don'tcha? Hehehe~

drop_descrip.line: Oopsie! I totally just dropped something by mistake~! I'd better pick it up quick! Hmm? Saw something you shouldn't have, Commander? Hehehe~ That makes you my partner in crime now!

feeling5.line: L-listen, I'm really grateful that you hang out and let me mess around with you! I've got something important to say... Come here so I can whisper... C'mon, a little closer... *smooch*♡ Hah, got 'em! Expect much more teasing to come~

home.line: Time to spice up Cavalla's drink with a little... Darnit, you caught me in the act, Commander... All I wanted to do was give it a more mature but alcohol-free taste!

login.line: How about a... KAPOW! Gave you a real scare, didn't I? Teehee~ Turned out pretty good, if I say so myself~

main1.line: Commander, you seen Taihou anywhere? I've got an explosive surprise for her!

main2.line: Which do you like more: this dress, or my ordinary getup? Why do I even ask? Hehehe~ C'mon, don't be shy and answer the question~

main3.line: Over here, Commander! You agreed to be my accomplice right when you caught wind of my plan, so you've gotta follow me around the whole day~

touch.line: You're gonna dig up location info under the guise of dancing with someone? Hey, pretty good idea! Huh? You just wanna dance? With me?

touch2.line: I wonder how people would look at you if I set off a firecracker right now... Wanna find out? Heheheh~

unlock.line: Oopsie! I totally just dropped something by mistake~! I'd better pick it up quick! Hmm? Saw something you shouldn't have, Commander? Hehehe~ That makes you my partner in crime now!

detail.line: Maybe I'll get Archerfish to hop in a box too. We can handle the wait, but can you handle that many surprises~? Hehehe~

drop_descrip.line: Surpriiiise! I was in the box all along! ...Did I really freak you out that much? Heehee~ Here, have this voucher as an apology. Come see me later to use it~♪

expedition.line: The commission team is back? The next time you visit me, bring some friends along!

feeling5.line: By the way! I've got a secret discount menu. If you wanna know the code phrase for it, come closer so I can whisper it to you. Closeeer... Mwah!♡ That was all a lie! Thanks for being so easy to trick~

home.line: Meow nice to see you! Teehee~ Popping outta the box never fails to get a reaction from you~♪

login.line: C'meown in! What can I get mew? The meows and mews are part of the theme, mew see!

main1.line: Soooo~ Among all the kitties here, who's your favorite, Commander~?

main2.line: I don't prank people while I'm on duty~ That is, unless they're someone I like~♪

main3.line: The reason I'm just lounging around right meow is 'cause I've already taken everyone's orders~♪

mission.line: You like me so much you'll skip work just to see me? Heehee~ Golly, look how these missions are piling up~♪

touch.line: For every prank you fall for, you get a minute of one-on-one chat time with me! Pretty sweet deal, am I right?

touch2.line: I wonder what'd happen if you touched other girls like you touch me... Wanna find out? Heheheh~

unlock.line: Surpriiiise! I was in the box all along! ...Did I really freak you out that much? Heehee~ Here, have this voucher as an apology. Come see me later to use it~♪

battle.line: Give me strength, my friends!

detail.line: I'm no fish out of water that can't fight on the surface! It's no problem for me!

drop_descrip.line: Gato-class submarine – Cavalla, Hull Number SS-244.

expedition.line: The commission team has returned safely!

feeling1.line: I hate you!

feeling2.line: Fear of failure can be overcome by showing your courage!

feeling3.line: Sometimes, courage alone isn't enough... And that's when I need your strength, Commander! With your instructions, we can overcome anything!

feeling4.line: I've been feeling sick lately... I can't fight with the same flair as I used to when I think about you... That's it, it's gotta be your fault, Commander! ... Actually, I'm not so sure...

feeling5.line: I had a dream where you carried me and walked around the port... It was really weird! But for some strange reason, it makes me feel happy... I wonder why...

home.line: Commander, if you need the expertise of a submarine, just call on Cavalla!

hp_warning.line: I won't give up, no matter how bad it gets!

login.line: Morning! You're right on time today!

lose.line: Bah... This happened just cause the sea is so salty...

mail.line: A new message has arrived! Wonder if it's from one of my submarine friends!

main1.line: Could we make submarines stronger? By, for example... giving them stronger, better weapons or something?

main2.line: It's so boring to just sit here and twiddle my thumbs... Give me something to do, Commander!

main3.line: Whew! The breeze feels almost as good on land as it does at sea!

mission.line: Do we get a boatload of rewards if we do these missions?

mission_complete.line: Ooh! A boatload of rewards! Let's treat ourselves, Commander!

profile.line: I was given a golden opportunity during my maiden voyage and sank a carrier! ... It was a pretty risky move, and it wasn't easy! But in the end, I came out on top! If you wanna hear the whole story, just ask!

propose.line: Whuah! Hold on a sec! Why are you hugging me out of the blue?! What are you doing?! You call this "weight training"? A-are you kidding me?! Everyone's staring at us, so let go already!

skill.line: I've been waiting for this chance!

touch.line: Ahahaha~! Stop! Ahahah~! That tickles– ahahaha!

touch2.line: I-I'll have you arrested!

unlock.line: I'm Cavalla, the Eagle Union submarine! I'll make this fleet famous through glorious victories, so just you wait, Commander!

upgrade.line: I feel stronger! Heheh!

win_mvp.line: You can thank Cavalla for this victory! Hehehe~

detail.line: Some snacks for Albacore and a torpedo model kit for Dace... These convenience stores really have everything, don't they!

drop_descrip.line: You're late, Commander! ... What's all this? Heheh, it's loot I got from the stop n' rob's bargain bin! Here, have some bread!

expedition.line: A-are they the fabled Fantastic Forty Percent Off?! ... Oh, it's just the commission team.

home.line: Commander, hotdogs are 50% off today!

login.line: I've been waiting for you, Commander!

main1.line: IT'S A SUPER RARE! Holy mackerel! Commander, look! Hehehe~ See what I just got?!

main2.line: I snagged myself a limited-edition Sara plushie! Aren't you jealous~? ... Y-you already own one? D-did they scam me?!

main3.line: School life is a lot more fun than I expected! I might just be a natural scholar!

mission.line: A mission? Is that my homework?

touch.line: No, Commander! You can't have my precious discounted chips!

touch2.line: I bet you waited for me to leave school just to do that!

unlock.line: You're late, Commander! ... What's all this? Heheh, it's loot I got from the stop n' rob's bargain bin! Here, have some bread!

detail.line: Here, Commander! A bouquet for you! I heard from Shoukaku that you like these!

drop_descrip.line: Look at all the cute balloons and flowers, and the delicious food as well! Hehe! Parties are the best!

home.line: Hey Gridley, come take a pic of me and the Commander! Thanksies!

login.line: Oh! I've been waiting for you, Commander! I was seriously worried that you'd gotten yourself lost!

main1.line: I'll gather up tons of balloons then take off into the sky! Yeah, as if! Hehehe~

main2.line: Hrrmm, still not old enough to drink, huh... I'm not a kid anymore, so what's the big deal?!

main3.line: Teach me how to dance, Commander! I wanna do it with you like everyone else does!

touch.line: A toast to the party! Hehehe~ That's how you do it, right?

touch2.line: I'm gonna tell on you for that!

unlock.line: Look at all the cute balloons and flowers, and the delicious food as well! Hehe! Parties are the best!

battle.line: Bluegill, setting out!

detail.line: I wonder if there's a way to become friends with Yuubari, that girl cooped up in the science department...

drop_descrip.line: Gato-class submarine – Bluegill, Hull Number SS-242.

expedition.line: Commander, the rewards from that commission have arrived!

feeling1.line: It's okay! You just need to bask in the sunshine for a bit, and your troubles will surely all go away!

feeling2.line: Bluegills are, in fact, a type of sunfish! ...You knew that? Welp, and here I was hoping to tell you a surprising fact.

feeling3.line: There you are, Commander! Come here! ...What's wrong with me hugging you? Am I holding you too tight? That's not it? Then what is it?

feeling4.line: I figured out why my hugs bother you! It's because it feels embarrassing, right? Well, don't worry about that! I asked around, and nobody thinks less of you for it! ...W-was I wrong?

feeling5.line: So my hugs really put you in a pickle, huh, Commander... I'm sorry for that! I can't help it, I just feel super, *super* happy when I hug you! Hey, what if I wait with my hugs until you say you're ready? Okey-dokey! Just tell me whenever you want one!

home.line: Good job, Commander! Come here!

hp_warning.line: Oh dang, oh shoot!

login.line: Welcome back, Commander! Let's part these curtains, like... This! Hehe, now the sun's gleam reaches in here too!

lose.line: They nearly got us... But it won't go the same way next time!

mail.line: Is this mail for Bluegill? Oh, it's addressed to the Commander...

main1.line: Sunny days are always good swimming days!

main2.line: Hey, that's not a blank sheet, that's Bluegill's personal file on the back! Look! I wrote the whole thing myself!

main3.line: How long are you gonna have a staredown with your desk, Commander? C'mon, let's catch a break!

mission.line: Commander, if you're heading out for a patrol, why not take Bluegill with you? It might be good to have me!

mission_complete.line: Mission complete! Now it's time for a swim! ...Huh? Too early for a swim? But why?

profile.line: I'm Bluegill, Gato-class submarine. I saw action all over the sea and gave my enemies a real scare. Hehe, I'll shine on at this port, too!

propose.line: Can I hug you now, Commander?! Yay! Sharing a hug with you just feels like total bliss~ Hehehe~ Stay put, I wanna enjoy our embrace a little longer!

touch.line: You want a fight with me? You asked for it! Take *this*! Blue knockout punch!

touch2.line: Whoa, whoa! Commander! You've kinda crossed a line here!

unlock.line: I've finally found one! My own commander! ...Hehehe, from now on, you're Bluegill's commander!

upgrade.line: Wooo! Wow, I've really gotten nimbler!

win_mvp.line: I hereby name this victory "The Battle of Bluegill"!

detail.line: I've heard I can throw the ball faster if I have my feet raised, like a pitcher! ...It doesn't work like that?

drop_descrip.line: Look out for Bluegill's ultra-reliable defense, Intrepid! Hehehe, Commander, stay here and see the results of Bluegill's special training!

home.line: Bluegill catches, Bluegill throws! Oh no! Look out! Sorry, Commander, I didn't mean to throw it at you! Hehehe...

login.line: I wish baseball was as easy as diving... I'll still give it my best shot, though! Bluegill's a go-getter!

main1.line: With you and Coach Bogue helping me, I'm destined to become a pro player!

main2.line: I'll stun everyone with my skills when the next baseball league rolls around!

main3.line: Intrepid! Bluegill's by your back! Don't forget that!

touch.line: Is... this the proper throwing stance? I'll memorize it!

touch2.line: Stop playing dirty!

unlock.line: Look out for Bluegill's ultra-reliable defense, Intrepid! Hehehe, Commander, stay here and see the results of Bluegill's special training!

battle.line: Trap set! Let's goooo!

detail.line: My new gig must leave me with little time to play pranks? Haha, my friend, a true idol can perform AND play pranks, too! If you want an example, look no further than Sara!

drop_descrip.line: Lights! Camera! Albacore! Ahaha, don't worry about it, I'm just getting fired up over here! Oh, did you come up with a better idea? Tell me, tell me~

expedition.line: Teehee! I get this feeling like the commission team is about to enjoy a surprise concert!

feeling1.line: You're really ruining it for the other members, you know that?

feeling2.line: Being an idol's pretty good! I get to sing, dance, and smile for a massive audience! ...That sounds nothing like what I'd enjoy? Really, huh?

feeling3.line: Hey, is that for me, Commander? Aww, how nice of you~ In return, I'll keep quiet about how you were ogling us while we practiced~

feeling4.line: Oh, Commander! Morniiing! Did you see the note I left about a date? It's your job as the producer to see to our personal needs, y'know~ I'll write down whoever else wants one, so be sure to give it a look~

feeling5.line: I want to be your center-stage idol that dazzles the audience, Commander! Heh, just kidding! Our WHOLE unit has to reach stardom together, after all. Hehehe~

home.line: Your next line is, "Why is Albacore prompting me to speak?"

hp_warning.line: Oh shoot, I screwed up!

login.line: Morning there, P! Let's make the most of today!

lose.line: Welp... I've got one final ace up my sleeve!

mail.line: Uh, Tashkent, where's the Commander's mail? ...Oh, hi, Commander! No, just talking to myself!

main1.line: Surprise! How's my new stage prop look?

main2.line: Most of the stuff we're wearing was brilliantly handmade by Dido! Curious about that doll she's got, though. What's it represent?

main3.line: I wanna see Taihou's concern in person! We should totally set some time aside for that!

mission.line: We've got new job offerinos!

mission_complete.line: Job donesy-done! Whew, I'm pooped.

profile.line: Here comes Albacore, submarine-slash-idol! I'm unique, I'm in the groove, so make some noise as I perform for you! Vocals, dancing, you name it, I can do it!

propose.line: Say what? Idols aren't allowed to be in relationships? Yeah, well, I was a shipgirl before I became an idol, so it's all fine! This pretty little ring is mine now~ As are you, Commander~

touch.line: I wouldn't be here without your support!

touch2.line: I wonder what'd happen to you if I were to scream "I'm being molested!" right now... Wanna find out? Heheheh~

unlock.line: Lights! Camera! Albacore! Ahaha, don't worry about it, I'm just getting fired up over here! Oh, did you come up with a better idea? Tell me, tell me~

upgrade.line: My idol rank has gone up!

win_mvp.line: Encore! Encore until our next encounter!

battle.line: Heh-heh! Prepare to get served!

detail.line: A submarine's gotta take care of her skin if she goes diving a lot. Not much you can do about the tan, though!

drop_descrip.line: Balao-class submarine – Archerfish, Hull Number SS-311.

expedition.line: Commission goodies, coming in! If I bring them to you, will you gimme YOUR goodies? Ahaha~♪

feeling1.line: There are tons of reasons nobody thinks you're hot. Cough up some dough, and I'll give you a crash course on why~ Ahaha~

feeling2.line: Got plans to go anywhere today? I might tag along and keep you company.

feeling3.line: It feels soooo good to sneak between that sleeping fox's tails and floof them~ Though I'll admit, it's not cool to disturb someone's sleep like that. Ahaha~

feeling4.line: Here's some yummy soup for you, made with lots of love! Teehee~ Wanna taste test it? All righty, but what do you say we skip the spoon... and have you lick it from my finger instead~?

feeling5.line: Well, well, finally able to keep up with me, huh? But now's where the real fun begins! Grab my hand and let's go on a date!

headtouch.line: All I get is a headpat? I was expecting something more... Hehehe~

home.line: Welcome back home, daaaarlin'~ Ahah! Look at you blushing again! Hahahaha!

hp_warning.line: What a pain in the ass...

login.line: Wake up, Commander! It's time to get to work! If you slack off, that's gonna be a paddling~

lose.line: They beat me once, so what? I'll get 'em next time!

mail.line: New mail? Could I have a look at it? I'll have to get real, real close to do it~

main1.line: You've gotta focus when you're working, Commander! ...Let me guess, you can't focus with me around, right? Hahaha~

main2.line: Start paying attention to me, or I'll leave to take a trip around the world. Okay, I'm exaggerating. I'd just go gather data on the areas around the port.

main3.line: Y'know, Commander... A voyage is a lot more fun with a hot girl within arm's reach.

mission.line: Skilled and sexy commanders don't keep girls waiting... for mission results, that is~

mission_complete.line: Mission complete! Aren't you glad I have both brains and good looks~?

profile.line: I'm part of the Balao class, plus I hold the record for the biggest ship ever sunk by a submarine! I doubt anyone's ever gonna beat it.

propose.line: I knew this was coming when you called for me outta nowhere~ Don't be nervous now, just hold still and close your eyes. We're gonna do some hot stuff, you and I ♡

skill.line: Once you commit, there's no pulling out~ Ahaha~!

touch.line: Hm? What's up? Did something neat happen? Come on, tell me!

touch2.line: Nuh-uh, you have to earn it~ No more groping like this, got it? Hahaha~

unlock.line: Mm hmm~ So you're the Commander? Teehee. You're a total hottie, so wanna go out with me? Like right now? ...Heh, just kidding~ You should see how red your face is~ Ahaha, you're a funny one~!

upgrade.line: Don't you think I'm even hotter now? Hahaha~

win_mvp.line: This is just par for the course when you sortie me~

home.line: What's this drink... "Bluest Blue?" Ah. The name alone makes it obvious Bluegill came up with it. It's just carbonated water on the rocks.

login.line: Welcome to a paradise of relaxation and recreation! Where you can get skip a little work and nobody'll find out~

main1.line: What happens when you give a Meowfficer bunny ears? It gets promoted to a hare admiral! Hahaha~

main2.line: Shinano's not coming? That sucks. I already mixed a special cocktail for her and everything!

main3.line: You deserve a super special reward for all your hard work, Commander~ What kind of reward? Hahaha~ Well, what do you want?

touch.line: Hm? Got something on your mind? Just say it, I promise I won't poke fun of you for it~

touch2.line: Don't you start making excuses now! The drinks I served you were alcohol-free!

unlock.line: You're our lucky guest today, Commander~ You get a taste of my secret concoction... Excuse me, I meant to say "cocktail!" Relax, it won't do anything weird to you~ Probably. Ahaha~

detail.line: What, you think my tail sticks out too much? I can just hide it, like I usually do♪

drop_descrip.line: Would you look at that – we're sat next to each other in class. Looking forward to doing some "extracurricular activities" with you this term. Hehehe~

headtouch.line: Hm? Have I done anything to earn a headpat? Oh well, do it all you want~

home.line: So, did you get the soda I asked for? Nah, I'm just messing~ Wait, you actually bought it? Heheh, then don't mind if I do!

login.line: Morning, Commander! Finished with your homework? If not, I'll let you copy mine. Not for free though – you gotta give me something in return~

mail.line: There's mail for you in your desk drawer. Imagine if it's a love letter! Hahaha!

main1.line: I wonder what that sleepy fox is up to. Snoozing in the Napping Club's secret spot, maybe? I think I'll pay her a little visit.

main2.line: Being surrounded by cute girls day in and day out is no excuse for not paying attention in class. Your grades are gonna plummet if you don't focus~

main3.line: What to do after school's out... How 'bout we go around port holding hands? I bet the other girls would flip their lids if they saw that. Hehehe~

touch.line: Anything I can do for or to you? Us adjacent classmates gotta help each other, you know~

touch2.line: This, in the classroom of all places? I dig your boldness~

unlock.line: Would you look at that – we're sat next to each other in class. Looking forward to doing some "extracurricular activities" with you this term. Hehehe~

battle.line: I, I've found the enemy!

detail.line: Submarines were born in an attempt to imitate the nautilus. When you look at things that way, the ideas for a lot of inventions were derived from animals.

drop_descrip.line: Narwhal-class submarine-Nautilus, Hull number SS-168.

expedition.line: Hehe, I took a little sneak peek, and there's a lot of goodies.

feeling1.line: Commander, you're going to become even more of a loner at this rate...

feeling2.line: Ugh... I'm so sorry, Commander. I didn't do it on purpose... I was just trying to follow you for a little longer...

feeling3.line: Umm, I'm not a stalker. I'm not trying to make a hobby out of sneaking up on people either... It's just that, I like being with you, Commander... so I end up following you around... Ehehe.

feeling4.line: Commander, are you, um, going on a walk right now? You always go around this time to catch a breather. I know this from experience, hehe.

feeling5.line: Commander, you're taking a different route than normal today... Oh, um, you wanted to go somewhere a bit more private for the two of us? I, I see! O-of course I'd be glad to accompany you! Hehe~

headtouch.line: Nautilus is not a small animal...

home.line: Hauu! ...Commander, it's not your fault, so please don't apologize. I wasn't standing behind the door on purpose...

hp_warning.line: W-woah! Crash dive!

login.line: Good morning, Commander. I popped out of nowhere again? Actually, I've been behind you this whole time.

lose.line: What should I do if everyone mistakes me for an enemy...?

mail.line: Commander, did you get the new mail? Phew, thank goodness...

main1.line: I wish I could dive deeper and get to know the secrets of the sea...

main2.line: Commander, want to try writing a message-in-a-bottle? Someone across the ocean might read it one day.

main3.line: Commander? Oh, um, it's nothing. I was just wondering if you noticed me or not...

mission.line: Commander, you seem to have quite a few missions still. I'd like to be of use to you in some way...

mission_complete.line: We're all done with the mission... Huh? I was a great help to you?

profile.line: I'm Nautilus, Narwhal-class submarine – Ah, um, not that "Captain Nemo." During that war, my friends shot at me by mistake, and I managed to do something incredible without realizing it... Overall, I think ended up being quite useful to everyone...

propose.line: Ehehe, Commander, if you like me that much... O-of course I'd be glad to remain with you forever~♪

touch.line: Th-that tickles...

touch2.line: Y-you're acting awfully suspicious...

unlock.line: Nice to meet you, Commander. I'm Nautilus from the Eagle Union... Um, did I scare you? A-actually, I've been following you this whole time, so I thought you already noticed me...

upgrade.line: I hope... my torpedo doesn't end up being a dud again...

win_mvp.line: Huh? I'm the MVP? How'd that happen?

detail.line: Bunny suits are made to imitate bunnies. If you like bunny girls, that means you also like bunnies, right? Um, it doesn't work like that?

drop_descrip.line: Phew~ Standing for a long time really wears you out... Hwah?! Commander, when'd you get there? Um, if you'd like, would you like to come exercise with me?

home.line: Um, Commander, I'm not standing behind the door, so you don't have to be that careful.

login.line: Commander, I'm over here. (*whispers*) I, I was noticed, right...

main1.line: Commander, your coffee's already gone cold. Huh, I forgot to remind you earlier....?

main2.line: The Almanac of Marine Life was really interesting. I really want to see all those mysterious creatures in person.

main3.line: I'm really good at hide-and-seek. When I was playing with Dace, I managed to stay hidden 'til the very end! Teehee~

touch.line: Huh? My earrings are on crooked?

unlock.line: Phew~ Standing for a long time really wears you out... Hwah?! Commander, when'd you get there? Um, if you'd like, would you like to come exercise with me?

battle.line: Commander, this way!

detail.line: It's so quiet underwater... But there are such colorful fish and coral all over the place. Lively, but peaceful... Isn't the contrast wonderful?

drop_descrip.line: Commander~ Ehehe, can I introduce you to some of my new friends? Here's Miss Tropical Fish, and Mister Manta Ray... Oh, and Mister Dolphin too! Oh, umm, this friend here can be a bit mischievous at times, and often causes quite a bit of trouble...

expedition.line: I took a peek outside, and I saw our friends making gifts for the commission team~

home.line: I'm right here, Commander. Hehehe, even underwater, I know I'd never lose sight of you!

login.line: H-hey, Commander, what do you think of my big ribbon? See how it floats up in the water? Isn't it cute and soothing?

main1.line: I love diving, but it does get a little lonely when the fish don't notice me...

main2.line: Mister Dolphin, do you want to swim together? Did you come just to invite me? ...Hey, don't pull there~!

main3.line: I wonder why... Even when I'm swimming underwater, I always end up wandering to you, Commander...

main4.line: We're having a barbecue later after our swim? O-okay! Is it alright if I join in?

touch.line: Oh, Commander, no sneaking any peeks...

touch2.line: Geez! You're just as mischievous as Mister Dolphin...

unlock.line: Commander~ Ehehe, can I introduce you to some of my new friends? Here's Miss Tropical Fish, and Mister Manta Ray... Oh, and Mister Dolphin too! Oh, umm, this friend here can be a bit mischievous at times, and often causes quite a bit of trouble...

win_mvp.line: I'm the MVP...? Well, I did get to fight with the Commander... Okay, sure!

battle.line: I'm very happy to have become everyone's repair ship

detail.line: Commander, I'm leaving the resupply of medical drugs and equipment to you

drop_descrip.line: Repair ship ー Vestal, Hull Number AR-4!

expedition.line: The girls of the commission team have returned. I wonder if they got injured...

feeling1.line: Commander, as punishment for angering me, this injection will be painful

feeling2.line: That reminds me. Commander, have you been paying attention to your health? I'm in charge of it? I don't mind, but please take care of it yourself, alright?

feeling3.line: Yes, yes~ It seems you're too reliant on me recently~ Well, I'm happy that I'm so trusted, but Commander, you might become totally useless at this rate...

feeling4.line: Hmm...  As a guardian angel, I have to treat everyone equally, so I can't just take care of you, Commander. However, personally speaking, I cannot say I can't provide you some extra~ spe~cial~ ser~vice~

feeling5.line: This is what a personal doctor is like...! 24-7 full-time care, and taking care of your well being! --Eh? That's too much? Is that so...

home.line: Commander, please tell me if you are hurt

hp_warning.line: Oh no! I have to treat the injuries!

login.line: I, Vestal, am always ready to heal wounded people

lose.line: I will not abandon everyone. Let's all return together.

mail.line: Commander, there are new mails

main1.line: Commander, if you keep daydreaming, I'll leave you alone and go play with Enterprise!

main2.line: Commander, have you checked your fleet's condition before sending them out?

main3.line: Has Enterprise been eating properly? I'm really worried...

mission.line: Commander... um... I think we should check the missions one more time...

mission_complete.line: Your mission rewards are here~!

profile.line: I am the one in charge of maintenance, Vestal. I was tasked to look after Enterprise exclusively, so if there's anything up, please say the word. But if you underestimate me just because I'm a 'support', you'll have another thing coming, you know?

propose.line: Hahaha, now you'll never be able to reject my nursing, Commander~ What are you getting embarrassed for~ It's alright to leave everything to me, you know?

skill.line: Yeah yeah, it's time for repairs~

touch.line: Wh-why is my heart beating faster...

touch2.line: Ah, no...I-It's so embarassing...

unlock.line: Greetings, Commander. I am repair ship Vestal. I worked exclusively for Enterprise. I'm happy if everyone is healthy~

upgrade.line: It's so good that I can take better care of everyone now~

win_mvp.line: Don't worry. With me, the fighting damages can be repaired.

battle.line: The sea breeze is so refreshing, isn't it~

detail.line: Although summer is a vacation period for many, Doctor Vestal is in all year round♪

expedition.line: I think those girls are starting to develop tans from going on so many commissions.

feeling5.line: As your personal doctor, I will always be by your side, ready to– Hm? Doctors don't usually dress like this? Aha~ It's fine though, isn't it~? I want to go on a date with you, after all~

home.line: Commander, please don't forget to change clothes once we get back home. Otherwise, you may catch a cold from wearing wet clothes.

login.line: Commander, please be aware of the risk of heatstroke when at the beach.

main1.line: I'll stay here and watch over everyone, so you go on ahead into the ocean, Commander~ Now, now, don't be disappointed, you can enjoy yourself on my behalf~

main2.line: Commander, would you like me to apply some sunscreen to your skin? There's no need to be hesitant, I'm actually quite good at it~

main3.line: Enterprise, South Dakota, it's all right to have a showdown, but don't drag others into it~

mission.line: Commander, I'm thinking about giving you the "Hygiene in Summer" mission~

touch.line: You want to go in the ocean with me...? Hmm, I suppose I should accept your invitation and take a quick dip. But just a quick one, okay~?

unlock.line: Listen, everyone~! Playing by the beach is fun, but please keep safety in mind! If you begin to feel ill, come see me~!

detail.line: The tortilla... is engulfing me... So warm and comfy... Commander, don't eat Laffey...

expedition.line: Look at all the groceries coming in...

home.line: Laffey's shift will be over soon... Want to go take a nap together?

login.line: Zzzzzz... Oh, Commander. If you're going to order, I'd recommend the Teriyaki Twister.

mail.line: It's a delivery order... Laffey wants to order delivery too after heading back to the port.

main1.line: Are you ready to order? Okay. Laffey can remember your order just fine. Ayanami, make sure you remember the customers' orders too.

main2.line: What a great smell... But, Laffey is the store clerk, and can't eat the customer's food...

main3.line: So sleepy... But have to get up, before Zed chews me out...

touch.line: The bunny-ear cap is cute? Mhm. Laffey agrees.

touch2.line: Only a perv... would do these things at a store.

battle.line: Battle, start... Zzz...

Anyhow, I was one of the prototypes for the Worcester class, and as an improvement on the Atlanta class, AA is my A-game! Just leave anything with wings to me!
