expedition.line: Confirming the commission team has returned. I'll go collect the goods.

feeling1.line: Your commanding ability has been evaluated... Simply following your orders is detrimental.

feeling2.line: I've determined that establishing mutual trust between us is beneficial to my battlefield performance. So, without further ado, allow me to check your schedule... Hm? Is information-gathering not customary when getting to know someone?

feeling3.line: Your individual tastes and interests... That's a good perspective. I'll ask my acquaintances for basic info later... For now, open your mouth. I made borscht, and this will help me determine your tastes. Come on, say "ahh."

feeling4.line: Though calling it a "date" is a misnomer, a date does present a great opportunity to learn your habits and savoir-faire. Here is your schedule for today. Give it a quick read, then we'll get started.

feeling5.line: I trust you, Commander, and I want to become intimately familiar with you. However, I'm unable to fully determine your feelings towards me due to my own ineptness... Do you trust me the way I trust you? Do you, as others would say, love me?

headtouch.line: ...Hm? What are you doing?

hp_warning.line: The operation is going awry... What is this?!

login.line: Ah, Commander. Pardon me for starting work without you. Pay me no mind and begin with your own tasks.

Good day. I'm B class' Bulldog. ...I'm an adult so please do not judge me by my looks. I hope you aren't an adult who does that, Commander. 
I'll be in your care.

feeling5.line: Commander, I'm a straightforward person, and I'd like my partner to be as well. So be open-hearted and simply say what's on your mind. In return, I will be sincere with you as well.

home.line: Don't overexert yourself after returning from the battlefield. Relax.

login.line: Do you know how long you've kept me waiting, Commander? What's the meaning of this?

lose.line: Ugh... You will pay dearly for staining my dress! Know this!

mail.line: Your mail, Commander. Don't forget to read it.

main1.line: I hate it when others underestimate me because of my size!

main2.line: No one knows what's on a person's mind if they don't say it aloud. I do not like people who are roundabout.

main3.line: I wish you would compliment me for being honest, rather than for being "cute." Not that I mind compliments like that.

mission.line: Stop pretending like you haven't seen the new missions and get them done already.

mission_complete.line: Commander, our rewards have arrived. Well done, I say.

profile.line: I'm Jersey, of the J class. While I have neither noble blood nor a particularly outstanding combat record, my personality is what it is, so spare me your complaints. What happened in Malta was just a slipup. But, admittedly, mistakes are mistakes. That much I know.

propose.line: Now that I think about it, we've been so straightforward that we've not even done anything romantic... But now at least we know each other better than anyone else. I say we let romance into our lives starting today.

skill.line: Now's not the time to be taking it easy!

touch.line: What, you want to nuzzle against my lap? You can keep your fantasies in your dreams where they belong.

touch2.line: C-Commander?! I-I-I appreciate your straightforwardness, but now isn't the time...

unlock.line: Are you the Commander? My name is Jersey, and don't you forget it.

upgrade.line: I will not let your efforts go to waste.

win_mvp.line: This is the might of the J class! Regret your own carelessness!

battle.line: I-I'll try to stay where the Commander can protect me!

detail.line: Everyone has someone they want to protect... So don't protect just me, okay, Commander?

drop_descrip.line: M-class destroyer – Matchless (G52.)

expedition.line: I hope I can go on a safe transport mission together with you, Commander...

feeling1.line: I should've known... You can't possibly protect me...

feeling2.line: My name might make me seem invincible, but that's not true at all. Don't mistake me for a Main Fleet ship just because of my name!

feeling3.line: Duke of York is tough, cool, and... Hehe~ She must make you jealous, too~

feeling4.line: The feelings I have for you, and the feelings you have for me... Which of the two is more passionate?

feeling5.line: Physical scars heal over time, but mental scars never go away. So, please, don't make my heart ache!

home.line: I like it better when you're here, it makes me feel at ease...

login.line: You look sad, Commander... Let's try this... Hehe~ Feel better?

lose.line: S-someone, help meeee!

mail.line: I'll go and get your mail~!

main1.line: You know flattery won't get you anywhere with me, right?

main2.line: Oh dear, it's getting cold again... Commander, can you lend me your coat when we leave port?

main3.line: I hope I can just stay as your secretary forever... Hm? What? I didn't say anything!

mission.line: I-I'm scared... I want to stay with you...

mission_complete.line: You look so awesome from behind, Commander!

profile.line: I'm Matchless, a Royal Navy M-class destroyer! After my escort missions in the Arctic, I was in the Battle of the North Cape, and then I helped escort Queen Mary! My name makes me sound powerful, but in reality, I'm totally helpless!

propose.line: Aww... I'm so happy... Thank you... Commander, I may not be able to protect you, but I'll do everything I can to protect your smile and warm your heart! Please, Commander, be happy!

touch.line: Can I just stay with you forever, Commander?

touch2.line: Because of that... I'm subtracting a few points off your record~!

unlock.line: We meet at last, Commander! I am Matchless, an M-class Destroyer! Ah, although my name is "Matchless," I'm actually very weak. Ehe~ Commander, will you protect me?

upgrade.line: Maybe you got stronger too, Commander?

win_mvp.line: Time for a photo~! C'mon, let's take a picture!

detail.line: Commander, the super-luxurious ice cream crepes you bought are soooo good! Thanks! ...That's right, you should try some too. Come on, don't be shy, open up~

drop_descrip.line: Ah, Commander, over here! Hm, you're going to take care of all the plans for today's date? In that case, I look forward to seeing just how suave you can be! Hehe~

feeling5.line: Commander, stick out your arms~ Yeah, just like that! Huuug! Hehe~ ...Hm? It's hard to hold that posture? None of my business~ You should be able to endure it for my sake, right~?

home.line: Commander, today, you're going to be escorting me full-time. You'll lose points if you let your attention wander~

login.line: Oh you, Commander, you're going to lose points for keeping a girl waiting! Hehe, just kidding! I arrived a bit too early~

main1.line: If some questionable individuals suddenly showed up, you'd be there to protect me, right?

main2.line: Hmm... it feels like someone is always staring at me... is it just my imagination?

main3.line: Haven't decided on where to go yet? That's totally fine, I'm happy to just have you here.

touch.line: Commander, you're in charge of all the bags! Do your best for me, all right~?

touch2.line: Commander, I'm going to give you a big fat zero on today's performance.

unlock.line: Ah, Commander, over here! Hm, you're going to take care of all the plans for today's date? In that case, I look forward to seeing just how suave you can be! Hehe~

battle.line: How-dee-doooo! I'm gonna shoot yooou!

detail.line: Is it fun to hang out with me, Commander? ...Ah, sorry, never mind that.

drop_descrip.line: M-class destroyer – Musketeer (G86.)

expedition.line: Wooow! Look at those mission rewards! We could fill a bathtub with all this oil!

feeling1.line: Come on... Return to your former self, Commander...

feeling2.line: No matter what life throws at you, always be optimistic, happy, and positive! You just gotta be!

feeling3.line: I always have tons of fun hanging out with you!

feeling4.line: We should all forget our worries and live to have fun! Don't you think so too, Commander?

feeling5.line: So much has happened since we first met... But I haven't changed a bit!

home.line: Take a gander at my new marching act, Commander! Relax, I'm only using blanks this time!

login.line: Morning, Commander! Nice weather today! Click, click... bang! I'm not sure why, but I'm always brimming with energy!

lose.line: Time to make a sneaky exit~♫

mail.line: Heehee~! See? I told you something nice would happen today!

main1.line: Something nice is gonna happen today~ That's what I'm feeling!

main2.line: Why am I always smiling? Hehehe, because I've been having so much fun ever since I came here!

main3.line: The injuries I've sustained from combat? Hehehe, they don't hurt at all.

mission.line: Finish them all in one go!

mission_complete.line: Hehehe~ It's just human instinct to smile at the sight of money! Yeah, that's it! Smile, Commander~!

profile.line: I'm the Royal Navy M-class destroyer Musketeer! I was in the Battle of the North Cape! Commander, little Musketeer is gonna shoot straight through your dreary heart with a bang bang!

propose.line: Thank you, Commander! This is the best thing I've ever gotten! Hey, tell me: have I given you some good memories, too?

skill.line: Locked and loaded~! Ready to fire!

touch.line: Hehehe~! You've reloaded me with energy!

touch2.line: It's not like I *dislike* it, but... Yeah, I actually don't dislike it!

unlock.line: I am the M-class Destroyer, Musketeer! Hehe... I knew something good was going to happen today~ Commander, can you point me to where the port is? Here? Or over here?!

upgrade.line: Take aim~! Fire! Bang!

win_mvp.line: I'm gonna punch a hole straight through your heart~! Heheh, I've always wanted to say that!

battle.line: Chaaarge! Ehehe, don't I sound like a flagship?

detail.line: Wales, someone can be small and still have a lot of potential, you know! Ehehe, Echo doesn't know what that means, but maybe they're words of praise~?

drop_descrip.line: E-class destroyer – Echo.

expedition.line: The commission girls are back~♪ Echo will go check if they brought any yummy snacks with them~

feeling1.line: Commander, people have said you've become a deadbeat, but what is a deadbeat even...? Hmm, in any event, Echo will do everything possible to make you more productive~ Let's begin by having you greet me properly~

feeling2.line: Commander, please be positive. Be like Echo: smile, and be happy~ Ehehe♪

feeling3.line: Commander, you can't give up so easily. You must get into shape~ Come on, take a stroll around the port with Echo~♪

feeling4.line: Echo made cookies~ Have a bite, Commander! ... It's too sweet for you? Ehehe, Hood said they have the signature "Echo flavor"~♪

feeling5.line: Commander, can we go someplace far away... *Yawn*, I must've been sleeptalking... Hm? So you're okay with going somewhere with Echo? Hooray! Let's go somewhere, then!

home.line: Would you like to eat snacks with Echo~? ... You aren't hungry? In that case... you can just watch me while I eat.

hp_warning.line: I need to hold out just a little longer... Edinburgh will come save me, I'm sure of it!

login.line: Ah, Commander~♪ Ehehe, you're back! You know, Echo was reaaaally lonely~ Hurry up and come play with me~

lose.line: Ugh... don't bully meee...

mail.line: Mail has arrived~♪ Maybe there are yummy snacks enclosed within it~ Ehehe~

main1.line: I made a promise to Edinburgh: I must return to port now and then, no matter how far away I go~♪

main2.line: Be it with my E-class sisters or strangers, I can make friends with anyone I have fun with, so don't worry about me!

main3.line: Echo is by your side, Commander! And if you give Echo a high-five, you might feel more motivated!

mission.line: Commander, we should finish our missions! It's not good to be negligent~♪ Aha, don't you agree that Echo's suuuuuper duper reliable~?

mission_complete.line: Mission complete~♪ Echo will bring you the rewards, Commander!

profile.line: I'm Echo, an E-class destroyer of the Royal Navy. I was in the Battle of the Denmark Strait along with Hood and Wales, after which I brought Wales safely back to port~ Ehehe, it's a memory I cherish! Oh, also, Edinburgh is really precious to me!

propose.line: What are we here for? I don't quite get what this is for... Okay, if you give me candy, then I will stay with you to the end! Okie dokie, I'll open my mouth, so please feed me candy~♪

skill.line: Here I come! Witness Echo's might!

touch.line: Commander, carry me like a princess! Echo's quite lightweight! ... Ahahaha~ Commander, that tickles~♪

touch2.line: Wha...? Hood said I shouldn't let people touch me there...

unlock.line: Hello, Commander~! Echo, reporting in! So, after I finish checking in, can I have a reward? Ehehe~♪ I loooove candy, you see~

upgrade.line: Ehehe~♪ I don't know if I've gotten stronger, but I'm grateful, Commander~♪

win_mvp.line: Wowee~♪ Echo got MVP? Ehehe~ So, you're basically praising me?

battle.line: Lemme at 'em!

detail.line: I was just looking for you, Commander! Let's do something fun.

drop_descrip.line: Tribal-class destroyer – Eskimo.

expedition.line: The commission team's back? I'll go get them!

feeling1.line: You're no fun at all, Commander...

feeling2.line: My outfit? It's different because I served in some pretty frigid waters back in the day~ Heheh, it's pretty cool though, huh? What do you think?

feeling3.line: Y-you saw my room? Well, when I get too bored, I end up taking apart the furniture... and then I don't know how to put it back together. But why, though?

feeling4.line: Too noisy? Hmm, well, I'm just trying to get your attention. Everyone's really... Oh no, could I be bothering someone? I'd better go apologize!

feeling5.line: I've been good? Eheheh, that's all thanks to you, Commander. Since you've been giving me so much attention, I don't need to bother anyone else. I can just wait until you have time for me. Riiight?

home.line: I finished all the work you left here for me.

hp_warning.line: It's not time to retreat yet!

login.line: Commander, you kept me waiting so long I got mad and took apart your chair! Wh-what if I can't put it back together...?

lose.line: Oh noes... Sorry, Commander...

mail.line: Commander, I got the mail for you~ Heh heh. It was nothing. Don't mention it.

main1.line: Commander, let's build an igloo when it snows! I'm pretty good at those!

main2.line: Yippeeee! Yahoooo! Ah, Commander, errr~ Why am I horsing around like this? Just bored, I guess.

main3.line: All right, target acquired: daydreaming Commander. Eskimo head smasher! GO!

mission.line: A new mission? All right, a new mission!

mission_complete.line: Commander, here's all the mission rewards. Take a look at them already!

profile.line: I'm Tribal-class Destroyer Eskimo! During the war, I mostly served in the Home Fleet. I defeated Z19 at the Battle of Narvik, but then Z2 struck back at me... After that, I did good work in the Mediterranean.

propose.line: All right, I promise, Commander. I'll work hard, and be good. I won't cause any more trouble! Just keep on giving me more attention! Eheheh!

skill.line: All right! Have a taste of this!

touch.line: What's up, Commander? Time I get to work? All right, time I get to work!

touch2.line: Oh? Something on my coat?

unlock.line: Eskimo, Tribal-class Destroyer, is here! Oi, this fleet's not half bad! Nice to meet you, Commander!

upgrade.line: Yes! Now I'm feeling it!

win_mvp.line: Yes! I'm the MVP! Now cheer for me!

drop_descrip.line: Oh woe, nobody wants to play with me because they're all too busy~ ...Oh, hello little Manjuu... Heheh, maybe I'll play a prank on you instead!

home.line: Woohoo, Commander's back! All right, let's go swim or something!

login.line: Commander, shhhh!

main1.line: Ehehe... You have no choice but to play with me! ...Commander! Oh, it's nothing!

main2.line: Miss Belfast and Dunkerque? You brought ice cream for me? Thanks a ton! Ah, got any for the Manjuu? Huh, what do you mean you're not falling for that?

main3.line: Commander, you done with work yet? You're not? Aw, I wanted to play...

touch.line: Oww! All right, please stop bonking me... I just got bored because you wouldn't play with me... Okay, okay, I won't bully the Manjuu anymore...

unlock.line: Oh woe, nobody wants to play with me because they're all too busy~ ...Oh, hello little Manjuu... Heheh, maybe I'll play a prank on you instead!

battle.line: Alright...! Let's go all-out!

detail.line: A change of clothes for the commander, the menus for tomorrow's meals... Oh, Commander. When did you get here? ...Don't mind me, I'm just doing some daily preparations~♪

drop_descrip.line: I-class destroyer – Icarus.

expedition.line: Commander, would you like me to go greet the commissions team in your stead?

feeling1.line: ...If you keep this up, I'll be the only one left who's willing to keep looking after you, Commander...

feeling2.line: Commander, I've sworn to protect you and everyone else at the port. I'll use all my might to destroy anything that dares to hurt you!

feeling3.line: Commander, haven't you been working a bit too hard recently? You need to make sure to get some rest when you can... If you fly too close to the sun, your wings will melt, and you'll fall down, you know? ...Huh? What am I saying...?

feeling4.line: Mm... The more I stay by your side, the more I want to do your work in your stead... Do you think I'm getting a bit too attached to you...?

feeling5.line: "You, who are like the sun, make me feel your warmth just by being there. You, who are like the sun, make me afraid of being swallowed by your warmth." Commander, can I come... a bit closer to you?

headtouch.line: Hehehe. You know, this feels kind of nice.

home.line: Welcome back, Commander. I cleaned up the room while you were away. ...N-no, there's no need to praise me. It really wasn't a big deal!

hp_warning.line: My torpedoes still aren't ready... I can hold out for a bit longer...!

login.line: Commander, did you just arrive? Hehe. There are documents on your desk. I'll have your tea ready in just a moment, so please get started on your work.

lose.line: If only I could have shot another volley of torpedoes...

mail.line: I've finished sorting out the new mail! Should I bring it over?

main1.line: Commander, please let me know when you head out! Whether it's an umbrella or a coat, I'll be sure to have it ready for you.

main2.line: Eskimo looks like she wants some attention... Commander, I'll do something about her, so please focus on your work. ...That's right, I can call Abercrombie over!

main3.line: I guess destroyers really have their limits... If only I had bigger guns or torpedoes... Oh, I was just talking to myself. Please don't mind me!

mission.line: There's a new mission. Let's do our best!

mission_complete.line: The mission's been completed! How wonderful!

profile.line: My history as a ship...? I escorted Hood and Warspite, and also participated in anti-submarine missions... Basically, I've been here and there and done this and that. I guess you could say I have quite a bit of experience? That being the case, feel free to call upon me, whether in battle or otherwise!

propose.line: Just as I've become unable to part with you, have you come to feel the same way about me? I'm so happy! From now on, I'll be sure... to ask you for lots of things♪

touch.line: Was there something you wanted me to do?

touch2.line: I-I'm not sure if we should be doing this...

unlock.line: Well met, Commander. I am Icarus, I-class destroyer from the Royal Navy. I specialize in escort and anti-submarine operations. I look forward to working with you.

upgrade.line: Mmh~ One step closer to achieving overwhelming firepower... Err, I mean, I'll be more useful to the commander!

win_mvp.line: We won! It's all thanks to you, Commander!

detail.line: I've already prepared your changes of clothing and daily necessities in advance. Make sure you don't neglect your health while I'm away participating in this exercise, alright?

drop_descrip.line: This is a special exercise for our on-site medical facilities! Well, that's what they said anyway, but isn't this kind of weird...? I feel like I'd rather be taking care of others, not the other way around...

home.line: I wonder if... I should just let the Royal Maids clean your room instead...

login.line: Commander, did you come by to check up on me? Though I might look like a patient, I'm actually perfectly fine~

main1.line: Looking out the window of this hospital room at the scenery is making me oddly emotional...

main2.line: These bandages and this IV are just here for practice. They're not the real deal, you know?

main3.line: It's hard to move around properly in this... I'm sure there will be an impact on my firepower, too...

touch.line: Even in this situation, I'm sure there is something that I can do for you, Commander.

touch2.line: C-Commander? We're in the medical facility, you know...

unlock.line: This is a special exercise for our on-site medical facilities! Well, that's what they said anyway, but isn't this kind of weird...? I feel like I'd rather be taking care of others, not the other way around...

detail.line: No matter how many times I see it, it never gets old... It's simply amazing that we're able to create amazing sets like this at the Port.

drop_descrip.line: "Let's go explore the ocean together! What special things will we be able to find today~?" Hehe, how's that, Commander?

home.line: Commander, how would you like to join me in the shoot? I think I'd get more fired up if we're in the same shot... Hehe~

login.line: The manjuus and I are all ready to go! You can start taking pictures whenever you're ready.

main1.line: So this is what the submarine girls see while they battle... Hehe, the scenery down here is amazing.

main2.line: This swimsuit fits me nice and tight. It's so easy to move around in it!

main3.line: Oh, I caught you spacing out, Commander. I had the manjuus take a picture as proof, too. Why don't you take a look? Heehee~

touch2.line: W-We're still in the middle of the shoot, Commander!

unlock.line: "Let's go explore the ocean together! What special things will we be able to find today~?" Hehe, how's that, Commander?

detail.line: I cleaned your room earlier, and was pleasantly surprised to see that it was well-organized. Great work not leaving documents strewn about, Commander~

drop_descrip.line: I hope your work's going well, Commander! I've been here playing with these kitties since finishing my duties. Here, I brewed some fresh tea to help you recharge~

home.line: Welcome back, Commander. How about a break? I've prepared some cake for you. I do hope it's to your liking.

login.line: What a good little kitty cat you are~ Hold still, let me get that itch for you~ Same goes for you, Commander. Let me know if you've ever got an itch, I'll take care of it for you~

main1.line: Commander, it's time to eat. I put my all into the preparations! I... went too overboard? E-Err...

main2.line: Comparing me to the Royal Maids is like comparing night and day. There's no way I'd be able to measure up to true professionals.

main3.line: I think I understand your daily schedule now, Commander. These are part of the duties of a maid, aren't they?

touch.line: Commander? It seems you really enjoy touching people. Let's go tell everyone about this interest of yours!

touch2.line: Is this... also part of the duties of a maid?

unlock.line: I hope your work's going well, Commander! I've been here playing with these kitties since finishing my duties. Here, I brewed some fresh tea to help you recharge~

battle.line: Remember to mind your safety, even when you're fighting.

detail.line: I don't want any harm to come to Janus. Please take good care of her, and don't try to take advantage of her kindness.

drop_descrip.line: J-class destroyer – Jervis.

expedition.line: The commission's done. Make sure to wash your hands after carrying things, or else our next meeting might be in the infirmary.

feeling1.line: I cannot comprehend people who do bad things yet act like all is right with the world... Yes, people such as you, Commander.

feeling2.line: Mhm, that should do it. Please be more careful next time. Oh, Commander? As you can see, I've just finished my treatment. Are you feeling unwell, or... just slacking off again?

feeling3.line: Try not to get yourself hurt when you're out on sortie. It's going to be a huge headache for me if you end up bedridden.

feeling4.line: Of course, it falls upon me to look after you should you get injured... And while that's rather troublesome, for some reason, I do find that prospect quite appealing... I wonder if I'm coming down with some weird illness myself...

feeling5.line: I wonder if there's a cure for my selfishness... Hey, Commander, what reason might one have to develop feelings for her patient? Hm? You want me to tell you? ...As if, you prat.

headtouch.line: What are you doing, may I ask?

home.line: Welcome back–– Oh my, you have some scratches on you. You shouldn't be so careless as to put yourself in danger... I'll treat you right now, so please stay still.

hp_warning.line: Nothing some emergency treatment can't fix!

login.line: I wonder if it is an acceptable thing to keep your secretary waiting like this.

lose.line: Let's withdraw. Phew... I'm glad we were able to rescue everyone in time.

mail.line: New mail has arrived. If you miss any response deadlines, I can't help you with that.

main1.line: Your nose is practically buried in your paperwork. If you don't want to live in a blurry world, I'd advise you to be mindful of your posture.

main2.line: When treating people, the emphasis should always be on the "people" part. Administering the port operates on the same principle. Though it's fine to be absorbed in your work, try not to neglect the people around you.

main3.line: Did Janus say anything weird to you lately? ...Nevermind. She's a kind-hearted girl, but sometimes acts without thinking. It can be a bit of a pain sometimes...

mission.line: Leaving work unfinished is like allowing an illness to go untreated. By the time things get unmanageable, it may already be too late. *sigh*... Why do people choose to be so irresponsible anyway?

mission_complete.line: Mission complete. Don't forget to look back on your work to see if there's room for improvement.

profile.line: I am Jervis, J-class destroyer. I participated in several operations with the Royal Navy. If you are inclined to sum up my service as "lucky"... I suppose I don't mind. It's normal for people to become fixated on what stands out most to them, no?

propose.line: Seeing as how you aren't a complete plank, I suppose I can give you an answer. Taking care of you isn't something I can't handle... Huh? You want me to say "I love you?" Y-you idiot... Maybe we can save that for next time...

touch.line: ...Let me see your hand. Good, there's nothing wrong with it.

touch2.line: Surely you're not going to say that was an "accident," are you?

unlock.line: I am Jervis, J-class destroyer of the Royal Navy, and my duty is to assist the injured. You seem to be in pretty good shape, Commander, so my services probably aren't needed? I'll be taking my leave for now.

upgrade.line: I do wonder if you're improving yourself while everyone else is getting stronger.

win_mvp.line: Is anyone injured? Please allow me to administer some basic treatment.

detail.line: I'm helping out because the Maid Team is somewhat understaffed right now. What about my outfit...? Is there something wrong about wearing maid attire while performing maid duties?

drop_descrip.line: Phew... That about does it. Next on the agenda is... Huh, Commander? What are you doing here?

feeling5.line: As a maid, I am able to take care of you even when you are not ill, yes? ...Not that I care though. I'm not interested in becoming your maid; it was merely a thought experiment... Yes, nothing more than that.

home.line: Since you have nothing better to do, why don't you lend a hand and help me hang up the rest of these sheets? Surely you didn't come here just to watch me work?

login.line: I thought a certain someone came here to slack off, but turns out they had spare time and wanted to help out, huh... I guess there's nothing stopping you.

main1.line: Janus went to participate in the "Maid Experience Day." A real hard worker, I tell you. If she runs into any problems, won't you quietly lend her a hand? ...But, don't bring me up at all.

main2.line: Are you seriously going to stay here until lunch? I'm telling you now, I only cook for my patients. If you're fine with that, you're free to do as you please.

main3.line: Huh?! Why'd the wind suddenly kick up...?! Phew, that was a close one... Maybe I should just have you keep an eye on this for me? Just in case~

touch.line: I'll be fine. I can still reach. More importantly, where have your eyes been wandering?

touch2.line: Seems like the sheets aren't the only things that need cleaning. Let's put that dirty mind of yours through the wash too.

unlock.line: Phew... That about does it. Next on the agenda is... Huh, Commander? What are you doing here?

battle.line: Don't worry, Janus, you can do this! You can totally handle those enemies!

detail.line: So much stuff happened today... Mm, I should record it down in my diary... C-Commander?! Th-this is just an ordinary diary... Sorry! I can't let you read it!

drop_descrip.line: J-class destroyer – Janus.

expedition.line: The commission team has returned... P-please allow me to come with you! ...Well, actually, it's fine if you don't...

feeling1.line: "I knew it... I can't do anything after all... or be of use to anyone..."

feeling2.line: "I still have trouble talking to people who aren't my J-class sister ships, but... I can at least greet the Commander normally now! I'll keep working hard to make sure I can help a lot more people from now on!"

feeling3.line: "Jervis said something terrible to the Commander again today... Even though I'm sure she didn't mean that... If I were to say something like that to the Commander... Actually, there's no way that'd ever happen..."

feeling4.line: "Spending time with the Commander is always so much fun, and I feel my courage growing as well... I hope that we'll always be together, tomorrow and every day after that... It might be wishful thinking, but I hope this silly dream of mine comes true..."

feeling5.line: "Whenever I can't be with the Commander, my chest aches... Jervis said this wasn't a sickness, but rather 'covetousness'... Am I a covetous girl? Do I crave the Commander's attention so badly...? Commander, I don't want to be a nuisance to you, but I don't know what I should do..."

headtouch.line: That feels so nice... Pweh?! S-so sorry! I was completely distracted by something else just now...

feeling1.line: You know, Commander, if you keep pushing me like this I'm going to break.

feeling2.line: Commander, have you devoted yourself to the fleet once again today?

feeling3.line: Commander, you need not work yourself so hard, you know? Why not let, say... One of my maid sisters take some of your workload... Hmm?

feeling4.line: It's not like everything needs to be done one hundred percent perfectly all the time. Just take it easy. It's good enough for government work. You need to cut loose more often.

feeling5.line: Commander, if you don't know how to relax, just let me be your guide. Hm? What will I do? Erm, well, wait a tick and let me think! Ehehehe~

home.line: Commander, your office is much bigger than I expected... You know, this would be the perfect place to play hooky for a bit...

hp_warning.line: Aieeee! Pl-please settle down!

login.line: Oho! Commander, let us combine forces to finish the day's work as soon as possible!

lose.line: Aieeee! L-let us beat a hasty retreat!

mail.line: Who's the letter from this time?

main1.line: Commander, why don't we put a nice old phonograph right there in your office?

main2.line: The maids would be running ragged right about now... I am terribly unsuited to that sort of work.

main3.line: Honour guard? Bite your tongue! I am a Royal Knight under the command of King George V!

mission.line: A mission, is it...? There's still a bit of time until the deadline. I think we can worry about it later... don't you? Hehehe.

mission_complete.line: The mission rewards came in! Now there's no rush, but you'd better not forget to collect them.

profile.line: I am the name ship of the Southampton-class. During the war, I was the only one of my sisters to be sunk. How lucky of me... Ugh. Let's not speak of such unpleasant memories...

propose.line: Now, I know marriage is a solemn and serious ritual, but don't worry, I'm not going to stand on ceremony with you, Commander! Indeed, I have only one request: that whenever I wish to see you, Commander, you be there for me ♪

touch.line: Are you tired? Well then let's lie down for a nap, shall we?

touch2.line: I-I'm not a maid! ... Err, rather, you can't do that to a maid either!

unlock.line: Good day, Mast- ahem! My name is Southampton. Let me know if there's anything I might do for you. Oh and, not to be a bother, but is there a space here where I can make tea and enjoy some music?

upgrade.line: I've grown stronger! But I do hope you won't increase my workload. Hehehe.

win_mvp.line: We have seized the day! Yaay!

detail.line: Dressing up all Sakura style has me feeling like I want to listen to some Sakura music. Ehehe.

drop_descrip.line: Hello there~! Royal Knight Southampton is reporting for duty in a Sakura-style outfit! Hehe, don't you have something to tell me about my new look, like how cute it is? Come on, don't be shy. Speak up~

home.line: What do you say we do a bit of New Year's rearranging in the office here, make it a little easier to faff abo... Ahem, easier to polish off those official duties. Hehe.

login.line: Commander, Happy New Year! Now it's off to the shrine for a special blessing, isn't it? Heheh, easy does it then.

main1.line: I think this here is the "Demon Breaker Arrow," isn't it? Seems to be some kind of warding charm... brilliant!

main2.line: I got one of those omikuji fortunes for you at the shrine, Commander. Let's see, what does it say...?

main3.line: I find myself wanting to dive into all the girls' festivals now~ What delightful holiday do we have next? I'm so excited!

touch.line: Commander, come do the shrine business with me! Let's see, I think the Sakura girls did it something like this... you put your hands together, don't you?

unlock.line: Hello there~! Royal Knight Southampton is reporting for duty in a Sakura-style outfit! Hehe, don't you have something to tell me about my new look, like how cute it is? Come on, don't be shy. Speak up~

detail.line: Do you get how it feels to kick back and let loose to some heavenly music now? Ehehe.

drop_descrip.line: Good day, Comm—Err, I guess it's "Master?" Ugh, I do prefer calling you Commander though... Anyway, I've been practicing the violin to help create better atmosphere around the shop. Did you come here because you were captivated by the sound of my music?

home.line: Good work, Commander. Y-you want to know what I've been up to...? Well... I've been slacking off for a bit, ehehe. Please keep it a secret from the others!

login.line: Commander, since you're here, take a seat and relax! Sip on some tea and enjoy some good music~!

main1.line: I mean, this is something all the Royal Maids can do. Even I've learned most of the skills necessary for being a maid.

main2.line: I thought it'd be nice if we didn't have to play music live, but Her Majesty demanded that we provide live music for her at the venue...

main3.line: Commander, have any song requests? It's a special treat from me. O-oh, but... nothing too difficult, please!

touch.line: An encore? Alright. Here's a special song, just for you~

touch2.line: Eek?! I played off pitch because of you, Commander!

unlock.line: Good day, Comm—Err, I guess it's "Master?" Ugh, I do prefer calling you Commander though... Anyway, I've been practicing the violin to help create better atmosphere around the shop. Did you come here because you were captivated by the sound of my music?

battle.line: I'm still a member of the Royal Knights, you know!

detail.line: When I spin around in this dress, don't you think the fluttering ribbons make me look kind of like a butterfly? Commander? Um, Commander, are you there? What's wrong, are you so entranced that you're totally speechless?

drop_descrip.line: The Royal Knight, Southampton, makes her grand entrance in glorious wedding garb~! Oh, Commander, you look a bit on edge. Here, c'mere for a second~ Ehehe. *rub rub* Well? Feeling a bit less stiff?

expedition.line: It's time to greet the commission team, right? Let's stroll over leisurely, just as Newcastle does.

feeling5.line: That one weird trick that I told you about earlier? It's going on a date with me! Ehehe, I guess you get what I meant now? ...After you finish working? Fine, I guess I have no other choice. I'll help you out a little bit!

home.line: Excellent work as always, Commander. Please enjoy some hot and fresh tea while relaxing to the music I picked out myself~♪

login.line: Welcome back! Mast... Err, pardon me! Umm, Commander? That's just the same as before... Oh, how about, "Dear?" Hmm... I hope that's not too over-the-top for you.

main1.line: Commander, you look like you're drowning in work. I'll teach you this one weird trick that'll make all of your problems go away~! Ehehe.

main2.line: You enjoyed my cooking? Hooray! I asked Sheffield to give me some pointers, and put my heart and soul into it. Ehehe.

main3.line: Shh! Commander, come over here! Ehehe. Over here, we'll be able to slack– I mean, take a break, without Sheffield catching us.

mission.line: Wait, the mission's... deadline is right in front of us?! There's no time left to procrastinate, is there... Oh no...

touch.line: What's wrong? I'm perfectly capable of working without slacking off if it's for your sake~♪

touch2.line: I-I guess it's fine... You did give me a ring...

unlock.line: The Royal Knight, Southampton, makes her grand entrance in glorious wedding garb~! Oh, Commander, you look a bit on edge. Here, c'mere for a second~ Ehehe. *rub rub* Well? Feeling a bit less stiff?

win_mvp.line: A glorious victory, befitting a member of the Royal Knights! Ehehe~♪

battle.line: "Garbage" will pile up if you don't "clean" it up...

detail.line: Hmm? "Cleaning" things up with a gun falls perfectly within a maid's normal line of duty, Master.

drop_descrip.line: Sheffield-class Light Cruiser - HMS Sheffield

expedition.line: Master, does the sound of my gun not remind you of something? Perhaps, something like the commission fleet that you've kept waiting?

feeling1.line: I see, Master, you are remarkably similar to a pest, morphologically. The world is full of mysteries.

feeling2.line: I understand, Master. You've finally awakened to the realisation that you are an oversized lump of non-combustible rubbish, and your psyche is screaming for me to grant you the sweet release of... Just kidding, please wait while I make tea for you.

feeling3.line: To facilitate ease of reading, I took the liberty of organising and re-categorising all the books on your shelf. Please check the results.

feeling4.line: I should learn... from Belfast's example? A maid should serve her master wholeheartedly without asking for anything in return. In contrast, that one is quite greedy... but, I am a bit envious...

feeling5.line: Master, are you troubled by the way I talk and act toward you? If so, you must understand that is the way I express my love, my beloved Master. Yes, it's true.

home.line: Good work, Master. There is still some work for you to take care of. Please do your best.

hp_warning.line: So, you pests have a few tricks up your sleeves...

login.line: Please mind your step, Master... Right there... is where I just mopped.

lose.line: Master, please assign me to the rear...

mail.line: Master, I've already sorted your mail.

main1.line: "Master, I love you." Please believe me, I put at least 30% emotion into those words.

main2.line: Master, if you wish to take a nap, please tell me ahead of time. I will make sure you don't oversleep, with this gun.

main3.line: Belfast dotes on you too much, Master. At this rate, I'm afraid that you will turn into a useless lump of driftwood.

mission.line: Please entrust all "cleaning" tasks to me.

mission_complete.line: Master, do you plan to give all the mission rewards to me?

profile.line: I am the Town-class light cruiser, Sheffield. I've basically only fought against Iron Blood, having witnessed the demise of Scharnhorst, and participated in the hunt for Bismarck and Tirpitz. However, I underwent repairs throughout the end of the Second Great War and was unable to sortie. If there's nothing else you'd like to know, I would like to head back now.

propose.line: Upon the name of Virgin Mary I pledge, may the hammer of love be dropped upon those that would harm my master... Master? U-um, I wasn't doing anything in particular. You must have heard me wrong. Anyway, let's get this absolutely mortifying ceremony over with as soon as possible...

skill.line: Do you hear that? The ringing of your death knell.

touch.line: Pest- I mean, Master, what requests do you have? I beg your pardon, that was a slip of the tongue.

touch2.line: I do hope you have this same kind of strong spirit on the battlefield.

unlock.line: Ah... I thought you were a vermin, so I fired on instinct... You're my new Master? Excuse me. I am a member of the Royal Maids, Light Cruiser Sheffield. I am yours to command.

upgrade.line: Hmm... this feels a bit of all right. Thank you, Master.

win_mvp.line: Are you satisfied with these results, Master?

battle.line: Let's hurry up and get this over with. The night wanes.

detail.line: Maid by day, and secret agent by night? Hmm, that does fit the Royal style. Unfortunately for you, it's just your imagination.

drop_descrip.line: ... Did you find out about my undercover identity? You leave me no choice. Master, I cannot allow you to leave this room... Of course I'm jesting, it's merely a hobby.

login.line: Master, what kinds of missions are we to carry out tonight?

mail.line: Master, what do you plan to exchange for this all-important piece of mail?

main1.line: The slumbering city, silent and dark, inexplicably makes me feel at ease...

main2.line: Master, it is not incomprehensible that you would desire some excitement in your life, but please focus on the work at hand.

main3.line: Do not let your guard down for even a second, and always be ready to fight. From this point, a secret agent and a maid are quite similar. Huh? Maids don't have to fight? Master, your jests are quite rich.

touch.line: Master, you don't have to come all the way up to get me. It's going to be a pain to get you back down safely.

touch2.line: Out of respect for your bravery, I shall reserve this special bullet just for you.

unlock.line: ... Did you find out about my undercover identity? You leave me no choice. Master, I cannot allow you to leave this room... Of course I'm jesting, it's merely a hobby.

battle.line: Regardless of the occasion, there is always time to take out the trash.

detail.line: Swiftsure, don’t stay in your room while the festival is going on. Go out there and socialise with the others. Of course it's worth the effort...

drop_descrip.line: The Sakura Empire's summer festivals... they're quite noisy. It will be difficult to keep things clean with so many people around... Despite that, I'm still having a good time. Is there a problem?

headtouch.line: Do you need something?

home.line: Not a bad selection of fireworks. I thought that I had nothing to see since I've had to put on so many opulent displays of pyrotechnics for Her Majesty's enjoyment, but I feel like these are pretty tasteful.

login.line: So this is where you were, Master. I was afraid that you had gotten lost and almost mobilised the entire Maid Team. What exactly were you doing?

main1.line: So this is cotton candy... Mmf.. It's very sweet... Nn... What are you waiting for?

main2.line: Master, what do you think about this festival? If you're enjoying it, perhaps we can go to a similar Western-style event next time.

main3.line: Southampton, why did you run off to the festival when you're supposed to be on duty? Ugh... What am I going to do with you...

touch.line: This outfit is quite breezy. I will have to thank Ms. Victorious on behalf of the Maid Team.

touch2.line: I keep a gun with me at all times.

unlock.line: The Sakura Empire's summer festivals... they're quite noisy. It will be difficult to keep things clean with so many people around... Despite that, I'm still having a good time. Is there a problem?

detail.line: Don't worry, I've hidden my gun. If anything happens, I will protect you.

drop_descrip.line: The fact that you're asking your own maid to be your partner at the ball shows a concerning lack of gumption as a human being... However, if you go and make a fool of yourself, it will reflect poorly upon my standing as a maid. Therefore, I have no choice but to accompany you.

expedition.line: Your enthusiasm for this party is understandable, but please do not forget about the commissions.

home.line: Master, I do hope you haven't forgotten that there is still a party to attend... How hopeless you are. Allow me to tidy up your appearance.

login.line: There is no need for panic, Master. I've become quite accustomed to your lack of punctuality.

main1.line: Making your maid be your partner is a difficult request that falls outside normal lines of business. As fair compensation, please bring me a cake later.

main2.line: As your partner, I will naturally draw plenty of unwanted attention. I must steel myself mentally.

main3.line: I can see other members of the Maid Team going about their business... What a strange fetish you have, Master, to make someone who should be working behind the scenes take center stage...

touch.line: You'd like to escort me? Normally, I'd decline because that'd be embarrassing, but... you'd look so wretched that I simply have no choice but to accept.

touch2.line: Master, please do not get carried away in your excitement.

unlock.line: The fact that you're asking your own maid to be your partner at the ball shows a concerning lack of gumption as a human being... However, if you go and make a fool of yourself, it will reflect poorly upon my standing as a maid. Therefore, I have no choice but to accompany you.

battle.line: I shall defeat our foes in one fell swoop.

detail.line: Why am I braving this dungeon with you, you ask? Well, I don't believe any other party would take it on with a master less capable than a mere maid.

drop_descrip.line: Allow me to warn you ahead of time, Master. I will not come to your rescue if you spring another trap, so please mind your step henceforth... Just kidding. It is a maid's duty to aid her master, after all.

expedition.line: The commission team has returned. May I suggest that you contact them?

feeling5.line: (As long as we're in this dungeon, I have the Master all to myself. I would ordinarily be insubordinate to ask for this exclusivity, but if the Master so desires it...) Oh, not at all. I have no desire to remain here for as long as possible.

home.line: Welcome back, Master. It surprises me to see you on the frontlines. While it's true you're helpless in a battle, your mere presence does inspire courage.

login.line: It is good to see you, Master. Please let me know when you've chosen an infiltration route.

mail.line: You have received a letter. Now is the most opportune time to read it, Master.

main1.line: Have you truly had ample rest, Master? Considering your stamina, I sincerely cannot fathom a scenario wherein we reach the end of this dungeon together.

main2.line: *sigh*... As much as I wish I could use my firearms to "take out the trash," doing so would entail wreaking havoc on the stage dressing.

main3.line: To think we must crawl through ventilation shafts. How revolting... Oh, it's nothing. Please, Master, lead the way – I insist.

mission.line: You have received a new quest, Master. I pray it's nothing that will put you in danger.

mission_complete.line: Your quest rewards have come in. Please put them to good use.

touch.line: Please, allow me to protect you, Master. You will make this more difficult for me if you suffer an injury.

touch2.line: Is this how you would portray a monster?

unlock.line: Allow me to warn you ahead of time, Master. I will not come to your rescue if you spring another trap, so please mind your step henceforth... Just kidding. It is a maid's duty to aid her master, after all.

win_mvp.line: It pleases me to know you can be of some use during these dark times as well, Master.

battle.line: C'mon then, let's have a go!

detail.line: You can always count on me, Master! There's bound to be things ya can't do that I'm right capable of!

drop_descrip.line: Gloucester-class light cruiser – Manchester.

expedition.line: Commission completed, innit, Master! Let's go say hi to the team!

feeling1.line: That's just not how ya do it, Master.

feeling2.line: Being a Royal Maid, it's me duty to serve you, innit. So whenever ya need something, just hit me up!

feeling3.line: Right, so a good maid serves her Master proactively, eh... Cheers, Gloucester! I'll give the idea a go and clean Master's room right now then!

feeling4.line: Blimey, I should've thought this through... Can't enter Master's room without the key, obviously... Oh, hey up, Master. I was just thinking I'd clean your room...

feeling5.line: S-sorry, just feeling a bit tense to actually be inside your room... Yeah, of course I'll do a proper job cleaning it! Also, just wondering... c-could I pop around sometimes just to... see you, you know?

headtouch.line: Bit embarrassing, this, Master...

home.line: Welcome back, Master! Feeling a bit parched? I'll pop over to the Royal Maids, then!

hp_warning.line: It's alright! I can keep going!

login.line: Hey up, Master! Just got done tidying up the office. Go on then, have a seat! ♪

lose.line: They really did us in, eh? ...Easy now, Master, I'm well alright.

mail.line: Letter, innit. Let's see... This how ya open it?

main1.line: If your work's not coming along, how about stopping to clean a bit? Tidy workspace improves your mood, dunnit?

main2.line: I've proper wanted to learn cooking and stuff, but Gloucester says bollocks to that and won't let me. I'm not too dischuffed about it, but still...

main3.line: I can do me maid tasks AND fight at the same time! Problem is, there's not much maid stuff you can do mid-combat, sadly...

mission.line: Missions, eh... Right, blimey! Gotta start looking for one you can do!

mission_complete.line: You... You've completed all of 'em? That's bloody brilliant, Master!

profile.line: Me name's Manchester, Town-class light cruiser of the Royal Navy! I ran in convoys and helped with shipping during the war, and did loads of other missions too! Although I did make a hasty decision or two, and I didn't exactly meet a glorious end and all. Hehehe...

propose.line: I can't believe I'm getting an oath ring from you... I-I'm guessing ya won't mind me coming to your room when I feel like it? Relax, I'd never peek under your bed, 'course not!

touch.line: Hey up! Need something?

touch2.line: Oh, Gloucester's gonna be right livid if ya keep that up, Master.

unlock.line: Pleasure meeting you. I'm Manchester, Royal Navy light cruiser. Heheh, looking forward to serving ya, Master-and-Commander!

upgrade.line: Brilliant! Cheers, Master!

win_mvp.line: Cheers for helping me achieve a graceful win, Master!

detail.line: That's good, now just stay still... Actually, don't I need to do something before giving ya the shot? It's too late to ask Sheffy by now... Eh, oh well! Besides, I'm no ordinary nurse – I'm a succubus nurse! This'll go just fine!

drop_descrip.line: Master, it's time for your injection! Hmm... Nowhere to be seen, eh... Then I guess I'll keep the sickbed warm until Master comes ba– Eep! M-M-Master?!

home.line: Ahaha! Brilliant work out there, Master! Now, come here and show me your neck~ Heheh, try to hold still now~♥

login.line: Fooound you! Come on, Master, it's time for your shot~ Heheh♪

main1.line: Hmm. A nurse's job isn't to clean rooms... but is it her job to clean her Master's body? Oh gosh, what am I even thinking...

main2.line: What's up Gloucester's costume? I think she goes against her by-the-book nature to dress all fancy for special occasions... Ya think that's the case, Master?

main3.line: We're in for a right bastard of a cleanup the day after Halloween, but this is all worth it for that! Plus, that'll be a chance for the Royal Maids to shine, wunnit!

touch.line: Do ya want me to go slow, or do I just jab it in?

touch2.line: M-Master, don't move around so much!

unlock.line: Master, it's time for your injection! Hmm... Nowhere to be seen, eh... Then I guess I'll keep the sickbed warm until Master comes ba– Eep! M-M-Master?!

drop_descrip.line: Welcome to the beach, Master! Pretty hot today, innit. If you'll have me, I'm right okay with spending the day together.

expedition.line: That group has got to be... Ah! It's the commission team!

feeling5.line: So, how was today, Master? Oh, sorry if ya felt obligated to hang out with me! I'll admit, I did kind of drag ya along from place to place... You had fun nonetheless? Heehee. Happy to hear it♪

home.line: I'm done cleaning your beach house, Master. Now how 'bout reflecting on your battle over there? I'll go fetch ya a beverage!

login.line: I heard today is Unconditional No Work Day. That means ya have to kick back and relax, Master!

main1.line: Got you a fizzy pop, Master! I can make a cocktail out of it if ya want.

main2.line: Nelson's not too interested in the beach volleyball tournament... What about you, Master? I can sign ya up, no problem.

main3.line: Can we talk about Ark Royal? She says she's using her camera to keep an eye on the destroyers, but we all know that's a bloody lie...

touch.line: Yeah, Master? Need something?

touch2.line: W-was this my fault...? *blushes*

unlock.line: Welcome to the beach, Master! Pretty hot today, innit. If you'll have me, I'm right okay with spending the day together.

win_mvp.line: Ah, my swimsuit... Err, never you mind, Master! What matters is that we won!

battle.line: Please check your remaining ammunition stocks.

detail.line: If you have the time to gape at working maids, you have the time to do your own work. Master.

drop_descrip.line: Gloucester-class light cruiser – Gloucester (HMS Gloucester.)

expedition.line: You should check on the commission team, Master. Do consider how it may affect their assessment of you.

feeling1.line: I do not speak to things.

feeling2.line: Everyone makes mistakes. But I will use my experience to reduce the opportunities my master has to make such mistakes. Do be aware.

feeling3.line: Master, you must keep a healthy, balanced diet. If you find it troublesome, I can cook your meals for you. Such is a maid's duty, after all.

feeling4.line: Master, you must be mindful of your comportment around women, particularly the way you touch and handle them... If you find this challenging, I am willing to practice with you. Ahem, now then...

feeling5.line: Master, we must improve your daily habits if we are to raise your work efficiency... If you would like, Master, I could take care of- Rather, I would be happy to stay with you.

home.line: Welcome home, Master. Have some tea. Now then, I must ask, you were fully committed to your duties during the sortie, yes?

hp_warning.line: This is not going according... to plan!

login.line: Punctuality is not a virtue, it is rather a duty. Master, do bear that in mind.

lose.line: I beg your pardon, Master. I have failed you.

mail.line: Do check your mail... If you would prefer I not remind you, you need only check it sooner.

main1.line: More trouble from the Royal Maids today... Belfast, do look after this troop of clumsy louts.

main2.line: That Fiji is always buying cosmetics, clothes and the like... You must not learn from her, Master. Life is to be lived in moderation.

main3.line: A maid has a maid's work, the master has the master's. The maids serve the master, while the master serves everyone. This is the way of the world.

mission.line: You have as yet uncompleted tasks... I will continue to remind you until all of your missions have been completed.

mission_complete.line: You have uncollected mission rewards. If you would rather I collect them for you, simply direct me to do so.

profile.line: I participated in a number of operations as a member of the Royal Navy. And while I was prepared to face my own sinking, I never would have imagined it would come thanks to a shortage of ammunition... Master, I swear to you that such a fatal mistake will absolutely never happen again.

propose.line: Master, you need not resort to such methods to keep me by your side... But if this is indeed your wish, I, Gloucester, am happy to oblige...!

touch.line: Do you need something of me? As your maid, Master, I will do what I can to satisfy your requests above and beyond our typical responsibilities.

touch2.line: Take a seat over there. I am going to educate you on the proper way to treat a lady.

unlock.line: Gloucester, light cruiser of the Royal Maids, at your service, Master. It is my honor and my duty to assist you in becoming a most magnificent commander.

upgrade.line: Excellent choice. Now, if you could also strengthen some of the other girls as well, I'd be delighted.

win_mvp.line: This is but a trifling victory. Master, should you be satisfied with such triviality... I would find that rather troubling.

detail.line: It was a terrible mistake letting Fiji handle this festival costuming... "Spice up this bit and the Commander'll love it," and such. It's all a game to that girl...

drop_descrip.line: Gloucester, light cruiser of the Royal Maids, at your service for the Spring Festival... You say I look displeased? I beg your pardon, it's just... Such holidays are in fact quite busy for the Maids. We have much on our minds. It is none of your concern.

home.line: The port is all done up for the festival. But I get a headache when I think about having to put it back as it was...

login.line: Master, how is your work coming along? Let's avoid having you at the office for the holiday.

main1.line: The floor is filthy again...? Oh those girls... I told them a thousand times to wipe their dirty shoes before coming inside...

main2.line: Master, you should find a bit of time to spend with the girls. Don't forget those packets of New Year money.

main3.line: The Royal Maids are preparing tonight's banquet. As long as Belfast is there, I don't think they will have any issues... Actually, I think I will go take a look after all...

touch.line: Master, it's impolite to stare at a lady, maid or otherwise.

touch2.line: We'll have to shackle the master until the end of the festival, I'm afraid...

unlock.line: Gloucester, light cruiser of the Royal Maids, at your service for the Spring Festival... You say I look displeased? I beg your pardon, it's just... Such holidays are in fact quite busy for the Maids. We have much on our minds. It is none of your concern.

battle.line: Wh-Wh-What to do?? First let's retre... I mean, intercept them!

detail.line: I'm not going to give these to you no matter how much you stare at me.

drop_descrip.line: Edinburgh-Class light cruiser ー Edinburgh, Hull number 16!

expedition.line: When it comes to military commissions, I'm a pro!

feeling1.line: Since it's Commander, I have to be even more careful... *stare*...

feeling2.line: Everything goes well when 'that girl' does it, so it should be fine if I'm a little clumsy, shouldn't it?

feeling3.line: I've been lectured by Bel again... Forgetting to lock doors when going out, and turning off the tap... What the heck! She's totally not like a little sister!

feeling4.line: Phew... I've finally found you, Commander. Actually... Aaaah-- Who the heck! Who left the banana peel here!

feeling5.line: Commander, want to have a walk together before it gets dark? Yes, don't worry. The lights were switched off, and the windows were shut. Everything's OK! ... W-what? ...Wh-Where did the keys go?!

headtouch.line: Thanks! I'm feeling a bit more energized.

home.line: I made cookies! Please have a taste... They taste the same as Bel's? Well, we're sisters, after all!

hp_warning.line: Gh... At least let me protect the gold...!

login.line: Ah! I'm not doing anything weird! I'm just transporting gold bars into the room!

lose.line: Gh... the bullion...

mail.line: Commander, there's a new ma... Wh-What? Where's the mail? Where did I leave it... ??

main1.line: I want to be as elegant as Hood but, well...

main2.line: Eeeh! ...Bel, where are you? I forgot my keys again...

main3.line: Hmhmm~ Even Scharnhorst had to turn tail and run away when she saw me!

mission.line: You have to finish your missions properly!

mission_complete.line: I seem to have forgotten about something... Well, whatever!

profile.line: I am the lead ship of Edinburgh class of the Royal Navy. Sometimes it is stressful having an overly capable little sister... I took part in the pursuit of Bismarck and Scharnhorst, as well as many patrol missions in Atlantic, North sea and Mediterranean. In the end, I sunk with all my gold due to Ironblood torpedoes...

propose.line: Hmhm, I'm fine with sharing some of my money-luck with you. ...The gold? No! That belongs to the Belfast Foundation!

skill.line: No matter how thick the armor is, it can't win against the power of gold!

touch.line: Hey!! Don't touch that! It's gonna fall!

touch2.line: Commander, a lady would never hide her gold bars there!

unlock.line: This is my turn, you might say! I am 'her' older sister, Edinburgh! In a sense, I am the 'most accomplished' light cruiser!

upgrade.line: It seems like I've become luckier!

win_mvp.line: Crushing the enemies with elegance... That, is the elegant Ediburgh of the royal family!

battle.line: Tsk tsk, we don’t need her here. In any case, Belfast will always be by my side. Fleet, prepare for interception!

detail.line: Hmm...this Alchemy is really mysterious, but once I mastered it, then Belfast’s trust fund will...

drop_descrip.line: Why doesn't she have to go to school with me...she says she’s a maid for the Queen? Well, me too! You can be a maid and school girl at the same time...tsk tsk---

expedition.line: Belfast, before you go to greet the girls returning from commission, could you brush my hair? It's a mess...

login.line: This pendant is so cute, right?! I copied from that girl. Let's call her “Belfast”.

lose.line: M-my Belfast, are you ok?!

main1.line: Belfast, wake me up before you wake up Elizabeth. Otherwise, she will criticize me for getting up late again...

main2.line: Do I look like a child who’s so easily bullied? Hehe, but as elegant as I am, no wonder I am called a fairy.

main3.line: Victory, let me rub your cheeks again, doing so always brings me good luck.

touch.line: Commander, wanna try my snacks? Ah~~

touch2.line: Commander! C’mon out now will ya. I can't study this way…

unlock.line: Why doesn't she have to go to school with me...she says she’s a maid for the Queen? Well, me too! You can be a maid and school girl at the same time...tsk tsk---

detail.line: I'm a Royal Maid, I'm certainly not afraid of any- Hyaaaaah!? Wh-wh-where did that come from!? ... Phew... D- don't scare me like that now!

drop_descrip.line: Ahem! I made this special candy just for Halloween! Here, Commander, take some! Wooaaooah! Wh-who put this pumpkin here? It, it was me?!

home.line: Bel, are you really turning down the Halloween event because you're too busy with Head Maid duties? Gosh, you really ought to make time for your sister~

login.line: Ah! I'm just transporting the Queen's bullion in the pumpkin! It's not what you think!

main1.line: They're saying I've got spicy candy mixed in here...? That's odd... I hand picked them all myself... Now where did that rumor come from?

main2.line: Ta-daaah! It's a special Halloween Maid uniform! Lovely, innit? Heheee, I'd say bits of me even outshine Bel!

main3.line: Gneisenau's costume there, it's a bit... Um, it's something...

touch.line: Halloween candy delivery! You there, Commander, how would you like a treat endorsed by the Queen herself?

touch2.line: Oi there! Don't be doing that when I'm busy!

unlock.line: Ahem! I made this special candy just for Halloween! Here, Commander, take some! Wooaaooah! Wh-who put this pumpkin here? It, it was me?!

battle.line: It's a maid's duty to remove their master's obstacles.

detail.line: Is something the matter, master?

drop_descrip.line: Edinburgh-Class light cruiser ー Belfast, Hull number C35!

expedition.line: Master, the ladies who went off for commissions have been waiting for you to greet them.

feeling1.line: Correcting her master is also a maid's duty...

feeling2.line: I'm terribly sorry... I'm still new to this fleet, so I'm somewhat unfamiliar with my duties and cannot serve you at 100% capacity... Please look forward to my continued service.

feeling3.line: This is something I made using the connections I have to the fleet. Please have a taste -- Is the taste to your liking?

feeling4.line: It is important to observe your intentions sensitively. Especially intentions that you yourself are not aware of, master... I'm mean, you say? Hehe. Recently I've come to enjoy your troubled look a little. By all means, please forgive me.

feeling5.line: Are you awake? ...Hehe, your sleeping face was so cute, I couldn't bear waking you up... How did it feel, resting on my lap? You are free to enjoy it to your heart's content

home.line: Welcome back, master. I've readied some light snacks over here.

hp_warning.line: Everyone, the main dish has yet to come!

login.line: Welcome back, master. I've prepared the tea. Furthermore, I've sorted the documents over here. Please work at your leisure.

lose.line: Please retreat first, master. I still have some matters to attend to.

mail.line: There's a new letter. Shall I read it for you, master?

main1.line: In order to become an excellent master, you must start from self confidence. Please do your best to turn your will into action, master.

main2.line: Do you want some tea? Ah... if you want something else, I'll prepare some coffee or whiskey.

main3.line: Sunbathing on Thames river wasn't bad. But this current life of mine is better...

mission.line: A new mission has been given to us, master. Please confirm it.

mission_complete.line: Your rewards have been delivered, Master.

profile.line: Good day to you. I am Belfast, the second ship of the Edinburgh class. I have duties as the head maid while being the Royal Navy's greatest cruiser. I had taken part in many battles, and borne witness to lady Scharnhorst's fall... Those are but the past for a maid. Please say something should you have a need for me.

propose.line: Now this is a little troubling... I'm fine with simply protecting you, my master, as well as occassionally enjoying your troubled look... But with such an important bond being formed, I've become wanting to serve you even more, as well as receiving more of your attention, master...

skill.line: Dear enemies, this is going to be a little bit painful

touch.line: Aimlessly touching a lady is not a gentlemanly behaviour. Please behave yourself around others.

touch2.line: It's a maid's duty to dedicate her all to her master. Would you like to see, master?

unlock.line: Are you my master? Pleasure to meet you. I am Belfast the maid. From now on, I dedicate myself to you.

upgrade.line: I won't let you down.

win_mvp.line: Oh my, I didn't spend as much effort as cleaning up a stain in a tablecloth.

detail.line: The outfits of the Dragon Empery do have a certain charm. Perhaps I can give them a little recommendation to the rest of the maid team. What do you think?

drop_descrip.line: Hehe... Master, why are you so stunned from seeing me? I thought you perhaps wanted to see me in a qipao... was I mistaken?

expedition.line: Master, what do you think about handing some red envelopes to the hardworking girls still out on commissions?

feeling5.line: Did you know, Master... all I can do for you is to learn from the cultures of the other camps in order to provide you with better service. But all this pales in comparison to all that you do for us on a daily basis, yet you take yourself for granted... What a lovable but also hateable person.

home.line: I baked this pastry for a certain Master who is so absorbed in work to the point of forgetting to eat. Please enjoy it.

login.line: Welcome back, Master. I specially procured some different teas from the Dragon Empery. Which one would you like to try first?

main1.line: A variety of culinary techniques and seasoning methods... the food culture of the Dragon Empery is truly eye-opening.

main2.line: It's customary in the Dragon Empery for everyone to get together on New Year's to have a banquet? Ahh, so many people to serve... my maid's soul is trembling!

main3.line: Only a few girls from the Dragon Empery have joined our fleet. Because of that, I can't afford to let them feel lonely.

touch.line: Despite the fact that it is a holiday, I am still ready to sortie.

touch2.line: I see, Master. The biggest drawback of this qipao is its ability to rob you of your self-control.

unlock.line: Hehe... Master, why are you so stunned from seeing me? I thought you perhaps wanted to see me in a qipao... was I mistaken?

detail.line: It is only by maintaining a well-regulated lifestyle that one may keep a cool head and act appropriately when backed into a corner... It is with this in mind that I, Belfast, serve my Master as a maid.

drop_descrip.line: This is special cold-weather equipment inspired by Eagle Union designs. It was made for practical purposes such as special operations in frigid climates, and as such, was not designed with appearances in mind. Please do forgive me, Master.

home.line: Welcome home, Master. You may rest easy knowing the Royal Maids are here to protect you.

login.line: Welcome home, Master. Your coffee is ready. Please, enjoy it at your leisure.

main1.line: Madam Enterprise's cooking has improved noticeably. This is certainly thanks to Madam Vestal's lessons, but no doubt the Master is another important reason.

main2.line: Such a willful appearance... a maid uniform is of course the appropriate dress for a maid, is it not?

main3.line: It would be nice if I spent more time with my sister, hm...? I must agree with you, Master. I beg your pardon for making you worry so.

touch.line: Do let us know if you have any needs that the Royal Maids might service.

touch2.line: I'm afraid this battle dress may not adequately satisfy you, Master. I beg your pardon.

unlock.line: This is special cold-weather equipment inspired by Eagle Union designs. It was made for practical purposes such as special operations in frigid climates, and as such, was not designed with appearances in mind. Please do forgive me, Master.

upgrade.line: This power, it certainly is not just for the sake of destruction.

win_mvp.line: A victory for the Master...

battle.line: Belfast of the Royal Maids, reporting in.

detail.line: It is a maid's duty, in service to her master and Her Majesty, to uphold the elegance of the banquet and safeguard it from disgrace.

drop_descrip.line: Good evening. The Royal Maids will be chaperoning this event. It is my hope to prevent any inappropriate behaviour that might interfere with the enjoyment of the attendees. Please pardon any inconveniences this may cause.

home.line: Please continue to enjoy the banquet, Master.

login.line: Master, are you pleased with the festivities?

main1.line: Master, the arrangements for the venue's security have already been made. Indeed, Madam Ark Royal graciously offered her assistance. Be at ease.

main2.line: Dear Sister, let me handle the patrols. You go relax with your colleagues... I just want Master all to myself...? Goodness, as if that has anything to do with it...

main3.line: Have a drink...? Very well, if you wish to drink, I can certainly accompany you... But I'm afraid these Sakura Empire wines are the only ones that... No matter, let us have that drink.

touch2.line: Master...? Please, have some self-respect. We are in public.

unlock.line: Good evening. The Royal Maids will be chaperoning this event. It is my hope to prevent any inappropriate behaviour that might interfere with the enjoyment of the attendees. Please pardon any inconveniences this may cause.

detail.line: Master, what would you like for lunch? I prepared some... Hmm? You're fine with just that? Master, you can't have snacks as a meal.

drop_descrip.line: Hehe~ Judging from your expression, Master, my outfit has not fallen short of your expectations. As time is precious, allow me to serve you to the utmost on this "date."

home.line: Master, if you don't know where you'd like to go next, why don't we just wander around for a while? Sometimes, the most serendipitous sights are the most memorable of all.

login.line: I am accustomed to being the one who makes the arrangements, but occasionally letting others make plans for me has merits of its own. Master, our next location is for you to decide. Hehe~ I'm looking forward to it.

main1.line: This snack seems to be quite popular these days. Master, would you like some? Here, say "ahhn~" Hehe, so this must be a part of the reason why it's popular.

main2.line: As a maid, it is my duty to serve you. However, so that you may leave a positive impression of yourself upon others, I will entrust the duty of carrying these bags to you, Master.

main3.line: I should pick out some outfits for the other maids as well, not just for me... Of course, I'll be doing the same for you, Master. Hehe~

touch.line: Holding hands? ... Master, there's something nostalgic about this feeling.

touch2.line: Even on a date, one ought not be too impatient. Understood, Master?

unlock.line: Hehe~ Judging from your expression, Master, my outfit has not fallen short of your expectations. As time is precious, allow me to serve you to the utmost on this "date."

detail.line: Whether serving my master or managing a restaurant, it is my responsibility as a Royal Maid to handle it promptly and efficiently. Now then, are you satisfied with my performance?

drop_descrip.line: Welcome, table for one? Of course, right this way. Oh? What is it? Ah... I'm filling in for the manager at the moment, so that makes you my customer rather than my master, no?

home.line: Here is the pizza you ordered. Do take your time and enjoy it.

login.line: Your menu. I would recommend our new offerings here. There is also a promotional campaign of which you might take advantage.

main1.line: Miss Fubuki is rather excitable, but she is a clever and hardworking girl. Just give her a bit of direction and she'll figure it all right out.

main2.line: While the customer is free to order anything she wants, as a maid I feel it is my responsibility to offer healthier suggestions. Particularly to the Union girls who order litres and litres of cola...

main3.line: Leading customers to their tables, organising shifts, management... all of this would make a fine training program for the Royal Maids.

touch.line: Yes, what can I get for you?

touch2.line: While it is indeed a maid's duty to offer everything to her master... Not to be presumptuous, but you could consider the time and place.

unlock.line: Welcome, table for one? Of course, right this way. Oh? What is it? Ah... I'm filling in for the manager at the moment, so that makes you my customer rather than my master, no?

detail.line: Master, is there something I can do for you? Holiday or no, I am here to serve your every wish.

drop_descrip.line: It took me quite some time to prepare a suitable traditional Sakura Empire outfit. Terribly sorry. Master, won't you please allow this Belfast to serve you for another year?

home.line: You want me to join you for a shrine visit...? I'd be delighted. Your Belfast will gladly accompany you.

login.line: Happy New Year, Master. The maids have prepared you some New Year's dishes from the Sakura Empire. Please, enjoy.

main1.line: An elegant fan emphasizes its holder's poise. Would you like to hold one, Master? Hehehe.

main2.line: I was concerned that traditional Sakura Empire attire might hinder my maid work, but rather, it's easier to move than I thought.

main3.line: Madam Hiei instructed me in the ways of Sakura Empire cuisine. In exchange, the Royal Maids will assist her with her next banquet. Do look forward to it, Master.

touch.line: Master, if you're tired, please take a rest here.

touch2.line: Everything has its time and place, Master.

unlock.line: It took me quite some time to prepare a suitable traditional Sakura Empire outfit. Terribly sorry. Master, won't you please allow this Belfast to serve you for another year?

detail.line: I'm not going to give up being your maid. Besides, who could understand you better than me?

drop_descrip.line: Are you destined for me? Greetings Belfast, from this moment onwards, I will always be with you.

feeling5.line: Am I getting used to my new role? You really asked me a tough question, but...there's no sweeter question in the world.

home.line: Anything interesting today? Tell me while we enjoy some dessert.

login.line: Is today the same as usual?

main1.line: Master, dear, darling...some hard choices to make. Or do you have other ideas?

main2.line: Just do according to your own plans, in my heart you will always be the best.

main3.line: Wearing this makes it a little inconvenient to do things...but if you like it so much, then just be a bit more patient...

touch.line: In comparison to standing behind you, I can see more when standing beside you.

touch2.line: W-wait a moment...honestly, I'm cleaning right now..

unlock.line: Are you destined for me? Greetings. Belfast, from this moment onwards, I will always be with you.

battle.line: Listen up! Our pride rides on this battle! Let's take this seriously!

detail.line: ...Idiot! Did no one teach you that it's rude to stare at a girl?!

drop_descrip.line: Arethusa-class light cruiser – Arethusa, Hull Number 26!

expedition.line: The commission team is back. Hurry up and check the results from them, you idiot!

feeling1.line: I cannot acknowledge a commander like you!

feeling2.line: I do not acknowledge a Commander like you! Hmph!

feeling3.line: Don't get carried away! I came here because of a tasty cake! It's still too early for me to acknowledge you!

feeling4.line: You do have some positive qualities... Hmph! My opinion of you is slightly improved! There's still a lot for you to do!

feeling5.line: Umm... Good work... I mean, it's nothing! I just made some snacks since I felt like it, so hurry up and eat them!

home.line: You're so lacking at work that you're only good at returning here!

login.line: Commander, I'm gonna get angry if you don't take this seriously!

lose.line: Ugh... How could I fall here... of all places...

mail.line: It's your mail so hurry up and get it. ...It's not like I'm concerned about who it's from! Hmph!

main1.line: Even if they are allies, I will not show mercy to any threat towards  my comrades!

main2.line: ...Leaving me alone like this... I-I'm not feeling lonely or anything!
