main3.line: Hmph! You suck, Commander, so stop making me worry about you!

mission.line: Idiot! Stop sleeping! There's a new mission!

mission_complete.line: Doesn't the reward suit you just fine? Hurry up and get it!

profile.line: I am the Arethusa class treaty cruiser, Arethusa: the first cruiser in the world designed with vertical armor! --Hmph! The fact that I'm amazing was decided from the beginning!

propose.line: You dummy. You're making this too formal! This... should've been done a while ago...

skill.line: If we keep doing this dillgently, it will all work out!

touch.line: I-it's not like I'm fond of being touched by an idiot like you! ...I just feel sorry for you since you're so lonely!

touch2.line: Aaah! Pervert! Molester! Lewd! Go and die!

unlock.line: You can be at ease now that I, Arethusa, have come. If anything, Commander, don't you dare become my hindrance!

upgrade.line: Commander, don't get in my way!

win_mvp.line: Hmph! I will not acknowledge you just because you complimented me!

battle.line: Such disobedient kids~~ They must be punished~

detail.line: Geez~ If you keep on looking at me like that, I'll be reporting you to the authorities~

drop_descrip.line: Arethusa-class light cruiser – Galatea, Hull Number 71!

expedition.line: Commander~ *arms folded* let's head to the docks and greet the girls who went off for commissions

feeling1.line: Do you understand? Even the red string of fate is not absolute. I no longer think about anything concerning you anymore, Commander~

feeling2.line: It takes a long time for the bond to form after you tie the red string of fate. Do try hard, Commander~

feeling3.line: I like you Commander, but it's important for all of us to be together. I'm troubled~

feeling4.line: Commander, let me have your ear... *kiss*. I like you~ ... Yep. Such a thing would have to be done in reality, right~

feeling5.line: The red string of fate was what made me grow from a seed, and you, Commander, were the one who made me bloom~ You're so great~ *kiss*

home.line: Aaaah cease your attacks! I'm on your side!

login.line: I'm going to do this and that again today. Please take care of it~

lose.line: Hmph! ...I curse you to be destroyed by my allies!

mail.line: Mail time~ I wonder what reward I'll get for bringing it to you~?

main1.line: Commander, I'm wearing new clothes today! --Hmm? I didn't say I'm heading out!

main2.line: Commander, are you free? How about taking a walk together? I want to link our arms and be seen by the other girls

main3.line: Hmm? Did you not hear that? ...There's no helping it. Lie down over here and let me check your ears

mission.line: Yes, let's see what today's missions are about~

mission_complete.line: I'm gonna take your share of the rewards too, Commander.

profile.line: I am Galatea, the second ship of the Arethusa class. I may not look like it, but in my service in the Mediterranean, I achieved some results~ You'll regret it if you underestimate me~

propose.line: With this, the bond of fate has been formed~ There's still a long way ahead of us, so let's take care of each other, darling~

skill.line: This has nothing to do with my fate~

touch.line: Hehe~ Commander, you really like to engage in skinship, don't you? Well, just this once, I'm allowing you to continue a bit more~

touch2.line: Ah... You're daring, Commander --Well then, do you want to hear my wishes?

unlock.line: I am Galatea, the 2nd of the Arethusa class~ Do you believe in fate, Commander? It is fate that I meet with you~

upgrade.line: This too is fate~

win_mvp.line: You cannot escape from me! Be good, and accept~ your~ punishment~

battle.line: May we be blessed with victory~

detail.line: Commander, is there anything I can help you with regarding equipment?

drop_descrip.line: Arethusa-class light cruiser - Aurora, pennant number 12

expedition.line: Commander, it will be a problem if you keep staring at me and forget about the girls who have returned from commission.

feeling1.line: Commander, please refrain from making a fool of yourself in public.

feeling2.line: Commander, would you like to see the roses that I planted? I have a lot of different kinds~

feeling3.line: The goddess, Aurora, was said to have "rose-coloured fingers." Though the same can't be said for me, my fingers at least smell like roses. Commander, want to check for yourself?

feeling4.line: Commander, come here for a moment~ ... Hehe, this rose suits you best after all! Eh? I'm not making fun of you... In that case, why don't you pick one out to put on me? I'm sure I'll love whatever you pick~

feeling5.line: Lately, some girls have been grumbling that I've been monopolosing all your time... But, I'm not going to back down on this. Commander, you too should be prepared to deal with a bunch of sulking girls~

home.line: Good work. Please take some time to relax.

hp_warning.line: Light of dawn, illuminate our path...!

login.line: My name symbolises the break of dawn. Ehehe~ Do you feel more energetic from seeing me?

lose.line: It seems I have not yet become accustomed to the battlefield...

mail.line: There's new mail, shall I read it aloud for you?

main1.line: Dragon Empery? Oh, it's a great place. Mm... for example...

main2.line: Even though I don't mind if you stare at me, please do your work properly~

main3.line: Hold still, Commander, there's something stuck on your cheek... There! Now, please do your best at work~

mission.line: Commander, a new mission dossier has been issued. I have already highlighted the most important parts, so please look over it.

mission_complete.line: Some mission rewards had not yet been collected, so I retrieved them in your stead.

profile.line: I am Aurora of the Royal Navy, fourth ship of the Arethusa-class. You are welcome to call me the "Goddess of Dawn," but please forget any nasty-sounding nicknames you might hear like the "Silver Phantom." Commander, perhaps you are familiar with some of the other names that I've been called?

propose.line: "A rose by any name would smell as sweet." Whether I am called Aurora, the "Goddess of Dawn," or even Chongqing, I am still the same me. Yes... I will always be at your side.

skill.line: Commander, helping you solve problems and leave worries behind is also part of my job~

touch.line: Commander, want to take a break and come water the flowers with me?

touch2.line: Commander! I... I'm going to be mad! Jeez! I'll really get mad!

unlock.line: Greetings, Commander. I am the fourth ship of the Arethusa-class light cruisers, Aurora. From now on, I shall serve as your secretary. Please feel free to ask anything of me~

upgrade.line: Commander, I'll be able to help with even more things now~

win_mvp.line: How wonderful, Commander, we won!

detail.line: My outfit is a bit surprising? Ehehe, from now on, you'll learn more and more about a different side of me~

drop_descrip.line: I have long prepared for this day... Commander, would you like to listen to my storytelling?

login.line: Commander, welcome back. Please take your time, I only just got here myself.

main1.line: Commander, would you like to eat hotpot? If you're not good with spice, I'll prepare a two-sided pot~

main2.line: If you're tired, why don't you enjoy a mandarin while listening to me read a story?

touch.line: Eh? What's the matter? Ah, I was just thinking... it'd be great if things could stay like this next year, and the year after that, and forever more...

unlock.line: I have long prepared for this day... Commander, would you like to listen to my storytelling?

detail.line: Commander, I often perform in the main plaza. It'd be nice if you could come and listen.

drop_descrip.line: I've always believed that music is unique in its power to touch one's heart, so I decided to learn the violin. Commander, please enjoy my performance.

feeling5.line: Commander, after everything is over, let's travel around the world, bringing blessings to the far corners of the world with our music. This is something only we can do.

home.line: You must be weary, Commander. Allow me to soothe you with my music.

main1.line: The pigeons always seem to gather to the sound of music. Hehe, turns out that they're hungry.

main2.line: Commander, are you interested in learning an instrument? I'd recommend the piano so that you can accompany me!

main3.line: Commander, if you ever find yourself lost and confused in the dark, you can always seek out my music!

touch.line: Are you tired of working? Well, is there anything you'd like to listen to?

touch2.line: Jeez, Commander, this is going to get in the way of my performance...

unlock.line: I've always believed that music is unique in its power to touch one's heart, so I decided to learn the violin. Commander, please enjoy my performance.

detail.line: The operas are just a glimpse of the Dragon Empery's five thousand rich years of culture and history... As a ship with a deep connection with the Dragon Empery, I hope to share the charm of these ancient traditions with many more people!

drop_descrip.line: "Next, Aurora will perform something you've never seen before - traditional Sichuan mask-changing opera!" Hehe... Commander, I look like the real deal, right?

feeling5.line: Commander, is there some mask that represents... um, "love?" Huh? Just show it with my own face? G-goodness, Commander, an elegant lady is supposed to maintain her composure.

home.line: Commander, you must be tired. Ahem! Please have some refreshments while you enjoy my upcoming performance!

login.line: What kind of performance should I prepare for today? I have too many things to choose from...

main1.line: One of the specialities of Sichuan opera is something called "mask changing." It lets you quickly portray different emotions, or even different characters. Hehe, it took a lot of practice to be able to do this.

main2.line: "Behind each minute on the stage is ten years of practice." The Dragon Empery's old adages are quite thought-provoking...

main3.line: Commander, do you know how many different types of plays there are in the Dragon Empery?

touch.line: What are these weapons for? Um, right now, I mostly play the flower girl character, but I hope to be able to play some warriors too! Hehe~

touch2.line: C-Commander?! If you keep this up, I'm going to use my polearm and sword, and um... it's going to hurt!

unlock.line: "Next, Aurora will perform something you've never seen before - traditional Sichuan mask-changing opera!" Hehe... Commander, I look like the real deal, right?

detail.line: As you know, Commander, the rose petals in the finger bowl came from roses that I planted. Hehe~

drop_descrip.line: Commander, please relax and take a seat. This is a special place for just the two of us... Just kidding, did I get your heart racing just now? Ehehe~

expedition.line: The way you're staring at me... are you waiting for me to remind you to welcome the others back? Hehe~

feeling5.line: Don't worry. Even if you belong to everyone else, Commander, Aurora belongs only to you. Hehe, this way, the other girls won't come to resent you~

home.line: Well done. Which would you like, rose, saffron, or mint tea?

login.line: Do you feel a little better when I'm by your side, Commander? Hehe~

main1.line: I've adorned your office with more than just roses... Azaleas, peonies, cyclamen, carnations... Is it not better to foster a warm and harmonious atmosphere?

main2.line: Elegance, grace, and strength of spirit... I must work harder in order to become your supporting pillar.

main3.line: A lively festival can be quite enjoyable, but there's also value in relaxing in a spacious room.

touch.line: Do you know what the embroidery here means? Hehe~

touch2.line: Commander...?

unlock.line: Commander, please relax and take a seat. This is a special place for just the two of us... Just kidding, did I get your heart racing just now? Ehehe~

battle.line: Battle time! Eyes ahead, everyone!

detail.line: What's up, Commander? Missed me, have you? Hah, alright, have a seat and I'll get you some tea.

drop_descrip.line: Fiji-class light cruiser – Fiji.

expedition.line: Commission team's come back. Don't forget to go greet them! Or else you'll hurt their feelings.

feeling1.line: You need something, Commander? I'm kind of unavailable, really.

feeling2.line: All combat, all makeup, all the time, that's me!

feeling3.line: Oh yeah, anyone in the fleet you fancy? Want me to assist you with them? Come on now, don't get your knickers in a twist~ I can keep a secret~

feeling4.line: Oh, hey, Commander. I was just about to head out. Getting dressed right now, you see~ Ah, don't be shy, you can look~ Later, I wanna get a look at you, too~

feeling5.line: Slow to catch on, aren't you~ Right, question! Could you believe there's a girl out there who's always talking about love with you, isn't afraid to undress before your eyes, and has grown quite fond of you?

home.line: What're you staring into space for? Is that your way of saying "I want a hug"?

hp_warning.line: It's like back in Crete... Sod that! I'm not letting that happen again!

login.line: Had supper yet, Commander? If not, I could cook you something up.

lose.line: Commander, take everyone with you and retreat! Leg it...!

mail.line: Mail's here, Commander. I'll leave it here, so check it when you've got the time.

main1.line: Jamaica? Ah, yeah, proper oddball, that girl~ But it's all good as long as she's having fun, innit?

main2.line: What's up? You look knackered... Fancy a nap in my lap, maybe?

main3.line: Hey, take a gander at this, Commander! Fancy what I've done with my hair? How about my nails?

mission.line: You can't just go leaving missions unfinished, Commander~ Let's go finish them. Remember: I'm right with you.

mission_complete.line: Mission rewards, hooray~! Done your job proper, I'd say, Commander.

profile.line: Name's Fiji, I'm pretty much the nameship of my class. Things I fancy include... What? Spare the details? Then, if you're asking about my service record, all I did was fight in the Battle of Crete. Pretty rubbish record, innit... ahaha. Just gonna have to live with it and work on it, you know?

propose.line: Hey, is my makeup looking decent? What about my outfit? Reckon I look as pretty as it gets? ...Good~ I've never dressed for this occasion before, so I want to look as good as possible~

touch.line: Feeling lonely, Commander? I'm always here for you.

touch2.line: If you wanna know my three sizes, can't you just ask? I mean, if you do, I'll tell you~ Hahaha~♪

unlock.line: Heeey! Fiji's here~! Are you the Commander? Hmmm...? Pfft... Hahaha! You don't look too shabby! Nice seeing you, Com~man~der~♪

upgrade.line: I'll do my part on the battlefield all proper like, so you can rest easy, Commander.

win_mvp.line: Just doing my part on the battlefield, really!

detail.line: Hehe, what do you think about my outfit, Commander? Pretty nice, isn't it? ...You don't know where you should be looking? Haha, you cheeky little...

drop_descrip.line: Did I keep you waiting, Commander? Ahaha... A girl's gotta take her time before stepping out onto the streets, remember? Come on, take my hand, and let's get going! Hehe~

home.line: Welcome back! Hmm, how are we gonna celebrate your hard work? Ahaha, what do you think about a candle-lit dinner?

login.line: Commander, we've talked about the importance of being punctual before, right...? As compensation for making me wait, we're gonna shop 'til we drop! Ahaha!

main1.line: The joy of going shopping is knowing that every time you go out, there's something new to be discovered. Commander, I'll let you handle the "spoils" of our shopping trip.

main2.line: You've gotta try on some new clothes during your downtime every now and then! Hehe, want me to help you pick out some clothes, Commander?

main3.line: Girls need to do a lot of preparation before going out, you know? Hair, makeup, clothes, you name it... So, if you want to see us at our cutest, you've got to be patient~

touch.line: When we're on a date, it's only natural to lock arms and lean against you like this~ Ahaha, are you embarrassed, Commander?

unlock.line: Did I keep you waiting, Commander? Ahaha... A girl's gotta take her time before stepping out onto the streets, remember? Come on, take my hand, and let's get going! Hehe~

battle.line: My heart is utterly unclouded...!

detail.line: Boss, can you check if these chains are covering my left eye? I'll reposition my arm.

drop_descrip.line: Fiji-class light cruiser – Jamaica.

expedition.line: Boss, the commission team has returned... "Stop posing on the veranda"? U-understood...

feeling1.line: Unfortunately, Boss, it seems your Goals differ from mine...

feeling2.line: Boss, care for a chat? There seems to be a need for us to Know one another.

feeling3.line: An age of justice? That is not what I want. Where there is light, there is dark. Evil cannot be eradicated so easily, Boss.

feeling4.line: You end up on the path of Evil if you only focus on your own justice, your own desires. Never let the Darkness out of sight. I'm here with you, Boss.

feeling5.line: One needs a Heart of Justice. As long as we have it, no matter what struggles we face, we will surely see our journey to the end. We are Just, therefore... you are never alone, Boss.

home.line: I feel Evil wriggling within the depths of my heart... Boss, let's enjoy this Peace while it lasts.

hp_warning.line: Victory comes to those who are determined! Stand Proud!

login.line: Boss, my Eye has seen it... Your necktie is slightly loose.

lose.line: It's not pain I fear... it's being completely helpless... Ugh!

mail.line: Boss, you have mail from one of your partners.

main1.line: Boss, is the "you" that my Eye sees really "you"?

main2.line: Boss, care to race with me? I will show you what real Lighting looks like.

main3.line: I feel it. Somewhere in the world, the darkness of night is enveloping something...

mission.line: Boss, are there any Missions for me to tackle?

mission_complete.line: Boss, we've received mission rewards. Me? No need. I'm satisfied with Standing here and basking in my sense of accomplishment.

profile.line: It is I. I, Jamaica, who sabotaged Iron Blood's operation in the Barents Sea; I, who sealed Scharnhorst to her fate: to sink in the Battle of the North Cape. Operation Tungsten? Of course I was there. As was I during the subsequent civil war... As long as Evil continues its march, I will keep fighting... Yes, all my choices were made by Justice itself...

propose.line: Boss, what we are doing is carving a path through the Wilderness. And being here to walk beside you is the greatest blessing of my life.

skill.line: The eulogy of life... is the eulogy of Courage!

touch.line: ...Boss, keep your hands to yourself. Otherwise you'll startle me when I'm concentrating.

touch2.line: ...Boss, t-this isn't the place for this...

unlock.line: Ugh... my eye is throbbing again... So you're the Boss, huh? The name's Jamaica. All is in the name of Justice...

upgrade.line: It's not enough... I need more power...!

win_mvp.line: Eradicating you fiends is the meaning of Justice.

detail.line: Boss, if you have time, wanna help me upgrade my bike? I got some sick ideas.

drop_descrip.line: Hey Boss, you talkin' about my sweet bike? Heh, I made it myself by scrounging up parts from Akashi's place. Pretty cool, huh?

feeling5.line: I used to consider myself a drifter, a vagabond with no home and no destination. But I learned that I was wrong, Boss. No matter what happens, I'll always come back... to home.

home.line: Boss, come take a seat. We're gonna forget all about the the smoke of the battlefield, and feel the wind at our side.

login.line: Boss, the weather be fine today. Wanna go for a ride?

main1.line: When somethin' is on my mind, I just keep on riding until my troubles are left far, far behind... However, it's really easy to get lost.

main2.line: Boss, when I drive, I like to go fast. When you're sitting behind me, make sure to hold on tight!

main3.line: Boss, what if I named this bad boy here "Dark Bolt?"

touch.line: Boss, do you wanna try riding too? Be careful, this guy's got some serious horsepower.

touch2.line: Boss... even though I told you to hold on to me tight, I didn't mean right there...

unlock.line: Hey Boss, you talkin' about my sweet bike? Heh, I made it myself by scrounging up parts from Akashi's place. Pretty cool, huh?

detail.line: Akashi said she'd give me this bike in exchange for some "marketing." Sooo... Boss, what do you think? Wanna buy one?

drop_descrip.line: Look, Boss, this is the new bike that Akashi sent me. She said she wanted me to be her brand ambassador... Doesn't that job sound badass?

feeling5.line: I once thought myself a traveler, with nothing to tie me down, with no real destination... Turns out I was wrong, Boss. I'll always come back to you, no matter what happens.

home.line: Boss, the mountains are lovely this time of year. How about it?

main1.line: This baby's got more horsepower than the other one, even if it's less reliable. She's still a good bike.

main2.line: Worried about your hair? Well, safety's the most important thing on the road, so you'd better hang on to this helmet.

main3.line: Boss, would you like to learn about motorcycles? I thought you might. Let's begin with starting the engine. First...

touch.line: Do you hear it, boss? The rumbling of her engine? She thirsts for the open road. What are you waiting for? Hop on! But don't forget your helmet.

unlock.line: Look, Boss, this is the new bike that Akashi sent me. She said she wanted me to be her brand ambassador... Doesn't that job sound badass?

battle.line: It's a maid's duty to remove her Master's obstacles!

detail.line: To perform a curtsy, a lady puts her feet across each other like— Forgive me, I failed to do it...

drop_descrip.line: Edinburgh-class light cruiser – Belfast.

expedition.line: Master, the ladies have returned from their commission and are waiting for you.

feeling1.line: You are more troublesome than a kitchen stain, Master.

feeling2.line: There are so many ships here... Master, does "commander" refer to an incredibly wealthy person who owns a shipyard?

feeling3.line: Do I feel nervous? Well, Master is a nice person, and none of the ladies here are merchant ships, so I have nothing to be nervous about.

feeling4.line: I now completely understand how you think, Master... Umm, is this what's known as "empathy"? No, perhaps it's just overly easy to understand you, Master...

feeling5.line: Master, do you think I will be a lady worthy of you, when I grow up?

home.line: Are you hungry, Master? I'm feeling quite peckish. Shall we eat together?

hp_warning.line: Master, perhaps it would be a good idea to retreat...?

login.line: Master, would you like some tea?

lose.line: A lady must be elegant, even in defeat... *Sob*...

mail.line: Master, would you like me to leave this letter here...?

main1.line: You'd like whiskey and coffee... Umm, d-do you not drink tea...?

main2.line: Master, is there anything you would like me to do?

main3.line: Master, neglecting your commander duties is a big no-no!

mission.line: Master, should you really let all these mission documents pile up...?

mission_complete.line: The mission rewards are here. If I prove to be of service to you, will I receive rewards too?

profile.line: I am Belfast, born in Harland and Wolff. Yes, the same place as the Titanic. I actually have an older sister. She hasn't taken care of me very much, however... Umm, that's all I was going to say. Master, what type of person are you?

propose.line: Does this mean you "approve of me"? Thank you, Master. However... if I wear this ring, people may get the wrong idea about you... P-perhaps you should think this through more thoroughly?

skill.line: Dear enemies, this is going to be a liiiittle bit painful.

touch.line: Master, you'll end up a failure if you rely on others too often. Sometimes, you must— Mmh, you leave me no choice. I-I won't help you next time, okay...?

touch2.line: Don't worry, Master. Even if you go to prison, I will still bring you your meals.

unlock.line: My Master is also a commander... Umm, so the commander is a captain of a ship? I don't quite understand, but... I will stay here for a while if you don't mind. I am Belfast, maid-in-training. It is a pleasure to serve you.

upgrade.line: I'm not quite used to fighting, but please have faith in me.

win_mvp.line: This isn't... anything to brag about. Isn't that right, Master?

battle.line: Such a lovely day. Let's get this pointless fighting over with quickly.

detail.line: You'll have to get a bit closer if you want to share this umbrella.

drop_descrip.line: Southampton-class light cruiser – Newcastle (HMS Newcastle.)

expedition.line: A familiar scent rolls in on the sea breeze... the girls are back. Shall we head out to greet them together?

feeling1.line: I have trouble keeping people at a distance. I apologize if this has caused any misunderstandings between us.

feeling2.line: Rest assured. I will perform my duties to your expectations.

feeling3.line: The weather report says rain today. Do bring an umbrella if you need to go out.

feeling4.line: Your smile reminds me of the wind in my hometown... it's that warm, westerly breeze. Hehehe.

feeling5.line: If you take your eyes off me, you never know when I might take up my umbrella... and fly away with the wind♪

home.line: Welcome home. Let me take your coat... You're unharmed, thank goodness.

hp_warning.line: Phew... It's a good thing I bought that insurance.

login.line: Would you rather have a cup of coffee, a spot of tea, or a splash of pale ale before work?

lose.line: I've brought such trouble upon you once again... what a dreadful shame.

mail.line: Mail for you... Do you think perhaps it's from me?

main1.line: While I may not have as many battle commendations as my younger sisters, I'm confident none of them know how to enjoy life quite like I do.

main2.line: I'm no good at these cat and mouse games. Sigh... Why don't you just have a seat and we'll talk like normal people...?

main3.line: Everyone comes into this world with all kinds of hopes and dreams... But not everyone will lead a life full of adventure and surprises.

mission.line: It's work that must be done, but we can do it at your pace.

mission_complete.line: Hard work is not always well rewarded... But it seems this time at least, luck was on our side.

profile.line: I am Newcastle of the Southampton subclass of Town-class light cruisers. While my record is one of the longest, I also somehow had the most free time... It would be nice if I could make it to retirement safely this time as well.

propose.line: ...It's remarkable how you've turned this ordinary, quiet life into something so unforgettable... Aah... I feel like my heart is about to beat out of my chest with happiness and satisfaction. How will I ever be the same again...?

skill.line: Glory to the ordinary, the commonplace!

touch.line: It's like... a couple of small animals playing with each other. Hehe!

touch2.line: ...You like my soft bits so much, do you? Now then, what if I were to give you a nice, soft, satisfying embrace?

unlock.line: I thought I had gotten lost, but how fortunate that I ran into you. I am the Town-class light cruiser, Newcastle. Thank you for looking after my sisters.

upgrade.line: Mmm... feels so warm.

win_mvp.line: This victory drink is a bit strong for me... I think I'd better hand it off to you.

detail.line: There are always interesting things happening here at the port. I can feel my quiet, ordinary life slipping farther and farther away... Of course, that's not to say this lifestyle is all that bad.

drop_descrip.line: This outfit makes me stand out a bit too much... But, as long as it makes you happy, I'm just as pleased.

home.line: Are you tired after all that...? Then let me service you with a powerful healing hug.

login.line: I've prepared a barley tea for you today. Now then, steel yourself, and give the day's work all you've got.

main1.line: Do we have time to call up my sisters to join us for some teppanyaki?

main2.line: It's nice I can push all the maid work onto my sisters, but spending the whole day reading a book by myself is a tad dull...

main3.line: I've heard summertime is when you see a certain type of rose blooming... But I'm not sure if our port has that particular rose?

touch.line: It's what it is... But if you keep at this, my outfit is going to get ruined...

touch2.line: If it's the outfit you're interested in... Sigh... I suppose it's too late to stop you at this point?

unlock.line: This outfit makes me stand out a bit too much... But, as long as it makes you happy, I'm just as pleased.

battle.line: Let's get the senseless violence over with, and then have ourselves a picnic.

drop_descrip.line: I've got an all new outfit here. Does it please you...? Hehe, seeing you all giddy like that is going to rub off on me as well.

home.line: Welcome home. Would you like dinner, a bath, or would you like... A nice, soft hug?

main1.line: My quiet, peaceful life has been riled like these waves, and you need to take responsibility for that.

main2.line: ...All your staring at me is quite a big hindrance to my work. If you have something you need from me, maybe you could wait until I'm finished?

main3.line: Looking to the future has never been one of my skills... Do you think you could take care of this one for me?

touch.line: In the interests of fairness, I think I should be toying with you next time?

touch2.line: ...Don't you think you'll regret it if you keep going?

unlock.line: I've got an all new outfit here. Does it please you...? Hehe, seeing you all giddy like that is going to rub off on me as well.

battle.line: Let us bring victory and glory to our honourable Master!

detail.line: My honourable Master, what would you like to learn more about today? Literature and culture? Logistics and strategy? The fine arts? Or, perhaps, you are more interested in more... carnal knowledge...?

drop_descrip.line: Dido-class light cruiser – Sirius.

expedition.line: My honourable Master, I have information regarding the results of a commission, so please relocate to the sofa and get in a relaxing position.

feeling1.line: ...I implore you to be more honourable, my slightly disappointing Master.

feeling2.line: I take honour in my service to you, Master. However, should you find my service unsatisfactory in any way compared to the Head Maid, I kindly ask of you to tell me.

feeling3.line: To me, there is nothing more honourable than to have the privilege of serving you, my honourable Master.

feeling4.line: If you find my embrace to be relieving, then I would gladly do so again at your command, my honourable Master.

feeling5.line: I ask of you to stand proud and illuminate all the world with your glorious image, my honourable Master...!

home.line: It is good to see you return. There is tea and a light meal prepared for you. And, if you'll pardon my initiative, I have also prepared a creep... a crêpe. Would you like to have it now?

hp_warning.line: As the Masters maid, I shall not be defeated!

login.line: It is good to see you return, my honourable Master.

lose.line: How shameful... My honourable Master, it seems I have made a mess of myself. Please give this naughty maid her due punishment.

mail.line: My honourable Master, the mail is here.

main1.line: "Cleaning"...? If it is combat you are referring to, then I vow to meet all expectations you set for me, my honourable Master.

main2.line: Regardless of what may ever happen, I shall always accompany you, my honourable Master.

main3.line: Achieving a balanced diet is essential for one's health. Therefore, although my cooking skill may be unsatisfactory to you, please do not forgo the meals I prepare, my honourable Master.

mission.line: A mission of this magnitude is inconsequential. Isn't that correct, my honourable Master?

mission_complete.line: My honourable Master, the mission rewards have arrived.

profile.line: I am Sirius, the 5th ship in the 2nd group of the Royal Navy's Dido-class of light cruisers. I participated in Operation Pedestal in the past, but now I serve as a Royal Maid and have the privilege of fighting for my honourable Master.

propose.line: Oh, the bliss of getting to make this wondrous vow... Please, close your eyes for this unseemly maid and permit her to feel your warmth... My honourable Master...

skill.line: My honourable Master, please grant me strength!

touch.line: Please refrain from intimate contact while others can see us, my honourable Master.

touch2.line: If you wish for me to service you tonight, then... M-my apologies! I made a rather careless assumption...

unlock.line: It is an honour to meet you. I am Sirius of the Royal Maids, here to assume the position. Henceforth, Master, I shall serve you to protect your glory and your beliefs.

upgrade.line: My honourable Master, I shall become even more gorgeous for you.

win_mvp.line: My honourable Master, I have cleared the path so that you may move forward.

detail.line: No matter what clothing I wear, I am still your maid and live only to fulfill your expectations, my honourable Master.

drop_descrip.line: My dear, I changed into the new outfit as per your request. I would be most grateful were you to offer me words of praise, Master.

feeling5.line: Whether it's under the swirling lights of the ballroom stage, or in the smoke and explosions of the battlefield, there will never be anything more radiant than you in my eyes. My honourable Master, please allow me to gaze upon you and be at your side, always...

home.line: There is no greater happiness than your safe return, Master. Would you like to gather everyone to have tea?

main1.line: Every single maid dreams of being able to stand beside her master in such a dress... Please forgive me for my presumptuousness...

main2.line: This dress seems ill-suited for combat... but since it is your wish, Master, I shall humbly carry out your will.

main3.line: This necklaces suits me well...? Thank you for praising this unworthy maid, my honourable Master.

touch.line: Oh, my Master who has intoxicated me with passions so, it is an honour to have been chosen as your dance partner.

unlock.line: My dear, I changed into the new outfit as per your request. I would be most grateful were you to offer me words of praise, Master.

detail.line: Worry not, for I have come prepared for every occasion. Food, drinks, magazines, sunscreen, contingency combat armaments, life-saving equipment, and... a cat? Why are you here? ...Oh, umm, I was just talking to myself!

drop_descrip.line: I've received ample advice from my colleagues in the Maid Team regarding swimwear etiquette. My honourable Master, are you pleased with my appearance?

login.line: No matter where we are, I shall do my utmost to keep you safe. My honourable Master, simply enjoy yourself, however you please.

main1.line: My honourable Master, why are you staring at me so intently? Did this humble maid err somewhere?! ...I'm overthinking things...?

main2.line: Swimming? If... if you wouldn't mind teaching me... Um, sorry, a lowly maid has no right to request your valuable time...

main3.line: My honourable Master, are you tired? Something to rest on...? ...Um, if you wouldn't mind, then... feel free to use my body...!

touch.line: My honourable Master, allow me to protect you from the sun.

touch2.line: Understood. If you would like to see me in a bikini, then... Is, is that so? I'm terribly sorry... I prematurely jumped to conclusions yet again.

unlock.line: I've received ample advice from my colleagues in the Maid Team regarding swimwear etiquette. My honourable Master, are you pleased with my appearance?

detail.line: I made some Dragon Empery dishes, however they turned out quite... Pl-Please, do not be concerned! *This* year, I vow to make delectable food that shall suit the honourable Master's palate!

drop_descrip.line: I have heard it is part of a maid's duties to dress to her honourable Master's liking over the holidays. Would this outfit happen to... satisfy the honourable Master's wishes?

home.line: My outfit is unsafe to wear in windy weather? Are you concerned with my wellbeing and would not want me catching a cold? Oh, honourable Master, your thoughtfulness humbles me!

login.line: Happy Lunar New Year, honourable Master. I have made a cup of tea for you.

main1.line: My honourable Master, if you'll forgive my asking, have you eaten any unusually shaped, unstuffed gyoza? ...P-Pardon me, I was merely wondering...

main2.line: This naughty maid is deeply obliged to have the privilege of spending the holidays with her honourable Master.

main3.line: nil

touch.line: My perceptive Master, would there happen to be dust clinging to my dress...?

touch2.line: If you wish me to service you in these Dragon Empery garments, then... Oh, my apologies! I've made yet another careless assumption...

unlock.line: I have heard it is part of a maid's duties to dress to her honourable Master's liking over the holidays. Would this outfit happen to... satisfy the honourable Master's wishes?

battle.line: We'll carry forth our tradition of "meeting our enemies head-on." Let's charge forward heroically!

detail.line: It is said that a woman's charm is greatest when in front of a lens... Commander, I trust that you'll bring out my best side~

drop_descrip.line: Ceres-class light cruiser - Curacoa (D41)

expedition.line: Shall I greet the girls who are returning from commissions?

feeling1.line: My apologies, but I believe it would be best if we maintained some distance.

feeling2.line: Would you like some snacks? My old students used to love these - please have some.

feeling3.line: Commander, would you like to come to my next lecture? It would be a great encouragement to all the girls.

feeling4.line: Sometimes, I think about what I would do if I had a day off from maid duties... Oh my, it seems that I can wholeheartedly focus on serving you today, Commander.

feeling5.line: Whether as a maid, or as your partner, I am happiest when you rely on me, Commander.... Hehe, this is today's snack. Please have some~

home.line: Good work during the sortie. Want to take a breather so you can think about your next step? There's plenty of time to spare, so make sure to cherish your health.

hp_warning.line: It's do or die... I have to go all out!

login.line: All the preparations are complete, Commander. Please give your orders - I will delegate tasks to ensure that our missions get finished.

lose.line: I've been thoroughly discredited...

mail.line: Mail has arrived. There appears to be no bad news anyway.

main1.line: A fly? Don't worry, they'll disappear after a few moments~

main2.line: To have a junior as exceptional as Belfast... I have to redouble my efforts~

main3.line: I have already cleaned the office, Commander. I would imagine that having a comfortable work environment is of great importance to you.

mission.line: It's not good to let missions pile up. Should I plan them out for you?

mission_complete.line: Commander, we should arrange to collect the mission rewards.

profile.line: I am Curacoa, light cruiser of the Royal Navy. I've served in several wars, so my combat experience is fairly rich. I hope that I'll be able to train some children to carry on our duty.

propose.line: Right now, I am convinced that there is nothing happier than being in your arms, Commander. Please take care of me from now on, my beloved Master~

skill.line: Please be at ease. I shall always be here~

touch.line: If there is anything you need, please call for me right away~

touch2.line: Are you trying to flirt with me? Perhaps... there might be a better place for that.

unlock.line: Though this is the first I'm meeting you, I can't help but to feel a sense of familiarity from the bottom of my heart... I am Curacoa - from now on, allow me handle the various affairs around port. Please look forward to it!

upgrade.line: My anti-air capabilities have been upgraded. Great~!

win_mvp.line: To think that I'd get MVP... sorry about that~

detail.line: This outfit's design is rather bold... I'm more accustomed to my maid uniform...

drop_descrip.line: As I am but a maid, it is a great honor to be able to wear such a gorgeous outfit… How do I look, Commander? "Not sure where to start feasting your eyes?" Oh my... Commander...

home.line: Holidays in the Dragon Empery seem to have a lot of complicated customs. Perhaps they are comparable with a Royal maid's code of etiquette? Hehe~

login.line: Commander, it's been a long time since you've been able to enjoy a moment of rest, hasn't it?

main1.line: My obligations as a maid do not end when I am not in my uniform. If you need anything, just let me know.

main2.line: Everyone is busy with Spring Festival preparations... but I'd like to take this opportunity to slack off a little~

main3.line: You'd like to know if there are any secrets behind the Dragon Empery's culinary and artistic crafts? Hehe, stay tuned~

touch.line: Commander, you want to rest in my lap? If you'd like, go ahead~

touch2.line: Commander, I see that you've also become quite bold.

unlock.line: As I am but a maid, it is a great honor to be able to wear such a gorgeous outfit… How do I look, Commander? "Not sure where to start feasting your eyes?" Oh my... Commander...

detail.line: Curley is always walking around with that stony expression... Maybe she and I have a different understanding of "how a maid ought to present herself?"

drop_descrip.line: It is my honour to be of everyone's service. Light cruiser Curacoa takes it upon herself to continue serving you, Master.

login.line: If you're still agonizing over today's itinerary, why not have have a cup of tea and reset yourself?

main1.line: Seeing everyone's growth and maturity... somehow puts my mind at ease.

main2.line: My abilities as an anti-air escort? Why, it's my next best thing, after being a maid of course.

main3.line: Being in a room that has been cleaned properly will also clean your mind of distractions.

touch.line: You may give me orders at any time, Master.

touch2.line: Why don't we save these kinds of things for... after work?

unlock.line: It is my honour to be of everyone's service. Light cruiser Curacoa takes it upon herself to continue serving you, Master.

battle.line: Let's show our enemies what a Royal maid is capable of.

detail.line: No matter the time or place, as a maid or as a soldier, one must always remember to observe proper etiquette.

drop_descrip.line: Ceres-class light cruiser - Curlew (D42)

expedition.line: Commander, a commission has returned. Please follow me to greet everyone who is returning. It's proper etiquette, after all.

feeling1.line: To think that there would be people who cannot comprehend Royal etiquette at all...

feeling2.line: The details make up the difference between success and failure, whether in etiquette or in battle. Commander, please remember to always be attentive to details.

feeling3.line: Please do not blame me for being too strict. Royal etiquette is not something can be easily mastered.

feeling4.line: Just like libations, there is a time and place for drinking black tea. What, you want to have tea right now...? F-fine.. since it's been so long since you've had a break, I suppose there's no harm to it...

feeling5.line: Being with you reminds me of the time I used to live with my sister. She'd always instruct me on how to be a prim and proper maid. I wonder if I've managed to become... an excellent maid just like her...

home.line: Good work, Commander. I've prepared tea today according to your instructions from earlier. Please enjoy.

hp_warning.line: T-trigger the anti-air defence alarm!

login.line: Welcome back, Commander. Your tie is crooked... let me fix it for you. Your otherwise refined attire cannot be taken seriously with such a flaw.

lose.line: It appears that I need to have higher expectations of myself.

mail.line: This mail is for you. Don't worry, I'll be sure to leave when you are ready to check it.

main1.line: Royal etiquette is steeped in social and life philosophy. Please keep that in mind at all times.

main2.line: I already am a perfect maid? Surely you jest... have you not met my elder sister yet?

main3.line: Lately, your etiquette has improved greatly. However, don't get too proud, Commander.

mission.line: A new mission has been posted. Please complete it as soon as possible - it's rude to keep others waiting.

mission_complete.line: A mission has been completed, but don't over-celebrate in an undignified manner, Commander.

profile.line: I am Curlew, one of the Royal Navy's Ceres-class light cruisers. C-class light cruiser? N-no, that's not the correct classification, please don't use that term anymore...

propose.line: Since I have already made my oath with you, it would be improper if I was the only one instructing you. What would I like you to teach me? ...Master, can you please... teach me the etiquette of "love"?

touch.line: Please be mindful of your posture. Be confident and stand tall so that you can earn the respect of others.

touch2.line: C-Commander... what is the meaning of this...

unlock.line: Greetings, I am your Royal maid, Curlew. The responsibility of supervising the master’s daily routine falls on the maid. I will help you become a Royal gentleman through and through, so please pay attention and work hard.

upgrade.line: I am one step closer to becoming a perfect Royal maid. Thank you, Commander.

win_mvp.line: As long as you strive for excellence, victory will naturally follow.

drop_descrip.line: You can feel the profound heritage and culture of the Dragon Empery from all these customs and outfits for the Lunar New Year's Festival… It seems to be ever more necessary to study the traditions and etiquette of this wondrous culture.

home.line: Good work, Commander. Today, would you like to try some tea from the Dragon Empery?

login.line: Welcome back, Commander. Today, I'll be visiting the girls from the Dragon Empery to learn a bit more about their customs. Would you like to come with me?

main1.line: Commander, even if you're just eating a pork bun, please make sure to use a serviette.

main2.line: Etiquette is closely linked to culture, so it's no surprise that there are many differences between the Royal Navy and the Dragon Empery.

main3.line: The girls from the Empery said that they'd be willing to teach me a few New Year's greetings. Once I've learned them, I'll be able to give you some blessings!

touch.line: For a Royal maid like myself to don the attire of the Dragon Empery... isn't this what cultural exchange is all about?

unlock.line: You can feel the profound heritage and culture of the Dragon Empery from all these customs and outfits for the Lunar New Year's Festival… It seems to be ever more necessary to study the traditions and etiquette of this wondrous culture.

detail.line: You've noticed my new fittings? Don't worry, they will not impact the execution of my duties as a maid.

drop_descrip.line: I am now more capable than ever of demonstrating the Royal Maids' style. Though I am not as talented as my sister Curacoa, I sincerely hope you will find my service satisfactory. It is a great honour to work for you.

home.line: You must be exhausted. I have prepared today's tea with your comfort in mind. A maid must always be aware of her master's condition, as well as mood. Relax, and enjoy. Hehehe.

main1.line: "To improve is to change. To be perfect is to change often..." One should bear this quotation in mind.

main2.line: Maintaining this new equipment takes significantly more time. I suppose that's the price of strength.

main3.line: To study etiquette is to pursue knowledge. "Only in properly managing oneself is one fit to lead others..." Let's move forward together, Master.

touch.line: I've made some adjustments to my outfit as suggested by the others. What do you think, Master?

touch2.line: M- Master, what are you... Aie?!

unlock.line: I am now more capable than ever of demonstrating the Royal Maids' style. Though I am not as talented as my sister, Curacoa, I sincerely hope you will find my service satisfactory. It is a great honour to work for you.

battle.line: All ships, forward...! Form up on me!

detail.line: Um, sorry I made such a mess... Sheffield tried to teach me how to clean, but I'm a lot worse at it than I expected... Ahaha...

drop_descrip.line: I am Swiftsure, a light cruiser of the Royal Navy... If it is not too much for one such as myself to ask, I would like to support your fleet in whatever way I can.

expedition.line: Commander, the commission is nearly complete. If you head out now, you should be able to meet them as they return.

feeling1.line: Someone like me deserves a Commander like this...

feeling2.line: Commander, do you have something for me? I can handle anything... Oh, but only if you're okay with me...

feeling3.line: Fiji is always telling me to smile more. Is she right? Oh... Sorry, I must be boring you with this...

feeling4.line: The Commander told me to help Jamaica fix up her bike. Hehehe, it turned out to be a lot more fun than I thought... Oh, Commander, sorry... about that... just now...

feeling5.line: I think I'd probably be better off being all cool like Sheffield than trying to smile all the time like Fiji... Right? If I every so often let slip a smile that could catch the Commander's eye... Oh, um, forget everything I said just now!

home.line: Excellent work. I've prepared a report for you. Take a moment to look it over.

hp_warning.line: I have to get the others to safety, at least...!

login.line: Good morning. Here is your work for the day... *Sigh*...

lose.line: Sorry. If only I had tried harder...

mail.line: Commander, you have new mail. Oh, I've been checking about once per hour. So I don't think I've... no, I haven't missed any.

main1.line: Commander, let's work as hard as we ever do, eh?

main2.line: Commander, do you think a Lady of the Royal Navy should be more elegant? Not like the maids, I mean Fiji and Jamaica... They stand out quite a bit... is that alright?

main3.line: I envy the Knight Commander. If only I could comport myself so... Sorry about that. Forget I said anything.

mission.line: Commander, I've finished sorting out these tasks. Do look them over.

mission_complete.line: Commander, I've finished tallying up the mission rewards. Do look them over.

profile.line: I am Swiftsure, of the Royal Navy. I joined towards the end of the war, but with it winding down and fate taking some odd twists and turns, I wasn't able to perform as expected. If it pleases you, I will serve the fleet with everything I have. Oh, but if it doesn't, you need not worry about me...

propose.line: I'm really sorry about all this. Are you honestly okay with someone like me...? The way I am...? Umm, if you're alright with me, then I'll gladly be your partner! Commander, thank you so much!

skill.line: Get the timing right... I should be able to do this!

touch.line: As your secretary ship, I am responsibile for everything in all of the reports.

touch2.line: Commander, um... I think fleet regulations call this kind of thing "inappropriate..."

unlock.line: I am Swiftsure, a light cruiser of the Royal Navy... If it is not too much for one such as myself to ask, I would like to support your fleet in whatever way I can.

upgrade.line: Swiftsure, swiftly and surely, everyone is counting on you...!

win_mvp.line: Um, I... really tried...

detail.line: Unicorn, this is how you do this problem... Oh sorry, Commander, I'm currently helping the others study. Please make yourself feel at home.

drop_descrip.line: Commander, why are you here...? Me? Yes, as you can see, I'm still studying... I figured that acquiring knowledge would be the best way to make up for my lack of experience on the actual battlefield.

login.line: Good morning. Here is the outline for today's course. Please make sure to review it.

mail.line: Commander, you have new mail. I've instructed the Manjuus to help fetch the mail for me even when I can't do it myself, so worry not.

main1.line: Fiji, don't you know that studying is good for you? Come on, Commander, care to back me up on this one?

main2.line: While I have served as a flagship before, that has nothing to do with what's going on now. I have to be humble and learn from everyone.

main3.line: I often see Edinburgh in the library. She's always grumbling about what's going on in the maid team or something...

touch.line: I look cute when wearing glasses...? Err... Um, that wasn't my intention...

touch2.line: Commander, I d-don't think you should be doing this at school... Ahh!

unlock.line: Commander, why are you here...? Me? Yes, as you can see, I'm still studying... I figured that acquiring knowledge would be the best way to make up for my lack of experience on the actual battlefield.

home.line: I just made a snowman with the others... Huh? Did you want to see it, Commander? Um, in that case... Oh, right! That snowman already got knocked down and remade into something else! You shouldn't look at the one I made...

login.line: Happy Lunar New Year, Commander. Why don't you set aside your work today and take some time off?

main1.line: Um, are you redecorating the office? Do you need me to help?

main2.line: I got some red envelopes as gifts from my seniors in the fleet. Ahaha... I'm not sure how I feel about this...

main3.line: Commander, the more free time everyone else has, the less free time you seem to― Um, oh my...

touch.line: If you're cold, p-please... feel free to use my shawl.

touch2.line: C-Commander... What if someone sees us...?!

unlock.line: I agreed to try on this outfit, but... I know these fancy outfits don't suit me... H-huh, I look gorgeous?! ...Thank you very much. Even if you're just trying to make me feel better, I appreciate it...

battle.line: Take a deep breath, Swiftsure... Everyone, please commence attack on the enemy!

detail.line: So I need to put this headband on... I wonder what kind of hairstyle would be good? Um, let's tie my hair up like this... Actually, maybe twintails would be better instead?

drop_descrip.line: W-welcome! ...Ugh, I'm still way too nervous... Ah, um! H-how may I serve you today, Commander...?

home.line: Welcome back, Commander. If... If you'd like, please enjoy this refreshing beverage...

login.line: Commander, what will your first order be?

mail.line: Commander, there's new mail for you. I apologize, but I didn't have the time to check its contents beforehand. If it's alright with you, I'd like to check the contents with you, right now...!

main1.line: Commander, is something wrong? ...Is this outfit really too stimulating, like Sheffield said it was...? Or... is it actually too conservative, like Fiji said it was...?

main2.line: Everyone acts much more freely when they're at the beach. Do you think I should do the same? A-Alright, I'll give it a try... Y-Yo!

main3.line: When I'm helping Neptune, I feel like a completely different person. ...Oh. What would you like to have, Commander?

touch.line: Um... This outfit really is quite embarrassing...

touch2.line: ...Eek! C-Commander...!

unlock.line: W-welcome! ...Ugh, I'm still way too nervous... Ah, um! H-how may I serve you today, Commander...?

battle.line: Show them neither mercy nor pity...

detail.line: I am the Longbow of Crécy, and the Shield of the Realm... By your will, I am at your disposal.

drop_descrip.line: Bellona-class light cruiser – Black Prince.

expedition.line: Ah! Commander, I think the commission team is back.

feeling1.line: Commander, are you my... enemy?

feeling2.line: Commander, do you have something for me? I'm sure I can handle it.

feeling3.line: Commander, why are you laughing? Did something funny happen? Won't you please tell me too?

feeling4.line: You like sweet girls, do you, Commander? Well... hrrmm... What if I were to hug you like this? Would that make me seem sweeter?

feeling5.line: I'm very important to you, am I, Commander? ... Now what am I supposed to do with that? Treat you even sweeter than I do now?

home.line: Welcome back, Commander. Did you have a good fight?

hp_warning.line: Do I carry on? Or do I retreat?

login.line: Commander, back again same time as always, eh?

lose.line: I failed... No, it can't be...

mail.line: Mail call? I wonder what it is? Could it be your dismissal?

main1.line: A Maid? Me? Certainly not... But I do know how to make some simple dishes, and I suppose I could bring you some tea.

main2.line: I can see the water from here. Commander, do you like the ocean?

main3.line: Commander, are you daydreaming? What say... I join you and we daydream together?

mission.line: Dereliction of duty is grounds for court-martial... Maybe you should see to those missions?

mission_complete.line: I sorted through the mission rewards, but I'm not sure I did it right...

profile.line: I am a modified Dido-class... rather was it Bellona-class? ... Right then, you could say I'm quite well-travelled. Will you be sending me all over the world too?

propose.line: The way you treasure me gives me such warmth and solace... This is what true happiness is, isn't it? Commander, please, I beg you, let us share in even more happiness...

touch.line: Commander? Something about my body caught your attention, did it?

touch2.line: Commander, does that feel nice to... touch?

unlock.line: Err, you're... the Commander, yes? You don't know who I am? Ah, right, I've yet to introduce myself... I'm Black Prince of the Royal Navy... Will that suffice?

upgrade.line: Commander, have I really grown stronger?

win_mvp.line: They're a fleet of smouldering hulks... Not a single one left afloat.

battle.line: You dare disturb the Commander's vacation? You won't get away with that.

detail.line: Oh, is it that time already? I've prepared a few simple dishes. Commander, shall we invite the others to join us?

drop_descrip.line: Sorry to keep you waiting, Commander. Thank you very much for taking me on vacation. Standing in front of you like this... is a little embarrassing... Nevertheless, what do you think of... my swimsuit?

home.line: What's wrong, Commander? Are you still preoccupied with work?

login.line: I didn't think this swimsuit stood out, so I was surprised when you still found me right away...

mail.line: It's the mail? Don't tell me our vacation is over already...

main1.line: The sea is a tempestuous battlefield, and yet the beach is a relaxing Eden. What an incredible duality.

main2.line: Beach volleyball? I've heard it's quite fun. Do you think I could give it a try?

main3.line: The sand is so soft, so fine. It feels so pleasant between my toes...

touch.line: Are you tired, Commander?

touch2.line: Commander, the others are still here.

unlock.line: Sorry to keep you waiting, Commander. Thank you very much for taking me on vacation. Standing in front of you like this... is a little embarrassing... Nevertheless, what do you think of... my swimsuit?

detail.line: Too much sitting wears out one's legs. Stretching out like this... Aahhh, yes, that's much better.

drop_descrip.line: A "qipao," is it? This legendary dress from the Dragon Empery... Putting it on and enjoying some nostalgic music, makes me... Ahhh... Commander, might we relax like this a bit longer...?

home.line: The kitchen sure seems busy. What's going on... in there?

login.line: Commander, welcome home. Ooh, I just realized. I should probably be saying "Happy Lunar New Year," shouldn't I?

mail.line: Mail call... Must be some festival greetings? You're quite popular, Commander.

main1.line: Commander... Do you enjoy such nostalgic music?

main2.line: Hah... How should I spend this holiday? I think listening to music like this is quite nice... Aahh...

main3.line: It's a holiday. No need to move, no need to fight... Now why not make every day a holiday?

touch.line: Mmm... why not stretch out with me, Commander?

touch2.line: Is this... a festival custom?

unlock.line: A "qipao," is it? So this legendary dress from the Dragon Empery... Putting it on and enjoying some nostalgic music, makes me... Ahhh... Commander, might we relax like this a bit longer...?

battle.line: Disappear, like a fleeting bubble...!

detail.line: Um, sorry I got champagne all over you. I really feel bad about it... Next time, I'll be more careful.

drop_descrip.line: You can't have a party without champagne, right? Now, if I remember right, you're meant to give it a good shake before popping the cork... Oh no! Look out, Commander!

feeling5.line: The way to treat those important to you... is to cherish them, and share all your joys and sorrows with them, right? Mm, I'm glad to be sharing all my joy with you right now.

home.line: Another victory? Mm, then another bottle is in order... Huh, what do you mean I don't need to pop so many?

login.line: Commander... Would you like some champagne? Don't worry, I know how much strength to put into it this time.

mail.line: Mail? Is it... a party invite? We're already at the party though...

main1.line: Dido and Sirius seem to be busy with something... Should I go help out too?

main2.line: If every day was a party and there was no fighting to be seen... that would be a pretty nice world.

main3.line: You're not supposed to shake the champagne bottle if you're trying to drink from it normally, huh... I see...

mission.line: What do you think the punishment for forgetting about your missions should be... One glass, or one bottle?

touch.line: Want another glass? Mm, coming right up~

touch2.line: Commander, are you drunk? What's the matter? Your hand's all hot.

unlock.line: You can't have a party without champagne, right? Now, if I remember right, you're meant to give it a good shake before popping the cork... Oh no! Look out, Commander!

win_mvp.line: Shall I uncork a bottle to celebrate the victory?

detail.line: Um, want to talk about something? Uh... I'm not exactly a great conversation starter, but... Huh, just go with the flow?

drop_descrip.line: Oh... Welcome, Commander. Can I take your order...? Or maybe, you just wanted to kick back and relax? ...Either way is fine with me.

home.line: Commander, why don't you put your head down on the counter and take a nap?

login.line: I had Hermione prepare some hot tea beforehand. Feel free to have some if you're feeling worn out.

main1.line: You'd like me to mix a drink? ...I'm not sure I can do that... but I can serve pre-made stuff...

main2.line: You're not the only one who comes to unwind. Sometimes other shipgirls stop by, and if memory serves me properly, there are some real heavyweights who can down an entire mug like it's nothing...

main3.line: What's it like... to get sloshed? Do your eyes get all spinny? ...It's like, you're in a waking dream...?

touch.line: Want something to drink, Commander? I can only do the pre-made stuff though...

touch2.line: Are you sloshed? Maybe you should get in touch with Dido and the others...?

unlock.line: Oh... Welcome, Commander. Can I take your order...? Or maybe, you just wanted to kick back and relax? ...Either way is fine with me.

battle.line: I will "clean up" the pests that seek to disrupt this concert.

detail.line: Call you Producer? No thank you, Master works just fine for me. Or... would you prefer to be called a "pest?"

drop_descrip.line: I am Sheffield, from the Royal Maids. I will explain how this transpired to you, so please stop looking like the world has turned upside down.

expedition.line: Do I need to pre-record a gunshot to remind you? ...A commission fleet has returned.

feeling1.line: To prevent harm from befalling the other members, I shall first eliminate you.

feeling2.line: I've had to suspend maid duties due to my idol unit activities. I will make up for lost time after this is done.

feeling3.line: I'm playing very well? Master, you are able to follow in my footsteps as well... as long as you dedicate yourself to practicing every day.

feeling4.line: I used to think that doing maid work would make other jobs seem trivial in comparison, but reality certainly had a very different message for me... If you dare tell anyone else about what I just said to you, I'll have to sew your lips together... Just kidding, don't take it that seriously.

feeling5.line: The girl who you like is not the maid or the shining star, but "Sheffield?" ...A stale confession, but thank you. I'll remember that.

home.line: Ah, Master, welcome back~ You heard a weird voice, you say? It must've been your imagination.

hp_warning.line: I still have a contingency plan.

login.line: I finished cleaning up the office before I have to head off for lessons. I'd appreciate it if you don't mess it up while I'm gone.

lose.line: This failure was due to my incompetence. Sincerest apologies.

mail.line: There's new mail. I'll make sure to respond to the fanmail.

main1.line: I heard that there are some folks out there who get aroused from being abused by their favorite idol... I'll never understand.

main2.line: Defeating enemies with song? Utterly unrealistic, but might make for an interesting school project.

main3.line: To be honest, I'm a bit jealous of Belfast. Her talents are boundless, beyond just being a maid.

mission.line: A new offer? I shall prepare myself then.

mission_complete.line: So these are the royalties? I'm sure the other members will be pleased.

profile.line: Town-class light cruiser, Sheffield. I am currently serving as an idol at Her Majesty's request. Do you have a problem with that?

propose.line: No matter what I am, I will always love you with all my heart and soul, my Master. ...I wasn't being facetious. Really.

skill.line: May my song bring you eternal rest...

touch.line: I may not have my gun with me, but you would still be wise to mind your conduct.

touch2.line: Surely you're aware of the consequences for doing such things to an idol?

unlock.line: I am Sheffield, from the Royal Maids. I will explain how this transpired to you, so please stop looking like the world has turned upside down.

upgrade.line: I shall commit myself fully regardless of the workplace.

win_mvp.line: The concert went well.

battle.line: Flagship... is it? I, I can do this!

detail.line: Never thought the story would turn out like this! Cannot wait for next week's issue... Huh?! M-Master! Ahem! How may I help you?

drop_descrip.line: Southampton-class light cruiser - Glasgow (C-21)

expedition.line: The commission fleet has returned. Please remember to welcome them back.

feeling1.line: Would you please be so kind as to maintain a distance of at least three metres from my person so that I may properly carry out my duties as a maid, "Master?"

feeling2.line: You should rest if you're feeling tired... Th-think about those of us working for you.

feeling3.line: Master, I've brought you a change of fresh white linens... You'd prefer green, like the color of my eyes? I, I see...

feeling4.line: You'd like to see me in my casual attire? D-didn't you say I'd look cute in anything? I'll leave it to your imagination then~

feeling5.line: I made your bed, warmed your sheets, and ye ended up working all night anyway... Oh no, I'm not mad in the slightest. Hard work is to be praised, after all~

home.line: That'll do. Take a rest now.

hp_warning.line: tha...that's it?

login.line: Welcome back, Master. I've prepared tea.

lose.line: Have to think on that one... Don't wanna lose again.

mail.line: Looks like we got new mail. I'll grab it.

main1.line: Newcastle, ye ask? She's like a big sister and that's all I have to say to you... nothing else!

main2.line: Sheffy's got a sharp tongue, but really she's a sweet lassie.

main3.line: You wouldn't happen to like manga or...? N-never mind. Forget I asked.

mission.line: A new mission is here. Please check it soon.

mission_complete.line: The rewards are here. I'll put 'em away for ye.

propose.line: And so I thank God for bestowing upon me the gift of our meeting... And we're done, eh? Time to go home...? Huh? S-seal the vow with a k-kiss?! B-but... I...!

touch.line: You have something for me?

touch2.line: Ah?! I-I must be going...!

upgrade.line: Aye. I shall redouble my efforts.

win_mvp.line: Phew... That'd be enough for ye now, eh?

detail.line: Enterprise? I know her. We fought together at the Bay of Biscay, eh? Huh? There's another Enterprise...? I-I knew that!

drop_descrip.line: Y-ye said ye wanted ta see me wear something different, so... But this is not "cosplay" or somesuch! I do actually go to school...! D-do ye like it?

expedition.line: Commission team's back. I'll go get 'em.

main1.line: What's for lunch? How's this lunchbox here sound to ye? Just a little something I made meself...

main2.line: That Z23 from the Iron Blood's got a talent for teaching. Teacher or no. Not that I need the help.

main3.line: Borrowed this one from Ranger. Gotta finish it soon. It's the sequel to a story I've been waiting for.

unlock.line: Y-ye said ye wanted ta see me wear something different, so... But this is not "cosplay" or somesuch! I do actually go to school...! D-do ye like it?

battle.line: The enemy's been detected~

expedition.line: Commander, let's put our work on hold and go to greet the team that's just returned from commissions.

feeling1.line: Commander, why are you so stubborn...

feeling2.line: Doesn't Dido worry a bit... too much? She works so hard, and I know you don't hate her, but... please, watch over her some more, Commander.

feeling3.line: Commander, are you working overtime today? Then I'll bring over some coffee. ...Um, it's not a bother, you know? After all, being by your side no matter what is a Royal Maid's duty.

feeling4.line: Commander, if it doesn't bother you, would you mind leaving your laundry to me? Washing our clothes together saves time, but more than that, I want you to personally feel how great your clothes feel after being hand-washed by the Royal Maids♪

feeling5.line: Whew... I've finished cleaning the room. Next... Oh, welcome back. I'll prepare your meal right now, so please wait a moment, Commander.

home.line: Commander. For the time being, you're forbidden from doing more work, okay? You need to make sure to take a break from now and then.

hp_warning.line: It seems I let my guard down...

login.line: Good morning, Commander. Did you sleep well?

lose.line: Oh my, what a failure...

mail.line: Is this mail for you, Commander...? I apologize. I'll leave it here.

main1.line: It's not good to strain yourself by overworking. How about splashing some water on your face to refresh yourself?

main2.line: It seems like the price for this ingredient has gone up... Commander, from now on, we'll have fewer dishes that use this.

main3.line: Commander, watching you easily handle your work makes me feel happy... I wonder why?

mission.line: Commander, the more you don't deal with your work now, the more you'll have to deal with later.

mission_complete.line: This mission's reward is quite sizeable. Congratulations, Commander!

profile.line: I'm Hermione, a Dido-class ship belonging to the Royal Navy. In the past... I chased after Bismarck and participated in anti-submarine warfare in Sardegna... Besides that, there's nothing worth mentioning. Commander, do you have any questions?

propose.line: You'd like for me to stay by your side, forever...? Of course, Commander. Taking care of you is my job, after all. Ah, would this be what's called a "confession"...? Yes, of course. Commander, I'll be in your care, from now, 'til the end of time.

touch.line: A fizzy drink? ...What am I going to do with you? I suppose you can have just one bottle, all right?

touch2.line: Commander, it's good to pay attention to the time and place when doing something like this, you know?

unlock.line: Good day. I am Hermione, from the Royal Maids. I'm delighted to make your acquaintance, Commander.

upgrade.line: My, have I gotten stronger?

win_mvp.line: I'm sure Commander will be elated~

detail.line: Commander... Even ships can get sick. Please, make sure to take care of yourself, alright?

drop_descrip.line: My, what brings you here, Commander? Are you feeling unwell? That's no good... Why don't you come sit over here first? I'll start by taking your temperature...

home.line: Commander, please wait there for a moment. I'm examining someone else right now...

login.line: Hm? Commander, what brings you back here...? Umm, are you here to be... inspected?

main1.line: Gosh, Commander... If you pretend to be sick, even I'm going to get mad at you!

main2.line: Commander, don't you think this dress is a bit too small for me...? Um... I just feel like it doesn't fit me...

main3.line: Commander, please make sure that you pay attention to your own health. After all, I can't attend to you around the clock.

touch.line: Commander, let me perform an examination on you. Please come here and lie down on your side.

touch2.line: Are we... playing doctor?

unlock.line: My, what brings you here, Commander? Are you feeling unwell? That's no good... Why don't you come sit over here first? I'll start by taking your temperature...

detail.line: Actually... I bought this swimsuit back when it was on sale. I'm relieved that you like it...

drop_descrip.line: Commander, I've brought the chair. If you don't want to get in the water, feel free to sit here. ...Hm, me? Of course, I will remain by your side.

home.line: I've prepared a cool, refreshing drink for you. Please enjoy.

login.line: Commander, please leave work at the office, and relax to your heart's content today.

main1.line: These waves feel so nice~ Why don't you dip your feet in too, Commander? ...Hm? A big wave is... Eek!

main2.line: Overexposure to the sun isn't good for your skin. Why don't we move somewhere else in a little bit?

main3.line: A nap? Y-yes! Please take your time and relax to your heart's content. If something happens, hm... don't worry, I'll make sure you wake up when that happens.

touch.line: Wow, the sea is so pretty~ ...Hmm? I'm even prettier than the sea...? Jeez, Commander... Don't get all sappy on me now.

unlock.line: Commander, I've brought the chair. If you don't want to get in the water, feel free to sit here. ...Hm, me? Of course, I will remain by your side.

detail.line: I changed into slightly more formal attire in preparation for us having afternoon tea together. Do you think... it doesn't suit me well...?

drop_descrip.line: Would you care for some afternoon tea, Commander? Heehee~ This is one of my little hobbies when I'm not performing my maid duties.

home.line: Before you continue with your work, please enjoy a delicious slice of cake and unwind a little~

login.line: I've finished brewing the tea. Commander, do be careful, as it is very hot.

main1.line: A while ago, Miss Belfast recommended these delicious and economical snacks. Commander, are they to your liking?

main2.line: The first thing that comes to mind when one speaks of "elegance" must surely be Miss Illustrious or Miss Hood. Oh, you'd include me as well? Hehe, I'm honoured~

main3.line: Commander, I see you've finally managed to relax a bit. I suppose inviting you for afternoon tea turned out to be very fruitful after all~

touch.line: Hm? You'd like another serving of tea? Sure, here you go~ Please let me know if there's anything you want~

unlock.line: Would you care for some afternoon tea, Commander? Heehee~ This is one of my little hobbies when I'm not performing my maid duties.

detail.line: My fellow Royal Maids drew inspiration from the Dragon Empery's traditional attire when crafting these clothes. I do hope you like them.

drop_descrip.line: How are you feeling, Commander? Hehe, I'm not wearing my usual nurse's gown right now, but I suppose this isn't much different~

expedition.line: The commission team has brought back some quality herbs! I propose that we have some herb tea to celebrate.

feeling1.line: There has to be a cure for you out there somewhere... You're not beyond saving yet, I know it!

feeling5.line: Commander, how are you feeling today? I won't be giving you any medicine, but since food and medicine have the same root, I'll make sure to prepare some nutritious meals that you're sure to enjoy. Please leave it to me~♪

home.line: Breathing in these herbal fragrances is quite good for you. Commander, please feel free to relax.

mail.line: New mail has arrived. Did they procure the ingredients I asked for?

main1.line: It is often said that the best medicine is bitter, but I tried to make mine as sweet as possible to suit your tastes.

main2.line: I wonder what kinds of effects these herbs have... I should ask Dido later.

main3.line: I am quite proficient at following recipes and preparing ingredients. They're skills I often use as part of my work with the Royal Maids.

touch.line: Might you be... checking my pulse?

touch2.line: Commander...

unlock.line: How are you feeling, Commander? Hehe, I'm not wearing my usual nurse's gown right now, but I suppose this isn't much different~

detail.line: I never dreamed that I'd get to meet you as I wear this dress, Commander. I'm so, so very happy...

drop_descrip.line: I'm so happy to have come this far with you, Commander. May this gorgeous sunrise watch over us for all time... I love you, Commander.

feeling5.line: Hmhm~? The room's all cleaned, time for... Oh, welcome back, Commander. I'll prepare your meal right away, so please wait a bit longer~

home.line: Thank you for your hard work, Commander. Make sure to monitor your work-life balance. Otherwise, I may find a way to force you to rest... Hehehe♪

login.line: Commander, you look well. Is there anything at all I can help you with?

main1.line: Caring for your health, treasuring our life together... It doesn't feel like things have changed much, does it? I guess we've been the perfect team for a long time now.

main2.line: I've heard that spoiling people too much can make them lazy... But you'd never be lazy, Commander! Umm, so... It's okay to let me pamper you once in a while, okay?

main3.line: Commander, take it easy whenever you want to. I like you most when you're smiling without a care in the world♪

touch.line: Are you tired? You may rest your head in my lap, Commander.

touch2.line: M-may I seek your warmth, too...?

unlock.line: I'm so happy to have come this far with you, Commander. May this gorgeous sunrise watch over us for all time... I love you, Commander.

battle.line: Now, to steal Master's heart... with my dance!

detail.line: Between my idol lessons and shows, training and my maid duties, all to be useful to you, Master... It's a lot of work? You want to reduce my workload...? P- please don't throw me away...!

drop_descrip.line: I am the light cruiser, Dido, currently taking part in idol activities as part of the experimental Muse System. I learned more or less what idols are supposed to do from the others, so p-please... keep a close eye on me!

expedition.line: Tashkent tells me the commission team is back.

feeling1.line: Did I let you down, Master? What a despicable maid I am...

feeling2.line: No longer a maid serving her master, I'm now an idol.I've learned so much from the other maids, but I'm still not sure if I can do this right...

feeling3.line: I look good in my idol outfit? Thank you so much, Master...! Oh, does that mean I'm not a maid anymore?! Master, you aren't going to abandon me, are you...?!

feeling4.line: You mean you're excited to see me as a maid, and as an idol...? Sorry, I misunderstood...
