feeling5.line: I'm doing well as a maid, and as an idol...? I'm honoured by your praise! I'll keep working hard as an idol... No, I'll keep working hard in everything I do for you, Master!

home.line: Master, are you hurt? Do you feel okay? I may be an idol for now, but if you need me, I can still service you anytime...

hp_warning.line: I can't let the Master throw me away...!

login.line: Master, what would you have me do today? Idol things or maid things, I'll do anything you want!

lose.line: I can't sing as well as the Head Maid...

mail.line: Looks like some important mail, Master.

main1.line: Singing is more about conveying one's feelings than it is skill... So I will keep singing for you, Master...

main2.line: Madam Illustrious focuses so much on her footwork during dance practice... is it because of the mirror?

main3.line: My fellow maids, and the girls from the different camps come together to make a proper idol unit. It's truly amazing that you can bring all of us together, Master.

mission.line: We have a gig offer, Master. Won't you take a look?

mission_complete.line: Master, here are the rewards. It's all thanks to their hard work.

profile.line: I'm Dido, Royal Navy Light Cruiser. I'm but a lowly maid, and I never expected to be chosen to be an idol... But I'll do what I can!

propose.line: It's unthinkable that a lowly maid could shine onstage with all of you... But I will redouble my efforts to be worthy of the honour! All for the sake of my dearest Master!

skill.line: As an idol, for the Master...!

touch.line: You need only ask and I'll be happy to shake your hand, or whatever you may want!

touch2.line: Nnng...

unlock.line: I am the light cruiser, Dido, currently taking part in idol activities as part of the experimental Muse System. I learned more or less what idols are supposed to do from the others, so p-please... keep a close eye on me!

upgrade.line: I wonder if Albacore's idea could actually work...

win_mvp.line: I know I can do it if I work hard. I'll become an idol you can be proud of!

battle.line: Shall we go together?

detail.line: Hmm... You're staring at me so much... Did you happen to want these gloves?

drop_descrip.line: Arethusa-class light cruiser – Penelope.

expedition.line: The commission has been completed, and now I'm supposed to welcome the fleet back... But what comes after that?

feeling1.line: Commander... aren't you acting a bit weird?

feeling2.line: I shall wait for you here tomorrow as well, just as you instructed, Commander.

feeling3.line: If I leave the uncompleted work here, I wonder if eventually, I won't have to do it anymore.

feeling4.line: Would you like some of the rosehip tea that Aurora taught me to make? ...It's too sour? Hmm... Maybe I accidentally added vinegar...

feeling5.line: No matter how much time passes, I will continue to wait for you here, Commander. No matter what, I'll always wait for you to come back.

headtouch.line: Nnh... Are you treating me like a child?

home.line: I am glad that you have returned safely, Commander.

hp_warning.line: I... can still do this!

login.line: Commander, are you going on a sortie? I shall stay here and await your return.

lose.line: I have been defeated. My sincerest apologies...

mail.line: Hmm... Ah, I knew I was forgetting something... Um... Right. The mail. Commander, I brought you the mail.

main1.line: Paperwork, paperwork... Where did I put it again? On that shelf? I can't seem to remember...

main2.line: Pepperpot? ...Why yes, I do think that food generally tastes better with a healthy pinch of pepper.

main3.line: I want to get along with U-410. ...Mm, with you here, Commander, I'm sure it will be fine.

mission.line: "Remind the commander if there are any unfinished missions." ...Got it. Commander, you have unfinished missions. What are they about? Umm...

mission_complete.line: "Remind the commander to collect the rewards for completed missions." ...Got it. Commander, please remember to collect your rewards. What rewards? Umm...

profile.line: I am Penelope of the Royal Navy, Arethusa-class light cruiser. I participated in a transport mission with Aurora and her companions in the K Fleet. There were difficult times, but I managed to pull through. If only I had noticed her back then...

propose.line: A promise ring... proof that you always want to stay with me? Mm... But, even without this, as long as you think of me, sometimes call for me, and look at me... that's all I need.

touch.line: ...Hm? Is something amiss? I do believe I've been doing everything to your specifications...

touch2.line: Hm...? Commander, what are you doing?

unlock.line: Arethusa-class light cruiser... Penelope, is my name. From now on, I will be your subordinate. I hope that you... can at least remember my name.

upgrade.line: Have I become stronger than before?

win_mvp.line: Commander, I followed your instructions and emerged victorious.

detail.line: Aurora also gave me this incense burner. It's supposed to be good for recovering from fatigue, so shall we give it a try together?

drop_descrip.line: Aurora chose this outfit for me because... the Spring Festival represents a time of celebration in the Dragon Empery, and red is the color that best symbolizes that. What do you think? Does this outfit... make you feel more festive?

home.line: Commander, do you know about the Spring Festival? There are all kinds of interesting stories, and I'd like to hear more about that from you.

login.line: Happy Lunar New Year. I'm glad I can see you today.

main1.line: Haah... Commander, I'm sorry... At this rate, this incense... is going to make me fall asleep... Zzzzz

main2.line: The broth in the hotpot was as red as my clothes... It was a bit scary at first, but the food ended up being really delicious.

main3.line: The pattern on this fan was embroidered. I learned how to do it from Yat Sen and the others a while back, but my hands were trembling so much I made a mess of things... Ugh, I wonder how everyone does this so well.

touch.line: ...Hm? Already tired? You can lie down here if you'd like.

touch2.line: ...Um, Commander, I don't think... this is any way to conduct yourself.

unlock.line: Aurora chose this outfit for me because... the Spring Festival represents a time of celebration in the Dragon Empery, and red is the color that best symbolizes that. What do you think? Does this outfit... make you feel more festive?

detail.line: Here, I brought you your order. It's still frozen? Of course...? I never heated it up. Why...? You... never told me to...?

drop_descrip.line: Welcome, welcome. I've been working here as a maid, just as you told me to. Umm... Call for me only when you're ready to order.

home.line: "Welcome back, Master. How are Mew today?" What do you think about my greeting...? 'Kay, I'll see you later then.

login.line: Did you call? Well, what do you want? ...You still need some more time? Call for me when you've decided.

main1.line: Here's the menu. Call me if you need me.

main2.line: No, that's not it? ...What do you mean by that? There's no way for me to know unless you show me...

main3.line: Sure, here's the pepper mill. How much do you want? ...Oops, I spilled it all...

touch.line: Did you want some headpats? Sure. Good job, Commander. *pat pat*

touch2.line: Commander, it's fine if you're banned from the store for this, right?

unlock.line: Welcome, welcome. I've been working here as a maid, just as you told me to. Umm... Call for me only when you're ready to order.

battle.line: Anti-air combat, commence! Master, please lower your head!

detail.line: Master, is there anything new you'd like to wear when you head out on missions? ...If that's what you'd like, please leave it to me! It so happens sewing is one of my specialties♪

drop_descrip.line: Dido-class light cruiser – Charybdis.

expedition.line: A commission has been completed. I wonder how it went?

feeling1.line: I... Master, do you throw everyone to the wolves like this...?

feeling2.line: Hm-hmm~♪ Whenever, wherever, I'll be there to serve you as your maid. A-and please don't remind me of how I mess up sometimes...

feeling3.line: It may be an exaggeration to say "whenever, wherever," but... I simply wish to be there to serve you whenever you might need me... I'm sorry...

feeling4.line: If I do everything for you, you'll become incapable of doing anything for yourself? Am I that powerful of an existence...?

feeling5.line: I-I'll do everything for you, but in moderation... Wait! I'll just do my best to relieve some of your fatigue~ Roger! I'll make sure to exercise restraint!

home.line: Welcome back, Master! Let's make sure you don't overdo things and take a short break first~

hp_warning.line: Wh-where's the enemy?

login.line: Good morning to you, Master. Will you be starting off the day with some work?

lose.line: Redouble our rescue efforts! Master, please retreat and leave the others to me!

mail.line: I'm here to deliver this mail to you, Master.

main1.line: Fair winds and a following sea~ Master, if it's fine with you, please take me along in your next mission as well.

main2.line: There's nothing for me to do right now...? N-no way... Master, how could you do this to me...

main3.line: Master~ If you'd please change into– Y-you can't see the documents you're working on...? Ahh, I'm sorry!

mission.line: Master, there's a new mission for you! Y-you already knew about it? Oh...

mission_complete.line: Here are your rewards. Please check on them.

profile.line: I am the Dido-class anti-aircraft cruiser, Charybdis. With the motto, "Any task – anywhere," I performed my duties in different oceans across the world during the war. Master, whenever or wherever you need anything, just leave it to me!

propose.line: What's this, Master...? Y-you really weren't satisfied just having your fatigue relieved?! *sigh*... I-I mean, even without this ring... Oh! Is this a symbol of your permission for me to pamper you lots and lots more~? Heehee, my dear Master, of course I love you lots~

skill.line: Stay calm, it's time for our counterattack!

touch.line: Just leave it to me~♪

touch2.line: Master, is something wrong?

unlock.line: Dido-class light cruiser, Charybdis at your service. 'tis an honour to meet you in person, Master. May your everyday life be bathed in the warm sunlight, in the peaceful days that come.

upgrade.line: Behold my true power! Heehee.

win_mvp.line: An elegant victory, the way us Royal Maids do it... Ow! A-an undetonated shell...?

battle.line: There's no pampering in store for you bunch, only punishment!

detail.line: This room is brimming with Dragon Empery style. Hmm... I'm not exactly sure how to explain it, but it sure is nice and relaxing.

drop_descrip.line: *Pats thighs* Master, you poor thing~ Look how hard you've been working~ Hehe, hurry and come here so that I can pamper you~

home.line: *Pats thighs* Master, I'm right over here~ Heehee, you must be exhausted, right~

login.line: Goodness, what a troublesome master you are. Where have you been? I've been waiting to continue cleaning your ears~

mail.line: Your mail's here~ Please make sure you check it afterwards~♪

main1.line: Umm... Hmm... Oh no, I still haven't finished sewing the outfit Aurora requested... Dear me...

main2.line: My, someone is at the door... Oh, Master?! Please don't move, I'm not done working on your ears yet...

main3.line: Alright, Master~ I'll be cleaning your other ear now, so please turn around... Eek?!

mission_complete.line: The rewards have arrived without any issues. That's a relief~

touch.line: Ah, Master, please don't move around so much.

touch2.line: Ahhn...♡

unlock.line: *Pats thighs* Master, you poor thing~ Look how hard you've been working~ Hehe, hurry and come here so that I can pamper you~

win_mvp.line: Now, please allow me to continue pampering you once we return~

detail.line: Ugh... We haven't even done that much walking, but my feet are already sore... Changing into an outfit you're not used to isn't the easiest thing in the world. I wonder if Sirius and Black Prince are hanging in there...

drop_descrip.line: Tis a pleasure to see you, Master. I am delighted to be your partner for today. ...Oh, I was just trying to sound prim and proper! You don't need to look at me with such pity in your eyes!

expedition.line: The commission team is back, Commander. Ehehe.

login.line: Master, why don't you take the lead tonight? Heehee~

mail.line: The letter is right~ over~ here~! You don't see it?

main1.line: By the way, Master, who did you invite today? Umm, it doesn't particularly concern me, but Dido absolutely wanted to know.

main2.line: I wonder why Eagle is holding back so much? We went through the trouble of making all this delicious food, so...

main3.line: Isn't Sirius absolutely breathtaking in that dress? I know you've been staring at her too, Commander. Heehee~

touch.line: Did you want to shake your feet out as well?

touch2.line: This outfit makes me pretty irresistible, doesn't it?

unlock.line: Tis a pleasure to see you, Master. I am delighted to be your partner for today. ...Oh, I was just trying to sound prim and proper! You don't need to look at me with such pity in your eyes!

battle.line: For the safety and continued victory of my Master, I'll head out!

detail.line: Phew... This salty sea breeze feels wonderful, Master. Next time, I should bring the other ladies here to... Hmm... Do you have any ideas for what we should do? Maybe light a bonfire?

drop_descrip.line: As you can see, today's theme... is a seaside pampering, or something like that~ Heehee. I know you're no stranger to the sea, Commander, but today, we're here to play, not work. Just take it easy, and unwind~♪

expedition.line: The girls of the commissions team have been swallowed by a whirlpool, you know... Just kidding~♪ Look, they've returned already.

login.line: Master~ Ahaha, that's right~♪ I'm always ecstatic to come to the beach~

main1.line: Eskimo, don't go overboard with your pranks...

main2.line: Master, it's shallow over here~ ...Hwaah?! T-that was a huge wave just now...

main3.line: Clear skies and a refreshing breeze... The perfect weather for pampering you, Master. Wouldn't you agree~?

touch.line: I'd love to come back here every year with you, Master.

unlock.line: As you can see, today's theme... is a seaside pampering, or something like that~ Heehee. I know you're no stranger to the sea, Commander, but today, we're here to play, not work. Just take it easy, and unwind~♪

win_mvp.line: I'll have you know, I'm not actually bad at fighting. Heehee~

battle.line: A one-on-one battle shall have to wait for another day.

detail.line: My liege, would you like to have a bout with me? Of course, not a serious match, but just something to deepen our bonds... Next time, since you've got other work to focus on, you say? Understood. Whenever you're ready, please let me know.

drop_descrip.line: Bellona-class light cruiser – Bellona.

expedition.line: The commission team has returned. To be rewarded for one's toils is precious indeed.

feeling1.line: Only those with pride have the privilege to wield a sword in a duel. My liege, you still have much work to do to earn it.

feeling2.line: Though I was christened after a goddess of war, I'm not particularly fond of it. The only value I find in wielding a sword is in the pure enjoyment of the world of duels.

feeling3.line: Once I grasp my blade, the only thing in my sight is my enemy. In that moment, the sole thought in my head is to devote my all to defeating them.

feeling4.line: It's unfair to judge victory or defeat based solely on swordsmanship unless those involved are experienced. What I'm saying is, what is your area of expertise, my liege? Of course I'm curious, but I was also wanting to try something that doesn't involve a sword.

feeling5.line: If you're interested in learning more about me, how about we spar for a bit to our hearts' content? There's nothing that brings closer than that. Hehe, I'll show up on time, but I'll leave the time and place to you. I'm sure you wouldn't play dirty with me, my liege. Would you?

headtouch.line: Is this how you show your gratitude toward your subordinates? Duly noted.

home.line: My liege, good work out there... Um, your cuff and collar are all ragged... How about changing out first?

hp_warning.line: Purge all distractions. I'll fight with a level head!

login.line: My liege, I've been waiting for you. Have you prepared to face your toughest enemy today – your work?

lose.line: While we may look past our failures, we must not ignore what led to them...

mail.line: Mail? Is it a challenge to a duel? Please prepare... Huh? That's not the case?

main1.line: I much prefer fighting one-on-one compared to the disorder of a melee. There's a huge difference between focusing on one enemy versus taking stock of the big picture, after all.

main2.line: Hm? There are marks of wear on these gloves? How careless of me. I shall prepare a new set right away.

main3.line: My liege, your expression... Did something bad happen? If you need someone to give you a push, I'd love to be of assistance.

mission.line: If you think of your missions as a duel with an invisible enemy, your efficiency will go up.

mission_complete.line: These are the rewards for your completed missions. Please accept them as the spoils of the victor.

profile.line: I am Bellona, a member of the improved Dido-class, the Bellona-class. As a member of the Royal Knights, I participated as an escort during transport missions as well as participating in the raid on Tirpitz. After that war, various things happened... Anyway, please feel free to entrust me with any mission you see fit.

propose.line: It is the destiny of man to wither away with the passage of time. ...However, even if my passions wither with the passing of time, I find that my emotions only mellow and become more robust, as if a fine vintage. You are the first person I've desired something more than swinging swords with, so... Please, don't let me down.

skill.line: Come, we'll settle this with a duel!

touch.line: Well then, I shall accept this duel... Oh, um, you were just giving me some work to do?

touch2.line: Shall I take this as a provocation?

unlock.line: I am Bellona, improved Dido-class light cruiser of the Royal Navy. If I am not mistaken, you are the Lord-Commander? I have stated my name and title as per our code. I hope you will do so as well, my liege.

upgrade.line: The stronger I get, the greater my odds of victory.

win_mvp.line: I present this victory to you with pleasure, my liege. Of course, it shan't be my last victory either.

detail.line: I have always been curious about the kinds of work that Dido and the others always do. I had always thought that the work the maids did was not very difficult, but actually, it's quite comparable to fighting in a melee.

drop_descrip.line: My liege... No, excuse me, I should be calling you Master, right? Bellona of the Royal Maids, reporting in. My, you seem quite lost for words... I'll explain the situation to you later, so don't worry about it.

headtouch.line: Were you encouraging me? Please do not fret. My studies regarding the duties of a maid have been going quite swimmingly.

home.line: Welcome back, dear Master. Please take a nice rest until our next battle begins. Allow me to take your soiled clothes from you.

login.line: Good day to you, dear Master. Please give me your orders, whatever they may be. I am always ready to use my blade... Ahem, I am at your beck and call.

main1.line: When I think of the dust as my enemy in a duel... it's like fighting a phantom enemy that refuses to fight you face-to-face. I can only hope that there aren't that many.

main2.line: Hmm... These windows with bump marks are hard to remove, so they should be dealt with as an emergency... As for the furniture, let's just replace them.

main3.line: Looking at a room after a deep cleaning makes you feel a sense of accomplishment. The feeling of not even seeing a speck of dust feels as good as beating a very strong enemy in a duel.

touch.line: Let us clean up any unnecessary trash there might be.

touch2.line: You shouldn't underestimate the power of the Royal Maids.

unlock.line: My liege... No, excuse me, I should be calling you Master, right? Bellona of the Royal Maids, reporting in. My, you seem quite lost for words... I'll explain the situation to you later, so don't worry about it.

battle.line: Much easier than taking care of my friends...!

detail.line: Doing the bare minimum is unacceptable, whether for the maid or for the master. Please pull yourself together.

drop_descrip.line: Emerald-class light cruiser –Enterprise.

expedition.line: A commission has been completed. Please go take a look, Master.

feeling1.line: I am only serving you because you are my master. There's nothing more to it.

feeling2.line: Please feel free to call upon me whenever you need something. Be it cleaning your office or cleaning the battlefield, anything from maid work to military affairs fall within my purview.

feeling3.line: There's a girl you're interested in? Well then, if you'd like me to investigate more about her, please tell me her name. While I'd criticize you for being tactless, if it's your order... You won't tell me? Understood...

feeling4.line: You want to know how to confess to a girl you're keen on... E-even if you ask me, I wouldn't know anything about that... Don't you think I'm the wrong person to ask about love?

feeling5.line: This has to be some kind of joke. You're just trying to make fun of me, aren't you? ...N-no way... Of all people, I can't believe the person you were interested in was me all along... I can't believe it...

headtouch.line: Wh-what is it...?

home.line: Good work out there. Master, please head on out for your debriefing.

hp_warning.line: Keep calm, and carry on...!

login.line: I see you've arrived, Master. Here is your schedule for the day.

lose.line: We lost... But it's not your fault, Master. I should've worked harder.

mail.line: You've got mail, Master. I'll bring it over right away.

main1.line: Given your current efficiency, it seems unlikely that you'll be able to finish your work today, Master. Since Emerald won't be of any use, shall I call upon some of the other Royal Maids for assistance?

main2.line: Glasgow, I really enjoyed the manga you recommended the other day. What would you recommend next... Master?! I'm not up to anything, I swear!

main3.line: Please leave the cleaning to me. I'll make sure to take care of it without getting in the way of your work.

mission.line: New missions are in. They'll be done in no time if we work together.

mission_complete.line: That's all I can do for you. I'll leave you to check on the rewards.

profile.line: I am Enterprise, an Emerald-class light cruiser belonging to the Royal Navy. In the great war, I participated in support, escort, and transport missions, and even participated in combat from time to time. At the Bay of Biscay... Ahem, forget I mentioned it.

propose.line: From the way the celebration hall is decorated, to the blessings I've received from my friends, there's nothing lacking... I, I truly can't believe that I'm exchanging vows with you, Master... Ahh, I must be dreaming...

skill.line: I'll wipe the floor with you all!

touch.line: Did you need my advice?

touch2.line: ...I'm going to get upset.

unlock.line: I am the Royal Maid, Enterprise. I have been assigned to this port starting today. As part of the maids, I am in charge of cleaning, and my hobby is reading about all kinds of trivia. That's all I have to report.

upgrade.line: Thank you for making me stronger, Master. I shall return this debt to you in battle.

win_mvp.line: We won. Didn't take much brainpower either.

battle.line: Trust in your leadership and give the command!

detail.line: You know, Master, I think only the most outstanding maid should have the right to serve her Master... What do you think?

drop_descrip.line: Dido-class light cruiser – Scylla.

expedition.line: A commission has been completed. Master, I hope you aren't forgetting to welcome the team back? ...Good. I'm ready to depart any time.

feeling1.line: Don't ever think that I might leave you, Master. It is a maid's duty to care for her master, even if said master happens to be a little... wanting.

feeling2.line: Commander, you have a choice: me, or my friend and excellent Royal Maid Charybdis, who comes running whenever you need her? ...Heehee, you don't have to answer that. I just felt like asking.

feeling3.line: Is something wrong? Have you perhaps made a mistake, Master? Don't fret. Tell me everything, and let me think about it with you. No matter what, Master, you have our eternal respect as the great Commander♪

feeling4.line: You are the Master, and I am your personal maid. Why should there be any secrets between us? Heehee, don't you hide a thing. You want to rely on me more and leave more to me, don't you...?

feeling5.line: Heehee. Do you find yourself feeling that you can't do anything without me around? Poor Master. I'll just have to manage your everyday... Oh, I don't mind. I'm the only one who's seen your few shortcomings—your occasional spinelessness, indolence, and indecision. Yet even I still consider you the best Commander and the best Master ever~♡

headtouch.line: A reward, for little old me? Heehee, I'm delighted!

home.line: Don't worry about a thing. Everyone is safe at home in the port, and I'm prepared to devote myself to you. So... May I have my orders, Master? Heehee!

hp_warning.line: Do not fret, Master. I swear that I will return to your side.

login.line: Welcome home, Master. I got everything ready for you, so all you need to do is sit here... and get right to work!♪

lose.line: So this is how you look when you've been beaten... Heehee♡

mail.line: Master, you seem to be forgetting some mail addressed to you. Heehee, you're so forgetful!♪ But it's okay. I happened to bring it with me.

main1.line: Is there something you're looking for? I know where everything related to the Royal Maids' work is. Don't hesitate to ask.

main2.line: I couldn't help but notice that another girl was cleaning your office... Oh, it's fine, Master. But allow me to do it next time; I'm the maid taking care of you right now.

main3.line: I'm happy to help with whatever you can't or don't want to do. There's nothing wrong with accepting your shortcomings and relying on your maid♪

mission.line: Do you have unfinished business? That's no good... Allow me to help you, Master♪

mission_complete.line: Another mission complete. Heehee, I think your exploits are worthy of a medal.

profile.line: Dido-class anti-aircraft cruiser Scylla, ready to serve. I served as an escort carrier flagship in that war, but I was unable to perform any major exploits. But now... I am only a Royal Maid, here to devote heart and soul to you, Master.

propose.line: Have you finally found the determination to leave your everything to me? Heehee, of course I accept. Leave it all to your personal maid Scylla while you drown in my love forever and ever!♡

touch.line: Is something the matter? If there's anything I can do for you, please don't hesitate to ask.

touch2.line: A maid must be willing to give her everything to her Master. Please do as you wish.

unlock.line: Delighted to meet you, Master. Hopefully it is not too forward of me to greet you in such a manner. I am Scylla, Dido-class light cruiser. Heehee, as you can see, I am nothing more than an ordinary maid.

upgrade.line: Your favour is much appreciated, Master.

win_mvp.line: Please accept my sincere congratulations, Master.

detail.line: I'm your maid, Master, so I'm glad to be used however you see fit. Or do you... want to be "used" yourself, Master? Heehee...

drop_descrip.line: Did you come all this way just because I asked you to, Master? Or... would you prefer I call you "Senpai" here? If we're at school, then there's no reason for me to act maidly, now is there? Heeheehee♪

expedition.line: "Senpai," I'm about to show the other girls that look you had on your face. Are you sure you're ready for that? ...Heehee. Next time, don't forget to greet the commission team upon their return.

feeling5.line: There's no point trying to hide it, "Senpai." You're just going to have to give up and... Got you!♪ I could never show another girl how pitiful you look right now. But of course... If you would like the others to see, I would gladly obey♡

home.line: What brings you back here? Do you not have it in you to leave me alone? Or... Is there something you want me to do for you?

login.line: Welcome home, Master. Rather... "Senpai"? Did you finally remember our little promise?"

mail.line: "Senpai," your phone is ringing. Is that a call from someone? Such as... another girl, perhaps?

main1.line: "Senpai," do you need my notes from last class? I wrote all the important points, so it'll be just like you actually listened to the lecture!

main2.line: Where has Lady Argus gone? Oh, she's in remedial classes for failing grades? Goodness...

main3.line: We're just two good friends—in school, anyway. But outside this campus... Heehee, shall we call that our little secret?♡

main4.line: My, Glasgow, were you watching us? You were excited to see what Master's like at school, too, weren't you? Heehee, don't worry. I'll get plenty of pictures for you.

mission.line: This shameful begging isn't like the "Senpai" everyone relies on, now, is it? But it's okay... Leave this mission to me.

mission_complete.line: It seems you've finished all of your missions, "Senpai." Good job! You couldn't have done that with my help, right? Heehee!

touch.line: My eyes are up here, "Senpai"~♪

touch2.line: Is this the kind of stimulation you seek? Heehee, you're so naughty~♡

unlock.line: Did you come all this way just because I asked you to, Master? Or... would you prefer I call you "Senpai" here? If we're at school, then there's no reason for me to act maidly, now is there? Heeheehee♪

win_mvp.line: Well done, "Senpai." Look, everyone's cheering for you.

battle.line: Everyone, please be mindful of yourselves. Do not get hurt if possible!

detail.line: What's the matter? Your Excellency, what are you looking at so seriously?

drop_descrip.line: London-class heavy cruiser – London, Hull Number 69!

expedition.line: Yes, the commission is done on time. Let's verify the results, shall we?

feeling1.line: Your Excellency, please go elsewhere for your time. I shall handle everything here.

feeling2.line: Your Excellency, a moment please. There's a bit of a problem here... Mmm, yes!... Is there anything you need?

feeling3.line: Your Excellency, would you like to have tea together? If you're not done with your work yet, then please tend to it first. Of course, I will be with you.

feeling4.line: A date? If your Excellency can finish all the work for the coming days, then there's no reason for me to refuse. How about it? Do you want to make the effort?

feeling5.line: Please stay still! I had already told you to dress yourself properly. And your hair... You can be far too casual with your appearance at times, your Excellency... Yes, that should do. Where do we go for our date?

home.line: Good work. I'll handle the official matters, so please go have some hot red tea.

hp_warning.line: There seems to be a slight miscalculation...

login.line: Good day to you, your Excellency. I shall accompany you for today as well.

lose.line: ...I shouldn't be showing you manners when it comes to this.

mail.line: Your new mail is right over here. Please confirm it.

main1.line: Your Excellency... have you seen Amethyst? I've been searching for her.

main2.line: The Arctic was very cold. I still feel like i'm getting a cold from there...

main3.line: My, this is a fine day. Erm, well... I thought it's a good time for a conversation...

mission.line: Do your best to finish your missions today.

mission_complete.line: I've already made a list of the rewards. Please take a look at them when you have a moment.

profile.line: I am the lead ship of London class , London. I was a member of the First Cruising Fleet, and fought battles in North Atlantic and Pacific waters. Your Excellency, rest assured and leave the missions to me!

propose.line: Thank you, please leave it there. More than that, look at this, Your Excellency... Surprised? Hehe. With our relationship, you should know why I'm not saying anything about this~ But, now that this is the occasion, let me handle the meal for today, with lots of what we like to eat.

skill.line: Well then, I'm gonna try harder as well.

touch.line: Bodily contact is... No, I don't mind. I'm just not used to it.

touch2.line: Pl... please don't do such an improper thing!

unlock.line: First ship of the London class, London. Member of the First Cruising Fleet, while also having took part in battles of North Atlantic and Pacific missions. If there's a mission, rest assured and let me handle it!

upgrade.line: I'm glad, but please mind the allocation of resources.

win_mvp.line: Being praised by your Excellency is the greatest honor to me.

detail.line: Post-battle results, supply requisitions, next field of operations data analysis... Sorry for working overtime, I just want to assist you as much as I can... D-do you think I'm letting my personal feelings influence my work?

drop_descrip.line: Splendid work today, Your Excellency. Here are your documents for the next mission. It has everything you need to know, so please give it a read. Heehee, I'm happy to assist so that you may focus solely on achieving your goals.

home.line: Welcome back, Your Excellency. Hey, I wanted to ask you something about your... break times, I suppose. Heehee.

login.line: It's a bit chilly today, so I took out a coat for you, Your Excellency. You may feel it's unnecessary, but... it's just in case. Please bear that in mind.

main1.line: Although I do like the sound of filing paperwork normally as a shipgirl and getting paid a salary... For now, I'm content to serve by your side in this way, Your Excellency.

main2.line: Galatea told me about a personality test that has been making the rounds. It supposedly measures how much love is in your heart. Um, Your Excellency... would you like to take that test with me?

main3.line: Are you going outside? Alright, then please allow me to drive the car and pilot the mass-produced ship.

main4.line: Sussex, you ought to look into how to be of service to Our Excellency. Here, this is a book on developing secretarial skills. Read it when you have the time.

touch.line: Heehee. No need to hurry; I'm not going anywhere. I'll wait patiently until you've finished your work.

touch2.line: Mmh... Maybe I should get changed... Hm? You'd really prefer it if I stuck around a while longer?

unlock.line: Splendid work today, Your Excellency. Here are your documents for the next mission. It has everything you need to know, so please give it a read. Heehee, I'm happy to assist so that you may focus solely on achieving your goals.

detail.line: Never change out of this dress? I see you can be quite mean, Your Excellency... Still, I'll indulge you just for a while.

drop_descrip.line: Why are you so astounded, Your Excellency? You expressly requested an unforgettable and elaborate ceremony. Heehee, you'll make it weird if you keep staring so much, so won't you please take my hand now?

expedition.line: A commission has been completed. Do remember to thank the team that worked hard to bring us these resources.

feeling5.line: What would you like for dinner tonight, Your Excellency? If nothing comes to mind, we could go grocery shopping together first so you can think while we browse the wares. If you like... you could think of it as a date, too. Heehee.

home.line: I'm glad you made it back safely, Your Excellency. Shall I prepare you a hot cup of tea while you rest, as per usual?

login.line: Why, hello. Could you come a little closer? ...There we go. We need you to look your sharpest while at work!

main1.line: I know you're enamoured with my dress, but you must not let your infatuation impede your work.

main2.line: I've brought you refreshments to alleviate your stress. You needn't worry about putting on weight as they're made with healthy ingredients. Heehee.

main3.line: A posh anniversary and a simple life aren't incompatible. Which is to say, you can certainly look forward to a candlelit dinner.

mission.line: I've left a note regarding your new missions. Take them on at your own pace, Your Excellency.

mission_complete.line: Mission rewards have come in. I'll write up the goods summary, if you don't mind.

touch.line: Us holding hands has become a perfectly ordinary thing at this point, hasn't it?

touch2.line: How far our relationship has come...

unlock.line: Why are you so astounded, Your Excellency? You expressly requested an unforgettable and elaborate ceremony. Heehee, you'll make it weird if you keep staring so much, so won't you please take my hand now?

detail.line: I can always change back to my old outfit, but to be frank, I've always looked forward to being able to wear something like this. Your Excellency, would you like me to get changed?

drop_descrip.line: Um... Your Excellency, could you please stop staring at me like you don't recognise me? I didn't think that I'd get a new look for my retrofit, either... But, don't you think it's rather cute?

main1.line: I feel like my mood has been changing since I got my new outfit. Your Excellency, would you like to go for some dessert in a little bit?

main2.line: Your Excellency, please do not forget the fact that I am still your secretary ship. Now, please focus and get back to your work!

main3.line: Your Excellency, did you know that Sussex said that this outfit looks really pretty? You don't hear words of praise from her often, hehe~

touch.line: What am I going to do with you... Well then, Your Excellency, please rest for a while. I'll prepare the snacks.

unlock.line: Um... Your Excellency, could you please stop staring at me like you don't recognise me? I didn't think that I'd get a new look for my retrofit, either... But, don't you think it's rather cute?

battle.line: I do not mind, but I really have to bring victory to Commander~

detail.line: You appear to have time, Commander~

drop_descrip.line: London-class heavy cruiser – Shropshire, Hull Number 73!

expedition.line: Commander? Staring at me is one thing, but you should also look out for the commission team. They have returned, you know?

feeling1.line: Commander, you're in the way. Move aside, move aside

feeling2.line: Do you need something? I'm concentrating on work right now, so spare me the sweet talk~

feeling3.line: Commander, you are a good man and you have a prospective future. But after I think about it calmly, now is just not the time. I'm sorry!

feeling4.line: You are my type, Commander, but there are no specific reasons for me to like you so... I'm sorry!

feeling5.line: Please mind the time, place and mood when you do this, so I'm sorry! ... Ah! I don't mind the amount of times you confess to me~

home.line: You were dashing, Commander! I have to put in effort as well... Hmm, how about I heal your damaged heart from the battlefield, with my junior wiles?

hp_warning.line: Oh dear, this is bad!

login.line: Ah, have you come back, Commander? I was just about to go to your place~

lose.line: Commander, clumsy girls have their charms as well, wouldn't you say? Heh-hey~

mail.line: Commander, you have new mail~ Is it a love letter? It's a love letter, isn't it? Open it, open it!

main1.line: I am a little nervous when I am alone with you, Commander, but since you are alone I'm fu... fully calm myself~

main2.line: Com~man~der~ Help me~ Please, you are the only one I can count on~

main3.line: Did you know, Commander? Sometimes, making small mistakes can make one seem cuter~

mission.line: A new mission... If you finish it properly, I will re-evaluate you right away~

mission_complete.line: The rewards have been distributed~ Or could it be~ that you want a reward from me?

profile.line: The youngest of London class, and sent abroad away from my sisters. That is me~ Ah, it's not that I particularly wanted your sympathy, but if you give me a little bit of attention, I'll give you high points for that! ... Acting cute? Oh shush, I was being serious you know~

propose.line: I'm sorry... is what you thought I was going to say? Well Commander, from now on, my life is your life~

touch.line: If you don't do your work properly, even I will show an angry face for it. Com~man~der?

touch2.line: Ah! Commander, this is inappropriate!

unlock.line: London class' youngest, Shropshire, reporting for duty~ I've been told that I am air-headed and gullible, so I'll be giving you some problems~ Well then, my time awaits~

upgrade.line: It's alright to not become stronger. I'm fine as long as I can be of use to Commander~

win_mvp.line: You need not shower me with praises. Pay attention to others as well~

battle.line: For once, Shropshire's gonna act capable! Here goes!

detail.line: Someone's looking awfully lazy~ Watch out before Sussex says something to you. She doesn't get that being a bit of a good-for-nothing makes you that much cooler~

drop_descrip.line: As you know, I'm the youngest of London class, Shropshire~ I'm excited to work with you! Heheh, I look pretty capable now, don't I? Maybe I'll cause a little less trouble for you now, Commander!

expedition.line: You can look at me all you want! As long as you don't forget to check your commission rewards.

home.line: Look at you, Commander! I'm falling for you all over again! ...That's enough for now, right? I don't want you getting TOO excited from all this buttering-up~

login.line: Heheh, I've been waiting for you, Commander. I'll serve as your capable-ish secretary today!

lose.line: That wasn't on purpose, I swear~!

main1.line: Oh, you messed this up here... Is that you trying to show off your good-for-nothing side, Commander? Bwuh? You say this is a real mistake?!

main2.line: Commander, help meee~ You're the only person I can trust~ ...Okay, take care of this for me, please! Ehehe!

main3.line: London says changing clothes can change feelings. Buuut... Whose feelings are they supposed to change, I wonder~?

mission.line: A new mission... If you can do this, Commander, I might see you in a new light~ For real, I promise!

mission_complete.line: Ready for your big reward for a job well done? Drumroooll... Next time Sussex lectures you, I'll put in a good word for you!

touch.line: Is this a cry for help, Commander?

touch2.line: We can't do this! But I know you won't listen~ Hmph.

unlock.line: As you know, I'm the youngest of London class, Shropshire~ I'm excited to work with you! Heheh, I look pretty capable now, don't I? Maybe I'll cause a little less trouble for you now, Commander!

win_mvp.line: At least you're capable when it comes to complimenting me and the other girls, right? Heheh!

battle.line: Let's show the enemies our true strength!

detail.line: Errr, Graciously overlook my poor armour and firepower, please!

drop_descrip.line: Kent-class heavy cruiser - Kent, Hull Number 54!

expedition.line: Good! Your commission team has successfully returned!

feeling1.line: I'm disappointed... We don't make a good team at all.

feeling2.line: Commander, Let's play a game! No, it's not a catchphrase. I can change it anytime! Anyways, Let's play! Let's Play!

feeling3.line: Hey, Commander! Ah, nothing, nothing... Just keep doing you work. I'm happy just looking at you, Commander.

feeling4.line: Staring...? Ah, it's nothing. I'm just wondering why you're so good looking, Commander. I'll never get tired of staring at you!

feeling5.line: Commander! Commander! Want to guess how many layers of armor I'm wearing? If you get it right, you get a prize! If you don't, then you'll have to count the layers yourself...!

home.line: Welcome! I'm still full of energy!

login.line: Yo, Commander, let's go do something together!

lose.line: Ouch... Contestant Ken has been eliminated

mail.line: Warning! Radar indicates a paper plane folded with the new mail closing in at high speed!

main1.line: I forgot that Tigre isn't around...

main2.line: Commander, do you wanna race against me?

main3.line: I think I've seen ships from the Far East before... They look really strong!

mission.line: Hmmm, a new mission, want to take a stab at it?

mission_complete.line: Mission rewards! Let's take a look!

profile.line: I'm both one of the first County-class cruisers and the first ship of the Kent-class. Pretty impressive, right? Stuff like Armour can be made up with good motivation and a fighting spirit! Right?

propose.line: Oh wow! Thanks, Commander! But something this important needs to be kept in a safe place. I can't afford to lose it.....

touch.line: Yoohoo~ Want to play, Commander?

touch2.line: Oh... Commander... You big pervert...

unlock.line: Hey Commander! I'm Kent! How do you do? Good? Bad? Doesn't matter. Things will be better now that I'm here!

upgrade.line: Woah! Contestant Kent has become stronger!

win_mvp.line: Yeah! Contestant Kent is number one!

battle.line: The enemies look quite strong...

detail.line: My post-retrofit performance is very impressive!

drop_descrip.line: Kent-class heavy cruiser - Suffolk, Hull Number 55!

expedition.line: That cloud looks like cotton candy... hmm? Ah, Commander. The commission team is back~!

feeling1.line: ... The sky is so blue...

feeling2.line: Hmm, clear skies, so a great day to scout out the waters~ Do you want to come with me, Commander?

feeling3.line: Reconnaissance is a very important task! Huh, I'm losing focus? W-what are you saying? I'm just o-observing the weather...

feeling4.line: My big sisters are so strong, if only I could be of more help to them... Huh? I'm doing a good job as well? Hehehe... I received a compliment~

feeling5.line: Even though it's nice to receive compliments, I am much happier just being able to support you the best I can, Commander.... Why is that?

home.line: Good work, Commander! Care for a cup of tea?

login.line: Commander, you're back! Me? I'm looking at the clouds.

lose.line: *Cries*... If only I had paid more attention...

mail.line: Commander... hm... what did I want to say... Ah, right! New mail for you!

main1.line: My greatest accomplishments were done just watching the waves like this.

main2.line: Commander, want to watch the clouds with me? I bet we'll see some wonderful things!

main3.line: Don't look at me like that, I've been to plenty of places before!

mission.line: The weather sure is nice... Oh? Commander! You've got some new missions.

mission_complete.line: Commander! How can you also be so forgetful and forget to collect your rewards?

profile.line: I'm the fifth ship of the Kent-class. Although I look like this, I can still pull it off when it counts. During the Battle of the Denmark Strait, I basically saved the day!

propose.line: Hmph, the Commander has finally noticed that under all that hazziness there is brilliance to be found! From now on I can be as lazy as I want. ... Huh? I can't?

touch.line: ... C-Commander?

touch2.line: ... Ah! Commander! If you were here you should have said something.

unlock.line: Where am I...? Ah, excuse me! Do you kno....Oh! You're the commander? This is great! I'm Suffolk, I finally found you!

upgrade.line: Now I can protect myself even if I get lost again!

win_mvp.line: That cloud looks like a.... Oh? We won?

detail.line: Now I can do more than ever before!

drop_descrip.line: Whew... At long last, after all that hard work, I get to wear this uniform as well. Even though all I did was... Huh? Lead by example? Be a role model? I don't get it...

expedition.line: Hum~hum~hum~ Let's plant some flowers~ Oh! Commander, the commission team has returned!

main1.line: This skirt is so long.... One of these days I'll space out and trip on it....

main2.line: Commander, I found an interesting flower, do you want to water it with me?

main3.line: Commander, did you know? After my retrofit, my radar became super strong! Huh? Then keep working? I'm... I'm sorry...

touch.line: Commander, let me pour you some tea. Oh, oh, oh! Be careful!

unlock.line: Whew... At long last, after all that hard work, I get to wear this uniform as well. Even though all I did was... Huh? Lead by example? Be a role model? I don't get it...

battle.line: I'll... give it my utmost...

detail.line: I'm so embarrassed...

drop_descrip.line: Norfolk-class heavy cruiser - Norfolk, Hull Number 78!

expedition.line: It seems a commission's been completed.

feeling2.line: Commander... why did you call for me...? Anything I want to do...? I...would like you to tell me a story... Is that okay?

feeling3.line: Commander, could you tell me more stories...? This time I brought a fairytale book I want you to read to me...

feeling4.line: Commander... I'm afraid of the dark... I can't sleep...So can I sleep with you tonight...?

feeling5.line: Commander, you're so warm... Can I stay here with you forever?

home.line: Commander... if you don't mind, let me give you a massage... Uhh, never mind...

login.line: Commander, welcome back...

lose.line: *Cries*... I'm not so suitable for combat after all...

mail.line: ... New mail. I'm a bit jealous of you, Commander...

main1.line: I... don't like the winter...

main2.line: This name I inherited.... it's heavy.....

main3.line: If everyone doesn't get along... then that's no good.

mission.line: We've received some new missions.... Would you like to take a look, Commander?

mission_complete.line: Commander, your mission rewards are ready. Want me to pick them up for you?

profile.line: I'm... part of... the third group of County-class heavy cruisers... Please don't stare at me... What happened at the Denmark Strait was because my antenna froze... and not because I was scared!

propose.line: Mm... I too want to stay with you, forever and ever...

touch.line: Did I do something wrong...?

touch2.line: Ahh, Commander... You baddie...

unlock.line: H-hello, Commander... I'm... Norfolk... Um... Uh... It's a pleasure to meet you...

upgrade.line: You've given me more courage, Commander...

win_mvp.line: Is it really fine for me to receive such an honor...?

battle.line: I'll do my best to not embarrass my sister!

detail.line: My big sister is definitely cuter, at least compared to me.

drop_descrip.line:
Norfolk-class heavy cruiser, Dorsetshire, Hull Number 40
<color=#ffde38>Unlock build after receiving</color>

expedition.line: Ah, the commission team is back~! Commander, could you let me go on a commission with my sister next time?

feeling1.line: I really can't compare to my sister...

feeling2.line: It's not an exaggeration to say my sister is a world treasure, a gift from the heavens. It's an honor for me to have a sister like her.

feeling3.line: I'm fine the way I am? Aha, you really know how to give compliments, Commander. Compared to my sister though, I'm still but an ugly duckling.

feeling4.line: Ah, could it be that you've developed feelings beyond friendship for me? In that case I must properly respond to them.

feeling5.line: I've never actually thought that I would see such a day coming... How should I react?... Commander, can you teach me?

home.line: Good work, Commander! Come, sit and have some tea. I will tell you some things about my sister~

hp_warning.line: This is a bit of a struggle...

login.line: Welcome back~ What are we going to do today?

lose.line: Guh...! I can't fall here!

mail.line: Commander, there's mail for you~

main1.line: Is it not common knowledge that my big sister is the cutest in the world?

main2.line: For allowing me to use the intel my sister gave me, Bismarck is such a generous person.

main3.line: If it's about my sister, I could speak for three days and three nights and still not be done.

mission.line: Missions, huh? Makes me think of all the time I spent with my sister.

mission_complete.line: Here are your rewards! Please take good care of them.

profile.line: The offshoot of the County-class, the Norfolk-class, includes me and my sisters. My proudest achievement was giving chase to Bismarck and not letting my sister's intel go to waste. I am still far from matching her, so I must become a sister she can be proud of!

propose.line: You sure are a weird person, Commander. To chase after me who is but a tiny star to the bright moon that is my sister. But I too am attracted to you, if you are okay with someone like me then I would be happy to accept.

skill.line: Sister, please lend me your strength!

touch.line: So, Commander, you think I'm actually a bit too big?

touch2.line: You sure are weird, Commander.

unlock.line: Hello, I'm Norfolk's little sister, Dorsetshire~! I look more mature than my sister? Surely you jest! She's my role model!

upgrade.line: I'll continue to do my best, with my big sister as my goal~

win_mvp.line: This gets me one step closer to my big sister~

battle.line: Submit to the power of the Force!

detail.line: Feel free to admire the manifestation of my Force, though this is just the tip of the iceberg.

drop_descrip.line: York-class heavy cruiser - York, Hull Number 90!

expedition.line: The wheels of Fate spineths once more and we move yet closer to Elysium.

feeling1.line: The attraction of my Force has diminished... Could that be because ultimately you were nothing more than a Faker...?

feeling2.line: I can feel the Force guiding our paths. Care to try out this new potion for me?

feeling3.line: ...The attraction of our Friendship grows ever greater! Come, hold my hand, and let us commune!

feeling4.line: This feeling... Unmistakably, as long as you're by my side, I can unleash unlimited amounts of power. Is this the power born of our connected hearts, Love?

feeling5.line: I cannot control the explosions in my heart...! Come, hold me tight and we shall join forces and defeat our foes... Eek!

home.line: It is necessary to rest after a battle. Come, have a drink and relax.

hp_warning.line: This is a trial of fate...!

login.line: Back from your training? Come, Fate is calling for us.

lose.line: Guh.... This is the Nightmare of Suda Bay!

mail.line: This... may be a communication from the Unknown.

main1.line: This a special drink I've made, come, drink it and leave not even a drop!

main2.line: The Force may be essential, but one mustn't drown in its power.

main3.line: If battles are my destined Fortune then may they be even more fierce.

mission.line: The Tribulation calls to us.

mission_complete.line: Tribulations are not solely a quest for strength, but also the rewards along with it. Don't forget.

profile.line: The nameship of the York-class heavy cruisers? That is merely an alias... One day I will conquer the Nightmare of Suda Bay, and become the Master of fate itself.

propose.line: The time of the Promise descends upon us. O, Commander, take my hand and let us mend this world!

touch.line: The flow of the Force, can you feel it?

touch2.line: Bodily contact holds no significance at all to such a noble soul... Aahh!

unlock.line: If you were able to find me then you are also a user of the Force, no? I'm York, the magic-wielding York-class heavy cruiser. Let us fight against Fortune together.

upgrade.line: I can feel it, the Force courses through my body!

win_mvp.line: Be engulfed by darkness!

detail.line: The figure that suddenly showed up inside empty classrooms turned out to just be Eldridge. The mysterious stack of books in the library was nothing more than a Misdirection left by the Occult Club. And, the legends of the Ace who cloned herself to lead every sports club to victory; well, she was actually that incredible... But the Mastermind still hasn't appeared. Has my Investigation been misguided?

drop_descrip.line: The school has recently been consumed by a series of Mysteries... there must be some Mastermind lurking behind the scenes. Yes, another Tribulation awaits me! I shall part the veil and reveal all Truths!

home.line: Without delving further into the Zone, we will not be able to uncover the Truth. Luckily, with you here, I will be able to enter realms normally inaccessible to me!

login.line: Now then, let us begin today's Investigation! The Mastermind will fall into our trap sooner or later!

main1.line: Eyepatch? Nay. This is a tool that is necessary to seal off a portion of my Force.

main2.line: Difficult Words, annoying Formulae... Curses, will I be defeated by these things before I am able to reveal the Truth?!

main3.line: Exeter struggles with her Tests on a daily basis, but that is for the best. The true Tribulations are mine alone to bear.

touch.line: Until all Truths are revealed and the Mastermind's identity is brought to light, I cannot relent!

touch2.line: Eeek! Just now, could it be... There's no doubt about it. The Mastermind took over your body to issue me a Warning!

unlock.line: The school has recently been consumed by a series of Mysteries... there must be some Mastermind lurking behind the scenes. Yes, another Tribulation awaits me! I shall part the veil and reveal all Truths!

detail.line: Jamaica, Z36... Through this arduous battle, I have met many companions who also see through the veil. Now, I am no longer alone in my Rebellion against Fate!

drop_descrip.line: O Unfathomable King of the slumbering depths, hear the call of my Force and step into this world through the Azur Gate! ...Huh, Commander? Why did you show up?

home.line: Ohhhhh... The bastions of white sand were instantly reoriginated by the waves... such is the might of the Unfathomable Force!

login.line: You're back? Then let us continue. This time, the Unfathomable will respond to our summons!

mail.line: The messenger has returned from the depths. Could it be a message from the Unfathomable?

main1.line: So, the first summoning failed. Such are the tribulations exacted by the Unfathomable. But I shall not capitulate so easily!

main2.line: What's the matter, Commander...? Ah, could it be... the Unfathomable has left a clue upon my body?!

main3.line: Bloody hell, if not for the fact that my Force is nullified by the slumbering depths' domain, I could delve even deeper in the search for Truth!

touch.line: Excellent, let us combine our Force and channel it into this magic circle.

touch2.line: Ahh! ...No, can it be, your mind has been corrupted by the Unfathomable?

unlock.line: O Unfathomable King of the slumbering depths, hear the call of my Force and step into this world through the Azur Gate! ...Huh, Commander? Why did you show up?

detail.line: Shall we strengthen our oath? Then take this Soul String and connect it to my spirit! Excellent! Our bonds have grown even– Hm? What's the matter, Commander?

drop_descrip.line: Whoa... Is this my Uniform for the ceremony known as the Oath of Purity? Hohoho... This must be fate. Join me, Commander, and we shall make the world right once more!

feeling5.line: I'd presumed the ceremony would bring my Heart's explosions under control, but it instead only made them worse... Commander, you must hold me tight now, lest the Force swallow me whole! ...Oh, gosh!

home.line: There you are, my Soulmate! Please have a seat and drink from my special bonding potion!

login.line: Welcome back! I knew you were coming from the moment the Soul String began to fluctuate!

lose.line: Ahh... I tumble into the Nightmare's maws...

main1.line: The string that connects us is as strong as steel, Commander!

main2.line: Is the Soul String on too tight? Then let me make just... Ahem! What you feel is simply the Pressure of our bond, exerted at the moment of connection!

main3.line: If fate compels us to fight, then fight I will, with all my body and soul!

mission.line: We've received new Commands from up above. Together, we shall carry them out!

mission_complete.line: We've accomplished another Command! Can you feel the surge of Force?

touch.line: I feel your Essence of Love flowing into me!

touch2.line: Mgh...! Commander... I can't take much more Force... Eek!

unlock.line: Whoa... Is this my Uniform for the ceremony known as the Oath of Purity? Hohoho... This must be fate. Join me, Commander, and we shall make the world right once more!

detail.line: If the Force means something, it means having the will to always fight! And I will fight until I've overcome my destiny!

drop_descrip.line: This is no mere Upgrade, this is an Awakening! I will alter the course of fate itself!

home.line: I can hear the voice of Fate distinctly calling for me... Is this a new skill I've acquired...?!

login.line: For us to meet in this place, at this hour... There is no mistaking it; this is fate!

main1.line: I can feel the Force's power coursing through my body!

main2.line: I am a genius! I've perfected the Formula... Oh, Commander, good timing! I'd like you to taste this special concoction of mine!

main3.line: Once I feared the Nightmare of Suda Bay... but now, I shall prove that I can overcome it!

touch.line: Now, grasp my hand firmly! ... Could you feel my enhanced Force?

touch2.line: W-wait! Continue, and my Force will swallow you whole– Eek!

unlock.line: This is no mere Upgrade, this is an Awakening! I will alter the course of fate itself!

battle.line: I swear upon the honour of the Crown that I, Exeter, shall fulfill my duties and my destiny!

detail.line: I'm counting on you for the inspection, Commander.

drop_descrip.line: York-class heavy cruiser - Exeter, Hull Number 68!

expedition.line: The girls who went out on a commissions have returned. It is my duty to at least receive them properly, Commander.

feeling1.line: Please do not bring shame upon the royal family.

feeling2.line: Commander, don't be blinded by romance.

feeling3.line: Living with the royal family means I cannot decide my own fate. It is great to have met someone as excellent as you, Commander.

feeling4.line: Commander... actually... I was thinking, if you were a normal person and not a commander, would I come to like you as well...?

feeling5.line: What's important is the present. If there is such a thing as fate in this world... I believe we were destined to meet.

home.line: Exeter has returned to port! I will prepare the after-action reports right away!

hp_warning.line: May honour protect us!

login.line: As a royal elite, I shall not disappoint you, Commander!

lose.line: Curses... I shall have my revenge!

mail.line: Mail for you, Commander. I hope it is good news!

main1.line: I can feel the honour of being in the Royal Navy no matter where I am!

main2.line: York is talking nonsense yet again...

main3.line: My skirt gets wet all the time... Should I change into something a bit more suitable for battle?

mission.line: Please make sure to fulfill your duties - in the name of the Crown!

mission_complete.line: Honours and rewards have been delivered.

profile.line: Exeter, York-class heavy cruiser number two, reporting in! I took part in chasing down Admiral Graf Spee. No matter how numerous the opposition, I shall never back down when fighting for the honour of the Royal Navy!

propose.line: For better for worse, for richer for poorer, in sickness and in health, to love and to cherish, till death us do part, according to God's holy ordinance; and there to I give thee my troth, Commander.

skill.line: For the glory of the royal family!

touch.line: Even though I'm a member of the royal family... you still treat me as an equal, Commander. I'm touched.

touch2.line: ...!! T-this kind of... please, don't... As a member of the royal family... if someone saw us like this...

unlock.line: Exeter, York-class heavy cruiser number two, reporting in! In the name of the Royal Navy, I swear that I shall contribute to your cause, Commander!

upgrade.line: For the honour of the royal family, I shall not be humiliated!

win_mvp.line: I am the successor of a long line of royals, and shall embrace my destiny with countless victories to come!

detail.line: York took a look at the roses earlier and went off about them being "Bloody Roses" or something. Just more of the usual, huh?

drop_descrip.line: Cheers, Commander. I'm glad that the party is a success. Well, I should take care as well to not sully the honour of the royal family with my actions.

home.line: The lovely smell of roses makes for a wonderful atmosphere. Please relax for a bit, Commander.

login.line: Sorry for the wait. Well then, let us head to the party. I, on behalf of the Royal Navy, would like to give you a warm welcome.

main1.line: I'd really like for my sister to stay silent around the others so as to not sully the glory and dignity of the Royal family, but...

main2.line: The parties Her Highness hosts are always fantastic. Everything about them is just so perfect!

main3.line: I can't stop worrying about the off chance that I'll spill some wine on this dress...

touch.line: Eek! I almost got some wine on the dress!

touch2.line: Aah! Don't surprise me like that! I ended up spilling some wine on my dress...

unlock.line: Cheers, Commander. I'm glad that the party is a success. Well, I should take care as well to not sully the honour of the royal family with my actions.

drop_descrip.line: Commander, what do you think? I look more mature than I did before... right?

home.line: Good work, Commander. Would you like to take a little break?

login.line: As a royal elite... Ah, um... Welcome back, Commander.

main1.line: Even though I said I had become more mature, there are things that can't be changed overnight...

main2.line: nil

main3.line: My clothes won't hang down into the water now, but don't you think this is a bit too revealing...?

touch2.line: Eek! Commander... P-please pay attention to the time and place...

unlock.line: Commander, what do you think? I look more mature than I did before... right?

battle.line: For the sake of not bringing shame upon the fleet, let us fight!

detail.line: Shropshire can be quite a handful to deal with... But, I suppose since she's the type of person who won't ever let herself draw the short straw, you should just let her be.

drop_descrip.line: London-class heavy cruiser – Sussex.

expedition.line: And that should be time... Commander, the commission team should be returning any moment now.

feeling1.line: London is too much of a people-pleaser, and all her coddling seems to have turned you into mush.

feeling2.line: The way London always has that smile plastered on her face no matter who she's around just rubs me the wrong way.

feeling3.line: London is the type of person who would easily be deceived by a bad person, but still continue to smile despite knowing that... Jeez, just why does she have to have that kind of personality...

feeling4.line: *sigh*... What's more, when I went to bring this up with her, she just gave me a pat on the head and said, "Thanks, Sussex, but it'll be alright." So, nothing changed at all... Good grief, why do people have to be so difficult...?

feeling5.line: At least I'll feel at ease leaving London in your care... No, you'll have to become even more distinguished, to the point that I won't be able to look away from you... huh? What did I just say...?

home.line: There's a lot to report still, but for now, good work.

hp_warning.line: Everyone, tighten the formation!

login.line: Are you ready to begin working? Don't come running to me if you find out later that you're missing something.

lose.line: This was due to my failure as a leader. Don't blame yourselves, everyone.

mail.line: Please do not forget to check your mail.

main1.line: Excessive kindness can become poison. One must be strict when the situation calls for it.

main2.line: If you have time to gawk at me, you should get your work done first. After you finish, then you can, um...

main3.line: ... If you're tired, get some rest. I'm not saying this for your sake - it's simply better if you're ready to give it your all when the situation calls for it.

mission.line: Before acting, one must first consider the most efficient way of getting things done - you haven't forgotten, right?

mission_complete.line: So these are the mission rewards! Commander, you're quite the capable one~

profile.line: Other than the coastal defence battle in the Mediterranean Sea and that one naval battle up north, I pretty much carried out all my missions normally... Well, there was that one time I needed serious repairs... b-but anyway! Since I'm here, I'll continue to put my best foot forward. Commander, I expect the same from you!

propose.line: At first, I was strict with you only because I wanted to ease the burden on my sister... but gradually, I began to hope that you would become the most distinguished person in my life... As of now, you've already become that person...

touch.line: Commander, your collar is messed up. And your hair too... Hold still, I'll fix it for you.

touch2.line: Commander, sit right there! Good grief... I'll have to re-teach you some basic manners...!

unlock.line: So you're the Commander? Hmph! Let's make one thing clear: I'm not easygoing like my sister, London. I'll expect you to have your act together!

upgrade.line: Thank you. I'll continue to work hard on the next mission.

win_mvp.line: Don't think that winning is the only thing that matters. There are still many things I could have done better.

detail.line: London's complaining about how she doesn't want to wear her swimsuit again because it's "too revealing" ...*sigh*. She could probably benefit from learning to think more positively about herself, like Shropshire does.

drop_descrip.line: What are you spacing out for? Have you not gotten tired of staring at all the swimsuits yet? Good grief... Are you able to help set up the parasol or the beach chairs at least?

expedition.line: Commander, when you go welcome the commission fleet back, can you take this plate of ice-cold watermelon with you? It's a little courtesy from me.

home.line: How many times have I already told you, Commander? Finish your missions first before taking time off.

login.line: Commander, how's your work coming along? If I find out that you've snuck out here... Hehe~

main1.line: People aren't changing into swimsuits just for your viewing pleasure... Got it?

main2.line: You should watch yourself around Shropshire. That girl develops a variety of... how should I say this? ...Bad habits during the summer?

main3.line: Hm? It's nothing. When we're at the beach, you can do whatever you want. *sigh*... It's just that... looking at your mug makes me really uneasy for some reason...

mission.line: A mission? I'll also come with you... That's my job as secretary after all!

mission_complete.line: Did you buy this ice cream for me...? Th-thanks...

touch.line: Commander, are you also interested in surfing? Hehe, I'll teach you the basics.

touch2.line: You just won't learn your lesson...!

unlock.line: What are you spacing out for? Have you not gotten tired of staring at all the swimsuits yet? Good grief... Are you able to help set up the parasol or the beach chairs at least?

battle.line: The Royal Navy will prevail! Onwards!

detail.line: Miss Renown, do please let the Maids handle banquet security... the Commander is already here Honestly, how are we supposed to start the party without you?!

drop_descrip.line: What are you staring at me for? I'm just the same as any of the others... Y-you have a few more hands to shake? Of course...

feeling5.line: "If you want a d-drink, you can enjoy it like this..." That Ajax, how could she do something so wasteful...? I... What am I doing...?! Commander...?!

home.line: N-now that we're through with battle, perhaps we could relax a... No, we have to focus on the party for now!

login.line: How is your work coming along? Keep faffing about like that and you'll be putting in overtime!

main1.line: That Ajax, she's going to do that to the Commander again... I have to do something about her... Ah, it's nothing!

main2.line: How long are you going to stare at me like that? Don't you have anything better to do?

main3.line: My sister London is here... Phew, looks like I don't need to worry. I mean, it's London, there was never anything to worry about in the first place.

touch.line: Commander, look how crooked this is. You really must pay more attention to your formalwear... Right, there we are.

touch2.line: W-wait! Commander?! Eek...?!

unlock.line: What are you staring at me for? I'm just the same as any of the others... Y-you have a few more hands to shake? Of course...

battle.line: This is for you!

detail.line: Owner! Squeeeeze! Giving you huggles makes me all sleepy... *yawn*... Zzzzz...

drop_descrip.line: Heavy cruiser – Cheshire.

expedition.line: The commission team has come back, Owner!

feeling1.line: I loved you, Owner, I really did...

feeling2.line: I'm gonna make lots of yummy sweets for mew, Owner♪ ...Wait, what was step one again? I forgot...

feeling3.line: Do I start with the salt or the sugar? Or do I mix the batter? Oh, and then there's the juicy fruits Drake gave me! What do mew think, Owner?

feeling4.line: Aww... You were right, Owner. You can't make good sweets by mixing random stuff together... But I'm not gonna give up! I'll make something yummy eventually, you'll see!

feeling5.line: Lookie, Owner! I made this cookie with the help of my friends! ...Huh? Why is it moving? Oh, oopsie! This isn't a cookie, it's a manjuu! Sorry I got them mixed up, Owner!

headtouch.line: Try on this kitty ear headband, Owner! Come on, have a go!

home.line: Owner! It's fine if you forget to bring me a gift, but you can't forget to give me huggles!

hp_warning.line: I'm not giving up!

login.line: Owneeeeer! Mrreow~ Mmhh, you're so warm♪

lose.line: Do we fight back meow, before they catch on? No?

mail.line: There's mail for you! I wish I could read it, but I don't know most of these words...

main1.line: Hey, Bel! Show me how to make good sweets!

main2.line: You think I'm cute as a kitten? Heehee, you're making me blush, Owner♪

main3.line: Drake! Please buy me a gift on your next trip! Something sweet would be nice!

mission.line: You're amazing, Owner! You can do all these missions that are too much for me!

mission_complete.line: Don't stop meow, Owner! Go get your rewards, then it's time for the next mission!

profile.line: I'm Cheshire, the heavy cruiser! I'll do my best to be helpful to mew, Owner! I dunno exactly what I'm gonna do, but I'll do it well! Whee~♡

propose.line: Wowie, a present! ...It's a ring? Ah, I get it, you wanna trade with me! Okey-dokey! In return, you geeet... Yup, you get me! Huggles♪

touch.line: What do you have for me, Owner?

touch2.line: Here's another one for you, Owner!

unlock.line: Owneeeeer! Meeeow! Squeeze! Cuddle! Sniff! Heehee~ Here, you can have this as thanks for letting me give you the lovey-dovey cuddly-wuddly!

upgrade.line: Thanks, Owner♪ Have this in return!

win_mvp.line: Look, Owner! I won♪

battle.line: Enemy fleet in sight! All ships, fire at will!

detail.line: All systems functioning properly. Do not worry, Commander.

drop_descrip.line: Renown-class battlecruiser - Renown

expedition.line: The girls who went out on a commission have arrived. Please, let me go in their stead next time, Commander. I... don't like being on the receiving end of things.

feeling1.line: Commander, you cannot continue like this.

feeling2.line: Love letter? How does one love something like a letter? People love all sorts of things, but that one I cannot understand.

feeling3.line: Commander, you always ask me to accompany you for walks. Is something bothering you?

feeling4.line: ... Why would you arrange candles in a heart on the beach? And then... why did you cry when I said "aren't you afraid of the fire being extinguished by the wind"?

feeling5.line: Don't worry, I'm not that dense. Next time I will bring a cap and cover up the candles for you. Then you can tell me what is truly on your mind.

home.line: I will review this operation's performance and report back to you as soon as I can.

hp_warning.line: Speed is the best defense!

login.line: Commander, please give me your orders.

lose.line: ...I am sorry, Commander... I failed to live up to your expectations.

mail.line: If you have time, please look over the mail.

main1.line: No instructions, Commander? So we're using the, 'wait and see' strategy...?

main2.line: My propeller? Hood bumped into me one day, and before I reacted I received this in apology.

main3.line: What? You think Renown is cute...? Well, on her behalf, I give you my tha... Wait, what?!

mission.line: Commander, we still have missions to complete!

mission_complete.line: Please, claim the mission rewards!

profile.line: I am Renown, Battlecruiser of the Royal Fleet of the Royal Navy. I have experienced issues in both great wars, and have countless accomplishments for which I am proud. No matter what orders you give me, Commander, it is my duty to carry them out with all of my strength!

propose.line: Wait, Commander... Let... let me find some candles...and make a heart... and some covers to prevent them from being blown out.... t-t-then I'll... Please... don't look at me! I must be making a very strange face right now!

touch.line: ... It's a bit strange... Only you have ever done this to me, Commander...

touch2.line: ...!! Commander! I do not intend to resist... but still...

unlock.line: Renown, Battlecruiser of the Royal Fleet of the Royal Navy, at your service. My guns shall aim where your sword points, Commander.

upgrade.line: Your will is the source of my power.

win_mvp.line: Enemy fleet eliminated. Mission complete.

battle.line: Vaporize anything that moves into ash!

detail.line: Hi, Commander! I changed into something a little easier to move around in~

drop_descrip.line: Renown-class battlecruiser - Repulse

expedition.line: You've made me stay with you inside, so, as your punishment, you'll have to accompany me to check up on the completed commissions. Let's go!

feeling1.line: It's kinda boring being here with you... I'm heading out for a while!

feeling2.line: It's so boring indoors! Being outdoors is so much better... Commander, don't you feel bad sitting around all day? Let's go out and get some fresh air!

feeling3.line: My sister always says I'm too impatient, but I can't be bothered thinking everything through. Besides, you're always around, so I'll leave all the thinking to you, Commander!

feeling4.line: Com~man~der! Gotcha! Hmm? I'm too close? Hey, what's the problem with that~ Anyway, come and play with me~!

feeling5.line: You know, Commander, I am a girl after all. I'm not so crazy I'd defencelessly cling to someone I don't like. It's about time you noticed...

home.line: You can't rest right after reaching port! Go exercise more!

login.line: Hello, Commander! Let's go beat the heck out of our enemies!

lose.line: Ahh, the enemy was so persistent that I'm starving now... There's no way we could've won like this...

mail.line: Deliverygirl Repulse has arrived with your mail!

main1.line: Hey! Com~man~der~! Let's get some exercise~!

main2.line: You look strong, Commander. Want to spar sometime?

main3.line: Huh? You think I'm impatient?

mission.line: Missions! Missions! More missions!

mission_complete.line: Yes! Our rewards are here!

profile.line: I'm Repulse, a Renown-class battlecruiser. I may not look like much, but I've been tons of places with the higher-ups! Though I prefer going out on my own! "Repairs"? Ahahaha, I'm hoping you won't keep me locked up indoors every day, Commander...
