propose.line: Huh?! You're happy with me? I'm not as elegant as some other royal girls, and I don't dress all that great... But when it comes to my feelings for you, I rank second to none!

touch.line: Huh? I thought you'd be into softer girls than me...

touch2.line: Whoah! S-stop… You're awful! I'm a girl, you know!

unlock.line: I'm Repulse, a Renown-class battlecruiser. I participated in the pursuit of Bismarck, but we couldn't catch up to her. Ever since then I've been a part of Force Z... I don't ever want to see a torpedo again...

upgrade.line: Commander, want to go take a stroll out to sea? I'll protect you!

win_mvp.line: Hooray! We won! Quick, decisive victories are my favourite.

battle.line: May glory be with us today.

detail.line: Feel free to admire the glory of the Royal Navy to your heart's content.

drop_descrip.line: Admiral-class battlecruiser - Hood, Hull Number 51!

expedition.line: Having completed numerous commissions is a sign of glory. May I suggest rewarding those girls?

feeling1.line: *Sigh* Seems like you must learn it the hard way.

feeling2.line: Commander, it's such a great afternoon. Shall we have a chat? ... Hm, alright... I'll talk about the times when I was with Renown.

feeling3.line: Though I speak of being refined at all times, you need not force yourself, Commander. Your normal self is the most charming, after all.

feeling4.line: Hm? I'm too close? A lady must be elegant, but they must also seize the initiative towards the targets of their own affection.

feeling5.line: "Shall I compare thee to a summer's day? Thou art more lovely and more temperate... So long as men can breathe, or eyes can see, so long lives this, and this gives life to thee." ... A beautiful verse. Commander, could you read it out loud to me?

home.line: Commander, may I offer you some warm tea? We can drink it as we review your battle.

hp_warning.line: Even I am slightly angered.

login.line: Welcome back, Commander. Care for a cup of tea?

lose.line: Victory and defeat are commonplace among those who fight, and it is we that have all the time in the world!

mail.line: It's unopened... Commander... It would be ungentlemanly to ignore the messages of others.

main1.line: An outstanding commander must have an in-depth knowledge of tea.

main2.line: This word is... ah, so I read it wrong. Sorry, my eyes fail me.

main3.line: Listen more, speak less. You should listen to the opinions of others, but also retain your own judgment.

mission.line: Commander, we have been entrusted with new missions. Please look through them.

mission_complete.line: With glory comes rewards. Please do not forget about the latter.

profile.line: Indeed, the glory of the Royal Navy now stands before you. Being able to maintain an air of elegance at all times is the hallmark of royalty. The Denmark straits? Soldiers know of victory and defeat alike. It was no more than a temporary setback.

propose.line: Aha, look how nervous you are. You can't convey your feelings to a lady when you're this nervous. However, your feelings have definitely reached my heart... I would happily oblige.

skill.line: Elegance is not just for show.

touch.line: Appropriate contact is indeed essential. Shall we dance?

touch2.line: Commander, you should understand the consequences of disrespecting a lady... Are you prepared?

unlock.line: Are you the commander? Greetings and well met. I am the glory of the Royal Navy: Hood. Wherever I go, victory follows.

upgrade.line: Your efforts will definitely be rewarded.

win_mvp.line: The warm sun and the cool breeze: a brilliant victory.

detail.line: My brilliance is like that of the sun? I'm in a good mood so I'll accept this praise of yours.

drop_descrip.line: What a feast for sore eyes. I feel great~! Vacations really should be at the beach! Let's show Sara your beach ball, Cygnet!

login.line: Good day, Commander. Let not the heat shaketh thy inner peace. Keep calm and carry on!

main1.line: So me and the other girls are going to play beach volleyball The player on my team that scores the least will be subjected to a small punishment game.

main2.line: I can see the whole harbor from the mountain top, this is the best place to watch fireworks.

main3.line: To be elegant at all times is the mannerism befitting of a lady.

touch.line: The beach volleyball game is about to start. Let's find a good place to watch, Commander!

touch2.line: This is exactly why Wales will always be a Prince and never a King.

unlock.line: What a feast for sore eyes. I feel great~! Vacations really should be at the beach! Let's show Sara your beach ball, Cygnet!

detail.line: Rose patterns as well as our Royal Navy's motifs... How splendid this is! I must express my gratitude to those who dyed this kimono.

drop_descrip.line: Thank you for inviting me on this wonderful trip. Now that I have donned this beautiful outfit, shall we partake of a Sakura Empire tea party– leisurely and elegantly?

feeling5.line: "As the heat retreats, harvest melons and eggplants, welcoming Autumn." ...My, what an evocative and refreshing poem. Commander, let's set aside all our worries and enjoy this trip, just the two of us.

home.line: Commander, would you like to try some roasted twig tea? Do be at ease while bathing in its elegant aroma.

login.line: You can have some of the maid team's black tea if you'd like, but why not try some of the Sakura Empire's green tea today?

main1.line: The Higashi Chaya District? ...Oh, isn't that a town famous for its teahouses? Hehe, a perfect place for enjoying the Sakura Empire's tastes and smells. I definitely hope to go there.

main2.line: Add hot water to the matcha and stir gently with this bamboo whisk– The Sakura Empire has a truly profound way of appreciating tea...

main3.line: Commander, why don't you take some photos as reference for Comet and the others? We might as well get as much out of this trip as possible - not just souvenirs, but also sources of inspiration.

touch.line: Commander, how's my technique?

unlock.line: Thank you for inviting me on this wonderful trip. Now that I have donned this beautiful outfit, shall we partake of a Sakura Empire tea party– leisurely and elegantly?

win_mvp.line: A gentle breeze, a soothing fragrance– An elegant victory indeed.

detail.line: Compared to the overly grandiose national parades, I greatly prefer the relaxing companionship of a single escort. Commander, will you be my escort?

drop_descrip.line: Beauty is not always over the rainbow. Sometimes it is right in your backyard. Commander, how would you like to spend this quiet, lovely day right here with me?

home.line: Tea is of paramount importance to a leisurely outing. Naturally, I will leave that to you, Commander.

login.line: The gentle sunlight, and a refreshing breeze – today is a fine day to venture outside.

main1.line: Watch out for the stairs? Indeed, I'll do just that. Thank you for remembering that my eyesight can be troublesome.

main2.line: If you don't have a destination in mind, why not simply enjoy the scenery all around us? For example... the roses in full bloom in this garden.

main3.line: I can see that Bismarck is finally learning to shed the burdens placed upon her shoulders. Hehe, don't you think she should be more true to her feelings?

touch.line: Commander, you'll properly fulfill your duties as my escort, yes?

touch2.line: Commander, when we get back, would you like another lecture on how to properly escort a lady?

unlock.line: Beauty is not always over the rainbow. Sometimes it is right in your backyard. Commander, how would you like to spend this quiet, lovely day right here with me?

battle.line: It's time I showed you the style of a royal lady.

detail.line: Horseback riding isn't really something to be praised. It's part of raising any royal lady... You say the others were impressed? My, and you, too?

drop_descrip.line: Whoa, there... There you are, Commander. You could have waited at the clubhouse... Why yes, the view is just beautiful, isn't it? Hahaha, thank you for bringing me here today.

home.line: Thank you for your work, Commander. The weather is lovely, so I brought this lovely little horse from the stable to greet you.

login.line: Commander, how will you be going back? Would you like to ride together on my horse?

main1.line: Commander, if you're willing, you should try feeding horses. I promise it's adorable to see them eating right out of your hand.

main2.line: Riding a horse through vast expanses of greenery is lovely, but I think I'd like to try riding on the coast sometime. Of course, I'll need the proper equipment.

main3.line: Cygnet wants to try riding, too, so I'm going to pick out clothes for her later. Want to join me, Commander? Heehee.

touch.line: Riding raging waves, running through the plains on a horse—Either way, it's a piece of cake for me. Hahaha!

touch2.line: I hope you'll use a gentle touch with the horse, as you do with me.

unlock.line: Whoa, there... There you are, Commander. You could have waited at the clubhouse... Why yes, the view is just beautiful, isn't it? Hahaha, thank you for bringing me here today.

win_mvp.line: Whether you're on the lush plains or the open seas, the winds of victory are ever so pleasant.

drop_descrip.line: If the smooth path only allows one person to travel at a time, then I’ll gladly walk the path not taken with you hand-in-hand.

home.line: Commander, everytime I picture your face, my heart races and my spirit soars like a skylark at dawn.

login.line: Don't be so impatient, Commander. The boundless sea is rushing towards you with open arms.

main1.line: Which black tea did you prepare for us, Commander? Please allow me to build up my anticipation for this tea party.

main2.line: Commander, once the seven seas have returned to peace, let’s organize another “Imperial Cruise”.

touch.line: Commander, let me teach you the proper etiquettes of being with a lady.

touch2.line: There’s no need to be in such a rush... I’ll always be by your side.

battle.line: Royal Navy, search and destroy!

detail.line: There are many things that I do not understand in the Codex of the Royal Knights! Commander, can you offer me any guidance?

drop_descrip.line: Renown-Class Battlecruiser - HMS Renown

expedition.line: Commander! The commission fleet will return to port in ten minutes! Please... Wait, did I get the time wrong...?

feeling1.line: Commander, please get your act together! Renown shall not abandon you!

feeling2.line: I mustn't neglect my training or my studies... I'll do my utmost each day so that I may become a proper knight. Commander, do you want to follow this path as well?

feeling3.line: Work is important, but taking breaks is also important! Coming from a Royal Knight, you're overworking yourself! After you finish this, please make sure to get some rest!

feeling4.line: Commander, why did the knights in that book betray their own king? Renown is nothing like those knights! I would never betray you even if it cost me my life!

feeling5.line: So, Commander, is it fine for Renown to always stay here? Being close to you gives me strength, and above else, my love for you is absolute! ...Huh? Did I say something weird...?

headtouch.line: Myahh?! Wh-what are you doing?!

home.line: You're not too bad, Commander... If Renown also works harder, will she be able to... be like you one day?

hp_warning.line: Renown shall break your lines!

login.line: Commander, Renown is awaiting your orders! Please issue today's commands!

lose.line: My apologies, Commander...

mail.line: This one's for you, Commander. This one's also for you... and this one too...

main1.line: As long as Renown is here, no harm shall befall you, Commander!

main2.line: The serious and dedicated Little Renown is cute? I see, I'll be sure to pass on the message to... wait, what?

main3.line: It's not just you. Everyone here at port is truly amazing... I must redouble my efforts...!

mission.line: Commander, please allow Renown to handle the missions! H-huh? Commander, you're doing them all yourself?!

mission_complete.line: Heave-ho... C-Commander, the m-mission rewards are... wooooahhhh!!

profile.line: I am the battlecruiser Renown, and I was training in Govan before coming here! Being able to weigh anchor ahead of schedule is a testament to my strength... Indeed! I will do my utmost to live up to everyone's expectations!

propose.line: A promise ring? I know about this! Um, "I pledge to defend the weak and act with valor..." Oh, all I have to do is read this? Well then... "through thick and thin, we shall share our pain and willingly give love eternal." ...Commander, does that sound right?

skill.line: The enemy shall never see my back turned!

touch.line: Candy? I'll have you know, Commander... Renown has no use for such things!

touch2.line: Commander! That's in violation of Royal etiquette!

unlock.line: The Renown-class battlecruiser Renown has come to join your ranks! My stature may be small, but my desire to succeed is great!

upgrade.line: For the Commander's sake, I'm ready... to become stronger!

win_mvp.line: I've done it...! Wait, no! The books clearly teach that it is foolish to gloat over a single victory! Self control... self control...!

battle.line: Witness the might of a super-dreadnought!

detail.line: Peasant! Who permitted you to peak?! I-I have not prepared myself yet...

drop_descrip.line: Queen Elizabeth-class battleship - Queen Elizabeth, Hull Number 00!

expedition.line: The subjects tasked with a commission have returned. Go at once and see if they brought me a tribute!

feeling1.line: You useless servant! I will have you relieved of your post!

feeling2.line: Work hard for the great Elizabeth!

feeling3.line: I'm sitting here for just a moment because I like the mood! Don't start getting any strange ideas!

feeling4.line: H-hmph! You have been slightly exceeding in your duty, thus I will make an exception and promote you to captain of the Royal Guard! When I call for you, you will come hither immediately! Understood? Immediately! Swiftly! At maximum speed!

feeling5.line: Hey, can't you just leave your work to your underlings? How can you be a proper consort if you aren't always by my side?! I-I would be so lonely...

home.line: A fine display, I shall be benevolent and permit you to rest.

hp_warning.line: Why are you spacing out?! Hurry! Get them!

login.line: Despicable, to have me wait on you for so long!

lose.line: How despicable! To have brought shame to the great Elizabeth! You better remember this!

mail.line: I have no interest in the contents of your mail... Mmh...

main1.line: Being petite is a noble characteristic, understand?

main2.line: You're saying I bumped into you? That's because you didn't make way for the Queen!

main3.line: Do not touch my belly, it's rude!

mission.line: Hurry and finish the mission! Do not skip your work!

mission_complete.line: Kneel before me and accept your mission rewards!

profile.line: I am the super-dreadnought of the Royal Navy. Make sure to remember my name! My military achievements? I let my subjects take care of those kind of things. I simply need to watch them do their work!

propose.line: Finally you have arrived before me. Foolish servant! Just how long did you intend to make me wait?! ...But I acknowledge your endeavors. Come here, I am giving you permission to take my hand! Yes! From now on I will always be with you!

touch.line: Please do not touch our noble body so casually

touch2.line: W-wait... You fool, what are you doing?! I-I'll sentence you to death!

unlock.line: Are you the commander? You are still 100,000 years too early to command me! Well, I shall be generous and give you a chance... From this day on, you will be one of my faithful servants!

upgrade.line: I have no need to get any stronger! But... well, if you're going through to effort of doing it, then...

win_mvp.line: Piece of cake! There are no mistakes in my actions!

detail.line: We shall allow you to bask in our splendor! ... Now out with your praise already! Lowly servant!

drop_descrip.line: Hah haah! You're a lucky servant this evening! We shall allow you to accompany us to the party! ... B-but it's not like I chose you because I like you! I just... Yes! I just sort of chose randomly! Got it?!

main1.line: So as not to embarrass me at the party, you need to practice your dancing! Y-you could practice with m-... You don't want to bother me?! B-b-but it really wouldn't be much trouble!

main2.line: It is a servant's duty to clear the way for the Queen, are we clear?!

main3.line: Bel! Is everything ready for the party? N-not that I'm excited about it or anything! I'm just supervising my maids!

touch.line: Hm, hmph! ... Considering the lengths to which you went for this party, we shall overlook your boorishness for now. Be grateful for your queen's leniency! Lowly servant!

touch2.line: Aie! Warspite!! Level your fifteen-inch guns at this insolent servant! Off with its heeaaaaaad!!

unlock.line: Hah haah! You're a lucky servant this evening! We shall allow you to accompany us to the party! ... B-but it's not like I chose you because I like you! I just... Yes! I just sort of chose randomly! Got it?!

battle.line: This is the Queen's stage!

drop_descrip.line: Now this is a stage worthy of our majesty! You are not to leave our sight, servant! Let your passions burn for me!

headtouch.line: How improper!

home.line: Fine work. As a reward, you may have this portrait of me. Keep it well!

login.line: Hah hah! Spread the word, servant! Let all be dazzled by our splendour!

main1.line: "Grovel before me, servant!" ...Hm? It feels a bit different from usual...?

main2.line: Like so...? Is this cuter? Very good then, well done, Matchless. My servant will be blown away!

main3.line: A maid idol...? What is it Bel and Gloucester have been teaching you?

mission.line: An offer for me? W- well, it is a Queen's duty to hear out the commoners...

mission_complete.line: I've included a favour in your rewards. Show me your gratitude!

touch.line: Encore? Heh heh. I could give you a few more!

touch2.line: Watch your hands, servant! Or it's the oubliette for you!

unlock.line: Now this is a stage worthy of our majesty! You are not to leave our sight, servant! Let your passions burn for me!

win_mvp.line: Valiant, spread word of our victory far and wide!

detail.line: Servant, do advise me on these "club activities." I have heard much commotion about "idols" or something like that...

drop_descrip.line: Hehe, behold the new outfit that I had Akashi make for me! Impressive, no? Prostrate yourself before the elegant charm of my school uniform, servant~♪

home.line: Mathematics, check. History, check... Physical Education? Pass! A noble like me playing basketball with commoners? Unthinkable!

login.line: Your Queen has arrived! Do make way, my subjects!

mail.line: Time to check my locker~♪ ...Hm, a note from Newcastle? Um... "Already cleaned for you." ...Oh, I see.

main1.line: Bel, where's my cake...? Servant, take Neptune with you and make yourself useful!

main2.line: Warspite, how fares the tea party plans with Nagato and the others? Have George and the knights deliver the invites to them!

main3.line: "Field trip?" Let us make our way to Sardegna! Have Veneto regale us with the most exquisite banquet!

touch.line: Did you go buy candy from the student store? Heh, even a noble such as myself must learn the tastes of commoners.

unlock.line: Hehe, behold the new outfit that I had Akashi make for me! Impressive, no? Prostrate yourself before the elegant charm of my school uniform, servant~♪

win_mvp.line: Ehehe, why it's only natural, of course! Nothing like that self-proclaimed "spiritual leader!"

battle.line: Fight for your queen!

detail.line: "Be not enchanted by dreams of silver and gold. There are yet many ways to earn your coin." ...Well said, Warspite.

drop_descrip.line: Did I hear that you're supposed to give out red envelopes during the Dragon Empery's New Year? This is a fine chance to display the magnanimity of the Queen of the Royal Navy! ...Don't just run off with your gift! Spread the word of my glory, my servant!

home.line: You've done well. This red envelope is your reward!

mail.line: You are to check your mail at once...! And I do not mean this red envelope!

main1.line: Servant, bright us some of that Dragon Empery tea! We wish to compare it with Edinburgh's black brew!

main2.line: Heh heh, you doubt the wealth of a queen? Just you wait for the next Royal Banquet!

main3.line: It seems different places have different customs for New Year's gifts, eh? Hmph, no matter. So long as you carry on as a good servant, we may reward you at any time!

touch.line: You have our permission to collect this New Year's gift!

touch2.line: Watch your hands, servant! I curse you to lose your wallet!

unlock.line: Did I hear that you're supposed to give out red envelopes during the Dragon Empery's New Year? This is a fine chance to display the magnanimity of the Queen of the Royal Navy! ...Don't just run off with your gift! Spread the word of my glory, my servant!

detail.line: You're not my master! I'm your master!

drop_descrip.line: Warspite, what in the world is all this... The Maid Team has to sift through all this paperwork?! I'm tired already... I wish I never mentioned wanting to experience what it's like to be a maid... And you, stop staring and help me already, servant!

home.line: Nothing beats Edinburgh's hand-brewed black tea! Wouldn't you agree, my servant?

mail.line: I shall check the mail in your stead, my servant! ...Hmm, I wonder what this says...

main1.line: Warspite, what's taking you so long? ...What do you mean you can't move around easily in a skirt?!

main2.line: Being a maid is no easier than carrying out public duties... So come help me already, you lowly servant!

main3.line: Bel, come clean up around the office! Heheh, any job that someone as noble as me carries out becomes a noble endeavor in turn!

mission.line: Hurry up and take care of the missions, you lowly servant!

mission_complete.line: Excellent, the rewards are here! Warspite, take these over to my servant!

touch2.line: Do you also do this to the girls in the Maid Team...?

unlock.line: Warspite, what in the world is all this... The Maid Team has to sift through all this paperwork?! I'm tired already... I wish I never mentioned wanting to experience what it's like to be a maid... And you, stop staring and help me already, servant!

battle.line: Servant, we go together!

detail.line: Hmph! A noble queen would never swim with the common folk! ...I-it's not because I can't swim! Fine. Let's race to that rock! I'll prove to you that I am a capable swimmer!

drop_descrip.line: Servant, what do you think you're doing?! Instead of wasting your life working, go have some fun in the sea for once! We went out of our way to come to the beach, so do not disappoint me!

expedition.line: What's that, little ones? The commission team is back? Good! I shall go and greet them!

headtouch.line: Wh-what are you doing?! A reward, you say? Well, this is hardly...

home.line: My, you've really given it your all! Heheh, I hereby permit you to rest! Take it easy by your queen's side, servant!

login.line: I left Valiant with all the busy work so I could take it easy today! Why don't you leave your work to someone else for once?

lose.line: Grrr... Servant! We will devise a plan to get them back!

main1.line: A beach party? Seattle, where is this coming from? ...Not that I mind, once my servant and Hiei arrive.

main2.line: Richelieu, wait! Why are you bringing the Meowfficers?! And Jean Bart, don't just stand there and watch! Stop her!

main3.line: You don't see the Royal Maids around? Well, of course not; I gave them the day off. My servant and the knights are here, and Neptune and Cheshire have always wanted to try maid work anyway! I see no cause for concern.

mission.line: You still have missions? Mm, I suppose I am a little concerned about Valiant...

mission_complete.line: The rewards have arrived! Hood, go take a look with the destroyers.

touch.line: How kind and perceptive of you to offer to refill my tea for me! Make sure you bring sweets, too.

touch2.line: Th-that was an accident, right?

unlock.line: Servant, what do you think you're doing?! Instead of wasting your life working, go have some fun in the sea for once! We went out of our way to come to the beach, so do not disappoint me!

win_mvp.line: Heheh!♪ George, be sure to record my accomplishments! And those of my servant, too!

battle.line: I would never let the commander's enemies escape!

detail.line: Don't be blinded by statistics. Victory depends on far more!

drop_descrip.line: Queen Elizabeth-class battleship - Warspite, Hull Number 03!

expedition.line: Commissions? I suppose I do miss running around on errands... Let's go. We need to welcome back those hard workers!

feeling1.line: Would you please not act like we're close...

feeling2.line: Commander, want to hear about the history of the Royal Navy? Maybe I should tell you something about the generals who used to accompany me.

feeling3.line: I'm not very elegant? I'm sorry that I'm not like Hood or the others... No... I'm not talking about my body...

feeling4.line: How do I put this... I'm considered to be one of the older girls, yet my body is like this... It might be unbecoming of one my age to compete with the younger girls, but I wanted to at least be attractive to you… What is a lady meant to do…

feeling5.line: Well, enough of that. I'm Warspite, the one who spites war. Hmph! However, whosoever tries to take the Commander away from me will first have to face my cannons!

home.line: Whew, not a bad fight. Let's rest for a while.

hp_warning.line: So this is how harsh the battlefield can be.

login.line: As long as I'm here, we can deal with any enemy, no matter how far they are.

lose.line: My damage control isn't functioning?! I've lost control of my steering wheel as well! Why now, at such a critical moment?!

mail.line: You've got mail, Commander!

main1.line: Your orders are absolute, Commander. They shall be my highest priority.

main2.line: This grand old lady can run faster without a skirt. Want to race with me?

main3.line: If you make fun of me one more time, you'll be eating my 15 inch shells!

mission.line: Accept your new mission and then get ready to head out, Commander!

mission_complete.line: Missions give out rewards once you complete them. Don't forget that!

profile.line: Elizabeth-class fast battleship, Warspite, reporting in. I hold the record for the longest ranged hit on a moving target. I've come close to being defeated quite a few times, but I managed to cheat death every time. This must be my fate.

propose.line: Finally the day has come! It looks like my efforts were not in vain... Let's go, Commander, I'm prepared for this. Officers, draw swords!

touch.line: Body contact...? I don't hate it...

touch2.line: Just so you understand, I'm definitely not that sort of, erm...

unlock.line: Greetings, I'm Warspite. I hold the record for the longest ranged hit on a moving target. Surprised? I'm smaller than you thought? Looks like we need to have a long talk...

upgrade.line: Battlefield, I'm coming for you.

win_mvp.line: Don't be confined by the so-called "limits". It is indeed possible to be unsinkable!

detail.line: The wreath that goes on Her Majesty's door... Hmm, Belfast told me that the best way to make it is with seashells! Commander, let's head out to sea to collect some!

drop_descrip.line: This year, I am in charge of delivering presents to the children of the Royal Navy. Let's get going once I finish decorating this Christmas tree!

feeling5.line: Apologies, Commander, it seems like our Christmas together was a bit unromantic. You... enjoyed it just fine? Heh, you're always like this... Well, at least, let us enjoy the rest of the night together while the bells of the Holy Night toll.

home.line: Good. Since you are here, I can proceed to my next battleground - the important mission of delivering these gifts!

login.line: Even warriors need to rest. Since it's a holiday, you shouldn't be too uptight either.

main1.line: Commander, do you want a present as well? If you really want one that badly, it's not like I can't give you one...

main2.line: Hmm... what present should I pick out for Her Majesty? It can't be too expensive or too cheap, and it can't be too exotic or too ordinary. What exactly can I get her?

main3.line: If I'm delivering Christmas presents, it's only natural to go through the chimney... Eh? Wouldn't that make me seem suspicious?

mission.line: Commander, while you're out delegating missions, mind helping me deliver this present to one of the kids along the way?

touch.line: Commander, come help me decorate this Christmas tree - I'm not tall enough to reach... W-wait, who gave you permission to pick me up?!

unlock.line: This year, I am in charge of delivering presents to the children of the Royal Navy. Let's get going once I finish decorating this Christmas tree!

battle.line: I'm going to win, even in a skirt!

detail.line: Don't let my name fool you. Warspite is ready to fight, whenever and wherever, even onstage.

drop_descrip.line: We have the finest equipment. Now to turn in a performance worthy of Her Majesty's beauty... Behold, the Royal Stage!

login.line: The day's schedule is in your hands.

lose.line: If I were just a little faster...!

main1.line: I'm no idol... Yes, idols are nothing like me... Hm...

main2.line: What do you think of this outfit? It was made with input from the Royal Knights. Should be different from the others'.

main3.line: Her Majesty is certainly all in at the moment, but I'm worried she may suddenly lose interest...

mission.line: A gig request...? Maybe you'd better give this to Illustrious...

mission_complete.line: Rewards. I never thought Cesare would be sending them.

touch.line: Are you fixing my equipment?

touch2.line: Is it time to call the police?

unlock.line: We have the finest equipment. Now to turn in a performance worthy of Her Majesty's beauty... Behold, the Royal Stage!

win_mvp.line: (Did I take it too far...?)

drop_descrip.line: Warspite, retrofitting complete. Mm, I rather like this feeling of being rejuvenated... Now, Commander, let us make our way towards new battlegrounds!

login.line: My range extends even farther. Commander, send me out to fight, won't you?

main1.line: It is my duty as your secretary ship to counsel you, Commander. I won't hesitate to speak my mind if you make a poor decision.

main2.line: Survival is the key to becoming a stronger person.

main3.line: Battle is the fire that feeds one's growth. And so I fight with all that I have, in every conflict.

touch.line: Commander, if you have something to say, just come out and say it. I'm happy to listen.

touch2.line: My important parts haven't grown at all...? Seems like someone wants to taste my high-angle mounts...

unlock.line: Warspite, retrofitting complete. Mm, I rather like this feeling of being rejuvenated... Now, Commander, let us make our way towards new battlegrounds!

battle.line: I expect everyone to do their duty.

detail.line: What are you staring at?! Keep it up and I'll gouge your eyes out!

drop_descrip.line: Nelson-class battleship – Nelson, Hull Number 28!

expedition.line: Com-man-der! Did you forget about the returning commissions again?

feeling1.line: I... don't even know what to tell you anymore... *Sigh*...

feeling2.line: They let the likes of you be a commander? What a joke. Listen up! To be a commander, you must first... (One hour later)... Got it? Then work harder.

feeling3.line: Just with results like these you want me to... You did all this yourself? Don't laugh! I suppose I can make an exception and admit that you did well this time. Hmph!

feeling4.line: What are you looking at? I do approve of people who take of their work seriously. Besides, in the beginning I just thought you were unreliable, I never said you weren't serious!

feeling5.line: Go out on a date? Well... It's not as if I won't, as long as you keep on working hard then...

home.line: Have you witnessed the might of the Royal Navy?

hp_warning.line: Hmph, this is nothing!

login.line: Hmph. Are you done lazing around? I sorted out your documents, so I'm hoping you'll get some things done.

lose.line: To humiliate me like this... I'll get you back!

mail.line: I picked up your mail while I was out on my walk. Read it and be thankful.

main1.line: Experience from what's known as "failure"? Only a loser would say something like that!

main2.line: I'm not just talking about you, but those who wave around empty words of "friendship" and "efforts" do not belong here.

main3.line: One should only do work one is capable of. You still don't have what it takes to be entrusted with important tasks... Keep honing your skills.

mission.line: Why are you daydreaming if there are still missions to complete?

mission_complete.line: Are you trying to make me get the rewards for you? I'll give you 10 seconds to do it yourself! 1, 2...

profile.line: If you don't know who I am, go back to the naval academy and start over. I have no need of a commander who doesn't know me. ... You're calling me slow?! Huh?! That's brave of you to say... Stand still, I'll launch some knowledge into your head with my cannons!

propose.line: Stand straight and puff your chest. You are the one I have chosen to spend the rest of my life with. This is something you should be proud of! ... Of course, to be chosen by you, is my honor... I'm not arrogant anymore? ... W-why, you... Do you want me to beat you up that badly?!

skill.line: You're making a big mistake if you think I'm going to underestimate our enemies!

touch.line: Are you trying to get a taste of my cannons?!

touch2.line: Off to the bottom of Trafalgar with you, Com-man-der!

unlock.line: You're the commander? You don't look very capable to me, though. I'm Nelson. I'll be following your orders, for now.

upgrade.line: I suppose I should show a little appreciation for you; nice work.

win_mvp.line: Hmph. Enemies like these aren't even worth the time.

detail.line: I wasn't really planning on dressing up at all. I was just a little curious, so... I-it looks good on me? ... T-thanks... Hey, don't get carried away!

drop_descrip.line: This costume... *Sigh*, whatever. It's Halloween, so some kind of entertainment is to be expected. But listen here: I'm not dressing up because I WANT to participate, okay?!

home.line: W-what are you gawking at?! What's so weird about my costume?!

login.line: I'll overlook your slacking at least for Halloween. But when this day is over, you don't get to slack off any more!

main1.line: Stop taking pictures, Rodney! I don't want people to see me like this...!

main2.line: I guess it's okay to have fun with everyone like this sometimes... What? Did I say something funny?

main3.line: What are you standing around for? It's a holiday; don't you have better things to do?

touch.line: If you try anything weird at all... then you'll be in a world of pain!

touch2.line: Do you wanna end up like this pumpkin?!

unlock.line: This costume... *Sigh*, whatever. It's Halloween, so some kind of entertainment is to be expected. But listen here: I'm not dressing up because I WANT to participate, okay?!

detail.line: Rodney's with Colorado's group – they went to the shooting gallery. We can check that out, if you want... M-me, get lost among the crowd? Like that would ever happen! Especially when, you know, we're holding hands...

drop_descrip.line: Hey, are you even enjoying yourself? At least pretend to have fun when I went out of my way to invite you, or else I'm going to lose sleep over this! ...Look behind me? What are you– Oh...!

expedition.line: A commission should be completed by now? Y-yeah, I know! I don't need you to remind me!

feeling5.line: You'll have to shape up if you want to go out with me. Firstly, you... Look, I've told you a dozen times by now! This is not a date, you're just giving me a guided tour around the festival grounds!

home.line: You just witnessed the might of the Royal Navy! ...Ack! Y-you did NOT just see me trip! Got it?

login.line: Make this day count, you hear? Y-you should know how to celebrate a holiday. You're not THAT stupid...

main1.line: Look, those girls are dancing. Heehee, they seem to be having fun. That's the "Awa Dance," if I remember right.

main2.line: I will compliment the Sakura Empire on its impressive craftsmanship. Just look at their blue dyes and this tailor-made yukata.

main3.line: These fireworks are gorgeous... You are looking at them, right? I don't want to stand here and watch them all alone... N-no, I don't mean that the way you think!

mission.line: That's quite a few missions. Shouldn't you entrust some of these to other people?

mission_complete.line: I tasked the manjuus with collecting those rewards because I don't want you to leave... N-no, I didn't mean it like that!

touch.line: (Mgh... This sash feels far too tight, even compared to my regular uniform... Never thought a yukata would compress my breasts...)

unlock.line: Hey, are you even enjoying yourself? At least pretend to have fun when I went out of my way to invite you, or else I'm going to lose sleep over this! ...Look behind me? What are you– Oh...!

battle.line: For glory, we fight as one!

detail.line: I can't believe the Commander is into this stuff... Did everyone else already know? I don't wanna ask Rodney outright... I know. If I just make a bold move on the Commander, then... Hyah?!

drop_descrip.line: H-hey, are you sleeping all day, or what? My retrofit is all done. Hmph, you might've widened the gap between us, but... I'm gonna keep on pushing my limits! Got it?

expedition.line: We can always rely on allies who see a job done right.

feeling5.line: W-we may be going out, but isn't that just in a work sense? Keep doing your best, and maybe we can make it real... Don't betray my expectations, okay?

home.line: You can't just collapse out of nowhere because you're tired... Or m-maybe you want to be stepped on?! You pervert! *blushes*

login.line: There's TONS of stuff to do today, so don't think you'll be able to do it all without my support! Get it together, Commander!

lose.line: Even with this retrofit... Ngh!

main1.line: We use our experiences of failure to forge a path to success. You should remember that, too. (whispering) Don't push yourself too hard, though.

main2.line: Do I hear... West Virginia playing her guitar? It's crazy how many talents she has... N-not that I'm jealous! Don't get it twisted!

main3.line: A d-d-d-date?! Wh-where is this coming from?! As a leader, you should prioritize improving yourself! ...I know! I'll join you in doing just that!

mission.line: If you have time for this, then go do your missions, or something!

mission_complete.line: I brought your bonus. Don't expect me to do it again!

touch.line: What are you trying to pull?

touch2.line: D-do you really want to get stepped on?!

unlock.line: H-hey, are you sleeping all day, or what? My retrofit is all done. Hmph, you might've widened the gap between us, but... I'm gonna keep on pushing my limits! Got it?

win_mvp.line: They were too weak for you and me. Hah!

battle.line: Mmm... I'm looking forward to everyone finishing their work too~!

detail.line: Need me to explain the details?

drop_descrip.line: Nelson-class battleship – Rodney, Hull Number 29!

expedition.line: Hehe, Commander. The girls are back from commission!

feeling1.line: Even I'm a bit disappointed...

feeling2.line: The weather is pretty nice. Want to take a walk, Commander? Let's relax and chat for a while. What do you think?

feeling3.line: Commander sure is gentle, always slowing down to match my pace when we're taking walks... I'm moved by details like this.

feeling4.line: Not respecting the chain of command can mean big trouble, it has happened before……Of course it's ok for us since we're so close~

feeling5.line: Commander, want to have dinner together tonight? I'll make your favorite dish... Hmm? it's not a holiday or something like that... I just thought of it just now... If you want, Commander, we can do it every night~.

home.line: Let me make a cup of tea~

hp_warning.line: Can I increase my firepower?

login.line: Ah, Commander, you're back! I was just tidying up the documents, please have a look.

lose.line: I can still fight... but we should probably retreat, for now...

mail.line: I've brought your new mail, Commander.

main1.line: I'm here to help you with anything you need.

main2.line: If the Commander doesn't mind, please allow me to keep you company!

main3.line: Commander, if you keep slacking off, even I will get angry.

mission.line: Commander, shall we complete our new mission?

mission_complete.line: Here are your mission rewards. Let's take a look!

profile.line:
I'm Nelson's little sister, Rodney! Um... us sisters are pretty famous right?
 Erm, you've heard that my fighting style is unbefitting of my appearance? Well well, Commander, such rumors are, of course, false~

propose.line: Everyday I spend with the Commander is a special day, I hope days like these will last forever.

skill.line: There's no need to be polite when dealing with enemies.

touch.line: What is it?

touch2.line: Please don't do this in the command room...

unlock.line: Hello, I'm Rodney. I shall be in your care from this day forward.

upgrade.line: I hope you're looking forward to my performance from here on out!

win_mvp.line: Hmm, I think I accidentally wasted a lot of ammunition...

detail.line: Don't be shy, Commander~ Come on, come on over here~ How do you feel? Are my hands too cold?

drop_descrip.line: Although it's a gift from the Commander, it's still embarrassing to wear this....Commander, do you think you could teach me how to swim?

login.line: It's so hot... I can't imagine doing any work! Commander, how about we take a cold shower together??

main1.line: Beach volleyball? But I finally got a chance to be intimate with you...I'll PASS~

main2.line: I'll love whatever gifts you give me!

main3.line: I'm wiped out. So much swimming! Commander... can you carry me home?

touch.line: Commander, could you put some sunscreen on my back?

touch2.line: How's that? The feeling of a bona-fide Big Seven

unlock.line: Even if it's the Commander's gift, wearing it is pretty embarrassing. Commander, want to teach me how to swim?

battle.line: It is time for me to carry out my duties once more!

detail.line: Perhaps I should hold up a fan like this? ...Like this? *click* Oh, great advice, Commander! Akashi said that changed the mood of the shoot completely, ehehe.

drop_descrip.line: Miss Akashi, shall I look at the camera next? Understood. Oh, Commander, I did not expect you to grace us with your presence here as well! Yes, the photoshoot is proceeding smoothly. By the way, is there a favorite pose you'd like to see?

home.line: Welcome back. What you're smelling right now is the fragrance of Dragon Empery tea... Yes, my friends here recommended it to me.

login.line: I was delighted just to have you stop by, but I can't believe you even brought me refreshments... How about I pour you a cup of tea as well?

main1.line: It's my first time wearing clothes like these, so I'm trying to figure out the perfect way to show off my legs... Commander? Hehe, have you been enchanted?

main2.line: You're worried that I might be feeling cold? Well... how about you check by holding my hand?

main3.line: Long photoshoots really are quite tiring... Commander, how about going for some coffee together after we wrap this up?

touch.line: Thank you so much for helping me put this fur on!

touch2.line: We're still not done with the photoshoot~ Hehe~♪

unlock.line: Miss Akashi, shall I look at the camera next? Understood. Oh, Commander, I did not expect you to grace us with your presence here as well! Yes, the photoshoot is proceeding smoothly. By the way, is there a favorite pose you'd like to see?

win_mvp.line: I'll have to check on our inventory of ammo when we get back.

detail.line: I have paperwork, practice, and dinner to see to today. The more burdens I can take off your mind, the happier it makes me~

drop_descrip.line: I never imagined that this dreamlike situation would come to pass... Commander, have you also been looking forward to sharing this moment with me? Hehe~

feeling5.line: Care to have dinner with me tonight, Commander? I know all your favourite dishes~

home.line: Well strategised, Commander. Wait just a minute while I go brew some tea.

login.line: My heart is at rest when I see you happy, Commander~

main1.line: Every day with you is a day worth celebrating... Hmm, phrases like these feel rather cheesy, so I'll keep them to a minimum. Knowing you, you already know how I feel, Commander.

main2.line: Each minute you slack off is one less minute of the day we'll have together. Please try to stay focused, for both our sakes.

main3.line: Commander, do you have any plans for the next naval holiday? If not... we could go on a date somewhere. What do you say?

touch.line: I've read that physical intimacy deepens a relationship the more you do it~

touch2.line: Please, let's put this on hold until we're alone, all right?

unlock.line: I never imagined that this dreamlike situation would come to pass... Commander, have you also been looking forward to sharing this moment with me? Hehe~

win_mvp.line: That's why you shouldn't underestimate a Big 7!

battle.line: Let us go forth and plant our banners!

detail.line: My standing within the Royal Family? Hmm... If I had to draw a comparison, I'd say "Knight Commander" would be the most fitting... Hahaha...

drop_descrip.line: King George V-class battleship – King George V.

expedition.line: There's some commotion by the port...? Oh, it seems to just be the commission team returning.

feeling1.line: I favor those of character, and those who can cook. Commander, you are neither.

feeling2.line: By the way, Commander, are you a good cook? Hmm? Despite my appearances, I've spent many hours honing my skills to sate my own appetite.

feeling3.line: How's that, commander? Are you impressed by my cooking abilities? Here, have as much you desire. Seeing you enjoy my food pleases me.

feeling4.line: Commander, so you're learning how to cook? Hmm, colour me impressed. I look forward to trying the dish that you're making for me.

feeling5.line: My greatest hobbies in life are food and fighting. While I am more than capable of fighting alone, dining by myself is quite difficult and lonesome. To be able to find someone who can share both of these things with me is truly a joyous thing.

home.line: Commander, did you thoroughly enjoy the battle?

hp_warning.line: Hmph, how interesting!

login.line: Commander, did you already partake of supper?

lose.line: Do not be demoralized. Neither victory nor defeat are decided by a single battle.

mail.line: A letter, huh? Now then, is this a challenge, or a love letter?

main1.line: Commander, this fleet only functions because of you. Don't get sloppy on us.

main2.line: Wales and Yorkie? It's a bit of a shame that they don't act more like cute little sisters, but I am glad that they have strong personalities.

main3.line: In my eyes, there is no leader in this world more worthy of my loyalty than Her Majesty, Queen Elizabeth. Does that make sense to you, Commander?

main4.line: The Royals' cuisine is all bland? Hogwash. That's just an unfortunate stereotype.

mission.line: New missions, eh? It would be ideal if we got something a bit more challenging.

mission_complete.line: Supper tastes best after the day's missions are all complete. Wouldn't you agree, Commander?

profile.line: The nameship of the King George V-class battleships is none other than me. I served as flagship for my country, leading the fleet into numerous battles including the fateful encounter with Bismarck. After getting a brief taste of that thrill, I have been craving to cross swords with her once again... But I digress - is there anything else you'd like to know about me?

propose.line: They say that "the quickest way to one's heart is through their stomach," but you've managed to win over both at once. Commander, shall we share all our meals together from now on?

skill.line: The glory of the sun that never sets shall not fade!

touch.line: Why do I have a mountain of snacks before me? Isn't it obvious? One cannot move on an empty stomach.

touch2.line: Ohh? I wasn't aware that you possessed such audacity, Commander.

unlock.line: So this is my new battlefield. Ahh, how I've long awaited this... By the way, are you my commander? You are in the presence of King George V – do use me well.

upgrade.line: Hmm... I suddenly feel like having a lavish feast.

win_mvp.line: Make no mistakes. I shall ensure both victory and the safety of all my comrades.

detail.line: Hmm...? These clothes seem a bit too tight. Commander, mind helping me loosen up the zipper in the back?

drop_descrip.line: Sorry to keep you waiting, Commander... I don't get to wear a dress very often, so it took me a bit longer. Let's get going, then. Remember, you'll be the lead tonight. Haha~

expedition.line: Commander, let's call it a day after this commission is finished. Everyone has a right to enjoy the banquet.

home.line: Commander, if we don't hurry, all the food is going to get cold.

login.line: Take my hand, Commander. I'm still not used to walking around in this dress.

mail.line: An invitation to the ball? Hehe, want to go together, Commander?

main1.line: Ugh... I'm expected to act more proper when I'm wearing formal attire. Can't even go around trying all the different delicacies, what a drag...

main2.line: We are able to enjoy a jubilant night like this because of all the hard work we've put in. Commander, let's make the most of it.

main3.line: Hmm... Yorkie and Wales are going at it again. Commander, excuse me. It's rare that the three of us get to have a sisterly reunion.

mission.line: Issuing tasks during our banquet...? Those folks sure know how to ruin the mood.

mission_complete.line: Let's use these rewards to decorate the venue.

touch.line: It seems... that Belfast and Hood are already attending to Her Majesty. Looks like we'll be free to enjoy ourselves, Commander.

unlock.line: Sorry to keep you waiting, Commander... I don't get to wear a dress very often, so it took me a bit longer. Let's get going, then. Remember, you'll be the lead tonight. Haha~

win_mvp.line: Bad luck, friends. You chose the wrong day to get in my way.

battle.line: Courage is necessary for success… All ships, fire!

detail.line: Fate can be easily derailed, Commander.

drop_descrip.line: King George V-class battleship – Prince of Wales, Hull Number 53!

expedition.line: The commissions are complete, it is your duty to welcome them back.

feeling1.line: Keep your distance. You are not qualified to command me...

feeling2.line: I heard that my current name was chosen because my original one could bring misfortune, but... judging by how things turned out... it seems I'm unable to escape my fate...

feeling3.line: You never know how many plans, hopes, and efforts would sink into the sea with you, Commander. So try not to die too easily.

feeling4.line: Fighting fair and square is my motto. I wish it could be the same when it comes to my own feelings. So... can you stay with me a bit longer? I have something important to tell you, Commander...

feeling5.line: I had a dream, a dream of that time which makes me feel hopeless even now... But when I open my eyes and see you by my side, it feels like life... like life isn't so bad after all...

home.line: Sometimes victories come down to nothing but luck. Don't get too full of yourself, Commander.

hp_warning.line: Get up! We're going to go look for a fight!

login.line: Welcome back. Shall we have tea before getting back to work?

lose.line: A horse may stumble even though he has four legs. Let's try again next time.

mail.line: You have a new message, Commander.

main1.line: Expensive isn't always better, but it's your job to maximize our combat capability, Commander.

main2.line: I don't want to suffer the pain of losing my comrades again...

main3.line: Would you like to have some tea? I have also prepared some sandwiches. By the way, I am a fan of pickles.

mission.line: Commander, it's time to put you to the test.

mission_complete.line: Rewards received! You performed beautifully.

profile.line: I'm the second ship of the King George V-class battleships, the Prince of Wales. I once escorted the Prime Minister to sign the Atlantic Charter. Making my mark in the history books of weaponry? Hmph, how dare you mention that in front of me.

propose.line: To me, the ritual isn't as important as the fact that you're the person that I've accepted... However, receiving something like this still makes me happy. Thank you, Commander... I'll keep this with me forever!

touch.line: Let's have chat, Commander.

touch2.line: You know what doing this means right? *Smiles*

unlock.line: You're the Commander? Very well. I, Prince of Wales, shall let you witness my true strength.

upgrade.line: Let's not repeat failure again...

win_mvp.line: The taste of victory is always sweet.

detail.line: Regardless of the time and situation, to ignore a fair maiden is most ungentlemanly.

drop_descrip.line: I'm not a big fan of beach volleyball, but Hood begged me... I swear, that girl! She just can't get enough of the sun! You've got to cheer for me!

expedition.line: I'll welcome the girls home from commission. Take a rest if you're really tired.

feeling5.line: Love with you is like priceless treasure. I wouldn't trade even an entire kingdom for it!

home.line: I know it's tempting to eat ice cream during the summer, Commander, but don't eat too much otherwise you'll get a stomachache!

login.line: To  truly experience the charm of all things, first one must sincerely love them. Commander, the same goes for girls too.

mail.line: New mail? Hood, stop staring at me. They aren't for me!

main1.line: How's my swimsuit, Commander? Haha, let me teach you how to compliment a girl in this kind of situation.

main2.line: Commander, leave all the admin stuff to me. Everyone else is waiting for you on the beach!

main3.line: Hood, you should get some sun once in a while too, you know.

mission.line: Fear not for dangers and obstacles, leap over challenges, and charge towards your goals. This is how unprecedented accomplishments are achieved!

mission_complete.line: Good work, Commander! How about a massage? People tell me I've got the best technique.

touch.line: {namecode:79} looked pretty depressed after she lost the ball game... Commander, why don't you go and comfort her?

touch2.line: Do you need me to teach you how to properly treat girls?

unlock.line: Although I don't really want in on the beachball game, but it was a request from Hood....That sun-loving girl. Don't forget to cheer for me!

upgrade.line: I can't die happy until I see Prinz Eugen with a true and honest smile on her face.

drop_descrip.line: I've been wearing Royal attire my whole life, so a change in pace doesn't seem bad. Oh, Commander, good timing. Can you explain to me how to celebrate the New Year here?

expedition.line: Since it's the New Year, it would be sad if there was nobody to greet the girls returning from commissions. Don't you think so, Commander?

feeling5.line: To be able to experience a new culture like this, and spend the New Year peacefully... is like a dream come true. Commander, it's all thanks to you. As expected of the one I chose.

main1.line: Commander, are you cold? You can borrow my coat if you'd like. Ah, don't worry about me, I'm fine.

main2.line: Learning about the customs of the other nations is quite interesting. I feel like I get along better with the Sakura girls now.

main3.line: I miss my black tea a bit, but I suppose "when in Rome, do as the Romans do." I guess I should fully enjoy the culture of the Sakura Empire.

mission_complete.line: You're still hammering away at those missions even during the New Year? You sure are hard-working, Commander.

touch.line: Why are you staring at me? I'm... suave? Hehe, I suppose I should take that as a compliment.

unlock.line: I've been wearing Royal attire my whole life, so a change in pace doesn't seem bad. Oh, Commander, good timing. Can you explain to me how to celebrate the New Year here?

detail.line: While destiny tends to fly off the rails pretty often, flying off the course during a match would be a major accident. Commander, be careful while you watch the match.

drop_descrip.line: Oh, Commander. Worry not. Since I've been given this job, I will see through it until the end. Besides, it's been a while since I've gotten this fired up. Haha!

home.line: Let's put on a performance to be remembered – for the sake of your victory.

login.line: Oh, you're back. Did you run into any of my sisters on the way here?

main1.line: The Manjuus drive these things... Sure, it's a mystery how they're able to turn the steering wheel, but I'm more curious about how they're able to step on the accelerator...

main2.line: Whether in a match or in a battle, a machine's or ship's capability isn't everything. Depending on the driver's skill or the commander's directions, the course of the match or battle can be completely reversed. Hehe, that's exactly what makes betting fun.

main3.line: These clothes make eating quite difficult... Oh, I give up. Commander, you can have the rest of my sandwich.

touch.line: Does something about this outfit bother you?

touch2.line: Heh, I won't let you go any further.

unlock.line: Oh, Commander. Worry not. Since I've been given this job, I will see through it until the end. Besides, it's been a while since I've gotten this fired up. Haha!

battle.line: I look forward to the 21-gun salute celebrating our victory.

detail.line: This black dress is like a dark night dotted with twinkling stars... to put it how York might describe it. Commander, it's okay to compliment people's outfits, but it just gets embarrassing if you go too far.

drop_descrip.line: I expected you sooner, Commander. I decided to practice the saxophone while I had some time alone... You shouldn't keep a lady waiting in the future. Heehee. Anyway, I suppose we could listen to a song before we set off, no?

home.line: You look tired, Commander. Say, you should come and listen to my playing for a while. Let me soothe your ears with a solo concert just for one.

login.line: Oh, Commander, are you finally awake? Listen to the knights' gentle alto tune... Heehee, it's dreamy, isn't it?

main1.line: We may be knights, but that doesn't mean we're all about fighting. Versatility is the true mark of a Royal Knight... is what I'd like to say, but that isn't true for some of us. Heheh.

main2.line: Concerts in formal clothes are great and all, but jam sessions with friends you can relax with are such fun. You should give it a try, Commander.

main3.line: Eugen? How much do you intend to make the Commander drink? You don't mean to get the Commander drunk enough to help you pester your friends, do you? Hahaha!

touch.line: Normally, touching the performers is strictly against the rules... But I can't deny the comfort of your gentle touch.

touch2.line: Commander? If I have a wardrobe malfunction, you'll help me, won't you? I certainly hope you wouldn't let me perform like that.

unlock.line: I expected you sooner, Commander. I decided to practice the saxophone while I had some time alone... You shouldn't keep a lady waiting in the future. Heehee. Anyway, I suppose we could listen to a song before we set off, no?

battle.line: Sinful roses of blood, bloom around me! Bloom!

detail.line: Dost thy heart cry restlessly in my absence?

drop_descrip.line: King George V-class battleship - HMS Duke of York.

expedition.line: O mesmerising Narcissus, do remember my warning when greeting those who return. Be misled not by the illusions swirling in the water.

feeling1.line: It would appear... that I must get a little more violent...

feeling2.line: What a nice gaze. Through thy pupils, I can see another world.

feeling3.line: How thy visage tempts me so with each passing moment... I must ask of thee, just how sweet is thy blood?

feeling4.line: How unfathomable... looking at thy sleeping visage hast made me replete with calmness... Now, pray that thou dost not wake, for I know not what I would do to thee...

feeling5.line: O ignorant snake, hast thou only realised now, how long I have hopelessly been in love with thee? Therefore... would thou give thy everything to me?

home.line: Oh, triumphant nightingale that has overcome death itself, what plagues thee enough to silence thy song?

hp_warning.line: Perhaps I have indulged myself too much...

login.line: O unclean snake, who is it thee lusts after today?

lose.line: Ahh... why dost thou obstinately refuse to obey me...

mail.line: Thy visage when reading and concentrating, unbudging and focused, resembles one of Michelangelo's sculptures. I do not dislike such determination.

main1.line: The secret behind my battle prowess? Hehe, I sink deeply into visions of the enemy torn from limb to limb. What follows is only natural.

main2.line: Wales, dost thou intend to hunt the same prey as me?

main3.line: Please be at ease and close thine eyes. Sink into my embrace, and let thy thoughts flow away.

mission.line: Such fair weather is rare indeed. 'twould be a pity to return to port so soon.

mission_complete.line: Only the moon and sweet liquor fail to disappoint. We shall share the most unforgettable of nights.

profile.line: I am King George V-class' Duke of York. Scharnhorst? An interesting one indeed, but now, thou art the one who captures my interest the most... My... if thou displays such an expression to me, I won't be able to contain myself...

propose.line: Even the most ingenious poet cannot describe the beauty of this moment. Hehe, close thy eyes, feel my warmth, and listen to the beating of my heart. This is the one who shall be thy lifelong partner...

skill.line: All ye, weep at your own demise!

touch.line: The night is both lengthy and brief. Come, blow out the light burning within thee, and accompany me into the dark.

touch2.line: Ahh, how beautiful... thy eyes, normally placid, burning with the fires of lust...

unlock.line: I see. So the scent that has been driving me crazy... emanates from thy soul. O sinful Commander who tempts me so, engrave my name upon thine heart - Duke of York, of the Royal Navy.

upgrade.line: Did thou hear? A sound that makes my blood boil, like wind passing through the forest in the dead of night.

win_mvp.line: There exists no living being that can resist the embrace of death.

detail.line: Ahaha... I can hear the beating of thy heart. Yes, throb, throb... Ahh, what an enrapturing sound...

drop_descrip.line: This luscious scent... doth emanate from thee. What dost thou feel when gazing upon my new dress? Hehe... thy lips may lie, but thy eyes do not.

feeling5.line: Become intoxicated with me. Then, giveth me thy purity, thy, devotion, and thy love. In return... I shall pledge thee an eternity of comfort within my bosom.

login.line: Dost thou wish to try this blood... coloured fruity beverage?

main1.line: Thou need not be nervous. This attire is but a temporary one... Perhaps thou believed to have escaped from my usual self? Ahaha...

main2.line: Even though a night eternal may be out of the question, dost thou not wish... to sink into the embrace of night with me?

main3.line: Following thy ideals are akin to swimming endlessly against the current... However, the way thou refuseth to bow thy head before fate gives me ample reason to remain by thee. Hehe...

touch.line: Dost thou intend to spend the night alone, or perhaps... wouldst thou like to partake of a drink with me?

touch2.line: Art thou able... to entertain me a bit longer?

unlock.line: This luscious scent... doth emanate from thee. What dost thou feel when gazing upon my new dress? Hehe... thy lips may lie, but thy eyes do not.

win_mvp.line: Come, now... shall we commence our waltz upon the battlefield?

detail.line: Love that can be robbed away holds no value. Only by becoming mine entirely will thou be worthy of my absolute attention.

drop_descrip.line: My beautiful Adonis, why dost thou refuseth to take refuge in the trove of everlasting love... Perhaps my outfit can finally pierce thy heart? Hehe~

main1.line: Wales, thou shalt not take my Adonis from me... Hehehe, but out of compassion, I shall allow you to have a third of our precious time together.

main2.line: Yes, thy gaze... So full of resistance, yet also ready to give in at any time... How thine eyes can keep me entertained for all eternity...

main3.line: Thou canst not win, be it in the heated environment of this sport, or in the sweetness of my absolute existence...

touch.line: Beautiful, is it not? This outfit thou hath bestowed upon me is perfect for inspiring thy adoration... Is that difficult to understand?

touch2.line: The snake devours the fruit — thy desires, thy true nature... I have grasped it all. Hehehe~

unlock.line: My beautiful Adonis, why dost thou refuseth to take refuge in the trove of everlasting love... Perhaps my outfit can finally pierce thy heart? Hehe~

win_mvp.line: I prefer wine over champagne... But very well. We shall celebrate as thou so desires.

battle.line: Heheh, there'll be no mercy for you!

detail.line: To your friends, show no cowardice; to your foes, show no mercy – that is my creed. Hehehe~

drop_descrip.line: King George V-class battleship – Howe (HMS Howe.)

expedition.line: Do you need someone to escort the commission team home? I'm quite the experienced escort, I'll have you know.

feeling1.line: A kind deed to others is a kind deed to yourself – or so I was naive enough to believe...

feeling2.line: "Shape the world into God's vision" – if there is a God, what is his ideal world? It can't be one of perpetual war, that's for sure.

feeling3.line: Are you tired, Commander? Under the weather, perhaps? Heh, well, a nice cookie can fix that. Just eat one of these and you'll be right back to normal.

feeling4.line: Come visit the dorm next time we're having cookies, Commander. We'd all love to have you, and I especially want to spend some quality time with you.

feeling5.line: Bah, being indirect is just not like me. I adore you, Commander. Both as the leader of the fleet, and as my beloved special someone. I wish to know... do you adore me as well?

home.line: Nicely done out there. If you've got the energy to spare, perhaps you could write an after-battle report?

hp_warning.line: I can't... falter now!

login.line: How nice to see you. Now, let's get to work on today's tasks.

lose.line: Next time... victory will be ours.

mail.line: We've received what looks to be mail addressed to you.

main1.line: Wales and York are lovely ladies. At times, however, I struggle to keep up with their thought processes.

main2.line: George has always been good to me. She often treats me to a cookie or two... But I wish she'd stop treating me like I'm still a child.

main3.line: If you have a hard time making friends with an eccentric person, my advice is this: bake some cookies, and offer to share with them.

mission.line: Oh, missions? Are there any I can help with?

mission_complete.line: A mission's done. I can take care of claiming the rewards, no problem.

profile.line: Prior to my being sent to the Pacific, I always worked side by side with George. But aside from the one time we escorted our Sardegnian friends, I suppose I don't have too many notable feats to my name.

propose.line: Thank you for your sincerity, Commander. I will gladly be yours. I won't ask of you to share all your joys and sorrows with me, as I'm more than happy with just being by your side. Ah, that didn't sound like what I would say, did it? Well, hehehe~

touch.line: Do save the massage for later. I'm not tired yet.

touch2.line: Umm... What are you doing?

unlock.line: It's a pleasure meeting you, Commander. I'm Howe of the King George V-class. I hope we can build a healthy relationship.

upgrade.line: Phew... I'll return your gesture with valour on the battlefield, Commander.

win_mvp.line: Heheh, I'm in top shape today!

detail.line: Is this the place with the famously delicious cookies? Could we order some right away? I must taste them for myself!

drop_descrip.line: Sorry to keep you waiting, but now I'm ready to– Commander? What's the matter? It'll get dark soon if you keep standing around like that.

home.line: Well done on that sortie. Let's proceed with our plan, shall we?

login.line: Glad you could make it, love. Now, as for our plan today... Oh, should I not have made a plan ahead of time?

lose.line: I hope misfortune befalls you.

main1.line: Wales taught me the dos and don'ts of dating. Though enlightening, her advice seemed purposed for winning an ordinary girl's hand... So perhaps it's better intended for you, Commander?

main2.line: Peckish, are you? Then you can have this cookie George gave me.

main3.line: This dress is quite comfortable, actually. It's no trouble for me to walk a little longer.

touch.line: Have a seat if you need to rest, love.

touch2.line: Hm? Is there something on my dress?

unlock.line: Sorry to keep you waiting, but now I'm ready to– Commander? What's the matter? It'll get dark soon if you keep standing around like that.

battle.line: Swift and graceful, I advance!

detail.line: Oh, who will come to my rescue? George? Or perhaps... you, love?

drop_descrip.line: "Please, Master, save meee." ...Ugh, I can't get into the role. What sort of tone should I be aiming for, love?

feeling5.line: I'm curious what the Royal Maids mean when they say they "service" you... Heheh. Would you mind enlightening me after this rehearsal, love?

home.line: Splendid work. I would offer you a treat, but as you can see, my hands are tied...

login.line: "Masteeer, please untie meeee"... Hmm...

main1.line: Goodness... These cookie props are so enticing they're distracting me...

main2.line: How do you think Belfast would respond if I walked up to her and said, "I'm joining the Royal Maids starting today"?

main3.line: Memorising my lines is simple enough. Reciting them is another matter, though... How does Wales do it so effortlessly?

touch.line: I'll bake you your favourite pastry later, love.

touch2.line: ...Master?

unlock.line: "Please, Master, save meee." ...Ugh, I can't get into the role. What sort of tone should I be aiming for, love?

battle.line: A Royal Knight is not to be trifled with!

detail.line: What, you think my dress is ludicrously posh? It should be, considering what an important day this is... What about it is so important, you ask? Hm... That is an excellent question.

drop_descrip.line: Thanks for your patience, love. I've looked forward to this evening's party for a long, long time. Hopefully George, York, and company won't laugh at me after how much effort I've put into this ensemble... What do you think of it, Commander?

expedition.line: The commission team is back. Heehee, I suppose we have to wait with the champagne for a bit.

home.line: Welcome back, love. Go on and take a minute to rest. Let me know if you'd like to order anything.

login.line: I'm right here, Commander. Seeing as we still have time, why don't you try this new flavour of cookie I made? ...Now's not the time?

main1.line: Monarch has me a tad bit concerned... Ah, no, she fits in just fine, I just wonder if she likes the food on offer.

main2.line: All these foreign dresses have me mesmerised. I'd love to try some on for myself someday.

main3.line: I don't want to stand out TOO much – you're the star of the show tonight, after all.

touch.line: I can't walk all that fast in this outfit, so be a sweetheart and escort me.

touch2.line: Please, mind your manners...

unlock.line: Thanks for your patience, love. I've looked forward to this evening's party for a long, long time. Hopefully George, York, and company won't laugh at me after how much effort I've put into this ensemble... What do you think of it, Commander?

win_mvp.line: That is what I call an elegant victory. Phew... This will hopefully put George at ease.

battle.line: Heed my command! Forward!

detail.line: Look, isn't Elizabeth acting a bit too spoiled? And Warspite and the others are totally enabling that. I knew I should have been the one in charge... Huhh? I'm more or less the same...? Wh-what did you say?!

drop_descrip.line: Queen Elizabeth-class battleship – Valiant (HMS Valiant.)

expedition.line: Heheh, it seems that the commission team has been doing well. Do send them my best regards in my stead.

feeling1.line: I had great expectations for you...

feeling2.line: Good, you came. If you have no other work to do, play me in a game of chess.

feeling3.line: Y-you're better than I expected... F-fine, I won't go easy on you next time...!

feeling4.line: H-hold up! Chess is like a real-world exercise, so you have to consider all the various external factors! Th-that's right! That last match was a fake! A fluke! Doesn't count! Cancelled! Got it?!

feeling5.line: As my subordinate, you should be considerate of your superior... I mean, sh-shouldn't you let me win at least once? I've lost to you so many times that I barely even have the confidence to play chess anymore... A-anyway! Lose to me! Just once! It can even be on purpose! This is an order, got it?

headtouch.line: Wh-what are you doing?!

home.line: My attendant, how fares the combat situation? Do tell me in detail.

hp_warning.line: H-hey, hurry up and do something about this...!

login.line: It's about time! Now, show me today's itinerary!

lose.line: Ugh... H-how is this possible...

mail.line: Tsk... Why is all the mail for you...

main1.line: So thirsty... Ahem. My attendant, do tell the Maid Team to brew me some black tea. Hmm, on second thought... that'd take too long. You can do it for me, can't you?

main2.line: Charisma is the most important facet of a leader! To be charismatic is to command dignity, to imbue your every word with gravitas! Ahem... did you get all that?

main3.line: Snack time?! ...Ahem! A proper leader must know how to balance their work with their life. Please do not forget that.

mission.line: I'll leave this these trifling quests to you.

mission_complete.line: Even the most trivial quests at least deserve some rewards.

profile.line: Queen Elizabeth-class battleship, Valiant. Hehe, this fleet is known from Jutland to the Far East for its heroic majesty, and I am the reason for that! Now, Commander, you shall become my assistant so that you may prove your worth as a subordinate.

propose.line: Well done! You've gained my recognition as my trustiest spear in the arsenal! To reward you for your continued loyalty, I shall allow you to stay at my side and bask in my charisma! May this ring be a symbol of our bond~♪

skill.line: Everything dances within the palm of my hand!

touch.line: Speak your mind, my attendant. You have my ear.

touch2.line: What's the meaning of this?! Grrr... As a charismatic, generous, and VERY patient person, I will forgive you just this once!

unlock.line: To be Valiant is to be me. Remember this face, for it is the face of a fleet leader! ...Speaking of faces, who are you? The Commander? Very well! I shall treat you as my personal servant!

upgrade.line: Not bad, my attendant~ Do you want a reward?

win_mvp.line: A heroic battle commanded elegantly by the Commander— now this is the kind of flawless victory that befits me.

detail.line: Hey you, don't tell me you're actually enjoying being taken care of like this?! Grr... How unfair! How about this, next time, I'll be the patient, and you'll attend to my every whim!

drop_descrip.line: Hehe~ As this medical facility training is crucially important, a charismatic leader such as myself would be best suited to instruct everyone on– Wait a moment, what's with this outfit?! You there, explain the meaning of this at once!

home.line: I brought water for you. Make sure you drink plenty if you want to stay healthy... That's right, eight cups a day!

login.line: It's about time! ...Wait, just kidding! You're supposed to be the patient, right? How about you stop walking around so much? Get back in bed this instant!

main1.line: Don't get any weird ideas. I'm only pouring tea for you because you're the patient!

main2.line: When we're not training for this exercise, how about a game of chess? I already brought the board. I'll set it up, so just wait in bed!

main3.line: As a patient, so you're supposed to listen to the nurse! Mm... Besides, shouldn't you already be heeding my every instruction? You're my attendant after all...

main4.line: You're my patient today! Heheh, be grateful that you're now under the care of the charismatic nurse, Valiant, and heed my every command! ...It, it's not like I'm into this or anything, so don't expect me to do this every single time!

main5.line: It's time to get your blood drawn, so stick your arm out! ...Geh... I can't handle this stuff like Vampire does...

touch.line: What's the matter? Are you going to die if I don't take care of you~?

touch2.line: ...I, I'm only overlooking this because you're the patient!

unlock.line: Hehe~ As this medical facility training is crucially important, a charismatic leader such as myself would be best suited to instruct everyone on– Wait a moment, what's with this outfit?! You there, explain the meaning of this at once!

detail.line: O~ho~ho! With my regal display of wisdom and fortune, I have finally secured the Crown from Elizabeth's grasp! Heheh~ before you is the victor of the War of the Roses!

drop_descrip.line: Why the astonished look on your face? You heard me correctly! On this day, I am not merely Valiant, I am the regal and royal Queen Valiant!

home.line: Today, I feel like the world is mine~ Oh, you're back, my attendant? You may enjoy my cooking as a reward!

login.line: Do you remember how you are to address me today? Yes, "Your Majesty, Queen Valiant!" Make sure you do not forget this!

main1.line: Elizabeth lost a bet with me. Now, she has to surrender the Crown to me for a day, and do whatever I tell her to~♪

main2.line: See to it that I, Queen Valiant, am the center of all attention at tonight's party! Huh? Don't overdo it...? I, I know that!

main3.line: Are you well-versed in ballroom dancing? Hrmm... It's decided! You shall be my dance partner tonight!

touch.line: H-how dare you lay your hands on Queen Valiant!

touch2.line: Hwah?! ...Ahem! I'm feeling extra charismatic today, so I will forgive your transgression for today!

unlock.line: Why the astonished look on your face? You heard me correctly! On this day, I am not merely Valiant, I am the regal and royal Queen Valiant!

battle.line: Everyone, follow my lead!

detail.line: You're not looking all too great... Is something on your mind? If there's something troubling you, please feel free to open up to me. It's not good to bottle things up inside...

drop_descrip.line: R-class battleship – Revenge.

expedition.line: The girls are back from their commissions. Shall we go greet them together, Your Excellency?

feeling1.line: Please, don't give in to despair! If you just reform yourself, there will surely be a day when you are accepted by everyone!
