feeling2.line: U-umm... Your Excellency, regarding the time I bumped into you when we first met... Are you truly alright? ...Should we get your body checked?

feeling3.line: Protecting the weak is the duty of us Royal Knights—Uhh, I'm not saying that you're weak, Your Excellency. Though, when we're on the battlefield, you're definitely on the side of "having to be protected"...

feeling4.line: Your Excellency, you always work so tirelessly for our sake... You really should try to make some time for yourself. When you do, I'll stroke your hair, and cheer you up, telling you things like, "Good work, Commander, you've done such a good job~"

feeling5.line: Your Excellency, not only are you the most important person in this port, but you are also the most important person in my life. That's why your safety is paramount to me—whether here, or on the battlefield... I'll make sure to protect you with all I've got.

headtouch.line: Um, excuse me...

home.line: I'm relieved that you were able to make it back safely. For now, please get some rest.

hp_warning.line: I won't back down... Hah!

login.line: Good morning, Your Excellency. Is there anything I can help out with today?

lose.line: I guess I shouldn't have forced things so hard...

mail.line: There is mail addressed to you, Your Excellency! Should I bring it to you right now?

main1.line: Eek?! I apologize, I didn't notice the papers on the table... I'll get to them right away!

main2.line: Not so long ago, I accidentally bumped into a destroyer while hurrying along... I'm glad that neither of us were hurt, but...

main3.line: If you spend too long working, your neck and shoulders are bound to become stiff. H-how about I give you a nice massage to help you loosen up?

mission.line: Is there a new mission? Please let me know any time if you would like my assistance.

mission_complete.line: Allow me to retrieve our rewards for the missions we've completed! ...Oh, I need to check the list first...?

profile.line: I am Revenge, lead ship of the Royal Navy's Revenge-class battleships. I partook in the Jutland campaign, but since I participated mostly in escort missions afterward, I wasn't able to see too much action in that great war... I'm sorry... you must be disappointed to hear this.

propose.line: *pant* *pant*... I heard you needed something from me, so I ran here as fast as I could... Wait—this is... a ring? N-no way, I-I-I-I'm sorry! This is so sudden, I don't know what to say... B-but, gladly! Of course!

skill.line: I shall protect the Commander and my allies!

touch.line: Did something urgent come up? Then, put it over there... Y-you just want to chat for a bit...? I'm sorry for jumping to conclusions...

touch2.line: That's a discourteous thing to do to a lady. Don't you agree, Your Excellency?

unlock.line: ...Woah?! S-sincerest apologies, I wasn't watching where I was going... Oh, you're the Commander? S-splendid! Battleship Revenge of the Royal Navy, at your service!

upgrade.line: Thank you very much. I'll make sure to live up to your expectations.

win_mvp.line: Alright, let's keep this up!

detail.line: The Royal Maids and the Royal Knights both work hard to protect our allies. Volunteering like this renews my sense of purpose.

drop_descrip.line: Hrmm... *sigh*... Looks like I bungled this one too... I sure hope the Commander doesn't see me like th– Hwuh?! C-Commander? P-please give me a moment! I'll straighten this out right away... Waaah!!

home.line: *pant* *pant*... Phew... I can't believe I'm getting this tired from just cleaning... Your Excellency... Why don't you also take a short break?

login.line: Welcome back, Your Excellency. As you can see, I'm currently in the middle of cleaning...

lose.line: I can't believe I failed again... Waah...

main1.line: Leave this to me... Eek! Your Excellency, I apologize... It wasn't on purpose, I swear!

main2.line: The office is all tied up, the documents are organized as well... Alright! Both the Commander and Her Highness should be pleased with the results!

main3.line: Your Excellency, I've learned how to brew proper black tea and make cookies from the Royal Maids... I-if there's a chance in the future, I'd like to...

touch.line: I, I'm fine. Something like this is nothing a maid can't handle... Especially for a Maid-Knight like me!

touch2.line: H-how should I serve you at a time like this...

unlock.line: Hrmm... *sigh*... Looks like I bungled this one too... I sure hope the Commander doesn't see me like th– Hwuh?! C-Commander? P-please give me a moment! I'll straighten this out right away... Waaah!!

win_mvp.line: Fighting on the battlefield is so much easier than being a maid...

battle.line: Come! Let's settle this, fair and square!

detail.line: Loyalty reverberates through my blade, glory booms through my barrels! Behold, the light of my royal sabre! ...Ugh, that's so cringeworthy! Although it does sound cool... C-Commander?!

drop_descrip.line: Battleship – Vanguard.

expedition.line: The commission team is back. Let's head out to receive them, Commander.

feeling1.line: *sigh*... If you're not suited for the job, just admit it so we can find a replacement. Stop acting tough, it just makes you look pathetic.

feeling2.line: So, what's on the schedule for today? ...You'll be working overtime filing paperwork? I'm sorry to hear that. Be that as it may, you will be present during today's exercise, right?

feeling3.line: While yes, I am a palace guard, that doesn't mean I should be stuck in port. Won't you let me sortie already? *sigh*... I'm going mad. The stress is killing me...

feeling4.line: What? You're working overtime AGAIN? I understand it has to be done, but this is a bit ridiculous... I won't force you to order a sortie, but please, can't you make one happen somehow? ...You can? Brilliant!

feeling5.line: Mmmmh! That was refreshing! Thanks, Commander – I really needed that! It's days like these that make serving as a palace guard worth it. Now, you who guides my sword, what is your next order?

headtouch.line: Yes? How can I help?

home.line: The Commander has returned! Ladies, arrange for repairs and a debriefing! Commander, get some rest – I'll take it from here.

hp_warning.line: Tsk... What a persistent bunch!

login.line: The Commander has arrived! Ladies, at attention! ...Now, let's get to work, shall we?

lose.line: Tsk. You'll pay for this, you hear?! ...No, I'm fine. Take the others and retreat, quickly.

mail.line: I've brought you a letter. Give it a read, Commander.

main1.line: You may rest assured, King George. If Her Majesty and the Commander so desire, I will gladly be the spearhead that sunders the enemy line.

main2.line: Is that Bismarck over there? Gracious, this will be quite awkward...

main3.line: The port seems to be all in order, and I can confidently say you're as well-guarded as can be!

main4.line: Pardon my bluntness, but Royal cuisine is total shite. Sure, different people like different things, but something's wrong if even I as a native think it's rubbish.

main5.line: Here's your programme for today, Commander! ...Damn, that's at the same time as the show I want to watch... N-no, just talking to myself!

mission.line: Word of a new mission has come in. Have a look, Commander.

mission_complete.line: Mission complete. *sigh*... I should've checked on it sooner.

profile.line: I am Vanguard, the battleship that was launched after the end of the war. My sword is yours – may it bring glory to your port. Also, if I may make a request... please do NOT call my weapons "old-fashioned."

propose.line: By this ring, my sword and my life now belongs to you, 'til the end of time! ...All righty, do you mind if I tone down the formality a bit? I mean, what's the point in being super serious 'round the clock?

touch.line: My duty as a palace guard is to aid and protect you at all times.

touch2.line: Thank you for ceasing your inappropriate behaviour right at... *gasp*! Do you have a death wish?

unlock.line: I am Vanguard, palace guard of the Royal Knights! I hereby pledge to you my sword, and the full extent of my loyalty! May glory be yours, and God save the Queen!

upgrade.line: My sword's purpose is to bring glory to the Royal Navy – and to you, Commander!

win_mvp.line: Hoorah! Victory is mine! May the Commander's name and mine alike go down in history! ...Oops! I didn't mean to say that aloud!

detail.line: Why do you insist on having me as a maid? I can hardly cook and I'm terrible at cleaning. Wait... Don't tell me maids are your kink...

drop_descrip.line: "Please let me know if you need anything, Master"... I'm starting to think you're making me wear this as a sick joke. The reason being, I am obviously NOT fit to be a Royal Maid... Even if I do adore their uniforms...

expedition.line: The commission team has returned to port. I shall accompany you to them.

feeling5.line: How would you evaluate my performance as a maid? Ill-suited though I am for this job, I can still accomplish any task you can throw at me... Y-you want me to keep doing this? You know, I really feel like you just enjoy watching me suffer!

home.line: A salute for the Commander's return! By the way, bring me along for the next sortie, would you?

login.line: The Commander has arrived! ...I know that's not what a maid would say, but it's not like I could pull it off anyway...

lose.line: This sucks... I told you I wasn't cut out for this.

main1.line: While Royal Maids also participate in battle, their approach differs greatly from us knights. The only way I can put it is... they hold back too much?

main2.line: Yes, Master? ..."Getting the hang of this," eh... Are you making fun of me?

main3.line: I alone get to protect you, my honourable Commander. No one will take this privilege from me!

main4.line: nil

main5.line: I have both secretary AND maid work to do... *sigh*... Will I ever get to sortie again?

mission.line: You have a new mission, Master. Please review it.

touch.line: As you say. Your wish is my command.

touch2.line: Compare me to any of the other maids and I'll destroy you.

unlock.line: "Please let me know if you need anything, Master"... I'm starting to think you're making me wear this as a sick joke. The reason being, I am obviously NOT fit to be a Royal Maid... Even if I do adore their uniforms...

win_mvp.line: I beat the crap out of them with grace and elegance! Hahah!

battle.line: P-please don't charge ahead so fast...

detail.line: I was watching the girls perform a training exercise, and a stray training round hit me... N-no, I'm not injured, but... It really hurt...

drop_descrip.line: R-class battleship – Royal Oak.

expedition.line: The commission team is back. Would you mind if I went with you to greet them? I'm a bit of a slow walker, but...

feeling1.line: I just know you turned out this way because I was holding you back, Lord Commander...

feeling2.line: I'm among the most senior Royal Knights, but I can't lead anyone. Heck, it takes all I have just to keep up... This fleet doesn't need a shipgirl like me.

feeling3.line: I think my speed should be enough for patrol work from now on. Okay, I hope this next one goes safely... Please, please don't let me run into any submarines!

feeling4.line: Oh, my... Was I really so helpful, Lord Commander? The old me would never have believed that... Umm... P-please let me handle even more missions!

feeling5.line: Not only did you not abandon me, but you've been considerate and even given me confidence in myself... S-say! If it's alright with you, could you teach me about more than just fighting and working...?

home.line: Lord Commander, thank you for your efforts. Is there anything I can help you with? ...Anything is fine, really...

hp_warning.line: Why does this keep happening to me...?

login.line: Hyah! Sorry, I wasn't standing behind the door on purpose... Umm, I'm okay, okay? You don't have to worry or apologize...

lose.line: Why is this happening? I tried so hard...

mail.line: Ah... There it is! Who in the world folded the mail into a paper airplane?

main1.line: Excuse me, Lord Commander! Oh, I didn't mean to interrupt... Umm... I'm not a fan of such quiet places. They make me remember painful things...

main2.line: Lord Commander, don't stray training rounds come at you when you leave the window open...?

main3.line: I at least have to see these documents delivered... Yes, I'll do my best to be back as soon as possible!

mission.line: Lord Commander, you might want to finish those missions soon...

mission_complete.line: Thank goodness... Back home safe from another mission. Ah, Lord Commander, I hope I wasn't holding you back!

profile.line: Introduce myself again? Okay... Umm, my name is Royal Oak, and I'm a Revenge-class battleship from the Royal Navy. I was able to accomplish something in the Battle of Jutland, but I ended up getting badly damaged after... I just hope I can escape my bad luck here at this port.

propose.line: I-is this real? I'm not dreaming... Lord Commander, you'd really give me something this valuable? Of course, I've always hoped that I could have this honour someday, and I'm as happy as can be! Umm, anyway, I happily accept!

touch.line: Ack! D-don't touch me out of nowhere, or you'll scare me...

touch2.line: Eeeeek! *pant* *pant*... P-please, no more!

unlock.line: I am Royal Oak, battleship under the Royal Navy. It's an honour, Lord Commander... I hope to overcome my weaknesses and pull my weight here, so... I-I'll be counting on you...

upgrade.line: "The Mighty Oak." Do you think I can live up to that...?

win_mvp.line: Phew. I managed to do my job... right?

detail.line: P.E. is a nightmare. I don't want to drag my friends down in the relay race, and I don't want random baseballs hitting me... I wish there was some way to skip it.

drop_descrip.line: Commander? Oh, what a coincidence... Were you slacking– err, I mean, taking a break, too? I can make some room for you if you'd like?

home.line: Lord Commander, you don't need to fret over me. Though I am happy to have you here with me...

login.line: Lord Commander, there's no teacher or hall monitor behind me, is there? Phew... Good.

main1.line: I'm not the worst at classroom learning. If there's anything you don't understand, I-I could help...?

main2.line: If you want to pass the time, how about reading? For some reason, there are lots of confiscated novels and manga here...

main3.line: By the way, how does Her Majesty normally spend time at school? Huh? She's actually bad at P.E. just like me?

touch.line: The others might realize something's up if we go back now...

touch2.line: I-if a hall monitor sees this, everyone will know!

unlock.line: Commander? Oh, what a coincidence... Were you slacking– err, I mean, taking a break, too? I can make some room for you if you'd like?

battle.line: If you believe in your fleet, we'll work our hardest to meet your expectations!

detail.line: Statistics aren't important, it's how you take advantage of them.

drop_descrip.line: Hermes-class aircraft carrier – Hermes, Hull Number 95!

expedition.line: Hold on! Our fleet has come back from commission. Let's see what they've earned.

feeling1.line: Have you fallen to the forces of darkness, Commander...? I'll have to defeat you then!

feeling2.line: What's up, Commander? Interested in duels? Don't worry, we'll start from the beginning, I'll teach you! The most important thing is spirit!

feeling3.line: Interests in anything besides dueling? Hmm... I've never thought about it. Will you show me something new, Commander?

feeling4.line: Mmm... Commander, I decided to engrave your portrait on the back of my cards. That way you're always with me!

feeling5.line: If two duelists fall in love, Commander, they can undertake more duels together! They also must truly understand each other... I think that requirement is already fulfilled for us... so... shall we try?

home.line: Gotcha! Your dueling was hot out there!

login.line: You're back. Now it's time to duel!

lose.line: I won't surrender. My turn... Let me go!

mail.line: You've got new mail, Commander. I wonder if it's a request for a duel!

main1.line: It is my wish to duel with {namecode:89}

main2.line: In each plane and every card resides a soul.

main3.line: It's my turn!Victory aside, I also want to bring happiness to everyone.

mission.line: Missions are like challenges, Commander. Let us challenge ourselves to even greater heights.

mission_complete.line: Rewards' is a good of a word as "duel". Let's see what you've got!

profile.line:
I am called Hermes, I was the second aircraft carrier to be ever built. 
 The only carrier to be sunk by the Sakura Empire? Can't do much about stuff like that. But if I ever get the chance, I want to duel that first carrier.

propose.line: This feeling is……! The bonds formed between Commander and I here shall open up a brand new future, a path of brilliance! It’s our turn, draw!

touch.line: What, you want to duel?

touch2.line: Hmm.... If the Commander is interested, I'll properly reward you each time you win.

unlock.line: Glory to the cards, my soul to the duel d... I mean, the flight deck! I am Hermes. Commander, give me your orders!

upgrade.line: The new me now can move to even greater heights with my deck!

win_mvp.line: When the stars gather in one place, our bonds will illuminate a new future!

battle.line: Hangar, gate open!

detail.line: For a true duelist, there are no accidents, Commander.

drop_descrip.line: Our glory coalesces into the bonds that forge a bright new future! Let's rev it up! Hermes, retrofit complete!

hp_warning.line: My path to victory does not end here!

login.line: I've been waiting. The cards... no... my burning soul told me you'd returned.

lose.line: No one is truly undefeatable... If you give up now, you were never worthy of being my Commander.

mail.line: There is something present in the mail beyond what you can see with your eyes. That is: friendship.

main1.line: Houshou is strong. And now I know. That strength comes from her kindness.

main2.line: Your spirit is a great weapon, and an even greater weakness. No matter where you are, you must not forget that.

main3.line: Centaur taught me how to make this. Try it. I'm showing you that I'm more than just a duelist.

touch.line: That's the wind... Commander, follow my wake!

unlock.line: Our glory coalesces into the bonds that forge a bright new future! Let's rev it up! Hermes, retrofit complete!

win_mvp.line: Hatred, no matter how deep it runs, will always be weak.

battle.line: Training... Aircraft carrier Argus is present and prepared!

detail.line: "You may enter. Come, and witness the glorious history and tradition of Argus"... I-I mean... If you don't mind...

drop_descrip.line: Light aircraft carrier – Argus.

expedition.line: The commission team has returned. Just like carrier-borne craft, you have to welcome the girls back after you've sent them away!

feeling1.line: Ah! If you don't need anything, I'd best be taking my leave! Phew...

feeling2.line: "With the ancient wisdom gathered by sending off countless fledglings, I will lead you, Commander"... May I lead you? If you'll have me, anyway.

feeling3.line: You'd like to take me around on your off day? If it's no trouble, then I'll gladly take you up on that offer. Oh... But I'll need you to bring me back to my dorm before curfew...

feeling4.line: Thank you for another lovely day, Commander. Oh, it's getting late... I'd best get back to my dorm soon, but I-I'd like to take a walk together, first! I'm sorry... May I ask you to indulge me a little?

feeling5.line: Phew... Ehehe, curfew's come and gone already. Say, Commander? What if we kept hanging out together and gazed at the night sky together? There's no point in going back to the Royal Navy dorms, since it's past curfew already.

headtouch.line: You'll make a new hat for me?

home.line: Phew... Welcome back, Commander. *pant* *pant*... I managed to make it back in time before curfew...

hp_warning.line: B-but the Royal Navy's tradition and glory...!

login.line: Shall we get to work, Commander? It's getting late. I don't think we should wait any longer...

lose.line: Urgh... Is this my punishment?

mail.line: A letter's arrived. As for the envelope... Umm, should I just cut it open with scissors?

main1.line: "Fall before the might of my ancient, glorious power"... U-umm, could you go a little easier on the office work, please?

main2.line: Houshou? Oh, thank you for the treats! Are these meant for a tea party? No?

main3.line: You're going out? Okay, I'll take care of the place—Oh, but if you think you'll be out late, please remember my curfew...

mission.line: We have word of a mission. Are you sure we shouldn't take a look at it...?

mission_complete.line: Is the mission complete? Phew... That's great to hear.

profile.line: "Know me as Argus, oldest carrier in the world. With the glory and tradition of the Royal Navy at my back, I come to you to lead the next generation of heroes"... I could never say something that grand with a straight face. I'm... looking forward to working with you, okay?

propose.line: I swear on the tradition and glory of the Royal Navy that I, aircraft carrier Argus, will always work my hardest for our mutual happiness. Commander... Would you hold my hand, please?

touch.line: Is this... a lesson?

touch2.line: B-be gentle, please... *blush*

unlock.line: "Know me as the Royal Navy's own Argus, bearer of a hundred all-seeing eyes, the primordial standard aircraft carrier and first to possess a full-length flight deck." W-will that do...? Sorry. As you can tell, I'm no good at introductions...

upgrade.line: "My rigging, tempered a thousand times over"... I just hope this is enough to help me hold my own in a fight...

win_mvp.line: Me, MVP? You're not joking? I can't believe it...

detail.line: Hosting school events is really such a task. I've been so sleep deprived lately... *yaaawn*... No, that's enough yawning. I still have work to do...

drop_descrip.line: Yaaawn... Umm, did I doze off again? Oh no... Organising school events gets so hectic I always end up working right up until curfew... Just give me one more minute, please...

expedition.line: Costumes, materials, and printed materials are all done. I've contacted the commission team, as well... Things are really coming together. Phew...

home.line: Welcome back, Commander. We have some time until our next plans, so feel free to take a little break.

login.line: Sorry you had to come and help me, Commander... Umm, so what were today's tasks, again?

main1.line: Achoo! ...Thank you. Of course sleeping here all the time would lead to me getting a cold. I should be more careful...

main2.line: There are strange things going on at the haunted mansion? C-Commander, I'm sorry... Would you mind accompanying me?

main3.line: Implacable! You can play that game at home, but you can't bring it to the festival! What do you mean, why? A-aren't you embarrassed?!

mission.line: There are still things to be done before the school festival... Let's begin with these missions.

touch.line: Is it time for the next item on our schedule?

touch2.line: Whawha?!

unlock.line: Yaaawn... Umm, did I doze off again? Oh no... Organising school events gets so hectic I always end up working right up until curfew... Just give me one more minute, please...

win_mvp.line: We won! None can rival the Royal Navy's glorious tradition!

battle.line: I-I'm a little worried about my back...

detail.line: "Take a good look upon the majesty and poise of Argus as she graces the venue." ...I feel much better practicing my bearing with you, Commander. Heehee.

drop_descrip.line: "Gaze upon this glorious dress. Admire its brilliance, tremble, and..." If you don't mind, would you please take Argus' hand?

expedition.line: The commission girls are back. Why don't we invite them to the party?

home.line: The Commander picked this dress for me, so I need to wear it right... Commander? Welcome back. Did the mission go well...?

login.line: Does this look right? Let me try spinning around—Hyah?! C-Commander, I'm sorry...

main1.line: How long will this party go on? If it goes too late, my curfew... N-no, I'm not just trying to go home, I swear!

main2.line: In fairy tales, girls lose their fancy clothes after midnight... And that means I... Eep... A-Argus, stop thinking such shameful things...

main3.line: Don't drink too much at the party, now. If you get drunk, how am I going to change clothes? ...You want me to get Hermes and the others to help? G-good idea! Why didn't I think of that?

mission.line: The mission correspondence...? R-right! Now, where did I put it...?

touch.line: Am I really wearing it to perfection...? Commander, do you see any issues? Y-you can feel for yourself, if you want...?

touch2.line: B-be gentle, please...

unlock.line: "Gaze upon this glorious dress. Admire its brilliance, tremble, and..." If you don't mind, would you please take Argus' hand?

win_mvp.line: "This attire will do perfectly for the parade celebrating my triumph." Phew...

battle.line: Leave the rear support to me... I'll... do my best...!

detail.line: Big brother... do you want to know more about me?

drop_descrip.line: Aircraft carrier – Unicorn, Hull Number I72!

expedition.line: The big sisters out for commission have come back... Big brother... will you greet them?

feeling1.line: Big brother, you're the worst...

feeling2.line: This over here is Yuni. Yuni the Unicorn... is my friend... Ehehe

feeling3.line: When things become dangerous, Yuni will protect me-- It won't be dangerous because you are here, big brother? Ehehe. You are like my knight...

feeling4.line: I've been working hard, you know? ...Supporting big sister... taking on missions... transporting things... Am I a good girl? Am I a helping hand, big brother?

feeling5.line: Big brother... can I be selfish before you? Can I have you pamper me...? I, Unicorn... am actually not a good girl... Is that alright as well?

headtouch.line: Big brother... is Unicorn a good girl...?

home.line: The fleet... returned safely... Good work, big brother. My lap is... alright, you know?

hp_warning.line: Big brother... that hurts...

login.line: Welcome back, big brother... Are we going to sortie for today as well?

lose.line: Outside is... so scary... Can I go back...?

mail.line: Shall we... check your mail?

main1.line: Desstroy Moad'? There is no such thing...

main2.line: Yuni's horn... cannot transform, you know?

main3.line: 'Entee'...? I have no idea what you are talking about, big brother...

main4.line: Will I, Unicorn, grow up to be just like big sister Illustrious one day?

mission.line: Don't forget about... your missions...

mission_complete.line: Don't miss... your rewards...

profile.line: Royal Navy's... support carrier... I am Unicorn... I was born to support my big sister Illustrious... Later, I went to support other big sisters... but everyone treated me nicely. I worked hard in lots of different ways, you know? ...It would be nice if I become a little dependable... Ehehe, I'll work harder, big brother

propose.line: This... precious thing... Are you really giving it to me? I, Unicorn... will work hard... That's because... I like big brother a lot!

touch.line: Ehehe... Big brother... that tickles...

touch2.line: If it's you, big brother... it's alright...

unlock.line: I... I am... The Royal Navy's... Unicorn. ...Commander, can... can I call you... big brother?

upgrade.line: Did ...Unicorn become more mature....Onii-chan?

win_mvp.line: Was I... of great help to you, big brother?

drop_descrip.line: Unicorn... is now a songstress... *giggles* Unicorn's song has reached Onii-chan's heart.

main1.line: Onii-chan, does a fancy dress like this look weird on me?

main2.line: Yuni has grown up too *giggles*!

main3.line: 'Listen to my song!' Am I acting like a songstress? *giggles*

main4.line: Sister Illustrious... do I seem more mature to you now...?

touch.line: Hehe... Onii-chan, do you want to listen to my song?

unlock.line: I have... become a songstress~ ehehe... It would be nice if my song can reach Onii-chan...

detail.line: B-big brother... please don't stare at Unicorn so much... Uuu...

drop_descrip.line: Big brother... this present is for you... I hope you'll like it... Eh? Just seeing me in this outfit is the best gift? Ohh~ b-big brother...!

main1.line: These are called "Spring couplets." The big sisters from the Dragon Empery taught Unicorn how to write this, ehehe~

main2.line: "Firecrackers" seem to be a specialty of the Dragon Empery... Ah, this one is just a prop. It won't go off...

main3.line: Big brother... Has Unicorn grown a bit bigger?

unlock.line: Big brother... this present is for you... I hope you'll like it... Eh? Just seeing me in this outfit is the best gift? Ohh~ b-big brother...!

drop_descrip.line: Ah, big brother, you're here... Ehehe, I only just got here as well. Um... shall we go then? I kind of... want to go to the amusement park...

feeling5.line: Before coming on this date... there was a lot I wanted to say to you, big brother... But now I don't think I need to... because I already know what you're thinking... and what you're feeling. Big brother, do you also know mine?

home.line: There's no need to be in a hurry, okay? Unicorn will always wait for you, big brother.

login.line: Big brother, there are a lot of rides that Unicorn wants to go on, together.

main1.line: Big brother, when we're riding the roller coaster, is it okay to hold your hand?

main2.line: Ferris wheel... recommended for couples, eh? Ah, b-big brother! It's nothing...!

main3.line: The carousel... it's so pretty... Huh? Big brother, I can... sit with you?

mission.line: Big brother, if you have some important business, you can go ahead and take care of that first... Unicorn will be waiting for big brother, always...

touch.line: Big brother, being able to spend time together at an amusement park... and hold hands like this... makes it seem like we're lovers, ehehe...

touch2.line: B-big brother... there are a lot of people here...

unlock.line: Ah, big brother, you're here... Ehehe, I only just got here as well. Um... shall we go then? I kind of... want to go to the amusement park...

detail.line: A grab bag? Is that Unicorn's present...? Th-Thank you! I wonder what's in it... Ehehe, this is so much fun♪

drop_descrip.line: So this is a "kimono" from the Sakura Empire... Changing into it is difficult but... if you like it, then Unicorn is happy!

home.line: About my hair... Big Sis Illustrious did it for me. Is it cute...? Ehehe.

login.line: Happy... New Year! This year, I can spend New Years with you... Ehehe.

main1.line: I heard that, by decorating the arrow that acts as a charm against evil spirits, even bad luck is warded off.

main2.line: Yuni, you changed into New Years' clothes too? Ehehe

main3.line: A decorated pineapple in front of a mirror cake? ...The Sakura Empire's New Year is really interesting...

touch.line: Big brother, are you coming with me to visit the shrine?

unlock.line: So this is a "kimono" from the Sakura Empire... Changing into it is difficult but... if you like it, then Unicorn is happy!

detail.line: It's all thanks to yours, and Illustrious's, and everyone else's support that I can get up onstage and sing!

drop_descrip.line: So I'm... an "idol" now... I'm not sure how well I'll do... But I'll give it my all...!

home.line: I'm a little nervous, but... with you by my side, Big Brother, I know I can do it...

login.line: You came to watch me practice, Big Brother...? I'm so glad!

main1.line: I hope my song gets through to everyone...

main2.line: I'm like... an angel? That's, a b-bit much...

main3.line: Yuni will stay with me, right? Take the mic for me... Thank you, Yuni♪

touch.line: You're the only audience I need, Big Brother! I'll... always sing my best for you!

unlock.line: So I'm... an "idol" now... I'm not sure how well I'll do... But I'll give it my all...!

detail.line: Unicorn is very healthy. She won't get an upset tummy...

drop_descrip.line: Oh, big brother... Unicorn is reading right now. Mm, yeah, while eating ice cream... Big brother, want to have a bite?

home.line: Shhh... Please don't wake Yuni up, big brother...

login.line: Big brother... are you here to read with Unicorn? Yay, I'm so happy...

main1.line: Mmmh~ The ice cream is so cold... but so yummy...

main2.line: Big brother... what flavor of ice cream do you like better, vanilla... or strawberry?

main3.line: Illustrious gave me this storybook... Mm, some of these stories are still hard to understand though...

touch.line: Unicorn won't catch a cold~ She also has this blanket over here...

touch2.line: Noo... the ice cream's going to drip onto the pages...

unlock.line: Oh, big brother... Unicorn is reading right now. Mm, yeah, while eating ice cream... Big brother, want to have a bite?

detail.line: The "hospital food" Miss Jervis made was the most amazing thing I've ever seen... Um, if I could also cook like that... Maybe I would be able to feed big brother myself... Ahh... *blushes*

drop_descrip.line: Unicorn... is now serving as a nurse. Umm... Big brother, would you mind being Unicorn's patient...?

expedition.line: The big sisters in the commission fleet have come back... Oh, since you're a patient now, maybe I should go welcome them back...?

home.line: Good job on your sortie... Um, now then, big brother... Are you feeling unwell anywhere...?

login.line: Big brother, will you help me with my nurse practice today? Um, can you p-please lie down over there first...?

main1.line: If I use this stethoscope... I'll also be able to hear big brother's pounding heart clearly...

main2.line: I learned a lot about nursing from Miss Perseus, you know? She explained it to me very carefully... but there are still some things I don't quite get...

main3.line: Thanks for bringing me the thermometer, Yuni... Ehehe, yes, you're a very reliable helper~

touch.line: Today, I am your nurse, and yours alone, big brother. Ehehe~

unlock.line: Unicorn... is now serving as a nurse. Umm... Big brother, would you mind being Unicorn's patient...?

detail.line: Big brother... you truly understand me.

drop_descrip.line: This is... an important outfit for an important ceremony... yes! Unicorn and Yuni are both ready for this! Big brother... how do I look?

hp_warning.line: I can do it... for you, big brother...!

login.line: Big brother! Eheheh... I'll always be here waiting for you to come back.

lose.line: Nng... I have to... be strong... for big brother...

mail.line: The mail...! Yuni got it for us~

main1.line: Um, big brother... I've been working really hard lately, so... Do you think maybe, when we have a day off... We could go out together?

main2.line: Yuni and I got matching outfits... ehehehe...

main3.line: I've been learning to cook from some of the older Royal Navy girls... Ehehe. I can't wait to surprise you. Oh! I guess you won't be surprised, since I just told you... Hm...

main4.line: Even when I become an elegant lady like Illustrious... can I still stay with you all the time, big brother...?

mission.line: A mission... Can I help with it?

mission_complete.line: Wow... that's a lot of rewards. Good job, big brother.

touch.line: Big brother, can I hold your hand a bit longer...?

unlock.line: This is... an important outfit for an important ceremony... yes! Unicorn and Yuni are both ready for this! Big brother... how do I look?

win_mvp.line: Unicorn got to help big brother...! Ehehe...

battle.line: Unicorn... can now fight alongside everyone else!

detail.line: Illustrious said that Unicorn grew a little bigger... Do you think that's true? Ehehe...

drop_descrip.line: Unicorn has finished her retrofit... Now she can do more for you and her friends!

expedition.line: The friends in the commission fleet have returned... Big brother, can you take me with you?

headtouch.line: You're also very nice, big brother... Ehehe~♪

home.line: Ehehe, Yuni also wanted to tell you "Welcome back," big brother.

login.line: Welcome back, big brother... Are you going out today as well? Unicorn and Yuni are ready to come with you...

lose.line: Unicorn... will protect everyone!

main1.line: Yuni has become big and strong, so Unicorn has to do her best too!

main2.line: Unicorn's new rigging seems... to be giving off light... Do you want to take a closer look?

main3.line: Unicorn wants to be just like you, not just on the battlefield, but in all kinds of other ways as well! She will do her best!

main4.line: If you get tired, you can rest in Unicorn's lap... (Ehehe, I really want to see big brother's sleeping face...)

mission.line: Can Unicorn help... with your mission?

mission_complete.line: Ehehe, there are so many rewards that not even Yuni can carry them all~

touch.line: Big brother... You can also rely more on Unicorn, you know?

touch2.line: Bad big brother... Ehehe, bad~♪

unlock.line: Unicorn has finished her retrofit... Now she can do more for you and her friends!

win_mvp.line: Unicorn... was able to be of help!

battle.line: Elders, let us strive together for victory!

detail.line: My... appearance? Right, well, my name derives from a mythological creature, so that's why I look rather... fantastical?

drop_descrip.line: Centaur-class light aircraft carrier – Centaur.

expedition.line: I can hear it. A whisper on the wind... Hehe, just kidding. Huh? The commission team has returned.

feeling1.line: How could my beloved fleet turn out like this...

feeling2.line: Commander, would you mind introducing me to some of the fleet Elders? I don't much like being alone...

feeling3.line: It, it isn't really that shocking that I use polite language with the destroyer Elders... is it? B- but to me, those girls are also my Elders, worthy of respect!

feeling4.line: Spending so much time with the Commander and my Elders has shown me a side of you I never expected to see. For example... Admirable person though you are, Commander, you do sneak away from your duties from time to time. Hehehe.

feeling5.line: I understand now that the others are ordinary people, just like me. But it's still not wrong to treat them with respect. ...Not only as their Childe, but also as their sister-in-arms.

home.line: I'm learning a lot from how you and the Elders fight, Commander.

hp_warning.line: Just as the Elders do, I shall hold fast!

login.line: Commander, I swear to follow the examples of my Elders and strive for greatness once more today!

lose.line: Forgive me, Elders...

mail.line: Commander, some new mail has come in. I'll go fetch it for you.

main1.line: By the way, supposing I really was a "Centaur," like a half-man, half-horse? Wouldn't that be funny...? What do you think, Commander?

main2.line: Peaceful, carefree days certainly are lovely, and yet I can't help but wonder from time to time, why was I even born?

main3.line: Serving as your secretary ship gives me so many chances to interact with the Elders. I can learn so much from them. Thank you, Commander!

mission.line: Commander, shouldn't you head out to complete this mission? I'll accompany you.

mission_complete.line: Commander, how should we handle the mission rewards?

profile.line: I am called Centaur, name ship of the Centaur-class aircraft carriers. As I was constructed only after the Second Great War, I lived a peaceful life, in spite of it all. And so to me, all the ships of the fleet, even the little destroyer girls, are my Elders. I am at your disposal.

propose.line: Having been born into a world of peace, I certainly can't say I am glad to fight... But to meet you, Commander, and to be assigned to your fleet, these are the things that truly make me glad.

skill.line: I've learnt from the Elders, I'll show you their courage!

touch.line: You want to try pulling my bowstring? Hehe, it's harder than it looks, huh?

touch2.line: Commander, you're embarrassing me...

unlock.line: So this is the place where all my Elders who fought in the Second Great War gather... Greetings, Commander, I am Centaur, at your service.

upgrade.line: Thank you, Commander. I continue to strive toward the examples of my Elders.

win_mvp.line: Commander, I think I'm catching up to the Elders, maybe, just a bit...?

detail.line: The Elders haven't been shy about complimenting my figure, though I can't help but feel a little bit embarrassed...

drop_descrip.line: Even though I see the ocean every day, changing into this swimsuit gives me a totally new outlook on it. How about you, Commander? Don't you feel at ease?

feeling5.line: Commander, let's go to the beach together after sunset and watch the stars. I'll show you my constellation. And then we'll have... a chat.... sound good?

login.line: Commander, what would you say to a stroll on the beach?

main1.line: Taking in the ocean, feeling the sea breeze, letting the sounds of the waves lap against my ears... I feel completely at peace here.

main2.line: Coming to the beach with my Elders, and of course with the Commander, to spend a day off is so delightful.

main3.line: Commander, Elder Hermes has been talking about this "Summer Duel Tournament" that's about to begin. Why don't we go watch together?

touch.line: Commander, is this pose okay? How about my expression? Hehe, all right then, make sure you get my good side.

unlock.line: Even though I see the ocean every day, changing into this swimsuit gives me a totally new outlook on it. How about you, Commander? Don't you feel at ease?

detail.line: You want to see me dance...? W-well, I'm not very practiced, but if that's what my Commander wants...

drop_descrip.line: I never imagined you would give me such a splendid dress, Commander... I think it's called a "qipao..." is it? I'll try it, revealing though it is. Wh-what do you think...? Do I look... nice?

home.line: It really looks like the whole fleet is having a good time and getting along so well... This season is truly delightful.

login.line: Looks like everyone from the Dragon Empery is in the midst of preparing their Spring Festival celebrations, but I'm not sure there's anything I could help with...

main1.line: In the coming year, I'll be trying even harder to learn from my Elders!

main2.line: I learned a special dance from the Elders of the Dragon Empery, I do hope it pleases the Commander and the other Elders.

main3.line: Commander, if you're feeling stressed, I could massage your back for you, help you relax a little?

touch.line: These fans and my shawl are so soft to the touch~ Commander, would you like to feel?

touch2.line: Th-the Elders are all watching...

unlock.line: I never imagined you would give me such a splendid dress, Commander... I think it's called a "qipao..." is it? I'll try it, revealing though it is. Wh-what do you think...? Do I look... nice?

battle.line: If I'm chasing you, don't think you'll get away so easily, haha~

detail.line: Commander, adding milk to your black tea is a fine way of enjoying it as well~ If you get a chance, be sure to give it a try.

drop_descrip.line: Attacker-class escort carrier - Chaser (D32)

expedition.line: The girls on commission have returned. I wonder if they managed to pick up any tea leaves along the way.

feeling1.line: Commander, you've been in pretty rough shape recently. If there's something bothering you, it wouldn't hurt to let me know~

feeling2.line: Even though I was born in the Eagle Union, I was treated very warmly in the Royal Navy. Belfast even taught me how to make a proper cuppa~

feeling3.line: Every time I set sail, some seagulls will be flying overhead. Legend has it that this signifies a safe journey~ Every time I see these little guys, I always feel at ease.

feeling4.line: Commander, it is important for you to develop a refined taste in a timely manner~ Would you like to try some of my freshly-brewed tea? I have the utmost confidence in this particular skill, hehe~

feeling5.line: Commander, when I'm alone with you, I feel like the taste of tea becomes even more mellow and sweet~ Could this be... what love tastes like?

home.line: Commander, you're back! Let me take a look... Great, you won without even a scratch~

hp_warning.line: My flight deck's on fire! Hurry and put it out!

login.line: G'day, Commander. For beauty and health, start your morning with a cuppa~!

lose.line: Drats, my flight deck caught on fire again...

mail.line: Commander, your air express mail is here.

main1.line: Launching and landing carrier-based planes is a bit of a sensitive topic. You'll end up in hot water if you're not careful.

main2.line: Commander, have you seen an aurora before? The dazzling, ever shifting bands of light illuminating the night sky... I'd really like you to see for yourself.

main3.line: I'm really worried about the escort destroyers. As soon as they see submarines, they immediate charge forward. Please remind them to stay in escort formation.

mission.line: Commander, new missions have been posted. Don't get lazy on me now~

mission_complete.line: That's quite a nice haul from the mission rewards. As expected of Commander, ever so hardworking.

profile.line: I am a member of the Royal Navy's Attacker-class escort carriers. Although I served in the Royal Navy, I was originally born in the Eagle Union and even stayed in the Dragon Empery for some time. I really dislike submarines, but I should be fine as long as we deal with them carefully~

propose.line: Commander, are you confessing to me? Hehe~ I'm very impressed that you're being so straightforward and brave~ But before I can reciprocate, can I propose something? Just for the two of us... a secret tea party...

touch.line: Commander, my aircraft are in ace condition, ready to deploy at any time!

touch2.line: This is no way to treat a lady~

unlock.line: Greetings, Commander. Escort carrier Chaser, reporting for duty. Rumour has it that the tea and refreshments prepared here are simply delicious. Of course, I look forward to meeting friends here who share my refined taste, hehe~

upgrade.line: My my, at this rate, I'm might even catch up to those regular carriers.

win_mvp.line: Even though I'm an escort carrier, I won't lose to the regular aircraft carriers when it comes to ability~

detail.line: After spending some time in the Empery, I started to realise that, in addition to black tea, I sometimes wanted to enjoy the fragrance of green tea as well.

drop_descrip.line: Does this dress from the Dragon Empery not suit me well? Though I was born in the Eagle Union and raised by the Royal Navy, my time in the Dragon Empery also left a deep impression upon me. Why don't we have a chat about their profound culture and tea? Hehe~

feeling1.line: I have a commander who is as bitter as oversteeped green tea that has been left out and forgotten.

login.line: Hm? Commander, you're back~ Is there a story you'd like to hear from me today?

lose.line: Ugh... there's this saying that "for soldiers, both victory and defeat are standard issue."

main1.line: The Dragon Empery's traditional dances seem difficult to learn... Eh, you'd like to learn them with me? In that case, we should be able to learn them in no time~

main2.line: Eh, fireworks display? Um, I think I'll pass... I'm... not good around fire.

main3.line: (yawns) ... Ahh, I stayed up too late last night exchanging stories with the Empery girls, so I'm really sleepy...

mission_complete.line: Mhm! As expected, Commander, you've finished the mission! Hurry and see if we were rewarded with any tea~

skill.line: I see you~ Don't think you can run from me!

touch.line: Commander, do you like my qipao? Don't you think blonde hair matches the aesthetic of the dress quite well? Ehehe~

touch2.line: Oh dear... Commander, flirting is fine but please don't go overboard~

unlock.line: Does this dress from the Dragon Empery not suit me well? Though I was born in the Eagle Union and raised by the Royal Navy, my time in the Dragon Empery also left a deep impression upon me. Why don't we have a chat about their profound culture and tea? Hehe~

detail.line: Our work takes us to the far corners of the world. Keeping a game console on hand to stave off boredom is a good idea, isn't it?

drop_descrip.line: Heck yeah! Another achievement down! ...Huh? Good day, Commander. Is there something wrong with my appearance? Hehe, I'm from the Eagle Union after all, of course I'd know a thing or two about entertainment~♪

feeling1.line: Commander? It wouldn't hurt to go outside and do something else every now and then, all right?

home.line: All right, time for me to grab that high score!

login.line: C'mon, Commander! Which stage are we gonna clear today?

main1.line: Long Island, down to host another raid next time? I want to get some new equipment~♪

main2.line: Bogue's pitches are way too overpowered... No matter how hard I try, I can only hit two or three out of ten...

main3.line: Listen to this, Commander! I learned how to cook from Mullany! ...Eh, I learned the wrong thing...?

touch2.line: Jeez... games aren't enough for you?

unlock.line: Heck yeah! Another achievement down! ...Huh? Good day, Commander. Is there something wrong with my appearance? Hehe, I'm from the Eagle Union after all, of course I'd know a thing or two about entertainment~♪

battle.line: Careful, now. The battlefield is no place to worry about fuel economy.

detail.line: The big mirror in my room? What about it? If I told you, "I just like mirrors," would that satisfy your curiosity?

drop_descrip.line: Colossus-class light aircraft carrier – Perseus (HMS Perseus.)

expedition.line: Look, Commander... No, I'm not angry, I was just going to tell you a commission is done.

feeling1.line: You really are like a can of rancid surströmming.

feeling2.line: I can hear just fine, Commander, so don't go yelling in my ear, thanks...

feeling3.line: If you ask me, people should be able to say whatever they want... Oh, hello there, Commander. Just talking to myself.

feeling4.line: I'm a total moron... Why am I so rude to the Commander when I just want to be friends... I'm so, so stupid...

feeling5.line: How would I describe you? I dunno, I guess like a storm in the middle of a peaceful voyage... No, no, I didn't mean it like that... Sorry, what I meant to say is, um...

headtouch.line: ...Yeah?

home.line: One quick battle, and you're knackered already, Commander? You have the stamina of a beached whale.

hp_warning.line: ...I can't afford to mess around, huh.

login.line: There's some saying that goes, "the early bird catches the worm." ...If that's true, I guess you'd starve, Commander.

lose.line: Damn, we lost... Sorry.

mail.line: You've got mail. Nope, didn't bring it with me. Next time, ask, and I'll consider it.

main1.line: If you need my help with something, just say it. You do need to try and accomplish it on your own first, though.

main2.line: Work is like food, in a way; leave it sitting for too long and it goes bad. Just so you know.

main3.line: I heard Yuubari and Akashi get up to fun experiments in the lab. I kind of wanna see one. Kind of.

mission.line: What kind of lazy cat are you, just lounging around all day instead of doing missions?

mission_complete.line: Those mission rewards will expire if you don't claim them. Maybe.

profile.line: I'm Perseus, the Colossus-class light aircraft carrier. Sadly, I didn't enter service until the war had ended. Don't have much in the way of a reputation or experience as a result. Still, I'll try to do a good job. All right, is that good enough? *sigh*...

propose.line: Obviously I don't hate you, Commander. How could I, when I adore talking to you and being patted on the head? L-look, I'm trying to say... I love you. I mean it...

touch.line: Maybe try finishing your work before you "chat me up" or "interview me" or however you wanna sugarcoat it?

touch2.line: You must really want a seat at the naval jailhouse dinner table, huh?

unlock.line: I'm Perseus, from the Royal Navy. You can pronounce it "Per-see-us" if you want though... Well, whatever. Are we done here? Great. Nice meeting you.

upgrade.line: Thanks a bunch... Well, yeah, didn't you want a thank-you?

win_mvp.line: Looks like the enemy will have to, uh, try harder next time.

detail.line: I'm still learning, but I know how to give injections and stop a haemorrhage in theory. Can I practice my knowledge on you, Commander?

drop_descrip.line: I'm Perseus, I will be your nurse today. Use this button to call for me if you need anything... Yes? Did you need something?

home.line: Your health is seriously concerning, Commander. Want me to get you some vitamins?

login.line: Honestly, I have no idea what sort of face to put on when pretending to be a nurse.

main1.line: It's noble to help those in need, but don't go overboard with it. What I'm trying to say is: unless you NEED my help, just make do on your own, Commander.

main2.line: Now to practice turning a gravely injured person over... You, I'm gonna need you to lie on your back.

main3.line: Nice new med tech. Commander, I want you to be my guinea pig– Excuse me, I mean, experiment assistant.

touch.line: You have a healthy look in your eyes, Commander.

touch2.line: You belong in the bed of a jail cell, not of a hospital.

unlock.line: I'm Perseus, I will be your nurse today. Use this button to call for me if you need anything... Yes? Did you need something?

battle.line: With courage and loyalty, we shall prevail!

detail.line: You want to know about my appearance? Unlike Elder Centaur, my name is not based on a mythological creature. If I had to say, the land where those with my appearance lived in the ancient times when legends roamed the world... Oh, am I talking your head off?

drop_descrip.line: Centaur-class light aircraft carrier – Albion.

expedition.line: The whispers of the wind... tell me that the girls have returned from their commissions. Let me know when you're ready to meet with them.

feeling1.line: Was there something amiss with the way I conducted myself...?

feeling2.line: As a Childe of the fleet, I can only hope to learn from the examples my Elders set in battle, as well as from how you manage the fleet. There is much for me to learn in terms of techniques, mental attitude, as well as everyday customs.

feeling3.line: Hmm... Perhaps I need a new way of addressing my Elders of the destroyer class... And then there are the blueprint ships as well... But they're still my Elders... What should I do...?

feeling4.line: Elder Commander, should I leave these documents over here? Urgh, I knew it would feel weird to call you that... Calling you one of my Elders doesn't feel respectful enough, and frankly, feels quite strange to say out loud...

feeling5.line: How should I address the Commander then? Lord Commander? I'm sure my Elders have much more intimate ways of address... Ugh, I can't believe I sabotaged myself from the start, even though I'd like to have a closer relationship... Maybe I should try a different approach, like a date or something...?

home.line: You did a great job, Commander. Please call for me if there's anything I can do to lighten your load.

hp_warning.line: I've got to dig my heels in... I don't want to be a burden to my Elders!

login.line: Light carrier, Albion, at your service. I await your orders.

lose.line: How did I manage... to be so clumsy...

mail.line: There seems to be some new mail... Would you like to take a look?

main1.line: If you require a change of pace, I would like to suggest taking a stroll through the forest with Elder Centaur. I would especially recommend the forest by the hills, as the wind there feels particularly nice. Hehehe.

main2.line: The ships of my class use a variety of arms in battle, so I don't think trying to copy their fighting style will be of much use to me. Instead, I can learn from their battle-readiness.

main3.line: Grey Ghost...? I'm not sure I can shoulder the burden of sharing a nickname with Elder Enterprise... I-if you're fine with it, I do suppose you can call me that, if you wish...

mission.line: Let us work towards the completion of your missions. It is by following your example that we shipgirls reach new heights.

mission_complete.line: The rewards for your completed missions are here. Should I... check the address to confirm whether they've arrived at the right place?

profile.line: I am the Royal Navy light carrier, Albion. I was constructed along with Centaur after that great war, and was one of the first aircraft carriers to carry out newly-developed tactics. Please watch over my growth under the tutelage of my Elders, Commander.

propose.line: A... Promise Ring? Um, I don't recall ever asking for one though... You're giving it to me because you love me? O-oh! Yes, I see! I apologise for being so thick-skulled that I didn't have an inkling of your feelings for me. Ehehe, thank you... very much. ♥

skill.line: Please watch what I can do, my dear Elders!

touch.line: U-um, go ahead... So long as you don't touch the rigging of my bow...

touch2.line: H-how embarrassing... Ugh...

unlock.line: My name is Albion, sister ship to light carrier Centaur. As a Childe to this fleet, I hope to receive guidance from everyone in this fleet–– Um, Commander, that also makes you one of my Elders, right?

upgrade.line: The strengthening was a success. Commander, please see for yourself how the ride feels next time we head out.

win_mvp.line: The unblemished Albion thus claims this victory!

detail.line: I-I apologise for making a fool of myself... If it's alright with you, can I tag along with you for a bit longer? I'm sure if I try hard enough, I'll be able to step on you more satisfactorily... But don't worry, I'm just playing a role.

drop_descrip.line: Ah, umm... If you keep staring at me like that... Oh, um, Commander, this is supposed to be a Royalty of the Night costume, right? In that case... Would you mind kneeling for me first?

feeling5.line: Commander, please continue serving me until the end of time. If you keep your end of the bargain, I swear that I... ehehe, will always take care of all your needs. Both faeries and vampires live long lives, so regardless, I'll always be with you~♪

home.line: Impeccable results. Oh, I suppose I should have a more condescending attitude towards you...? Umm, I suppose those were... passable results?

login.line: Tonight, I shall make a servant of you, Commander. Um... Excuse me, but could you do this favour for me please? *bows*

main1.line: Shall I become a faerie, a vampire, or even a succubus...? Hmm, I wonder, which of these do I see myself being?

main2.line: Elder Vampire has taken me under her tutelage, but it's quite difficult to walk in this outfit... Oh, I'd be just fine with you by my side, though.

main3.line: It feels quite awkward having to give you orders... You know what? You should be the one ordering me around after all. Just say the word, and it shall be done.

touch.line: This outfit is a bit too tight around certain places... Ugh...

touch2.line: So this is what you're like when you've been seduced... I'll have to keep this in mind... Whew... *blushes*

unlock.line: Ah, umm... If you keep staring at me like that... Oh, um, Commander, this is supposed to be a Royalty of the Night costume, right? In that case... Would you mind kneeling for me first?

win_mvp.line: A victory as unblemished as... Oh, I wonder if I can still say that in these black clothes... I-in any case, a victory is a victory!

battle.line: The battle is on. Everyone, stick close to me!

detail.line: I spy with my little eye a naughty cat who's snuck into my room to snoop around for secrets... Got you! Hm? No, Commander, this the creature in question – not you.

drop_descrip.line: Colossus-class light carrier – Theseus.

expedition.line: The commission team's come back. Do you know what comes next, Commander?

feeling1.line: Don't cross that delicate line, Villainous Fiend – or else I'll do everyone a favour and eradicate you.

feeling2.line: Funny our paths should cross here, Commander. Were you looking for me, perchance? Heehee, you're like a doggy, sniffing around in search of its friends♪

feeling3.line: Care to join me? The woods are the perfect place for a tea party... Picnic? Hmm, I suppose it is more like a picnic, now that you say that...

feeling4.line: How's your evening, our Champion? Not too much work? Not feeling burnt out? Heehee. Do give me a call if you need anything. I'll do everything I can, and still consider the things I can't do.

feeling5.line: Eyes open for my marvellous... Heehee, oh, it's nothing important. I simply used an incantation that tells me whenever you're in a spot. Saves you the effort of having to tell me. Convenient, no?

home.line: Splendid work, our Eagle of Victory. Before you go reflect on your performance, shouldn't we celebrate this triumph first?

hp_warning.line: I will not... succumb so easily!

login.line: Good morning, Guardian Knight of the Port. Hope you slept well. You can call on us anytime if you need a word.

lose.line: Well, we lost... Commander, let's retreat for now and have another go later.

mail.line: Oh, this letter is addressed to you. I just assumed it was for me, since it arrived by homing pigeon.

main1.line: Hi there, Unicorn. Do you mind if I take little Yuni on a tour de dessert again? ...Huh? What is it? Did I say something odd?

main2.line: All this work piling up reminds me of herbs brewing in a cauldron... Eyes open, Commander. I'll have this done in a flash.

main3.line: They say to strike while the iron is hot, but I'd say strike even if it's not. What I'm driving at is: let's take a break and clean the office, shall we?

mission.line: Ah, missions... Got it. Shall we do them together, Commander?

mission_complete.line: Heehee. These are more rewards than you can shake a stick at. How lovely.

profile.line: Colossus-class light aircraft carrier Theseus, at your service. Sadly, I just barely missed my chance to fight in the war, but that's okay. Much like my namesake's ship, nothing will change who I am now.

propose.line: I understand. You've given me the ring, but aren't sure how to profess your love. I'll do the honour, just... Oh, you worked up the courage? W-well, that's good! Heehee. Did I do a good job?

skill.line: Eyes open for my might! Taaake THIS!

touch.line: I'm here and listening if you need someone to talk to♪

touch2.line: Whoa! What's gotten into you?

unlock.line: I am Theseus, Colossus-class light aircraft carrier. Well met, Shepherd of the Fleet. If you ever need someone to carry out combat, housework, or an incantation, just call my name.

upgrade.line: Eyes open for my newfound strength!

win_mvp.line: How'd I do? Did I successfully realise the plan you had in mind, Commander?

detail.line: Eyes open for my catering skills, Commander! Oh, shoot, this is actually tough to balance... Maybe this is best left to the professional Royal Maids.

drop_descrip.line: Steaming hot manjuu buns, ready to be served! Let us have a big feast then gather rosebuds, Commander. Oh, a "holiday gathering" doesn't involve literal gathering?

expedition.line: The commission team is back. I have some carp ornaments on hand, so... Yeah, let's go hand out some gifts!

login.line: Like the saying goes, the early bird catches the worm. We'd better get a move on before people snatch up all the food, Commander.

main1.line: Gosh, there are so many restaurants. Makes you want to check them all out, doesn't it, Commander?

main2.line: You're meant to have yum cha tea with these manjuus? Sounds questionable... These buns are a far cry from biscuits at a tea party.

main3.line: Unicorn, you and I have... quite different outfits. See, this is an Empery-style dress. The wings make me look a bit like a swan. Heehee.

touch2.line: Oh wow... *blushes*

unlock.line: Steaming hot manjuu buns, ready to be served! Let us have a big feast then gather rosebuds, Commander. Oh, a "holiday gathering" doesn't involve literal gathering?

battle.line: The battlefield... Heh, I'm getting all fired up!

detail.line: There are many Royal Navy ships named "Eagle," and I will go great lengths to maintain its honourable reputation.

drop_descrip.line: Eagle-class light aircraft carrier – Eagle (HMS Eagle.)

expedition.line: Commission complete. Let's go and offer the returning team some biscuits. Don't worry about me, I can do without.

feeling1.line: You're betraying everyone's trust in you by acting like this. Pull yourself together, for god's sake!

feeling2.line: People say I'm not great at socializing, a fact that I begrudge. But my social skills aside, I do know my manners.

feeling3.line: I'm not a frequent attendee at Royal Navy tea parties... Which isn't to say I don't want to, it's just... they bring out snacks at tea parties... What do you think I mean, Commander?! I'd gain weight, that's the problem! ...Sorry, I lost my cool for a sec there.

feeling4.line: Despite my low-calorie diet and daily rigorous exercise, my weight stays the same... *sigh*, I guess my past status as a battleship defines me more than I think... But why?! How does everyone else manage to lose weight just fine?!

feeling5.line: You are irreplaceable to me. Whatever becomes of me... Scratch that. I'll stay the way I am now, just for you. Because I think this is what made me equally irreplaceable to you. Am I right?

home.line: My body weight's still the same as it w– Oh! Commander! Didn't think you'd be back so soon. A-anyway, you'd better give our next mission plan a look!

hp_warning.line: A warrior of the Royal Navy won't back down so easily!

login.line: Great to see you! Based upon your punctuality, I can already tell that you're a responsible commander.

lose.line: Tsk, I've taken damage after fighting for so long... I'll need repairs when we return.

mail.line: There's mail for you. Don't forget to give it a look.

main1.line: Let's see what's on the menu today... Fruits and a vegetable salad. Ideal for a low-calorie diet.

main2.line: How much do I weigh? Ahem, you'd better drop this topic, or else...! Okay, I'm just exaggerating. But I hope you understand that it's a sensitive topic for me.

main3.line: A band of Iron Blood submarines ran away before I could as much as say hello. Again... Guess I'll have to come up with a good way of approaching them.

mission.line: There's still unfinished missions, Commander. We should get them done sooner rather than later.

mission_complete.line: Now that's the face of an accomplished commander. Good job.

profile.line: After having been converted from a battleship into an aircraft carrier, I provided much early experience for the Royal Navy's carrier forces, and my final moments were spent fighting on the battlefield. Though I met a noble warrior's end, I do wish I'd been done in by a cannon or an airstrike, rather than a submarine.

propose.line: I once met my final obstacle in the Suez Canal... But if you ever need saving, I will overcome any obstacle to get to you, Commander. This is my promise not just as a warrior, but as your lover.

touch.line: What is it? An invitation to get lunch? Hmm... Sorry, but could you go in my place?

touch2.line: You see, this is the reason why we have to teach people proper etiquette.

unlock.line: The name is Eagle. I intend to serve your fleet to the utmost of my abilities as a proud warrior of the Royal Navy.

upgrade.line: Enhancements, huh... I just wish they wouldn't affect my weight...

win_mvp.line: To show compassion to your foe is to put the safety of your allies at risk.

detail.line: I've come well prepared in hopes of learning the ropes of our infirmary.

drop_descrip.line: This may be an exercise, but even so I will give it my all. Right now, I am not just a Royal Navy warrior, but a medical resident as well. If you ever feel ill, come see me, Commander.

home.line: "Weight Loss and Health Care Metholody," eh... Oh, ahem! Good to see you again, Commander. I-I was just reading medical literature, that's all!

login.line: Debrief me on your symptoms. Oh, that doesn't sound like what a doctor would say? Then how about... Do you feel ill?

main1.line: I've come up with a new, healthy diet that improves your physical stamina. Care to give it a try?

main2.line: Treating wounds and saving lives – being a doctor comes with great responsibility, but also great pride.

main3.line: Are you scared of needles, Commander? I understand. Then as part of this training, we should give you a shot, just so– Oh, okay, maybe we shouldn't.

touch.line: Let's take your temperature, just to be sure. Mind if I assist with that?

touch2.line: Umm... Are you feeling lightheaded, Commander? Do you need a thorough examination?

unlock.line: This may be an exercise, but even so I will give it my all. Right now, I am not just a Royal Navy warrior, but a medical resident as well. If you ever feel ill, come see me, Commander.

battle.line: Is that it? Hah! Swordfish squadron, prepare for battle!

detail.line: Ark Royal, ready for inspection!

drop_descrip.line: Aircraft carrier – Ark Royal, Hull Number 91!

expedition.line: Commissions have been completed, Commander. If there are any cute destroyers in the fleet, allow me to welcome them back myself.

feeling1.line: You can't compare with the destroyers, Commander...

feeling2.line: I... I'm going to say this in advance, but... those destroyer girls... u-um... I kid of... I mean... I kind of hold them dear... I know how to mind my manners... It's not... it's not a crime!

feeling3.line: I thought you were finally going to have me Court Martialed, Commander! I'm grateful to finally be recognized by you. It's nothing to be ashamed of? Commander, I, Ark Royal, will follow you forever!

feeling4.line: G-good grief... If you were the same size as those destroyers, Commander, I wouldn't be so embarrassed... I was fine with doing this with the little ones... but with you...

feeling5.line: If I were closer to you, Commander, I could get closer with the destroyers too... Of... of course, that can only happen with your approval. I'm more than happy to help you with destroyer inspections! Is that all right, commander?

home.line: Is it time for a break? I'm going to see my destroyer sisters then!

hp_warning.line: If only a destroyer would give me a hug!

login.line: Ready for orders, Commander. I am confident in any kind of battle!

lose.line: Damn, trapped!

mail.line: Do you need to me read out your mail, Commander?

main1.line: You look like you're busy, Commander. I won't bother you then. Let me know if you need anything.

main2.line: Commander, umm... can you tell the destroyers to come to my room? I'd like to give them presents.

main3.line: This is... So cute! *pat pat* Eh? Wh-when did you get here, Commander?!

mission.line: Commander, it's a soldier's duty to complete missions!

mission_complete.line: Commander, to leave your rewards unclaimed is disrespect to the mission.

profile.line:
Ark Royal, reporting in! I'm the first aircraft carrier specifically designed and built for the role in the Royal Navy, I'm proud of being a prototype to all other carriers that followed. 
 Little needs to be said about my feats against the Bismarck. Rather I must ask, are there any of those cute little destroyers in our fleet?

propose.line: I'll take care of all the destroyers from now on! No one can touch Commander or my destroyers. No one!

skill.line: It's time for you to leave!

touch.line: Your warm hands keep me energized to keep fighting, Commander!

touch2.line: Eh... Commander... please don't... Why are you doing this?!

unlock.line: Ark Royal, reporting in for duty! I am confident in all manners of battle. Why, it was I who managed to destroy Bismarck's rudder!

upgrade.line: Oh! oh! oh! Allow me to protect you, my destroyer friends!

win_mvp.line: An enemy who loses their ability to steer will be doomed!

detail.line: It is dangerous to let the destroyers play on the beach alone... I suggest setting aside time every day to allow them to frolic together.

drop_descrip.line: Nothing says summer like the sun, the beach, and destroyers... Ahem! Th-that's right! Even though we're relaxing, we still have to keep an eye out for enemy destroyers! Commander, I may be in a swimsuit, but I'm ready to sortie at any time!

login.line: Summer, huh... Commander, do you enjoy the summertime? I know I do.

main1.line: To be honest, Commander, I wanted to provide everyone with some toys to play with while on the beach, but don't know what would be well received. Could I go consult the destroyers to see what they think?

main2.line: Commander, why have you been staring at me this whole time? Huh, I'm "quite the beauty when I'm not running my mouth"...?!

main3.line: Some say that my tastes are a bit questionable, but I have complete confidence in my abilities as secretary ship. I'll take care of the work!

touch.line: Destroyers frolicking around in swimsuits? Where?! ...Commander, don't mess with me like that!

unlock.line: Nothing says summer like the sun, the beach, and destroyers... Ahem! Th-that's right! Even though we're relaxing, we still have to keep an eye out for enemy destroyers! Commander, I may be in a swimsuit, but I'm ready to sortie at any time!

battle.line: Time to get rid of some troublemakers!

detail.line: You need to inspect what's on my camera? Well... let's not worry about it until after the party. I promise I'll hand over every last negative!

drop_descrip.line: One tends to let her guard down at a party like this, but worry not! Put the ball in my hands and let Ark Royal keep you safe!

home.line: Ooooooh! Brilliant! Perfect! – Ahem! Erm, well, that's right! This is just your average, everyday record keeping here. I'm not doing anything weird at all! No siree!

login.line: Commander, status report: all quiet over here.

main1.line: This camera is strictly for security recording purposes. You never know what might happen. Of course, I could also use it to record some tender moments.

main2.line: Are you cold, Commander? You can have my jacket.

main3.line: This party is so noisy, so rowdy. It's my responsibility to take watch over those sweet, innocent, little destroyer girls!

touch.line: Oh, don't worry about me. While everyone else sinks into the enrapturing atmosphere of the evening, someone has to stay sober and alert.

touch2.line: You want to dance with me? But, Commander, this... isn't this a little out of the ordinary?

unlock.line: One tends to let her guard down at a party like this, but worry not! Put the ball in my hands and let Ark Royal keep you safe!

detail.line: I can use this gun for ceremonial salutes, as well. I'll put her to good use at the banquet!

drop_descrip.line: Commander, Happy New Year. Oh no, I'm not going hunting. I'm patrolling the port during the New Year's celebrations. Naturally, I volunteered for the job.

home.line: To be able to watch over the destro– The fleet here, that's the best new year's gift anyone could give me.

login.line: The more peaceful and inviting the atmosphere, the more one wants to protect it. What do you think, Commander?

main1.line: Oh those destroyers in their Eastern dresses... Ah, I was just thinking how captivating it all is. These New Year's celebrations really are splendid!

main2.line: I have already committed everything important about the New Year's programming to memory. If you need anything, Commander, do let me know.

main3.line: Wherever there is trouble, I shall be there! Such is my solemn oath as guardian of the new year!

touch.line: Commander, would you like to personally carry out the gun salute? Mind the recoil.

touch2.line: My neckline is off? Oh, thank you... Oh my, no, it doesn't go like this, does it?!

unlock.line: Commander, Happy New Year. Oh no, I'm not going hunting. I'm patrolling the port during the New Year's celebrations. Naturally, I volunteered for the job.

detail.line: I've been here a few times before. They've never seated me near destroyers due to my reputation... But that's fine. I anticipated as much.

drop_descrip.line: This is the place, Commander. What are you going to order? Me, I think I'll have the same as you... Yeah, so what? I just felt like grabbing a coffee with you for once.

home.line: I'm relieved to see the destroyers are back safe and sound. Wish I could be with them on dangerous missions... Ah, forget I said that. I'm not going anywhere, you hear?

login.line: Oh, you're back. Well, I'm not actually surprised – I saw you coming.

main1.line: Mmm, the smell of coffee beans... Don't give me that "wasn't expecting to hear that" look! Even I can appreciate a good cup of coffee!

main2.line: Wh-where'd you get that camera?! Oh god, don't tell me it's all over for me... What? That's your personal camera? Oh, I see... Phew.

main3.line: I record everything that goes on in here. Let's just say it's for security reasons. That's the only reason, you hear?! My conscience is clean!

touch.line: Sod off! I'm not letting anyone have my destroyer footage!

touch2.line: Commander, please, save it for another time. I'm trying to hear what the destroyers are talking about.

unlock.line: This is the place, Commander. What are you going to order? Me, I think I'll have the same as you... Yeah, so what? I just felt like grabbing a coffee with you for once.

drop_descrip.line: I never thought a day would come when even I don such attire... Ahem. Your Excellency, I shall protect your happiness, as well as that of my destroyer sisters!

feeling5.line: Since we've grown so intimate, I assume it's now safe to tell you that I've become... r-r-rather intimate with the little destroyers too! Of course, you are still number one in my heart, Your Excellency!

home.line: Taking a leisure break, I assume? Then won't you accompany me to check on the little destroyers, Your Excellency?

mail.line: Allow me to read your letter aloud, Your Excellency.

main1.line: nil

main2.line: nil

main3.line: nil

main4.line: I brandish my rigging to protect this sacred moment in time!

touch.line: Interested in trying my home cooking? I've trained under the Royal Maids, and I'm 99% sure I can prepare a good meal!

unlock.line: I never thought a day would come when even I don such attire... Ahem. Your Excellency, I shall protect your happiness, as well as that of my destroyer sisters!

detail.line: Everyone has something dear they wouldn't give up for the world. Whatever yours may be, Commander, allow me to protect it with you!

drop_descrip.line: Ark Royal retrofitting complete! Now I can protect you, my friends, and of course, the little destroyers, to the very end!

home.line: I need to go check on the destroyers! I'll be right back, Commander!

login.line: At last you're here, Commander! Assign me any missions you need done!

main1.line: My Swordfish squadrons are in tip-top condition today! Likewise for my Fulmar squadrons!

main2.line: It is customarily destroyers that protect carriers, but there's nothing wrong with reversing that. Don't you agree?

main3.line: To protect what's close to you, you must always keep a watchful eye on the horizon. I trust you to do that, Commander.

touch.line: As long as I have your support, I can brave the battlefield without reserve!

touch2.line: Commander...? Excuse me, but what's gotten into you?!

unlock.line: Ark Royal retrofitting complete! Now I can protect you, my friends, and of course, the little destroyers, to the very end!

battle.line: Why cause unnecessary conflict?

detail.line: Could you help me pick up that handkerchief...? I'd lose my balance if I try to pick it up myself...

drop_descrip.line: Illustrious-class aircraft carrier – Illustrious, Hull Number 87!
