expedition.line: The light shall disperses the fog of darkness. Oh? The girls are back!

feeling1.line: Not even my light can reach the darkness within your heart?

feeling2.line: Commander, what do you find most important in a girl? Seriously, could you look me in the eyes when we're speaking?

feeling3.line: Commander, while I'm like this, I take a special liking towards suprise night attacks. Seriously, I didn't mean it like that, but is the Commander into things like that?

feeling4.line: Commander... do you want to try... a soft landing?

feeling5.line: No matter what you ask of me, Commander, I'll accept it... So, Commander, please tell me how you feel about me.

home.line: Feeling tired? Relax for a while. How about a massage?

hp_warning.line: Don't panic, Commander. I'm here!

login.line: Greetings, Commander. I've tidied up a bit here. What do you think?

lose.line: Let's retreat, lest I lose my life...

mail.line: Here's your mail, Commander! Should I open it for you?

main1.line: Have you seen where did I put my planes? Oh? Right in front of me? Sorry, something blocked my line of sight.

main2.line: Commander... can you feel my heartbeat through the palm of your hand?

main3.line: Commander, why are you always staring at me? Am I that pretty?

mission.line: Commander, it's no good to leave missions unfinished.

mission_complete.line: Don't forget to collect your rewards, Commander!

profile.line: Greetings, Commander. I am the armored aircraft carrier Illustrious. I may seem gentle, but I have quite the temper. I single-handedly bullied the Italian fleet during the raid at Taranto.

propose.line: Even though light should be shared equally among us all, it's fine for you to have a bit more. After all, I've received something important from the Commander as well.

touch.line: It's as though... I've received your recognition, Commander. I feel so relieved.

touch2.line: Seriously, Commander, you're like a little kid.

unlock.line: Greetings, Commander! Aircraft carrier Illustrious reporting in! I pray that you will bring love and peace to this world. May the light be with you.

upgrade.line: This way we can radiate our brilliance even further.

win_mvp.line: The light shines upon our land of triumph.

drop_descrip.line: Sun kissed skin, scrumptious snacks and delicious black tea. It’s as if both my mind and body have been rejuvenated— Commander, care to join me for some leisurely chit-chat?

main1.line: Commander, how does it taste? Today’s scones are Edinburgh’s signature dish.

main2.line: Commander, black tea is supposed to be sipped~ At the very least, pay attention not to spill your drink.

main3.line: Compared to the glaring sunset, I prefer this bright and gentle sunlight, what about you Commander?

touch2.line: Commander, you can’t act this way… at the tea party.

unlock.line: Sun kissed skin, scrumptious snacks and delicious black tea. It’s as if both my mind and body have been rejuvenated— Commander, care to join me for some leisurely chit-chat?

detail.line: I always feel my heart racing when I wear a different outfit in front of you, Commander~

drop_descrip.line: An invitation to the ball? Hehe, I would be honored to go... as long as you don't decline, Commander~

login.line: Good day, Commander. Are you ready to attend the ball?

main1.line: As dance partners, we should hold hands like this... Commander, can you feel my warmth?

main2.line: nil

main3.line: The orchestra has started playing~ Commander, would you like to dance with me?

touch.line: Did you want to talk, Commander? I'll always be here to listen to you~

touch2.line: Commander, being proud about doing something inappropriate doesn't make it any less inappropriate.

unlock.line: An invitation to the ball? Hehe, I would be honored to go... as long as you don't decline, Commander~

drop_descrip.line: This is my first time wearing such exotic fashion, hehe~. Commander, if you like how I look, how about showing me off a little~?

home.line: Good work out there, Commander. I've prepared some authentic incense for you. Why don't we close our eyes for a bit and uplift our spirits~

login.line: Greetings, Commander. Sorry for taking so long, but fixing my clothes took quite a bit of time... I'm not late, am I?

main1.line: I look like a princess from a foreign country? Hehe, you're making me blush...

main2.line: Commander, it is only because of you that we are able to experience so many different cultures. Being able to be at your side is my greatest pleasure~

main3.line: Commander, can I lean against you and rest for a while? This time, I want to listen to your heartbeat~

unlock.line: This is my first time wearing such exotic fashion, hehe~. Commander, if you like how I look, how about showing me off a little~?

detail.line: This festival may be a foreign custom to many of us here, but I think it's delightful we get to enjoy it nonetheless. And it's all thanks to your efforts, Commander. Hehe.

drop_descrip.line: It is my honour to get to wear another faction's garments. However... this traditional Dragon Empery dress feels rather tight around the chest area...

home.line: You're looking well. What good news have you brought Illustrious today?

login.line: How do you do, Commander? May this splendid holiday wash away all your worries.

main1.line: All these Iris flowers are not just for showy decoration, they make for some aromatherapy as well. Hehe.

main2.line: These Dragon Empery decorations all have a certain... unique charm to them, don't they?

main3.line: Commander, you absolutely must try the Empyreal cuisine the Royal Maids prepared. I've heard even Her Majesty praised the flavour. Hehehe.

touch.line: Is there something you would like to do with me?

touch2.line: Just this once, on this special day, I'll indulge your childishness~ Hehehe.

unlock.line: It is my honour to get to wear another faction's garments. However... this traditional Dragon Empery dress feels rather tight around the chest area...

battle.line: I devote this song to peace...

detail.line: No matter where you go, I want my melodies to follow you... As such, I've asked Formidable to record them. Just let her know whenever you'd like to hear one, Commander.

drop_descrip.line: A gentle melody for a peaceful celebration. Today, Commander, I offer this tune to you and the people of the port. May my melody please your ears♪

expedition.line: The commission team has returned, I see. Erm, then the next song I should play is...

headtouch.line: Heehee. Commander, is something wrong?

home.line: Commander, congratulations on another well-fought battle. You... would like me to play a tune for you? Heehee, then I hope this healing song meets your expectations.

login.line: Are you awake, Commander? I shall once again accompany you throughout your day.

lose.line: I know that kindness alone is not enough to win, and yet...

main1.line: Excuse me... Would you like to take a break? Haha, then I'll play a tune to help you relax—Oh. You'd prefer if we rested together...?

main2.line: So Indomitable didn't come, after all... No, I know that she and Formidable don't feel comfortable at these occasions. I told them they don't have to force themselves.

main3.line: Where did I learn to play the harp? Hmm... Heehee♪ Would you believe me if I self-studied, just like with singing?

touch.line: Please rest within this gentle melody, Commander.

touch2.line: Commander? ...Heehee, wait just a little longer.

unlock.line: A gentle melody for a peaceful celebration. Today, Commander, I offer this tune to you and the people of the port. May my melody please your ears♪

win_mvp.line: This tune, and this brilliance, will commemorate our triumphant return.

detail.line: I'll always be with you no matter where you go, Commander!

drop_descrip.line: The end of sorrow, the beginning of happiness, and the desire for eternity.

home.line: Tired, Commander? Why not take a rest? Eh, on my lap? It can't be helped I guess.

login.line: Greetings, Commander. Did you have a good rest?

main1.line: When will true peace come to these waters?

main2.line: Commander, my heart is beating so fast. Can you feel it?

main3.line: You're always number one in my heart, Commander.

touch.line: Just whisper in my ear if you have anything to say~! *giggles*

touch2.line: I'm not opposed to intimacy, every now and then~!

unlock.line: The end of sorrow, the beginning of happiness, and the desire for eternity.

battle.line: Sigh, all that cannons and gunpowder can do is make is war even uglier...

detail.line: In both love and war, one should be brave~ So, be brave, and if you need support, I shall be there!

drop_descrip.line: Illustrious-class aircraft carrier – Victorious.

expedition.line: Stop loafing around! I promised the commission team that I'd use my planes to photograph the moment they entered the port!

feeling1.line: I'm fed up~! I'll knock you out stone cold!

feeling2.line: You know about me from the Battle of Trafalgar? Umm, aren't you thinking of somebody else? Please, Commander~ Who you're thinking of is totally unrelated to me.

feeling3.line: My part in the pursuit of Bismarck and Operation Tungsten? I was just in the mood to help, I wasn't at all trying to earn any honours.

feeling4.line: I'm not in such a great mood... Are you free, Commander? Great! Then let me dress you in something fabulous! Seeing beautiful things makes me feel better, you see!

feeling5.line: I wonder what the future you will be like, Commander~ Of course, I already quite like the way you are right now. ...Goodness, you're blushing ear to ear. How utterly adorable you are~

home.line: To celebrate your victory, why not wear this olive wreath? I'm certain it'll suit you.

hp_warning.line: Oh dear, I've let my guard down.

login.line: The quiet sea, the cool sea breeze... Even in this moment, the birth of new, beautiful things blesses us.

lose.line: Remaining dignified even in defeat: this is how one should lose a battle!

mail.line: Handwritten letters are so much better than typed ones. Don't you think it's interesting how you can deduce the author's emotions based on their handwriting, Commander?

main1.line: War is ugly. And this olive wreath is the symbol of peace and beauty.

main2.line: Tirpitz, if you won't come out and have fun with me then I'll bomb your room again!

main3.line: I don't like violence, but using it is often the quickest solution to many problems...

mission.line: Only I have the privilege of being selfish. Don't even think about pushing missions onto me.

mission_complete.line: Fine, but just this one time! I won't help you with your missions a second time!

profile.line: I'm Victorious, Illustrious-class aircraft carrier number two! From the Atlantic Ocean to the Indian Ocean, and even the Pacific... where the ocean breeze goes, I follow!

propose.line: Don't think too hard about it. Just follow my lead at your own pace. ...Come on, this is a day to celebrate, don't be so nervous~ From this day on, you'd better work hard to always please me!

skill.line: O beautiful world, sing to me a song!

touch.line: When you feel down, I also do. Come on, you have someone as beautiful as me beside you, so why not be happy?

touch2.line: Y-you just did "that," didn't you?! B-by "that," I mean...

unlock.line: I am the one called Victorious, Aircraft Carrier of the Royal Navy. Yes, sing my name as you herald the coming of the symbol of victory. As long as I am here, our endeavours shall be smooth!

upgrade.line: Words are not needed to praise me! It's not people's words that touch the heart, it's their actions!

win_mvp.line: When my foes have been this thoroughly defeated... not even I, the symbol of victory, can truly be glad.

battle.line: Since you messed up the day off I was so looking forward to, I'm going to have to punish you!

detail.line: Do you need advice from the beautiful Victorious? Whether it's fashion tips or relationship trouble, you can ask me anything~!

drop_descrip.line: Hum~ dee dum♪~ I'm all dressed up, and my hair is perfect! Commander, I'm ready to go! Don't keep me waiting on a holiday!

home.line: Phew, is the battle finally over? As I said, let's go out and have some fun!

login.line: Way! Too! Slow! Commander, what does your schedule look like today? Hurry up and finish so you can take me shopping!

main1.line: Rest is for the sake of being able to work better! Therefore, set aside that work and come play with me~!

main2.line: Tirpitz, come and play with me~ I won't do anything to you~!

main3.line: Stay in tip-top condition so you can work hard and play hard! That's my motto~!

touch.line: This outfit is surprisingly warm... Even in this kind of weather, I don't feel cold at all!

unlock.line: Hum~ dee dum♪~ I'm all dressed up, and my hair is perfect! Commander, I'm ready to go! Don't keep me waiting on a holiday!

battle.line: Let's teach them a harsh lesson!

detail.line: A few words of advice from me: Invitations should be sent early, the venue should be grandiose, the programme should be discussed with everyone, and your attire should be flamboyant — just like mine~♪

drop_descrip.line: Are you preparing to hold an event for the port? Hehe, sounds like you could use my help. Don't worry, with someone as beautiful as me around, anything you do will surely be blessed with success!

home.line: As a celebration of victory, why not decorate your office with this red New Year poster? Isn't it about time for a change in atmosphere?

login.line: ♪~ What should we start off with today?

main1.line: Having trouble deciding? If I was in your position, I'd just circle everything, then figure out the specifics later.

main2.line: Unicorn, what kind of outfit would you like for next time? I'll make it for you~

main3.line: I'll have an eye out for you, so if you need me for anything, just call~

mission.line: If you have any questions about your mission, you can always ask me. I'll be glad to give you my advice.

mission_complete.line: I shall guide you until the rewards are secure in your hands— so, why don't you hurry up and do that?

touch.line: I added a slight twist to my outfit this time. Can you spot what it is~?

touch2.line: Y-you put your work down just to do something like this?!

unlock.line: Are you preparing to hold an event for the port? Hehe, sounds like you could use my help. Don't worry, with someone as beautiful as me around, anything you do will surely be blessed with success!

win_mvp.line: A beautiful victory — now this is elegance~ Hehe~♪

battle.line: This is a bit hard to move in... Though I hardly need to lift a finger to achieve victory.

detail.line: A beautiful lady deserves beautiful surroundings. Oh, I'm joking♪ However beautiful the surroundings, I need you to be complete, Commander.

drop_descrip.line: *Yaaawn*... Basking in the autumnal night's wind while gazing at the moon is the very definition of elegance, is it not? Heehee. Right now, I am not acting as a Lady of the Royal Navy, but rather as an "ojou" of the Sakura Empire elegantly enjoying her tea... Hyeep! Hot?!

expedition.line: For the souvenirs... Oh! It's our turn to get souvenirs from the commission team.

home.line: To celebrate this victory... Oh, I'd better eat my watermelon now! Heehee♪

login.line: *huff puff*... The tea feels warmer than it should be because it's getting chilly outside... Should I just switch to iced tea instead?

main1.line: It's nice to for once have someone else tailor my clothes for me... I think I'll read up a little on Sakuran clothing when I return home.

main2.line: Invite Indomitable to come along next time? It'd be a hard idea to sell, because she feels just wearing a kimono is a chore. Though, maybe she will agree if YOU invite her?

main3.line: *Yaaawn*... Get me some dangos, Commander♪ I've heard they're a must-eat when you're gazing at the moon.

mission.line: Give being selfish a try, Commander. For example, you could decide, "I'm not doing any missions day!"

mission_complete.line: So, you completed a mission. I'll let you have this piece as your reward.

touch.line: I'll have another bath when I come back♪ Would you like to join me, Commander?

touch2.line: H-how forthright... *blushes*

unlock.line: *Yaaawn*... Basking in the autumnal night's wind while gazing at the moon is the very definition of elegance, is it not? Heehee. Right now, I am not acting as a Lady of the Royal Navy, but rather as an "ojou" of the Sakura Empire elegantly enjoying her tea... Hyeep! Hot?!

win_mvp.line: Elegantly, gracefully, and beautifully – that's how I will beat you up!

battle.line: Ladies of the Royal Navy have many virtues, but mercy to enemies is not one of them!

detail.line: ?! ... Ah, I was just doing a bit of tidying up. Please, come right in.

drop_descrip.line: Illustrious-class aircraft carrier – Formidable.

expedition.line: Commander, the commission is complete. Shall we go to the harbour and greet the team?

feeling1.line: I'm afraid I've contracted a disease that gives me a dreadful headache when you're nearby. Would you mind going someplace else?

feeling2.line: Commander, is there something required of me? If you have a moment, why not join me for a cup of tea?

feeling3.line: My big sisters Illustrious and Victorious, like so many other ships you've gathered here, vouch for what a great commander you are. Now come, let this cake be a symbol of our new friendship. Take a bite, won't you?

feeling4.line: Truthfully, even though I'm a Lady of the Royal Navy, I sometimes want to have a bit of fun too. A side of me that I can't normally show except to people close to me like Illustrious... Doesn't that make you want to get closer with me?

feeling5.line: Commander, good day to you ♪ Shall we share another cake today? The maids have prepared a dreadfully sweet treat for us! Hmm...? I decided to let my hair down a bit more for you, Commander. Hehehe, I wonder if you'll find me just as captivating a Formidable as I was before?

home.line: Hmm~♪ Hmm~♪ C-Commander! I am p-pleased that you have returned!

hp_warning.line: You are all to redouble your efforts!

login.line: Commander, you're uncharacteristically punctual today.

lose.line: Why you miserab- Ahem! You are truly worthy adversaries, but next time victory will be mine!

mail.line: Commander, I'm leaving the mail right here. Please don't forget to review it.

main1.line: Commander, if you're not making any progress on your work, why not take a break? I've prepared tea and crumpets.

main2.line: No harm in taking a rest while the Commander's dist– Heavens! Victorious! G-good day. Do you have some business with the Commander?

main3.line: On the day of my launch, hmm... What a shame... though I didn't do it on purpose... Well! All water under the bridge now, isn't it?

mission.line: Commander, please don't forget to review the mission list I prepared for you.

mission_complete.line: Commander, please don't forget to review the list of mission rewards.

profile.line: I am Formidable, third ship of the Illustrious class. I operated in the Mediterranean for a time, crossing swords with a certain Veneto. Thereafter, I found myself all across the Seven Seas. While my service record is not particularly impressive, I feel I made a small contribution to the war effort.

propose.line: I, Formidable, hereby dedicate my life to the love of my Commander, through good times and bad, rich times and poor... This is quite long, so I'll omit the rest~ Now then, Commander, it's your turn. I know it's a long vow but you are not to skip a single word ♪

touch.line: I must admit, Tirpitz is quite the hard nut to crack.

touch2.line: Commander, is this the appropriate way for one to behave?

unlock.line: Good day, Commander. I am Formidable, third ship of the Illustrious class. Pleased to make your acquaintance.

upgrade.line: Formidable shall not disappoint.

win_mvp.line: What a magnificent victory! Let us press the advantage.

detail.line: Are you done warming up, Commander? Right then, into the water with you♪

drop_descrip.line: A Lady of the Royal Navy exudes elegance even when wearing her swimsuit. Huh...? Y-you're not seeing it? Really... that's weird...

home.line: I was simply waiting here for you. Don't think too much on it, Commander.

main1.line: Don't you find the atmosphere rather dreary...? What if we put on some rock... Er, something a little more stimulating?

main2.line: Hmm, that would be Hood. Even in a swimsuit she's the picture of nobility. Of course, that's nothing I'm not incapable of...

main3.line: Don't fret, Warspite. I wouldn't be able to swim without the Commander's help either!

touch.line: Huh? Illustrious?! Grr... You tricked me, Commander. Now you're in for it!

touch2.line: Okay, I see how it is. The salty sea air has gotten you all frisky, Commander. Hehehe...

unlock.line: A Lady of the Royal Navy exudes elegance even when wearing her swimsuit. Huh...? Y-you're not seeing it? Really... that's weird...

detail.line: What do you think of my outfit? I was only able to wear it with the help of Dido and the others...

drop_descrip.line: Yes, this will do wonderfully! Thank you, ladies. Phew... Getting dressed is so dreadfully time-consuming... Ahem! How silly of me. I must not whine in the presence of others.

home.line: Commander, are you still busy? I appreciate the work you've put in to prepare tonight's party.

login.line: Ahem. I see you are as punctual as ever. Thank you for attending the party.

main1.line: Sirius made a few errors at the beginning, but thanks to Dido, they were finally able to get me changed safely...

main2.line: Commander, your collar is all crooked. Here, come have a look in the mirror.

main3.line: I wonder what kind of dresses my sisters will wear... Ahem. I have no doubt that they will be splendrous indeed.

touch.line: You'd like a dance? Very well, Formidable shall be your partner.

touch2.line: Commander?! Th-the maids are still here!

unlock.line: Yes, this will do wonderfully! Thank you, ladies. Phew... Getting dressed is so dreadfully time-consuming... Ahem! How silly of me. I must not whine in the presence of others.

battle.line: Search and destroy!

detail.line: Expect great things for me, for I am Glorious! Of... of course! I'll be your glory forever!

drop_descrip.line: Courageous-class aircraft carrier – Glorious, Hull Number 77.

expedition.line: Commander, after your commissions are complete, you should... uh... hm... collect your rewards!

feeling1.line: Commander, you're making me feel uncomfortable.

feeling2.line: You can't be too careful in war... That being said...

feeling3.line: The kids in the sky have been working very hard. Can't they rest with me for a while? ... ... Commander, in times of war, is there no room for warmth?

feeling4.line: Commander, it's quite late. Why not rest a bit? I've made some black tea... Mail? It's in your tea, of course... *Zzzzz*

feeling5.line: Commander, if you are tired you can always rest in my embrace. Eh? Didn't you say yesterday that was the best way for you to recover?

home.line: You need to always keep your guard up, Commander.

hp_warning.line: Sm- smokescreen!

login.line: Today is a good day. Good weather puts you in a good mood to get work done!

lose.line: Next time, I'll scout out the enemy before we attack!

mail.line: I'll put the tea here... Mail? Ah, yes! There's new mail for you!

main1.line: Ardent and Acasta did the best they could, but I...

main2.line: I'll be more prudent in the future. Only then can I avoid meeting disaster again!

main3.line: Commander, glory and courage go hand in hand. However, Courage isn't the same thing as recklessness.

mission.line: Rest up and then finish your missions in one go!

mission_complete.line: I won't forget this time... *ahem* Commander, collect your rewards!

profile.line: I'm the Royal Navy's heavy crui... *ahem* ex-cruiser, now aircraft carrier, Glorious! I was just being careless when I was sunk by Scharnhorst and Gneisenau, not because they're better than me!

propose.line: If we face it together, there is nothing we can't overcome, Commander. Are you ready to accept your Glory?

skill.line: May victory and glory be ours... hopefully!

touch.line: Any guidance?

touch2.line: Commander, you're holding the glory of the Royal Navy

unlock.line: Royal Navy large crui– *ahem* aircraft carrier Glorious, reporting in! Commander, stand up straight, for your glory has arrived!

upgrade.line: Thank you, but power alone is not enough to win...

win_mvp.line: A glorious triumph!

detail.line: You're saying... that failures are just learning opportunities? Thanks, Commander, I do feel a lot better now.

drop_descrip.line: Being able to occasionally have a peaceful school life... is something I could get used to. Commander, look at the markings on this butterfly - aren't they lovely?

home.line: Commander, remember to not let your guard down on your way home.

login.line: When I put on this uniform, my mood seems to lighten up compared to usual...

main1.line: Commander, Ardent told me about some fascinating places. Want to go check them out after the operation is over?

main2.line: Commander, what would you consider an ideal school life?

main3.line: Even though I still have much to learn... I swear to bring you true glory one day, Commander.

touch2.line: Hey!! Commander, you scared the butterfly away...

unlock.line: Being able to occasionally have a peaceful school life... is something I could get used to. Commander, look at the markings on this butterfly - aren't they lovely?

detail.line: I shall strive to always be your beacon of glory, Commander! ...B-but, that doesn't sound convincing at all while I'm wearing this dress, does it...?

drop_descrip.line: I heard that the Sakura Empire's traditional attire was really hard to put on... but the Dragon's Empery's outfits are even more... Huh?! Commander, p-please look away!

feeling5.line: Commander, if you're tired, feel free to rest in my lap. Not only is it ideal for you to replenish your energy, but it is also my duty to provide you succor.

home.line: Commander, don't let your guard down... Huh? I'm the one who looks more vulnerable right now?!

login.line: Commander, the glory of... the glory of the Royal Navy will...! F-forget it!

lose.line: I must gain a better grasp of the situation on the battlefield.

mail.line: The hot water is over here... Oh, the mail! Um... I'm so sorry, I could've sworn the mail was right there...

main1.line: Are you talking about Ark Royal...? Do you not think that it is appropriate for us adults to monitor the growth of our Destroyer sisters, even off the battlefield?

main2.line: I bought this outfit because I thought it looked gorgeous, but... then this happened... Wh-what do you mean I can just leave it like this?

main3.line: The scent of plums wafting upon the evening breeze is so calming... Oh no, I still have to finish my secretary duties!

touch.line: You don't want me catching a cold, is it? I appreciate your concern.

touch2.line: B-but, the glory of the Royal Navy... (blushes)

unlock.line: I heard that the Sakura Empire's traditional attire was really hard to put on... but the Dragon's Empery's outfits are even more... Huh?! Commander, p-please look away!

win_mvp.line: To Glorious goes the victory! Commander, thank you for your support!

battle.line: In Her Majesty's name, I shall vanquish the wrongdoers.

detail.line: Tea parties with the Illustrious sisters are fun... until it's my turn to brew tea. Do you know how this suppressed yearning feels, Commander?

drop_descrip.line: Implacable-class aircraft carrier – Implacable.

expedition.line: The commission team has come back. You arriving on scene quickly to thank them is the best reward they could ask for.

feeling1.line: Surrender to darkness if you wish, but where should those who see you as their light go?

feeling2.line: My name suggests I'm vindictive: unwilling to offer mercy or compassion. In truth, I simply believe in my loyalties and convictions. As someone with great responsibility, surely you agree it's best not to fixate on the little things.

feeling3.line: What I desire is more than a mere symbol of victory – I crave someone who will answer my thoughts, sentiments, desires, and expectations. In other words... Indeed, if you do not know how to do so, why not try listening to my every word from now on? Heehee~♥

feeling4.line: Strong sentiments – be they faith or lust – do not necessarily lead to sin. There's no fun in being a slave to your conscience. If I were to offer myself to you, no strings attached whatsoever, gladly accepting is the right thing to do.

feeling5.line: Love arises from the human's primordial desire for companionship. Once someone beckons you, it only makes sense to cast aside your doubts, and indulge in that sweet, succulent euphoria... Heehee. Yet, you seem to have difficulty accepting this. Deny yourself all you want. Seeing how long you can fight your urges is fun in its own way.

headtouch.line: Excuse me? Do you want the same done to you? Heehee♥

home.line: Oh, welcome back... The stuff in your cup looks off? You mean the tea I brewed for you? Why?

hp_warning.line: Heehee. I'll get you for this.

login.line: May blessings find their way to you, Commander. Through who? Yes, who indeed.

lose.line: This defeat is like a stain on a white veil... Tiny, yet vexing.

mail.line: There's a letter for you. Remember, people have high hopes for you, and you're not one to disappoint.

main1.line: Why the long face? Concerned about your friends at sea, or simply stressed over work? Don't bottle up your feelings – let it all out.

main2.line: Tell me, among the four Illustrious sisters, whose tea is your favourite? ...Ah, you want to know mine? Hmm... I'd say it's the robust Assam.

main3.line: Showing neither mercy nor pity, never being appeased, stopping for nothing – that's what it means to be implacable. Perhaps you'd like to test me, Commander?

main4.line: Trouble concentrating, Commander? Let's get you back on track with a rousing distraction. Go on, take a look~♥

main5.line: Brain fog, you say? I may have just the cure – Royal Navy cuisine, enhanced with tongue-sizzling spice. Care for a taste?

mission.line: Are you tired of performing your neverending duty? Heehee. Here I thought you enjoyed it, considering how unswerving your commitment is.

mission_complete.line: A mission's been completed, has it? Heehee. May this bounty bring you joy one doesn't find every day.

profile.line: I was made as an improvement to the Illustrious class. Sadly, like many late arrivals to the war, my name is only an insignificant footnote in the chronicles of victory. Be that as it may... have you started thinking about how you're going to "use" me, Commander?

propose.line: You still deny yourself? Heehee, I understand. The shackles of inhibition are hard to break. Just close your eyes, relax, and empty your mind as I've taught you. I'm going to give you a mark of pleasure that will never go away♥

touch.line: People have many reasons for pursuing physical contact. What's yours, Commander?

touch2.line: Say, Commander... Are you just playing around, or are you being a sinful little thing? Heehee~♥

unlock.line: A most blessed meeting, Commander. I am Implacable, Royal Navy armoured carrier. There's no need to be in such a hurry to tell me about yourself. Your past, your future; your mind, and your body – heehee, shall all be revealed to me in due time. So, let's get to know each other, slowly but surely, little by little.

upgrade.line: A blessing, straight from you? Heehee. Allow me to give you my own blessings~

win_mvp.line: We should celebrate this triumph. After all, Lady Luck only lifts the hem of her dress to those who'll look♪

battle.line: It's time to see the results of your studies. Don't let me down♪

detail.line: Would you rather be a teacher or a pupil, Commander? Imagine being the pupil everyone looks up to, but you have naughty thoughts about your teacher... What a stimulating scenario that would be~♥

drop_descrip.line: Oh my... It seems I've shown you a rather unseemly side of me. Would you help me clean up here, Commander? You know... before any of the other girls find out. Heehee~♥

expedition.line: The supplies seem to have arrived. Hmm... Surely you don't plan on making poor little me fetch them?

headtouch.line: Oh my, are you trying to take advantage of me when I'm vulnerable~?

home.line: Commander, have you seen the tea I made earlier? No? Maybe a Royal Maid mistook it for something dubious and poured it down the sink...

login.line: You will surely have a blessed day. Why? Because I'm attracting all the bad luck♪

lose.line: Ugh... Sorry, I should've been more diligent.

main1.line: Gosh, I'm soaked... What a pain. Should I go get changed after all?

main2.line: As it turns out, the cafeteria's "ultra spicy" meal isn't very spicy at all. Maybe I'll make note of that on the next school survey.

main3.line: I assume you've already given some thought to how to deal with "eccentric" pupils? Heehee. I'm interested to see how you "educate" those who step out of line♥

touch.line: My button's come undone? Heehee, thanks. So, Commander... What are you really getting at here?

touch2.line: You've been waiting for this chance to make your move, haven't you? Heehee♥

unlock.line: Oh my... It seems I've shown you a rather unseemly side of me. Would you help me clean up here, Commander? You know... before any of the other girls find out. Heehee~♥

win_mvp.line: Nothing makes a teacher happier than seeing her pupils get good results♪

battle.line: Bad guys that disturb the peace will be dealt with, like this!

detail.line: Illustrious is steady in her steps!

drop_descrip.line: Illustrious-class aircraft carrier – Illustrious, Hull Number 87.

expedition.line: Everyone has come back from their commission. I'll have to hurry to bring the refreshments out to them!

feeling1.line: Were my prayers for love and peace not even enough to reach the person closest by my side...?

feeling2.line: Commander, for the sake of love and peace, you mustn't quarrel with others, all right?

feeling3.line: Ah, Commander, wait a second... Here, use my handkerchief... Ehehe, there are some cake crumbs stuck on the corner of your mouth~

feeling4.line: I heard that sitting down to talk with someone can help relieve your worries. Commander, if there's anything bothering you, I'd be glad to hear you out.

feeling5.line: Commander, you seem to not be feeling well... Are you tired from working too much? Hm... Ah, Commander, here... *pat pat* What a sweet child~ I heard this will help you not be tired... right? Ehehe, don't you feel better already?

home.line: Good job, Commander. Would you like Illustrious to give you a back massage?

hp_warning.line: For the sake of love and peace, I must not be scared!

login.line: Good day, Commander. I helped organize a little bit based upon how you had things before. How does everything look?

lose.line: For the sake of a world of love and peace, next time... you won't get away!

mail.line: Commander, there's mail for you. Umm, where did I put it... Oh, there it is! Here!

main1.line: My planes? They're right here. Ehehe, everyone's so well-behaved.

main2.line: Commander, I'll be there for you any time you're feeling lonely.

main3.line: What an even more wonderful world it would be if everyone could understand each other.

mission.line: Commander, are you worried about the unfinished missions? Is there anything I can help you with?

mission_complete.line: Mission complete! Thanks to your efforts, we'll be able to further spread the light of love and peace!

profile.line: I am the world's first armoured aircraft carrier, ehehe. One day, I'll do my best for the glory of the Royal Navy!

propose.line: S-so this is a promise ring... such an important thing, for me...? Ehehe, thank you so much! I may still be immature, but I will work hard to become the person of your dreams. No, I'm sure I'll be able to do it~♪

skill.line: Holy light, pummel our enemies in the name of love and peace!

touch.line: Commander's hand is so big... much bigger than mine...

touch2.line: Is this some sort of new game...?

unlock.line: Good day to you, Commander. I am Illustrious of the Royal Navy. We'll spread the holy light of love and peace all across the ocean, right~♪

upgrade.line: With this, I'll be able to further spread the light of love and peace...

win_mvp.line: We're one step closer to a world of love and peace.

battle.line: And now, a song of peace――

detail.line: One, two, one two, Ah... Thank you, Commander. I'm not sure why I just can't keep my balance...

drop_descrip.line: I am the newest addition to the Muse System, Illustrious. Through my songs, I shall spread the light of love and peace— Don't you think that's a wonderful thing?

expedition.line: It seems the commission team has returned. I wonder if they have the material for Victorious's clothes...?

feeling1.line: I do hope my song can return you to normal, Commander...

feeling2.line: To prepare for my idol activities, I borrowed some selections from Formidable's music collection. I find it rather noisy, but powerful, in a way that shakes my ears and in fact my whole body... Is that not right?

feeling3.line: At the Commander's request, I referenced a song by Comet and the girls. The gentle melody and soothing voices made me truly understand how idols can make people smile.

feeling4.line: I've been practicing with the other girls. I find I can sing gently, or energetically, and even smoothly... and it's all thanks to you, Commander. Hehehe.

feeling5.line: May my radiance touch you, Commander, and carry from the stage my song and dance of peace and love.

home.line: ♪~Ooh, welcome back, Commander. Can you give our new song a listen?

hp_warning.line: We can't let the light go out...!

login.line: Good day, Commander. What will we be practicing today?

lose.line: It seems the power of song alone was not enough...

mail.line: Reading fan letters is so delightful. What about your mail, Commander?

main1.line: What if we had a little tea party after our next practice?

main2.line: When one watches Tashkent and the girls dance so vivaciously, it makes one's heart pound. Hehehe.

main3.line: The theme of my costume is "the starry cosmos," isn't that romantic? How delightful. Hehe.

mission.line: Dido prepared this list of tasks for us. Do take a look at them, Commander.

mission_complete.line: Mission accomplisheed. Look over the rewards and... what's next on the schedule?

profile.line: I am the name ship of the Illustrious-class armored carriers... Oh, should I call myself "Idol Illustrious" now? I lack experience, but I will do what I must for the sake of peace.

propose.line: I can feel your support, and your hope for me... And I see your eyes full of happiness as you look upon the stage, and upon me, Commander. Hehehe.

skill.line: I will bring the light to you in song.

touch.line: Are we practicing for handshake events? All right, thank you very much, Commander.

touch2.line: Commander, do remember to maintain decorum when touching an idol.

unlock.line: I am the newest addition to the Muse System, Illustrious. Through my songs, I shall spread the light of love and peace— Don't you think that's a wonderful thing?

upgrade.line: It's not just about the shining image, it's also about conveying one's voice.

win_mvp.line: Our stage is brilliant and dazzling. Hehe~

battle.line: M-me, flagship? Sounds like a pain in the... Err, it's nothing! I'll do it!

detail.line: My Illustrious-class sisters are all outstanding. Should you run into any problems, they would be more than glad to help... Me? Um, well, I suppose I wouldn't mind offering you some advice...

drop_descrip.line: Illustrious-class aircraft carrier – Indomitable.

expedition.line: The commission team has returned. I shall await your return, so you should go greet them soon.

feeling1.line: *sigh*... I knew I shouldn't have gotten my hopes up...

feeling2.line: Commander, are you busy right now? Oh, wow... You look totally lost in your work... Ahem, well then, I suppose I should leave you to it.

feeling3.line: My hobbies? Hmm... Honestly, I haven't given it much thought up until this point. Let's see... what I like isn't so much finding things to do, but rather finding ways of not doing anything.

feeling4.line: You should learn how to relax every once in a while precisely because you're always working so hard. Learning how to clear your mind and let go isn't as easy as it sounds. But don't worry if you can't do it right away, Commander. Hehe, I'll show you exactly how to do it next time~

feeling5.line: Hehe, I see you're also slack– Err, I mean, nourishing your body and soul. That pleases me greatly. Alright, let's continue practicing the art of clearing our minds on a regular basis! As for where to conduct the lessons... how about in my room?

headtouch.line: Hyah?! Gosh, how rude of you to interrupt my daydreaming!

home.line: Commander, congratulations on a most excellent sortie. Of course I wasn't doing nothing. I was praying for your success with all my might.

hp_warning.line: If this drags on, I'll seriously be in trouble...

login.line: Good morning, Commander. Ehh? You're going to start working already? Why not get into the zone first by, say, opening up the window and basking in the breeze?

lose.line: Seems like I'll be in the docks for a good while... Well, don't threaten me with a good time, I suppose.

mail.line: New mail? Are we being told to go on vacation? Huh, what do you mean that's not possible?

main1.line: Oh my, an invitation to a tea party? ...Though, I think I'll pass. Keeping up airs is soooo tiring.

main2.line: Sleep revitalizes the body, daydreaming revitalizes the mind, and strolling refreshes one's mood. I'll have you know, all forms of relaxation serve a purpose, and are DEFINITELY not slacking off.

main3.line: *Yaaawn*... Can't get motivated right now... Huh, work? I've already finished all of it.

mission.line: New missions, huh... Should be no problem at all for someone as experienced as you, right?

mission_complete.line: That's another mission taken care of! Hehe, you're pretty good at this, Commander.

profile.line: As the fourth member of the Illustrious class, of course I'd be somewhat different from my sisters... Hey, I'm talking about hangar capacity here, not service history or repair length.

propose.line: An oath ceremony? That sounds like something that could turn into a real pain in the ass... I'm not saying there's anything wrong with you, Commander. I mean, a ceremony is just for show, so it shouldn't matter if... Wh-why are you making me say something so embarrassing anyway?! Anyway, we're done here, so I'll be heading back!

skill.line: Maybe I should start to get serious...

touch.line: Did you need something? Though, it'd be great if you didn't...

touch2.line: Double my vacation time, buy me some sweets, and I'll keep this a secret. Hehe, not such a bad deal, right?

unlock.line: I am the fourth ship of the Illustrious class, armored carrier Indomitable. *Yawn*... I seem to be getting a bit drowsy... Would you mind if we continued this later?

upgrade.line: I've gotten stronger, but... maybe I shouldn't let anyone know that.

win_mvp.line: I'm the MVP? I wonder if I shouldn't have tried so hard...

detail.line: Knowing how to brew tea is one of the essentials for the Royal Maids, no? Well, that's something even I can do. Though only once a day, no more than that.

drop_descrip.line: *Sigh*... I thought changing into maid attire would break up the monotony, but just getting into these clothes has tired me out... Oh, Commander? You came at a good time. Shall we slack off together?

home.line: The Royal Maids are always carrying all sorts of yummy snacks back and forth... I wonder how they can control themselves.

login.line: Welcome back, Master~♪ All righty, that's all my maid-motivation used up...

main1.line: What jobs am I capable of doing? Let's see... Oh, I can warm up the bed for you before you go to sleep?

main2.line: Now that I think about it, considering how capable you are as a commander, doing a maid's job should hardly be considered work, right? Maybe I'll have you take over the rest of my maid duties... Ahaha, well, it was worth a shot...

main3.line: I'm sure someone with THIS many maids would live an absolutely blessed lifestyle... Ugh, it's making me jealous the more I think about it...

touch.line: Are you trying to give me a massage? My shoulders were just starting to feel a bit stiff, so massage away~

touch2.line: I'm going to tell my sisters, you know?

unlock.line: *Sigh*... I thought changing into maid attire would break up the monotony, but just getting into these clothes has tired me out... Oh, Commander? You came at a good time. Shall we slack off together?

battle.line: Evildoers! I'm not scared of you!

detail.line: I hear that you're an evil taskmaster who punishes shipgirls when they don't do exactly as they're told... Hwah? That's not true? I dunno, you're kinda suspicious...

drop_descrip.line: Illustrious-class aircraft carrier – Formidable.

expedition.line: I heard there's tasty milk chocolate in the commission supplies... I-I didn't say anything. How about we go greet the commission team?

feeling1.line: I-I'm sorry! I-I'll listen better from now on, so don't get mad at me...

feeling2.line: Do you need something? Ladies of the Royal Navy are quite busy, I'll have you know—You say there's a party full of sweets? And we don't have to be all stuffy and formal? AND big sis Illustrious said I can go? Hmmm... O-okay, I'll go! I'll go!

feeling3.line: You want to know if ladies of the Royal Navy get tired? It's not so bad; we only have to constantly mind our manners and carry ourselves with elegance... Ugh, it's a hassle! I just wanna lie on the couch and eat candy—Ahem! F-forget you heard that!

feeling4.line: You're a lot like me, Commander. Every day is so full of things you must do, you're only able to do what you want to do in private. Even grown-ups have it rough... But it's okay! I will do whatever I can to help you! Not that I know exactly what that entails...

feeling5.line: I always thought you were a strict and scary person, so I acted cold to you... N-now I know that you're a good person and fun to be around! Commander, you're my best friend! Ehehe!

headtouch.line: Hawawah! D-do not rustle the hair of a proper lady!

home.line: While you were away, a few of the older girls visited. They all left messages, which I wrote down on this sheet of paper for you... (whispering) The Commander's really suspicious...

hp_warning.line: Don't hit me, don't hit me! Ah...

login.line: W-welcome back... I suppose I should start my etiquette training now, right? For example, practicing how I stand and sit...

lose.line: Th-the Commander's gonna lecture me... Urk...

mail.line: Commander, I brought your mail. I heard that's part of a secretary's job... I-is that right?

main1.line: I'm about to go to a tea party with the others... Commander, do you have a mirror? I want to make sure I'm looking sharp... No, you don't need to help me! I can do it myself.

main2.line: Little Bel, how much longer are you going to be? "It's only been three minutes"? You mean you've ALREADY taken three minutes!

main3.line: One of my Royal Maid sisters told me I'd turn "plump" if I ate too much cake. Does she think I believe these childish lies? ...C-Commander, that is a lie, right?!

mission.line: Missions? Can we eat candy if we finish them all?

mission_complete.line: Commander, the missions are all done now, so you should take a break. ...You're too busy? It must be hard being grown-up...

profile.line: Illustrious-class aircraft carrier number three, with a promising future of becoming an armoured carrier. Commander, I humbly request your aid in training me to become a proper lady... Huh? What kind of sweets do I like? Why are you asking me... I like all kinds of sweets!

propose.line: People tell me that you only give these to those you really care about... Does that mean I'm your best friend, too? Ehehe, I'm overjoyed! I'd better go tell big sis Illustrious about this!

touch.line: I-it is rude to touch a lady without her permission!

touch2.line: Just you wait! I'm gonna go tell big sis Illustrious aaall about all the bad things you did!

unlock.line: Hmm... Are you the so-called "Commander"? You don't look all that scary, but maybe this is what they call camouflage...? Hmm... I dunno... Oh! I'm the third Illustrious-class ship, Formidable. It's... a pleasure to meet you?

upgrade.line: Wooow. You can use airplanes for this, too?

win_mvp.line: Hmph. Do not underestimate Formidable!

battle.line: Please remain calm. The darkness will only make the stars shine brighter.

detail.line: I am not the harbinger of death... I am just..... guiding them after their times are up

drop_descrip.line: Erebus-class monitor – Erebus, Hull Number I02!

expedition.line: I'm not particularly interested in embarking on commissions... The other girls always say I see weird stuff. I suppose it can't be helped... Anyway, your girls are back!

feeling1.line: Commander, if you fall into darkness, know that it will be me hunting your soul...

feeling2.line: It was hard to take care of my sister at the beginning, but I got used to it... used to being alone? I'm just used to the fear of it.

feeling3.line: Whenever I'm afraid, all I have to do is think of my little sister. It gives me the strength to push on. Even though my sister can't be without me, I can't be without her either.

feeling4.line: I'm afraid no longer. Being next to you, I'm willing to become the darkness to your light; And if that light were to swallow me... No, even if I was to be devoured, that would be fine too.

feeling5.line: Where there's light, there's darkness. Wherever you are, I'll be near. This isn't fate but the law of this world... It's nothing, it's just something that I've wanted to say for a long time, if I ever found someone who I truly liked.

home.line: The silence after a battle is divine. Take your time and rest.

hp_warning.line: The darkness is with us.

login.line: Commander, I'm always here, awaiting for your summons...

lose.line: Even if you manage to defeat me, you'll never escape the infinite darkness.

mail.line: Letters are what connect humans. Hold them dear.

main1.line: Did you just have an out-of-body experience?

main2.line: I'll always protect my little sisters.

main3.line: I have to say, this warmth, I don't dislike it.

mission.line: You'll experience an eternity of restlessness if you die with incomplete missions.

mission_complete.line: Rewards are but worldly possessions. It makes no difference to me whether you collect them or not.

profile.line:
Erebus, my name, sounds surreal?
My predecessor was a ship which carried explorers to the North Pole and never returned... like a journey into the abyss.
Please pay more attention to my sisters!

propose.line: Shadows chase after light, and light embraces the shadows. I've heard of foolish lovers who erase each other, but who can judge another's love? Isn't that right, Commander?

touch.line: Allow me to channel forth the whispers of the dead...

touch2.line: ... ... uh... ... I'm sorry, it seems like I was having an out-of-body experience.

unlock.line: Commander, is that you? I'm Erebus. I followed your voice and have come from afar.

upgrade.line: The purer the darkness, the calmer my mind.

win_mvp.line: Allow me to harvest the souls of our enemies.

detail.line: I am still but a shadow. The only difference is, I've found a small, small thing to strive for.

drop_descrip.line: Those who embrace the shadows will find only an illusory happiness... But for me, that much is sufficient.

home.line: Commander, would you like some sweets to replenish your energy?

main1.line: Commander, there's no need to be reserved. I still have a lot of chocolate.

main2.line: nil

main3.line: Commander, just being able to watch you like this, and give you chocolate, is enough to make me happy.

touch.line: I'm here, as always.

touch2.line: Were you able to touch happiness, Commander?

unlock.line: Those who embrace the shadows will find only an illusory happiness... But for me, that much is sufficient.

win_mvp.line: No matter how long the night, the dawn will come again...

detail.line: Terror really wanted to go to the Halloween party with me, but... I...

drop_descrip.line: "I am the witch of Hallow's Eve, here to guide your soul into the ever darkness"... that's what the concept of the Halloween witch is about, right?

feeling5.line: Forming a contract with a witch will allow one of your wishes to come true. In return, your souls will forever be bound, unable to separate from one another... Commander, tell me... what is your wish?

home.line: I can hear the wailing of souls passing through the ever darkness... You want to know what they're saying...?

login.line: The Halloween event has started. But, I'm supposed to wait here until it's my time to come out.

main1.line: Legend has it that real monsters come out on Hallow's Eve... Shall we search for them?

main2.line: These festivities have diluted the ever darkness with noise and light... but it's not such a bad thing.

main3.line: T-trick or treat...? Oh, right, you can have this special bewitched candy.

touch2.line: Commander, have you been possessed by a perverted ghost?

unlock.line: "I am the witch of Hallow's Eve, here to guide your soul into the ever darkness"... that's what the concept of the Halloween witch is about, right?

battle.line: Even Terror... is getting terrified...

detail.line: Your eyes look just like those weirdo' eyes, Commander...

drop_descrip.line: Erebus-class monitor – Terror, Hull Number I03!

expedition.line: Commander, commissions are finished... You know, I lost my hand during a commission. It took everyone quite some time to help me find it...

feeling1.line: Terror is terrified of you, Commander.

feeling2.line: Aren't you afraid of me, Commander? My body feels cold... I am always depressed... I always feel.... like a corpse.

feeling3.line: I remember my sister being with me, ever since the very first time I opened my eyes... She's always been there for me. She's my only family...

feeling4.line: It's warm next to my sister, it's warm next to the Commander too... I feel like I just got a new family member... I'm so happy...

feeling5.line: Commander... please touch my heart... It has never beaten this fast... it has never been this hot... This is all... because of you, Commander...

home.line: Rub my head, Commander...

hp_warning.line: Terror... is getting terrified...

login.line: Commander... I've been wanting to talk... to you... about...

lose.line: *Cries*... I'll try to hold out until you tow me back to port, Commander...

mail.line: A letter... Would anyone write a letter to me?

main1.line: Commander, could you put away those peas? And the lawnmower……

main2.line: Is is that weird for me to have a 'heart'?

main3.line: Commander……are you……a wind player?

mission.line: How about some missions for exercise...? Otherwise my knee may break again...

mission_complete.line: *coo, coo*~! Commander, I've got your rewards...

profile.line:
I'm the second ship of the Erebus-class monitors.
The Abercrombie-class ships are no match for me and my sister... We spent a lot of time in the Dardanelles strait. Bombardment missions... piece of cake.

propose.line: Times like these, should I laugh, or should I cry? I'm... I'm not really sure... but Terror knows... I know I've never been this happy before...

touch.line: Can you feel... my warmth?

touch2.line: *Stares...*

unlock.line: Monitor ship... Terror... Abercrombie-class ships are no match for me and my sister... We spent a lot of time in the Dardanelles strait. Bombardment missions... piece of cake.

upgrade.line: I feel as if my body... is much more agile now.

win_mvp.line: Commander, I... I worked really hard. I didn't cause you any trouble, did I?

detail.line: "From the depths of Sheol, I emerge from eternal slumber to claim your soul" ... This line sounds like something my sister would say.

drop_descrip.line: I have to dress up as a ghost for Halloween, but I'm not very good at making complicated costumes... Is something like this okay?

home.line: Trick-or-treating? I'm a little excited...

login.line: Boo! Scaring people... it's done like this, right?

main1.line: I wanted to spend some time with my sister, but she doesn't seem to be interested in Halloween...

main2.line: Today, everyone will be dressed up as monsters and witches, so I will fit in with them...

main3.line: Children will ask for candy from adults... but Terror is no longer a child- Eh? Candy, for me? Thank you...

touch.line: Commander's hand... is nice and warm...

touch2.line: If you keep touching, the bandages are going to come lose...

unlock.line: I have to dress up as a ghost for Halloween, but I'm not very good at making complicated costumes... Is something like this okay?

battle.line: Tee hee, what should I knock out first? Their bow? Turret? Engine?

detail.line: It's so much fun to fire my gun~!

drop_descrip.line: Roberts-class monitor – Abercrombie.

expedition.line: Target spotted, calculating trajectory... Bugger, it's just the commission team. Laaaame...

feeling1.line: Tee hee~ Commander, did you know you can use the Mark I as a blunt weapon? I'll show you! (Pow!)

feeling2.line: Tee hee~ How do you like my habanero curry? – Huh...? W-wait, Nelson! I didn't know that one was yours! – Don't hurt meeee!

feeling3.line: Oh, Commander~! Com-man-der! Coooommaaaandeeeer! What? It was nothing. I just wanted to see your face~ Tee hee~

feeling4.line: Feeling stressed out? Then try out my Mark I! Fire a shot for every worry you have to make them disappear with a bang! You'll get hooked on it!

feeling5.line: I wonder if I can combine you and my Mark I... Commander, for the next sortie, how about you sit atop it while issuing commands?

home.line: Hey, Commander~ Brought back anything gander-worthy? Like a piece of wreckage or parts from a crashed aircraft or something?

hp_warning.line: Whuaaah! My armour!

login.line: That loud bang? Tee hee~ You were gone for so long I was getting bored, so I let a shot loose~

lose.line: Tsk. Lame.

mail.line: Oh, have I hidden your mail~? Want it back? Then get some snacks and bar-ter for it! Bar-ter for it!

main1.line: My hobby's collecting shell casings~! Hey, don't you think shell casings are super cool?

main2.line: Top of the mornin', granny Hood!

main3.line: Whuaah! Hey, Wales! Granny Hood is giving me creepy looks~!

mission.line: Commander, there are new missions! Tee hee~ What'll we be sinking this time? I can't wait~

mission_complete.line: Commander, is the next mission gonna be as fun as the last one?

profile.line: I'm the Monitor Abercrombie. My sister and I used to help with shore bombardment around the Mediterranean Sea. Tee hee~ It's way more fun to shoot stationary targets~

propose.line: W-wow! Thanks! I'll never take it off! I-in exchange, take my Mark I! Roberts told me you're supposed to give your partner your dearest possession at times like these!

skill.line: Be torn to shreds by my shells!

touch.line: Commander, want some crisps? Here you go! ... Roberts, come here! I found the crook who ate your crisps!

touch2.line: Whuaaah!

unlock.line: Take THIS! – Oh, Commander? Tee hee~ I'm Abercrombie! Lovely weather today, eh~?

upgrade.line: Tee hee~ I might be loading a teensy bit too much gunpowder~

win_mvp.line: Kaboom! Ahaha~ You can't beat the Mark I!

detail.line: Trick or treat! Give me candy, or you'll taste one of my pranks! Although, even if you give me some... well, you'll see for yourself! Tee hee~

drop_descrip.line: Kabooom! You thought it was a pumpkin, but it was me, Abercrombie, with my Mark I! Commander, did I scare you senseless? Muahaha!

home.line: I wonder how people would react if they got my custom-made horseradish candy~ Tee hee~!

login.line: Tee hee~ Who knows where I've planted my pumpkin surprise~

main1.line: Take a gander at my Halloween Mark I! Looks cracking, doesn't it!

main2.line: Nelson's wearing a Halloween costume?! Really?! Let me have a look at it, Commander!

main3.line: If only we had more holidays where you could cause mischief and get away with it scot-free~

touch.line: Shake hands with my Halloween Mark I! Come on, Mark I, show the Commander your special trick~!

touch2.line: Taste the retribution of my Mark I! (Pow!)

unlock.line: Kabooom! You thought it was a pumpkin, but it was me, Abercrombie, with my Mark I! Commander, did I scare you senseless? Muahaha!

detail.line: Carrot juice has just the perfect consistency. You can put anything you like in the glass, and nobody'll know!

drop_descrip.line: Now for a ghost pepper while nobody's looking... Tee hee! Perfect! I wonder who'll be the lucky one to sip– C-Commander?! You didn't see anything suspicious... Right? Tee hee~

home.line: Bring our customers their drinks, Manjuus! And be careful so you don't drop them!

login.line: ello there! How about a glass of delicious and nutritious carrot juice? ...Wait, stop, not that one! THIS one's for you! Phew... Disaster averted...

main1.line: Shaking the bottle? Pfft, that's the oldest trick in the book. I'll teach you a newer one, Commander!

main2.line: Oh bollocks! It's Nelson! Quick, Commander, I need a place to hide!

main3.line: You're silly, Erebus. All I asked for was a little inspiration, not the full recipe for some kind of magic potion!

touch.line: Bottoms up, like adults do! Drink up, Mark I!

unlock.line: Now for a ghost pepper while nobody's looking... Tee hee! Perfect! I wonder who'll be the lucky one to sip– C-Commander?! You didn't see anything suspicious... Right? Tee hee~

detail.line: Huh? You think I'm cute? Aww! I did everything I could to give off a different vibe, so I wanted you to call me gorgeous or fashionable! Th-though I do still appreciate the compliment.

drop_descrip.line: Tadah! I've got a banquet dress! Heehee~ I decided to go with something refined and voguish this time, as opposed to cute! I mean, it's a dress fit for a banquet, so I think it makes me look pretty grown-up.

expedition.line: Commander, the girls who went on commission are back! Let's take them to the party with us!

headtouch.line: Whoa whoa! No rustling my hair! You're gonna mess it up!

home.line: Good work today, Commander! Let's take a little break before we go back to the party. I'll bring you a snack... I mean, hors d'oeuvres!

login.line: Welcome back, Commander! Are you ready to dance with me?

lose.line: Ack... Maybe I'm not ready for this dress after all...?

main1.line: Let's see, the dance moves here... Left, right, and then... Huh? Is it left next, or was it right...? Whoa, whoa...?!

main2.line: Commander, umm, let's review a little more before the performance! Otherwise, I'm gonna step on your feet during the dance...

main3.line: C-Commander, I know I'm cute—I mean, pretty—in this dress, but it's embarrassing when you stare so much...

touch.line: Are you tired already, Commander? But we're about to dance...

touch2.line: C-Commander, we're at a party! Be a little more refined...!

unlock.line: Tadah! I've got a banquet dress! Heehee~ I decided to go with something refined and voguish this time, as opposed to cute! I mean, it's a dress fit for a banquet, so I think it makes me look pretty grown-up.

detail.line: I gotta gather my courage and invite big brother to the party today... Ah? B-big brother... Did you hear that? Oh...

drop_descrip.line: Big brother...? I was just practicing my trumpet, if you were wondering... Umm, what do you think? I hope you like my trumpeting...

home.line: No matter how busy you are, I'll always be waiting here for you.

login.line: Big brother... Did you come to listen to me practice? It makes me a little nervous, but I'm glad you're interested...

main1.line: Concerts are hard... I need to practice more. But if you're there, I'm sure it'll go well...

main2.line: It's a good thing Yuni can hold the sheet music... Hm? You'll help too, big brother? I dunno if I can practice while I look at your face...

main3.line: Big brother... What if we slacked off together? Indomitable told me about it. She says bad girls do it, heheh...

touch.line: Do you mind if I... ask you for something a little greedy...?

touch2.line: Big brother... W-we're all alone right now... ///

unlock.line: Big brother...? I was just practicing my trumpet, if you were wondering... Umm, what do you think? I hope you like my trumpeting...

battle.line: So this is a battlefield? Ahaha... how interesting.

detail.line: Want to know about this? It's called a trident. Don't you think it's cool?

drop_descrip.line: Light cruiser – Neptune.

expedition.line: Commander, I shall temporarily grant you permission to leave my side so that you may greet the girls who have returned from commissions.

feeling1.line: Commander, did you know how high my expectations were for you at first? What a shame, for you shall now never know.

feeling2.line: Commander, I have a question. If in the future you were given the option to sacrifice me for world peace, what would you choose?

feeling3.line: The correct answer is - to do everything in your power to prevent that situation from occurring in the first place. Heehee~ Commander, if you wish to woo me, you will have to use your brain more~

feeling4.line: Having that said, I believe that a truly intelligent person knows how to rely on others when appropriate. Ah, that's right~ Commander, would you feed me some cake?

feeling5.line: Commander, have you planned where we're going to go for our date? If you have picked out an outfit for me, why don't you help me put it on? Eh~? "Why don't I wear it myself?" Silly, that's what love is all about~ L.O.V.E~♡

home.line: You've done well to return home safe and sound.

hp_warning.line: I seem to have underestimated the battlefield...

login.line: That simply will not do, Commander, keeping me waiting all this time~

lose.line: I shall not repeat this mistake again.

mail.line: Commander, there's mail for you. Hmm? I didn't do anything in particular~

main1.line: Unlike the other girls, this is my "maiden voyage" onto the battlefield. I wish to confirm for myself what this oft-touted "difference in experience" looks like.

main2.line: Commander, if you get on your knees and beg, "Please, Mistress Neptune," perhaps there would be a chance for something nice to happen?

main3.line: Commander, if you wish to taste my freshly-baked cake, then please first brew your finest tea~

mission.line: Commander, I see you have allowed your unfinished missions to pile up. I am not very fond of lazy people, you know?

mission_complete.line: Commander, what do you hope to gain through not collecting the mission rewards? Perchance you are waiting for me to remind you?

profile.line: My background? Ehehe, I am the large light cruiser who only existed on paper, Neptune, so it is understandable that you have never heard of me before. Though I have yet to step onto the battlefield, my abilities are top notch... allow me to prove that to you in live combat~

propose.line: "You are my world?" Did you think you could fool me with such flattery? Ehehe... well, I suppose there's a chance that I would let you fool me~ But first, you would have to repeat it ten times, nay, a hundred times~

skill.line: I have no intention of getting friendly with the enemy~

touch.line: You would like to challenge me to a game? Very well. Do not expect me to hold back though, hehe~♪

touch2.line: That simply will not do, Commander. You cannot seek to gain my attention that way.

unlock.line: Who am I? I am the Royal Navy's large light cruiser, Neptune. I shall see to it that you will never forget my name~♪ Yes, pleased to be of service~♪

upgrade.line: As expected!

win_mvp.line: Ehehe~ As a special service, I shall allow you to praise me more~♪

battle.line: How uncouth, spoiling the mood like this...

detail.line: My daily routine is nothing but missions and sorties, so it’s nice to be able to get dressed up and have a good time. Hehe~

drop_descrip.line: Hehe~ I usually let the other girls have all the glory, but even I must sometimes give you something to remember me by. Merry Christmas, Commander~

login.line: Commander, Merry Christmas~ ♪

mail.line: Commander, why don’t you take a guess which box I put your mail into~?

main1.line: Commander, if you kneel in front of me and beg, you might just get something very nice in return~ Hehe~

main2.line: Commander, did you already forget? If you want a present from me, you must first give me something that I’d be satisfied with~

main3.line: Since joining the fleet, I’ve made a lot of friends. Especially Shropshire — she’s both a good friend and a good rival.

touch.line: Commander, would you help me out with these presents that I prepared for Seattle’s party? They’re going to be for everyone~

unlock.line: Hehe~ I usually let the other girls have all the glory, but even I must sometimes give you something to remember me by. Merry Christmas, Commander~

win_mvp.line: That should wrap things up. Commander, let’s continue our party~

battle.line: You, going against the Commander? That simply won't do~♪

detail.line: Commander, I know you actually attend all sorts of parties with the Royal Maids. Buuut, heehee~ Don't you think I'm a cut above those girls when it comes to these kinds of situations?

drop_descrip.line: Welcome to our celebration, Commander. At this breathtaking venue, I, Neptune, shall be the one to show you around, rather than the Royal Maids. Heehee~♪

home.line: Welcome back. Now then, please take my hand once more. Oh... Is the trident getting in the way?

login.line: That simply won't do, Commander. As you are the guest of honor, we cannot have you arriving late. You've kept me waiting, you know. Heehee♪

lose.line: Was I too preoccupied with putting on airs...?

main1.line: Allowing some other girl to attend you instead of choosing me? That simply won't do, Commander... Just kidding♪ I'll be waiting right here, so make sure you say hello to everyone~

main2.line: Commander, have you forgotten the magic words when you want me to take you somewhere? "Please, Mistress Neptune." Remember?

main3.line: Charybdis' demeanor seems rather out of place compared to the rest of the Royal Maids... Say, Commander, how would you like it if I tried to act extra high-and-mighty to get you to do all sorts of stuff for me?

touch.line: That's right, the party venue is right in front of you. Heehee~♪

touch2.line: That simply won't do, Commander. Everything has a proper time and place, you know?

unlock.line: Welcome to our celebration, Commander. At this breathtaking venue, I, Neptune, shall be the one to show you around, rather than the Royal Maids. Heehee~♪

win_mvp.line: You're welcome~♪ It was only possible because of you, Commander.

battle.line: Depend on me! I will make sure this fleet returns home without as much as a scratch!

detail.line: You are the one and only being who matters to me... Until I met you, there was nary a single soul who believed in me.

drop_descrip.line: Battleship – Monarch.

expedition.line: I wonder what efforts it took to materialise me... Hmph, regardless, I will see to it they are repaid in double.

feeling1.line: Are you saying that I am inferior to them?!

feeling2.line: I only survived in that dark world by believing that I am excellence itself, and thus irreplaceable...

feeling3.line: Love needs no repayment. No matter how much the Royal Family neglects me, my loyalty to them is unwavering.

feeling4.line: So, they can still laugh together... Perhaps I wasn't discarded for nought, then... I have never felt this way before.

feeling5.line: Commander, to me, you are the most special, most dear person in existence. You always have, and always will be...

home.line: That was a marvellous welcome. Hmph, were I the only one returning, would anyone welcome me at all...?

hp_warning.line: If Wales were me, she would probably have sunk long ago.

login.line: Splendid; you're back. I, Monarch, am superior to the likes of Wales and York. Wouldn't you agree, Commander?

lose.line: Am I... being discarded yet again?

mail.line: You've received mail regarding the war. You would do best to check it.

main1.line: Wales and York... I despise them for bereaving me of my existence, but I cannot resent them for succeeding me.

main2.line: A younger sister? If I have one, her name would be... Prince of Wales... That has a rather nice ring to it.

main3.line: I will make the world understand how foolish it was not to choose me.

mission.line: Let me handle this mission. I shall prove my excellence!

mission_complete.line: For as long as I exist, it isn't over. I am excellence itself, therefore I must exist.

profile.line: I am the battleship named Monarch, one of the rejected King George V-class designs. Hmph, though I was once forgotten, now I live and breathe...

propose.line: Even if the world no longer needs me, you will always need me. That is more than enough for me... Hahah, perhaps I was materialised with the sole purpose of meeting you. Even if so... I am happy.

skill.line: Not even the Queen's orders can subdue me!

touch.line: Is my presence needed, Commander?

touch2.line: Do not fall victim to those degenerate habits of theirs.

unlock.line: We meet for the first time. I am the battleship Monarch. Hmph, once I was discarded, but now I am needed; how ironic... Is this how low the Royal Navy has sunk?

upgrade.line: Hmph, sure enough, I am the most excellent of the King George V class.

win_mvp.line: Heed my words: depend on me! I will always win!

battle.line: Allow me to demonstrate the elegance with which a lady of the Royal Navy comports herself.

detail.line: Stand up straight and puff out your chest, Commander. You're the only one I deign to— You're not sure where to look? Well, why not look me in the eyes then?

drop_descrip.line: Hmph. One's outfit is merely superficial. True nobility must come from within. Don't you agree, Commander?

login.line: Don't just stand there gawking, Commander. There remains much to be done today.

main1.line: nil

main2.line: Shall I teach you the Royal Navy's courtly dances?

main3.line: Such splendid dress is normally reserved for special occasions. But for me, every day I exist is a day to be celebrated.

touch.line: You like this dress, do you? Hmph, I see you've learned the art of empty flattery from Wales. But nonetheless... thank you...

touch2.line: I admire your bravery. Now would you rather I stab or trample you? Or would you prefer to taste a volley from my guns?

unlock.line: Hmph. One's outfit is merely superficial. True nobility must come from within. Don't you agree, Commander?

detail.line: "Paint our jubilant memories of this festival into history"? Hmph, she's as grandiloquent as ever, isn't she?

drop_descrip.line: So, an Eastern outfit this time... Hmph. My nobility is evident regardless of what I wear. However, since you prepared this outfit especially for me, it would be unbecoming of me to not express my gratitude. Thank you.

login.line: This festival comes but once a year. I shan't let you waste it working yourself to death. Come, let me handle that. The fleet will survive you taking a break.

main1.line: Tsk, Wales, must you always pester me with this Dragon Empery chinoiserie? I'll learn about their customs myself, without you.

main2.line: A New Year's wish? Naturally, I wish to prove you were right to choose me. That isn't going to change.

main3.line: Though I am a proud lady of the Royal Navy, I find myself deeply moved to have this chance to experience a festival from an exotic culture.

touch.line: You desire my company? You should have said so.

touch2.line: Have you been afflicted with Wales's vile proclivities? Commander?

unlock.line: So, an Eastern outfit this time... Hmph. My nobility is evident regardless of what I wear. However, since you prepared this outfit especially for me, it would be unbecoming of me to not express my gratitude. Thank you.

battle.line: What'll it be for dinner today? A plate of torpedoes, or a bowl of cannonfire?

detail.line: The reason I adore you is because animals take the first person they see to be their lover... Uhh, I mean, their parent! Not that that's got to do with anything! You're my owner just because, and I love you just because! It's as simple as that!

drop_descrip.line: Heavy cruiser – Cheshire.

expedition.line: A commission team's back! Let's head over there and give 'em something to play with!

feeling1.line: Hrmph... Why'd the first love of my life have to be such a disappointment?

feeling2.line: Where've you been, Owner? If you went to do fun stuff without inviting me then I'm gonna be a pouty tabby!

feeling3.line: Hey, Owner! I was playing with this Sakura Empire girl earlier, and I got to touch her cat ears! REAL cat ears! Aren't you jealous? ...What? You did that ages ago? Hrmph, well there goes my brief moment of triumph!

feeling4.line: Is there a chance you'll get fed up with my displays of affection, Owner? If so, I need to double down to make sure that never happens! Lemme give you a hug~♡

feeling5.line: If it weren't for you, I'd never have materialized in this incredible world, never made so many adorable friends, and worst of all, I never would have gotten to experience being in love with you, Owner! You're just perfect, y'know that~? Cuddly wuddly~ I love you so, so much~♡

headtouch.line: My kitty ears are a detachable hair accessory! You try 'em on too, Owner! Just for a quick moment, please, c'mon!

home.line: Weeelcome back, Owner! Are you okay? Gave the baddies a good beating? Didn't develop a crush on anyone else? Alrighty, then everything's all good!

hp_warning.line: Meowch! It hurts, but I'm not about to let my owner down!

login.line: Owneeeeer! Glomp! Squeeze! Cuddle! Sniff! What, I'm "overenthusiastic?" Well, that's just how excited I get when I see you, Owner~♡

lose.line: Why don't we slink away before they notice?

mail.line: The mail's here! I wanna see what's inside! Pretty pleaseeee?

main1.line: Hey, Owner, know any funny stories about the Royal Navy? Or any other faction, that's fine! I wanna learn stuff!

main2.line: I'm not a cat, okay? I might be as cuddly as a kitten, but I'm not an actual cat!

main3.line: Oh, Master, would you care for some tea~? Hehehe, that was my Royal Maid impression! How was it, Owner?

mission.line: There's no mission we can't accomplish with our combined pawers, Owner!

mission_complete.line: Mission complete! Don't you think these tasks are a little too easy for us?

profile.line: I'm Cheshire, a heavy cruiser from the Royal Navy! Until I met you, I was just a stray in the sea of people's imagination! Which is to say, both my body and soul belong to you, Owner! Squeeeze~♡

propose.line: Now that you've made it clear how precious I am to you, I need to respond by saying, "I love you, Owner!" a hundred times or more! Starting right now! Stay right where you are until I'm finished! Here we go! I love you, Owner!!!

touch.line: Ahah~♡ What is it, Owner? Come on, I know you want something just from looking at your face~

touch2.line: No more surprise touchies! At least tell me when you're gonna do it!
