unlock.line: Meeeoooow! I haven't slept like that in forever! Hrm? Are you the one who woke me from my sleep? Woohoo, that makes you my owner! "Why?" Because I've totally fallen for you, duh!

upgrade.line: Thank you, Owner!

win_mvp.line: We won! See that, Owner? We wooooon! Meoww~!

detail.line: Don't think I didn't notice you earlier, Owner! You left to play with someone while I wasn't looking, didn't you? Not that I mind, really! But you could've at least let me known first!

drop_descrip.line: Cheer up, Owner! Jeez, why are you so bummed out when we're at the beach... Because it's just a normal playdate instead of a romantic date? What's the difference anyway? C'mon, let's go head down to where the others are~!

home.line: Wow, there are so many cuties here besides me! But, heheh, I'm the top cat when it comes to being cute and sexy! Isn't that right, Owner?

login.line: Are you feeling good, Owner? Yay, then it's time to start our seaside date!

main1.line: There's only one reclining chair? So what~ We'll just share it, silly Owner~ I'm pawsitively fine with doing it that way♡

main2.line: I'm all thirsty! Time to chuggy-chug a nice, cool drink! ...Mmhh! I feel like a new person!

main3.line: Fishing? Nuh-uh, I don't wanna. Time spent fishing could be time spent playing games with you, Owner!

touch.line: Need to lie down, Owner? Okey-dokey! Which headrest do you want: my thighs, or my soft tummy? Hehehe♡

unlock.line: Cheer up, Owner! Jeez, why are you so bummed out when we're at the beach... Because it's just a normal playdate instead of a romantic date? What's the difference anyway? C'mon, let's go head down to where the others are~!

detail.line: Welcome, welcome, Owner~ If you've got any requests, don't be shy, don't hesitate, I'll try my best and sing a song that's really great~♡

drop_descrip.line: Welcome, welcome, Owner~ If you've got any requests, don't be shy, don't hesitate, I'll try my best and sing a song that's really great~♡

expedition.line: The girls just came back from that commission! I wonder if Drake was with them?

home.line: Hey Owner, what do you think of everyone's dresses? Are there any outfits you want to see me in? ...I look gorgeous in my current one? Squeeee! I love you, Owneeeeer~♡

login.line: Owneeeeeer! ...Oopsies, that was improper of me! I'm dressed like a refined Dragon Empery lady, so I need to act the part!

main1.line: My beloved Owner~♡ Squeeze, cuddle, sniiiiff~ I love being with you so much~♡

main2.line: Sexy cleavage, trendy fashion, and obligatory kitty ears: the perfect package of cuteness~ How do you like it, Owner?

main3.line: Relax and get cozy, Owner~ Now's not the time for work, it's time to hang out with me!

mission_complete.line: Mission complete! Let's claim those rewards right meow, Owner~

touch.line: Is there something I can do for you, Owner?

touch2.line: I'm always okay with getting intimate with you, Owner~

unlock.line: I'll sing a song for you, Owner~ Ahem... Wait, I'm not sure I know any Dragon Empery songs, actually...

win_mvp.line: Nicely commanded, Owner!

detail.line: If I were a princess, I bet you'd come to my house, sat atop a white horse and ready to pick me up~ Right, Owner?

drop_descrip.line: "Owner~ I've come to take you to the ball~" ...That's exactly what you were going to do? Eh, doesn't matter who does it~ All that matters is we'll be there together~♪

home.line: Owner, could you lift my dress's train for me? It'll drag along the ground otherwise... Aww, thank you~♪

login.line: We'd better get going soon, Owner! My horse here is starting to get restless~

main1.line: Think we'll meet any magical creatures out in this forest, Owner? You know... Like fairies? I once read a nursery tale about those!

main2.line: Owner! Lookie! I found a twelve-sided snowflake! Aww, it melted...

main3.line: Offer you my hand...? I don't get it. I'm happy just to take your hand and cuddle like we always do! Rubrub~ Squeeze~

touch.line: Myeh-heh♪ Your eyes are just glued to me, aren't they, Owner? Ahem... "You may feast your eyes; gaze all you wish"~♪

touch2.line: You're silly, Owner~ You know what I think about surprise touchies~

unlock.line: "Owner~ I've come to take you to the ball~" ...That's exactly what you were going to do? Eh, doesn't matter who does it~ All that matters is we'll be there together~♪

battle.line: Alright, let's do this with fanfare!

detail.line: All great odysseys must begin somewhere, but true glory only awaits those who reach their destination... That's why you ought to stay your course until the very end!

drop_descrip.line: Heavy cruiser – Drake.

expedition.line: Instead of collecting supplies like this, wouldn't it be better to just raid the enemy for... Actually, never mind.

feeling1.line: I am willing to turn a blind eye to a few accidents, but if you keep doing this intentionally, don't expect any mercy from me.

feeling2.line: Everything goes on the battlefield. Whether you fight fair-and-square or use backhanded methods, it matters not. History is written by the victors.

feeling3.line: Oh right, Commander. Did you have any interest in navigation... or rather, adventure? I've been recruiting mates. If you're interested, let's go look for treasure or uninhabited islands or something!

feeling4.line: Sure, it's great to travel together and all, but aren't all these places too close by? Port, the surrounding areas, and the nearby ocean... Sigh. Honestly, going to these places doesn't make me excited at all. Next time, I'm taking you somewhere farther away.

feeling5.line: I see. So what you're telling me is that it's not the place that matters, but that if I'm with you, anywhere is fine? ... Haha... W-Wait... are you saying...

home.line: Nice job, Commander. How would you like some fresh... grapes? Hehe, come on~ don't drop 'em!

hp_warning.line: Ugh, they got me!

login.line: You've finally come. What should we start with today? It's great to think about battle plans and all, but how about sending me on a sortie first?

lose.line: How humiliating... I'll get you back for this! Just you wait!

mail.line: Here, a letter for you. Anybody find information on some treasure?

main1.line: Basically, ships arm themselves with armor and equipment—in other words, with artillery and torpedoes. Meanwhile, humans arm themselves with courage and intelligence—in other words, with perception and wisdom.

main2.line: While I don't hate customs and ceremony, I do prefer the simpler things.

main3.line: The dew-kissed fruit of the morning makes for the best juice. Don't you agree?

mission.line: Doing mundane tasks is totally not my style. Um... Why don't we check the rewards first?

mission_complete.line: Can't complain about the bounty, but I just feel like there's "something" missing.

profile.line: I'm the Royal Navy heavy cruiser, Drake. If you weren't aware of my existence before, I'll make sure you know now by showing you the power of my 9.2 inch guns!

propose.line: Don't you think it's strange too? This feeling that's not quite 'having my heart stolen' or 'feeling vexed,' but more just... 'feeling embarrassed'? ...Gosh, it's all your fault that I'm not acting like myself! ... But I don't quite hate this feeling either... Well? Do you get what I mean?

skill.line: You won't find any mercy here!

touch.line: I tend to get along better with people who are straightforward. If there's something you want to say to me, say it clearly.

touch2.line: Huuh? You sure have some guts.

unlock.line: So you're the Commander? Seems you've got some backbone. I'm the Royal Navy heavy cruiser, Drake, and I'll be joining your fleet. Just making sure, you will deploy me, right?

upgrade.line: Now that's the kind of sound I want to hear from my main guns! Ahahaha!

win_mvp.line: Victory always leaves you feeling nice and refreshed!

detail.line: Artificial waves? Hmm, this might be more fun than I thought. Time to show off my swimming skills!

drop_descrip.line: Phew... Swimming like this doesn't feel all that refreshing... Hey, how about you stop staring and come join me?

home.line: Good exercise followed by some exquisitely cool watermelon, man, it's just the best! Hey, you'd better get over here and have a bite, or I'll finish this whole thing by myself!

login.line: I heard this is a nice place to swim. Imagine my surprise to learn it wasn't a beach, but an outdoor pool... Still, I guess if we're just killing time, this is as good a place as any...

main1.line: C-could you stop staring at me like that? You're starting to weird me out...

main2.line: Hahah, seems like this manjuu needs some more practice if it's struggling with these meager waves!

main3.line: *sigh*... I'm not feeling satisfied yet. Guess I'll go for another swim...

touch.line: Ooh, my shoulders were starting to get a little stiff. You're not half-bad, eh~

unlock.line: Phew... Swimming like this doesn't feel all that refreshing... Hey, how about you stop staring and come join me?

battle.line: I shall take you on.

detail.line: A pleasure to see you today. I hope to spend another wonderful day with you today, dear Commander. Mhm, quite the reason to rejoice.

drop_descrip.line: Light Cruiser—Plymouth

expedition.line: A commission has been completed. Let us rejoice now, dear Commander.

feeling1.line: Rejoice, dear Commander, for you can still turn to me for help now.

feeling2.line: You may rely on me more, Commander. After all, my duty is to help you help everyone.

feeling3.line: I don't know too much about the Royal Maid Corps. Since I support you just as they do, there should not be much difference in our positions. Do you agree, dear Commander?

feeling4.line: Rejoice, dear Commander, for I shall be assisting the Royal Maids today. ...With the assistance of my colleagues, I shall be able to support you to an even greater capacity –a reason to rejoice indeed.

feeling5.line: Commander, are there any wishes you'd like to have fulfilled today? I am no longer here just to support you. Should you desire, I shall assist you, serve you, and of course, love you... Rejoice, dear Commander, for there is nothing I will not do for your sake.

headtouch.line: Your hand feels most pleasing upon my head. Thank you.

home.line: Rejoice, dear Commander—I have come to bring you a full-course Sardegnian meal. ...It's too heavy, you say?

hp_warning.line: I'm ashamed to show you my unsightly side...

login.line: Rejoice, dear Commander, for this morning is most refreshing. How shall we start our day?

lose.line: So this is the taste of defeat, Commander. How repugnant.

mail.line: Rejoice, dear Commander, for new mail has arrived.

main1.line: Oh, do be careful now... Miss Edinburgh, it seems that the rumors of your clumsiness were... not greatly exaggerated.

main2.line: Did you need some papers disposed of. *BOOM* ...There you go. Rejoice, for I have turned your troubles into a pile of ash!

main3.line: Having trouble focusing on your work? Well, I suppose I could tell you a fairy tale. A long, long time ago...

mission.line: A new mission has arrived, Commander. Allow me to– Hmm? You're going to do it yourself?

mission_complete.line: The mission rewards are here. Let's open it—it'll be destroyed if I fire a shell at it? Understood.

profile.line: I am the blueprint ship Plymouth, an alternate branch of the Edinburgh class. I give my thanks to you for manifesting me in this port. Please, use me as you see fit.

propose.line: Rejoice, dear Commander! Starting today, I shall become your exclusive-use shipgirl! By exclusive, I mean special... Basically, I've become someone special to you, so can I stop looking after you today and just rejoice for myself? Heehee~

touch.line: You'd like to hear me sing? Then, please tell me what you'd like to hear—if it's something I don't already know, I'm willing to learn.

touch2.line: Yes, do as you please with me. As long as it makes you rejoice, dear Commander.

unlock.line: I offer my greetings to you who has manifested me, Commander. I am the blueprint ship, Plymouth. Starting here and now, I stand ready to execute your every order. May you rejoice in our blessed encounter.

upgrade.line: Strength flows through me. Rejoice, dear Commander, for I have become "easier to use."

win_mvp.line: Victory is ours. Rejoice, dear Commander.

battle.line: This is rather embarrassing, but...

detail.line: Are you satisfied after seeing me in my swimsuit? If you'd like to see me in another outfit, just give me your order. W-whether it's a maid outfit, or a bunny girl outfit... as long as it makes you rejoice...?

drop_descrip.line: Rejoice, Commander. I have no doubt that this refreshing sensation will bring you the utmost satisfaction. Come, let us enjoy this experience together.

home.line: Good work on your mission. Is there anything you'd like me to get for you, dear Commander? Since we're at the pool, how about... some toys, some fruits, and some wine? How does that sound?

login.line: Rejoice, dear Commander, the sun's rays shine as splendidly as usual — which means, it's a perfect day for a soak in the pool.

main1.line: Dear Commander, if you are feeling restless, might I recommend taking a dip with me in the refreshing water?

main2.line: You want some song suggestions? Well, if you're fine with the kind of screamo Miss Ulrich has been showing me, then... Oh, I don't need to sing it for you?

main3.line: Will you be swimming? Then let me make the pool larger... Excuse me, would you mind getting out of range of my main battery? Oh... Dearie me.

mission_complete.line: The mission rewards have arrived. Rejoice, dear Commander.

touch.line: Sure, let's laze around together.

touch2.line: Revel in me. Rejoice to your heart's content, dear Commander.

unlock.line: Rejoice, Commander. I have no doubt that this refreshing sensation will bring you the utmost satisfaction. Come, let us enjoy this experience together.

win_mvp.line: Be it the cooling waves or the taste of victory, please indulge as much as you'd like, dear Commander.

battle.line: Good weather, even better mood~ Let’s go!

detail.line: Hehe, are you that lonely Commander?~

drop_descrip.line: Special type I {namecode:2} Destroyer Class— {namecode:2}

expedition.line: Hey~ The Commission fleet is back, stop sleeping!

feeling1.line: I thought the Commander would understand me...

feeling2.line: What’s in my hands? I think it’s called “Gohei” or something like that. It looks so pretty when swung back and forth, so I thought to grab it with me~

feeling3.line: Not sure how my sisters are faring… Although, since they are my sisters, I’m sure they’re prospering wherever they are!

feeling4.line: What type of girls do you like, Commander? Hmm? I’m just curious. Ha~ perhaps you’ve misunderstood me?

feeling5.line: I was implying something before? Regardless, no matter what type of girls you like, as long as you will like me in the future, then that’ll be just fine~ Hehehe.

home.line: First, you do this, then this....?! C-Commander, welcome back~ Hahaha, I wasn’t up to anything!

hp_warning.line: Looks like this isn’t the time to joke around...

login.line: Commander, how are ya feeling today?~

lose.line: That hurts so much… Commander, let’s run away!

mail.line: Here’s some mail~ ah… So it’s for the Commander...

main1.line: The weather today sure is beautiful, don’t you think, Commander?

main2.line: Listen up {namecode:14}, even if the Commander is a total loser, but I am totally (probably) reliable!

main3.line: Even if the Commander praises 100 times, that still won’t be too much... hmm, or perhaps 100 praises will be a bit tiresome to listen to.

mission.line: Commander, there are so many uncleared missions—— ahhh~!!! Were you being lazy again?

mission_complete.line: Commander, the mission rewards are here~ With me being here, perhaps there are more rewards now? Hehe.

profile.line: Yoohoo~ I am the destroyer who recently made the world tremble, call me {namecode:2}! Sorry, I’m not trying to be complacent, in fact, I was in many battles… although none of them are worth writing home about… I will continue to do better!

propose.line: Even though I said that the Commander would like me “in the future”, but it seems that “future” has become unexpectedly sooner~ Were you a bit shy when I asked you?~ Hehehe.

skill.line: Hmph, taste the power of the Special type Destroyers!

touch.line: Help with work? O right… Looking at the Commander being so idle, I almost forgot about work~

touch2.line: Wow! You scared me to death!

unlock.line: Yoohoo~ yours truly {namecode:2} class has arrived, so you’re the Commander? I'm looking forward to your guidance~

upgrade.line: Wow?! Excellent condition!

win_mvp.line: Uh-huh, I’m good right~

battle.line: Let's finish this so I can make it to school!

detail.line: I didn't oversleep! I was just doing stuff I like and ended up losing track of time...

drop_descrip.line: Oh no! I-I'm gonna be late for school! Y-you need to speed up too, doggy! *Pant*... *pant*... Why'd none of my sisters wake me up before they left?!

lose.line: Fight or run away to fight another day!

main1.line: nil

main2.line: The Fencing Club, the Reading Society, the Economics Association, the UFO Research Organization... Dang it, I wanna join them all!

main3.line: Belfast's going to hang out with Edinburgh after school... Maaan, I wish my sisters would come see me, too...

touch.line: Commander, you got any more work you need help with? I've gotta go walk the doggy in 15 minutes!

unlock.line: Oh no! I-I'm gonna be late for school! Y-you need to speed up too, doggy! *Pant*... *pant*... Why'd none of my sisters wake me up before they left?!

battle.line: It's so hot... Let's mop up the enemies quickly so we can go home...

detail.line: I-I feel my consciousness... flapping away...

drop_descrip.line: "C-come on in! We've got special offers for you!" ... W-wait, is this really what a "sexy mascot" would wear? It feels pretty different from what I was expecting... And boy, is it stuffy in this thing...

home.line: N-nicely done!

login.line: C-come on in! ... Oops, I mean, welcome back, Commander!

main1.line: I did promise Akashi I'd be the mascot... but it kind of feels like she tricked me...

main2.line: Could you help me pick these up, Commander? Wearing this makes them... mmrgh... impossible to reach, you see...

main3.line: What? The forecast warned about high temperatures? ... That's no biggie, I've already gotten used to it being really hot...

touch.line: C-Commander, don't touch me... I'm going to lose my balance...

touch2.line: Wh-what? What the heck are you doing, Commander?

unlock.line: "C-come on in! We've got special offers for you!" ... W-wait, is this really what a "sexy mascot" would wear? It feels pretty different from what I was expecting... And boy, is it stuffy in this thing...

win_mvp.line: Heheh! Wearing this costume... doesn't impact my performance at aaaall!

battle.line: Maybe my tuba... is useful in battle after all...?

detail.line: Didn't think an instrument could be so fun! I have to teach others about the joy of music!

drop_descrip.line: Check it out, Commander! What do you think? ... No, not my dress! I'm talking about the tuba! Want me to play a tune for you~?

expedition.line: Tooooot! The commission team has come back, Commander! ... No surprise: this tuba's reminding potential is totally next-level♪

feeling5.line: If I ever perform on stage, will you be there to listen, Commander? Actually, it'd be even better if you could be my maestro~

home.line: Did my pre-sortie motivational song serve you well, Commander?

login.line: My marching solo will wake you up, Commander!

main1.line: Let me play you a motivational song, Commander! Tooooot! ... Wh-what? That's annoying...? Sorry!

main2.line: You should learn an instrument so we can play a song together, Commander!

main3.line: Oh yeah, what do you think about my dress, Commander? Does it suit me? I absolutely adore it, it's all fluffy and stuff!

touch.line: Do you wanna hear a song, Commander? You got it! Manjuus, you all ready to go?

touch2.line: Whuah! ... Don't expect me to feel bad if I smack you with this thing, Commander!

unlock.line: Check it out, Commander! What do you think? ... No, not my dress! I'm talking about the tuba! Want me to play a tune for you~?

win_mvp.line: Okay, let's play a victory march to celebrate... H-hey! Wait for meeee!

drop_descrip.line: The whole world's going to feel the tremors from my debut! I'm Fubuki, the Special-type idol!

main1.line: nil

main2.line: nil

main3.line: nil

detail.line: If my sisters saw me working hard... would they say something like "Fubuki's such a hard-working role model?" Ehe... ehehe... Ah, I'm so so sorry, I just spaced out for a bit!

drop_descrip.line: Welcome, welcome! Oh, Commander! I've actually started working here part-time, but I'm still learning— Wooah?! Phew... Th-that was a close one...

home.line: This Oxy-cola goes to this table, and uhh, a few more minutes on this pizza, and umm... Ahhh! This would be so much easier with a clone of me here!

login.line: Commander... Err, I mean, welcome! What would you like to order~?

main1.line: Sigh... When will I be able to handle this job as easily as Miss Belfast does?

main2.line: You want to chat with me? Sure, as soon as I get finished with all this stuff... Ughh...

main3.line: Did someone call for me? Excuse me, I'll be right there! Oh hey, it's Akatsuki and the others!

touch.line: Commander, this bell is just for decoration...

touch2.line: Eep?! It's hard to keep my balance, so stop with that already!

unlock.line: Welcome, welcome! Oh, Commander! I've actually started working here part-time, but I'm still learning— Wooah?! Phew... Th-that was a close one...

battle.line: I have a little experience with leading a fleet, but...

detail.line: Why does everyone want to touch my ears? What's so special about them...?

drop_descrip.line: Special Type I-class destroyer number two – Shirayuki.

expedition.line: Sounds like the commission team has returned to port. I heard their footsteps.

feeling1.line: I, I don't want to hear your noise...

feeling2.line: I've not heard anything suspicious today... And that's a good thing.

feeling3.line: I don't like crowds. All the noise they make gives me headaches... I much prefer quiet places.

feeling4.line: We could share an umbrella on a rainy day, go for a walk, and just listen to the sound of the raindrops... Hm? Did I say something out loud just now?

feeling5.line: Can I snuggle you up for a minute? Thanks... I can hear your heart going ba-thump, ba-thump. It's really soothing~

headtouch.line: Eep?! S-stop it, that tickles...

home.line: *clap* *clap*... I'm glad you're back. Let's have some tea together.

hp_warning.line: This doesn't look promising...

login.line: I see, so that's how your footsteps sound... I'll commit it to memory.

lose.line: They beat us... I'll cover our retreat!

mail.line: Here's your letter. You should read it before it becomes old news.

main1.line: I like the scritchy-scratchy noise paper makes when you write on it. It's relaxing.

main2.line: Fubuki's always bursting with energy whenever I see her. I'm honestly impressed with her...

main3.line: A carrot? Uhh, no thanks? What do you think I am? A rabbit?

mission.line: More new missions... Ugh... Could I call over Fubuki for some extra help?

mission_complete.line: That noise... Sounds like our rewards are here.

profile.line: I'm Shirayuki, Fubuki-class destroyer number 2. I served Destroyer Squadron 3 during the war, and... that's pretty much all I have to say. I'll make myself useful to you and the rest of the fleet.

propose.line: Is your heart racing, Commander? That's okay, because mine is too. Hehehe~ So, do you promise to always, always be with me? You're not going to regret it? Great! Then we're wed now!

touch.line: Is there something you want to talk about, Commander?

touch2.line: Wh-what do you think you're doing?!

unlock.line: Fubuki-class number two, Shirayuki. I'm a bit quieter than my elder sister... Mm, pleased to meet you.

upgrade.line: Motivation overclocked! ...Is what Fubuki would say, I bet.

win_mvp.line: It's over? Phew... Looks like everyone's okay, too.

detail.line: Today it's my turn to look after the bunnies. No, I said "look after," not "be looked after by."

drop_descrip.line: Whoa now! There's enough food for everyone, so don't fight over it! ...Commander? Don't just stand there, give me a hand, please!

home.line: Come here, little bunny. There, that's a good girl... Phew. Finally got them all to settle down.

login.line: I recognize that sound. It's you, Commander! Heheh. I know it by heart.

main1.line: Maybe I should also bring some hay along with the carrots... No, Fubuki! You can't feed that stuff to a bunny!

main2.line: I guess the ears really are the first thing people go for when they see a bunny... No, I'm talking about bunnies, not me!

main3.line: Oh, to be a happy rabbit, spending my days eating, sleeping, and playing with humans...

touch.line: There's a lot you have to keep in mind when playing with a bunny. For starters...

touch2.line: R-rally, bunnies! Bite the commander!

unlock.line: Whoa now! There's enough food for everyone, so don't fight over it! ...Commander? Don't just stand there, give me a hand, please!

battle.line: What nice weather... That means the battle should go smoothly, right...

detail.line: Oh, these bandages? They're just in case I bump into a tree branch again... B-but you don't need to worry about it! I'm already used to it...

drop_descrip.line: Special Type I Fubuki-class destroyer number four – Miyuki.

expedition.line: Commander, the friends we sent out on commission have returned safely... Thank goodness they're fine...

feeling1.line: Commander, you're scary... P-please stay away from me...

feeling2.line: Thank you for accepting me here...! I will do my best to repay this act of kindness! B-but first, I need to not cause trouble for you...

feeling3.line: Commander, was I able to do something useful for the fleet today? ...I did a great job? Yay! I, I'll continue to give it my all...!

feeling4.line: After we're done with work, is it okay if I stay with you a bit longer, Commander? I think I've become a bit more confident, all because of... I mean, all thanks to you...

feeling5.line: C-C-Commander, th-there's something I really want to tell you! Um, uhh, I... Nevermind, s-sorry! ...*sniffle* I can't even get myself to say it in practice, how could I ever make the Commander know my feelings...

headtouch.line: I, I will be okay...

home.line: Commander, good job on your sortie! Um... you didn't get hurt, did you? Did everything go well with the battle? Oh, sorry, I must be bothering you again...

hp_warning.line: *sniffle*... I hate it when this happens...!

login.line: G-good morning, Commander... Is there anything I can help with today? I, um, would like to be more useful to you...

lose.line: You don't need a useless girl like me, right... I'm so sorry...

mail.line: C-Commander, new mail has arrived... Sh-should I go sort through them first...?

main1.line: Fubuki is as outgoing as ever... If only I could be brimming with positivity just like her... F-forget I said anything...

main2.line: My tail is warm and fluffy...? Um, p-please don't go touching it all of a sudden... I'm a bit sensitive there...

main3.line: Um, is the fog rolling in? Bad weather makes me feel really uneasy... I really hate bad weather...

main4.line: Naka and her sisters are the ones who make my tail look pretty and nice... I can't do it all by myself...

mission.line: You've been assigned new missions...? Commander, should I go with you to check on them?

mission_complete.line: Commander, the mission rewards have arrived... Should I go bring them in for you...?

profile.line: I am a Special Type I Destroyer from the Sakura Empire, Fubuki-class number four, Miyuki... Due to some bad luck, I was never able to be of use... B-but, Commander, please don't hate me! I, I'm sure I'll be able to do something useful for you!

propose.line: W-wow... C-Commander, I'm always down on myself, and keep causing trouble for you... But you still want to stay by my side? I, I see... Thank you very much! I also... have always, always loved you, Commander!

skill.line: I don't want to have to say goodbye ever again...!

touch.line: C-Commander, did I mess up...?

touch2.line: P-please, don't do that... at least not where others can see...

unlock.line: Is this... my new home? C-Commander, it's an h-honor to meet you... I'm one of the Sakura Empire's special-type destroyers... Number four of the Fubuki-class, Miyuki. P-please command me as you see fit... Eep...

upgrade.line: Th-thank you very much! ...I, I'll work twice as hard!

win_mvp.line: I hope I managed to do something useful...

detail.line: I have to be careful not to cut myself when chopping the vegetables... Otherwise, Commander will be worried about me...

drop_descrip.line: Commander, I think the goods over here are a bit cheaper... Umm, I'm doing fine on my budget still, so we can pick out some more things to buy. A-also, I'll get to spend more time shopping with you... Ah, d-disregard that please... *blushes*

expedition.line: Our friends who were out on a commission are back. But, it'll be a while until they'll stop by to restock, right?

feeling5.line: I wish I could still go shopping with you after the pop-up café event ends... Huh? We'll all still be together after that, so you don't mind going with me...? Ahh... Thank you... Thank you so much, Commander...

headtouch.line: Ehehe...

home.line: Commander, are you still working on the after-action report...? I'm so sorry I couldn't help you even though I'm supposed to be your secretary... Huh? I already did you a big favor when we were shopping? I see, that makes me feel better...

login.line: Commander, what are we going to go buy next?

mail.line: Commander, you've got new mail... Would it be better if I read through it first...?

main1.line: Do I like going shopping by myself? N-not really... The way people look at me is a bit scary... so I usually go with Fubuki or Shirayuki...

main2.line: Eek?! My tail got caught between the shelves... Nngh... Commander, please help me! *blushes*

main3.line: It's important to stock up on food, you know? Just in case we can't go shopping because of bad weather, like a typhoon or something...

main4.line: Commander, are you going to stop by the Sakura pop-up café next time? I learned to cook a new dish, so... I can deliver it to the dorms too if you'd like...

mission.line: There's a new mission... Go ahead and take a look at it. You don't need to worry about me...

mission_complete.line: The mission rewards are in... D-do you think we could go fetch them together...? *blushes*

touch.line: Eep...! What's wrong? Oh, I'm going to hurt myself if I keep rubbing the pointy part...? Oh, th-thank you...

unlock.line: Commander, I think the goods over here are a bit cheaper... Umm, I'm doing fine on my budget still, so we can pick out some more things to buy. A-also, I'll get to spend more time shopping with you... Ah, d-disregard that please... *blushes*

win_mvp.line: I want to be more useful to you, Commander...!

battle.line: Want to go... to Solomon?

detail.line: I've inspected the communication equipment. It won't cause any more problems...

drop_descrip.line: First ship of special Type II {namecode:6} class destroyers, {namecode:6}.

expedition.line: Commander, a commission has finished.

feeling1.line: I don't really want to get any closer.

feeling2.line: Ayanami's impressions of Commander? I don't really know.

feeling3.line: Commander, you're always saying that my ears are cute... But why won't you touch them?

feeling4.line: If there's one thing that worries me... it would be when you are not at my side.

feeling5.line: I don't particularly... like or dislike combat. I just do what must be done. But if it's for you, Commander... maybe I can get a bit stronger.

headtouch.line: I don't really get it but... I'm a bit happy...

home.line: Commander, you're a little like me on the battlefield... That's... pretty cool.

hp_warning.line: I don't want... to be alone...

login.line: Commander, have you eaten yet? Here's some snacks.

lose.line: It's okay... I'll recover quickly.

mail.line: There's... new mail...

main1.line: {namecode:6}'s ears... are they cute? I don't understand... As long as you're happy, Commander!

main2.line: I've been having nightmares of all the girls getting lost... I'm certain that it's my fault, too...

main3.line: Commander? No, nothing. I just wanted to see if you were here or not.

mission.line: Commander, we've been notified of new missions.

mission_complete.line: The rewards for the previous mission are here.

profile.line: I am Ayanami, an improved Fubuki-class destroyer. I am not afraid of combat. Though just a destroyer, I can fight any enemy...

propose.line: Rest assured... This time, no matter what happens, I'll survive and return to you... because I'll always want to see you again...

skill.line: Bear witness to the true power of the "Demon"

touch.line: Uuu... it tickles...a bit.

touch2.line: Commander... please... don't touch there so much... It's making me feel weird...

unlock.line: I'm... Ayanami. I am often called the "Demon." Pleasure to meet you.

upgrade.line: My power is overflowing...

win_mvp.line: MVP? I don't really get it, but... thanks.

drop_descrip.line: I heard that... I need to wear a costume like this to participate in Halloween festivities. Commander... do I look cute?

main1.line: Are these... sweets? Thank you. I will try them.

main2.line: There are fun things outside of combat and training too...

main3.line: If I stand on this pumpkin lantern... will I be closer to reaching the skies?

touch.line: I think... I like this costume.

touch2.line: Tonight, I am not a demon... but a witch!

unlock.line: I heard that... I need to wear a costume like this to participate in Halloween festivities. Commander... do I look cute?

battle.line: This song... fits the battlefield well.

detail.line: When I put on my headphones, the music flows and washes away everything in the world... except you...

drop_descrip.line: Commander, want to listen to music together? Do you like... this non-combat-oriented Ayanami?

expedition.line: Training and commissions... there''s no time to slack off...

login.line: Commander, before work starts, want to listen to music together?

main1.line: Commander, Javelin asked if I could play later. Is that okay?

main2.line: Commander, what kind of music do you like? I like... um, rock?

main3.line: Ikazuchi said she was playing something called a "mobage." Commander, do you know what that is?

mission_complete.line: I'm somewhat looking forward to today's rewards...

touch.line: Ayanami's riggings... can also become musical instruments. Commander, do you want to hear me play?

unlock.line: Commander, want to listen to music together? Do you like... this non-combat-oriented Ayanami?

win_mvp.line: "As long as you're smiling..." What does that mean?

detail.line: This outfit feels light and easy to move in, not bad at all... Very cute? Um... thank you...

drop_descrip.line: Compared to the way we celebrate New Year in the Sakura Empire, the festivities of the Dragon Empery have a completely different atmosphere... But, I don't really mind the liveliness... Commander, do you like festivals?

feeling5.line: I wish you a happy and peaceful holiday~ Commander, I hope that we can continue being together like this forever...

login.line: Commander, the girls from the Dragon Empery seem to be having a banquet... Want to come with me to have a look?

main1.line: This year's zodiac animal is... Eh? Commander, did you see where the piglet ran off to?

main2.line: Commander, are we under attack? I hear a lot of explosions... Eh? So those are a form of celebration? That sounds interesting, yes...

main3.line: What is this "ding-a-ling" sound? It reminds me... of our New Year back home...

touch.line: Commander, this dress is made with really comfortable materials... Want to feel...?

touch2.line: Commander, you can't... lift that part...

unlock.line: Compared to the way we celebrate New Year in the Sakura Empire, the festivities of the Dragon Empery have a completely different atmosphere... But, I don't really mind the liveliness... Commander, do you like festivals?

detail.line: Training to be a waitress is something that Ayanami has never experienced before. It's very novel, yes...

drop_descrip.line: "Welcome, Commander..." I should greet customers like this... yes?

feeling5.line: When I'm off work, I want to spend some time with you, Commander... I'll make you a special bento that I learned how to make at work... Is that okay, Commander?

home.line: Would you like a special combo meal to celebrate your safe return?

login.line: Commander, what would you like to order today? The menu is right here...

main1.line: Laffey said that it's important to diversify your diet. So... today, would you like something sweet, Commander?

main2.line: Javelin is always so energetic, no matter what she's doing. I'm a little jealous...

main3.line: Being a waitress... is harder work than I imagined...

touch.line: I should hold the serving platter... like this? Commander, are you trying to help me? It's okay, I think I can manage on my own.

unlock.line: "Welcome, Commander..." I should greet customers like this... yes?

battle.line: I'll show you the power... of Ayanami and her friends!

detail.line: Even though we were supposed to use our codenames, Kaga just went and spilled the beans. It's a bit troublesome when nobody is going to use them...

drop_descrip.line: Ayanami here. Successfully infiltrated Commander's office. Oh... Commander saw me. Operation failed...

headtouch.line: They're ears, not horns...

login.line: Commander, want to join Ayanami in cover ops training? ...Hmm, actually, that seems futile.

lose.line: The concealment function that Yuubari added was not very useful...

mail.line: The mail's been... Oh, the members of the maid team responsible for protecting you have already looked it over. It's fine to open it.

main1.line: Those Cloak of Invisibility things that they have in the Royal Navy are really cool... they make me a bit jealous...

main2.line: When I need help, I usually turn to Shouhou or Zed. As for Fubuki... she always hears me out on a variety of stuff. I'm very thankful.

main3.line: This cloak that Yuubari developed for me... has a function that "always conceals its wearer's face." That's... probably good.

main4.line: Commander's office is always protected, and it is absolutely safe. There's no need to worry.

touch.line: Commander, want an apple? They're really good.

unlock.line: Ayanami here. Successfully infiltrated Commander's office. Oh... Commander saw me. Operation failed...

upgrade.line: This power... is for the sake of protecting my friends...!

win_mvp.line: The enemy's lookouts have been taken out succcessfully. Thank you, Commander.

battle.line: An idol's duty is to protect everyone's smiles!

detail.line: Z23 is always looking out for us... Even though she has her own schedule to worry about, she always helps us manage ours.

drop_descrip.line: I guess I'm making my idol debut? Um, Javelin and the others are making their debuts, so, I also had to... Commander, what are idols supposed to do normally?

home.line: If I imagine performances to be like battles, and think of the audience as enemies... Err, wait, that's not going to work.

login.line: Commander, I'm currently practicing my dance routine. Want to watch?

main1.line: Singing and dancing are no problem for me, but smiling is hard... Javelin said that's what makes me cute though. Is that true, Commander?

main2.line: Commander, Z23 told me that rock n' roll and idols don't really go together. Do you think I could make metal cute?

main3.line: Fubuki seems to also be doing idol training. We should go see her... in a little bit.

main4.line: I never knew that there were so many things to do as an idol. I'm getting all fired up.

touch.line: Commander, this is what I learned from my lessons today.

unlock.line: I guess I'm making my idol debut? Um, Javelin and the others are making their debuts, so, I also had to... Commander, what are idols supposed to do normally?

win_mvp.line: Victory pose. Yeah.

detail.line: Now, I know that I'm not alone anymore... because you're here after all, Commander...

drop_descrip.line: I'm still... your Ayanami... though I'm not very used to this outfit... Commander, does it suit me?

feeling5.line: I enjoy being with everyone, but... I'd also like to spend more time alone with you, Commander...

home.line: Commander... shall I rub your shoulders?

login.line: No matter where you go, Ayanami shall always walk three steps behind you. Commander... shall we go?

main1.line: I'm not sure... I understand the meaning of these clothes... but since you'd like me to wear them, I don't mind...

main2.line: Everyone was staring at me so excitedly... I'm not used to this...

touch.line: Commander, I like cuddling with you like this... It feels nice.

touch2.line: This feels... a bit weird after all... But, if you like it, I don't mind...

unlock.line: I'm still... your Ayanami... though I'm not very used to this outfit... Commander, does it suit me?

win_mvp.line: Commander, as long as you're by my side, I won't lose.

battle.line: It will be all right, Commander... Believe in me...

drop_descrip.line: Ayanami, retrofit complete. I feel stronger, yes... Having that said, Commander, can you pat my head? I want to be spoiled a bit...

main1.line: Commander, I feel like I can work a bit harder when I'm with you...

main2.line: Being with everyone makes me happy... so I want to be able to stay together...

main3.line: Commander, if you leave me alone... I'll be hurt...

touch.line: Commander's hands... are so warm...

unlock.line: Ayanami, retrofit complete. I feel stronger, yes... Having that said, Commander, can you pat my head? I want to be pampered a bit...

win_mvp.line: If it is for everyone's sake... I am willing to become the "Demon."

battle.line: Destroyer Division Six, embark!

detail.line: T-the reason I sleep with the lights on is because... i-it is not because I am afraid!

drop_descrip.line: Type III {namecode:11}-class destroyer number one - {namecode:11}.

expedition.line: We may use my searchlight to find our way home! Huh? ... You have no need of it? R-really...?

feeling1.line: Commander, you must cheer up!

feeling2.line: I am a little worried... about {namecode:13} and {namecode:14}...

feeling3.line: Commander, do you perhaps wish to see my true right eye?

feeling4.line: I cannot sleep well without my sisters by my side... T-that is not to say I am lonely! I-it is because I am concerned about them!

feeling5.line: We Division Six destroyers have always been together! And... um, surely you will be together with me forever as well, Commander?

home.line: Commander~ Did you bring back any shiny items? ... Hm?! N-not at all, I am not asking simply because I want such things!

login.line: My name is {namecode:11}, I am the ninja who will banish all the darkness in the world! ... Whoa! Commander, w-when did you get here?!

lose.line: Damn... I-I shall get you next time...

mail.line: New mail for you! Uh... I will read it out loud for you!

main1.line: Sometimes I do not understand what {namecode:13} and {namecode:14} are trying to say...

main2.line: Can {namecode:12} find her way here on her own? It has me somewhat worried...

main3.line: W-w-what! Anyone would be shocked from suddenly seeing a person's shadow cast in the light in the middle of the night!

mission.line: The ocean at night is a little scary... N-nay, I am not scared! B-but may I propose we do missions during daytime? You must agree, right?!

mission_complete.line: Rewards~ rewards~!

profile.line: I am {namecode:11}, a special-type destroyer! Destroyer Division Six consisted of me and my sisters! I was the first to be built and the first to be sunk! The Battle of Guadalcanal? I-I was trying to cast my light on the enemy! I was by no means scared of them! ... Ahem, you shall witness how strong I truly am... that you will!

propose.line: A promise that binds us for eternity... I understand! Then I shall show you my true right eye, right this mo... T-there is no need for it? All I need to do is close my eyes instead? Re... really...?

touch.line: {namecode:12}... I really miss her...

touch2.line: S-should you touch me there again... then I will not be able to restrain myself!

unlock.line: I am {namecode:11}, the oldest ship of Destroyer Division Six! Well met, Commander. I sincerely hope you will let me rebuild Division Six! ... Huh?! You do not permit the formation of destroyer divisions?!

upgrade.line: As the oldest of my siblings, I must work even harder!

win_mvp.line: This is the true power of a ninja!

detail.line: I made friends of these bears on my journey! I suggest you try befriend them too, Commander... Er, forsooth!

drop_descrip.line: Is this the place called the Northern Parliament?! It is colder than I thought... Th-thank goodness I brought gear for extreme environments! Hibiki, please wait a bit longer! Your sister is coming to see you!

home.line: To one day find Hibiki – that is the reason I set out upon this journey!

login.line: Being fully prepared is the key to going in the right direction! Say that again? The East lies *that* way?

main1.line: I've still not found Hibiki... I really do wonder when we'll meet again.

main2.line: It is thanks to my compass that I have arrived at the Northern Parliament! Huh? How long has the needle been frozen in place?!

main3.line: I'm curious as to how Ikazuchi and Inazuma are faring...

touch.line: Would you care to harken to one of my tales of valor?

touch2.line: Oooh, I feel myself warming up! I don't know why, though... Something about it feels strange.

unlock.line: Is this the place called the Northern Parliament?! It is colder than I thought... Th-thank goodness I brought gear for extreme environments! Hibiki, please wait a bit longer! Your sister is coming to see you!

detail.line: My companion and I have shared so many miles together... Hm, maybe next time I should call my cohorts to take her for a spin together!

drop_descrip.line: What do you think, Commander? I have a brand new outfit and a brand new companion! I am no longer a plain old ninja... I am now a motoninja!

home.line: My bond with my companion has grown even deeper!

login.line: Motoninja Akatsuki, reporting in! Commander, your orders please!

main1.line: My companion's lights are strong indeed, but I still find these night roads rather difficult...

main2.line: Back before I had broken her in, my companion here gave me a lot of trouble. But these days? We move as one and the same!

main3.line: Inazuma and Ikazuchi are going to be impressed with my companion!

touch.line: I'm afraid you can't ride her, Commander...

touch2.line: Wooooaaaahh!! I'm losing control!

unlock.line: What do you think, Commander? I have a brand new outfit and a brand new companion! I am no longer a plain old ninja... I am now a motoninja!

battle.line: No ambushes! Let us fight face to face!

detail.line: This obstacle will be child's play if I'm able to leverage my ninja skills... I-I'm going the right way this time, I'm sure of it!

drop_descrip.line: Look out! Move, Commander! ...Phew. To explain, I am helping Santa give out Christmas presents! Now excuse me, I cannot tarry here or I'll be late... Wait, have I come to the wrong place? WHAT?!

expedition.line: The commission team has returned! Speaking of... Where did my presents for them go?

home.line: I could've sworn we met here just a minute ago... Wait, a-am I going in circles?!

login.line: These presents must all be delivered before the end of today... Commander, we should depart at once!

lose.line: I m-must maintain my posture...!

main1.line: I'm well acquainted with how to use a grappling hook! ...What? Oh no! The presents!

main2.line: Hmgh! Oh goodness... That's a long way down. C-Commander, how did we end up ascending so high?!

main3.line: Hibiki will deliver the remaining presents? Phew, that's good to know...

mission.line: The sp-spirits of Christmas roam the port at night? C-C-C-Commander! It takes more than that to perturb me, I'll have you know!

touch.line: Umm, C-Commander... You will stop my fall, won't you?!

touch2.line: C-careful, lest the rope come loose!

unlock.line: Look out! Move, Commander! ...Phew. To explain, I am helping Santa give out Christmas presents! Now excuse me, I cannot tarry here or I'll be late... Wait, have I come to the wrong place? WHAT?!

battle.line: I shall dance around our foes!

detail.line: Inazuma's elephant is quite the clever fellow. Heehee, let us see if it can catch this ball!

drop_descrip.line: Welcome, Commander, to DesDiv 6's tent of entertainment! For our first act, I shall perform for you my most stunning ninjutsu! ..."Circus"? I've never heard of this word before!

expedition.line: The commission team has– Oh no, oh no! ...That was close... Thank you for breaking my fall, Commander...

home.line: You've returned, Commander! Let us continue the performance! Hi-yaaah! Behold! Jutsu of Concealment!

login.line: I see... So it's called a performance, not an exhibition... Be that as it may, the show must go on!

main1.line: Ikazuchi, are you all right?! ...Phew... Don't make your sister worry like that!

main2.line: Behold! Jutsu of Flame Escape! ...*cough cough*! This darned pyrotechnic device is needlessly complicated!

main3.line: Don't just stand there, Hibiki – come and assist! ...Your anchor really contains a hidden camera?! ...You just made that up? Aghh! Hibikiiii!

mission.line: A mission, you say? It shall serve as a fine side act!

touch.line: Watch and be amazed, Commander!

touch2.line: H-hands off!

unlock.line: Welcome, Commander, to DesDiv 6's tent of entertainment! For our first act, I shall perform for you my most stunning ninjutsu! ..."Circus"? I've never heard of this word before!

win_mvp.line: My ninjutsu is no mere acrobatic act, it's authentic! ...At least I'm fairly sure it is!

battle.line: Heheh~ Hibiki is super strong~! If you don't believe me, just take a look at this~♪

detail.line: Everyone in the 6th DesDiv is super unique! There's Ikazuchi, Inazuma, and we even have Akatsuki the ninja! I love everyone! Ehehe~

drop_descrip.line: Type III Akatsuki-class destroyer number two – Hibiki.

expedition.line: Ah, that's right, the commission fleet seems to have returned? Should I go with you to welcome them back?

feeling1.line: Commander, it seems like the only way to get you to open your eyes is to get a bit rough... *sigh*...

feeling2.line: I've been making Akatsuki worried all this time. I have to apologize to her properly, as well as thank her.

feeling3.line: Akatsuki, you've been pretty gung-ho about getting the 6th DesDiv back together... Well, the name's not that important as long as we're all together. That's what I think anyway~

feeling4.line: Ah, that reminds me! Commander, have you been taking care of yourself properly? We'd be in serious trouble if you got sick and collapsed or something... Well, even if that happened to you, Hibiki would tenderly nurse you back to health~♪

feeling5.line: Commander, why don't you tell me your story? I'm really interested! ...Why? No particular reason~ Haven't we exhausted all the other topics already? Ehehe~

home.line: Good work out there~ Well, having that said, you still have a lot of stuff that needs to be done... Ahaha...

hp_warning.line: I won't let it end like this!

login.line: Commander, did you just pop in~? All righty... Let's both get some good work done today!

lose.line: Awww... Looks like I'll have to go back to port for repairs...

mail.line: Mail? Show me as well! Show me!

main1.line: Verniy...? It has a nostalgic ring to it...

main2.line: I'm so glad that we can all be together again~♪

main3.line: If you don't need me for anything, I'm going to go play with Ikazuchi and Inazuma~

mission.line: We sure have all sorts of different missions, huh... Don't sweat it though! I'll help you out!

mission_complete.line: Missionnnn... complete! ...Hey, Commander, you should get pumped up too!

profile.line: I'm Hibiki, from the 6th DesDiv~♪ I fought in many battles with my friends, and even saw the end of things. That's good and all, but... having to go in for repairs at that time was a bit awkward... Ahaha...

propose.line: I've been waiting so long for this! Ehehe~ I love you, Commander! ...Ah, look at you getting all bashful~ But my turn's not over yet. I love love love you~! Ehehe~

touch.line: Yo! Did you call me, Commander?

touch2.line: Ah~! Commander, I bet you did that on purpose just now!

unlock.line: Nihihi~ We finally meet at last, Commander! The name's Hibiki! Don't you forget it!

upgrade.line: So this is that "leveling up" thing that Ikazuchi mentioned? Nihihi~

win_mvp.line: Heheh~ I'll be taking that gold star~!

detail.line: Well, um, y'see, sorry to keep you all waiting for so long. I do feel kinda bad about it, but since we're all here, let's cheer up and put the past behind us! That's right, look forward! Ehehe~!

drop_descrip.line: New Year's finally comes to port! I, Hibiki of the 6th DesDiv, will be marking my new arrival in my New Year's attire! Commander, don't you dare change the channel - you've gotta watch my every move~!

headtouch.line: Want to know more about oni horn? Or this golden badge here?

home.line: Good work~ Even though it's the New Year's season, there's still a mountain of work to get through, isn't there~? Looks like I won't get to sleep the day away after all, *sniff*~

login.line: Commander, you haven't started working yet?

main1.line: Akatsuki, you went all the way to the South Pole to look for me?! W-well, I certainly didn't expect that...

main2.line: Just like me, Fubuki seems to also like being the center of attention. But for whatever reason, only she keeps getting herself into weird situations. Why is that?

main3.line: This brisk weather is nothing compared to the cold of the Northern Parliament! Huh? I'm comparing it to the wrong thing?

touch2.line: You couldn't control yourself because I looked too delicious? Commander, you beast~

unlock.line: New Year's finally comes to port! I, Hibiki of the 6th DesDiv, will be marking my new arrival in my New Year's attire! Commander, don't you dare change the channel - you've gotta watch my every move~!

battle.line: I see! So all we need to do is press that auto button in the top left and we'll be fine!

detail.line: If you bow deep and beg for it, I'll make your wishes basically come true! ... It didn't work? Um, well... that's because you haven't wished hard enough yet!

drop_descrip.line: Type III {namecode:11}-class destroyer number three - {namecode:11}.

expedition.line: If you let a completed commission just sit there, does it gain any "interest"?

feeling1.line: I see! This means that if I just let myself get washed away by the ocean then I can come back home...

feeling2.line: Commander, if there's ever anything you don't understand, just ask me. After all, I've used up more oil than you ever will in your life.

feeling3.line: It's my birthday tomorrow. Have you gotten a gift for me yet? You didn't know it was my birthday? Ah, well... see that pendant over there? Buy it and give it to someone you like, I'm sure they'll be delighted!

feeling4.line: Commander! I found a sweet way to make a ton of money! Um, it says "if you invest 10,000 coins then I can recruit 2 more people for my startup, and you'll see a monthly 30% profit",stuff like that... But what's a "startup"...?

feeling5.line: I see! This thing making my heart race is called "love"! Alright, I understand. That means...! W-wha...? I feel so lightheaded... It feels like the world's spinning around me... Is this "love" too?

home.line: Times like these call for fine wine and good food! Hard work shouldn't go unnoticed and all that! Hm? Where do we get it from? From the dorm! There's plenty of it there!

login.line: I see! You just "logged in" didn't you? Human language sure is profound...

lose.line: I see...! Times like these you should P2GSOE2PTG4U! Pay to get someone else to play the game for you! Or you can just let me handle it instead!

mail.line: I see! This is that... thingy! The thing you need to bring with you to be let into that one chocolate factory!

main1.line: Almost as fast as {namecode:18}? So, the wind is faster than thunder and lighting?

main2.line: I see! So {namecode:14}-chan landed the "First Strike" in the World War!

main3.line: I see! So if I stay in the shipyard all the time I'll become a "Phoenix"! Yep, I'd be a... "Thunder Phoenix"...?

mission.line: You haven't finished the mission? ... That sounds about as bad as not finishing your job.

mission_complete.line: Come on! I'm the commander's secretary, but I can't claim rewards on his behalf?! What are the people in charge thinking!

profile.line: I'm {namecode:13}, an {namecode:11}-class destroyer. I may not look like it, but I'm a Sakura Empire veteran. Even {namecode:83} calls me... um, what was I called again? Anyways, it was something like that! You can count on me to do my job! Also, see that LIKE button? Give it a good tap and make sure to subscribe to my channel!

propose.line: Just gotta write my name here, right? ... Um, I don't think I get it... {namecode:14}-chan, care to explain this? ... "After you sign it, you'll belong to the commander forever"? Okay, got it!

skill.line: I see! This is the power that two sisters have!

touch.line: I see! This is one of those ordinary "greeting" things, right?

touch2.line: Uh, umm... is this what I think it is? I know full well the meaning of w-what you did! I-I see...

unlock.line: I am {namecode:13}…I’m simply not very talkative...I think you’ll be seeing a lot more of me in the future, Commander.

upgrade.line: I'd rather have my "ratings","likes",and "gimme" stats enhanced instead!

win_mvp.line: I see! Now this is what you should expect of someone as "prestigious" as me! Er, or was it "pretentious"...?

detail.line: If it's inevitable, then hopefully the Commander will only take a small bite…. no, wrong! It’s, it’s probably better if {namecode:13} can be spared just this one time!

drop_descrip.line: {namecode:13}, {namecode:13} has been transformed into tea! What should we do! {namecode:14} and {namecode:13} will get slurped up by the Commander!

main1.line: {namecode:13}, {namecode:13} still have a lot of anime to catch up on, Commander. At least let {namecode:13} finish the season she’s watching! Pretty please!

main2.line: It smells so, so good… {namecode:13} just can’t take it anymore and wants to have a bite.

main3.line: That being the case! What would {namecode:13} be like in another world… then?

touch.line: C-Commander, {namecode:13} is falling off from the plate, whoaaa—

touch2.line: Ha… So it turns out that the Commander already knew {namecode:13} is {namecode:13}...

unlock.line: {namecode:13}, {namecode:13} has been transformed into tea! What should we do! {namecode:14} and {namecode:13} will get slurped up by the Commander!

drop_descrip.line: Inazuma and I have been to a lot of festivals together, but this would be the first time that I've gone with you, Commander. Isn't this totally like a date?

main1.line: nil

main2.line: nil

main3.line: nil

detail.line: Commander! If you get the Inazuma DLC, you'll have a full set of wings!

drop_descrip.line: I'm the fairy of thunder that shatters the night to herald the dawn! I see, I see! That is a good backstory! Commander, want to head to the party together?

home.line: Going straight from grinding EXP to grinding at the party, huh? I'd expect nothing less of you, Commander!

login.line: Commander, finally decided to "log in," huh? Wanna join the party?

main1.line: I've brought a bunch of mouth-watering strawberries! Commander, wanna try one?

main2.line: We thought Akatsuki had gotten lost again, but Hibiki seems to have bumped into her. I see, I see, so that's what we call a "random encounter!"

main3.line: Don't you think this tooty manjuu is a bit annoying? ...You don't even see it, Commander?

touch.line: How am I supposed to fly with only one wing? ...Well, even if I had two, it probably still wouldn't work out!

unlock.line: I'm the fairy of thunder that shatters the night to herald the dawn! I see, I see! That is a good backstory! Commander, want to head to the party together?

battle.line: Hm... Huh?! We've been ambushed!

detail.line: Commander... it seems you're always holed up in your room...

drop_descrip.line: Type III {namecode:11}-class destroyer number four - {namecode:11}.

expedition.line: Commander... your "gasoline" and "resources" have arrived.

feeling1.line: Commander, no matter what you may become, I will always be with you.

feeling2.line: Commander, I will assist you.

feeling3.line: A shared sorrow is one made half, and shared joy is one made double. So please feel free to talk to me about anything.

feeling4.line: Commander, no matter where you go, I will always be with you. ... However... I don't think I can... leave the boundaries of this screen...

feeling5.line: Commander, it's terrible for your body eat junk food all the time. How about cooking your own food once in a while? Hm? Don't worry, I'll taste test it together with you!

home.line: Welcome back, Commander. Even if you didn't "acquire new characters",I will always be here.

login.line: Is that... you, Commander? I can't believe you're logging in at this time of day... shouldn't you be doing something else?

lose.line: Phew... Commander... you're very good at running away...

mail.line: You have mailophobia? ... You don't have to be scared, I'm here with you.

main1.line: Commander, your biggest flaw is how kind you are.

main2.line: {namecode:40}... she's helped me quite a lot...

main3.line: "Salvaging" is my specialty!

mission.line: If you leave your missions unfinished forever... then you'll end up having to do this bad thing called "overtime".

mission_complete.line: This month's bonus pay won't be postponed into the next month.

profile.line: I am... the Sakura Empire's {namecode:11}-class type III destroyer, {namecode:14}. As the youngest of my class, I participated in a lot of battles in the World War. But I prefer escorts, transports, and rescues over combat. ... Commander? Would you like to have your head patted too?

propose.line: Commander... please feel at ease. I would never abandon you. Even if you've had enough and run away, I will always, always be waiting here for you.

skill.line: If only everyone were here with us...

touch.line: Commander... could you pat my head?

touch2.line: Commander... there's no medicine that can fix you.

unlock.line: Are you the commander...? You don't seem very reliable... Ah, sorry, my self-introduction. My name is... {namecode:14}.

upgrade.line: Phew... I'm glad that didn't hurt as much as I thought.

win_mvp.line: ... I'M the MVP? ... Is this fleet... doing okay?

detail.line: Mr. Commander, after you swallowed {namecode:14} up... you must be ready to sortie.

login.line: ...{namecode:14}’s heartfelt wish, has it been communicated? …Mr. Commander...

main1.line: Are you hungry… Mr. Commander?

main2.line: Are you trying to find {namecode:14}, Mr. Commander? {namecode:14} is right in front of you.

main3.line: Mr. Commander, you’re always so gentle...

touch.line: Mr. Commander, are we starting this… please accept all of {namecode:14}, both the good and the bad—

touch2.line: Mr. Commander, have you heard {namecode:14}’s heartfelt words? You’re really amazing Mr. Commander!

unlock.line: It doesn’t matter if {namecode:14} becomes Mr. Commander's dessert… but if {namecode:14} cannot be found, Mr. Commander will feel so devastated, perhaps he won’t be able to command the fleet… so… please! Please convey {namecode:14}'s heartfelt wish to Mr. Commander——

detail.line: Commander, you didn't just buy these clothes for me because Ikazuchi asked you to, right? It doesn't bother me. Not one bit...

drop_descrip.line: I usually go to festivals with Ikazuchi, but this would be my first time going with you. Hmm? Where should we visit first?

feeling5.line: Commander, I know I'm super cute and all, but you'll develop social anxiety if you constantly cling to me and ignore everyone else. Since I'm also super responsible, you should go to the festival and enjoy the company of others.

home.line: Prioritizing work over Inazuma... Commander, you sure are a workaholic.

login.line: I was beginning to think that you forgot about our plans, Commander.

main1.line: Commander, I'd like some taiyaki. Is that okay?

main2.line: It feels unexpectedly nice to walk around without my shoes... Commander, why don't you try it too?

main3.line: Commander, you can go check out everyone's yukatas if you'd like. I'll look around by myself first.

touch.line: Commander, no matter how much you poke me, I won't have any Live2D.

unlock.line: I usually go to festivals with Ikazuchi, but this would be my first time going with you. Hmm? Where should we visit first?

detail.line: If you combine both of our wings, there might not be much room left on the screen... Why don't you edit it in and see for yourself, Commander?

drop_descrip.line: I'm the fairy of lightning that illuminates the stars in the night sky... So that's what we're going with, huh. Commander, will you accompany me to the party?

home.line: Whether you are fighting, taking care of commissions, or just checking daily missions, I will always be waiting for you here.

login.line: Commander, I'm glad you haven't forgotten the promise you made with me and Ikazuchi.

main1.line: Akatsuki said she wanted to join us so we can have a 6th DesDiv get-together at the party, but she seems to have gotten lost on the way... I hope Hibiki is able to find her.

main2.line: "The moon is beautiful tonight" is supposed to be a pretty famous line, right? Eh... How'd you already know about it, Ikazuchi?

main3.line: Ikazuchi seems to have brought you some strawberries. Judging from your expression, I'm... supposed to bring you blueberries?

touch.line: Commander, shall I bring you something to eat or drink?

unlock.line: I'm the fairy of lightning that illuminates the stars in the night sky... So that's what we're going with, huh. Commander, will you accompany me to the party?

battle.line: L-l-l-look out, get out of the way! My breaks aren't working!

detail.line: Commander, what are you looking at? Hm? Come on, tell me...

drop_descrip.line: {namecode:15}-class destroyer number one -  {namecode:15}.
