feeling1.line: Huh...? I got lost and ended up next to the commander... I'd better run...

feeling2.line: Huh? Commander? Thank goodness~ I thought I'd gotten lost again... You saw me leave and come back here 5 times? *Giggles* Then today's a surprisingly lucky day~

feeling3.line: Huh...? Commander? I realized a while back that I'm always by your side, did you cast some kind of magic on me?

feeling4.line: *Whimper*... Commander, you're being mean... I thought I'd do something to you in return~ So I'll let you hug me...

feeling5.line: Commander, recently whenever I see you I've wanted to tell you something, and I try to catch up to you, but then I forget what I wanted to say... It has to be something important... But what could it be...

home.line: Commander, you didn't get lost out there? Wooow!

login.line: Huh? So this is where you were, Commander... *Giggles*

lose.line: Gah... ow ow... what in the world hit me...?

mail.line: Commander, there's mail!

main1.line: Commander, did you see my torpedo? ... It went off somewhere suddenly.

main2.line: Weird... lately I seem to forget what I'm forgetting... What am I gonna do...

main3.line: *Yawn*... So tired... I hope the commander isn't looking... so I'll sleep for a bit longer...

mission.line: We've got a job to do! This time I won't forget!

mission_complete.line: Commander, I brought... Huh, what's this in my hand?

profile.line: I'm the first ship of the {namecode:15}-class, but I was meant to be part of the {namecode:30}-class... Anyway, where am I? Why am I introducing myself...? I don't really know... But I hope I can be of service.

propose.line: Ah! Now I remember what I wanted to say! But... you said it first... even though I wanted to be the first to say it...

skill.line: Huh? Where are we? Oh no, it's the enemy!

touch.line: *Yawn*... I get so tired when people touch me...

touch2.line: Whua... it feels weird when you touch me like that...

unlock.line: Um, I'm {namecode:15}, the first ship of the {namecode:15}-class... Hello, Commander. My name is {namecode:15}... Huh? I just said that? Hm... I don't know how to get back home, so I guess I'll stay here. I hope I can be of service.

upgrade.line: Huh... Commander, where are we? My body feels so warm...

win_mvp.line: All ships, open fire! Wa... wait... we've already won?

drop_descrip.line: H-here they come... Your order, and your cutesy dutesy maid... Whoaahh! I'm sorry! Look out!

lose.line: *Sob*... I messed up again...

main1.line: Commander, have you seen my torpedo...? Standing on it...? Wait... Oh noooo!

main2.line: nil

main3.line: Are you hungry, Commander? Umm, I have a sandwich... strawberry cake, and some coffee, if you want...

touch.line: Whooahhh! ... Gosh, that was too close... Thanks, Commander...

touch2.line: Eek! C-Commander! Look out!

unlock.line: H-here they come... Your order, and your cutesy dutesy maid... Whoaahh! I'm sorry! Look out!

battle.line: Awoo! I'm not gonna go easy on you all!

detail.line: Woof? ... What?

drop_descrip.line: {namecode:15}-class destroyer number four -  {namecode:16}.

expedition.line: Commander, a commission's been... A compliment's good enough, so stop patting my head!

feeling1.line: Hmph! ({namecode:16} ignored you.)

feeling2.line: Got any food?!

feeling3.line: "Grr! Who will I bite today?" How's that? Awfully violent, right? ... Good, now my sisters will stop telling me I'm like a dog outside of battle!

feeling4.line: My sisters are still laughing at me and it's your fault! What are you gonna do to fix it? I won't let you off the hook with... *Giggle*... with just a... *Giggle*... headpat...

feeling5.line: Commander, rub my belly… Huh? I've heard you should show your belly button when you're apologizing to someone... Next time I mess up I'll let you rub my belly, so don't get angry at me... Th-that tickles, ahahaha!

home.line: Commander, Commander, wanna eat something together?

hp_warning.line: I'll show you what the Nightmare of Solomon looks like!

login.line: Ugh, Commander... "Shake paws"?! Are you making fun of me?!

lose.line: Damn it, I can't believe… I lost…

mail.line: Hey, mail for you. Is it a challenge for me? I won't lose!

main1.line: Commander, seriously, stop throwing that frisbee at me. I'm not a dog~!

main2.line: *Sniff sniff* I smell meat! Where is it?! Tell me right now!

main3.line: It's so boring when I don't get to fight... Commander, wanna have a go? Let's do it!

mission.line: Another new mission? You adults sure are a pain...

mission_complete.line: Commander, Commander, hurry up and check the rewards to see if there are any snacks!

profile.line: I'm {namecode:16}! People call me the "Mad Dog of Solomon"! Heheh, I sound pretty strong, don't I? I'd never lose in a brawl! Hm? It's snack time? Commander, tell me where those snacks are!

propose.line: Pro... mise? What's that? You mean from now you'll always pat my head, never get angry when I screw up, and let me eat tons of tasty food?! Hell yeah, I'm in!

skill.line: Turn to junk floating in the Solomon Sea!

touch.line: Grr... Stop treating me like a kid.

touch2.line: Grr… I'll stuff you into guns and send you off to space, you damn molester!

unlock.line: I'm {namecode:16}, fourth ship of the {namecode:15}-class. I'll tell you this right now: I'm pretty loud at night, so brace yourself.

upgrade.line: Commander, take me out to the sea already. I really wanna test out my guns~

win_mvp.line: Missions involving breaking stuff are my specialty!

battle.line: Snowball fights are my specialty as well!

detail.line: It's cold? It doesn't feel cold at all to me!

drop_descrip.line: Come out of your office, Commander! You'll become lazy if you huddle up next to the heater all day! Let's go out and play in the snow!

login.line: The hell you looking so sad for, Commander? C'mon, let's roll around in the snow together!

main1.line: It's too warm in here, it's making me sleepy... Mmmh... Commander... meat... so yummy...

main2.line: Woof! Focus fire on the commander! Victory shall be mine!

main3.line: Gotta eat hotpot during winter, right? Hotpot? Let's make some hotpot!

touch.line: Shiratsuyu, Shigure, let's have a snowball fight!

unlock.line: Come out of your office, Commander! You'll become lazy if you huddle up next to the heater all day! Let's go out and play in the snow!

detail.line: Commander, look, these are my spoils of war! Ahh, I'm so glad that there's so much delicious meat to chow down on at the banquet!

drop_descrip.line: Commander, look at me, look at me! What do you think of my new outfit? If you like it, wanna give it a feel?

feeling5.line: Even though I had a ton of fun and ate a ton of yummy food tonight, nothing beats being at your side! Ehehe, Commander, play with me a bit more~

home.line: Awoooo! This skewer is so yummy! Nnh? Commander, want a bite? Here's a piece for you!

login.line: I heard there's gonna be a ton of meat at the banquet! I can't wait any longer!

main1.line: Erm, where'd Shigure go... I bet she went off to have one of her dumb contests with Yukikaze again!

main2.line: I heard there's also going to be a ball tonight. Commander, how do you dance?

main3.line: Be careful not to get my clothes dirty? Mhm, I already know! I really like this outfit too, so I'll take good care of it!

touch.line: Ehehe... Commander, are you taking me to get more delicious meat, or to have even more fun?

touch2.line: Commander! I'm gonna get super mad!

unlock.line: Commander, look at me, look at me! What do you think of my new outfit? If you like it, wanna give it a feel?

detail.line: A letter to Santa? Hell yeah, I'll write one too! "One huge cut of steak, thanks"... Bam, perfect!

drop_descrip.line: Christmas! The day Santa Claus drops by and leaves presents, right? Hell yeah, I'm pumped! Aren't you pumped too, Commander?

feeling5.line: I saw you, Commander! You were stuffing the stockings with presents last night! Which can only mean... you're buddies with Santa Claus! Hehehe, I really love you, Commander!

home.line: Before we go to bed, we gotta hang our stockings by the fireplace! Man, I can't wait for tomorrow morning! Heheh!

login.line: Hop onto my sleigh and we'll go for a ride, Commander!

main1.line: Check it out, this outfit's real easy to move in! Useful in a fight, too... Huh? No fighting? Dammit...

main2.line: Commander! Squeeze! ...See, Agano told me something nice would happen if I cradled your head like this! So, this "nice thing," what is it?

main3.line: Well... Since I pulled the sleigh last time, now it's your turn to do it, Commander!

touch.line: Woof? Playtime? Playtime!

unlock.line: Christmas! The day Santa Claus drops by and leaves presents, right? Hell yeah, I'm pumped! Aren't you pumped too, Commander?

battle.line: *Woof*! I won't let you lay a finger on the Commander!

detail.line: I dunno why, but wearing this makes me feel like I'm always by your side!

drop_descrip.line: Look, Commander! Isn't this kimono thing all, like, red and white and cool? I dig it! ... But what occasion is it for?

expedition.line: Commander, the commission team's back! ... Where's my headpat? C'mon, I want one!

feeling5.line: I don't get complicated stuff, but I know that I love you, Commander! Anyone who dares to try messing with you will first have to argue with my cannons!

hp_warning.line: You shredded my cherished clothes... Now you've made me MAD!

login.line: Commander! Heheheh~! I knew it was you just from the way you smell!

lose.line: Commander... It's impossible to fight while wearing this stuff...

mail.line: Commander, here's your mail! Hope I didn't get the wrong letter...

main1.line: Commander, you busy? If not, can we play? We can play whatever you want!

main2.line: Oh yeah, I tried making some food for you the other day, but I ended up wrecking the kitchen...

main3.line: When there's nobody to fight, just gazing at you keeps boredom away... Doesn't keep sleepiness away, though...

touch.line: Commander! Did I do something praiseworthy?! Heheheh~! Pat me, c'mon!

unlock.line: Look, Commander! Isn't this kimono thing all, like, red and white and cool? I dig it! ... But what occasion is it for?

battle.line: I'm gonna mess you up!

detail.line: Shake? S-sure... Wait, the heck are you making me do?!

drop_descrip.line: Woof...? Am I imagining it, or did you get shorter, Commander? Unless... it's me who's gotten bigger? Seriously?! Nobody told me retrofitting makes you taller!

expedition.line: Commission team just got back, Commander! ...Now, where's my headpat? Don't be stingy now!

home.line: Need a drink? No problem! Gonna go buy a slab of steak while I'm at it!

login.line: I'm starving here, man... Gimme a steak before we set out! C'mon!

main1.line: Shigure's still keepin' her rivalry with Yukikaze going... What's the point messing with the same person all the time?

main2.line: Oh yeah, it's snack time! What we having today, Commander? C'mon, tell me!

main3.line: Just watching Nowaki and Laffey makes me wanna doze off... Aw, crap! Nuh-uh, not sleepy in the least!

touch.line: Stop treating me like a kid already! Look how big I've grown!

touch2.line: Woof?!

unlock.line: Woof...? Am I imagining it, or did you get shorter, Commander? Unless... it's me who's gotten bigger? Seriously?! Nobody told me retrofitting makes you taller!

win_mvp.line: Victory's mine! Gimme a victory rub, Commander! I deserve a reward!

battle.line: Let's give a warm welcome to our foolish enemies~!

detail.line: Stupid Commander! Look at me again and I'll bite you!

drop_descrip.line: {namecode:15}-class destroyer number two -  {namecode:17}.

expedition.line: Hm? Guess it's time. Heheh, I don't even need to actually head out, for as long as I'm in the fleet, bountiful rewards are guaranteed♪

feeling1.line: I curse you with bad luck! You idiot!

feeling2.line: You want good luck? It's not something you can just get.

feeling3.line: Luck comes when you least expect it, you know? For example, like this! (Shigure jumps) ... Commander, maybe you caught a glimpse of my underwear just now~?

feeling4.line: Getting pranked by me is a lucky thing on its own, you dunce♪ Although I do like that about you.

feeling5.line: Heheh, silly Commander, you can rely on me as much as you want. I'll do anything you want~! As long as you love me like this, I'm yours♪

home.line: *Laughs* Guess who's back~!

hp_warning.line: We're gonna lose? That can't be~!

login.line: Commander! You're late! Go get ready~ I've been waiting for you.

lose.line: N... Not bad... You'd better remember this!

mail.line: I brought you your mail~ Now guess which hand I'm holding it with♪

main1.line: It's so peaceful... How about we play a game of luck?

main2.line: The gods seem to really love me, so hurry up and shower me with compliments♪

main3.line: You don't look too good. How about a torpedo to cheer you up?

mission.line: Huh? Work? Geez, it's ALWAYS about work...

mission_complete.line: *Tsk*... If it weren't for the rewards then who'd bother with these jobs...

profile.line: I'm {namecode:17}, ship number 2 of the {namecode:15}-class. I worked pretty hard in the First Fleet before I was reassigned to the Second Fleet and participated in the fated Battle of Leyte Gulf... I was the sole survivor, but I'll never forget the bravery everyone showed in that battle... {namecode:79}... {namecode:78}... how I miss you...

propose.line: You just can't be left alone, Commander... Worry not, I will stay by your side and take care of you forever♪

skill.line: I am {namecode:17} of Sasebo! Watch closely!

touch.line: Stop touching me! Don't blame me if something blows up!

touch2.line: Commander, let's play a game. I'll give you 5 minutes and if you haven't been caught by the police at that point then I'll withdraw my report~

unlock.line: I'm {namecode:17}, a {namecode:15}-class destroyer. I don't wanna brag, but I've got the Goddess of Luck watching over me~ Heheh, it's about time people acknowledged that luck is also a part of one's strength♪

upgrade.line: Mhm, making me stronger is a smart decision.

win_mvp.line: That was a good fight, considering how they suck♪

battle.line: Oxygen torpedoes: prepare for simultaneous launch!

feeling1.line: You are not worthy of the luck of Yukikaze the Great~

main1.line: Wa ha ha! Yukikaze the Great is invincible!

touch2.line: What are... you doing... nngh!? Go die!!

main2.line: My gothic dress? Heheh~ You might think I've gotten tired of hearing it, but... I shall allow you to praise the beauty of Yukikaze the Great! Haha!

main3.line: Swinging around too much shakes around your brain and makes you stupid...? And the only way to fix it is to stay in one spot and work? Really?! Um, I suppose... it can't be helped then...

I'll have you know I am not the namesake of my class for nothing, and I will defend Destroyer Division Eighteen's glory!

detail.line: ... Touch me in the wrong way and you will die.

expedition.line: I waited 1 whole minute for you, yet you did not realize that a commission had been completed… It really is true, you are a big fool who cannot do anything if I am not around.

feeling1.line: There exists no cure for your stupidity...

feeling2.line: I am the polar opposite of {namecode:19}… If she is light then I am shadow. Commander? Yes, of course, you are a big fool. I do not hate her, but who knows if I hate you…?

feeling3.line: I will come in the dead of night and devour you soul… I said, and you actually believed it? It was in fact my embers that chased away so many pests, and yet you thought I would harm you? You tremendous fool…

feeling4.line: What an idiotic, troublesome commander you are, wishing to make everyone happy… I simply cannot let your stupidity go unsupervised.

feeling5.line: *Sigh*... Would it not have been better if I could have been your guardian angel instead… Then I could always intervene… I mean, "protect" you when need be.

home.line: You may stare all you wish, but it will not make me start floating...

login.line: Could one say "long time no see," perhaps...?

lose.line: Curses upon you all…

mail.line: You seem to have "mail"… I should not have to help you with this too...

main1.line: Floating…

main2.line: I am bad at dealing with hotheads.

main3.line: You're standing beside me because I have a "cooling aura"…? Are you an idiot?

mission_complete.line: "Rewards" have arrived… Ah, do not task me with collecting them, you may do it yourself.

People mistakenly think my name refers to ghosts, but it is merely the name of a natural phenomena. I personally prefer to think of my appearance as a "cosplay"... That aside, I humbly ask for your kind treatment, you idio... my dear Commander.

skill.line: O, will-o'-wisps, join me for this strike...

touch.line: Enjoying yourself, are you?

touch2.line: You have a thing for ghosts? You really are something...

unlock.line: I am {namecode:20}, the second ship of the {namecode:19}-class... I humbly ask for your kind treatment, Commander.

upgrade.line: You certainly are a big fool, spending such precious resources on me…

win_mvp.line: I never imaged they would be this weak…

detail.line: Commander, did you come to help out? To thank you, I shall offer you a 20-percent discount on these mooncakes...

drop_descrip.line: Mooncake Merchant

feeling5.line: I heard that in the Dragon Empery, the Mid-Autumn Festival is a time to be reunited with your loved ones. Commander, are you going to go watch the moon with your favorite girl? ... You want to go with me? Saying that won't get you anywhere... Fine, Commander, as a token of my appreciation, I'll give you a 50% discount.

home.line: That dumb Akashi, why'd she have to go and order so many of these... when am I going to be able to clear out this stock...?

login.line: Happy Mid-Autumn Festival... I hope I said that right...?

main1.line: Lotus seed mooncakes, osmanthus mooncakes, five-nut mooncakes... If it sells well, it's a good mooncake, wouldn't you agree?

main2.line: These sky lanterns look just like the full moon tonight. Commander, would you like one?

main3.line: These mooncakes are one hundred percent authentic, unlike the tech p... Err, I didn't say anything.

touch.line: Commander, you'll have to pay for anything that you touch.

touch2.line: Commander, why don't you calm down with a nice cup of tea...? Poured on top of your head, that is.

drop_descrip.line: If you have this much money remaining... then you may visit me and spend it with confidence... A discount, you say...? Of course... Someday, I shall give you one...

home.line: Gawking won't earn you a... *Groan*... Then just for beverages, I could give you... F-fifty percent off.

main1.line: Commander, you can make up for quality with quantity. Believe in yourself and pursue your dreams...

main2.line: Work diligently and you will only be a fool by your appearance.

main3.line: I take my work both as a secretary and shopkeeper seriously... If I feel like it... I could offer you a 5% discount.

touch.line: Yes, yes, your wish has been heard. Please make your way yonder to amuse yourself with my will-o'-wisps.

touch2.line: Groping a shopkeeper like this... is surely not a turn-on of yours...?

unlock.line: If you have this much money remaining... then you may visit me and spend it with confidence... A discount, you say...? Of course... Someday, I shall give you one...

battle.line: I can't fall asleep now...!

detail.line: The Leyte Gulf? I don't remember very much of it...

drop_descrip.line: {namecode:19}-class destroyer number fifteen -  {namecode:24}.

expedition.line: Someone's come back... Is it lunchtime now...?

feeling1.line: ... I can't sleep with you next to me...

feeling2.line: Movies? They aren't really my thing...

feeling3.line: {namecode:130}... I promise I'll help you this time...!

feeling4.line: I tried too hard to be brave in Leyte Gulf... In the end I couldn't save anyone...

feeling5.line: Zzz... Commander... It's fine to take some time off and nap every now... and then... Zzz...

home.line: Commander... *Yawn*... Today's weather is perfect for a nap...

hp_warning.line: W-what's going on?!

login.line: Zzz... Fiiine, I'll get up in a second... The sun... is so warm... Zzz...

lose.line: Where... am I? Who's shooting at me?

mail.line: I don't really need a bedtime story...

main1.line: If only I'd tried harder when I was in Truk...

main2.line: I like this place, I don't need to hurt any of my allies here...

main3.line: {namecode:25}... {namecode:22}... We're all together again in my dreams...

mission.line: A-a mission? I hope it won't be difficult...

mission_complete.line: Your rewards won't disappear even if you don't collect them... I think...

I was unable to save {namecode:130} in Truk, but when I was in the Leyte Gulf I came running to {namecode:62}'s rescue. In the end I couldn't save everyone... but in my dreams we're all still together...

propose.line: This is... proof of a sisterly bond?! Commander, you want to be my sister? ... I've got it all wrong?! But that's what {namecode:130}-chan told me...

touch.line: Huh, what? Commander...? *Giggle*... *Yawn*...

touch2.line: *Giggle*... You're like {namecode:130}-chan, Commander...

unlock.line: This place is... Huh? Are you the commander?! Ahem! Destroyer {namecode:24}, reporting in!

upgrade.line: Zzz... Huh? It's over already?

win_mvp.line: Hm? I'M the MVP?! What a lucky day!

battle.line: I-I'll give it all I've got!

detail.line: C-Commander, um... I-I'm glad you're c-checking in on me, but...

drop_descrip.line: {namecode:30}-class destroyer number one – {namecode:30}.

expedition.line: Commander, um, the commission team is back... I-I should go greet them? N-n-n-no, there's no way!

feeling1.line: C-Commander, i-if you get any closer then I'll s-shoot you!

feeling2.line: C-Commander, do you think it's possible for me to get over my fear of s-strangers...?

feeling3.line: Umm, C-Commander... C-can I ask you to be my... conversation practice partner...? I-I... want to make friends with everyone in the fleet...

feeling4.line: *Sob*... I can't, I-I can't do it! ... B-but maybe I can hold a conversation with you, Commander...

login.line: *Cries*... I can't possibly be a secretary...

lose.line: *Cries*... I really am not suited for combat...

mail.line: Commander... Y-you have mail...

main1.line: I miss my sisters so much...

main2.line: C-Commander... p-please don't stare at me so much...

main3.line: I-I'm quite timid, b-but I'll work really hard! ... I hope...

skill.line: P-please get out of the way, everyone...!

touch.line: I need to talk with you more oft... Eek?!

touch2.line: ...!! (It seems {namecode:30} has fainted.)

unlock.line: I-i-it's nice to meet you, I-I'm Hatsuha... U-um... P-please don't stare at me so much...!

upgrade.line: I hope I can be of service to everyone...

win_mvp.line: Did we... win?

unlock.line: Woah... These stalls have all sorts of amazing things~ Commander, will you help me pick a gift out for Ariake? Hm, let's see... How about this Daruma doll?

detail.line: Commander, what do you think is the proper way to play on the beach? ...You want to hear my opinion instead? Um, I... I think I like the stuff the kids do...

drop_descrip.line: I was really looking forward to playing with you at the beach, Commander, so I changed into this swimsuit. Umm... Ariake told me that I had to choose something that was easy to move around in, and cute enough to make you lose your mind... Was she pulling my leg?

home.line: Hatsuharu taught me that adding a twang of salt to watermelon brings out a completely different flavor. If you'd like to give it a try... It's great, isn't it? I'm glad you liked it!

login.line: The weather has been great all day. It's perfect for swimming or sunbathing.

main1.line: First, do some stretching... Okay! It's finally time for my debut match of beach volleyball, right? Ariake is watching me too, so I've got to do my best!

main2.line: Wearing a fancy swimsuit like this is a little embarrassing for me. C-Commander, do you think something easier to move around in like what Wakaba is wearing would be better?

main3.line: Making a sand castle is a lot harder than I expected... How did Takao and the others manage to build something like THAT...?

touch.line: Shall I bring you some fruit juice?

touch2.line: Mmgh... The sun's making me all sweaty... Hwaah?! Commander??

unlock.line: I was really looking forward to playing with you at the beach, Commander, so I changed into this swimsuit. Umm... Ariake told me that I had to choose something that was easy to move around in, and cute enough to make you lose your mind... Was she pulling my leg?

win_mvp.line: Battle complete. This is a victory that Ariake and the others can be proud of!

detail.line: Here you go, Commander. Um, your tea! It's Ariake's favorite kind, but I do not know if it will be to your liking or not...

drop_descrip.line: Ariake-class destroyer, Yuugure, has completed retrofitting. Ehehe, from now on... Ariake and I will be in your care once more, Commander.

expedition.line: A commission has been completed. Commander, please make sure to stockpile our resources for construction.

feeling5.line: The gentle sea breeze, the warm sunlight, and the sound of waves upon the beach... Every day here at port is filled with happiness, because I can be together with both you and Ariake...

home.line: Welcome back, Commander. I'm preparing tea for Ariake, so please wait a moment for me to bring you yours.

main1.line: I feel like I've gotten a little taller after my retrofit... and it makes Ariake seem shorter in comparison... Ugh...

main2.line: (whispers) Hatsushimo, you'll trouble Commander if you do that! ...I-I wasn't saying anything!

main3.line: Wakaba, Commander, I have some walnut daifuku for you. Um, huh...? You don't need the wrapping...?

unlock.line: Ariake-class destroyer, Yuugure, has completed retrofitting. Ehehe, from now on... Ariake and I will be in your care once more, Commander.

upgrade.line: Hiei, this time... I swear...!

win_mvp.line: Ariake, Commander, I did it! Mhm... I really won!

battle.line: Naught but death awaits those who oppose my master.

detail.line: Your Grace... Please don't stare at me so...

drop_descrip.line: Kagerou-class destroyer number three – Kuroshio.

expedition.line: Your Grace, the fleet you dispatched on commission has returned as scheduled.

feeling1.line: ... Your orders?

feeling2.line: A true ninja has no need of emotion. She needs only her master's will to execute.

feeling3.line: While I struggle with Your Grace's concepts of "communication" and "games," still... I... can't say I dislike them.

feeling4.line: Your Grace, I beg your pardon. Recently I find myself distracted from the mission, thinking again and again about Your Grace's "communication." Please, you must punish me...

feeling5.line: So this is an "emotion"... before such things I had no problem keeping a clear head, but even now it seems not so wicked... Yes, this "emotion" drives a powerful need to stand by Your Grace's side, and it grows ever stronger.

home.line: Your Grace, are you tired? Is there any way I can be of assistance to you?

login.line: Your Grace, welcome home.

lose.line: Your Grace, it is time to retreat. I will cover your withdrawal.

mail.line: Your Grace, a letter has arrived.

main1.line: Hm...? Your Grace? Did you want me to say something?

main2.line: I am not sure what to say... But I would be happy to listen to anything Your Grace wishes to impart.

main3.line: The flower in my hair? It was a gift from Oyashio. Oyashio, she's... very colorful.

mission.line: Your Grace, a new mission has been issued.

mission_complete.line: Your Grace, mission rewards have been issued. Inspect them at your leisure.

profile.line: Third ship of the Kagerou-class, Kuroshio. As part of the 2nd Fleet and Destroyer Division 15, I joined in the Battle of the Java Sea, operations in the South Pacific, the Third Battle of the Solomon Islands, and other engagements until I was sunk during a transport mission. ... I will not let that happen again. I will commit all of my resources to ensure that I am of service to Your Grace.

propose.line: I once thought that absolute devotion to the mission was all there was to being a ninja, but I have learned so much from you, Commander... I, Kuroshio, from this point forward, am no longer your shadow alone, Commander, I am now your partner. And we will stand together until the end of our days.

touch.line: Kuroshio, awaiting orders.

touch2.line: As this body belongs to Your Grace, please do with it as you will... Nnng... Aaaah...

unlock.line: Third ship of the Kagerou-class, Kuroshio reporting in... I am here to carry out my master's will.

upgrade.line: I stand ready to execute your will.

win_mvp.line: I am Your Grace's shadow. I have no need of glory or acclaim.

battle.line: Come one, come all!

detail.line: Commander, don't I look ninja-like when I do this with my hands? Ehehe, that's because Kuro taught me~

drop_descrip.line: Kagerou-class destroyer number four – Oyashio.

expedition.line: Commander~ The commission's done.

feeling1.line: No matter what you do, Commander, Kuroshio has no problem following you... But I'm not so forgiving. For her sake, Commander, en garde!

feeling2.line: Commander, would you like to watch my show? By all means, come on over and take a seat~ The more the merrier, after all!

feeling3.line: As a ninja, my sister is always very serious... And since I'm a puppeteer, I always thought it would be nice to make her laugh sometimes. That's kind of a tall order though, ahaha...

feeling4.line: Commander, you're awesome. Not only do you know what I'm thinking, but you help me get through to everyone else... One day, I'm going to make Kuroshio laugh, and I know you'll definitely be there to see it!

feeling5.line: Commander, I thought it would be great to be as clear-headed as Kuroshio... But there's no way I could. I like Kuroshio, I like you, and I like puppet shows. That's just who I am.

home.line: Kuro, why don't you give the Commander a massage? Yes, I think hopping around the shoulders should do the trick?

login.line: Commander, how are you today? Would you care to enjoy one of my famous puppet shows? Come on! How about it?

lose.line: Ugh! Commander! Quickly, take the others and run!

mail.line: Commander, guess which torpedo has your mail in it? If you're wrong... well, it probably won't blow up♪

main1.line: Commander, will you come to watch my show when you have free time?

main2.line: Kuro is my dear friend! Her namesake is obvious, isn't it? My oh so serious big sister!

main3.line: Of course the strings are a puppetry thing. So why do I put torpedoes on them? Ahaha... Let's call it an old trade secret.

mission.line: Commander, let's go knock out one of those new missions~ I need to get some new material♪

mission_complete.line: Commander, the mission rewards are here~ Let me see if there's any props I can use in there♪

profile.line: I'm the fourth ship of the Kagerou-class, Oyashio. I've always been close with Kuroshio. She can tell you everything you need to know, so just ask her~♪ Oh, unless...? You'd rather I act it out for you?

propose.line: And so the Commander and Oyashio lived happily ever after for all the rest of their days... Ehehe, even if the audience might get sick of it, I'm hoping the rest of our story is a long, happy comedy♪

skill.line: The fun has only just begun, right~♪

touch.line: Commander, isn't it amazing how nurturing Oyashio is? ... Er! I'm talking about the ocean current!

touch2.line: Huh?! Grraagh! ... Oh, Commander, I'm sorry... that's just how we've been trained in this line of work...

unlock.line: My big sister is a ninja, and I'm a puppeteer. Isn't it amazing how diverse our world is~? I'm the fourth ship of the Kagerou-class, Oyashio. And with my puppet Kuro, I will dazzle you, Commander.

upgrade.line: Oooh! I just came up with a new idea for a show!

win_mvp.line: And thus, the Commander led our fleet to another victory! That's the end of this episode!

battle.line: Shall I assume command? Understood! I won't disappoint you!

detail.line: Houshou's carrot cake is just divine! I hope to taste it again sometime.

drop_descrip.line: Shimakaze-class destroyer – Shimakaze.

expedition.line: Hmm... Commission teams don't run into ambushes out at sea, do they...?

feeling1.line: If you manage to right all your wrongs, then maybe you'll earn my forgiveness!

feeling2.line: I am THE strongest destroyer! Or, so I'd like to think. But to truly become the strongest, I'll have to hone myself through my training and sorties!

feeling3.line: People often say I'm too hasty, but isn't swift decision-making supposed to be a good thing? Plus, if you don't fight with all you've got, it could come back to haunt you! Hehehe!

feeling4.line: Commander, what things motivate you to keep fighting? I'm just asking out of curiosity. Whatever they are, I will fight for them alongside you! ...Yes, I know, I swear not to get ahead of myself this time!

feeling5.line: Could we go somewhere together after finishing our work today? B-because, well, we hardly get any time for ourselves during office hours... Okay, look! I'm saying I want some alone time with you, Commander! Would you... oblige?

headtouch.line: Mweeehhh... Please, d-don't touch my ears! It makes me shooo weak... Aaaahh...

home.line: W-welcome back, Commander! ...No, it's nothing, really! I was just wondering when you'd return...

hp_warning.line: Don't die on me now, engines... Please hang in there!

login.line: Commander, you're not the type to dilly-dally around, are you? That makes two of us! We'd better begin our work for the day!

lose.line: I-I'll reflect upon my errors...

mail.line: Apropos of nothing, I think you should check your latest mail.

main1.line: My rigging calibration checks out. I'm fully prepared to sortie at your command!

main2.line: My shoes? They're quite special. In fact, these shoes are what allow me to go faster than everyone else! Ha-hah!

main3.line: The Sakura Empire is home to many sword-wielding shipgirls... If I ever get the chance, I'd love to borrow and swing someone else's sword for myself.

main4.line: Any two people can come to an understanding as long they're both willing to listen! That's what I've always believed!

mission.line: Aha! I spy with my little eye incomplete missions! Full speed ahead for those rewards! Right, Commander?

mission_complete.line: Mission completed! Quick, let's check what rewards we've earned!

profile.line: I'm Shimakaze, the sole Shimakaze-class destroyer! I boast the highest speed and best torpedo capabilities of all fleet destroyers – a pivotal part of any torpedo squadron! No type of operation is beyond my capabilities! Ha-hah!

propose.line: What is THIS?! Wasn't this meant to be an emergency mission briefing?! Wait, what's this ring...? I fell for it, hook, line, and sinker! But why trick me into coming? I would've agreed to it if you'd just told the truth!

skill.line: Maybe I should turn this into one of my secret moves!

touch.line: Huh? Have I done something incorrectly?

touch2.line: Eek! What has gotten into you?! If I didn't know any better, I'd think... Well, just this once, I'll turn a blind eye to it.

unlock.line: I am Shimakaze, the world's one and only Shimakaze-class destroyer! You must be the commander! Let us join forces and work towards our goals, together!

upgrade.line: I can become even faster... even stronger!

win_mvp.line: All right! Another first-place finish!

battle.line: I'm truly in my element in this outfit!

detail.line: Commander! Why not play a round of Shipgirl Bounty Hunter? There are many nice prizes you can win!

drop_descrip.line: Hippity hoppity! Grab a glass and have a sippity! Whew, I must say, this outfit was tricky to get into. Still, you made an exquisite pick, Commander!

home.line: Outstanding work! I will provide tonight's entertainment act! As soon as I come up with something entertaining... Hmm...

login.line: I'm positively brimming with energy! Tonight, let us "party hard," Commander!

main1.line: Abukuma invited me to go fishing with her! So, I'm going out to meet– Y-you think it's best if I change clothes first?

main2.line: Suruga! You should try a bunny girl costume too! ...Y-you wouldn't be caught dead in one? Isn't that a little extreme, even for an aversion?!

main3.line: These frills fit around my ears perfectly! Which is good, because I'd become lethargic if they were too tight...

touch.line: Would you like a refill, Commander?

touch2.line: There being no danger of skirt-flipping doesn't make this tolerable behavior!

unlock.line: Hippity hoppity! Grab a glass and have a sippity! Whew, I must say, this outfit was tricky to get into. Still, you made an exquisite pick, Commander!

win_mvp.line: I'm the fastest, strongest destroyer... And that's a fact!

detail.line: The sheer scale of this set is staggering! I've run around all over the place and still found no sign of the exit... What?! I've been going in circles all this time?!

drop_descrip.line: Whoa-whoa-whoa! Why'd I end up here again?! Even though I've been running for a whole hour! ...Commander?! Waaaah, I'm so glad to see you! Please, help me get out of heeeeeeere!

expedition.line: The commission team has come back! But as it stands now, we can't meet them!

home.line: Ah, Commander! Heehee~ I stumbled across this delicious tea just earlier! Join me on a break and we'll drink it together!

login.line: After much thinking, I've realized that I'm not Alice, but rather the White Rabbit! So isn't it weird that I'm lost in here?

main1.line: Whoa! There's cake over there! Heehee... No, Commander! Finding the exit comes first, like I told you before!

main2.line: If Suruga was here, how would she... Wait, COULD Suruga even find a way out of this place? Because I am completely out of ideas!

main3.line: There's the exit! Watch, I'm going to make a mad dash for– Owie! Th-this is just a dang mirror!

mission.line: Laffey could find a way out if she were here... Whoa! Word of a new mission just came in!

touch.line: Mhm! Allow me to show you the right path to your destination!

touch2.line: At least it's not my... No, ears or not, it's embarrassing when you touch me like that!

unlock.line: Whoa-whoa-whoa! Why'd I end up here again?! Even though I've been running for a whole hour! ...Commander?! Waaaah, I'm so glad to see you! Please, help me get out of heeeeeeere!

win_mvp.line: Hippity hoppity! That's what happens when you underestimate me!

battle.line: I fight at peak performance even in this swimsuit!

detail.line: Hippity hoppity! Let's go for a swim in the sea! It'll be a boatload of fun, Commander!

drop_descrip.line: You can't keep sprinting across the sea forever. Sometimes, you need to rest and recover your strength. Speaking of, you may use my parasol if you like, Commander!

home.line: Welcome back, Commander! I just got back as well – from a long swim, in my case!

login.line: Please sit over here and relax, Commander! I'm going for a quick run around!

lose.line: I'm almost more scared of being pursued by sharks than the enemy...

main1.line: Naganami must surely hate getting her tail wet... One could say the same about my ears, I suppose.

main2.line: Now, now, Kii, please don't try to pressure Suruga into... Wow! You'll really let me take her place in the beach volleyball tournament?

main3.line: I don't need sunscreen – I can simply dart in and out of the shade! Fwoosh, fwoosh!

touch.line: Whatever it is you need, I'm all ears.

touch2.line: Do you think this is acceptable in broad daylight?! Please!

unlock.line: You can't keep sprinting across the sea forever. Sometimes, you need to rest and recover your strength. Speaking of, you may use my parasol if you like, Commander!

detail.line: Would you like a mooncake, Commander? This batch was made specifically for the occasion. I can personally vouch for their good taste!

drop_descrip.line: Oh no! Commander, look out! ...Phew. That was really close. Apologies for my clear lack of attentiveness! I shouldn't have been in such a rush to deliver all these mooncakes...

expedition.line: The commission team has returned! I'll go deliver them a couple of mooncakes! Hippity hoppity!

home.line: Welcome back, Commander! Today is a day to celebrate with friends and family, so let us all get together and enjoy ourselves! I will join you, of course!

login.line: Hippity! This feels like a terribly unlucky day for me! ...Oh no! The mooncakes!

mail.line: One mooncake, two, three... Wait, a letter? Oh, right, I was supposed to deliver this to you, Commander!

main1.line: Kii! Who's the lady in your company? ...Oh! A friend of Suruga, I see! Say, could I ask you to tell me where she is? I'd like to share my mooncakes with her!

main2.line: These mooncakes aren't the biggest, but they are quite dense. I've only had one, yet I feel stuffed as a turkey!

main3.line: Whoa! Nice catch, little manjuus! Better pick these mooncakes up quickly, before... Oh no! Now that manjuu pounding mochi fell over!

touch.line: Ugh, running too fast can be dangerous after all... *sniffle*

touch2.line: Whoa! Commander?! Please! This is NOT how you're supposed to act!

unlock.line: Oh no! Commander, look out! ...Phew. That was really close. Apologies for my clear lack of attentiveness! I shouldn't have been in such a rush to deliver all these mooncakes...

battle.line: Watch out for them submarines and torpedoes. Full speed ahead!

detail.line: Hoho~ What about me's gotten you so interested?

drop_descrip.line: {namecode:124}-class destroyer number one – {namecode:124}.

expedition.line: Guess the commission team's back again all in one piece. Hum hum, splendid!

feeling1.line: You're more boring than I ever imagined, Commander.

feeling2.line: Commander, only rookies and small-timers judge equipment by how new it is.

feeling3.line: My hobbies? 3 rounds of food and sleep and a bit of teasin' you. Hohoho~! That look there is what I wanted to see.

feeling4.line: Well, Commander, what type of girl do you fancy~? Me? Maybe someone more refined? ... But is that really true? Right, I've got that on tape now~! Now the question is: who will I play it to~?

feeling5.line: Commander... Ya know, I like you~ Oh dear, your face is all red~ So red it's even reached your ears~!

home.line: Look at you, back safe and sound! Reward yourself with a sip of my nutritious drink! Hey now, don't be shy~!

login.line: Aha, you've finally showed up~! Will we be doin' anything interesting today?

lose.line: Ugh... Should've known I can't keep up like this...

mail.line: Mail, eh... It ain't an errand from the Union, is it...?

main1.line: Winners are those who hold out 'till the very end!

main2.line: Hawksbill! That girl couldn't beat me, but she put up a real good fight.

main3.line: Those Fifth Carrier Division folks... they're pretty nice...

mission.line: Duties, eh. How's about we go give it a look?

mission_complete.line: Hm? Payment for those duties? Right then, take care bringing 'em here!

profile.line: I'm {namecode:124}, {namecode:124}-class destroyer number one. I was a part of the First Destroyer Division. My name's got a mighty ring to it, don'tcha think? Hoho~! I fought in numerous battles in the Pacific Islands since the start of the World War, so me being a fleet veteran ain't just for show or me being whimsical. I may not look it, but ASW is my forte. Every time I think about my battle with that wolf pack my blood starts to boil~

propose.line: Commander, it ain't too late to change your mind yet~ Yeah, that's it, take your time thinking about me~ Hm? The door? Oh no, it looks like it's been locked shut~ What will we do~?

skill.line: Sorry, ain't got time for one-on-ones.

touch.line: Oh? You need somethin'?

touch2.line: Well well, looks like your naughty desires are starting to show themselves. How about an exorcism for ya?

unlock.line: {namecode:124}, First Destroyer Division ship number one, has arrived. Are you certain you're the commander? Then things are gonna get interesting from now on. *Giggle* Enjoy watching me do my work~

upgrade.line: Yup, I'm just oozing with energy~ Hoho~! Now I can go on another rampage~

win_mvp.line: You see this? This is what years of experience looks like!

drop_descrip.line: Ohohoho, you must have a sharp eye if you've decided to retrofit me~ Now that I've been chosen, I cannot afford to embarrass you. Now, take a good and thorough look at this veteran's aspirations~

main1.line: I went for a romp with some of those Mutsuki-class children, but they proved no more than a bothersome bunch of pipsqueaks.

main2.line: My wind chime? It quite strikes my fancy, though it is a bit too large. Watch yourself so you don't get whacked by it!

main3.line: Ah, Haguro, Ashigara, and Myoukou... How I miss the days of watching over those younglings~

touch.line: Aren't you a needy commander. You require my assistance, do you, now?

unlock.line: Ohohoho, you must have a sharp eye if you've decided to retrofit me~ Now that I've been chosen, I cannot afford to embarrass you. Now, take a good and thorough look at this veteran's aspirations~

win_mvp.line: Being in the first Destroyer Division and being the first of my class, it's only natural I also get first place!

battle.line: Don't do anything too dangerous, okay?

detail.line: I wonder how my sisters are doing... I'm worried about them...

drop_descrip.line: Kamikaze-class destroyer number four – Matsukaze.

expedition.line: The commission team is back, Commander. It's not nice to keep them waiting!

feeling1.line: Sigh... Where did I go wrong with you...

feeling2.line: If you don't have anything to do, you should tidy things up. Organization is fundamental to leading a good life.

feeling3.line: Yeah... I'm pretty bad with electronics... You should teach me how to properly use them, Commander!

feeling4.line: Lately when I'm alone, I've been asking myself "is the commander taking care of himself?," "is he eating enough?," "does he think about me?"... Ahh, never mind that last one!

feeling5.line: You just need to focus on your goals and I'll handle all the minor details. I'm happy to help you with anything, not just combat or missions~!

home.line: You must be tired after that last battle... Don't overexert yourself, come here and lie down.

login.line: You can't fight on an empty stomach, Commander! I made lots and lots of food, so eat to your heart's content!

lose.line: Ugh... I'll be fine, just make a break for it, everyone...

mail.line: Letter for you, Commander! Want me to read it out loud?

main1.line: This thing I've got? It's what's known as a ladle. Yeah, if it was a little smaller you could even serve tea with it.

main2.line: This place is lacking in greenery... We should put some potted plants in here, Commander~!

main3.line: Ahhh, the smell of laundry hung out to dry in the sun~ Isn't it great?

mission.line: Are you doing your duty properly, Commander? I'm here if you need me.

mission_complete.line: You've done great, Commander. Bravo, bravo!

profile.line: I'm the Kamikaze-class destroyer Matsukaze! I was in Destroyer Division 5 along with my sisters. We're a little outdated compared to something like the Mutsuki-class, but we won't let any newer classes beat us when it comes to combat or escorts! ...Sigh... I wonder how Asakaze's team will fare without me...

propose.line: You're saying you want to take a lifelong vow with me? Eheheh, sure~ Then I, Matsukaze, swear to always, always look after you!

skill.line: Don't you dare try to hurt my commander!

touch.line: Yeah? Are you feeling tired? Then wait just a moment, I've finished making some snacks!

touch2.line: Eek?! ...Commander, sit right over there! You need to be scolded!

unlock.line: This is the fleet everyone's in, right? Seems pretty rowdy~ I'm Matsukaze! Nice meeting you!

upgrade.line: Thanks! You could have saved caring about me for later, though.

win_mvp.line: Heheh, you'll have a really bad time if you underestimate a veteran!

detail.line: I doubt this fan will be of any use when it gets cold...

drop_descrip.line: There we go... My fan is too big, and I'm not used to carrying it around yet... Ah, right, come here for a sec, Commander~ I'll fan you with some cool air~ Come on now, no need to be shy~

login.line: Welcome back, Commander! How are you? Hungry? Then have a seat, I'll go get you something to eat!

main1.line: I think this thing will be handy for drying clothes or futons out in the sun! Mhm, I think I'll test it right now!

main2.line: Commander, look! There's a big "matsu" written on my fan! Mhm, I have to say I'm quite fond of it~!

main3.line: Umm... have you heard about "work-life balance"? It's bad to rest too much, but it's not good to work too much either.

touch.line: Hm? Are you hungry? Or do you want me to fan you?

unlock.line: There we go... My fan is too big, and I'm not used to carrying it around yet... Ah, right, come here for a sec, Commander~ I'll fan you with some cool air~ Come on now, no need to be shy~

battle.line: Ah! Those are the meanies who steal people's candy!

detail.line: Candy is the best snack!

drop_descrip.line: {namecode:33}-class destroyer number one – {namecode:33}.

expedition.line: Comainder! The older girls are back! I wonder if they brought me any candy?

feeling1.line: Where's {namecode:34}... I miss her...

feeling2.line: Both candies look tasty... I can't choose a single one... Help me pick, Commander!

feeling3.line: Comaindeeeer! Let's play together! What should we play? You pick, Comainder!

feeling4.line: Comainder! Let's play house! You'll be daddy and I'll be mommy!

feeling5.line: "Hey! Did you go out to meet that woman again today? ... Are you still trying to hide it from me?! You... you reek of adultery!" ... Huh? I saw it on TV! ... What does it mean? I dunno!

home.line: I'll take some candy while the comainder's still... Oh!

login.line: You want some candy too, Comainder? You're not getting any of mine!

lose.line: *Sob*... Comainder...

mail.line: Comainder, you have mail! If you want it you'll have to give me candy!

main1.line: Co... main... der? I can't pronounce that... "Mommy" and "daddy" are easier to pronounce!

main2.line: First apple, then mango... next time I'll buy one that tastes like strawberry!

main3.line: One, two, three, four... I forgot... six... after that comes... eleven! Then nineteen! I did it!

mission.line: Mish... shun? What's that? Is that a candy?

mission_complete.line: Rewards, rewards~! Candy, candy~!

profile.line: I'm {namecode:33}, I'm in the "Thirtieth Destroyer Division," and I'm the oldest {namecode:33}-class ship! There are newer ships, but I'm strong! I love candy! I hate Stu... Um... I can't pronounce that... Stookuhs? I hate those!

propose.line: Prow... miss? Does that mean we're close friends? Hm... Okay! Comainder, I'll give you some candy! That makes us close friends!

skill.line: I'll show you how powerful candy is~!

touch.line: I won't give you my candy, even if you are the comainder!

touch2.line: Comainder, that tickles!

unlock.line: Co... main... der? Are you like my mommy or daddy? Hm? Ah, it's Commander! This my candy, I'm not giving you any!

upgrade.line: Will you give me more candy now? ... You won't?!

win_mvp.line: We won~!

home.line: If you're tired from walking, we could take a break at that bench up there. Erm, I took the liberty of bringing some light handmade foods...

login.line: Commander, I hear seaside strolls are great for blue-skies days like today. I can show you around, if you'd like!

main1.line: The sunlight's a little harsh in the afternoons... Commander, w-would you like to come under my parasol with me? I-it may be useful practice for... physical affection, too.

main2.line: I was so excited and busy planning last night that I didn't get much sleep. When I relax, I get so sleepy... No, Umikaze, you have to try harder... Zzz...

main3.line: Yamakaze gets a plushie, but what souvenir would Kawakaze like? Commander, do you have any advice?

mission_complete.line: Mission complete! Ehehe... The seagulls seem happy, too.

touch.line: C'mon, Umikaze! You're brave enough to hold hands by now!

touch2.line: Eep! C-Commander...

unlock.line: Commander, it is my pleasure to accompany you today. Umm... What do you think? I decided to go for a different outfit this time... D-do you think it's cute?

win_mvp.line: Did I manage to help? Thank goodness!

battle.line: Woo! Follow my lead!

detail.line: Hehe~ You wanna play with me, Commander?

drop_descrip.line: Shiratsuyu-class destroyer number eight – Yamakaze.

expedition.line: Commander! Our commission buddies brought back heaps of good stuff!

feeling1.line: Grrrrr! (Yamakaze is wary of you.)

feeling2.line: When those mean Meowfficers gang up on me, I scare them off with a roar!

feeling3.line: Commander, Commander! I wanna play with you! We could call over Umikaze and Kawakaze, too!

feeling4.line: Could we please go to the zoo, Commander? I wanna listen to the cries seagulls, and bears, and dolphins!

feeling5.line: You're always so nice to me, so I'm gonna be nice back! If any baddies show up, I'll send them scurrying back to mama! ...Huh? You'll protect ME instead? But... why?

headtouch.line: Rooooar!

home.line: You're back? Here, the seat's all yours!

hp_warning.line: Owwieee...

login.line: Woooo! I'm pumped and ready to do some work!

lose.line: Bwaahh! Get me outta here!

mail.line: I've got your mail right here, Commander!

main1.line: If you don't play with me right now, I'm gonna roar at you! Fine... Rooooar!

main2.line: Hey, Kawakaze! Have some fun for once and come play with me and Umikaze!

main3.line: Being lazy is super lame, Commander! Come on, you've gotta work!

mission.line: New missions have come in! Let me at 'em!

mission_complete.line: Mission complete! Do I get a share of the loot?

profile.line: I was the flagship of DesDiv 24 during the war! Impressive, right? Oh, and don't get me confused for Arashi!

propose.line: Woohooooo! I feel I could explode with how happy I am! Not literally, obviously~ Commander, I love you so much!

touch.line: Do you wanna play knock-out boxing?

touch2.line: Argh! I'll turn you into red paste!

unlock.line: Roooaar! Shiratsuyu-class destroyer Yamakaze is here! ...So, um, I'm looking for this "Commander" person. Any idea where they might be? ...Oh! That's you, huh?

upgrade.line: Woohoo!

win_mvp.line: We won! Hip, hip! Hooray!

detail.line: I'm gonna surprise everyone with a jaw-dropping trick at the banquet venue! But first I need to come up with a total jaw-dropper... Hmm...

drop_descrip.line: Voilà! Don't go anywhere, Commander! My magic show will start in just a sec! To start with, let's hear a roar! Roooaar!

home.line: Commander! Can I borrow your seat for a sec again? Just one second, I promise!

login.line: I'm prepped and ready for my big trick! Woo!

mail.line: Presto! I've magically retrieved your mail!

main1.line: White doves should be part of any good magician's act!

main2.line: Watch closely! I'm now going to make this flower dis– What the?! Why'd it turn into a handkerchief?!

main3.line: Heehee! This trick's definitely going to stun Umikaze and Kawakaze... Stop it, Commander! No peeking!

touch.line: Come over here, Commander! I'm gonna show you my coin trick~

touch2.line: Woah! Stop trying to figure out my tricks!

unlock.line: Voilà! Don't go anywhere, Commander! My magic show will start in just a sec! To start with, let's hear a roar! Roooaar!

battle.line: War... war never changes.

detail.line: I like fishing. When fishing, you can just clear your mind and not think about anything.

drop_descrip.line: Shiratsuyu-class destroyer number nine – Kawakaze.

expedition.line: A commission's done. Don't forget to read the report.

feeling1.line: In the end, you're just someone who can't exceed my expectations, Commander.

feeling2.line: In war, there is no right or wrong, no beauty or ugliness. This is true for both ally and enemy.

feeling3.line: Have you not experienced war, too? Then why do you still believe in fairy tales like justice, love, or harmony...?

feeling4.line: I abhor the stupidity and naïveté of those who refuse to face reality and continue shouting about their hopes and dreams. But you're not like that... are you?

feeling5.line: "Your dreams will come true if you don't give up on them"... Hmph, what a trite answer. But, if that's what you say...

home.line: What happens when the battle ends? The next one begins, that's all.

hp_warning.line: This pain... isn't enough to distract me!

login.line: Just another uneventful day.

lose.line: I'm still... afloat. If that's good or bad, who can say...

mail.line: Mail for you. Me? Not a fan of the stuff...

main1.line: Shells are weapons to silence one's enemies with. That's all they are, no matter how you sugarcoat it.

main2.line: If there's something you're wondering, ask Jintsuu. I'm... if I must say, I'd say I'm more like Sendai.

main3.line: Pretty cheerful gang you've got going with this fleet...

mission.line: New mission's appeared. ... What? Do I have to make small talk with you?

mission_complete.line: Mission rewards are here. Let's see if they were worth the time. But first, accept them.

profile.line: I'm Kawakaze, 3rd ship of the improved Shiratsuyu class, or simply the Umikaze class. Destroyer Division 24 comprised of my sisters and me during the war. Ah, Solomon... True, it is a place of many memories. The Iron Bottom Sound, Northampton, and the last thing I remember...

propose.line: I'm astonished that I'm doing this with you... We've been together so long that your wishful thinking has rubbed off on me... And for doing so, you'll take responsibility, won't you...?

skill.line: Relax. I will end this in an instant.

touch.line: How I feel about secretary work? Work is work, I don't have any preferences. Secretary or not, I don't care.

touch2.line: ... Now you've really done it...

unlock.line: The name's Kawakaze of the Shiratsuyu class. I have no intention of becoming your friend. Spare me your introduction.

upgrade.line: Getting stronger... feels okay.

win_mvp.line: The Solomon Islands... they call for me...

drop_descrip.line: Mhm. Lightweight clothing makes it easier to fight. Thanks, Commander... "It looks cute on me"? W-well, thanks...

login.line: Today might actually be an eventful day.

main1.line: On the battlefield, you swing your weapon and defeat the enemy, no more. Thinking about other things comes after the battle.

main2.line: Sendai, how about we have a match? As for our spectators... I suppose we could ask Jintsuu and the Commander.

main3.line: Seems having some cheerful people by your side might not be so bad.

touch.line: Do you like kendo, too? I'll work you to the bone to make you good at it. ... Huh? You don't wanna do it?

touch2.line: Phew... I was considering chopping off your hand, had you gone any further.

unlock.line: Mhm. Lightweight clothing makes it easier to fight. Thanks, Commander... "It looks cute on me"? W-well, thanks...

battle.line: I fight... for the one I love!

detail.line: I want you to pay Lady Nagato a visit from time to time. There's little I can do to ease her loneliness, but I believe that you can. Don't you worry, I know you'll still come to see me as well.

drop_descrip.line: This must be the dream you've awaited so eagerly... Of course, I vowed to be with you to the end of our days. I shall take my rightful place beside you and your wishful thinking. We are... together.

feeling5.line: "Your dreams will come true if you don't give up on them." They will, so let us make them real. I swear it to you upon all my being.

headtouch.line: What is it?

home.line: When the fighting ends, I will always be here waiting for you. Put your mind at rest.

login.line: Today is another day devoid of change. But nothing needs to change if I can happily remain by your side.

main1.line: The same sword that takes lives can also save them. It is my goal to become that: a sword that protects.

main2.line: You must not fixate on only either brains or brawn. The ideal leader is both wise and strong. Ahahah, here I am, paraphrasing Naka.

main3.line: You've got a cheerful gang going with this fleet. And you are a part of it, Commander.

mission.line: You have new missions. Shall we have a casual discourse while you review them?

mission_complete.line: Mission rewards are here. Hopefully, they'll have been worth our efforts.

touch.line: How I feel about secretary work? Work is work, that is all. I will gladly do anything for you.

touch2.line: It's humiliating to watch the other girls get ahead of me...

unlock.line: This must be the dream you've awaited so eagerly... Of course, I vowed to be with you until the end of our days. I shall take my rightful place beside you and your ideals. We are... together.

win_mvp.line: The Commander, Lady Nagato, and all my friends depend on me. I cannot afford to lose now.

battle.line: I-I'm supposed to give orders?! ... Whuah?! C-come on, everyone!

detail.line: Ugh... C-could you please not stare so much...?

drop_descrip.line: Yuugumo-class destroyer number eight – Kiyonami.

expedition.line: The commission team just returned to port. Umm... I think we should go check on them...

feeling1.line: Everyone's been saying the Commander is a mean person... Commander, is that really true...?

feeling2.line: Why do I like to hide behind you...? Umm, that's because... I feel more comfortable with you leading the way, Commander...

feeling3.line: Ugh... It's so scary at night... Commander, w-when it gets late, could you pretty please lead me to the dorm...?

feeling4.line: I have many more fluffy friends than just Hoppy... Commander, would you like to come visit my House of Fluffs sometime later...?

feeling5.line: I'm not scared of the dark or planes when I'm with you, Commander... W-would you mind if, from now on, I walked ahead of you, rather than behind you...?

home.line: Well done on the last sortie, Commander... W-would you like to pet Hoppy? I-it's really comforting to stroke his fluffy fur...

hp_warning.line: I-I'm not going to give up!

login.line: Welcome back, Commander... Come on, Hoppy, say hi to the Commander.

lose.line: Ugh... S-stay away...!

mail.line: Your mail has arrived! Let's take a look at it, Commander!

main1.line: I feel safe around Yuugure. I enjoy playing and having sleepovers with her. I wish I had more friends like her...

main2.line: Oh no, a-another air raid?! ... Commander, please don't scare me like that!

main3.line: I'm always doing my best, trying to catch up to everyone... S-so please, don't ever leave me behind, okay...?

mission.line: We still have quite a few missions to complete... Commander, can you do it...?

mission_complete.line: A mission... Yes, it seems a mission has been completed! You're quite the go-getter, Commander...

profile.line: I'm Kiyonami, the eighth Yuugumo-class destroyer... I had improved anti-air capabilities, but neither Yuugure nor I could really deal with things in the air... Ugh... If only I'd done a better job back then... B-but even so, I did achieve a couple of things! Wh-what I'm getting at is that I'll do the best job I can...!

propose.line: Will we really be able to be together forever from now on...? That's great...! N-now, I learned from Yuugure that... the next thing I should do is close my eyes and wait for you to do something, right? O-okay!

skill.line: W-we will do this together, Hoppy!

touch.line: Hoppy is cute, isn't he? Ehehe~ He's always there with me when I go to bed.

touch2.line: I-I'm not sure why you're doing this... B-but please stop, it tickles, Commander...!

unlock.line: Yuugumo-class destroyer Kiyonami, r-reporting for duty... And this is my friend, Hoppy... I-it's nice to meet you! ... Ugh...

upgrade.line: Hoppy and I think we got a little stronger...

win_mvp.line: I-I got... first place? Y-you're... not just joking, right...?

detail.line: I'm not sure what wrapping paper to use for my presents... Ummhh... Could you help me pick out a good one, Commander...?

drop_descrip.line: S-sorry to keep you waiting... Yuugure and I picked out this outfit together. She said it "looked very Christmassy," but it doesn't look weird, right? ... Ugh...

home.line: Well done on the last sortie. W-would you like a snack? I have gingerbread cookies and Christmas cake...

login.line: M-Merry Christmas, Commander! Phew... I think I said that right!

main1.line: I'm spending Christmas with Yuugure and some friends. D-do you want to be there with us too, Commander...?

main2.line: I've gotten presents for everyone I know. Th-that includes you, of course, Commander!

main3.line: All these warm lights at Christmas make me feel at ease... I wish it was Christmas all year round...

touch.line: Sometimes... Hoppy is on his own, but we always go to bed together at night.

touch2.line: Y-you'll make my hood come undone... Ugh...

unlock.line: S-sorry to keep you waiting... Yuugure and I picked out this outfit together. She said it "looked very Christmassy," but it doesn't look weird, right? ... Ugh...

battle.line: A real battle... I'll give it my all...!

detail.line: C-Commander, I haven't, um... disappointed you... have I?

drop_descrip.line: {namecode:26}-class destroyer number five – {namecode:125}.

expedition.line: Commander... a commission's been completed... I didn't get the time wrong... did I?

feeling1.line: I knew I probably wouldn't be of any use to you...

feeling2.line: Commander, is there something you wish me to do? I-is it possible I might have caused you trouble without realizing it?

feeling3.line: I'm trying my best not to cause trouble for people, but I don't know how... So instead I ended up making a lot of mistakes...

feeling4.line: Ever since I came to your base, I've started making considerably fewer mistakes... But even when I do, you don't get mad at me, so I've slowly but surely been able to get better... Also, when you encourage me by stroking my ears, your hand feels so warm...

feeling5.line: I'm timid and I often make mistakes, so I doubt I'll ever be very helpful to you, Commander... But I'm okay with that. Because what matters is...

home.line: Commander... you're not hurt, are you...?

login.line: Commander, I've sorted all your documents... You wanted your documents sorted... right?

lose.line: I've failed yet again...

mail.line: Commander, you have mail... Here... oh, wait, is it this one?

main1.line: I want to be useful to you, Commander, but if I cause you trouble instead... Then what will I do...

main2.line: If I cause you any trouble, I'll let you touch my ears and my tail, so please don't get mad at me...

main3.line: For this one you do this, then here you do... this... I think? I-I hope this will work...

mission.line: Commander, we have new missions. I'm certain it is a new one. I confirmed it myself...

mission_complete.line: Commander, I brought the mission rewards. I didn't make another mistake, did I...?

profile.line: I'm {namecode:125}, I'm the fifth ship of the {namecode:26}-class, I was constructed as part of the Circle Four Plan. But... I might be the least useful ship ever constructed... *Sob*...

propose.line: Even if they're a coward, even if they often make mistakes, what matters is telling your partner that you love them from the bottom of your heart, right...? This is the one thing I've believed ever since I was born... Okay, from now on I swear I'll always be with you, Commander...

skill.line: I-I'm not mistaken here, am I?!

touch.line: Commander? I'm worrying if I did something wrong today... I-I don't think... I have...

touch2.line: Eek?! C-Commander... you're seriously going to make me cry...

unlock.line: I'm {namecode:125}, the fifth ship of the {namecode:26}-class. I-I sincerely hope I can be of servish to... *Whimper*... I've made another mistake... Even though I practiced on it so much...

upgrade.line: Commander, whenever I think about failing to meet your expectations... it almost makes me start crying... *Sob*...

win_mvp.line: I hope I didn't cause any trouble for anyone...

battle.line: My s-skirt is gonna get blown away!

detail.line: Hyaa! C-Commander, when did you get here?

drop_descrip.line: Akizuki-class destroyer number nine – Harutsuki.

expedition.line: Commander! E-Everyone has come home safely!

feeling1.line: Commander, I wonder if you've been cursed...

feeling2.line: Back then, my sisters and I were all scattered to the winds... But, we are finally reunited again. It's a miracle...

feeling3.line: Aww.... m-my hair's all messed... Fusou's not here either, what should I do... Hm? You'd help me comb my hair? Thank you very much, Commander!

feeling4.line: Y-You'd like to watch my kagura dance? B-but, I still have a lot of practicing to do... Fusou said that rehearsals are just as important as practice...? I see! I... I'll do my best!

feeling5.line: C-Commander, please accept this! This is a protective good luck charm! "Marriage tie?" What do you mean...? C-Commander... you're a big bully...

home.line: Commander, you're safe! Thank goodness... my prayers were heard...

hp_warning.line: O gods, please give me guidance...!

login.line: Commander, w-welcome back!

lose.line: O gods, please save us!

mail.line: Commander, h-here... your letters...

main1.line: O gods, please bless this port so that everyone may come home safely.

main2.line: Yoizuki may seem cold, but she's very nice and is always thinking of everyone else!

main3.line: Good luck! I'll... be supporting you!

mission.line: C-Commander, umm... there are still missions left...

mission_complete.line: Commander, I've received the rewards!

profile.line: I am the ninth ship of the Akizuki-class destroyers, Harutsuki. Due to various circumstances, I wasn't able to do much, but... I'll make up for it this time, Commander!

propose.line: O gods, thank you very much for allowing me to meet Commander. I truly am blessed right now! So, um, Commander... though I'm still inexperienced, please take care of me!

skill.line: O gods, please watch over us!

touch.line: Commander? Would you like to try the sakura mochi that I made?

touch2.line: C-Commander! P-Please stop doing that... *sniffles*

unlock.line: I was guided here by the gods... Ah! M-My name is Harutsuki! Pleased to meet you!

upgrade.line: C-Can I truly become stronger like this?

win_mvp.line: Surely this must have been the gods' blessings.

detail.line: Um, Commander... It's a bit embarrassing if you stare at me like that...

drop_descrip.line: Happy New Year, Commander! I am currently on my way to give a Kagura dance at the shrine. If you have time... would you like to come see it?

login.line: All right, that should be all the rehearsing I need... C-Commander?! Just now, were you... watching me the whole time?

main1.line: I practiced a lot for this... so I hope I can do a good job...

main2.line: Fusou and Yamashiro went out of their way to practice with me! I'll have to make sure to thank them after this...!

main3.line: Gods, please watch over everyone this year...

touch.line: Do you like this outfit that much?

touch2.line: P-please stop that, Commander! You're going to mess up my clothes...

unlock.line: Happy New Year, Commander! I am currently on my way to give a Kagura dance at the shrine. If you have time... would you like to come see it?

battle.line: Be careful. Try to stay close to me.

detail.line: There is little I can do on my own. So, please, if I can assist in any way, don't be afraid to ask. I will help you.

drop_descrip.line: Akizuki-class destroyer number ten – Yoizuki.

expedition.line: A commission has been completed. Splendid work.

feeling1.line: I would prefer it if you'd stay away from me.

feeling2.line: Hm? I seem cold and distant to you? I've heard that from Harutsuki before... Oh, bother...

feeling3.line: I know that I can't always be by Harutsuki's side to help when she feels nervous. Yet, my body always acts on its own accord...

feeling4.line: You don't require my help, yet you keep me waiting by your side... Why is that? I don't quite understand...

feeling5.line: A "date"? What does that mean? ... It means we'll play together? Certainly, if that's what you wish. ... Why are you smiling? You're quite strange...

home.line: You must be tired. Should I prepare tea while you rest for a while, Commander?

login.line: You have returned, Commander. I have already sorted all your documents.

lose.line: They tricked us... Everyone, retreat! I will watch your backs...!

mail.line: Commander, I have left your mail here.

main1.line: Why I help people? I feel I should; therefore I do it... Is that strange?

main2.line: Some have mistaken me for a light cruiser... I wonder why... I don't look like one...

main3.line: "Forcing myself"? Not at all. If I were, my help would only have the opposite effect.

mission.line: We have received a mission. Is it something I may take care of?

mission_complete.line: I have brought the mission rewards. These should be all of them.

profile.line: I am the Akizuki-class destroyer Yoizuki. I specialize in anti-air combat. If you ever have any problems, please tell me. I will solve them quickly for you.

propose.line: This is how you've felt about me, Commander...? I've been slow to catch on, haven't I... But, do not worry, I pledge myself to you. I swear to always protect you, do exactly as you wish, and never again leave your side.

touch.line: Do you feel tired? Shall I give you a shoulder massage?

touch2.line: Commander, are you asking for a beating?

unlock.line: I'm honored to meet you, Commander. I have come to assist you. From now on, I can help you with your work whenever needed.

upgrade.line: This feels rather nice.

win_mvp.line: We have everyone to thank for this victory.

detail.line: I received a good luck charm from Harutsuki... It's nice when someone offers you their blessings.

drop_descrip.line: It's my turn? Hold on... Umm, could you please not stare at me like that? It's... making me feel uncomfortable.

feeling5.line: Will you enter with me for the three-legged race? Don't worry, we're unbeatable as a pair.

home.line: All the entrants are strong candidates... I'll need to exert myself for the next event, too.

login.line: I registered for several sporting events. I must give it my all so I won't slow down my teammates...

main1.line: Harutsuki, slow down and match your pace with mine... One, two! One two!

main2.line: It's quite hot today, Commander. I brought a drink with me... I drank a little from it, but... would you like to have some?

main3.line: Ugh... My hair is being annoying... Harutsuki's not here, either... Excuse me, Commander, could you give me a hand?

touch.line: Commander, I'm completely soaked in sweat... You probably shouldn't touch me.

touch2.line: Are you taking advantage of me at a time like this? Are you mentally prepared for what comes next, Commander?

unlock.line: It's my turn? Hold on... Umm, could you please not stare at me like that? It's... making me feel uncomfortable.

detail.line: The noise of the firecrackers is said to repel a monster called the "Nian." As for why this monster only appears during Lunar New Year's, I'm not quite sure...

drop_descrip.line: Mmh... Happy New Year. I'm working on hooking my friends up with these firecrackers... The bun I'm eating? I received it as a thank-you for my efforts.

home.line: I'm aware that setting off firecrackers is an important Dragon Empery tradition. That said... This many firecrackers may be excessive.

login.line: Is there anything I can help you with, Commander? You seem busy as ever, even during the Lunar New Year, so...

main1.line: Yat Sen's dim sum is wonderful. I'm particularly fond of this meat bun she made.

main2.line: If lighting firecrackers sounds too frightening, would you like to light a firework instead?

main3.line: Make a fai chun? Sorry, such things are beyond my means. You may wish to ask Hanazuki or Suzutsuki instead.

touch.line: Don't worry, it's not very heavy. I'm capable of carrying it.

touch2.line: Perhaps the noise of the firecrackers can dispel your sinful thoughts too?

unlock.line: Mmh... Happy New Year. I'm working on hooking my friends up with these firecrackers... The bun I'm eating? I received it as a thank-you for my efforts.

battle.line: Muahaha, all ships… set sail!

detail.line: O you mean this family emblem? I designed this myself, plus the clothes. I won’t accept any other comments except for “its cute”.

drop_descrip.line: The 11th Destroyer of {namecode:19} class — {namecode:142}

expedition.line: The commission fleet has returned, did you forget?

feeling1.line: Stay away from me, stupidity is contagious.

feeling2.line: My fan? Its military issue, not some ordinary fan. It’s used by Admirals, so don’t underestimate me… hehehe. Hmm? I said nothing.

feeling3.line: {namecode:128} and {namecode:127} are both so whimsical and wandering around. Those girls sure don’t have the temperment of being in the Navy. They still need to lean on me, being their big sister. Such a headache...

feeling4.line: Actually, even though I don’t care that much and I have confidence in myself, for the sake of asking… do you think I’m independent enough?

feeling5.line: What, I just asked offhandedly, you sure are opinionated… forget it. I’ll still listen to what you got to say. Just you wait, one day I’ll impress you.

home.line: You’ve worked hard today, please get some rest.

hp_warning.line: Such a tactical mistake...

login.line: So slow, are you like a turtle who’s stumbled onto the battlefield?

lose.line: Damn, give me… victory. Win or lose, that’s the way of life in the Navy.

mail.line: You’ve got mail… hmm? You read it, I didn’t really focus on what was written, don’t mind me.

main1.line: That {namecode:128} girl, as my little sister she always acts superior to {namecode:127}, even more than I do, darn…

main2.line: If only we discovered Tusk, then {namecode:70}-sama would not… sigh, forget it, what’s important is the present

main3.line: Official documents? Let me see… hmm… ahh I see I see...

mission.line: I’ve organized all the missions… say what, you want me to clear them as well?!

mission_complete.line: The mission rewards have been confirmed, I’ll leave the labor work of transporting it here to you.

profile.line: The 17th Destroyer fleet have been together for most of the time, and we participated in all sorts of sorties and operations for almost the entirety of the war. In the end I was with {namecode:70}-sama as we both made our last stand… to the end. So I don’t care about those little things.

propose.line: Commander, you’ve finally realized my greatness. To be frank… my ears are not twitching. I’m not that happy, shut up, let’s continue the ceremony!

touch.line: Don’t poke me unstoppingly, are you a monkey?

touch2.line: This type of things should not be tolerated, right? In that case, die...

unlock.line: So it turns out to be you, are you the Commander of the 17th Destroyer fleet from today onwards? You seem so ordinary. I am {namecode:19} class {namecode:142}, show me what you got, Commander.

upgrade.line: Thank you… my ears are twitching? Impossible, I’m not that happy at all.

win_mvp.line: We won… naturally, what’s there to gloat about?

detail.line: You should know that I designed this outfit just by seeing the family crest here. Do you think it looks good?
