drop_descrip.line: Before you raise a fuss about it, let me just tell you this - the concept of "Christmas" already existed during the Sengoku period, so there's nothing weird about putting on a Christmas outfit!

feeling5.line: Look here, Christmas nowadays is a holiday that you celebrate with those who are important to you. You came here knowing that, didn't you? Me? I... don't particularly object...

login.line: Merry Christmas. I suppose I'll let you take it easy today.

mail.line: Another greeting card for you... Curse you, what a normie.

main1.line: {namecode:143}, stop frolicking around like a little kid, and don't pull on me either! Ugh... what am I going to do with you?

main2.line: I still have to prepare presents for the three stooges... Jeez, can't they be a bit more considerate towards their big sis normally? Oh well, I suppose that's how it should be.

main3.line: It's snowing... Hmm? It's not like I particularly want to play in the snow or anything, but if you want to so badly, I suppose I can tag along.

touch.line: Santa Claus? ... Hmph, I graduated from that fairy tale long ago.

unlock.line: Before you raise a fuss about it, let me just tell you this - the concept of "Christmas" already existed during the Sengoku period, so there's nothing weird about putting on a Christmas outfit!

battle.line: Let us do like rock stars do and turn it up to eleven!

detail.line: Of course they had music during the Sengoku period! ...But they didn't have rock bands? Listen, it's called "getting with the times."

drop_descrip.line: Ugh... Even though we finally got all our gear, we still need more band members... Commander! Stop complaining and come hither! From now on, you're a member of the Sengoku Shredders!

expedition.line: What? Was I wrong? Hm... It's been quite some time since Tanikaze said she'd go receive the commission team... Hope nothing has happened to her...

home.line: Do we have any potential new band members? ...What? Nobody has even applied? Grrr... I suppose there's no point in getting mad at you for it, though...

login.line: Enough dilly-dallying! It's time to get on with today's rehearsal!

main1.line: Hamakaze said she won't join because it would "impact her academic performance"... Hmph! She doesn't know what she's missing out on!

main2.line: A band logo? Yes, and we'll use my family crest as the motif, of course!

main3.line: If you're going to rest, find something durable to sit on... I'm not "showing concern," just giving you instructions!

mission.line: Being a general is no excuse to skip out on rehears– Ahem! I mean missions.

mission_complete.line: You've brought the missions rewards? Splendid, Isokaze! I'll see to it you receive a castle for your efforts!

touch.line: Go on. Read the score and play the song like I taught you.

unlock.line: Ugh... Even though we finally got all our gear, we still need more band members... Commander! Stop complaining and come hither! From now on, you're a member of the Sengoku Shredders!

battle.line: I will lead the charge into batt... Hey, stop! Wait for me!

detail.line: One banner, one nation!

drop_descrip.line: Kagerou-class destroyer number twelve – Isokaze.

expedition.line: Our target: the base's docks! We must welcome back the commission team! Giddy-up, General!

feeling1.line: Hmph! I'm done playing with you! Hamakaze, Tanikaze, where are you?

feeling2.line: How I know so much? Urakaze-sama taught me everything about the warring states! She's really smart! But Hamakaze is still my best friend in the end! Heheheh~

feeling3.line: Western Army, attack! Fire on the Eastern Army! Our next move will be... Oh no! Hideaki was lured away! That's unfair, General! Darn, now I'm... *Sob*...

feeling4.line: General, let's play a game! Huh?! You've got work to do?! You really do? Do you want me to help? Then how about a massage? ...Hooray! I love you, General!

feeling5.line: General, Urakaze-sama seemed angry at me and said I've started being cold to Hamakaze! But I still want to play with you... So come on! Let's go play together with Hamakaze!

home.line: You make me proud, General! Hey, uh, listen! I have a report for you! You see...

hp_warning.line: I will never back down!

login.line: General! It's time to charge into battle!

lose.line: Hamakaze, Hamakaze where are you... You have to save me!

mail.line: General, I have a letter for you!

main1.line: General! Come play warring states with me! You can be... Ieyasu! I'll be Mitsunari!

main2.line: Hamakaze! Tanikaze! Let's depart! We're heading for the capital!

main3.line: Urakaze-sama, my coat has been torn again... Fix it for me!

mission.line: General! Put me in charge of the mission! I'll finish it you before you can say "set sail"!

mission_complete.line: General, our mission rewards are here! How much koku did we receive?

profile.line: I am Isokaze of DD17! In the past, you see, I've worked with Hamakaze, Urakaze, Tanikaze... oh, and Yukikaze! My service record stands second to none! And that's why you should put me in charge of your missions!

propose.line: General, if anyone starts being mean to you then tell me. Hamakaze and I will go and get revenge on them for you. We're here for you, because we're all friends!

touch.line: General, give me a piggyback ride! We must charge into the enemy stronghold!

touch2.line: Hahaha, that tickles~!

unlock.line: All units, attaaack! ...Wait a second, where am I?! Oh, I know you! Urakaze-sama said you're... the general! Hmph! I'm Isokaze, the one destined to become a general that will make the whole world tremble in fear!

upgrade.line: I am Isokaze, the leader of Destroyer Division 17!

win_mvp.line: Urakaze-sama, can you see my glorious victory?!

detail.line: General, I want my red envelope!

drop_descrip.line: General, General, look! It's my New Year's outfit! Urakaze made it for me! Let's play a bunch of Sengoku wargames this year as well!

feeling5.line: General, General! Make sure to wake me up for the New Year's shrine visit! Even if I sleep in, make sure to come get me! This year, we definitely need to go together!

login.line: General, Happy New Year!

main1.line: Woah! It's snowing! General, let's call everyone out and have a snowball fight!

main2.line: Why is everyone so sluggish during the winter? I think playing in the snow is suuuuper fun!

main3.line: General, General, look! It's a tiger! Rooooaarrr! Ahahaha~

mission_complete.line: General, what are these? New Year's presents?

touch.line: Huh? General, I'm not cold~ Ahaha, stop rubbing my belly, it tickles!

unlock.line: General, General, look! It's my New Year's outfit! Urakaze made it for me! Let's play a bunch of Sengoku wargames this year as well!

battle.line: The first smash hit is coming right up~!

drop_descrip.line: General! I, Isokaze, have done my utmost to prepare the equipment! Now, with Lord Urakaze's presence, our Sengoku☆War-Band is complete! Of course, you are more than welcome to join our ranks, General!

home.line: For the General's return, an ode of celebration... Uhh, I was going to practice this song with Urakaze...

login.line: General! Let us dedicate our souls to the rehearsal today!

main1.line: Hamakaze, tutor me~ I was practicing so hard that I forgot to do my homework...

main2.line: General! What kind of outfit should I wear? A suit of armor? Just a chestplate...?

main3.line: "Straight to your heart! Love delivered on the spear's tip!" ...How's that, General? Just like an idol, right?

touch.line: This outfit is so fluttery... Being cute is nice and all, but I want to be badass...

unlock.line: General! I, Isokaze, have done my utmost to prepare the equipment! Now, with Lord Urakaze's presence, our Sengoku☆War-Band is complete! Of course, you are more than welcome to join our ranks, General!

win_mvp.line: Viiiiictorrrryyyyyy~! As the sun shines, so do I!

battle.line: This wind... is perfect for battle!

detail.line: This time too... I swear to protect my friends!

drop_descrip.line: Kagerou-class destroyer number thirteen – Hamakaze.

expedition.line: Well done... Commissions are hardly a big deal compared to Rat Transports, right?

feeling1.line: Stupid meatheaded Commander...

feeling2.line: Commander, history surely won't repeat itself... right?

feeling3.line: I hope one day... Destroyer Division 17 can reunite here...

feeling4.line: The breeze feels really nice today... But we can't afford to rest yet! Yamato... wait for me...

feeling5.line: For as long as the wind blows, I will always be by your side.

home.line: Great job. Did everyone do their job during the sortie?

login.line: Now's not the time to lose focus, Commander.

lose.line: I have to rescue the survivors...

mail.line: Reading through these reports should be your top priority.

main1.line: Tanikaze, until you finish your training, don't expect to get much beauty sleep!

main2.line: Though I may be but a single destroyer, I'll still do all I can to protect everyone.

main3.line: Bou-no-misaki... where it all came to an end...

mission.line: Our next mission is...

mission_complete.line: Your grades are going up, Commander.

profile.line: I'm Hamakaze, 13th Kagerou-class destroyer. Although I took part in quite a few battles, it feels like I spent more time rescuing friends than sinking foes... And now, I fight once more to protect my friends.

propose.line: M-maybe we should wait until it's all over... Th-that said, I'd feel bad if I rejected you now, so I'll have to accept it... Hey, stop laughing!

touch.line: Hm? What are you looking at, Commander?

touch2.line: Eek! ... Commander, just where do you think you're touching?

unlock.line: Hamakaze, 13th ship of the Kagerou-class destroyers, reporting for duty. Commander, try not to get my name wrong.

upgrade.line: The wind grows stronger.

win_mvp.line: Heheh! This is nothing spectacular for me!

battle.line: Hm, hm... at this range, with these forces... we can win!

drop_descrip.line: Learning is exciting. The joy of acquiring new knowledge, the sense of achievement from solving difficult problems... you'll understand once you try it. So, shall we study together, Commander?

login.line: Commander, were you able to solve that question from yesterday?

main1.line: Urakaze, Isokaze, Tanikaze, have you all taken your seats? Then let's review the essentials of the last formula we studied.

main2.line: Improve yourself so that you can better protect those you care about. That's why I study as hard as I do.

main3.line: Here we'll use this equation, then do this... Hah, a trivial question like this is no issue for me.

touch.line: Commander, you won't find the answer underneath my skirt.

touch2.line: Commander, take your reading more seriously!

unlock.line: Learning is exciting. The joy of acquiring new knowledge, the sense of achievement from solving difficult problems... you'll understand once you try it. So, shall we study together, Commander?

win_mvp.line: That parabola... was beautiful...

detail.line: I do all the cooking while Tanikaze takes care of the cleaning. Are we the only staff, you wonder? No, we've got all these little guys helping us too!

drop_descrip.line: I'm experimenting with different flavors since we're running a pop-up café... Alright! I think I'll go with this one! Strap in, Commander, because you're about to do a lot of taste-testing!

home.line: Welcome! ...Oh, it's just you. Will you have the usual? Or do you wanna try the new menu items?

login.line: Come on in, Commander! I just worked out a new flavor and you're gonna try it right now!

main1.line: Welcome! I came up with this flavor after eating at tons of restaurants! No other store can match it!

main2.line: Tanikaze, could you come help me out in here once you're done cleaning?

main3.line: Does the little guy on this plate even have a name? I'm not sure...?

touch.line: I'd appreciate it if you'd leave your cutlery here after you're done eating.

touch2.line: You're not allowed inside the kitchen, Commander!

unlock.line: I'm experimenting with different flavors since we're running a pop-up café... Alright! I think I'll go with this one! Strap in, Commander, because you're about to do a lot of taste-testing!

drop_descrip.line: Commander, have you been having more fun since I arrived? ... I see, that's great! Ehehe... Hamakaze, getting hyped!

main1.line: Could you stop poking my cheek, Tanikaze... Hey, stop! No poking there, especially!

main2.line: I love seeing my friends smile. That's why...

main3.line: It's not over yet... This time, I'll triumph... at Bou-no-misaki.

touch.line: Commander, I think you can see further if you do it like this.

touch2.line: Eek! ... Commander, this is unacceptable!

unlock.line: Commander, have you been having more fun since I arrived? ... I see, that's great! Ehehe... Hamakaze, getting hyped!

battle.line: Destroyer Division 17, setting sail! Huh? Did I get something wrong...?

detail.line: Midway? I believe we won that battle... O-or am I wrong again?!

drop_descrip.line: Kagerou-class destroyer number fourteen – Tanikaze.

expedition.line: A team has returned to base, Commander.

feeling1.line: It's you... *Stares angrily*

feeling2.line: I still don't know very much about you, Commander.

feeling3.line: Usually valley winds are only there during noon, but I'm always here!

feeling4.line: Hehe~ You're wide open for attack! Poke~

feeling5.line: When I'm with you, it feels like time flows faster. Do you feel the same thing, Commander?

home.line: Wah! Welcome back!

login.line: I'm right here if you need me.

lose.line: What could I have done better...

mail.line: The winds have brought you new mail.

main1.line: Hamakaze-chan, you need to ease up a little! Pokey-poke~

main2.line: Y-Yukikaze's coming here? W-we should be able to get along... Hopefully...

main3.line: I always feel at ease when you're here with me, Commander.

mission.line: The mission isn't finished yet, Commander.

mission_complete.line: I knew you could do it, Commander.

profile.line: I'm Tanikaze, Kagerou-class destroyer number fourteen. I served as the flagship of Destroyer Division 17. There were a lot of aircraft in the Battle of Midway, but I hardly got bombed at all. Hamakaze-chan and I sunk a certain ship in the Kula Gulf... Hehehe~

propose.line: Ahh... Th-thank you so much... I-I happily accept. Um... uh, well, I-I... love you too, Commander! I-I'm so embarrassed...

touch.line: Wah! I wish you'd stop poking my cheek like that... Mmph...

touch2.line: Please, don't poke anything but my cheek!

unlock.line: I am Tanikaze, the winds have carried me from valleys to mountaintops... Commander, will you take me home?

upgrade.line: It's really windy today...

win_mvp.line: Did I do well enough to satisfy you, Commander?

battle.line: Are my sisters over there?

detail.line: Would you like to go to the beach with us, Commander? I want to build sandcastles with everyone!

drop_descrip.line: The butterfly flew... Huh? Where did it...? Hamakaze? Hamakaze?! Huh? Where are Urakaze and Isokaze? Where did...? We said we'd all go to the beach, so where did they go...?

home.line: Commander, are you ready to go to the beach?

login.line: Commander, do you know where my sisters are? We promised we'd go to the beach, together...

main1.line: Ugh... I want to invite Yukikaze, but... she's hard to approach...

main2.line: Commander, are my life jacket and float ring in order?

main3.line: We're going to the beach... so Isokaze shouldn't ask me to play warring states with her, hopefully...

unlock.line: The butterfly flew... Huh? Where did it...? Hamakaze? Hamakaze?! Huh? Where are Urakaze and Isokaze? Where did...? We said we'd all go to the beach, so where did they go...?

win_mvp.line: Ugh... I was just trying to get to the beach...

detail.line: Hamakaze accommodates customers, and I keep the café clean. It's not just us two; plenty of other people help keep the store running smoothly. But what do you think, Commander? D-do you think we're doing a good job?

drop_descrip.line: Commander, I'm mopping the floor right now. Please watch your step, as it's quite slippery over there... Eek! Owch... I suppose I should've watched my own step... Ahaha...

home.line: Welcome back, Commander! I'm hoping to keep this place tidy and welcoming for everyone at all times.

login.line: How's this? I'd say the place looks much cleaner now. Uh-oh... the bucket! ...Aww! I suppose I have more cleaning to do...

main1.line: W-welcome...! I'm practicing my waitress skills for when I have to do it for real! Thinking about it is a bit nerve-wracking...

main2.line: Having a vacuum-cleaning robot sure is convenient. Maybe I can go help Hamakaze with all the time it's freed up...

main3.line: I just realized... I've never given the little cutie that's always sitting on my head a name, have I...?

touch.line: Oh, you'll lend me a hand? Okay, then you can take my broom.

touch2.line: Eek! You almost made me knock over my bucket! Stop that!

unlock.line: Commander, I'm mopping the floor right now. Please watch your step, as it's quite slippery over there... Eek! Owch... I suppose I should've watched my own step... Ahaha...

drop_descrip.line: I am Tanikaze, the winds have carried me from valleys to mountaintops... Oh wow, a b-butterfly?! It really is a butterfly! Is this for me? Thank you, Commander!

main1.line: I really wonder... What might Urakaze-chan and Isokaze-chan be doing right now...

main2.line: Something good is going to happen today, Commander.

main3.line: You're a very warmhearted person, Commander.

touch.line: Wah! This time I'll poke you in return! Poke! Poke poke~!

touch2.line: Ah, I see! It's my turn now! Poke poke... Scratch scratch... Can I nap while you give me a piggyback, Commander? ...Zzzzz....

unlock.line: I am Tanikaze, the winds have carried me from valleys to mountaintops... Oh wow, a b-butterfly?! It really is a butterfly! Is this for me? Thank you, Commander!

battle.line: Anti-air preparations... is everything in place?

detail.line: I'd like to stay here forever... But at this rate, I won't be able to find Arashio.

drop_descrip.line: Asashio-class destroyer number one – Asashio.

expedition.line: Isn't it about time to welcome the others back?

feeling1.line: Arashio... Where are you?

feeling2.line: Every time I look out into the horizon, memories of that time come flooding back to me...

feeling3.line: I had another nightmare yesterday. Commander, would you please stay with me tonight? That black abyss, not being able to see anything... I'm scared...

feeling4.line: Commander, I'm at ease when I'm with you... But every time I think about Arashio, I get anxious again...

feeling5.line: Commander, you're somehow always able to put my heart at ease. But recently, I've discovered something else that scares me... Commander, you'll always stay by my side... right?

home.line: There is nothing more reassuring than being here. Commander, don't you think so too?

hp_warning.line: The situation... seems to not be ideal.

login.line: Welcome back, Commander. If you don't want to set sail right away, why don't you rest first?

lose.line: If only I had upgraded my anti-air equipment a bit more...

mail.line: Shall I go through the email for you? Maybe there's a letter from Arashio...

main1.line: Dampier Strait? I don't really want to think about that place anymore... More importantly, Commander, can you install another anti-air gun?

main2.line: Happiness is a full belly and a good night's sleep.

main3.line: *Yawns* ...It's already so late, but Commander is still at it... Please make sure to take care of yourself.

mission.line: Commander, your missions... Please show some motivation once in a while.

mission_complete.line: The mission rewards... can I use them to buy something to eat?

profile.line: Asashio-class nameship, Asashio. Arashio and I, along with our friends, formed the 8th DesDiv. Though we were disbanded in the end, I strongly believe that we'll be able to be together again one day. Commander... do you want to help me find them?

propose.line: If there's one good thing that's happened to me, it's that I was able to meet you, Commander. Will you stay by my side until I fall asleep? Tonight... and tomorrow... and every night...

skill.line: This time... I won't fail again!

touch.line: Don't worry, I... am not afraid anymore!

touch2.line: What a weird feeling...

unlock.line: I am Asashio. I've come to join this fleet in order to search for my missing comrade. Commander, do you also have someone who you could not give up on?

upgrade.line: I think... it'd be better to mount another anti-air gun.

win_mvp.line: It seems that I accidentally did something awesome...

detail.line: I wonder if I can find Arashio here at school...?

drop_descrip.line: My name is Asashio, and I just transferred here today. Pleased to meet you... Even though I might not be able to get caught up with the course work, Mr. Kitty and I will do our best.

login.line: It's time to go to school again... Commander, want to walk with me?

main1.line: How nice it'd be to go to school with Arashio...

main2.line: Mr. Kitty always likes to rub against peoples' legs.

main3.line: *yawn*...It feels nice to take a nap during class, but... I probably shouldn't, right?

touch.line: Commander... do you also want Mr. Kitty to rub against you?

unlock.line: My name is Asashio, and I just transferred here today. Pleased to meet you... Even though I might not be able to get caught up with the course work, Mr. Kitty and I will do our best.

detail.line: So warm... Commander, would you like some? Here, you should enjoy hot tea like this... Fwoo, fwoo... Then just let the warmth spread over you.

drop_descrip.line: Happy New Year, Commander. I am here to spend the New Year with you. Would you be so kind as to first help me down from here?

login.line: Commander, would you like some hot tea and a mikan orange?

mail.line: There are still letters coming in even though it's New Year's day.

main1.line: Are you cold, Commander? ...That's no good. Mm, you'll warm up if I give you a hug like this.

main2.line: I can't finish all the food that everyone brought... Commander, if you don't mind, could you help finish mine?

main3.line: Even though we can't have a tea party during the winter, it's fun to sit around and chat with everyone inside the kotatsu.

touch.line: Hold hands...? Okay.

unlock.line: Happy New Year, Commander. I am here to spend the New Year with you. Would you be so kind as to first help me down from here?

win_mvp.line: For your sake, Commander, I shall do my best.

detail.line: *Bum* *Bum* *Bum*... The drums' sound makes me feel all fluttery... Oh, Commander, are you okay? I'm... not too heavy, am I?

drop_descrip.line: Commander, thank you for coming to see me. I'm currently rehearsing my program for the Spring Festival performance. I do hope it is to your liking.

home.line: Everyone's been bringing me gifts. These snacks from the Dragon Empery smell so good... Commander, do you want some as well?

login.line: Flutter, flutter... I've been trying my best to learn these dance steps. How do I look, Commander?

main1.line: Shall I give you a shoulder massage since you've been working so hard? Rub, rub... Does that feel good?

main2.line: Um, Michishio chose this outfit, Arashio picked out this hair accessory, and Ooshio chose this anklet... Do you think they look good on me?

main3.line: The fact that all of us used to be separated... but can all come together to prepare for a show like this... is a dream come true...

touch.line: The long and fluttery sleeves are beautiful, aren't they?

touch2.line: It's hard to dance like this...

unlock.line: Commander, thank you for coming to see me. I'm currently rehearsing my program for the Spring Festival performance. I do hope it is to your liking.

win_mvp.line: If it's for you, Commander, I know I can win.

battle.line: Take care now so ya'll don't get hurt~

detail.line: Who's yer favorite girl, Commander? Reckon ya could tell me?

drop_descrip.line: Asashio-class destroyer number two – Ooshio.

expedition.line: Ah, the commission team's back? ...Ain't that nice~ Wish you'd let me go on one too~

feeling1.line: I reckoned we'd never be able to understand each other...

feeling2.line: Girls are just the cutest darn thing~ And who on earth doesn't like cute things?

feeling3.line: Whether they're boys or girls, if they're talented 'n cute, I love 'em all the same~ It's not yer gender that matters, it's what's inside~

feeling4.line: Yer a good person, Commander~ Now I get why the fleet believes in ya~ I'll letcha in on a li'l secret: I done fallen for a certain someone... Hehehe~

feeling5.line: Hehehe~ Yer the talented and cute person I fell for~ How 'bout you, Commander? Do ya love me too?

home.line: Ya made it back in one piece~ Ya ain't injured, are ya...?

hp_warning.line: We don't gotta force ourselves~

login.line: Commander, let's stay focused 'n work hard to make everyone happy~

lose.line: Ya can't let a small setback getcha feelin' blue~

mail.line: Got a letter for ya, Commander~ *Giggle*, ain't this a... luve letter?

main1.line: Yer makin' me jealous of how yer surrounded 'round the clock by such talented girls~

main2.line: Asashio's a real cutie~ Hehehe~

main3.line: Commander, if yer bored, why don'tcha call some folks over 'n we can have a tea party?

mission.line: It's mission time, Commander.

mission_complete.line: The mission rewards done arrived, Commander~

profile.line: I'm Ooshio, Asashio-class ship number two~ I served as the flagship of Destroyer Division 8 and did all kindsa things with Asashio, Michishio, 'n Arashio, 'n I was even awarded a few medals~ Then I took some damage 'n Asashio was put in charge, but that's all in the past now. Anyhow, why don'tcha tell me a bit 'bout this fleet?

propose.line: I love you, 'n you love me too, ain't that just the darndest thing~ Don'tcha agree, Com-man-der? ♡

skill.line: For the sake of the fleet~

touch.line: Wonder what I oughta make for desert... Ah, ya want some too, Commander? Aw heck, yer puttin' me in a tight spot~

touch2.line: Oh my, I better tell the others that yer a dangerous one, Commander~

unlock.line: Oh, I found me a talented-lookin' Commander~ "How so"? Cause I saw all them talented-lookin' girls ya got followin' ya~ I'm Ooshio. I'll be countin' on ya'll from now on~

upgrade.line: Thanks much~

win_mvp.line: I done saw how fine ya'll fought~

detail.line: This costume here's a bit too tight... I oughta get a new one next year...

drop_descrip.line: Merry Christmas~ Commander, we gotta go hand out presents to them destroyers~ You be Santa, I'll be yer reindeer~

feeling5.line: Commander, ya got time once we're done handin' out presents? Heheh, cause I've got a special present for you, my sweetheart~ Just don't be too surprised when I show it to ya~

home.line: I got presents for all you girls who made it back safely~ There's one for you too, Commander~

mail.line: Letter for ya, Commander~ Hehe, wouldn't it be nice if it's a thank-you letter from a good girl to Santa?

main1.line: Oh yeah, whaddya want for Christmas, Commander? I can get it for ya, even if it takes some lookin' 'round.

main2.line: Christmas is more fun when ya get everyone together 'n throw a big party~

main3.line: By the end of the year, everyone'll be smilin'~♪ Hehe, it makes me happy, too~

mission_complete.line: Ain't it more fun if we treat these mission rewards as presents from headquarters?

touch.line: You wonderin' why I wanna be the one handin' out presents? Cause I wanna see those cute smiles on everyone's faces, ya silly~

touch2.line: Well, fine... Think of it as my Christmas gift to you~♡

unlock.line: Merry Christmas~ Commander, we gotta go hand out presents to them destroyers~ You be Santa, I'll be yer reindeer~

battle.line: C'mon, ya'll, follow my lead~

detail.line: Wonder if Asashio's here yet... Not done been abducted by some criminal, has she... Am I just worryin' over nothin', Commander?

drop_descrip.line: Happy anniversary~ Today's a day to enjoy to yer heart's content, ya know? I'm just havin' fun in my own way, checkin' out cute girls from afar~ I appreciate yer concern though, Commander~

feeling5.line: Hm...? I've might've fallen for ya again, Commander... You look even more charmin' than usual... What about me? Ya think I'm cuter than usual?

home.line: The world is all spinny~ I guess I am pretty drunk... Commander~ What do I oughta do to sober up...?

login.line: Fancy a drink, Commander? It's pretty darn nice stuff~ Hehehe, don't be shy now! I might be heckin' drunk, but I won't bite~

main1.line: Albacore, don't go causin' mischief durin' the party, all right? Commander, I reckon you oughta tell her too.

main2.line: Michishio 'n Arashio almost love Asashio as much as I do~ That's why we all love havin' tea parties with her. You too, Commander, go become buddy buds with her~

main3.line: Commander, it ain't nice of ya to check out other girls while yer talkin' to me~! Where are yer manners?

touch.line: Commander? What're ya starin' at me for...?

touch2.line: Gawsh... Girl has a sip of wine 'n this happens... Yer lucky it's me ya did it to~!

unlock.line: Happy anniversary~ Today's a day to enjoy to yer heart's content, ya know? I'm just havin' fun in my own way, checkin' out cute girls from afar~ I appreciate yer concern though, Commander~

detail.line: It's nice wearin' a cute dress 'n minglin' with a bunch of cuties~ I don't mind you oglin' me if ya want, Commander.

drop_descrip.line: Should I hang this "fortune" poster here...? Oh, Commander, did ya also want a Spring Festival present from Ooshio here? Just kiddin'~ Hehe, anyway, happy Lunar New Year~

home.line: Go on, spend some time with all the cuties 'n have a relaxin' holiday!

login.line: Are ya fixin' for some tea, Commander? Then have some brewed usin' tea leaves I got from Yat Sen~

main1.line: Ain't family get-togethers a tradition 'round this time of year? I'll call over my sisters for a little tea time... No wait, we'll have tangyuan instead! Wanna join us, Commander?

main2.line: Kasumi, how's about joinin' us for a night out? You can bring Foo and yer friends too, if ya want~

main3.line: If everyone's happy, then I'm happy too~ You feelin' happy, Commander?

touch.line: My hair ornament's slid out of place? Aw, thanks, Commander~

touch2.line: Commander, this ain't the place or place for lewdin', all right~?

unlock.line: Should I hang this "fortune" poster here...? Oh, Commander, did ya also want a Spring Festival present from Ooshio here? Just kiddin'~ Hehe, anyway, happy Lunar New Year~

detail.line: These special-made uniforms're real nice – everyone looks so cute in 'em~ Whole school's a feast for the eyes, ain't it, Commander?

drop_descrip.line: Finally we're through with them mornin' classes~ Commander, would ya fancy havin' lunch with me? Heheh, yer wonderin' what I done made? You'll see for yerself soon 'nuff~

expedition.line: The commission team done returned. Give them hardworkin' girls a treat for their efforts~

feeling5.line: For dessert, we'll be havin' some schoolgirl eye candy~ Aww, why ya lookin' bummed out? I know you've always got room for sweeties, hon. Hehehe♪

home.line: Oh! I was just wonderin' where ya went. Is that a can of green tea? Much obliged~

login.line: How'd ya like my home cookin'? ...Heheh, glad to hear it~ Ya can have as much as ya want.

mail.line: Ya got a letter, Commander! Heh, do ya want me to leave it in yer shoe locker?

main1.line: I done made a lunch box for my li'l Asashio too. Stay right here while I go 'n give it to her.

main2.line: These kitties got such squishy li'l bellies~ Have a feel for yerself, Commander!

main3.line: What do ya say we invite Michishio 'n Kasumi over for a tea party after our club activities're over?

touch.line: Do ya wanna feed these li'l kitties, Commander? Heheh~

touch2.line: You tryin' to come on to me, Commander? Ain't you a real skirt chaser~

unlock.line: Finally we're through with them mornin' classes~ Commander, would ya fancy havin' lunch with me? Heheh, yer wonderin' what I done made? You'll see for yerself soon 'nuff~

win_mvp.line: Just goes to show what teamwork can accomplish~

battle.line: I don't want to lose any friends today!

detail.line: Commander? If there's anything you want me to do, please let me know. I love helping out.

drop_descrip.line: Third ship of {namecode:145} class destroyers, {namecode:147}.

expedition.line: Commander, shouldn't we go out to meet the girls you sent out on commission? It's about time for them to be getting back.

feeling1.line: I don't think I can be friends with you, Commander...

feeling2.line: Commander, can I give you a hand with anything? Any little old thing? Really, I can do aaaaaanything♪

feeling3.line: I've lost a lot of friends over the years... Asashio and them, Suzukaze, Umikaze... I'm so afraid to lose any more... I'll do anything for my friends...

feeling4.line: Helping people makes me happy. Hm? You don't want me to overdo it? You're worried about me after all, Commander~

feeling5.line: I'm not taking care of myself...? Commander, you're such a worrywart... Since you're so concerned about me, can I ask you for a favor? Commander, I want you to promise me you'll aaalways be with me, forever and ever...

home.line: You came back. Thank goodness.

hp_warning.line: Everyone... just a little bit longer...!

login.line: Oh, hello. Do we have everything we'll need today? Better make sure.

lose.line: Wait! Please don't leave me heeere!

mail.line: Commander, you've got mail.

main1.line: Laa laa laa ♪ It's another beautiful day today, Commander!

main2.line: What should I make for the girls today... Any ideas, Commander?

main3.line: It's great seeing all the happy faces here every day. I truly love it here♪

mission.line: Commander, I'm putting the new mission documents right here, okay?

mission_complete.line: Commander? The mission rewards have been delivered!

profile.line: I'm the third ship of the Asashio-class, Michishio. I was part of the 8th and 24th Destroyer Squadrons, until finally I was assigned to the 4th Destroyer Squadron. That's when I joined the Battle of Leyte Gulf... Hmm, even though I'm pretty unlucky, I'm hoping everyone here will still be my friend!

propose.line: I've never been so happy before... But I know today is just the start of an even happier life, isn't it? It definitely is, isn't it, Commander♪

touch.line: What's wrong, Commander? Are you tired? Thirsty? Hungry? Aaanything you need, I'll take care of it.

touch2.line: Aie! Commander... You're dirty...

unlock.line: Petaaals of the saaaakuuuraaa... Oh, hello, Commander. Nice to meet you. I'm Michishio. It's a pleasure.

upgrade.line: Now I'll be able to protect everyone.

win_mvp.line: B-but everyone pitched in... Um, I'm... I just, everyone's looking at meee!

detail.line: The butterflies go fluttering by~♪ Oh, the Manjuus are also chasing after the butterflies.

drop_descrip.line: Hello, Commander. Oh, you think I look good in this fluttery dress~? Thank you very much!

home.line: I'm glad I came along with my sisters~

login.line: Commander, would you like to take a stroll? There are cute little butterflies in this garden~

main1.line: Ooshio looks very mature in her dress, doesn't she~ It's a bit too soon for me still, right?

main2.line: These balloons? I got them from Ariake. She brought a bunch just for the occasion; isn't that amaaazing?

main3.line: It's so nice throwing a party in nice and warm weather! Commander, do you prefer this, or a fancy banquet?

touch.line: You want to see me spin around? Spiiiin, spiiiin~♪

touch2.line: Eep! Commander, my tail's all tickly~

unlock.line: Hello, Commander. Oh, you think I look good in this fluttery dress~? Thank you very much!

battle.line: Everyone, try to avoid getting hurt if you can...

detail.line: I feel a little sad when I see planes in the air... But it's okay, that's all in the past. What's more important is keeping my chin up and smiling. Right, Commander?

drop_descrip.line: Asashio-class destroyer number four – Arashio.

expedition.line: Commander, I believe the commission team has returned. Let us head over to receive them.

feeling1.line: Oh, Asashio? There there, there's nothing to be afraid of... You'll have to excuse me, I need to stay with Asashio.

feeling2.line: I'd like to get to know you, Commander. *Giggle*, what should we start with?

feeling3.line: Did you have another nightmare? Aww, relax, Commander, everything will be okay.

feeling4.line: It's gotten quite late... But I really enjoyed chatting with you! Say, don't your shoulders get stiff from sitting down all day? Would you like a massage?

feeling5.line: We're all to ourselves now. My heart's been thumping for some time now... Commander, could we huddle up next to each other, just for a little while?

home.line: Stellar work, Commander. Would you like to rest your head in my lap?

hp_warning.line: You must remain calm in the face of danger. Don't worry about me.

login.line: You don't find my appearance odd? I feel the best way to greet someone is with a smile!

lose.line: There's no need to worry, we'll win the next time!

mail.line: You've received mail. Shall we go see what it is, Commander?

main1.line: Asashio and I have always been together. Yup, we even sleep in the same bed. She's so quiet when she's sleeping.

main2.line: We might not always be able to stick together, but we'd never leave anyone behind... That's why this place feels like home to me.

main3.line: I've made you some tea. Take your time to savor it. By the way, is my tea-making ability to your liking?

mission.line: New missions have appeared. I'll gladly help you with them, Commander.

mission_complete.line: A mission has been completed. You did a great job, Commander!

profile.line: I am Arashio, the fourth Asashio-class destroyer. I was part of Destroyer Division 8 along with Ooshio, Michishio, and of course Asashio. Lastly... I hope I can stay with everyone this time around.

propose.line: Commander, I won't say anything indecent, but there's one thing I want to tell you... Umm... I'll always be there to support you. Your side is the place where I truly belong.

skill.line: I'll keep everyone out of harm's way.

touch.line: Mmh... I try not to think about why we all got separated. Besides, we got to reunite here, so let's instead live our lives happily ever after.

touch2.line: Eeeeek! ... Is this truly necessary to become an adult?

unlock.line: Destroyer Arashio, here to join your fleet. I'll provide everyone with the support they need~

upgrade.line: Now it'll be easier for me to avoid getting hurt. Thank you, Commander.

win_mvp.line: Why, I'm the MVP...? Hmm, this might not be so bad.

detail.line: The shimmering of fireworks reflected across the water's surface... How enchanting and ephemeral...

drop_descrip.line: Looks like you found me, Commander. Hehe, want to light some fireworks with me? Spending time together should be more fun than being alone, right?

home.line: Is this... a new sparkler? Thanks, Commander~

login.line: Commander, do you like fireworks? In that case, I'll help you light some~

main1.line: Sparklers might not be as gorgeous as the fireworks that blossom in the sky, but it's nice to be able to have something you can enjoy at your own pace.

main2.line: Asashio, will you be able to remember this place? Try not to get lost, okay?

main3.line: It's so quiet along the river bank... You can even hear the soft crackling of fireworks.

touch.line: Commander, I'm really glad I get to enjoy fireworks with you and the others~

touch2.line: Eek... Are you doing this because there are no people nearby...?

unlock.line: Looks like you found me, Commander. Hehe, want to light some fireworks with me? Spending time together should be more fun than being alone, right?

battle.line: Blue skies, blue sea, daba-dee...

detail.line: Whenever I ask Kinu if I can borrow her cute mask... she just tells me no way in heck...

drop_descrip.line: Special Type I-class destroyer number 10 – Uranami.

expedition.line: The commission team's back. Oooh, riiight, you already knew that.

feeling1.line: Laaaaaame.

feeling2.line: I keep a collection of cute pets. Stop by again and I'll show you my axofrostl and swolejuu.

feeling3.line: The massive Meowfficer's super fluffy... I mean, ripped. Built like a fridge!

feeling4.line: I'd love to hear some of Prof Commander's interesting little trivia. Tell me something about ghosts.

feeling5.line: Commander, when I'm with you it feels like I'm a fish in water, a bee that found honey, a ticking time bomb of joy that goes BOOOOM! ...Something in that ballpark, basically.

home.line: Welcome back, tweety-doo. That's what a Manjuu would say. Yup-yup...

hp_warning.line: I'm super scared right now.

login.line: Could you give me the go-ahead to play now?

lose.line: Time to scamper. Don't wanna be left behind.

mail.line: Whoosh, here comes a letter. Aaaand there it is.

main1.line: Uranami rhymes with rural mommy. Doodle-loo, nothing better to dooo.

main2.line: Help friends in need, defeat enemies with speed. That's my little motto.

main3.line: When I tell folks about the things I like, they all look super weirded out, then they strangerzone me. But oh well.

mission.line: One super serving of missions with a diet soda, coming right up.

mission_complete.line: Nice work on that serving of missions, Commander. You want more, help yourself.

profile.line: I'm the Type I... No wait, Type II... Last try: middle-of-the-pack destroyer, Uranami. My friends and I in Destroyer Division 19 worked really hard. Okay, serious question: what Type am I, exactly?

propose.line: Promise ring. So glitteryyyy. Can I just keep it on forever? Hehehe... I super love you, Commander.

touch.line: Something bothering you upstairs, Commander?

touch2.line: Whoopeeee.

unlock.line: What am I doing here? ...Hmmm? You're adopting me? Aaaaall righty. You lead-a-dee, I'll follow-a-loo.

upgrade.line: Done enhancy-pantsing yet? C'mawn, I wanna play.

win_mvp.line: I'm awesome... Or so they say. But why?

detail.line: Commander, come ski with me... Yeah, bring the Manjuus too...!

drop_descrip.line: It's snowing...! I've finished rallying the forces... so let us advance!

login.line: The best thing about winter... is skiing in the snow!

main1.line: Today, I will transform into a snow bunny!

main2.line: The snow is so sparkly and soft... it's very fun.

main3.line: You shouldn't underestimate me~ I've been practicing this whole time.

touch.line: Eep?! Commander, your hands are cold...

touch2.line: My outfit is thick, therefore wholesome...

unlock.line: It's snowing...! I've finished rallying the forces... so let us advance!

battle.line: Don't think too hard, just do your part and we'll win. Let's go!

detail.line: Oh, also, did you know my original name was "Destroyer No. 9"? ... I suppose it's a good thing they decided to change it.

drop_descrip.line: Kamikaze-class destroyer number five – Hatakaze.

expedition.line: Before you go collect those mission rewards, remember to give thanks to those who worked so hard for them.

feeling1.line: Could you acknowledge the error of your ways before other girls start thinking poorly of you?

feeling2.line: If you'd like, perhaps I could give you a wise lady's advice on how to interact with others?

feeling3.line: Different people must be treated in their own unique way. This is no secret to social success, but it will help make you more sociable.

feeling4.line: Ah, you should also take this amulet. It will make you more sociable. But beware: if you use it to hurt someone, you will be too.

feeling5.line: If something's on your mind, tell me. I may be old, but my experience has been useful for solving many problems. Besides, why would you hide anything from your partner? Ahah.

home.line: Admirable work out there. Have some tea and reflect on your tactics.

hp_warning.line: Agh... So this is why they say you can't flee from pain...

login.line: A commander should at the very least be on time. But considering your achievements up till now, you at least deserve some praise.

lose.line: It seems I have not kept up with the times...

mail.line: Check the new mail you received. Oh, also, I have a copy of it as well.

main1.line: I think Matsukaze feels compelled to worry about us so much, and sometimes we don't even know how we should respond...

main2.line: If you want to slack off all day, just resign. Oh, also, you have much work left to do.

main3.line: Kamikaze, could you stop teasing the Commander?

mission.line: Those with talent work a lot. Do not leave missions incomplete.

mission_complete.line: Well... I wasn't expecting this big of a reward.

profile.line: I'm Hatakaze, a Kamikaze-class destroyer. Oh, also, though my class might make me seem experienced, not only did I mainly engage in escort missions and achieve nothing spectacular, my story ends with my wish to fight the bitter end, like Kamikaze did, going unfulfilled. For someone like me, that's rather deplorable.

propose.line: It's me you want? But I'm not attractive, I'm just a bother who likes nagging about you... You're really not joking? I-if so... *Ahem*, then till the oceans of the world dry up, I will remain by your side.

skill.line: It seems to be my turn.

touch.line: Anti-air is crucial. Oh, also, the price one pays for negligence is much higher than you think.

touch2.line: ... Now if you'd just use that bravery for something else, my view of you might actually change.

unlock.line: You must be the Commander. I see... No, I'm not looking disgruntled. I'm Hatakaze of Destroyer Division 5. Oh, also, be ready. I will watch over you as your superior from now on.

upgrade.line: You needn't go so far for the likes of me... But I'm still grateful.

win_mvp.line: A victory is merely a victory. Garishness and applause are needless.

battle.line: Hehehe~ Now it's my turn to take command!

detail.line: You've heard I've only been on transport missions? No, I-I've totally fought before too!

drop_descrip.line: Yuugumo-class destroyer number five – Makinami.

expedition.line: If you don't take commissions seriously then you'll be in serious trouble!

feeling1.line: Hmph. ...Leave me alone.

feeling2.line: It'd be a shame to not go out and play on a sunny day like this! Right? Let's head out~

feeling3.line: Oww... I tripped again... Can you give me a piggyback ride back home, Commander...?

feeling4.line: Fine... I'll start looking where I'm going and not run and jump so much... Doesn't it get boring for you, always walking like that...?

feeling5.line: I-is this a bride carry?! H-hehehe... But I still think I prefer your piggyback rides...

headtouch.line: Do you want to do my hair...?

home.line: The team has returned! Hehehe~ Welcome back, everyone~

hp_warning.line: C-could we retreat?!

login.line: C'mon, stop being so blue and be positively positive!

lose.line: All we can do is place our hopes on the next one...

mail.line: Hey, Commander... Can you read what's written in this letter for me...?

main1.line: Kongou-san and Haruna-san were so nice to me... You should be too, Commander!

main2.line: Doing Tokyo Express runs... wasn't any fun at all...

main3.line: Night battles are what Desron 2 do better than anyone else!

mission.line: Oh, we've got another mission...

mission_complete.line: Heeey! A commission's done!

profile.line: I'm Makinami, I belonged to Destroyer Division 31. Serving as Kongou-san's and Haruna-san's escort, I helped in tons of battles in the Pacific! ...Hehehe~ I gave the Eagle Union a real beating in the Battle of Tassafaronga!

propose.line: If you ever get hurt, I promise I'll carry YOU back home! So can you give me a piggyback ride now? Hehehe~

touch.line: Umm, Commander... I'm not slacking off on pur... Eeek?!

touch2.line: Commander, why are you suddenly glomping me?!

unlock.line: I'm Makinami, the Yuugumo-class destroyer! I surfed the waves to come here! I'll be counting on you, Commander!

upgrade.line: Heh heh~ I feel stronger!

win_mvp.line: I'm just the best ship ever~

detail.line: I was running earlier and tripped on something... But Hamakaze helped me back up, and now I feel fine!

drop_descrip.line: All right, everything looks good! I'm super excited and my batteries are fully charged! I'm heading out~!

home.line: Oh right, it's almost time for class! I'm gonna need my notepad... Wait, huh? Where'd it go?

login.line: Hey, listen! I've heard there are these cool legendary things at school! Let's go check if they're true or not!

main1.line: Oh, it's Haruna! Hey, Harunaaaaa! Let's head to the classroom together~

main2.line: Hey, I know! We can trade snacks with each other, Commander! Lemme see what you brought for lunch~!

main3.line: Huh? You don't have any evening plans? In that case... Let's come up with something to do!

touch.line: You're gonna give me extra lessons, Commander? Hehe~ That sounds like fun!

touch2.line: W-wait, is this... Th-that "student and teacher" thing...?!

unlock.line: All right, everything looks good! I'm super excited and my batteries are fully charged! I'm heading out~!

battle.line: Foo, let's do our best?

detail.line: Kasumi can see lots of things that others can't, like Foo here, for example. Kasumi saw that Foo was all alone, so we became friends.

drop_descrip.line: Asashio-class destroyer number 10 – Kasumi.

expedition.line: "The commission team has been waiting for Commander for a long, long time." ...That's what Foo told me.

feeling1.line: Don't be sad, Commander. Kasumi will be your friend.

feeling2.line: Foo can't handle being around lots of people, so Kasumi also dislikes crowded places...

feeling3.line: Commander, Foo and Kasumi will always stay by yourside, because you're our friend.

feeling4.line: Commander, do you want to watch a movie with Kasumi? Kasumi likes movies with lots of friends that look like Foo... Let's watch one together?

feeling5.line: Foo will chase away all the bad guys that Commander cannot see. Kasumi will also protect you. We'll always be together...

home.line: Foo, Commander's back. Commander, your tea.

hp_warning.line: Kasumi... is very strong when she gets serious!

login.line: Hello, Commander. Foo, say hi to Commander too, okay?

lose.line: Foo, make sure to... protect the others.

mail.line: It'd be nice if Foo could get the mail...

main1.line: Foo is my good friend. We're always together.

main2.line: Kasumi... gets tired easily... Commander, your chest is really comfortable.

main3.line: Foo is always scared around Shiranui... Commander, is there no way to help Foo not be afraid of her will-o'-the-wisps...?

mission.line: Foo told me... that there are still missions left, and that Commander should stop slacking off...

mission_complete.line: "Mission complete~ Good job, Commander, Kasumi will give you a reward" ...Foo, what are you saying...

profile.line: I'm Kasumi, from the Asashio-class. During Operation Rei-go, my friends and I did our best to complete our missions. Without them, I would not have been able to accomplish anything alone.

propose.line: Commander, you've given me the most precious gift. That's why I'll give it my all to become the person most precious to you. ...Foo, what's the matter? I have to act more lovey-dovey? Um, then... *kiss*... Like that?

touch.line: Commander, would you like to talk to Foo?

touch2.line: Commander, Foo is biting you.

unlock.line: I'm Kasumi. Commander, are you my friend?

upgrade.line: Foo, is Kasumi any different...?

win_mvp.line: Foo, we did it.

detail.line: There's still a lot of the mochi Shiranui brought over... Commander, do you want some?

drop_descrip.line: Warm and comforting clothes... Warm and comforting red bean soup... Ahh, I love New Year's.

home.line: Foo, you want to eat some mochi too? ...I'm not sure that's possible, sorry.

login.line: Commander, Happy New Year's. Would you like... some piping hot red bean soup?

main1.line: The mochi inside red bean soup... is delicious and fun to play with. Seconds, please~♪

main2.line: Miss Ghost, would you like to be friends with Foo? ...Huh? You aren't really a ghost?

main3.line: I hope a new horror movie comes out during New Year's. Commander, I'd like to watch one with you.

touch.line: Commander, want some mochi? Say ahhn~

unlock.line: Warm and comforting clothes... Warm and comforting red bean soup... Ahh, I love New Year's.

detail.line: My bag is unzipped? Must be one of Foo's pranks. It's definitely not because Kasumi left in a hurry.

drop_descrip.line: Kasumi and Foo are excited about the new semester. Are you too, Commander?

home.line: You're giving a speech at the opening ceremony? I wonder what you'll talk about...

login.line: You're right on time, Commander. Just like Foo and Kasumi.

main1.line: Foo follows Kasumi everywhere, to and from school, and even in class.

main2.line: There are will-o'-the-wisps around port... Maybe Foo can befriend them.

main3.line: I wish Foo could help me with my homework.

touch.line: I dropped something? Thanks for telling me, Commander.

touch2.line: Commander, Foo is jabbing at you.

unlock.line: Kasumi and Foo are excited about the new semester. Are you too, Commander?

detail.line: Kasumi is here, so Foo is never lonely. And Kasumi has lots of friends, so everything is good.

drop_descrip.line: Kasumi thinks that her outfit has gotten a bit breezier. Foo said the same thing.

home.line: Welcome back, Commander. Kasumi brewed some tea. Have a cup.

login.line: Hello. Foo and Kasumi have been waiting for you.

main1.line: Kasumi wants to help people. Foo does, too. We're gonna try to be as helpful as we can.

main2.line: Kasumi has more energy than before. If you feel tired, just sit next to Kasumi and rest.

main3.line: Shiranui became a friend, so Foo isn't scared of her anymore.

touch.line: Foo said, "I wish I could talk to the commander too."

unlock.line: Kasumi thinks that her outfit has gotten a bit breezier. Foo said the same thing.

battle.line: Be careful, everyone. Watch out for the submarines...!

detail.line: I love the way countless flowers bloom vividly during the spring, but even so, I wouldn't want it to be spring all year long - that would be unfair to the flowers that only bloom in other seasons. Mhm, I'm sure the four seasons exist so that all flowers have a chance to bloom. Hehe~

drop_descrip.line: Akizuki-class destroyer number thirteen – Hanazuki.

expedition.line: The commission fleet has returned. Commander, should I bring some herbal tea with me to welcome them back?

feeling1.line: Commander, I do not wish to see you ostracized by anyone... But at this rate, I may not be able to do anything for you...

feeling2.line: The sun is shining brightly, and it's another beautiful day outside. Commander, if you aren't busy, would you like to view the flowers with me?

feeling3.line: It's embarrassing to admit it, but... I tried to pick up gardening several times but kept getting stuck because I couldn't decide what I wanted to grow... Commander, do you have any flowers that you're partial towards? I want to make up my mind this time!

feeling4.line: Some flowers bloom all year long while others are fleeting and ephemeral. Some are purely ornamental, while others have therapeutic uses... Commander, do you like flowers that bloom dazzlingly, or those that bloom silently and out of view? ...Ah, sorry, I'm not making any sense...

feeling5.line: Commander, I hope this is not too presumptuous of me, but may I decorate your office with some fresh flowers? I want to give you something that reminds you of me, even when I am absent... It's just a little selfish whim of mine, hehe~

home.line: Welcome back, Commander. The port is like our home now, nothing is more reassuring than being back here, right?

hp_warning.line: Ngh... As long as the others are safe...

login.line: Welcome back, Commander. Shall we continue our work? Should you have any concerns, please feel free to consult me. I shall do all I can to assist you.

lose.line: I see, because of my indecisiveness... I am terribly sorry for dragging everyone down...

mail.line: New mail seems to have arrived. If you need me to sort it for you, please let me know.

main1.line: Commander, do you prefer herbal tea, or black tea?

main2.line: Commander, Harutsuki seems to have gotten herself in some trouble. I'd like to check on her, so would you mind if I left you for a bit?

main3.line: "The sun in the west, the moon in the east, canola blossoms inbetween." I'd love to see this scenery myself.

mission.line: So many unfinished tasks... Commander, wh-where should we start?

mission_complete.line: Congratulations! As expected Commander, you've completed our missions with flying colors!

profile.line: I entered service during the tail end of the War as an Akizuki-class specialized for anti-air and anti-submarine capabilities... Err, I guess it was the Fuyutsuki-class... Or was it the Michitsuki-class... Err... S-sorry, I still have a lot to learn, so I'd greatly appreciate your guidance!

propose.line: I see that while my heart was still wavering, you've already made up yours. Then, I won't hesitate to reciprocate your feelings either... Hanazuki will gladly accept this ring. I'm so glad that I can be someone who is important to you...

skill.line: Hanazuki is here to offer support!

touch.line: Anything you need me to do, as long as it is within my abilities, I would gladly do for you.

touch2.line: Eek?! Um, if I may be so bold... this sort of behavior is... It would be best not to do this to the other girls...

unlock.line: I, destroyer Hanazuki from the Sakura Empire, would like to extend my humble greetings to you. As a member of the Akizuki class, I specialize in anti-air and anti-sub warfare, but please do not hesitate to call upon me where I am needed.

upgrade.line: I see, I see. That was quite educational.

win_mvp.line: It's only right that I offer my gratitude to everyone who fought alongside me.

detail.line: Even though it's the same sea as always, watching the clouds with you while wearing this unusual outfit is filling me with novel sensations I've never felt before...

drop_descrip.line: I've heard some say that summer is the season of cherry blossoms, lotus petals, and sunflowers, but... If you ask me, being able to leisurely enjoy the breeze with you feels pretty good too. Hehe~

home.line: Are you weary, Commander? If so, why not try some of my lavender honey tea? It's great for recovering from fatigue.

login.line: Today may be my day off, but if there is anything I can do for you, please do not hesitate to call upon me.

main1.line: Look, Commander, that coral reef... Hehehe, the "flowers" in the sea are quite beautiful as well, aren't they?

main2.line: This swimsuit... took a lot of agonizing over, but I eventually made my decision... Commander, what do you think? Does it look good on me?

main3.line: Gah...! ...Ah, s-sorry! I was just looking at the ocean... and suddenly shifted into anti-submarine mode... I know I shouldn't be so uptight during time off!

touch.line: Do you need me to lend you a swim ring?

touch2.line: Eek?! Ehh?! S-sorry! Ah, um, Commander, the strap is...

unlock.line: I've heard some say that summer is the season of cherry blossoms, lotus petals, and sunflowers, but... If you ask me, being able to leisurely enjoy the breeze with you feels pretty good too. Hehe~

battle.line: Let us ring in the new year with a splendid victory!

detail.line: The floral patterns on the Dragon Empery's dresses are so pretty... How should I thank Miss Aurora for picking out such a wonderful selection?

drop_descrip.line: What kinds of flowers should I decorate the office with for the Lunar New Year...? Ugh, I just can't decide! Um, Commander, will you be inspecting the interior? I'll show you around! Phew...

expedition.line: Everyone in the commission fleet has returned. I've prepared some gifts for them... Oh, should I set off some firerackers first?

headtouch.line: Commander... *blushes*

home.line: Zzz... Nnh... Hwah?! C-Commander? I'm so sorry, I must've fallen asleep while waiting for you...

login.line: Please tell me which tasks you'd like to start with, and which events you'd like to attend.

main1.line: The entire port is filled with the gentle aroma of fresh flowers~ Even though it's not quite spring yet, doesn't this holiday carry a bit of that longing for the early arrival of spring?

main2.line: Hibiki, and Kasumi? Wh-what's the matter...? Recommended events? Um, um... errr... C-Commander, help me...

main3.line: nil

touch2.line: Commander, um... N-nevermind! It's nothing...!

unlock.line: What kinds of flowers should I decorate the office with for the Lunar New Year...? Ugh, I just can't decide! Um, Commander, will you be inspecting the interior? I'll show you around! Phew...

battle.line: I'm the flagship? All right, just leave it to me!

detail.line: I give off warm and fuzzy vibes? Ehehe, I've heard that from the others as well~ It's a little embarrassing... Nuh uh, I don't mind at all. I'm really glad to hear it!

drop_descrip.line: Yuugumo-class destroyer number four – Naganami.

expedition.line: Commander, everyone in the commission fleet has come home. I'm sure they're all tired, so I'll go give them a warm hug!

feeling1.line: Commander, if there's anything bothering you, please let me know. I'll be waiting for you... as long as it takes...

feeling2.line: Everyone in the Mutsuki class is super fluffy and cute! Being at this port makes me so happy~!

feeling3.line: My tail is warm and fluffy, but Wakaba's is shinier in comparison... Hatsushimo's is slender, and Shimakaze's is tiny... Um, there are all different sorts!

feeling4.line: Oyashio taught me a little trick! If I remember properly, it goes a little like... this! This circle on your forehead is supposed to make you luckier when it comes to your love life, and also helps you become happier!

feeling5.line: Still not enough good fortune in your life? ...You leave me no other choice then! Even if you have bad luck, there's a way to compensate for it! I just have to pass it to you directly... Mmwah~

home.line: Commander, good job in battle! Hurry, come sit over here~ I'm going to give your shoulders a nice rub!

hp_warning.line: My friends are still fighting, so I can't afford to go down here!

login.line: Welcome back, Commander! Um, Naganami will always be waiting for you right here! That's because, well... I'm happiest when I'm by your side!

lose.line: I'll have to work much harder if I want to become an ideal flagship...

mail.line: Commander, new mail has arrived. Here, I brought it for you. Maybe someone brought good tidings!

main1.line: Jintsuu is always so knowledgeable and reliable... I wish I could be just like her...

main2.line: Commander, can you let me be flagship next time? I'll work even harder, for the sake of everyone's happiness!

main3.line: Lately, everyone has been circulating rumors that hugging me or cuddling my tail has healing properties, like coming out of a bath. They're even saying that it can cure colds... There's no way that's true, right?!

mission.line: I can probably help out with transport missions, but as for other tasks... By the way, Commander, I see you tackling all sorts of different missions every day! That's really amazing!

mission_complete.line: Mission complete! Great work today! Come, come, don't be shy – come rest on this big fluffy pillow!

profile.line: I'm Naganami, fourth ship of the Yuugumo class. During the War, I was primarily involved in transport operations, but I did participate in some large-scale operations and even served as flagship. Any hardship on the battlefield can be overcome as long as you believe in one another... I just know it!

propose.line: Um... Commander, I thought we had grown a lot closer, but this still feels a bit awkward... Wh-what should I do? ...Ah! Commander, try hugging my tail! I'm sure its warmth and fluffiness will help you loosen up! Mhm!

skill.line: Try this torpedo strike on for size!

touch.line: I'm more than just a ball of fluff, you know? Look, it's my smile and my ability to bring warmth to others that counts~

touch2.line: C-Commander, it's still work hoursss...

unlock.line: So this place is the port? Huh... Oh, Commander! I'm the fourth ship of the Yuugumo class, Naganami. It's a pleasure to finally meet you! Um... what's my selling point... Love! I love you, and everyone else as well!

upgrade.line: The feeling of warmth and safety... this is what it feels like to get stronger... Commander, thank you very much!

win_mvp.line: I didn't even realize I got MVP... But, this was only possible because of everyone's hard work!

detail.line: I want to be a maid who can bring happiness to everyone! ...I'm going to have to work even harder to make that happen...

drop_descrip.line: Akashi pushed me into getting this outfit, saying that it would surely make you happy, but... What do you think...?

feeling5.line: Commander, your entire body is radiating happiness – I can smell it! Huh? You want to try smelling my happiness? Um, in that case, come a bit closer... Even closer...

home.line: Commander... Um, I mean, Master! Welcome back! Whether you want to enjoy some refreshments, or take a nap on my tail... either way is fine!

login.line: I'll do my best to bring happiness to everyone at port, Commander! Just believe that one day, this place will be filled with happiness!

main1.line: This is the first time I've made sweets by hand. Commander, how are they? You'd like to have some more? Of course! I'll make them for you right away!

main2.line: Let's emulate the Royal Maids and form the Maids of the 2nd Torpedo Squadron! What do you think, commander?

main3.line: "Just spotting Naganami immediately causes one's mood to improve?" ...More weird rumors are circulating again... But if you believe that, Commander... Hehehe, I guess I'll believe it too!

touch.line: Being able to go about business as usual in this kind of outfit is no easy feat... Real maids are truly something...

touch2.line: Commander, at least let me set the tray down first! Eek! It's going to fall!

unlock.line: Akashi pushed me into getting this outfit, saying that it would surely make you happy, but... What do you think...?

battle.line: I, I'll do my best...!

detail.line: You feel a sense of relief when you see me? I'm not quite sure what you mean by that, but I'm glad that you're happy...

drop_descrip.line: There's still some time before the banquet begins, and I'm afraid I'm feeling a little sleepy... W-would you mind if I took a nap? Thank you...

expedition.line: Commander, our friends have returned from their commission. Sh-should we head down to welcome them back?

feeling5.line: Commander, are you happy? ...I don't mean like in general, but... like, when we're together... Um... As for me, when it's just the two of us, I feel amazingly happy...♡

home.line: Do you like it when I massage your back with my feet like this, Commander? ...Not in that sense? I see... I don't really get it though...

login.line: Commander, did you come just to see me...? Ohh, for the first thing I see when I wake up to be you... I must be dreaming...!

mail.line: We've got new mail. I'm sure it's good news.

main1.line: My tail is fluffy and warm, and you can even use it as a blanket... At least, that's what Oyashio and the others keep saying. Would you like to give it a try, Commander?

main2.line: Commander, whenever I gaze at you, whenever I talk to you, I feel so at ease that I could go to sleep... Hm? You feel the same way about me?

main3.line: This outfit feels a bit tight around the chest... Um, Commander, p-please don't stare at me so much...

mission.line: Commander, your missions are of utmost importance... Mm, so I'll wait for you right here...

mission_complete.line: Great job on finishing your mission, Commander! Um, ahem! Don't you want to cuddle up with my big, fluffy tail...?

touch.line: It's not time for the party yet...? Then, um, let's stay like this for a bit longer...

touch2.line: *pant* *pant*...

unlock.line: There's still some time before the banquet begins, and I'm afraid I'm feeling a little sleepy... W-would you mind if I took a nap? Thank you...

battle.line: It's time for me to get serious...!

detail.line: The sound of my voice puts you at ease? Th-that's great... it was worth practicing ahead of time!

drop_descrip.line: I wanted to help you relieve some stress, so I thought I would read some folk tales to you... When I mentioned that, Akashi suggested these clothes to me... Wh-what do you think?

expedition.line: Commander, the girls are back from their commissions! I'll head out to greet them!

home.line: Commander, good work! I'm ready for you as well. Well then, um, let's get started. Ahem... A long, long time ago...

login.line: Tonight, I'll be putting all my heart into reading, all for your sake!

mail.line: Oh, there's some new mail for us! ...I wonder if it's the storybooks I had ordered.

main1.line: ...The end. Commander, for the next story, should I try speaking in a softer voice... Huh? Commander? Looks like you've already fallen asleep, hehe.

main2.line: I wanted to surprise you, so I'll be reading one of my personal favorites to you today. If there's something you want to listen to next time, please let me know, and I'll have it ready!

main3.line: nil

mission.line: No more~ No matter how much you want to keep listening to the story, you need to prioritize your missions first!

mission_complete.line: You've finished your missions! Good job with them. Since you held tight and worked hard to complete them, I've prepared lots of rewards for you~

touch.line: You want me to read the next story? S-sure, I'd love to!

touch2.line: I-I'm going to lose my place...!

unlock.line: I wanted to help you relieve some stress, so I thought I would read some folk tales to you... When I mentioned that, Akashi suggested these clothes to me... Wh-what do you think?

battle.line: For the happiness of those we love!

detail.line: I'm by your side. Always have been, always will be. Your happiness is my happiness, Commander.

drop_descrip.line: Now that the big day is here, I'm awfully nervous... I-I'll be in your care now and forever, okay?

feeling5.line: In sickness and in health... No! You are already happy now, Commander, so... Healthy times aside, I don't know about... I-I'm sorry! Forget it, umm... Let's just be together forever!

home.line: Welcome home...d-dear! Calling you that now is still a little embarrassing!

login.line: It's amazing how happy I am just to be with you forever. Commander, let's enjoy another blissful day together!

main1.line: I've never done the san san kudo ceremony before. I hope I don't mess it up...

main2.line: My white kimono looks lovely? Why, thank you. I'll cherish the memory of it for all my life.

main3.line: Moving is rather difficult when I have to worry about my tail and the train... Heehee! That's another fond memory to look back on.

mission.line: It's time for a mission. I will naturally assist you. After all, finishing it early means more quality time with you!

mission_complete.line: Well done on another completed mission! Now we can spend some time together, just the two of us.

touch.line: You want to hold hands, don't you? I'd be happy to!

touch2.line: If you want to cuddle up with me and my tail, then...I don't mind. Indulge yourself.

unlock.line: Now that the big day is here, I'm awfully nervous... I-I'll be in your care now and forever, okay?

battle.line: May the odds ever be in your favor! Go forth!

detail.line: When my friends are counting on me, I can feel power surging within me that makes me feel like I can do anything!

drop_descrip.line: Akizuki-class destroyer number three – Suzutsuki.

expedition.line: The commission fleet has returned! Lemme take home the extras!

feeling1.line: Commander, you're gonna make me hate you...

feeling2.line: I may come across as a braggart, but that's because I'm pretty reliable! "Oh, Suzutsuki, you saved me! I don't know what I would've done without you!" Yeah, I get that a lot~

feeling3.line: Commander, you can rely on me as well! ...What?! You think you can one-up me...?!

feeling4.line: Hmm... What would I like the commander to do for me? ...Make tea? Pack my lunch? Carry me back to the dorms after I fall asleep? ...Th-th-that's way too embarrassing!

feeling5.line: Commander, get over here! Hup~ ...Mmhmm, that's much cozier. Now it feels more like I'm relying on you, doesn't it? See, you'll also have to take good care of me from now on~ Just kidding~♪ Ahaha!

headtouch.line: Look, fluffy and super pattable, right? ...Hey, I'm talking about Pooky, not my ears!

home.line: Team A is directly under my command. Teams B and C will follow the plan, and then... Oh, Commander, when'd you get back?

hp_warning.line: The real fight's only getting started!

login.line: Welcome back! ...Got any new jobs? I'm down for anything!

lose.line: Guh... No matter what, we all have to make it back safely...!

mail.line: Huh? The envelope got torn? ...Ahaha... Sorry 'bout that, must've been Pooky...

main1.line: "The invincible Suzutsuki is here! Your attacks shall not put a scratch on me!" How'd that sound? Hya hah!

main2.line: Ahaha! You'd rather sit atop Commander's head instead of mine? Very well, go forth! Oh, but no pranks though!

main3.line: Commander, you sure have a lot of work, don't you~ Look, Isokaze, Urakaze, being a warlord or a general is a lot of hard work. A better job would be to become Commander's retainers!

mission.line: A tough mission, huh? Lemme take a look, maybe I can help out!

mission_complete.line: Mission complete! Commander, don't forget about the rewards!

profile.line: I'm Suzutsuki, Akizuki-class destroyer. I was a member of the 61st DesDiv along with Akizuki and Hatsuzuki, and escorted Musashi and participated in Noshiro's rescue mission! Not a shabby record, right? I had a close call at the Battle of Bou-no-Misaki when I got hit by two torpedoes, but I managed to survive until the end!

propose.line: Ahahaha... Being in a situation like this is quite nerve-racking, isn't it? ...I thought I had mentally prepared myself... Commander, you c-can handle the rest... right...?

touch.line: This marking on my right cheek? You haven't heard of it, Commander? It's the latest fashion trend! Here, I'll draw one on for you!

touch2.line: C-Commander! Jeez, there are some things that you shouldn't be doing!

unlock.line: Ahaha, Pooky, listen up, we're gonna live here from now on! Uhh... Third ship of the Akizuki-class, Suzutsuki, reporting in! I'll be the one to protect my comrades and you, Commander! Just kidding~♪

upgrade.line: Give me more power, so that I may protect everyone!

win_mvp.line: The enemy general’s head is mine~! Just kidding, ahaha~♪

detail.line: I'm pretty refreshing and cool, right? Just like my name suggests~

drop_descrip.line: Commander, over here! We're about to start without you! Ahaha, what would you like to do, Commander? Beach volleyball? Sandcastle building? We can also go relax in the water if you'd like!

feeling5.line: Phew... Playing by the beach is super fun, but after all the commotion, I could use some relaxation... Yup, I'm gonna lie down right here! Mm... Yeah, just stay put like that. Hehe~

home.line: Not enough people for a game of beach volleyball? All right! I'll go play some watermelon splitting with Georgia first!

login.line: Commander, time out! Look, the others have already started playing without you~ Fine, fine... I shall be the one to accompany you then!

main1.line: Do we have enough people to build a sand castle? Great, count me in as well! Wait, Commander, hold on!

main2.line: Pooky likes coming to the sea as well, isn't that right~? Ah, careful not to fall into the water!

main3.line: Agano's not here? That's too bad, I was looking forward to playing with her... Commander, why do you look so relieved? Hm? It's just my imagination?

touch.line: Woah?! ...Oh, it's you, Commander, you surprised me... Hibiki shoved a crab in my face earlier and it gave me a nasty pinch...

touch2.line: Jeez, Commander! What are you doing in front of this many people?!

unlock.line: Commander, over here! We're about to start without you! Ahaha, what would you like to do, Commander? Beach volleyball? Sandcastle building? We can also go relax in the water if you'd like!

battle.line: You ready, Pooky? Let's— go!

detail.line: These markings are the proof of my battle scars as a warrior... they're not just doodles! Ugh... I swear, I'll be back for revenge after I train some more!

drop_descrip.line: I, Akizuki-class destroyer, Suzutsuki, shall not allow you to pass through these arches! Hwuh?! I missed the return again...!

expedition.line: The girls from the commission fleet are back! Darn it, I wish Hatsushimo could come with me!

login.line: Happy New Year, Commander!

mail.line: Suzutsuki, now reading the contents of your mail out loud!

main1.line: Aaahhhhh!! Jean Bart, you don't have to shank every shuttlecock out of existence!

main2.line: Pooky, I got some sunflower seeds from Hanazuki! Here, come and eat your fill~ Grow big and strong and scare the heck out of the commander~ Ahaha!

main3.line: I can't sit still during the New Year! After all, there are so many things going on that only happen during this time of year!

touch.line: Commander, make sure the matches continue smoothly!

unlock.line: I, Akizuki-class destroyer, Suzutsuki, shall not allow you to pass through these arches! Hwuh?! I missed the return again...!

battle.line: Enough talk! Have at you!

detail.line: All you do is loaf around in here... Are you a commander, or a deadbeat?

drop_descrip.line: Kamikaze-class destroyer number six – Oite.

expedition.line: The commission team has returned. I will see to the transport of the goods, and you to its inspection.

feeling1.line: I expect no betterment from you. Go on, let your name be irreversibly tarnished.

feeling2.line: What do you need from me? Make it quick.

feeling3.line: You need an attendant for your outing? Understoo– Wait, why would you need an attendant for a tour of your own port? ...You want to "hang out" with me? What does that mean?

feeling4.line: I cannot wrap my head around your need for an attendant when there are no hostiles at the port... Nor do I grasp this "hang out" business! Although I did enjoy our friendly exchange! E-e-end of report!

feeling5.line: All your talk of attendants and "hanging out" was just an attempt to seduce me, was it not? N-no, I mean nothing bad by it! Oh, forget it! You toyed with my heart, and now you must o-own up to it!

headtouch.line: What the–?! K-k-keep your hands off my ears!

home.line: No unauthorized persons entered the office in your absence. End of report.

hp_warning.line: When push comes to shove, retaliate...!

login.line: You came of your own accord. How fortunate... Never you mind. Get to work.

lose.line: We must start anew at boot camp...

mail.line: Correspondence has arrived. Don't come nagging later, saying I didn't inform you.

main1.line: How, I wonder, would one go about making Agano stop touching my ears...

main2.line: Urgh... Reading so much fine print text has given me a headache. Commander, requesting permission to rest...

main3.line: I like the quiet of the office, free from the jarring hum of propeller aircraft.

mission.line: To think a trivial task would have you up-ended like this... If you so insist it's impossible, then I will set an example.
