mission_complete.line: Mission complete. Will you get a move on already and process the rewards?

profile.line: I served as flagship of Destroyer Division 29 within Destroyer Squadron 6. I performed various escort and transport missions. Leave any tasks of this nature to me. End of report.

propose.line: I don't know what to do at this ceremony! You insisted on it, so it's your responsibility to g-guide me through it! E-end of report...

touch.line: Whuah! Would you STOP tickling me?

touch2.line: Whuah?! Wh-wh-wha-what has gotten into you, fool?!

unlock.line: I am Kamikaze-class destroyer Oite, assuming my post starting today. I will perform my duties, and anything beyond that I will decide on a case-by-case basis. End of report.

upgrade.line: You have my gratitude.

win_mvp.line: All I did was perform my duty, as I said I would.

detail.line: Watch closely, Commander. You are about to witness what unyielding focus looks like... What?! I missed again?!

drop_descrip.line: Commander, have you also come to play on the beach? You're telling me to be careful? Hmph, what misfortune could possibly befall me from a game of watermelon splitting... Gwaah?!

headtouch.line: Whuah! What are you doing?!

home.line: Truly, Kamikaze? You're certain I will become proficient faster if I wear a blindfold?

login.line: Oh, to hell with it! I will practice until I can effortlessly split this watermlon!

main1.line: Are we ready to start yet? ...Commander? Where are you? G-give me the signal, I'm waiting!

main2.line: Matsukaze made fried noodles! Oh, how mouthwateringly good they are! You ought to taste them for yourself, Commander.

main3.line: I'm much obliged for the help, Hatakaze! Now watch – I will cleave this watermelon in twain!

touch.line: Wh-what is it?

touch2.line: What in the name of–?! What is the matter with you?!

unlock.line: Commander, have you also come to play on the beach? You're telling me to be careful? Hmph, what misfortune could possibly befall me from a game of watermelon splitting... Gwaah?!

detail.line: The essence of the plum tree is best captured with erratic brush strokes... This is quite the elegant ink painting.

drop_descrip.line: Happy New Year to you, Commander. To celebrate the season, I had these garments tailor-made for me, using traditional Dragon Empery clothes as a basis. I don't look... childish, do I?

headtouch.line: Whuaah?! I've told you countless times! St-st-stop touching my ears!

home.line: Should you think of any good ideas for verses, tell me. I will write them down.

login.line: A New Year's poem... "Many riches will grace you soon – I want my new year's gift by noon"... No, this is backwards! I'm at the age where I'm the one who should give the young'uns gifts... Oh, Commander? When did you get back?

main1.line: "In the ninth year of Yonghe, and the year of the Water Ox..." Bah! The rest of the text is unintelligible to me...

main2.line: Writing a poem in seven steps? Is there a person on this earth capable of such a feat?

main3.line: Kamikaze, what should one offer the young'uns as a new year's gift, other than money?

touch.line: Eep! Y-y-you're doing this on purpose, aren't you?!

touch2.line: Eek?! Y-y-you reprobate! What's the matter with you?!

unlock.line: Happy New Year to you, Commander. To celebrate the season, I had these garments tailor-made for me, using traditional Dragon Empery clothes as a basis. I don't look... childish, do I?

battle.line: We can win this... Right?

detail.line: I like being alone in my own room. What exactly do I do in my free time? ...I'm not telling you.

drop_descrip.line: Yuugumo-class destroyer number three – Kazagumo.

expedition.line: The commission team's back. Don't forget to say hi to them... Me? Uhh, I think I'll stay right here.

feeling1.line: I guess we're all fated to be alone. You, me, and everyone else...

feeling2.line: You want to be friends with me? Okay, but if I find out you're planning something bad... then I'll never talk to you again.

feeling3.line: You're not a bad person, so we can be friends... Do I wish I had more friends? I'm... not gonna tell you.

feeling4.line: There have been rumors of this girl with long hair and skin as pale as a ghost's who appears out of nowhere at port... In fact, I think she's right behind you, Commander... What do you mean that's not gonna fool you? Well, I thought I'd just spook you a little...

feeling5.line: You're fun to be with, Commander. A lot of fun. In fact, you're my best friend... Hehehe~ I wanna always be with you. Always.

headtouch.line: I'm not a pet, so don't treat me like one...

home.line: Good going, Commander... You heard a strange noise just now? Uhh... I'm sure it was just your imagination.

hp_warning.line: Watch beneath the waves...

login.line: *Yawn*... Oh. You scared away the birdies, Commander.

lose.line: Ugh. I'm really out of it today...

mail.line: Mail for the commander? Okay birdies, go fetch... No, please don't fight over who gets to do it.

main1.line: Could you not stare at me like that, Commander? I can't focus like this...

main2.line: You're on duty, so no chit-chatting with me allowed, okay? ...I mean, if you feel really lonely, then maybe...

main3.line: I like the satisfying toot-toot noise that recorders make... Do you wanna hear it? It'll have to be later, not now...

mission.line: Look at all these unfinished missions... You should really do something about them.

mission_complete.line: Mission complete. Wonder if I'll get a reward for my efforts...

profile.line: Kazagumo, Yuugumo-class destroyer number 3. I served the 10th Destroyer Squadron, mostly running transport missions and naval evacuations. These little birdies are my friends. My hobbies? I'm not telling you.

propose.line: I think... this is when you promise to never leave me. First you say it, then it's my turn... Hehehe~ Thank you. I love you.

skill.line: I wanna get this over with...

touch.line: Commander... What are you up to? (Kazagumo throws you a suspicious look.)

touch2.line: You'll be cursed for this...

unlock.line: Kazagumo, Yuugumo-class, reporting for duty. I hope I'll be able to get along well with everyone else here... Commander, you're not cooking up some dastardly plan, are you? You look rather questionable...

upgrade.line: Thanks, Commander.

win_mvp.line: It'd be great if we could keep winning...

detail.line: I've practiced some more. I'll play you a song, if you'll listen... On second thought, maybe I won't.

drop_descrip.line: Toot~♪ Oh, Commander, did you hear me practicing my recorder? Umm, I'd appreciate it if you didn't tell the others.

home.line: Welcome back, Commander. You didn't bring company... did you? Okay, good. I don't want others to hear how not-good I am at the recorder...

login.line: Zzz... What is it, Commander...? Me? The breeze was just too nice and I fell asleep...

main1.line: Weird... I played pretty well just a moment ago, but now I can't do it...

main2.line: The name of the song I just played? I'm not gonna tell you right now. After I've mastered it, all right?

main3.line: You're so nice, hanging out with me even after school... I'm not taking up your time, am I?

touch.line: Ugh... I lost track of the tempo because of that... Thanks, meanie.

touch2.line: Oh... Seriously, Commander? You're messing up my melody.

unlock.line: Toot~♪ Oh, Commander, did you hear me practicing my recorder? Umm, I'd appreciate it if you didn't tell the others.

win_mvp.line: I'm glad we won. Hehehe.

detail.line: Why am I out here all by myself? Because I get to be alone with... Oops, ignore that. I can't tell you...

drop_descrip.line: *lick*... Oh, Commander, y-you're here for the fireworks? ...Want to watch them with me, then? I've got drinks. My ice cream? Umm... You can't have it.

expedition.line: The commission team came back. Go and meet them, Commander. I'll watch your things.

home.line: *blows* I'd better eat this ice cream before it melts... Would I get brain freeze if I just bit into it?

login.line: Who is that launching fireworks over there, I wonder? Watching from directly below seems dangerous, but I bet they look prettiest from there...

mail.line: If you really want some ice cream... Wait, you had it delivered with the mail? A-aww...

main1.line: You're tired from swimming? Take a break here with me. I'll watch over you, so you can even take a nap... if you want.

main2.line: Umm, actually, I've been practicing a new song. Want me to play—Ack, the fireworks! Maybe another time...!

main3.line: I wonder where Shimakaze went... How can she not be tired after playing on the beach all day?

mission_complete.line: You finished a mission. Is there a reward for me, too...?

touch.line: Does my swimsuit... look weird?

touch2.line: Huh...? Oh... *blushes*

unlock.line: *lick*... Oh, Commander, y-you're here for the fireworks? ...Want to watch them with me, then? I've got drinks. My ice cream? Umm... You can't have it.

battle.line: Vanguard Wakatsuki has arrived! Everyone, charge forward with me!

detail.line: Hyah! Hrah! ...Oh, Commander! As you can see, I was just practicing my swings! Would you like to join me?

drop_descrip.line: Akizuki-class destroyer number six – Wakatsuki.

expedition.line: A commission represents the trust of the requester. In other words, upholding that contract is righteous and good!

feeling1.line: Why did you have to leave me all alone? Did I do something wrong...?

feeling2.line: My reason for helping others, huh... Hmm, I've never actually given it that much thought before. How about you, Commander? I heard you've done so much for everyone here, so what's your reason for all that?

feeling3.line: Some people will turn their backs on their friends and their beliefs after gaining great power... You often read about these greedy powermongers in various stories! If I ever met someone like that one day... Hehe~

feeling4.line: Are you going somewhere, Commander? ...Th-then, bring me along with you too! I'll make myself useful somehow! ...Whenever you're not here, I... Oh, you're just going on a quick patrol around the port?!

feeling5.line: I shall protect you today, just as I do every day! ...Huh? I seem to be in an especially good mood today? Well, of course! Nothing makes me happier than being at your side and serving you faithfully!

headtouch.line: Is this my reward? Ehehe~

home.line: I am glad you've returned safely! Ehehe, I could hardly sit still while waiting for you to come back, Commander...

hp_warning.line: Woah, I've got to regain my balance!

login.line: Commander! Were you about to begin your work? Allow me to assist in whatever way I can! Do you have anything I'm able to do?

lose.line: I shall protect your rear, so hurry up and retreat!

mail.line: Commander, take a look at this! A top-secret letter has come! ...Oh, it's just an ordinary letter?

main1.line: Commander, please look over here! There're some little birdies by the windowsill... Aw, they flew off... Hmm, is there some way of approaching without scaring them away?

main2.line: Commander, is there any work I would be able to help with? I might not be able to understand a lot of these documents right now, but if I work at it enough, I'm sure I'll get the hang of it!

main3.line: I start to feel anxious when I'm not with my friends... Do you feel the same way when you're alone, Commander?

mission.line: Are you worried about this mission, Commander? Just let me take care of it then!

mission_complete.line: Mission complete! I don't think I've done anything worthy of praise, but it does feel great to overcome obstacles together with you!

profile.line: Akizuki-class destroyer, Wakatsuki, is at your service! Like my sisters, I specialize in anti-air combat, but I'm no slouch when it comes to surface combat either! Don't you worry - I will never betray your orders, and will strive tirelessly to protect you!

propose.line: I see! So this is a symbol of my fealty to you! From now on, I swear to always remain by your side and to protect you with my life! If you ever need anything, just call my name. I'll do anything for you!

touch.line: My blade is very heavy, so please be careful!

touch2.line: Woah, woah! What are you doing, Commander? That's the kind of stuff you end up groveling on your knees and apologizing for!

unlock.line: I'm Akizuki-class destroyer Wakatsuki. I heard your summons and came promptly to aid you, Commander! Kindly call upon me whenever you have need of me.

upgrade.line: My body has become lighter and faster!

win_mvp.line: The victor has been decided! Drop your weapons and surrender! Hahaha!

detail.line: If I do a good job, Musashi will pat my head! I've actually received a whole bunch of rewards today. Oh, you're going to reward me too, Commander? Hooray!

drop_descrip.line: Oh nooo! Look out, Commander! ...Oh, phew... I'm glad I didn't mess up your clothes because of my carelessness! Please forgive me for my blunder! I'll clean the floor up right away!

headtouch.line: Yay, I've been rewarded for my hard work! Ehehe~

home.line: I can't believe I made a fool of myself in front of you... I just wanted to help everyone out with the café, but ended up causing more trouble instead... Urgh...

login.line: Welcome back, Commander! Allow me to show you to your seat! ...Oh, please watch out for the coffee spill!

main1.line: Commander, don't you think keeping a few birdies around will liven up the café?

main2.line: Haguro, are you okay? Is it my fault? ...Oh, you're fine? Thank goodness. If someone falls down because of me, I'd have to get on my knees and apologize...

main3.line: Commander, I just cleaned this area, so please watch your step! ...We can't afford for there to be any more victims!

touch.line: Yes, I'll be right out with your order!

touch2.line: I, I'm going to tell my friends on you!

unlock.line: Oh nooo! Look out, Commander! ...Oh, phew... I'm glad I didn't mess up your clothes because of my carelessness! Please forgive me for my blunder! I'll clean the floor up right away!

battle.line: Go on, sink for me♪

detail.line: Where are you looking, hmm? Heehee~ You didn't realize I was behind you? Oh, Commander, for a tactical genius, you sure can be inattentive♪

drop_descrip.line: Akizuki-class destroyer – Hatsuzuki.

expedition.line: The commission team is back. I'll come along and welcome them back with you♪

feeling1.line: Huh? You're... not gonna pay attention to me? Why not, Commander? I don't understand... Uhh, should I say sorry, or something?

feeling2.line: (A note. It reads: I've gone somewhere far away. Please don't come looking for me. I hope you and everyone else have a good life. Yours truly, Hatsuzuki.)

feeling3.line: Did you think I was serious about going away? Oh. Well, uh... Sorry? I thought it'd be a funny prank – I didn't mean to actually make you worry... Ugh...

feeling4.line: I'm right here, and I'm not going anywhere. You don't have anything to worry about, Commander... I hope saying that while patting your head will make you calm down... Good. I know how important I am to you, so this should do the trick.

feeling5.line: Hehehe... Wait! I'M supposed to be comforting YOU, not the other way around! When did this happen? It's supposed to be MY turn to court you right now! ...Y-you can stop patting my head any time, you know... *blushes*

headtouch.line: I got this red string that will tie you and me together! Also, you can keep patting me♪

home.line: I'm first to welcome you back♪ Heehee~ No, that's not a given just because I'm your secretary~

hp_warning.line: I can take a lot of punishment, you know...!

login.line: I know this is your chair, but you'll let me sit on it if I ask, won't you? Great! Then, let's say only I can sit here♪

lose.line: We lost... Hmph.

mail.line: A letter... Is it really your secretary's job to read your letters before you do? Heehee.

main1.line: Say, Commander, aren't you forgetting something? Oh, I think you know what~ Try really, and you'll remember what you might've forgotten♪

main2.line: Are you in a pickle, Commander? Because if you are, you can ask me for help. Helping you is the whole reason I'm here~

main3.line: Honestly, Zuikaku is too laid-back. If she'd take my approach and go straight for you, you two would have a thing going by now... Heehee, it's better for me this way, though♪

mission.line: Want me to help with your missions? I bet you do. I'm your secretary, after all.

mission_complete.line: Mission complete... Don't you care about the rewards?

profile.line: I'm Hatsuzuki, Akizuki-class destroyer. During the war, I helped my allies and fought hard until I got ripped to shreds. I might just work my butt off again to help you, if need be... Th-there'll be no need for that? Oh...

propose.line: I knew it – you need me in your life♪ Now tell me, what's our life together gonna be like, going forward? Sugary sweet, or down and dirty? Either way sounds like pure bliss to me and I can't wait! Hehehehe♡

skill.line: Don't worry, I'm on the case♪

touch.line: Oh! Commander! ...No, it's nothing♪

touch2.line: Hmph. If you're gonna touch me, at least be honest about it...

unlock.line: Heehee, so this is where you were, Commander~ Hope you don't mind that I'm here now, too♪ Isn't it wonderful to have me so close to you? Also, you won't be able to run if I come any closer~

upgrade.line: Something tells me that you're reliant on me♪

win_mvp.line: MVP! Nobody says I can't hoard all the rewards from the Commander, right?

drop_descrip.line: Peace~♪ Do I look good in the pic? Don't I look so adorable you'll never wanna delete the photo, and have to stare at it every day to feel at ease? Heehee♪

expedition.line: Looks like the commission team's back. Are you really gonna go alone?

feeling5.line: Now I'm gonna snap pics of YOU in your cute swimsuit♪ Don't worry, I won't show them to anyone else! ...That's it, give me a big, big blush~

headtouch.line: Heeheehee♪

home.line: Welcome back with aaa... big splash! Heehee~ Get wet from head to toe!

login.line: Why don't you snap another? Oh, oh my~ You'll do it because you wanna, and not because I told you to?

main1.line: (Aaand set on home screen♪ Now the Commander will see my adorable swimsuit forever and ever♡)

main2.line: Hmph. Why are you looking at other girls? I'm not saying you can't, I just want you to look at ME right now.

main3.line: Silly Wakatsuki, if you wanna have fun, just change into a swimsuit and jump into the pool... Although, it's too late to nab the Commander now – I have exclusive dibs♪

touch.line: Ahahah! Are you teasing me back now?

touch2.line: I know I can't do anything about it... Still, I'm sorry they're not bigger...

unlock.line: Peace~♪ Do I look good in the pic? Don't I look so adorable you'll never wanna delete the photo, and have to stare at it every day to feel at ease? Heehee♪

win_mvp.line: Peace, peace♪ Tell me how perfect I am♪

battle.line: Show me what you've got!

detail.line: Hmph, know that I am a member of the glorious Kamikaze class! If you don't give me the respect I deserve... Oh? You made dango to share with me? Y-yes, yes, very thoughtful.

drop_descrip.line: Kamikaze-class destroyer – Asanagi.

expedition.line: You there, Commander! I hear the commission team is back. If you don't want a solid blow to the stomach, you'd best make them treats and meet them in person!

feeling1.line: Mm... Don't disappoint me so much, please. That is all I have to say.

feeling2.line: Hmph. You underestimate me... Normally, I would punish you with a hundred punches... But very well. I'll let you get away with one this time.

feeling3.line: Work must always be done quickly and efficiently. Oh, come now, I'll be here to help you. That should keep you from running into any trouble. You may rely on me from now on.

feeling4.line: What? You finished your work before me...?! No, I mean, you must be going faster because of my help, or... A fluke! It must be a fluke, of course!

feeling5.line: Whoa! ...N-no, nothing's wrong. I wasn't just neglecting my work because I was so focused on you, or anything! I mean, uhh! Yeah! You're doing this on purpose to distract me, aren't you?! Fess up!

headtouch.line: Th-this is mortifying! Why don't I sink my fist into your stomach and see how you feel then?!

home.line: Commander? Finally returned, hm? You have some nerve, ignoring me—Oh, you didn't see me? But I'm right in front of you!

hp_warning.line: Th-this is far from enough to make a Kamikaze-class shipgirl submit!

login.line: So you finally arrive, Commander! What in the world were you... Hey! Do not ignore me!

lose.line: Rrrgh! I-I just held back a little, that's all!

mail.line: Mail's come for you, Commander. Don't just ignore it! Read it already!

main1.line: What? You made tea for me? H-hmm, how thoughtful... You deserve praise! Expect a New Year's gift in your future!

main2.line: There you go messing up again! Prepare to feel my iron fist... You say no, it hurts too much? I-I suppose I don't mean to hurt you... Very well. One painless tummy strike, incoming!

main3.line: Oite, where did you hide my shoes?! Oh... They were a mess, so you sorted them all into the shoe box for me? H-hmm... Well, er... Thank you.

mission.line: Hmm, Commander... Do you know how many missions you have piled up? They'll keep piling if you ignore them, so how about you get to work?!

mission_complete.line: Mm, wait a second... This mission is completed! Goodness. Don't neglect your rewards now.

profile.line: I am the eighth Kamikaze-class ship, Asanagi. They once rudely called me number fifteen, but either out of sympathy or because they recognized my power, they've given me a new name. Now, if you're to be my Commander, you'd best straighten up! Otherwise, I'll have to instill some gumption in you!

propose.line: Heheh, that you'd give me this must mean that you want to depend on me forever! What? No? You want ME to depend on YOU? Wh-who would ever rely on you?! ...I'll accept this ring, but I still won't do it!

skill.line: Get ready for a faceful of my fists of fury!

touch.line: Ah, right there... Mm~ Commander, you are just a master of massage.

touch2.line: And what do you think you're doing, fool?! Goodness... What is so fun about touching me?

unlock.line: Well, well... Hmph. What a weak little child you are! I am Asanagi, of the Kamikaze class! I will be your subordinate from today on, but listen well! Cause me trouble, I will jab you! Annoy me, I will strike you! Do anything unbefitting of your status as Commander, and your tummy shall know the wrath of my fist!

upgrade.line: Well, I suppose I feel a little stronger... Only a little! A little, I say!

win_mvp.line: This is your punishment for underestimating the Kamikaze class!

detail.line: It's not as if we fight at all hours. You'd be better off if you learned how to relax. As someone who leads shipgirls to battle over the sea, you'd benefit the most from learning how to enjoy the ocean.

drop_descrip.line: *yaaawn*... Goodness me, there I go falling asleep. You understand how pleasant the sea breeze is, don't you? YOU calling ME a slacker!

home.line: Here, a towel. Your hair and clothes get wet during battles, don't they? Make sure you don't catch a cold.

login.line: Late again. You weren't out there playing with other girls on the beach, were you?

main1.line: If you fall for another shipgirl... you know what'll happen, don't you? My fists haven't dulled one bit.

main2.line: Say, Commander, why don't we take a break and watch the ocean over some tea? Calm seas are so relaxing.

main3.line: I notice you've been staring at my tummy...? Ah! Could it be... You plan to take your revenge over my previous punches?!

touch.line: Urgh, the sunlight is too strong... Don't blame me. I sunburn easily by nature!

touch2.line: Look how covetous you are~ Does the sight of me in a swimsuit excite you so?

unlock.line: *yaaawn*... Goodness me, there I go falling asleep. You understand how pleasant the sea breeze is, don't you? YOU calling ME a slacker!

win_mvp.line: Heheh, yes, yes! Continue to sing my praises!

battle.line: Combat trial for new equipment... begin!

detail.line: Be they canisters or weaponry, my developments in them are the latest!

drop_descrip.line: Yuubari-class light cruiser – Yuubari.

expedition.line: A commission is done! Hmm, I wonder if they brought us gifts...

feeling1.line: Master, could you just stay away from me?

feeling2.line: Master, what's on your mind when you stare at me? Hohoho, I'm rather perceptive, I'll have you know!

feeling3.line: I much prefer staying in the port than going on sorties. This is my home; by the blue seas, beneath the warm and dazzling sunlight... *Yawn*... Mmhh... Zzzz...

feeling4.line: What girls are your type, Master? Someone like me? You know, my type is people like you, Master~

feeling5.line: Do you want to nap with me, Master? Take this, it is my favorite pillow. Perhaps if you sleep on it, you will see me in your dreams. And if you do... Hehehe♪

home.line: Data collection complete. Now we shall use it to improve our gear.

hp_warning.line: Oww... No issue, as long as my equipment is fine...

login.line: With you by my side, Master, I have nothing to fear...!

lose.line: Dear me! ... Once I'm done developing new gear, I won't lose like this again!

mail.line: Hmm, this mail seems questionable... Master, I urge you to open it!

main1.line: *Yawn*...

main2.line: Melon bread? I'm extraordinarily curious as to how it tastes...

main3.line: The Gatos are terrifying... Why are such frightening submarines named after a catshark?

mission.line: You have incomplete missions... Hmm, it appears the results of my research will not be of any use...

mission_complete.line: Master, I believe it is time for a nap once you've finished your missions.

profile.line: I am Yuubari, Sakura Empire Yuubari-class light cruiser. I was developed under the constraints of a naval treaty, but this conversely allowed me to utilize a great number of new technologies. I served as the flagship of a Destroyer Squadron in the Pacific War. Hmm... I will need many oxygen torpedoes if I am to research them...

propose.line: I'm overjoyed♪ Starting today, every day when you wake up, the first thing you'll see in the morning is me~! Hehehe♪

skill.line: Feel the power of my advanced weapons!

touch.line: Your hand is so warm and gentle, Master~

touch2.line: Mmh... ugh... gah... stop, or I will bite!

unlock.line: I am light cruiser Yuubari. You say we've met before, Master? Hmm... b-but that's not possible... I don't have any sisters after all...

upgrade.line: Hmm... It seems to be a bit too tight in here...

win_mvp.line: Surely by now, you've begun to understand the importance of developing new gear, Master?

detail.line: Akashi is really enthusiastic about helping my research, but it feels like she has some ulterior motives...

drop_descrip.line: I've finally finished developing my new equipment! Since we still have time, let's go and try it out in live combat right now, Master!

home.line: Hehe, looks like the data collection went well this time too.

login.line: Master, are you here to help me gather data today?

lose.line: Hmm... Looks like I haven't upgraded my equipment enough...

main1.line: Research always comes with failure... but with your support, Master, all these difficulties will pass!

main2.line: Nnh... I'm a bit tired... Can I rest here for a while?

main3.line: The way I am now, I won't be afraid even if I run into a Gato-class, probably...

touch.line: Master, you have to remember to get some rest, all right?

touch2.line: Augh... I'm going to smack you!

unlock.line: I've finally finished developing my new equipment! Since we still have time, let's go and try it out in live combat right now, Master!

win_mvp.line: Master, have you realized the importance of having modernized equipment?

battle.line: Who is the enemy this time?

detail.line: What kind of girl do you like, Commander? Hehe. Oh yeah?

drop_descrip.line: First ship of the {namecode:46}-class light cruisers, {namecode:46}.

expedition.line: Commissions? That's part of my job too.

feeling1.line: Come on, Commander, cheer up~!

feeling2.line: Hmm... What should I cook for my little sisters tonight?

feeling3.line: Commander? Oh, nothing. I just wanted to say hi!

feeling4.line: An escort? That's my specialty. And this time? Ah, going to port with you, undercover?!

feeling5.line: Yesterday, I saw a side of my sisters that I hadn't seen before... Commander, do you want to see a side of me you haven't before? Hm... what should I do?

home.line: It's great to see that you returned safe and sound, Commander~!

login.line: Hey, hey~ Commander, were you daydreaming again?

lose.line: *Cries* Commander, let's retreat...

mail.line: Hehe, Commander~! You've got new mail~!

main1.line: You need to change clothes after getting soaked... Hey, do you want to borrow mine?

main2.line: It's great that {namecode:47} is finally making friends, but...

main3.line: Commander~ Your face is so~ cute~!

mission.line: If it's just taking a break once in a while, I think I can let that go.

mission_complete.line: Wow, finished already? Well done, Commander!

profile.line: I'm the first ship of the {namecode:46}-class light cruisers from the Sakura Empire. I took part in various battles in the Solomon Seas and in the center Pacific. During Midway, I took over {namecode:91}'s role as flagship after she sank and then coordinated our retreat. In the end, though, I too met the fate of being sunk by a submarine...

propose.line: ... Hey~ Commander, are you ready? Okay, I'm closing my eyes...

touch.line: Have you run into any trouble, Commander?

touch2.line: Sometimes I really don't understand what you're trying to do, Commander...

unlock.line: Eheh, I'm {namecode:46}. Commader, have you been anticipating my arrival?

upgrade.line: Oxygen Torpedoes.....I want.......

win_mvp.line: I hope every battle goes as well as this one did~!

detail.line: Commander, how do you plan on spending your Spring Festival? Me? ...Well, chilling in my room with a cup of tea sounds pretty good, or reading a book, or rolling around. Ehehe~

drop_descrip.line: Good evening, Commander. This room...? Ah, it's a special Dragon Empery-themed set I bought from Akashi's. It looks pretty snazzy and was on sale, so I picked it up. Ehehe~

feeling5.line: Whispering to you while cleaning your ear like this... kind of makes it seem like we're a couple, doesn't it? Hehe, forget I said anything. All right, all done. You can stay here and chat a bit more if you'd like~?

home.line: Look, Commander, the tea stalk is floating upright. I'm sure something good is going to happen today~

login.line: Commander, want some tea?

main1.line: Commander, have you seen Kinu? I told her I'd clean her ears, but she sure bailed quick... Seriously, what's wrong with cleaning your sister's ears...?

main2.line: Commander, you know, Abukuma started having tea with me, and will even let me clean her ears! Ehehe, th

touch.line: Commander, want me to clean your ears too? Sure, come here then~ *pat* *pat*

touch2.line: Jeez, Commander, don't blame me if I poke a hole in your eardrum~

unlock.line: Good evening, Commander. This room...? Ah, it's a special Dragon Empery-themed set I bought from Akashi's. It looks pretty snazzy and was on sale, so I picked it up. Ehehe~

battle.line: Nothing weird is going to pop out, right?

detail.line: *Cries*... I'm so glad that you're still this gentle with me, Commander...

drop_descrip.line: Second ship of the {namecode:46}-class light cruisers, {namecode:48}.

expedition.line: The girls have completed their commissions! I hope they didn't bring anything strange back...

feeling1.line: Is Commander a demon?

feeling2.line: *Cries*... Are ghosts scary because they don't exist in this world?

feeling3.line: Ah? A midnight adventure? That... it's not a good idea, is it? No, I'm not afraid!

feeling4.line: *Cries*... There definitely was something strange there just now! I already said a midnight adventure was a bad idea!

feeling5.line: You... you're going to protect me from anything that appears? You're... you're just making fun of me again, Commander... I'm not blushing! It's just a little hot...

home.line: *Cries*... Only you wouldn't pick on me, Commander...

login.line: Aaaaaah!!! Commander! Don't scare me like that...

lose.line: *Cries* ... Are they all demons?

mail.line: Commander, you've got new mail! I hope there aren't any curses written on them...

main1.line: Torpedoes are truly frightening...

main2.line: It feels creepy at night without any lights on, don't you think...?

main3.line: I've seen plenty of things in this world! You won't scare me so easily.

mission.line: Commander, I think you've still got a lot of unfinished work to do.

mission_complete.line: Mission rewards delivered! I wonder if there's anything good...

profile.line: Sakura Empire, {namecode:46}-class light cruiser, {namecode:48}, reporting in! I participated in battles at the Lesser Sunda Islands, Solomon Islands, and Guadalcanal. I've fought alongside many famous ships, so you've got to work hard to try and have as good of a reputation as I do!

propose.line: *Cries*... I hope you aren't messing with me, Commander! I'll never feel scared again, as long as you're with me... Can I trust you, Commander?

touch.line: Commander... you're so warm...

touch2.line: Uwa! It's touching me! It's touching me!

unlock.line: Woah! You... you scared me~! Oh, it's you, my Commander! I'm {namecode:48}... You're not here to pick on me, are you?

upgrade.line: Did I... get stronger?

win_mvp.line: Vi- victory? Commander, how did I do?

detail.line: A-all those Halloween monsters are just people in costumes, right?! ... There aren't any real ones roaming around, right?!

drop_descrip.line: There's many monsters roaming around during Halloween... B-but I'm not scared, okay?! ... Umm, err, uh... Can I hold your hand?

feeling5.line: If only I could board the pumpkin carriage and meet the prince of my... What?! Commander, h-how long have you been here?! D-don't stare at my face! *Sob*...

login.line: C-C-C-Commander! Trick or... o-or... I can't do it...!

main1.line: Monsters aren't real... Monsters aren't real... M-m-monsters aren't real....!

main2.line: W-w-why do they make even the pumpkins look scary?!

main3.line: L-l-looks like everyone's enjoying Halloween... I-I-I-I'm not shuddering, okay?!

touch.line: You make me feel safer than anyone else, Commander...

touch2.line: *Eeek*?! I-I'll turn you into a frog!

unlock.line: There's many monsters roaming around during Halloween... B-but I'm not scared, okay?! ... Umm, err, uh... Can I hold your hand?

detail.line: My sisters wanted to dress up as Santa Claus and go around handing presents to kids... I didn't go with them because I'm not good with the dark.

drop_descrip.line: Commander? I only came here to help wrap up all the presents for tomorrow, n-not because the fireplace is too cozy and I don't want to get up...

feeling5.line: I'm not really sure how Christmas should be celebrated. But just sitting next to you in front of the fireplace like this... is probably fine. Commander, i-it's a bit cold... I'd like to get a little closer...

home.line: I was told that this outfit would be good for wearing around the house, but it's a bit too loose... S-stop staring at me already.

login.line: Two people sitting in front of the fireplace like this... feels a bit like family.

main1.line: It's so cozy right next to the fireplace... There are even fuzzy Manjuus to cuddle~

main2.line: Um... Commander, what kind of presents should I give to everyone?

main3.line: I've already done my research. There are no ghost stories or anything of the sort related to Christmas... R-right, Commander?

touch.line: Are... you trying to share my body heat?

touch2.line: I knew it! You were trying to take advantage of me!

unlock.line: Commander? I only came here to help wrap up all the presents for tomorrow, n-not because the fireplace is too cozy and I don't want to get up...

detail.line: I had no idea donning a mascot suit was so demanding... Fubuki used to wear these all the time... That's way too insane...

drop_descrip.line: Wooah! ...I fell down again... But at least it's cooler now... Huh? A photoshoot? Noo, don't take a picture of me~

home.line: Mascot outfits are so hard to move around in... It's all dark and stuffy inside... Ugh...

login.line: I wasn't trying to spill the juice! ...Sorry...

main1.line: Haah... I wonder if I should take a little breather... It's so nice and cool...

main2.line: Card games? N-no way, that'd be way too hard...

touch.line: C-Commander, thank goodness you were here this whole time...

touch2.line: Ugh... I knew you'd take advantage of this opportunity to tease me...

unlock.line: Wooah! ...I fell down again... But at least it's cooler now... Huh? A photoshoot? Noo, don't take a picture of me~

drop_descrip.line: W-w-woah! W-wait up! You guys are going too fast! I'm gonna fall! I'm gonna faaaaall! You're supposed to carry me in a way that doesn't give me a heart attack!! Commander, something crazy seems to have happened with my cavalry~!!

main1.line: nil

main2.line: nil

main3.line: nil

battle.line: Leave the anti-air support to me!

detail.line: Commander, you've always been so kind to me~ Thank you~

drop_descrip.line: Retrofit complete! ...Umm, Commander? ...Wh-what's the matter? Do I really look that different...?!

expedition.line: The girls in the commission fleet have come back. Hopefully they didn't bring anything weird back with them?

home.line: Welcome back, Commander! I used to cuddle up to you after you got back from a sortie? D-did something like that happen? I think my memory's a bit fuzzy~ Aha...haha...

login.line: Gyah?! ...Commander, are you trying to scare me on purpose?!

main1.line: Y-you saw something weird?! Wh-wh-where?! ...Jeez! Don't scare me like that!

main2.line: Nagara said that I looked cuter before, but I think that's just because she likes to dote on me...!

main3.line: Kinu seems like the dependable type, but she sometimes gives off really scary vibes... Ugh, I just don't understand her.

touch.line: Commander, did I become a bit more dependable?

touch2.line: I... I'm not scared!

unlock.line: Retrofit complete! ...Umm, Commander? ...Wh-what's the matter? Do I really look that different...?!

battle.line: I could defeat you all with one pinky finger.

detail.line: Hmph. Let me share some little-known information with you, Commander. These aren't oni horns; they're dragon horns! Isn't that incredible? "Yes, yes, a dragon. I say so, and that means it is fact!"

drop_descrip.line: Nagara-class light cruiser – Natori.

expedition.line: Did you notice the commission girls are back? Heheh, you're not bad if you can keep up with my super senses.

feeling1.line: Everything you say is a cheap lie. I don't trust you...

feeling2.line: I'll share this with you alone, Commander. If I close one eye and push like this, I can shoot laser beams! Or so this old geezer says. I've never tried, because it's far too destructive.

feeling3.line: I see, I see. So you finally understand my strength. That's right! I can use this ability to triple the price of toys in the port stores! ...Hm? What is that good for?

feeling4.line: You just don't understand. If I can triple prices, then I can resell what I purchase for massive profits! Jealous? ...Y-you're not jealous?!

feeling5.line: Hmm, my "affinity" stat has gone up too high. My old man says this is going to interfere with my daily work! Commander, what do you plan to do about this?!

headtouch.line: Nngh, do not stroke my hair so casually!

home.line: Ooh~ You've finished your work! Then the workday is over! Maybe I'll go shopping with Nagara, or...

hp_warning.line: Kh, I'm fine! If I use my cheat skills, I can make it out of this...!

login.line: ♪~ I'm just so strong that I suffer from success~ Commander, join me! ...Not for work! For fun!

lose.line: This is not defeat! It's strategic withdrawal!

mail.line: If only there was some convenient feature that lets you know with an icon that you had unread mail... "You rely too much on humans. Here, I will notify the whippersnapper."

main1.line: I must pass a trial to unlock my true power, no? Come with me when the time is right, Commander!

main2.line: Ah, I'm hungry... Oh, Commander! Hey, treat me to a meal! "I desire pudding for dessert!"

main3.line: "By the way, there are plenty of ways to raise your attributes~ For example, these stats..." Old man, would you just cut to the chase and tell me how?!

main4.line: W-wait, Nagara! I-I'll clean it up, I promise, just don't throw away my manga... I know! Yura, let me hide them in your room for a little while!

mission.line: You STILL haven't finished your missions? Ugh, you average people... I'd have them done in the blink of an eye.

mission_complete.line: Huh? The Commander's missions are finished already?! Old man, why didn't you tell me?!

profile.line: I'm Natori, the third Nagara-class ship! As a light cruiser of the Sakura Empire, I often tell people that I fight with single-mounted guns and water scouting craft... But that is a ruse! For I am the incarnation of a dragon! My strength shatters boulders (with cannonballs) and soars over the sea (with my rigging)! So? Impressed?

propose.line: Oh, I can't leave your side anymore, Commander... You always look after me, and you listen to the things I say... That's just unfair! What is this, your trap?! Is that it?!

touch.line: ...Mm? What? Do you need me?

touch2.line: What are you doing to me?!

unlock.line: "Nuo ho ho! So this young whippersnapper here's the Commander! You don't look all that reliable to me~!" ...Argh, do not interrupt me when I am speaking! Ahem– I am the strongest light cruiser Natori, and this is my partner, Old Man Hiranuma! Nice to meet you!

upgrade.line: Ooh! My power... My power is surging! My stats are going through the roof!

win_mvp.line: Did you think you could withstand a dragon's might? "I've never seen a more foolish foe!"

detail.line: I've made everything up to the castle keep. At this rate, the sand castle competition is all but won... Heheh, now, time to go laugh at the others— "A giant wave is approaching! Watch ooout!"

drop_descrip.line: Mmfhuhu~♡ What's the matter, Commander? Enraptured by my charms? Heehee, you're frozen in place! You can't begin to think of how to compliment me, can you? "Enough staring, out with the compliments!"

home.line: Phew~ I am beat! Time for some juice and rest... Hey, old man! Do I have the power to create juice out of thin air? "You might be able to make fried chicken, but no juice, kiddo. Have that whippersnapper buy you some."

login.line: Mmfhuhu~♪ I'm a little different from the usual today, right? I'm sure you can figure out how, Commander♪

main1.line: Mhmhm... Very, very interesting! I see your passionate gaze upon me, Commander! That gaze is the essence of summer!

main2.line: Even the fish are knocked cold by my charms. Now's your chance for a big catch!

main3.line: I'd say my sensuality matches even Isuzu's now, no? See, old man? Even the Commander is speechless!

touch.line: Mmmm... There! My special ability allowed me to sense your approach! Incredible, no?!

touch2.line: Grr! My skin is too fine for you to be touching it so freely!

unlock.line: Mmfhuhu~♡ What's the matter, Commander? Enraptured by my charms? Heehee, you're frozen in place! You can't begin to think of how to compliment me, can you? "Enough staring, out with the compliments!"

battle.line: I'd like to wait a bit more and see what the situation is like...

detail.line: Sometimes, I feel like I'm not quite myself... That must be my other Self...

drop_descrip.line: Nagara-class light cruiser number four – Yura.

expedition.line: The girls are back from commissions. If you require assistance, shall my Self accompany you?

feeling1.line: I wonder if the fortune that foretold "calamity" was referring to you...

feeling2.line: Commander, if there's nothing for me to do, I'll be heading to the shrine behind the mountain to help out.

feeling3.line: You want to know more about my Self? Well, she's also a part of me... Mm, if I were to put it simply, she's kind of like my familiar.

feeling4.line: Your fortune said that bad luck would follow you around, so I, along with Abukuma and the others, made a protective charm that will ward off evil. Please be careful, and always carry this around with you.

feeling5.line: Whenever I think of you, I always worry that something bad might have happened to you. Please, stay with my Self's... no, my side. That way, I won't have to worry.

headtouch.line: Would you like to touch my horns?

home.line: It's good to see you, welcome back. I apologize, for I don't really know where to put these papers...

hp_warning.line: We should get back into formation.

login.line: Commander, um... good job making your way over here.

lose.line: It might be better to withdraw first...

mail.line: Shall my Self read it aloud for you?

main1.line: Commander, if you're concerned that the tea is too hot... Um, should I blow on it for you?

main2.line: Abukuma, I don't think that "only eating and sleeping" is a healthy lifestyle. I'm wrong about that? Well...

main3.line: The destroyers are... well, they're always so full of energy and zipping about, that it's honestly a bit hard to keep pace with them...

main4.line: Even when we can't see her, my Self is always by my side.

main5.line: You want to know more about my Self? Do I think she has some kind of special connection with the meaning of my name...? I sometimes wonder myself.

mission.line: Oh, Commander, I really think you shouldn't be neglecting these missions...

mission_complete.line: Oh, speaking of which... I haven't told you to receive the mission rewards yet... have I?

profile.line: I am the Nagara-class light cruiser, Yura. In a certain great war, I was the flagship of the Fourth Torpedo Squadron for a short period of time. I might have taken my leave earlier than my sister ships in that war, but this time, I swear that my Self will remain until the bitter end.

propose.line: Oh, to think that I'd be able to become your betrothed, Commander. ...Is this truly alright? Hehe, I'm so happy that I lost my composure... Thank you.

touch.line: Did you need something from me?

touch2.line: I have no choice but to become your wife now, Commander. Hehe~

unlock.line: Um... Would you happen to know where the Commander might be? My name is Yura, and I have just arrived here today. Are you the Commander? Um, do you have a signed note or certificate that corroborates that?

upgrade.line: Oh, I feel something awakening inside me...

win_mvp.line: My Self played a big role as well. I'll have to thank her for her help.

battle.line: I'll seduce you, alright. Hehe.

detail.line: When I'm wearing these clothes, I feel like I'm going to be exorcised... What do you think about them, Commander?

drop_descrip.line: Uh... I think these clothes are a bit too much... Commander, I... don't look out of place in these, do I...?

home.line: The wings are slipping off... Is there a mirror somewhere...?

login.line: Commander, um... W-welcome...?

main1.line: A succubus is a being that tempts people in their dreams... I-I'd never do anything like that!

main2.line: Isuzu, it's me, Yura! I'm not a ghost, you don't need to be afraid of me!

main3.line: I don't know if today is a day of celebration, but everyone seems to be more lively than usual. I wonder if the Commander will be all right dealing with them...

main4.line: It seems that thou are doing well. Hehe. Commander, do you perhaps prefer my Self to me?

touch.line: Oh, did you need something?

touch2.line: Maybe you were the real succubus all along. Hehe.

unlock.line: Uh... I think these clothes are a bit too much... Commander, I... don't look out of place in these, do I...?

battle.line: Just bring it on already!

detail.line: You're welcome to inspect the other stuff, but you'd be best off not casually touching my demonic raiments.

drop_descrip.line: Nagara-class light cruiser number five – Kinu.

expedition.line: The commission team must be getting impatient from waiting.

feeling1.line: Cowards shall never control a demon.

feeling2.line: You may look like someone who is too gentle to hurt a fly, yet you have control over this entire port. I'm a little interested in you.

feeling3.line: I've heard that Yuubari is responsible for developing new equipment. If possible, could you ask her to upgrade my equipment? For example, starting with my torpedoes...

feeling4.line: How about letting me treat you to a couple cups of sake tonight? Hah, don't worry, I just want to have a normal chat. Having a heart-to-heart over some fine spirits... what greater comfort in life is there?

feeling5.line: I feel like I can entrust myself to you. Is this where the demon finally finds her home...? Commander, if I was to become the blade you wield, how would you use it?

headtouch.line: Don't go around touching my head.

home.line: You look like you're in a good mood. Are you the type that gets motivated the more you work?

hp_warning.line: Ahaha! Now you shall witness the form of a true demon!

login.line: Hurry up and make today's plans.

lose.line: Even I have become obsolete...?

mail.line: I've already highlighted the important parts for you, Commander.

main1.line: Somebody I can't stand? I guess that'd be Nagara. She's the– Whuah, Nagara?! W-Wait, don't get any closer! MMPH, URMMMPHHH!

main2.line: A new model of oxygen torpedo...? I say, do get me one of those. I promise I'll draw out every bit of its power.

main3.line: My cloak's pretty cool? Heh~ you think so too, huh? ...Hey, stop trying to slack off!

mission.line: Don't forget about your missions. A soldier must fulfill the orders of their superiors.

mission_complete.line: Accept these rewards. You've earned this privilege.

profile.line: I am the Nagara-class light cruiser, Kinu. My name derives from Kinugawa, meaning "furious and violent like a demon's wrath." I live up to my name, but trust me - that is not something that you would want to see.

propose.line: Commander, you are the worthy one who has conquered a demon. Let us commemorate today's vow, and aim for greater strength together.

touch.line: You want to duel me? Don't worry, I'll give you a handicap.

touch2.line: Really? Are you trying to get me mad?

unlock.line: I'm Kinu. If you want this demon to do your bidding, then you'd better show me what you're capable of!

upgrade.line: I won't be able to test whether or not this strengthening worked outside of live combat.

win_mvp.line: Make an enemy of me, and your defeat is already ensured.

detail.line: What Takao is doing can't be considered a club activity... No, I didn't mean anything by it. I just do what I like.

drop_descrip.line: Grr! What are you here for? Speak up. ...Oh, you just wanted to take a tour of the club activities? Sorry 'bout that, I don't like getting disturbed in the middle of this kind of training.

home.line: Calligraphy and swordsmanship both hone the body and the mind. Commander, how'd these words come out?

login.line: Just finished my daily practice swings. Time to get back to work.

mail.line: You've received a lot of New Year's greetings, Commander. Remember to take a look at them.

main1.line: Unless you are a genius, you can never depart from the fundamentals. Even if you are a genius, you cannot afford to neglect the fundamentals either. That is the nature of swordsmanship.

main2.line: Prince of Wales and Repulse, huh? ...Hmph. I'd never call them cowards.

main3.line: Isuzu clearly is also an oni, but she's somehow afraid of ghosts. Me...? Guh, I suppose I can't deny that...!

touch.line: These little manjuu hardly make for good sparring partners. How about taking their place?

unlock.line: Grr! What are you here for? Speak up. ...Oh, you just wanted to take a tour of the club activities? Sorry 'bout that, I don't like getting disturbed in the middle of this kind of training.

win_mvp.line: Sorry, but these riggings are the real deal.

battle.line: Come! I will determine whether your hand is good enough or not!

detail.line: Eyes on your cards, idiot. This is not a staring competition... Wh-what? Are you hoping to unnerve me or something?

drop_descrip.line: Well? I've still got one card in my hand. If you want to win, then show me everything you've got! I will not have you disrespect me just for wearing a silly costume!

home.line: Give me a minute, I need to put on makeup... Just need to do like Isuzu showed me... There! I'm all ready now.

lose.line: Dammit! You've ruined my tights and skirt!

main1.line: Hey! Don't let any submarines near the wine! That goes for you too, Commander.

main2.line: What...? No, I'm not "cute!" I don't consider that a compliment!

main3.line: Cheaters can go to hell! Play fair, or don't play at all! Right, Commander?

touch.line: You'd be an idiot to underestimate the demon.

touch2.line: S-so my costume is just that seductive, huh?

unlock.line: Well? I've still got one card in my hand. If you want to win, then show me everything you've got! I will not have you disrespect me just for wearing a silly costume!

win_mvp.line: That's it? I've still got the demon card in my hand!

battle.line: This is a true oni's wrath!

detail.line: My oni mask? Ah, it's on the other side now. With my self-evident power, there is no need to flaunt such things.

drop_descrip.line: Retrofit complete... Look forward to commanding the might of the demon ascended. I shall not disappoint you!

main1.line: This time, I won't resign myself to obsolescence!

main2.line: Darn that Aoba... With how she's always absent-mindedly flitting about, what is she going to do when she ends up in actual danger?

main3.line: This mantle was specifically made for me. See, look here, and here as well... Gah! ...Ahem! Sorry, I got carried away. I just wanted to make sure you knew.

touch.line: If you want to spar with me, you'd better think thrice. One slip of the hand, and it won't be just a flesh wound that we're dealing with.

touch2.line: Ugh... I'm still a woman, you know! Have you no sense of decency?!

unlock.line: Retrofit complete... Look forward to commanding the might of the demon ascended. I shall not disappoint you!

battle.line: First Torpedo Squadron, {namecode:47}, Moving out!

detail.line: Don't push yourself too much, Commander!

drop_descrip.line: Sixth ship of the {namecode:46}-class light cruisers, {namecode:47}.

expedition.line: Commander, shall we return to port and do some fishing? The girls seem to be back from their commission as well.

feeling1.line: Don't touch me...

feeling2.line: What's wrong? If it's nothing then stay quiet, Commander.

feeling3.line: I look trigger happy? I actually prefer being an escort more than I do engaging in combat...

feeling4.line: Commander, should we go fishing today? Oh, there's work to do? I'll wait for you to finish then... Oh? No, it's fine! I'm more than happy to stay with you, Commander.

feeling5.line: I'm just a normal {namecode:47}... no one has ever cursed me to become a demon. If someone tries to hurt you though, Commander, I might just turn right into a demon!

home.line: Did everyone make it back in one piece?

hp_warning.line: Don't panic... wait for the right moment to strike!

login.line: Welcome back. Want to try some fresh torpedoes?

lose.line: Everyone, prepare to retreat... I'll cover the rear!

mail.line: You've got new mail!

main1.line: Commander, shall we go fishing? How about a game of chess?

main2.line: My name seems a bit complicated, but it's actually easy to read. Why don't you try it?

main3.line: Dress up? Oh... these socks are actually pretty easy to take off. Want to try yourself?

mission.line: We're starting a new mission. Got it?

mission_complete.line: These rewards aren't so bad...

profile.line: {namecode:46}-class light cruiser, {namecode:47}. I've spent most of my time in the First Torpedo Squadron. Although I look aggressive, I actually prefer other things like fishing and just cruising around... just like when I was at Kiska. Perhaps protecting others is a more suitable job for me.

propose.line: It's not for the other sisters in First torpedo squadron, but for me? Is that really alright? Ahh, this makes me happier than that one miraculous victory......thank you, Commander, I shall treat it as my most precious treasure.

touch.line: Be quiet, Commander.

touch2.line: Want to have a taste of my torpedoes, Commander?

unlock.line: Hi, Commander... I'm {namecode:47}. What are you looking at? My horns? Don't mistake me for {namecode:44} or {namecode:45}...

upgrade.line: This isn't a bad feeling at all...

win_mvp.line: I'm number one? Hm... I don't feel anything special...

drop_descrip.line: Combat retrofit complete! First Torpedo Squadron flagship, Abukuma, ready to sortie any time!

home.line: I've prepared snacks for everyone. Commander, there's some for you too! Come dig in!

main1.line: nil

main2.line: Have you finally memorized my name? Just read it out. You can give it a few tries~

main3.line: My expression seems a bit softer now? It's because I like the fleet and the Commander more than I did before~!

mission_complete.line: I brought back the rewards, Commander!

touch.line: Commander, did you call for me?

touch2.line: Hey! Commander, you're going to be eating torpedoes if you keep this up!

unlock.line: Combat retrofit complete! First Torpedo Squadron flagship, Abukuma, ready to sortie any time!

win_mvp.line: The most important thing is that everyone stays safe.

battle.line: Fighting is a drag... but losing is an even bigger drag!

detail.line: Not saying anything makes you look cool? Figures... you would believe something like that.

drop_descrip.line: Mogami-class Heavy Cruiser no. 1 - Mogami

expedition.line: You're going to go greet the commission fleet? I'll just stay here, so I don't end up ramming into someone.

feeling1.line: Well, a hapless fellow like me was bound to get stuck with a hapless commander...

feeling2.line: You must really have some strange hobbies, to want to associate with hapless folks like me. Oh well, if it's just talking... I suppose I can entertain you...

feeling3.line: My horn, huh... Well, I don't really mind, but... it kind of sticks out, doesn't it? I don't really like the attention... *sigh*...

feeling4.line: I already know that Mikuma and Nachi don't hold anything against me, but I can't forgive myself... *sigh*... Huh? My horn is cute?! ...I-idiot...

feeling5.line: Um... Commander, uh... maybe, umm, since you said you liked it... would you like to try... t-touching it?

home.line: Everyone made it back safely. Isn't that enough?

hp_warning.line: Have I spread my misfortune to everyone...?

login.line: Welcome back. Huh? You want me to say it with more emotion? Sorry, chief. Not sure I can help with that one.

lose.line: So this is what I'm made of...

mail.line: I picked up the mail. Can I leave it here?

main1.line: I wonder what Mikuma is doing right now... Well, I suppose there's nothing to worry about. She's not like me, after all...

main2.line: Are you sure you want me to be your secretary? Just about anybody else would be better for the job. I'm serious... I'm not just saying that to avoid work.

main3.line: Perhaps I should get Nachi to teach me how to be a little more cheerful... crap, hope nobody heard that...

mission.line: I finished organizing the task list. Even I couldn't mess something like this up... probably.

mission_complete.line: I'll go pick up the mission rewards. Commander, you can just stay put and keep working.

profile.line: I am Mogami, nameship of the Mogami-class... on paper, anyway. After what happened to Mikuma and Nachi at Midway, I have no right to call myself that anymore... In any case, feel free to hand me your work, but just don't expect much.

propose.line: Are you sure you won't regret choosing someone like me? If you say so... I suppose I can put in a bit more effort for our sake... A-anyway, please take care of me...

touch.line: You don't have to remind me, I'll get the work done.

touch2.line: Eek!! Commander, are you seriously interested in someone like me...?

unlock.line: Mogami, reporting for duty... Don't worry too much about me, just leave me be and I'll find my own place to crash.

upgrade.line: Thanks... What's the matter? Am I not allowed to express gratitude?

win_mvp.line: First place, huh. Got a problem with it?

battle.line: There are people waiting for me... so I refuse to lose!

detail.line: I look even cooler now when I don't say anything? Whatever... have it your way...

drop_descrip.line: Are you sure this is a retrofit and not some weird hazing ritual? I look... Well, I suppose I do feel stronger. Guess I'll try to work a bit harder. Wouldn't hurt for you to look forward to it a little.

login.line: Commander, you're back. Huh? I just happen to remember what your footsteps sound like.

main1.line: Recently, Mikuma has been telling me that I have more self-esteem... Not sure about that one though, I don't think I've really changed...

main2.line: Secretary ship duties? Well, I still think I'm not really cut out for it compared to the others... but if it's what you want, I'll keep doing it.

main3.line: Commander, be honest. What do you think about my new outfit after the retrofit? Um... if you like it, I suppose we can keep it like this...

touch.line: Maybe I should go practice using this naginata or something...

unlock.line: Are you sure this is a retrofit and not some weird hazing ritual? I look... Well, I suppose I do feel stronger. Guess I'll try to work a bit harder. Wouldn't hurt for you to look forward to it a little.

battle.line: Everyone, on me!

detail.line: My... horn? If it makes people remember me, then I believe it's not all that bad.

drop_descrip.line: Mogami-class heavy cruiser number two – Mikuma.

expedition.line: A commission has finished, Commander. If you're occupied at the moment, please send me in your stead.

feeling1.line: I've gotta warn my sister about how untrustworthy you are...

feeling2.line: Pardon me, Commander, I'm occupied with the task you gave me... Okay, how may I help? Communication? Yes, of course, communication is important.

feeling3.line: All Mogami-class cruisers were part of Cruiser Division 7, but because Kumano and Suzuya were launched later than me, it was I who had to look after Mogami. And for that reason, they aren't as close to her as I am.

feeling4.line: I'm always willing to support my sister, but owing to her somber personality... I don't think anyone but you can truly guide her, Commander...

feeling5.line: Jealousy... you say? It's never been on my mind... As long as I have my dear sister and my dear Commander... everything will probably be okay... I think?

home.line: Outstanding performance, Commander.

hp_warning.line: Don't panic! We still have a chance!

login.line: Welcome back. Let's try to get a lot of work done today.

lose.line: *Gah*...! This will serve as a lesson...!

mail.line: Here is the letter that arrived today, Commander.

main1.line: My sister is... probably sitting somewhere, alone, lamenting the past again. Commander, would you please excuse me for a moment?

main2.line: A secretary should be the Commander's right hand. Please don't hesitate to give me orders.

main3.line: I was the first heavy cruiser to sink in the war... Oh, never mind, it was nothing important.

mission.line: I have organized the mission rewards, Commander. Could you confirm them, please?

mission_complete.line: I have completed my inspection of the mission rewards, Commander.

profile.line: I am Mikuma, the second ship of the Mogami-class. I collided with my sister in Midway, but I don't resent her for it. On the contrary: she... Ah, forgive me for changing the topic so suddenly... I shall do everything I can for the fleet, so please give me your orders.

propose.line: Sorry for taking so long, Commander. Huh? I should call you "darling"? Umm... D-darling... This feels a little awkward, but it's something I should slowly get used to. Now, I hope we will be together for many long years.

touch.line: I'm standing by. Please give me your orders.

touch2.line: ... Commander, please be wary of accidental discharges from my cannons.

unlock.line: My name is Mikuma. I'm Mogami's little sister. If... if you don't mind, could you please look after her? She has a bit of an unusual personality, you see...

upgrade.line: Your kindness is highly appreciated. I swear to repay it one day.

win_mvp.line: This is nothing to get thrilled about!

detail.line: The Commander was staring right at me... Of course I'd be self-conscious, but it's not like what Suzuya said...! Just thinking about it is making me even more self-conscious... *blushes*

drop_descrip.line: Commander, may you and all our friends enjoy peace and good health... Alright, what did you think? That was a ceremonial dance I'd like to offer to everyone at the main event.

expedition.line: The commission team has returned. Want to take Suzuya and Kumano with you when you head over?

feeling5.line: Commander, I'd like you to take better care of my sister instead. Though I don't mind seeing the two of you together, the same can't be said for her. The two of us at the same time...? Um, o-of course that would be possible...

headtouch.line: My horn... is cute?

home.line: I left some drinks in the lounge area for you. Commander, please take this time to rest up.

login.line: Welcome back, Commander. Mogami should have already started heading back. Did something happen...?

main1.line: My sister seems to be troubled... Commander, let's hear her out together!

main2.line: I want to see my sister dance, but I'm better suited for an event like this.

main3.line: Kumano also wants to try dancing? That could be arranged... Wait, no! What if she tears her costume because her movements are too flashy?

mission.line: I've finished collecting the mission rewards. I think it's about to go check on my sister...

mission_complete.line: Mission complete. I'm sure my sister is also pleased by this. Heehee.

touch.line: Mikuma stands at attention. Please give your orders.

touch2.line: Umm, please mind my main battery... It might explode!

unlock.line: Commander, may you and all our friends enjoy peace and good health... Alright, what did you think? That was a ceremonial dance I'd like to offer to everyone at the main event.

win_mvp.line: I actually would've liked my sister to take these honors...

battle.line: You're going up against me!

detail.line: These bandages? They're not for when I get hurt, they're for wrapping around my fists... You'll struggle to find anyone who can actually injure me.

drop_descrip.line: Sendai-class light cruiser number one – Sendai.

expedition.line: Yo, commission's done. Don't tell me you're really considering just keeping those hardworking girls waiting.

feeling1.line: Think it's about time we say goodbye.

feeling2.line: I'm not much of a people person, so I'd rather you'd just leave me alone... Hey, relax. You're my boss, so I'll still do my job.

feeling3.line: I can't settle until I've made right out of wrong with my fists. That's my way of life. It's why I try not to get involved in anyone's business; I just don't wanna cause any trouble.

feeling4.line: Feels like I've been here a long time... I know I'm the one saying that, but still, it really has been a long time...

feeling5.line: People like you are pretty amazing. You do everything I want to, but just a bit better... When I'm with you, I even lose track of time... As long as you don't lose sight of who you are, I'll follow you to ends of the earth.

home.line: When's the next sortie? I've still got a ton of spare bandages.

login.line: I'm done warmin' up. Time to sortie, or what?

lose.line: Owwww... Ahaha... Guess this is it...

mail.line: Here, your letter.

main1.line: I dream of justice, justice for... Never mind. Let's write off that one as a joke.

main2.line: All I have are my principles and my fists. Even so, I'll always keep moving forward.

main3.line: Commander, who do you think is our worst enemy? The Sirens? I think it's our own minds.

mission.line: A mission... That's my kinda deal.

mission_complete.line: You sure you wanna ignore those mission rewards, Commander? Not that I really care.

profile.line: I'm Sendai, the first ship of the Sendai-class. Although my service record isn't as impressive as my little sisters', I served as the flagship of Destroyer Squadron 3 and fought in tons of battles. I bit the dust at Bougainville, but I did so as a warrior with no regrets.

propose.line: Commander, before you gave me this, I'd just have left you if you'd forgotten your principles... But now that you've given me this... Forget your principles, and you'll taste my fists of love and rage. *Giggle*

touch.line: Commander, you'll end up gettin' hurt if you approach me without warning.

touch2.line: You got a damn death wish? You askin' me to knock some sense into that skull of yours? Izzat it, huh?!

unlock.line: You're a commander? I don't need one... But maybe we were fated to meet, or something. Guess you've got me to look after too, now. The name's Sendai. Don't forget it.

upgrade.line: I'll become stronger, then I'll...!

win_mvp.line: Heh. Won't even need to replace my bandages.

battle.line: Sorry to say, but this is where you'll all die!

detail.line: Yeah? Oh, I'm working on my sortie pose. When goin' to war, you need a war pose, y'know?

drop_descrip.line: Hmh. Guess I won't be needin' these bandages anymore. Commander, how about we find out how strong I've gotten... by having you take one of my punches?

home.line: Nice work. Want some sweets? You can have some of mine. They're all stuff I personally like, though.

hp_warning.line: Sorry to say... but I can't afford to be defeated here!

login.line: You're back, huh? Focus on your work. Gimme a shout when it's time to sortie.

main1.line: Violence is the only solution I know of for my problems. That's why I envy you and Jintsuu sometimes.

main2.line: Whenever I try to be like Jintsuu and use logic to solve problems, I usually end up using my fists anyway. I dunno why, either...

main3.line: Hardships don't get under my skin, but I'm scared that I'll one day lose my way...

touch2.line: Hold still, Commander. We're pals, so I'll only hit you with 80% of my full strength!

unlock.line: Hmh. Guess I won't be needin' these bandages anymore. Commander, how about we find out how strong I've gotten... by having you take one of my punches?

win_mvp.line: Where'd I put my bandages... Oh, right, don't need 'em anymore... Totally forgot.

battle.line: All ships, charge forward!

detail.line: For the next operation, we need to allocate resources, and... Yes? Ah, help yourself, Commander.

drop_descrip.line: Sendai-class No. 2 light cruiser, Jintsuu.

expedition.line: Stop daydreaming! Commissions have returned!

feeling1.line: You might as well just leave the fleet management to me.

feeling2.line: I was a flagship before, but now I'm just a common warrior. Please treat me the same as you would the others.

feeling3.line: Commander, it's okay to respect my opinions, but please have confidence in your own judgment. I wouldn't be standing by your side if I didn't believe in you.

feeling4.line: Commander, why do you think those famous generals of the past were willing to bow to their superiors? Was it the limit of their abilities, or was it devotion to their leaders? In my case, perhaps a bit of both.

feeling5.line: Real leaders will always stick to their guns, no matter who opposes them. You can tell if their methods are correct by seeing who is willing to follow them. For example... me...

home.line: Books cannot teach you everything. Some things can only be picked up through live combat. What do you think, Commander?

login.line: Commander, how you spend your time off-duty is no business of mine. Once you arrive, however, please do your work properly.

lose.line: All ships, retreat! Do not make meaningless sacrifices.

mail.line: Commander! It's important to respond to messages promptly!

main1.line: If being cautious is considered cowardice, then shouldn't being brave also be considered recklessness?

main2.line: There is no single solution for everything. Only through comparison, practice, and even failure, can one find their own correct answer.

main3.line: Even if others don't understand my actions, I'll always do what I think is right... Even if you don't understand, Commander.

mission.line: Your new missions have been sorted. Please take a look.

mission_complete.line: Rewards are here... Hmm? Don't worry. I'm just thinking about how to make our fleet more efficient.

profile.line: I'm Sendaii-class ship No. 2, Flagship of the Second Torpedo Squadron, Jintsuu. People have criticized me for being a coward, but I proved myself in the Battle of Kolombangara. Let me show you the glory of the Second Torpedo Squadron once more.

propose.line: Deciding on the best course of action before acting cautiously has always been my creed. I can now say with confidence that choosing you, Commander, was the correct decision.

skill.line: I've been waiting for this moment!

touch.line: What's the matter? I'm just thinking about how to manage the fleet.

touch2.line: You've got more guts than I expected, Commander. Do you have the heart to face the consequences, though?

unlock.line: The battlefield can change at any second. Think rationally and act cautiously so that you may never be defeated in battle. Commander, have you been able to achieve this? Flagship of the Second Torpedo Squadron, Jintsuu, reporting for duty.

upgrade.line: Should we consider advancing deeper into enemy territory?

win_mvp.line: Is that it?

detail.line: I said I was taking a vacation, but even out here on the beach, I'm still thinking about the affairs of the fleet... I really am a workaholic, aren't I?

drop_descrip.line: Hmm? Is it unusual? Hah. Even I require a change of pace to clear my mind every so often. Commander, why don't you come out and get some fresh air as well?

home.line: Here, iced coconut water. Please have some.

login.line: After we finish work today, how about taking a break on the beach?

main1.line: If you relax too much, you'll become undisciplined. If you're too uptight, you'll only find yourself out of breath.

main2.line: Every year when it is swimsuit season, I can't help but to be envious of Sendai... Commander, I'm not being negligent in my exercise, am I?

main3.line: Commander, your mind has wandered off onto the beach, hasn't it? It’s written all over your face.

touch.line: Commander, you're concerned about it too, right? My tail is so conspicuous in this swimsuit...

touch2.line: You can't concentrate on your work when I'm wearing a swimsuit, right? Hehe, just consider this a test of will then.

unlock.line: Hmm? Is it unusual? Hah. Even I require a change of pace to clear my mind every so often. Commander, why don't you come out and get some fresh air as well?

detail.line: If you think about it, the Big Bad Wolf's plan has so many holes in it. For example, he could have left the grandmother alive and used her as bait... Ehehe, I'm just playing around.

drop_descrip.line: "Where do you think you're going so early in the morning, Little Red Riding Hood?" ...Oh, if it isn't the Commander. This might be my own little whim, but I often find myself thinking the same way as this character... If you don't mind, I'd like to hear your feedback about my acting.

home.line: Well done. I'll evaluate your battle plans for you, just like you evaluated my acting skills for me.

login.line: Even in fairytale-esque stories, there are hints of deception and trickery hidden throughout. Basically, make sure to stay on guard as you usually do...Hehehe♪

main1.line: The moment you plan on striking down your prey is the moment you should be most alert. One can never know when a hunter might try to use the opportunity for their own benefit.

main2.line: Speaking of hunters, none are better suited for the role than Sendai. I really wouldn't want to make an enemy out of her, even if it's just an act.

main3.line: Hmm... I know I have it down in my head, but when I start to act it out, I keep running into trouble. Do you have any advice for me, Commander?

touch.line: This outfit? ...Oh, it's what I have on before I turn into the grandmother.

touch2.line: And, checkmate. Hehehe~

unlock.line: "Where do you think you're going so early in the morning, Little Red Riding Hood?" ...Oh, if it isn't the Commander. This might be my own little whim, but I often find myself thinking the same way as this character... If you don't mind, I'd like to hear your feedback about my acting.

win_mvp.line: Maybe I should gobble you right up.

battle.line: Everyone, get ready! ... Press forward!

detail.line: Commander, do you have any tactics you'd like to discuss with me? If you'd like... we can also just sit down and have a chat.

drop_descrip.line: Since I've gotten used to living with you, Commander, I've decided to be more laid-back after receiving my remodel. My dance? Hehe... I can't show that to just anyone so easily.

login.line: Did you sleep well, Commander? Do you need any help with fleet administration?

main1.line: Sometimes it's hard to prove to others that what you believe is right. Commander, let's do our best together!

main2.line: Every now and then, I get a bit jealous of {namecode:38} and how straightforward she is...

main3.line: Even though some people may think that cautiousness is a sign of weakness, I'll be happy as long as our fleet truly understands me...

mission_complete.line: Rewards have been issued! Want to see something interesting now that we can take it easy?

touch.line: There's nothing wrong with wanting to see me dance... I'll show you, but only if you work seriously first!

touch2.line: Commander, please do not mistake my cautiousness for tolerance.

unlock.line: Since I've gotten used to living with you, Commander, I've decided to be more laid-back after receiving my remodel. My dance? Hehe... I can't show that to just anyone so easily.

upgrade.line: I can always work harder for the fleet!

win_mvp.line: I only gave the orders, the real credit goes to the fleet!

battle.line: My sisters, please look forward to my performance in battle!

detail.line: Commander, would you like to study together with me?

drop_descrip.line: Sendai-class light cruiser number three – Naka.

expedition.line: I think a commission has been completed. We should go and say thanks to the returning team!

feeling1.line: My sisters chose you because you just let them mess around without being scolded? How strange...

feeling2.line: What I do on my days off? Well, I get up and do morning training, I read for an hour, I do target practice for 2 hours, and then... Basically, I make full use of my vacation days! I have to work really hard to become stronger, you know?

feeling3.line: What are my hobbies? ...I don't really have one in particular. But I enjoy reading and training... Oh, would you like to train together with me? Heheheh~

feeling4.line: Hmm, I feel a little guilty over always making you come with me... Is there anything you'd like to do? We'll do it together, of course!

feeling5.line: Huh? Are you saying you've been waiting for a chance to go on a date too? Heheh, in that case~ Why don't we do it, Commander?
