home.line: There's nothing better than getting to come back home. Wouldn't you agree, Commander?

hp_warning.line: Everyone, stay calm! Let's change our strategy!

login.line: Welcome back, Commander! I'll try to be the best secretary you've ever had!

lose.line: Oh no! Commander, we should retreat immediately! Jintsuu said we shouldn't make meaningless sacrifices!

mail.line: Commander, I have mail for you. I picked it up on the way back from my training.

main1.line: If it looks like there's nothing for me to do, would you mind if I did a little training on my own? I won't get in the way of your work!

main2.line: Jintsuu is wise, Sendai is strong... but I'll work my way towards both brains and brawn! ...Ahahah, though I'm not sure if I can actually do it.

main3.line: If you're tired, would you like me to give you a good relaxation tip? I actually know quite a lot about it~

mission.line: I reorganized the mission list for you! Here, please choose one!

mission_complete.line: You've cleared another mission! You're so brilliant, Commander! I'll need to work just as hard!

profile.line: I'm Naka, Sendai-class light cruiser number three! Due to certain circumstances, my construction was delayed, I was redeployed to place after place, and my service record as the flagship of Desron 4 isn't much to brag about... but that's okay! I'll still work my butt off to try to surpass my sisters!

propose.line: You can stare as much as you'd like. Hehehe~ From now on I will use my brains and brawn to serve you, my sweetheart whom I love so much!

touch.line: Hum hum~♪ Oh, sorry, am I disturbing you in the middle of work...?

touch2.line: Eek! ...Please, Commander, try to stay focused on your work while in the office!

unlock.line: Nice to meet you, Commander! I'm the light cruiser Naka! My sisters are better known than me, but I swear that one day I'll be even more famous than them!

upgrade.line: With your support I can work even harder!

win_mvp.line: Compared to my goal of surpassing my sisters, this is no big deal at all!

detail.line: I heard that surfing is a great way to sharpen your motor skills, especially your sense of balance! C'mon, let's give it a try!

drop_descrip.line: Ahaha! Another big one's coming~! Phew~ that felt amazing~! Ah, Commander, let's hit the waves together, shall we?

feeling5.line: Surfing is pretty fun once you get the hang of it, right? What do you think, Commander? Wanna go on a surf date with me?

home.line: There's no way to keep this tail from getting in the way when I'm swimming, huh... Wait! I'm sure Sendai knows a way around it!

login.line: We've gotta warm up before hitting the waves! C'mon, Commander, don't keep me waiting!

mail.line: C-Commander?! We just got a message in a bottle!

main1.line: Sendai, how'd you split that watermelon blindfolded...?! Th-that was so cool...!

main2.line: I'm sure Jintsuu will be writing some report like "The Status of the Waves and Water in this Sea Region" after our vacation is over. Hahaha!

main3.line: It sure feels nice to just float around and let the waves sweep you away~

mission.line: Eh? Jintsuu, you even brought the mission documents along?

touch.line: Hehe, Commander~ Did you just offer to give me a massage~?

touch2.line: Commander... if you do this kind of stuff on the beach, all the girls will hate you, you know?

unlock.line: Ahaha! Another big one's coming~! Phew~ that felt amazing~! Ah, Commander, let's hit the waves together, shall we?

battle.line: Let's give it everything we have.

detail.line: Ah, if it isn't you, Commander. I was just making a snack. Could you taste it for pois... I mean, taste to see if it's done?

drop_descrip.line: Agano-class light cruiser number one – Agano.

expedition.line: Commander, the girls that went on a commission have returned. If you keep twiddling your thumbs, you'll miss your chance to welcome them back...

feeling1.line: Even breathing the same air as you do is unpleasant, Commander~

feeling2.line: I wonder what will happen today... *Giggle*, I'm looking forward to finding out.

feeling3.line: Commander, why don't we have a chat? Yes, I'm curious as to what kind of person you are.

feeling4.line: Me? I'm fond of interesting things. Such as... the act of toying with you, Commander... *Giggle*, you'll have to excuse me for that~

feeling5.line: Someone who toys with the person they like... Are you familiar with anyone like that, Commander? *Giggle*, perhaps it's me~

home.line: Commander, fantastic work on the last sortie. May I offer you some hot tea?

hp_warning.line: Dear me, it seems things have gotten rather serious.

login.line: Commander, it's not yet time for work. Are you confident you didn't get the time wrong?

lose.line: How careless of me... I will undergo special training when we've returned. *Giggle*.

mail.line: Are you sure this isn't a love letter from that girl you know? *Giggle*♪

main1.line: Commander, if you're tired, why not play a game of leapfrog and jump around in the office? It'll help improve your blood circulation~

main2.line: Though supporting from behind the lines is easy, doing so for long periods makes me grow tired of it...

main3.line: Commander, are you in need of some rest? Hm? *Giggle*, I just felt like asking. Stay focused and continue your work~

mission.line: I went ahead and sorted out the new mission documents.

mission_complete.line: Commander, if you keep tasking your secretary with collecting the mission rewards, your brain will eventually turn to mush. Although, it might be interesting if that happened... *Giggle*♪

profile.line: I am Agano, the lead ship of the Agano-class. My abilities as a light cruiser are first-rate, though my birth was just a tad bit late... Commander, it is a pleasure to be in your service.

propose.line: You have feelings for me, Commander? You wish to be with me forever? ... Why am I asking the questions here? *Giggle*, because, even for someone like me, wouldn't it be humiliating to have someone else take the initiative at moments like these...?

skill.line: They don't call me "state of the art" for nothing~

touch.line: These documents are for me... Hm? That's unusual? I like to keep business and pleasure separate, you see.

touch2.line: Oh, Commander~ *Grin*

unlock.line: Are you the Commander? My name is Agano. The pleasure is all mine, *giggle*... Never mind that, it was nothing. I'm eager to assume my position within your fleet.

upgrade.line: Please, have faith in the skill of this Agano-class light cruiser.

win_mvp.line: Did you witness my performance?

detail.line: Is this a satisfactory pose for the occasion, Commander? Or would it suit you better if I stuck out my chest slightly more?

drop_descrip.line: Even though I'm not really into this whole "Christmas" thing, if it means I get to toy around with your heart by wearing this cute outfit of mine, then I suppose I would be interested. Hehe~

home.line: I'd like to offer you a reward for working so diligently, even on a day as special as this.

login.line: Oh, aren't you back early? May I suggest starting with a review of today's schedule?

main1.line: Commander, would you please stand over there for a moment? I need an accurate reference for the snow sculpture I'm making~

main2.line: You've done well, Commander. Please get yourself some hard-earned sleep tonight. Ah, you thought I was teasing you with that request? *Giggle*~

main3.line: Commander, what are you wishing for this Christmas? Ah, you don't need to consider your options at length. I picked out your present long ago, you see♪

touch.line: *Giggle*, while I do enjoy a bit of teasing, being on good terms with you is more important. Commander, how about we set some time aside to watch the snowfall later?

touch2.line: Oh my, it appears my costume has caused an unintended development♪

unlock.line: Even though I'm not really into this whole "Christmas" thing, if it means I get to toy around with your heart by wearing this cute outfit of mine, then I suppose I would be interested. Hehe~

detail.line: This super-cute girl was sitting on a bench all by herself while looking a little lonely~ But too bad this scaredy-Commander won't even pounce on the opportunity~

drop_descrip.line: "Oh my, you're also out for a stroll? Hehe, my name's Agano. And what might yours be?" ...Jeez, Commander, take this more seriously. According to the setting, we just met for the first time.

feeling5.line: Why'd I ask you to play a dating game? Well, if I teased you too much, wouldn't that only make you dislike me? But since I can't help it, I decided to make it up to you this way~ Do you think better of me now, Commander?

home.line: You must be tired, right? Here, if you'd like, you can come lie down over here.

login.line: "Hey, are you here by yourself? Hehe. Why don't we... have a little chat, then?"

mail.line: More mail, huh... You're quite the popular one. Hmph~

main1.line: You haven't had anything to eat? If you'd like, you can have some of my crepe~

main2.line: "Um... do you mind if I shift a bit closer to you? It's a bit chilly out here..." What am I after? Jeez, way to spoil the mood...

main3.line: "Would you mind telling me more about yourself? I feel like... we have a lot in common~" ...Hehe, in other words, I want to learn a lot more about you!

mission_complete.line: All done with the mission? Did you also pick up a crepe for me? Thanks a lot~♪

touch.line: "Want to take a stroll with me?" *sigh*... It took me five minutes just to get you to ask me out. Commander, you have to take the initiative next time, got it?

touch2.line: Manhandling a girl who you barely just met... Heeh~ Commander, I didn't know you were that kind of person~

unlock.line: "Oh my, you're also out for a stroll? Hehe, my name's Agano. And what might yours be?" ...Jeez, Commander, take this more seriously. According to the setting, we just met for the first time.

win_mvp.line: Commander, it's more fun to play around this way~

detail.line: The competition tonight is considerably fiercer than I anticipated... This calls for a counterattack... Oh, it was nothing important. I was just thinking out loud about how, uh... fabulous that chandelier is.

drop_descrip.line: The blunt approach is not my style, but I cannot have Noshiro think I only inch my way to success... Oh, I was just talking to myself, Commander. Hehe, so anyway, would you mind being my partner for tonight's party?

feeling5.line: I am an... enigma to you? Why, I would say that you're the enigmatic individual between us, Commander. And yet, that makes one want to get to know you better, the sinful person that you are. Hehehe~

home.line: My, Commander, you look simply resplendent when you return from battle... I'm once again head over heels for you. I mean it.

login.line: Well, well. Were you hoping to fluster your lady by arriving late on purpose, Commander?

main1.line: Come to think of it, I haven't seen Noshiro around... Knowing her, she may be off on her own somewhere...

main2.line: Say, Commander, would you care for a drink? Me? Well, I can hold my liquor at least as well as you. Heheh.

main3.line: Please, Commander, you need not look so on-edge. I may enjoy teasing you, but I'm not so brash as to do it on this special occasion.

mission.line: You certainly are greeting many people tonight, Commander.

unlock.line: The blunt approach is not my style, but I cannot have Noshiro think I only inch my way to success... Oh, I was just talking to myself, Commander. Hehe, so anyway, would you mind being my partner for tonight's party?

battle.line: Please look over the battle plans, just to double check.

detail.line: Regardless of the situation, you should first calm down, think of a way forward, and only then act. That's how I tackle things.

drop_descrip.line: Agano-class light cruiser number two – Noshiro.

expedition.line: Please form the next commission team, okay?

feeling1.line: You seem to be in quite the hurry. For once, why don't you try calming down and reflecting upon your actions?

feeling2.line: I am currently contemplating over the last practice exercise. Do you not also have things you should be doing right now?

feeling3.line: An invitation to a joint practice session together from Agano... How troubling. It's full of intent to bully. Even though I want to refuse, I can't think of an excuse. Instead, would you be willing to assign some official duties to me around that time?

feeling4.line: Ahem. I'm only asking this because I keep hearing my friends use the term over and over, but... out of curiosity, what exactly is this concept called `a woman's intuition'...? "I have absolutely no clue," you say? I see. I guess it's an enigma to you, too.

feeling5.line: So this is what it feels like to have your heart throb. While I used to be just as inexperienced with this feeling as I was experienced with being perceptive and relying on my instincts... Yes, it's all clear to me now. My feelings, as well as yours.

home.line: Hm... Ah, sorry. I was lost in thought. So you've returned. Let's start by reviewing this past battle.

hp_warning.line: An enemy trap?!

login.line: My, you're quite early today. For starters, how about checking today's schedule?

lose.line: We have no choice but to pull back...

mail.line: Mail? I'll check to make sure there's nothing suspicious inside.

main1.line: ...Let's try thinking of some recipes for tomorrow's meals...

main2.line: Keeping everything neat and tidy shortens the time it takes to search for documents. Why don't we start by organizing the documents on your desk?

main3.line: Agano's exp... Yes, it's truly impossible to tell what's behind that fearless smile... She always ends up leading me around by the nose.

mission.line: If you feel overwhelmed by the number of missions, why not try sorting them based on priority?

mission_complete.line: I've received the mission rewards. Please double check that nothing has been left out.

profile.line: Just as Agano says, the great war in which we were born may have been an era of misfortune. ...No. As a member of the improved Agano-class, I should be able to make you satisfied with my work, if only there was just a place I could display my true strength.

propose.line: In order to not just accept your feelings, but to reciprocate them as well... Umm, let's see... I'll need to prepare meals, go on dates on days off, but I also need to make sure I don't lose motivation for my regular duties, like practice... Eh? Ah, sorry, I got lost in my train of thought. Huh? I-I should keep going?

touch.line: If you're stuck, why not stop what you're doing, and instead, think of a different way to proceed?

touch2.line: R-Regarding your conduct right now, I demand that you apologize and reflect upon your actions!

unlock.line: I'm the new arrival, Noshiro, second ship of the Agano-class, reporting for duty. Let's do our utmost to prove our worth to each other, shall we?

upgrade.line: Please, strengthen my combat ability.

win_mvp.line: If you lead with careful analysis and accurate decision-making, your victory is ensured.

battle.line: Now, let's put on a dazzling show!

drop_descrip.line: Just as I thought, this is the perfect place for watching fireworks. You came here thinking that too, didn't yo8u?

home.line: Where were you all this time? Don't tell me... you got lost?

login.line: It'll be a bit of a walk, but won't you come along with me?

main1.line: I only found this place by pure chance. Thinking back on it, I wonder how I was feeling when I stumbled upon this back alleyway instead of following the main road...

main2.line: Please, watch your step. The road is very narrow.

main3.line: If we're talking about dressing up properly for the festival, this is definitely the getup. However, I struggled a bit while changing into this. I even got laughed at by Agano. ...*sigh*

touch.line: Hm... Ah, I'll be fine even if you don't prop me up like that. ...Um, thank you very much.

touch2.line: Apologize and reflect upon your actions. Don't think that you're going to get away with it just because we're at a festival!

unlock.line: Just as I thought, this is the perfect place for watching fireworks. You came here thinking that too, didn't you?

battle.line: Freeze, and turn to ice... Your time is up.

detail.line: Don't worry. There's nothing for you to worry about. All the preparations for the party and the related formalities have all been taken care of. All that's left for you to do is to enjoy the evening while savoring this beautiful scenery.

drop_descrip.line: Commander, what are you standing around for? Did you also need a change of pace? That makes two of us— Come, there's nothing to be afraid of here.

expedition.line: Though it might not seem that way, we're actually pretty close to the Port. Shall we go and greet the Commissions Team?

feeling5.line: Hmm, I wonder what kind of scene this set is supposed to depict. A birdcage, crows, the sea, blue roses, and... you beside me... Um... Don't you think this is quite picturesque?

home.line: Once you've rested up, why don't we go and make our appearance at the party together?

login.line: Phew... Go on, fly away, little ones. Mind the cage on your way out, now... I've been taking care of these guys. What have you been up to?

main1.line: Wah! ...Sorry. I can't believe I almost fell... Um... T-Thank you for catching me...

main2.line: It's a given that I love the atmosphere here, but another reason I like this place is that I feel like I can finally get away from Agano's endless teasing here... Though, I'd rather she just stop worrying about me in the first place...

main3.line: This is yet another massive set built right in the Port. Yes, it's incredibly gorgeous... Honestly, when I saw it for the first time, I forgot I was in still in the Port for a moment. Speaking of which, didn't you also stand and stare in awe when you first came here?

touch.line: Hehe. I think even Agano would take a liking to this place, too.

touch2.line: Excuse me... How about I give you a massage... with this?

unlock.line: Commander, what are you standing around for? Did you also need a change of pace? That makes two of us— Come, there's nothing to be afraid of here.

win_mvp.line: In the face of well-crafted plans, resistance is futile. Accept your defeat.

detail.line: I like staying in places that are quiet and peaceful. They make me feel relaxed. The whisperings of the wind, the sound of flowing water, the harbingers of spring, and Commander's... Ehem, I-I didn't mean anything by that.

drop_descrip.line: Whew... Oh, are you cold by any chance? I have some hot tea for you if you'd like. If you want someone to chat with, I'd be glad to keep you company.

feeling5.line: Though the snow has piled up this much, it'll all melt with the coming of spring—becoming water that will nourish nascent life. I don't think I can remain cold like this for much longer, either. After all, before I was able to notice... spring has managed to start creeping into my life, too.

home.line: Welcome back. Oh... I know you're thirsty, but the tea's a bit hot. Take care not to burn yourself.

login.line: It's good to see you. How should we start the day off?

main1.line: You still haven't taken a sip yet. Is it too hot? ...Are you perhaps bad with hot things?

main2.line: It's not like I'm opposed to going into battle as a warship, but... I'd really like to save people as well. Much like Hamakaze's always done.

main3.line: The Manjuus' teapot is astonishingly authentic. I don't see any problems with adding one to the Office for daily use, either. Hehe.

touch.line: There's really no reason to push yourself to get some work done today. It's a precious day off, so why don't you enjoy it for a change?

touch2.line: Sigh... Of course you would do that.

unlock.line: Whew... Oh, are you cold by any chance? I have some hot tea for you if you'd like. If you want someone to chat with, I'd be glad to keep you company.

battle.line: 2nd DesRon, sallying forth!

detail.line: The snacks Agano asked for... Commander's documents... and then there's Jintsuu's... Phew... Things ended up real busy...

drop_descrip.line: Why don't you unwind for a bit before you start reflecting on the day's happenings? I'm sure it'll be far more efficient that way.

headtouch.line: What's the matter?

login.line: Phew... Now then, let's prepare ourselves for the work ahead of us.

main1.line: What is there to drink... Maybe some tea or coffee? ...No, I mustn't. Too much caffeine will interfere with my sleep.

main2.line: Even on my off days, I always end up working anyway... Maybe I'm also a workaholic, just like the Commander...

main3.line: This feels just like tutoring the little destroyers. Hehe~

touch.line: Hm? Oh, my apologies. I didn't realize you were calling for me.

touch2.line: Why don't we focus on work for now?

unlock.line: Why don't you unwind for a bit before you start reflecting on the day's happenings? I'm sure it'll be far more efficient that way.

drop_descrip.line: Welcom...?! What are you doing here? Wait, don't leave—I was just surprised, that's all... Well, what would you like to order?

expedition.line: The fleet's back from completing commissions. Make sure you greet them properly before coming back here, Commander.

feeling5.line: Ahem. "How's your order, Master?" ...Too emotionless? Then, how about, "How's your order, Master~♪"? ...Hey! Are you taking me for a fool?!

home.line: Welcome back. Sometimes, I don't really get how I should be treating you while in this outfit... Oh, it's the same for you? That's a relief.

login.line: Did you want me to call you "Master?" Understood... Master.

main1.line: If you're lost on what to order, how about I surprise you?

main2.line: I guess pigtails really do make you look considerably younger... I hate to admit it, but it's just like Agano said.

main3.line: Personally prepared meals aren't part of the service provided by the café, so I leave the cooking to the manjuus, but... if you insist, I wouldn't mind doing it for you.

touch.line: Please, take your time.

touch2.line: R-reflect on your conduct...!

unlock.line: Welcom...?! What are you doing here? Wait, don't leave—I was just surprised, that's all... Well, what would you like to order?

detail.line: I like being able to unwind and have some fun in my swimsuit, but long strolls along the beach are nice too. Um, if you don't mind... Maybe next time, the two of us could...

drop_descrip.line: ...Take that! Heehee... Ahaha! Phew... I know you don't like admitting defeat, but I got you pretty good there. I might have tried a bit too hard, but I'm pretty sure you were the one who told me to give it my all.

expedition.line: I've received word that the commission team has returned. Why don't you take a quick break from work and go welcome them back?

home.line: Welcome back. Care for refreshments? Heehee, make sure to finish the soda before it goes flat.

login.line: You should enjoy yourself at the beach, just like you ordered me to. Hehe.

main1.line: If you're stuck trying to think about what fun things to do next, why don't you ask the others? I'm sure they'd love to join you for anything you'd like.

main2.line: Sakawa... I have an inkling of where she might be. Wouldn't surprise me if she's at a beachside hut somewhere, stuffing her face with sweets. Sigh...

main3.line: I picked this swimsuit because you told me we were going to play on the beach, but instead... No, never mind. But did you perhaps... want to see me in something more risqué?

touch.line: Want another go?

touch2.line: Wh-where are you touching... *blushes*

unlock.line: ...Take that! Heehee... Ahaha! Phew... I know you don't like admitting defeat, but I got you pretty good there. I might have tried a bit too hard, but I'm pretty sure you were the one who told me to give it my all.

win_mvp.line: When it's time to fight, my mind is solely on the battle. Playtime's over; it's time to focus.

battle.line: Second Torpedo Squadron, heading out...!

detail.line: Agano did say that it's important to have a certain degree of flashiness, but... isn't this carriage just overkill? Well, if you think it's apropos, I'm fine with it too. Hehe.

drop_descrip.line: Receiving everyone's blessings is truly a deeply moving experience. But for now, let's set everything else aside and partake of our sweet bliss. After all, you're not just a spectator anymore – we're in this ride together, hehe~

expedition.line: Next up is welcoming back everyone from the commission team, right? Let's get going.

feeling5.line: My face... is all red? That's probably... because of how tightly you're holding me. Don't you ever get tired of me? ...I love you, hehe~

headtouch.line: What's up?

home.line: Welcome back. Hehe. To be honest, my feet are a bit sore. Do you think it was bad for me to wait here for you like a princess?

login.line: You said you'd be the one to escort me today, did you not? Here, take my hand... Mhm.

mail.line: Here's the mail. You know, I was thinking it'd be nice if you'd write me some... Err, n-nevermind...

main1.line: I'm pretty thirsty... Maybe some tea or coffee... Wait, I shouldn't. I won't be able to sleep if I drink too much. ...Oh, the same is true for you?

main2.line: What should we start off with today? ...Don't always make it about work. Isn't it about time you let me do something nice for you?

main3.line: You look like you're having a hard time... If there's anything bothering me, I can hear you out, you know? If I made a face like that, Agano wouldn't let me hear the end of it... Hehe.

mission.line: Still getting overwhelmed by work, huh? ...Hmph, you're as clumsy as ever. Guess I'll come help too.

mission_complete.line: Mission accomplished. Why don't you leave the rest to me and take a break?

touch.line: Hm? Oh, sorry. I didn't realize you called...

unlock.line: Receiving everyone's blessings is truly a deeply moving experience. But for now, let's set everything else aside and partake of our sweet bliss. After all, you're not just a spectator anymore – we're in this ride together, hehe~

win_mvp.line: I'm perfectly calm. Aren't you the one excited over the victory?

battle.line: Improvisation, expertise, and execution – that's what it's all about!

detail.line: Look who's here to see me again! Heehee, I know you would, since you really like me. Likewise, there's a lot about you I like – and dislike.

drop_descrip.line: Agano-class light cruiser number four – Sakawa.

expedition.line: You can stop staring at me already~ After all, we have to go welcome the commission fleet back, don't we?

feeling1.line: Didn't I tell you to leave me alone already? I don't like people who don't listen to what I say.

feeling2.line: Wow, we meet again! By the way, doesn't it feel like we've been bumping into each other every day since I arrived at the port? Well, you're the Commander, so I suppose there's nothing strange about that. Ehehe~♪

feeling3.line: Oh my~♪ Did you come to see me again? Ehehe, Noshiro's gonna be so jealous if she finds out. Well, sit down already. I'll go bring out the tea and snacks – these are some of my favorites from the Sakura Islands!

feeling4.line: Of course I know why you come to see me every day~ But isn't it a bit boring if I steal your thunder? At times like these... you're supposed to proclaim your passionate love for me at the top of your lungs, right~?

feeling5.line: W-wow, you really went and did it... Hearing it up-close like that is actually a bit embarrassing. Or, were you just teasing me? Did you know, I've been serious about you this whooole time?

headtouch.line: We patting people's heads now?

home.line: Welcome back! You won, right? I mean, obviously, you did. Otherwise it'd be tactless of me to greet you like this~♪

hp_warning.line: I won't have the wind taken out of my sails here!

login.line: Gooood morning! ...Oh, am I supposed to be all graceful and say "well met" or something?

lose.line: They actually beat us? How's that even possible?!

mail.line: Your mail's here. Mind if I read it?

main1.line: Oh my, were you just sneaking a peek at me? I don't blame you, since I'm just soooo cute~ You'll never get tired of staring at me, right? Heehee♪

main2.line: I can handle anything you throw at me. I'll breeze through anything, whether it's a sortie or a bunch of paperwork.

main3.line: Not to be a glutton, but, since I've been working hard, can't you spare me an itty bitty treat? Haha, how about something sweet?

mission.line: You sure have a lot of work to get through... Even if I lend you a hand, it'll probably still take a while, huh~

mission_complete.line: That's it for the paperwork! Let's see if you left anything out... Ah, found a spot! Gimme a sec to look everything through!

profile.line: I'm the Agano-class light cruiser, Sakawa! I wasn't able to do a whole lot during that war, but... I'm so grateful to you and all my friends here at the port for giving me another chance to fight! Mhm!

propose.line: Ehehe, did you steal another glance at me just before you put the ring on my finger? ...Y-you didn't? Geez, and here I am trying to show you what a maiden in love looks like...

skill.line: I'll show you what I'm made of!

touch.line: You were staring at me just now, weren't you? I bet you were~

touch2.line: An accident, huh... I never said you had to apologize!

unlock.line: I'm Sakawa, Agano-class light cruiser♪ And you're the Commander? I see~ I get why Noshiro is so into you. I am, too!

upgrade.line: Now that's a power boost. Best way to test it would be with a real battle, no?

win_mvp.line: Victoryyy! Now's a good time to congratulate me, no? I'd say it is. Heehee.

detail.line: Happiness is a mouthful of sweets from the Sakura Islands~ Don't you also want to share a bit of this happiness with Sakawa? Here you go then~♪

drop_descrip.line: Welcome! Heehee, you came because you were just so keen to see me, am I right? Then I've got to make you feel real welcome♪

expedition.line: We're giving Sakura confections to the commission team as a thank-you reward, right?

feeling5.line: M-my lips...? Even I'll get embarrassed if you suddenly try to kiss me, you know...? But, maybe we can go somewhere else later and–– Huh? There's something stuck to the corner of my lips?! Wh-what about the kiss...???

headtouch.line: I feel like I'm on top of the world~

home.line: Sorry to keep you waiting~ I've brought you your piping-hot tea! ...Oh my, I seem to have forgotten the teacups! Oh, um, what should I do...?

login.line: Come get your delicious and fluffy dango~ One for you, one for me, and we can share the last one~♪ Ehehe, goood morning~!

main1.line: Dangos are sooo good~ I could eat them for three days straight! But after that... I'd probably get sick of them and want some yatsuhashi instead~♪

main2.line: The stuff you ordered? ...Oh! I think I ate it by accident! Oh, silly me!

main3.line: Since we're trying to make our pop-up café the best it can be, I have to memorize the entire menu~ Heehee, I'll be making a whole lot of goodies later~

touch.line: Alright, what would you like to order?

touch2.line: Well, um... I suppose you just couldn't help it because of how cute I am, right...?

unlock.line: Welcome! Heehee, you came because you were just so keen to see me, am I right? Then I've got to make you feel real welcome♪

detail.line: Aww, you came to see me again! Are you sure you want to spend time with me, and not Noshiro? Heheh, do you feel guilty? It's okay~ We can always make it up to Noshiro after we have fun together♪

drop_descrip.line: Wow, look how far you pursued me. You must have really, reeeally wanted to see me, huh, Commander~? Heheh, want a popsicle?

expedition.line: Ooh, you were just looking at me, weren't you? I was juuust about to let you know that the commission team's probably back by now♪

feeling5.line: Isn't it easier to tell someone how much you love, love, love them when you're alone together? Ehehe, of course it is~ You've been trying to say it for a while now, right, Commander? I'll let you go first. Say it loud enough for me to hear, now♪

home.line: Have a nice, cool popsicle after that heated battle! Heheh, was someone looking forward to an indirect kiss?

login.line: A cool summer's day in the forest~ One for me, one for you, and halfsies for the bears~ Ehehe, welcome back!♪

main1.line: Whoa! Commander, you're soaked. Oh, I know; were you and Noshiro shooting water guns? Ahaha!♪ She never holds back when it comes to play.

main2.line: Swimsuits aren't just for the beach. They work great for swimming in rivers, too. Hm? You aren't going to swim, Commander?

main3.line: There's going to be a big fireworks show later, right? I'll save room for the feast later♪

touch.line: Would you like one?

touch2.line: I-is this because I'm in a swimsuit...?

unlock.line: Wow, look how far you pursued me. You must have really, reeeally wanted to see me, huh, Commander~? Heheh, want a popsicle?

win_mvp.line: I'm strong, aren't I? Ahaha, a swimsuit won't get in the way of my fighting!

detail.line: Doesn't it make people really nervous to sing and perform in these huge venues? I'm not, though, since I'm with you~

drop_descrip.line: Laaa la-laaa♪ Oh, Commander. Here to see me again? I know you're madly in love and want to watch me practice, but people will think you're weird if you keep coming and going constantly. Heehee♪

feeling5.line: You come to watch every day 'cause you love me so much, right? Heheh, we're all alone right now, so you can say it as loud as you want. ...Whoa?! I-impressive... *blushes*

home.line: Party prep, strategy meetings, exercises... You're so busy, Commander. Should you reeeally spend so much time watching me practice?♪

login.line: What am I practicing right now? Heheh, just guess, Commander♪

main1.line: Agano's dress is so mature, isn't it? ...Mine, too? Well, I doubt it's like hers~

main2.line: Just between you and me, I've been practicing my piano instead of singing. Heheh, did I trick you?

main3.line: Ah! You were just staring at me!♪ Could it be... You brought me treats? Woohoo!

touch.line: Do you know a lot about music, Commander?

touch2.line: Are you doing that because I look a little more... mature today?

unlock.line: Laaa la-laaa♪ Oh, Commander. Here to see me again? I know you're madly in love and want to watch me practice, but people will think you're weird if you keep coming and going constantly. Heehee♪

win_mvp.line: After I finish my jaw-dropping performance... should I bow for the crowd, you think?

battle.line: I have to do well in this battle!

detail.line: I'm a bit bored...

drop_descrip.line: First ship of the {namecode:53}-class heavy cruisers, {namecode:53}.

expedition.line: Commander! Ah... that hurts! I'm fine... I just wanted to tell you that commissions have been completed.

feeling1.line: (Furutaka ignores you as she passes by)

feeling2.line: Kako acts like that because she holds herself as the role model for heavy cruisers, but she's actually very gentle.

feeling3.line: Commander~ Oww! ...Ehehe... Thanks, I almost fell again. I'm trying to pay more attention so that I don't trip as much, but I was so happy that I let my guard down.

feeling4.line: Yeah... Being able to live with Kako and seeing my sisters from the Mikawa and 6th Fleet was always a dream of mine. Commander, you've made my dream come true. That's why... I'll do anything for you!

feeling5.line: If you're okay with this... then I don't mind, Commander. But... I've never been in a relationship before, so I don't know what it's like. Can you teach me?

home.line: Commander, I tripped again... Do you have a band-aid somewhere?

login.line: Commander, please be more careful when you open the door...

lose.line: We lost... Too bad...

mail.line: Sorry, Commander... I tripped and fell while getting the mail and now it's all wrinkled...

main1.line: Commander, Kako doesn't really hate you, so don't take it too personally.

main2.line: Um... because I'm not very smart, maybe Kako should take my place at meetings instead...

main3.line: Ouch...! Ahh, I'm fine... I just nodded off and bumped my head.

mission.line: A new mission, huh? Seems like it might be a bit tricky.

mission_complete.line: I bumped into something while getting the rewards... Oww...

profile.line: I'm the Furutaka-class heavy... Err, just call me Furutaka! I may not look it, but I participated in the First Battle of the Solomon Sea! I also helped my sister Aoba out a lot! In the end though, I rushed too far ahead and didn't make it back myself... Ehehe...

propose.line: I've never felt like this in my life before... But as long as I'm with you, I'll be able to feel this way more and more, right? I can't wait!

touch.line: What's up?

touch2.line: I never thought you'd take an interest in me, Commander... Frankly, I'm a bit happy~

unlock.line: Ah! Sorry for bumping into you... Huh? You're the Commander?! F-Furutaka, first ship of the Furutaka class, reporting for duty! Can you please forget what just happened? Ehehe...

upgrade.line: Thanks, Commander!

win_mvp.line: Eh? I'm the MVP?

battle.line: I'm much stronger than before!

drop_descrip.line: What's wrong, Commander? Why are you staring at me like that? My body? Yes, some things seem to have gotten bigger... Want to take a look?

expedition.line: It sure is nice weather, isn't it? I feel like taking a nap. Oh? The girls are back from commission~!

login.line: Commander, did you have a good rest? Me? Umm... I slept very well.

main1.line: I might have changed, but I'm still the same Furutaka, Commander!

main2.line: Ouch! Ah... I just bumped my head again...

main3.line: My hair feels a bit messy... maybe Kako can teach me how to tie it up.

touch.line: Commander~! Want to take a nap together?

touch2.line: Since you like me so much... I suppose it's okay~

unlock.line: What's wrong, Commander? Why are you staring at me like that? My body? Yes, some things seem to have gotten bigger... Want to take a look?

battle.line: In any case, I shall set the standard for heavy cruisers!

detail.line: If you want to say something, just give it to me straight!

drop_descrip.line: Second ship of {namecode:53}-class heavy cruisers, {namecode:54}.

expedition.line: The commission fleet has returned. Do you plan to sit here and wait for them to bring the resources to you?

feeling1.line: It seems that you'll never be able to earn my respect.

feeling2.line: I suppose I'll have to teach you how to behave in a respectable manner, Commander. Earning my acknowledgement is no easy feat, so I hope you've steeled yourself.

feeling3.line: To make this pose, put your hands here... What? You're embarrassed by me touching you? ...I'm blushing? Wh-what nonsense!

feeling4.line: You still have a long way to go, but I suppose you're doing well for now... Just how long do you plan to cling to me anyway? How despicable... it seems like you haven't learned anything yet.

feeling5.line: You've been learning quickly lately... About that... hm... If you want to experiment with me, I'm ready.

home.line: Taking a break? Well... since you put in your fair share of work, why don't you set the rest of these files aside for later?

login.line: Good timing, I just finished sorting your documents. Can you actually finish these?

lose.line: Tsk... Can't you work a bit harder?

mail.line: Mail's here. I'm surprised you have so many friends.

main1.line: This fleet is quite impressive, except for their commander.

main2.line: You made a mistake here. And here. Do I have to tell you how to do everything?

main3.line: I wonder how {namecode:55} is doing right now...

mission.line: New missions, Commander. Surely you can handle these.

mission_complete.line: So you can work hard as well, huh? Here are the rewards.

profile.line: Second ship of the {namecode:53}-class heavy cruisers, {namecode:54}! I was perhaps the first real heavy cruiser made for my country. Despite contributing to the first Battle of the Solomon Sea, I took too many risks and ended up being sunk by a submarine... My personality? I'm only like this when I'm around you. Open your eyes and learn the advantages of a real heavy cruiser!

propose.line: You've passed, but just barely! This is only the beginning... there's still a long way to go! What about me? If you want to spend the rest of your life with me, I'm ready!

skill.line: Let me show my true strength!

touch.line: Are you an idiot?

touch2.line: Why you little... Hello? Could I speak with the Military Police?

unlock.line: Second ship of the Furutaka-class, Kako, ready for orders. Why don't you show me whether you're worthy or not.

upgrade.line: I suppose I should thank you for this.

win_mvp.line: To think that you could do this much... I suppose I can offer you a word of praise.

detail.line: What do you want? Surely you didn't come to get lectured.

drop_descrip.line: Performance upgraded, improvements complete. This way I can finally... *cough* Oh, it's nothing, Commander. I must simply be more strict with you in the future. Are you ready for your psychological examination?

login.line: You're five minutes late, Commander!

main1.line: This is a step up from before, but you still messed up here. Are you doing this on purpose to get me angry?

main2.line: What am I writing? Your agenda, of course. Without it, you'd just slide right back to your old habits.

touch.line: I'll be here any time you have questions.

unlock.line: Performance upgraded, improvements complete. This way I can finally... *cough* Oh, it's nothing, Commander. I must simply be more strict with you in the future. Are you ready for your psychological examination?

win_mvp.line: Did you see that? This is the true power of our fleet!

battle.line: You're far too naive if you think  you can escape Aoba's eyes!

detail.line: What's up? You know I charge for intel.

drop_descrip.line: First ship of the {namecode:55}-class heavy cruisers, {namecode:55}.

expedition.line: "Come see a magnificent view of girls hard at work!" ...Okay! Commander, let's pack some snacks and head to port to conduct some interviews!

feeling1.line: Maybe I should go conduct some interviews overseas...

feeling2.line: Commander, could you tell me how it feels to have such a large har- I mean, fleet?

feeling3.line: It's been a while since since I've been stationed here, so I've managed to get some good information from everyone. At first they thought you were a shady person, but you seemed to have earned their trust. Good for you!

feeling4.line: I've made my fair share of mistakes, so I thought I could help by leaving something to commemorate everyone's hard work. Sorry for saying something so unlike me... but, you made me drop my guard. Now, you have to answer my questions!

feeling5.line: Alright, I've decided. For all my precious friends here, I will record their lives! Does that include you? Oh you, don't you already know the answer to that?

home.line: Commander~ of the girls out on commission right now... who's your favorite?

hp_warning.line: It's not very funny when I'm the one on the news.

login.line: Hehe~ Commander, I saw that~!

lose.line: I... Aoba... shouldn't be getting upset over this!

mail.line: Commander, you're way to careless with information... Take it, it's your mail!

main1.line: I believe that hard work pays off, you know. Eh? Why was I following you yesterday? I don't ever recall doing anything like that~

main2.line: Say, Commander. If you let me interview you, I'll share some juicy gossip with you. Like... which girls might be looking your way~

main3.line: It's sure hard getting a scoop... Maybe... I should make some news myself!

mission.line: Missions? I'm just here to record your heroic image, Commander. Oh? I need to go too?

mission_complete.line: Commander, stop lazing around. Go get your rewards and let me take a picture!

profile.line: Hai hai! The name's Aoba! I spent most of my days in the 6th Fleet, took part in many battles with my sisters, and did my best to survive until the end. Let's drop this boring topic, shall we? I was a writer for the Navy once, so I've picked up a thing or two. Commander, anything juicy going on around you lately?

propose.line: Just to be clear, I'm not good at this kind of stuff... so don't expect me to say anything romantic... ever! Well, maybe just once... Um... I... l-l-love... you!

touch.line: Ah, a good idea, finally! This will definitely make the front page!

touch2.line: Commander... It's not wise to mess with reporters.

unlock.line: Hmm, hmm... I can smell it. This fleet is going to make the headlines! So you're the Commander, huh? Just let me, Aoba, gather all the information without holding back!

upgrade.line: I think I'm getting closer to my next big scoop. Thanks, Commander~!

win_mvp.line: Okay, time to get a quick word from the losing side. Eh? Leaving already?

battle.line: Everyone! Stay alert, protect yourself, and don't be reckless!

detail.line: Health comes first!

drop_descrip.line: Second ship of the {namecode:55}-class heavy cruisers, {namecode:56}.

expedition.line: Commander, since you didn't go yourself, you should at least welcome back the girls who worked hard on the commission!

feeling1.line: It's not like I care what you do...

feeling2.line: Did you clean your room, Commander? Did you lock the door? Have you forgotten anything?

feeling3.line: Don't be too hard on my sister... She actually has a lot of guilt buried in her heart.

feeling4.line: I don't really like lecturing people... but I've gotten used to lecturing my sister, and you don't seem to mind. Eh? You actually appreciate it? Then... I guess I'll keep it up...

feeling5.line: Aoba is always so impatient! But she's my big sis, and she's very important to me. Just like you, Commander. You're precious to me as well!

home.line: Commander, it's important to balance work and rest. Since you just got back, why not take a quick break?

hp_warning.line: Don't panic. Get into formation!

login.line: Welcome back, Commander! Did you get enough to eat? If you're still hungry, I can cook something for you!

lose.line: We need to call a meeting and review this performance...

mail.line: Commander, do I have to tell you to check your mail every single time?

main1.line: Did you rest well, Commander? Health comes first!

main2.line: I'm not sure if Aoba is getting enough rest... Please make sure to check up on her!

main3.line: Work hard, play hard! That's the secret to a happy life!

mission.line: Commander, work will only pile up if you keep putting it off!

mission_complete.line: Commander, leaving your rewards there won't make them grow.

profile.line: Good day, I'm Kinugasa! I was in the 6th Fleet with my sister Aoba before it was disbanded. We fought together in many battles, like Wake Island, the Coral Sea, and the Solomon Islands. I'm not as lucky as her though... Anyways, Commander, try not to overwork yourself! Rest is important too!

propose.line: Jeez, Commander. Your sleeves and collar are messy as always, even for such an important occasion. I'll lecture you later~ let's carry on with the ceremony!

touch.line: Commander, did you also come to wind down with some light stretching?

touch2.line: Please take a seat, Commander. We're going to discuss fleet discipline.

unlock.line: Pleased to meet you! I'm Kinugasa. Have you been eating and sleeping well,  Commander? Don't be like my big sis... Speaking of which, is she also here by any chance?

upgrade.line: Being wasteful is no good, Commander.

win_mvp.line: Everyone, don't let your guard down just because we won!

battle.line: I've already seen through your tricks, hehe.

detail.line: Knowledge is power. Not only in battle, but for everything else as well... right?

drop_descrip.line: Tone-class heavy cruiser number two – Chikuma.

expedition.line: Hm... According to my seaplanes, it seems like the commissions team is almost here.

feeling1.line: I'm sorry. I'm not sure I can deal with someone like you...

feeling2.line: Let's see what my seaplanes' eyes have captured for me this time.

feeling3.line: Oh, are you curious about the intel I've gathered? Mm, like how everyone at the port feels about you? Just kidding, of course♪

feeling4.line: Mm... Even if there's something you really want to know, I can't just tell you... Right, how about this? You listen to one of my requests, and I'll tell you one thing you want to know in exchange. Hehehe♪

feeling5.line: Hehe. As payment for the secret I told you, you'll be taking me out on a date♪ ...No refunds allowed, of course.

headtouch.line: Are you trying to get my ears to spring up? Hehe~

home.line: Good work out there. Why don't you get started on the combat report? This experience will become the foundation for your next victory, after all.

hp_warning.line: This is nothing... This won't make me fall behind...!

login.line: Let's see... Well, it looks like you're right on time. Welcome back, Commander.

lose.line: It's because I wasn't able to get enough info on them...

mail.line: There's some new mail for you. Please make sure not to look over any new information.

main1.line: You want to know what people are saying about you? ...You know, if you're that curious, I suggest that you dig around a bit yourself.

main2.line: This is some juicy info here... Hm, I bet Aoba would love to hear about this~

main3.line: Just like the "eyes" on my seaplanes need maintenance, our eyes should be maintained properly as well. That way, we can make sure they work well when they need to.

mission.line: Commander, I don't think it's a good habit to neglect your duties.

mission_complete.line: Mission rewards... Lots of things here, so I'll leave the accounting to you♪

profile.line: I'm the Tone-class heavy cruiser, Chikuma. I can carry more seaplanes than my heavy cruiser counterparts—you could say I've got plenty of eyes in the sky. I'm good at the art of knowing things, don't you think so? Hehehe.

propose.line: Are you disappointed that I'm not surprised at all? Don't be, I really am, you know? It's just that I'm so happy, it far exceeds any surprise I might've felt~♡ Hehehe~♪

skill.line: Knowledge is the key to victory♪

touch.line: If you want some help, you should organize the information first.

touch2.line: Looks like I've grasped another weakness of yours, Commander♪

unlock.line: I am Chikuma. Pleased to make your acquaintance. Well, that might be the case, but I already know a bit about you... My, are you curious? You'll find out before long, hehe.

upgrade.line: My reconnaissance abilities have grown even sharper~

win_mvp.line: As long as the intel is correct, victory is guaranteed... Ehe♪

battle.line: Let's see the fruits of my daily training! All guns, open fire!

detail.line: Commander, acquiring intel is the first step to victory.

drop_descrip.line: First ship of the {namecode:63}-class heavy cruisers, {namecode:63}.

expedition.line: Commission complete! Is everyone putting forward their best effort?

feeling1.line: Stop slacking off, Commander!

feeling2.line: It is not unusual for a weaker force to defeat a stronger one in a naval battle. Victory or defeat is often decided by good judgment and split-second decision making. We must be thorough in our training in order to cultivate these abilities.

feeling3.line: Commander, remember to take breaks as needed. Your efficiency will be worse if you run out of stamina... Lap... pillow? It's fine by me... but will it really help you recover faster?

feeling4.line: I saw your light on, so I came to check on you. I had no idea you'd still be awake; even being a workaholic should have its limits! Come on, I'm not leaving until you fall asleep.

feeling5.line: Commander, I've finished processing those files. It's the end of the day, so why don't we grab dinner together? ... ... How's it taste?

headtouch.line: ... Please do this kind of thing to destroyers, not me...

home.line: This method of relaxing is inefficient. Why not try some of my specially-made energy drink?

login.line: Would you like some homemade pancakes, Commander?

lose.line: It's all because I neglected my daily training... Everyone, I'm sorry...

mail.line: New mail has arrived! Is this the latest training manual?

main1.line: If I get another chance... I'd like to pet Hatsukaze's head again.

main2.line: I've put on weight?! Commander... there are some things that even you shouldn't say.

main3.line: Bergall?! Phew... you were talking about someone else.

mission.line: Commander, please don't hesitate to ask for help!

mission_complete.line: Don't call it a day after finishing just one mission!

profile.line: I am {namecode:63}, of the Sakura Empire's {namecode:63}-class heavy cruisers. I participated in both the glorious victory of the Java Sea and the humiliating defeat at Leyte Gulf. Afterwards, I was struck by a torpedo and pursued by submarines. In the end, I could only watch from the South as my nation surrendered. It is hard to say whether that was fortune or misfortune. Anyways, Commander, you can always talk to me if something is on your mind.

propose.line: Commander, your body is no longer just yours alone. Make sure you take care of yourself properly... for me, okay?

skill.line: Burn this final sight into your memory!

touch.line: I'm supervising the destroyers' training right now. Please save it for later if it's not an emergency.

touch2.line: ... Commander, have some self-respect...

unlock.line: I am, {namecode:63}, first ship of the {namecode:63}-class heavy cruisers. Commander, is there anything I can help you with?

upgrade.line: I won't let such a small improvement get to my head.

win_mvp.line: This victory was made possible by everyone's efforts, not just my own!

battle.line: Hmph. Another bunch of blind idiots.

detail.line: What is it? Do you want to be my lackey?

drop_descrip.line: Second ship of the {namecode:63}-class heavy cruisers, {namecode:64}.

expedition.line: Mmhmm. It's important to work hard! Well, unless you're me!

feeling1.line: I wasn't talking to you!

feeling2.line: Commander, you're going to be unpopular forever if you don't pay attention to your appearance.

feeling3.line: Hard work? Not at all. A genius like me doesn't need to work hard. I get stronger just by breathing.

feeling4.line: Huh? Commander? What are you doing at the training area so late? You were worried about me? I-I was just taking a walk because I was bored. You heard cannon fire? Th-that was...

feeling5.line: I can't be honest with myself... because I can't stand the thought of people seeing me work hard... except for you, Commander. No matter who I become, surely you would...

home.line: Good work. However, you won't be able to catch up to me with even ten times the effort!

login.line: I-I'm not training.. I'm just... being lazy and laughing at the other girls as they work up a sweat.

lose.line: Damn it... just what went wrong?

mail.line: You want your mail? Only if you beg me nicely~

main1.line: My sisters in the Fifth Fleet? I miss them a bit... err, just once in a blue moon!

main2.line: Ghosts on the training ground? W-what are you, a kid? Who'd believe something like that?

main3.line: Salt Lake City? I'm going to show her that Lady Luck doesn't bless the same person forever!

mission.line: Only an idiot would be unable to complete such an easy mission.

mission_complete.line: Heheh, looks like you couldn't have done this mission without me!

profile.line: I am {namecode:64}, second ship of the {namecode:63}-class heavy cruisers. Though I said second ship, I am no "little sister". I fought my way all around the Pacific, and served as flagship multiple times. I am greatest heavy cruiser - bear witness to my elegance and power!

propose.line: I know I have a hard time being honest with myself, but... I'll try my best to make you the happiest person in the world! I swear my name on it!

touch.line: Commander, are you feeling lonely? I just happen to have more spare time than I know what to do with~

touch2.line: I-idiot... you're that fascinated with me? At least tell me in advance...

unlock.line: I'm {namecode:64}, the first post-treaty heavy cruiser from the Sakura Empire. My design is the very definition of perfection! I'll be in your care from here on out!

upgrade.line: I'm even more flawless than before!

win_mvp.line: Hehe, this is only normal, of course.

detail.line: A gift? It's not like I asked you to go and buy this for... Hahaaah, I guess you're so used to running around and getting things for me that you couldn't help yourself! Well... Sure, I'll take it!

drop_descrip.line: Howzit? Now that my retrofit's all done, don't I look even more perfect than before? Maybe now, our ever-so-reserved Commander here will be super impressed by my new abilities~ Wh-what do you mean I've been staying up too late training with my rigging? W-we're not gonna talk about that!

expedition.line: The commission team is really working hard. Heheh, hurry and go check out those rewards.

home.line: Thanks for your hard work~ Oh, you brought back tons of spoils... O-of course, you are working, like, fifteen times harder than before. I know you're catching up to me... *blushes*

login.line: The perfect Nachi put together your daily schedule for you! Now, let's get some work done!

lose.line: I don't know what went wrong, but... Let's run away, Commander!

main1.line: Lately, I've been running into Haguro early in the mornings... Hm? You say I should train somewhere else? Good idea... Instead of the Sakura Empire dorm, I should come to your—no, I obviously can NOT do that!

main2.line: You're feeling anxious? Hmm... Why not try working or crafting something to take your mind off of it? Like, say, origami?

main3.line: Whoa, you're just openly slacking off... Heheh, then I'll just... NOT join you, obviously! C'mon, Commander! There's work to be done!

mission.line: These missions are so simple, they could be done instantly. I know I could, but surely even you can, Commander!

mission_complete.line: You didn't even need my help! Heheh♪

touch.line: Feeling lonely, Commander? Heheh, same here... Uh, I mean, I'm just so darn bored!

touch2.line: Hm? What's up... Hyah?! H-hey, did you just do that on purpose?!

unlock.line: Howzit? Now that my retrofit's all done, don't I look even more perfect than before? Maybe now, our ever-so-reserved Commander here will be super impressed by my new abilities~ Wh-what do you mean I've been staying up too late training with my rigging? W-we're not gonna talk about that!

win_mvp.line: Get on your knees and beg, and maybe I'll forgive you♪ See how tolerant I am?

battle.line: Everyone, advance! The fortunes of war are with us!

detail.line: No matter how much you stare at me, I won't get any stronger... Commander, wouldn't it be better for me to sortie?

drop_descrip.line: Myoukou-class heavy cruiser number three - Ashigara

expedition.line: Commander, the commission fleet has returned.

feeling1.line: Commander, if I am a nuisance to you, please let me know...

feeling2.line: Commander, you wish to survey my room? That's fine... but please give me a moment to tidy up first.

feeling3.line: U-um.. I'm not very dexterous, but I'd like you to have this origami crane that I made... though I'm not sure you can really call it a crane. I've always wanted to do something like this...

feeling4.line: Commander, what's the special occasion? You even brought my toiletry and wash towel to my bedside today... woooahh! It's already this late? I completely overslept!

feeling5.line: Sorry, Commander... when you weren't here, I started feeling uneasy and... before I knew it, I had already folded a hundred paper cranes... Um, that's weird, isn't it...

home.line: Commander, it's fine to rest every now and then, but please don't go overboard with it.

hp_warning.line: This is the hour of reckoning! Chaaarge!!

login.line: You're finally back... Commander, would you spare some time to spar with me?

lose.line: I... I can keep fighting!

mail.line: The postman has already finished their job. Commander, why don't you go take a look?

main1.line: "Let your victories not be decided by the strength of your equipment, but by your abilities." That is what Myoukou taught me.

main2.line: "Let those who think of the Sakura Empire also think of your name?" Hmm... Yes, that is a goal that I indeed have been working towards.

main3.line: Commander, thank you for training with me every day. I'll continue to refine myself!

mission.line: There are still a lot of missions left... Commander, I don't quite understand how to do some of these. I hope I'm not dragging you down...

mission_complete.line: Mission complete! Commander, why don't you go check the rewards first?

profile.line: I am Ashigara, third ship of the Myoukou-class heavy cruisers. I had the privilege and glory of representing the Sakura Empire in the Royals' Coronation Fleet Review. My habitability? W-well... some things must be sacrificed in order to survive on the battlefield.

propose.line: Commander, sneak attacks are against the rules... There's no one else around, right? Th-then... maybe it's okay to cling a little bit. Commander, you're so warm...

touch.line: I got this from Myoukou. I often record what she says, so I can listen to her words when I have free time. Eh? Is that weird?

touch2.line: Ack...! U-um... I need to ask Myoukou about what I should do in this situation...

unlock.line: Ashigara, reporting for duty. Commander, my blade shall cut down all your enemies.

upgrade.line: Yes! With this, I'm full of energy!

win_mvp.line: N-not bad... I suppose... *blushes*

battle.line: My appearances shouldn't affect my combat performance... In any case, let's advance!

detail.line: "There's no need to overexert yourself." That's what Myoukou told me, anyway. Commander, hopefully you're not pushing yourself too hard?

drop_descrip.line: Phew... I finally managed to fix my dress... but I just can't seem to get used to it. Commander, how does my dress look? It's not strange, is it?

home.line: Phew... Let's take a break, Commander.

login.line: You'd like to train with me? Of course! Even dressed like this, I have no intention of losing!

main1.line: It's hard to put my hair up like this... Thanks to Myoukou's help, I was somehow able to manage...

main2.line: I can't sit here doing nothing all the time... Commander, if there's anything you need help with, please give me the order!

main3.line: This is how you do the lap pillow thing, right? I heard that it would help you recover from fatigue...

touch.line: Commander, is something bothering you?

touch2.line: Umm... C-Commander, Myoukou said that you shouldn't do stuff like this...

unlock.line: Phew... I finally managed to fix my dress... but I just can't seem to get used to it. Commander, how does my dress look? It's not strange, is it?

detail.line: I originally planned to bring headphones to listen to the soothing sound of Myoukou's... Err, I meant to say music! But, it might be more calming to just listen to the waves.

drop_descrip.line: This whole "fashion coordination" concept is still a bit hard for me to wrap my head around, so I'm glad Nachi helped me pick out a swimsuit. Now, I just need to... Hey, Commander! Open your mouth! H-huh?! But this is what Nachi told me to do... is there some sort of problem?!

home.line: I heard there are lots of crabs hiding on this beach. I wonder if I can snag a couple...

login.line: The cool, pristine waves splashing across my skin... What a comforting sensation.

main1.line: Under the azure skies, the seagulls and crabs also thrive... the summer seaside also has life of its own.

main2.line: I promised to play beach volleyball with Myoukou and Nachi, but we have an odd number of people... Commander, why don't you join us?

main3.line: Myoukou, I brought my training equipment. Today's regimen is... Oh, I don't need it today?

touch.line: Commander, did you want to take a break? ...Ahem! H-h-how about a l-l-lap pillow?

touch2.line: Eep?! ...Oh, I had cream stuck on me? Th-thank you, Commander...

unlock.line: This whole "fashion coordination" concept is still a bit hard for me to wrap my head around, so I'm glad Nachi helped me pick out a swimsuit. Now, I just need to... Hey, Commander! Open your mouth! H-huh?! But this is what Nachi told me to do... is there some sort of problem?!

battle.line: Give me a bit, and I'll get to it!

detail.line: So sleepy... Hm? You wanna know why...? Erm, it's none of your business... Err, I guess it's not right for me to hide stuff from you, Commander... Alright, I'll fess up! I pulled an all-nighter playing video games!

drop_descrip.line: Myoukou-class heavy cruiser number four – Haguro.

expedition.line: Commissions completed. What are you staring at me like an idiot for? Let's head out and greet'em.

feeling1.line: ...I'll take care of you right here, right now. Just kidding, I'd hate to lower everyone else's morale around here.

feeling2.line: *Yaaaaawn*... So tired... Don't you feel tired at all? Don't force yourself too much, or ya'll set a bad example for other girls who'd follow the lead and overwork themselves.

feeling3.line: Well, it's time to keep watch over the Commander's sleeping hours... Huh? Y-you still haven't gone to sleep?! This wasn't supposed to... I-I'm, um... looking for someone to play video games together!

feeling4.line: Commander, I apologize for having lied to you... Truth is, I didn't pull an all-nighter playing video games, I was actually carrying out some late-night missions... D-does it matter what my excuse is? I could blame a tengu, and nobody would believe me anyway!

feeling5.line: Ahaha, Commander, it's not good to intrude on people at this hour. But, um... if you'd like, why don't you join me in playing some video games? Not like there are any missions left to take care of, and it doesn't look like you're able to fall asleep anyhow... I-it's not a bother for you, is it?

headtouch.line: Hmm...?

home.line: *Yaaawn*. Oh, you're back... Guess I'm done for now... Wait, there's more to do, isn't there...

hp_warning.line: Who cares about miracles, so long as I can protect my friends...!

login.line: Mornin'. Oh, you're already here? Aren't you the real diligent type...

lose.line: So frickin' annoying... Ugh, we're backing off for now.

mail.line: You've got some letters. Yeah, yeah. I'll go get'em for you.

main1.line: Ya need me to tidy up around here? Sure thing. Then, if you'd please leave the office for around fifteen minutes...

main2.line: *Yaaaaawn* I'm beat... Having Myoukou lecture me first thing in the morning, then having Ashigara fret over me... Well, of course I know it's for my sake, but...

main3.line: Hmm? Ya heading out? Then I'll—what? You don't mind if I come with you, right...?

mission.line: Here're your missions. I'm here focusing on the ones you've assigned me, so good luck on yours.

mission_complete.line: Hm? You've already finished your missions? Nice, good stuff.

profile.line: Myoukou-class heavy cruiser, Haguro here. As you can see, I'm just a normal heavy cruiser who made things happen during night battles and stuff in the Great War. A miracle ship...? I mean, I've been called that before, but... it's embarrassing to be called that to my face...

propose.line: A-a pledge ring?! This has to be some kind of joke... No way. I mean, I'm perfectly fine with it, but are you fine with me...? I-I mean... I'm a total night owl...

skill.line: See if you can spot me!

touch.line: Hmhmm~ Oh, 'sup Commander?

touch2.line: What the...???

unlock.line: Guess you're the Commander, huh... Wassup? I'm part of the team now or whatever. You just mind your own biz and I'll mind mine.

upgrade.line: So as long as you put something trendy on... Don't mind me.

win_mvp.line: Piece of cake. Not much else for me to say, really.

detail.line: My skirt? Yeah, I'm wearing a skirt today... My skirt! S-stop, don't look! ...Ugh, what am I supposed to do about this now...

drop_descrip.line: Ow! That freakin' stings... Can't believe I actually slipped on the stairs and hit my foot. Just how clumsy am I? ...Oh, Commander? Uh, welcome?

expedition.line: Commissions completed. What are you staring at me for, let's go greet'em already. ...You don't need to worry about me, I'll be fine. Jeez.

home.line: You alright? Not hurt anywhere, are ya? Ehehe, I was just thinking that we could slack off together if you had happened to injure your foot as well.

login.line: Zzz... Oh no, I almost fell asleep while sitting down... Ah, Commander! Welcome back.

main1.line: Everyone's working together to clean up this pop-up café. It's designed specially to entertain you to the fullest, so everyone's working diligently... Perhaps too diligently, since that's why I slipped and hurt my foot.

main2.line: Musashi dotes on people so much, she's bound to spoil a bunch of girls rotten... I've always been rotten to the core, so I'll be fine, but... What about you, Commander? Would you like to be spoiled rotten?

main3.line: As our exemplar, Mikasa really is so frickin' cool... Compared to her, I'm just a clumsy brat... Ahaha...

touch.line: You want to treat my injury? T-thanks a lot... *blush*

touch2.line: W-what are you planning on doing to me...?

unlock.line: Ow! That freakin' stings... Can't believe I actually slipped on the stairs and hit my foot. Just how clumsy am I? ...Oh, Commander? Uh, welcome?

detail.line: If I move, you're gonna see everything... No, I don't want you to see my bits! Mmrgh!

drop_descrip.line: H-hey, help me out! ...No, I didn't come in here for fun. When I finished my security duty last night, I got to thinking about how I was going to give you chocolate for Valentine's and fell asleep. When I woke up, I was stuffed in this thing...

feeling5.line: Good! Keep it up! Almost there! Aaand, failed again. Hmm... I'd feel better if you could at least take the chocolate, but it's just not gonna work out. Ahaha! Thanks for trying, Commander.

home.line: Really missed my chance to give out chocolate, huh? ...Hm? N-nobody said you were the one I was most excited to give chocolate to, okay, Commander?

login.line: Man, is there any way to get out of this thing... Hm? You'll stay with me until help comes, Commander? ...For real?

main2.line: Atago, did you bring my sunglasses?

main1.line: Commander, even if you're at school, you can't slack off too much!

Feel free to leave both the enemies in the sky and on the sea to me. You'll need to deal with those underwater yourself. And one final reminder: don't get too close to me or you might get hurt!

main1.line: Commander, you're truly a kind person...
