main1.line: Commander is looking at... N-nothing, don't worry about it!

main2.line: Kumano, please don't make trouble for Mogami, all right? She's going to get a stomachache again...

main3.line: We're sometimes called the Suzuya class, but I still prefer being called the Mogami class. We all fought together during that war after all..

mission.line: I've arranged the status of our current missions. Please look over them.

mission_complete.line: The mission rewards have arrived. That is good news.

profile.line: I am Suzuya, third ship of the Mogami class. During that war, I fought alongside Mogami as a member of CruDiv 7. My last battle left me with a bit of regret... but I've been given a new beginning on this battlefield, and I'll fight alongside my new companions with a fresh outlook. I look forward to working with you.

propose.line: (whispers) Commander, when this ritual is over... you know what's next, right? Don't worry. I'll treat you better than anyone else. Isn't that right, darling~♡

touch.line: Commander... where do you think you're looking? Don't think I wouldn't notice... I could feel your gaze boring into me... Am I right?

touch2.line: Nnh... So this is what you were after from the very beginning... I knew it all along. I've always known, this entire time... Ehehehe~♡

unlock.line: I am Suzuya, Mogami-class heavy cruiser. I place myself under your command from this day forward.

upgrade.line: My abilities have been enhanced. Well done.

win_mvp.line: Congratulations. Eh, I'm the MVP...? Th-thank you very much...

battle.line: Enemies spotted! Guess we're rollin' up our sleeves and squarin' off!

detail.line: Yo, Commander! Hang out with me, now! Oh, is that a lollipop for me? 'Kay, some other time then! Nom!

drop_descrip.line: Mogami-class heavy cruiser number four – Kumano.

expedition.line: Commission team's back, yo. Don't got time for rhymes, but let's go!

feeling1.line: You're lame, you know that? Not tryin' to be mean, or anything, just saying. Listen, I've got a couple ideas for how to unlamify you.

feeling2.line: Commandeeeeer, I'm boooored, let's do somethiiiing. Yeah, it's candy, so what? Not like I'll turn into a lardo from a single– Hey, oww!

feeling3.line: Commandeeeer, I'm lonelyyyy. We can do whatever, just hang out with meeee. "Find someone else?" Wow, rude much? I wanna hang with you! C'mooon!

feeling4.line: You'll finally hang with me? Hell yeah! Wish you would've just said so from the beginning! Anyway, where we goin'? Y'know, just the two of us~♡

feeling5.line: Y-you really like me?! Really, huh... Thing is, I actually love you, Commander... Seriously, though! I do!

home.line: You gonna review that last battle? Aight, cool, go ahead. Wait, I'm the one who's gotta do it?

hp_warning.line: I'll return to port if it's the last thing I do!

login.line: There you are, Commander! Nice, nice! So, what's up today? We hangin' out together? Just work? Figures...

lose.line: Payback's-a comin', ya hear?!

mail.line: You've got a new DM– Err, I mean, new mail! And don't go ghosting whoever sent it!

main1.line: Huh? Me takin' the battle seriously surprised you? Well, yeah, I get serious when the situation demands it.

main2.line: So, Commander, what kinda girls do ya like? Wait, lemme guess, I'm your type, aren't I? Ahah!

main3.line: Soooo bored... Hey, could ya get Suzuya up in this place? I wanna chat with her about my next shopping trip.

mission.line: Ugh, missions? You're probs better off hittin' up Suzuya...

mission_complete.line: Sooo tireeed... Oh, crap! Hey, unclaimed mission rewards! C'mon, man!

profile.line: Name's Kumano, Mogami-class heavy cruiser! Back in the war, I was Cruiser Division 7, workin' my ass off! Shame about what happened at the island in you-know-where, though... Welp, no point crying over spilt milk. Just gotta do better this time.

propose.line: Uhh, "I take you, to have and to hold, from this day forward"... How'd the rest go? Agh, screw it, it's too long and I'm makin' a fool of myself in front of everyone! You don't mind if we bail and go straight to our room, right, darling?

touch.line: Well, well! Caught you admirin', Commander! Hehehe, you don't gotta act innocent. If you wanna stare, stare all ya want!

touch2.line: Weeeell, someone's feeling frisky, huh? Totes fine with me. Go on, touch me 'till you're content~♡

unlock.line: Bam! Heavy cruiser, Kumano, ready for action~! Commander, pleased to meetcha~!

upgrade.line: Sweet! This'll get me more time in the limelight, yeah?

win_mvp.line: MVP, baybee! Hell yeah! Give it up for Kumano!

detail.line: This is too revealing? Meh, not really~? I've seen submarines wearing more risqué stuff than this.

drop_descrip.line: It's time for Kumano's sexy swimsuit debut~! Just kidding~☆ Hey Commander, just where~ are~ you~ staring~? Ahaha~♡

feeling5.line: Yo, Commandeeer, how'd ya like my bikini? Come closer if ya need a better look~ Yeah, you bet I'm tryin' to hit on you.

main1.line: Commandeeeer, what're you up to? Get over here already, c'mooon!

main2.line: I wanna see Mogami in a bikini! Don't you? I do, at least! And you? Same, right?

main3.line: Phew, I'm tired! Commandeeeer, massage my feet and shoulders! ...Err, I didn't ask you to massage THOSE!

touch.line: Candy? Nuh-uh, this is mine, and I ain't givin' it away! Hahahah!

touch2.line: Hah, I knew this would catch your eye! You're like a little kid~

unlock.line: It's time for Kumano's sexy swimsuit debut~! Just kidding~☆ Hey Commander, just where~ are~ you~ staring~? Ahaha~♡

battle.line: Now I'm PISSED! I'm gonna beat the crap outta you!

detail.line: Aw, for real?! You lucked out and chose the best possible card! Hrmm... Hang on, are you cheating, Commander? You ALWAYS pick out the good cards!

drop_descrip.line: Now it's your turn, Commander! Which one's it gonna be~? You suuuure you wanna pick this card? ...I hear you, Suzuya! Stop tellin' the Commander what the cards are!

home.line: Ahah~ Back where we left off, Commander! So, which card are you gonna pick?

login.line: Psst, Suzuya! Commander's here! Hahah! Let's see you try to beat me this time, man!

main1.line: Hungry, Suzuya? Wanna order home delivery?

main2.line: Whatcha lookin' at, Commander? You more interested in me than the cards, or what?

main3.line: Taking your sweet time, huh. Mmh... Meh... *yaaawn*...

touch.line: Ahah! Is that your final answer?

touch2.line: You jelly, Suzuya? 'Cause you sure look it! Haha~

unlock.line: Now it's your turn, Commander! Which one's it gonna be~? You suuuure you wanna pick this card? ...I hear you, Suzuya! Stop tellin' the Commander what the cards are!

battle.line: I'm gonna evade all their attacks and dance around the– Oww!

detail.line: Who else are ya excited to see, besides me? Ahahah☆ Hey, I'm not jelly in the slightest. I know you, Commander. Just name like, 20 or 30 other people~

drop_descrip.line: Tadah! Get a load of my... dancer outfit! So, whaddya think? Ahaha~♡ Hey, Commander, where are those eyes wandering? Did ya see something ya like?

home.line: C'mon, take a seat~ I'mma give those weary bones a nice massage! Heheh, where should I start? Your shoulders, or your feet? Tickle tickle tickle♪

login.line: Welcome to my unveiling! Now let's see how many songs you can last before you fall for me~ Hahahah♡

mail.line: Aw crap, got an e-mail! Commander, pass me the phone!

main1.line: That's... Mikuma? When'd she become so damn hot and stylish? Sheeeesh... Even I'm swooning over here!

main2.line: Wanna see a rough rehearsal, Commander? Or are you gonna wait 'til the real deal?

main3.line: This dance is like, murder on your back. I'm gonna be recovering in bed tomorrow, so go easy on me~ "What're we gonna do then?" Hang out, duh! Ahah☆

mission_complete.line: We've got mission rewards~ Anything catch your eye?

touch.line: Ahah♡ Wait 'til I start shakin' it around~

touch2.line: Commander... Where's that hand of yours wanderin'...? ♡

unlock.line: Tadah! Get a load of my... dancer outfit! So, whaddya think? Ahaha~♡ Hey, Commander, where are those eyes wandering? Did ya see something ya like?

battle.line: Let us expel evil and bring purity to these blue seas.

detail.line: Ah, I'm feeling just fine, thank you. As a wanderer, my body is used to going days without eating or drinking... But you say the others would worry? Of course... *sigh*

drop_descrip.line: Heavy cruiser – Unzen.

expedition.line: The commission team is back. I can't wait to hear their stories, heehee.

feeling1.line: Normally, I would consider consigning people as immoral as you to death, but... I'm just joking. Please get a hold of yourself, Commander.

feeling2.line: Your care is appreciated, Commander. Whether it be battle, odd jobs, or caring for your affairs, please ask me for anything you may need.

feeling3.line: You'd like to know what I want? Well... Hmm... Ummm... I can't really think of anything, but don't presume I'm without desire. But... Hmm, this is a quandary.

feeling4.line: Commander, I came up with an answer to your question. Looking back, I've never felt... tied down. So I'd—oh, Commander? What's the matter?

feeling5.line: It seems my answer from before has you in a dilemma. But understand that, as long as it's you, I really don't mind... Oh, or do you happen to have other inclinations?

headtouch.line: Hmm, I'm not too sure about this...

home.line: Welcome back, Commander. Would you like to take a warm bath? It must be hard to meet with friends with the stench of battle still on you.

hp_warning.line: I mustn't inconvenience the Commander...!

login.line: Commander? You're quite early today. ...I, on the other hand, was tardy considering my role as your secretary ship, for which I apologize.

lose.line: Clearly... I've neglected my training.

mail.line: You have mail, Commander. Don't you think you should at least skim through it before you leave it in the box?

main1.line: Are you thirsty? If you'd like tea, I'll bring some right away... But you look like you need a nutritional drink.

main2.line: Looking for a diversion? You could take a little walk. Actually, there's a sacred mountain only three days away... Oh? That's too far for you?

main3.line: I don't just know about seals; I have some knowledge of feng shui dragon veins, too. There are other girls in the port who know much more than me, though, so I suppose you don't need to ask me... *glance*

main4.line: The Guardian Fox's little sister asks you questions incessantly? I suppose that would be difficult if you don't know the secret to victory. Commander, sometimes NOT answering is an option.

main5.line: Sometimes, fleeing from work and human relationships is a viable option. I won't tell you to forsake society, but maybe you could learn a little about the hermit mentality?

mission.line: You have a backlog of missions. Heehee, I understand. It's only human to procrastinate until right before your deadline.

mission_complete.line: You have some unchecked mission rewards. Heehee, don't worry. It's nice to watch them build up, isn't it?

profile.line: I am Unzen, a heavy cruiser made as part of the sixth shipbuilding plan. I'm unused to traversing this plane of existence, so I may lean on you for aid, Commander... But if you will accept me, I am more than happy to help—no, serve you. Heehee.

propose.line: I'm deeply honored by your proposal. While I don't feel deserving, I graciously accept... Heehee, it seems I'll have to train to be a bride, won't I, Commander?

skill.line: Boundless heaven and earth, expunge all sin and impurity––

touch.line: If I suit your needs, then please ask anything of me.

touch2.line: I know this training method... Would you like to try it on me, Commander?

unlock.line: The threads of fate stretch far, I see. I am heavy cruiser Unzen, and I shall avail myself of your hospitality for the time being. Ah, not that I am planning to leave you, Commander, but I do intend to take time off for personal matters every now and then. Heehee, I do enjoy letting the wanderlust take over.

upgrade.line: I'm even stronger now. Heheh.

win_mvp.line: Rokkou's manifestation, Kaimon's divinity. Victory comes as holy mounts rise through the clouds.

drop_descrip.line: Commander~ Come over here~♥ Heehee, you look surprised... I don't think I'm dressed strangely at all. Or... is this swimsuit not enough to satisfy you, Commander?

home.line: Commander~ Welcome home~♥ I see, so this is what makes you happy? It seems I still have much to learn... Heehee.

login.line: Commander~ Heheh, come sit over here with me. It may be... a little cramped, but it's enough space for two, isn't it?

mail.line: It seems there are letters waiting for you. It's okay. You may enjoy your break first and read it later.

main1.line: Would you like to join me, Commander? Soak your feet and feel heaven and earth's energy through the land, sea, and ocean breeze...

main2.line: There are some underwater hot springs nearby. How about you and I visit them later? They're quite close—it's just two days if we swim.

main3.line: Commander, when you go on vacation, you should have fun. Yes, it's a rare opportunity to... move your body a little, don't you think?

touch.line: This feeling of liberation... I'd love to feel more of this place's energy with my bare skin... Oh, I can't?

touch2.line: You'd even do that out here...? Heehee♥

unlock.line: Commander~ Come over here~♥ Heehee, you look surprised... I don't think I'm dressed strangely at all. Or... is this swimsuit not enough to satisfy you, Commander?

win_mvp.line: A shipgirl's power isn't tied to appearances... In other words, victory will be just as easy in this swimwear!

battle.line: All units, battle formations!

detail.line: The only value of war is the peace that follows it. I implore you to never forget this.

drop_descrip.line: Kongou-class fast battleship number one – Kongou.

expedition.line: Phew... time to take a break. Commander, does black tea suit you?

feeling1.line: You do not deserve victory!

feeling2.line: Commander, please be at ease, for victory shall soon come.

feeling3.line: Will Zuikaku be fine on her own...? Mm... I'll watch her from here. From this distance, she probably won't notice me...

feeling4.line: I've heard that people are most likely to reveal their sentiments at twilight... I wonder if you're also like this?

feeling5.line: That Hiei, trying to throw a party again tonight... Commander, do you have time to keep me company there?

home.line: Good work out there. Were you able to achieve your tactical goals?

hp_warning.line: Now is the time to make our comeback!

login.line: Have you had enough rest? The fleet now awaits your orders.

lose.line: Please rest at ease. This situation can still be salvaged.

mail.line: Adjust your strategies in accordance with the new information.

main1.line: No way in hell a battleship like me is going to get taken out by some flimsy torpedo!

main2.line: Come! Let's destroy our enemies, pass through that measly canal, and return to the land where I was born!

main3.line: I take myself too seriously? No, you take yourself too lightly!

main4.line: Horns? Oh, these things? They're just decorations on the hat. I wouldn't look much like a member of the Sakura Empire without them, right?

mission.line: Do I need to go do it myself?

mission_complete.line: Excellent! We're one step closer towards our ultimate victory.

profile.line: Nameship of the Fast Battleships, flagship of the 7th Combined Fleet, and the last Sakura capital ship to be laid down overseas - that is me, Kongou!

propose.line: Since you've put so much effort into pursuing me so passionately, it is only fitting that I give you the proper respect. Come, you've earned my hand.

touch.line: Wh-what is it!? An emergency!?

touch2.line: Hey you, don't tell me you've been subjecting my sisters to such depravity as well!?

unlock.line: I am Kongou, lead ship of the Kongou-class battlecruisers. I shall illuminate the path that leads to victory!

upgrade.line: Phew... another trump card to add to my hand.

win_mvp.line: To be victorious is to be elegant!

battle.line: Such a tasteless rabble!

drop_descrip.line: We must fully live in the present, whether during work or during leisure - this is my mantra. Commander, shall we go for an outing together?

home.line: Good work in your sorties today. If you're hungry, I don't mind splitting my dango with you.

login.line: Commander, are you well rested? There are still many hours to go.

main1.line: Commander, a break is not a break if you're constantly thinking about work. Besides, don't you think it's rude to be so preoccupied when you're supposed to be spending time with me?

main2.line: I'm used to always going out with my sisters, so to be able to spend time with you outside is rather novel for me.

main3.line: Commander, when the weather gets a bit warmer, why don't we go enjoy the cherry blossoms with my sisters?

touch.line: You're awestruck by my beauty? Hehe, something as obvious as that needs not even be said~

touch2.line: You... perhaps you're going to need a remedial course in basic etiquette.

unlock.line: We must fully live in the present, whether during work or during leisure - this is my mantra. Commander, shall we go for an outing together?

detail.line: This operating system is the fruit of Akashi and the others' hard work. Would you like to try it out... Actually, I guess it's best if you don't. Hehehe.

drop_descrip.line: "Celebrity Endorsement of the Port Medical Facilities"... Hehehe, you've made a wise decision picking me. Commander, I can leave the ad shoot to you, right?

login.line: Have you rested enough? Let's get back to work, as gracefully as always.

main1.line: This syringe filled with Manjuu plushies is an advertising prop, but isn't it quite adorable? Hehe~♪

main2.line: In a way, saving lives directly like this feels more fulfilling than fighting enemies on the battlefield.

main3.line: Good work completing your duties, Commander. Would you like to get checked up? After all, I am a nurse right now. Hehe~♪

touch.line: Oh? Would a different pose be better?

touch2.line: It seems like you need some more intense treatment, Commander...

unlock.line: "Celebrity Endorsement of the Port Medical Facilities"... Hehehe, you've made a wise decision picking me. Commander, I can leave the ad shoot to you, right?

battle.line: I excel in both theory and practice!

detail.line: Walking with you and taking in the scenery is quite pleasant, actually. Say, how about showing me that vantage point with an apparently exquisite view Hiei spoke of earlier?

drop_descrip.line: It would be a shame to pass on this lovely weather, Commander. Why have a dull commute by train when you can enjoy a leisurely bicycle ride in the sunlight, hm? Heehee♪

expedition.line: It appears the commission team has returned. Shall we treat them to the tea I bought from the school canteen?

feeling5.line: There is a number of school-related romantic things I hope to try at least once. For instance, walking home with my beloved, or making a lunch box and savouring it together... Oh, silly me, I've already done those! Heehee♪

home.line: Splendid work. I'd imagine Haruna went off to see her clubmates... As for me? I suppose I'm doing the same this very moment, my fellow going-straight-home clubmate.

login.line: Have you had a good rest, Commander? You've got a long day of school and office work ahead of you.

main1.line: This outing has reaffirmed to me the reason why we fight – to restore peace to all the world.

main2.line: Kirishima made this charm in her home economics class. It's quite well-made, don't you think?

main3.line: It seems the manjuus fell asleep. Heehee, seeing their adorable at-rest faces somehow makes me think of my sisters.

mission_complete.line: The fruits of missions form the foundation of victory, as someone wise once said.

touch.line: Oh, do I have a petal caught in my hair?

touch2.line: Excuse me, have you even considered how you're going to explain yourself to the Morals Committee?

unlock.line: It would be a shame to pass on this lovely weather, Commander. Why have a dull commute by train when you can enjoy a leisurely bicycle ride in the sunlight, hm? Heehee♪

win_mvp.line: Ah, the tailwind of victory. The very definition of envigorating, is it not?

battle.line: Hehe, shall we go enjoy the festivities?

detail.line: Hehe~ Which do you prefer: matcha, or black tea?

drop_descrip.line: Kongou-class fast battleship number two – Hiei.

expedition.line: Welcome back, everyone. Hopefully, none of you encountered any suspicious people?

feeling1.line: What a pity...

feeling2.line: Ehehe~ Commander, is there something on your mind?

feeling3.line: That Kirishima... She's actually quite the popular one...

feeling4.line: Being able to see everyone's smiles at the banquet makes all the hard work and preparation worth it.

feeling5.line: Commander, after tonight's banquet... will you be free? Hehe, please look forward to it~

home.line: Welcome back. The tea has just been brewed to the right temperature.

hp_warning.line: Commander... It's too early to give up just yet!

login.line: There is nothing more relaxing than a banquet following a battle... By the way, Commander, I'm free after this...

lose.line: Was I bested...?

mail.line: Are all of these new letters? Thank you for your hard work.

main1.line: *Sigh*... Whenever Kirishima comes to a banquet, all those kids that tag along with her usually end up making a mess of things...

main2.line: When it comes to warfare, wisdom and courage are equally important. We can't count on another miracle if we discard proper planning and rely on blind courage.

main3.line: Commander, I'll be able to protect you, no matter the situation. Hehe, I am called an "Imperial Ship" because I have that capacity after all~♪

mission.line: Let's finish while we still have the momentum!

mission_complete.line: Hehe, shall we celebrate by holding a banquet tonight?

profile.line: I am Hiei, the first Kongou-class battleship born in the Land of the Rising Sun. As an Imperial Ship, I witnessed the growth of our mighty fleet, and led our forces into the Battle of the Solomon Sea. Commander, have you finished your preparations? The banquet is about to begin.

propose.line: So this means... "We'll always be forever?" Thank you very much. I'll gladly accept it - however... If anything was to happen to us, I hope that you would consider yourself first...

skill.line: Be swept away by the raging waves!

touch.line: I can take you anywhere the ocean reaches.

touch2.line: Hehe. Commander, have you not gotten enough sleep yet?

unlock.line: I am the Imperial Ship Hiei, second of the Kongou-class, reporting for duty. Commander, where shall we go next?

upgrade.line: Today's breeze feels more pleasant than usual.

win_mvp.line: It was no big deal~

detail.line: Which pillow would you prefer? The soft one, the hard one, or... perhaps you'd like to use my thighs? Hehe~

drop_descrip.line: Look how late it is... Commander, shall we embark on a dreamy voyage together?

login.line: Adequate rest is important for improving your performance. Commander, I've prepared your pillow. Tonight... enjoy the best sleep of your life~

main1.line: Hehe, it seems like we'll be able to have a pajama party banquet. How about it, Commander? Would you like to join?

main2.line: Good night, Commander. Don't worry, I'll wake you up when the time is right.

main3.line: Ah, the plum blossoms shimmering under the moonlight... Commander, shall we go watch the petals together?

touch.line: Commander, the moon is beautiful tonight. Wouldn't you rather take in the beauty of the night sky instead of staring at me?

touch2.line: Hehe~ Someone seems quite energetic tonight, Commander.

unlock.line: Look how late it is... Commander, shall we embark on a dreamy voyage together?

detail.line: I never expected this Spring Banquet to take on a life of its own... By the looks of things, everyone prefers it when the atmosphere is a bit livelier. Hehe~

drop_descrip.line: I have to admit, these qipaos from the Dragon Empery are quite elegant... I might sound arrogant saying this, but I feel like this outfit really brings out my charm. Hehe, wouldn't you agree, Commander?

home.line: Putting your nose to the grindstone is commendable, but you should also know when to take it easy, Commander.

login.line: Commander, you came at just the right time. The banquet is about to begin.

main1.line: Commander, make sure you remember to have your closing speech ready. All right?

main2.line: You'd like... a red envelope as well? Normally, aren't you supposed to be giving out red envelopes to us? Heehee~

main3.line: During these times, it's best to just put aside your work and enjoy the festivities.

touch.line: Sake...? Hehe, since it's a special occasion, I wouldn't mind sharing a cup with you~

unlock.line: I have to admit, these qipaos from the Dragon Empery are quite elegant... I might sound arrogant saying this, but I feel like this outfit really brings out my charm. Hehe, wouldn't you agree, Commander?

detail.line: Did my sand castle capture your interest? This was only possible because of the clement weather, after all~

drop_descrip.line: We're headed for the white sands of the beach today. We all could use a breather every now and then, so let's just enjoy the sea breeze today. Hehe~

home.line: Have you been enjoying your time here? Hehe~ If you get thirsty, please help yourself to this water.

login.line: Commander, is this scenery to your liking? The blue skies and seas, and the merriment of friends frolicking on the beach...

main1.line: A seaside picnic might not be as lavish as the banquets I usually hold, but I am confident in my abilities to throw the best event possible~ Hehe, don't worry, some girls from the Eagle Union are helping me out.

main2.line: The seagulls are flying into the distance. I wonder if they're splitting apart or reuniting... Hehe~

main3.line: Oh my, staying under this scorching sun indeed seems bad for my skin... Commander, would you be so kind as to help me apply the sunscreen?

touch2.line: Commander, perhaps the sea breeze will help you come to your senses?

unlock.line: We're headed for the white sands of the beach today. We all could use a breather every now and then, so let's just enjoy the sea breeze today. Hehe~

battle.line: Let us begin!

detail.line: I wish I was as popular as Kirishima... Well, kind of...

drop_descrip.line: Kongou-class fast battleship number four – Haruna.

expedition.line: All right, I should head out and... Huh...? Not yet...?

feeling1.line: I've lost all hope in you.

feeling2.line: Kongou, allow me to give you a shoulder massage.

feeling3.line: After a tough battle, I feel like eating a whole bucket full of rice.

feeling4.line: Can you dance, Commander? You see, um... I was wondering if you could teach me how to do it...

feeling5.line: Commander, could I please be your dance partner for the next banquet Hiei is hosting...?

home.line: Well done out there. Did you run into any enemies?

hp_warning.line: It's not over yet!

login.line: Nice weather today. We should head out so we don't miss our chance to enjoy it. Don't you agree, Commander?

lose.line: Gah... I'm sorry, but... a loss is a loss...

mail.line: I like your voice, Commander. So... could you read this letter out loud for me?

main1.line: At last... At long last, I will have my battle with Wales...!

main2.line: When you've got bravery and willpower, no enemy is insurmountable. Isn't that right, Commander?

main3.line: Joushuu beef is some of the best around. Care to try some?

mission.line: Hiei, what do you say we get some exercise?

mission_complete.line: Kongou, I'm basically already an adult now.

profile.line: I'm Haruna, the Sakura Empire's speediest fast battleship. I fought hard till the very end. Once more, I will fight with all my heart, holding nothing back!

propose.line: T-this feels a little odd... From now on, you'll be my most beloved... H-how you "compare to my big sisters"? T-that's not at all what I was talking about!

touch.line: Do you like Hiei's handmade sweets, too?

touch2.line: Hah!!!... I'll keep my gloves on next time so I can strike you without getting my hands dirty.

unlock.line: Hello. I'm the Sakura Empire's latest fast battleship, Haruna. I prefer to use my fists over my blade, but I hope that won't be an issue.

upgrade.line: I've become faster!

win_mvp.line: Kongou! Please reward me!

battle.line: Shoot... No time... Let's finish them, quick!

detail.line: I think people will gawk at us if Kirishima and I walk around looking like this... *Sigh*... It's tough being popular...

drop_descrip.line: I think it's fine to enjoy school life once in a while... Hm? You wanna know what I'm listening to? Sure, if you're okay with just one earbud.

main1.line: I think I prefer working up a sweat in the sports field over reading in the classroom.

main2.line: Gotta join a club... There's the karate club... Maybe that'll work?

main3.line: I'm free all week after school. Why don't we hang out a bit, Commander?

touch.line: I always look forward to the lunch box Hiei makes for me every day.

touch2.line: ... Do you want me to beat you over the head with my bag?

unlock.line: I think it's fine to enjoy school life once in a while... Hm? You wanna know what I'm listening to? Sure, if you're okay with just one earbud.

detail.line: To no surprise, Kirishima is the life of the party. Everyone wants to dance with her... I-I'll pass, though...

drop_descrip.line: I guess that looks right... Since Kongou chose this for me, I must trust her judgment... Um, C-Commander, would you mind helping me out? ...It's a bit hard to walk in this outfit...

home.line: Nicely done. Let's get back to the party, shall we?

login.line: Hey, you're late. The party's already started. Oh well, let's get you a drink to whet your appetite.

main1.line: If I remember Wales's wine tasting advice right... First breathe in its aroma, swirl the wine in the glass, then take another breath... Wait... So when do you drink it?

main2.line: Hiei always gets real busy when a banquet or party is coming up. Commander, don't forget to praise her work next time you talk to her.

main3.line: Wow, this steak is really good! Heheh, see what I told you about Joushuu beef?

touch.line: A dance? You're on! I've been practicing tons just for this! Oops, give me a minute to get my bearings straight...

touch2.line: ...I'm warning you: the turrets aren't purely decorative.

unlock.line: I guess that looks right... Since Kongou chose this for me, I must trust her judgment... Um, C-Commander, would you mind helping me out? ...It's a bit hard to walk in this outfit...

detail.line: I knew this kimono looked good, but your approval is what really sealed the deal, Commander. It might not be the best kimono ever, but I'll gladly take a better-than-passing grade from you!

drop_descrip.line: "My dear Commander, is this dress that my sisters tailored for me to your liking?" ...Okay, no, I can't do polite Hiei-speak like she can... So, anyway, h-how do I look?

home.line: Hold the umbrella like this... then turn around and slightly loosen the kimono... Hmm, no, this isn't really my style... How does Hiei pull it off so– Commander?! You're back?!

login.line: Commander, you should get to work before Kongou gets mad at you.

main1.line: Getting dressed was easier than you might think, because I practiced it! See, you start from the bottom and... Oh geez!

main2.line: When I say I'll do something, I'll do it right! I'll prove that even I can conduct myself elegantly, as one of Kongou's sisters!

main3.line: I need to go over there, so come give me a hand, Commander... Nice, thanks. I'd rather not get my kimono soaked if I can avoid it.

mission.line: You'd best stay focused on completing missions, Commander.

mission_complete.line: This isn't so easy to move in, but bringing the rewards here was easy as pie.

touch.line: Watch this, I've got a stylish move for you!

touch2.line: What? Huh?!

unlock.line: My dear Commander, is this dress that my sisters tailored for me to your liking? ...Okay, no, I can't do polite Hiei-speak like she can... So, anyway, h-how do I look?

win_mvp.line: How's THAT, Kirishima?! I can battle even in a kimono!

battle.line: My cannons will decide this battle!

detail.line: Kongou brought me some tea. How about we drink it together?

drop_descrip.line: Kongou-class fast battleship number four – Kirishima.

expedition.line: You're knee-deep in paperwork... Want some help?

feeling1.line: Well, guess even you have problems you won't tell others about...

feeling2.line: Hiei manages to always stay calm, no matter the situation...

feeling3.line: Haruna and I are twins, but to me she feels more like an annoying little sister.

feeling4.line: You know, my big sisters are both really brilliant. That's why I have to work so hard not to hold them back... You think I'm brilliant, too? Hahahah, I'm happy to receive your approval.

feeling5.line: There'll be a dance at a party Hiei is organizing, so... could you be my dance partner? I mulled over it a bit, but you're really my only choice... Huh? Normally, it's the man who asks his partner for a dance? Ahahah, right, how stupid of me...

home.line: You're doing good work out there, Commander. For the next battle, what do you say about bringing me along?

hp_warning.line: This is it... The beginning of the end!

login.line: Commander, is there anything I can help with?

lose.line: Being able to meet one's demise in a battle of firepower might not be so unfortunate...

mail.line: You have mail. You must be really popular, Commander.

main1.line: Searchlights? Ahahahah... The battlefield is no stage.

main2.line: Why I wear this mask? Hahah, think you can guess why?

main3.line: Kongou, allow me to help... What? Y-you don't want any help, huh...

mission.line: Hum, hum. What should I take home with me as a souvenir...

mission_complete.line: Those girls seem exhausted from their commission. Let's go and carry them back to the dormitory.

profile.line: I am Kirishima, the youngest of the Kongou-class fast battleships. I once bombarded Henderson Field and that battleship South Dakota. Searchlights... and Type 3 Shells? ... Aha, hahaha...

propose.line: I-I never would've expected an attack from you... Well, this is embarrassing... *A-ahem*! Then, to return the favor... Commander, whenever you need a dance partner, I'll be yours.

touch.line: Were you starting to feel lonely, Commander?

touch2.line: I'm right here, Commander. Face your partner square on if you're going to do that. Ahahah, look at you~ Now it's you who's embarrassed.

unlock.line: I'm Kirishima, the fast battleship! Now, Commander, there's a long road ahead of us, and we should walk down it together!

upgrade.line: I wonder what'll become of me if these improvements continue...

win_mvp.line: When I use all my power, this is only natural.

battle.line: It's after-school cannon time!

detail.line: Commander, how about we go flower-viewing later after school?

drop_descrip.line: Commander, enjoying school life is all fine and well, but we must not forget our duty... That said, what missions are waiting for us today?

home.line: I made some sweets for my classmates. Let's hand them out together later.

login.line: Commander, your necktie is crooked. Want me to straighten it out for you?

mail.line: "Mailing" seems to have gotten pretty popular at school lately. Thanks to that, I've gotten pretty good at writing.

main1.line: nil

main2.line: Commander, if there's anything troubling you, you can always tell me.

main3.line: I haven't picked a club to join yet... The Archery Club? That actually sounds pretty good... Huh? I'm "not suited for that"?

unlock.line: Commander, enjoying school life is all fine and well, but we must not forget our duty... That said, what missions are waiting for us today?

detail.line: Seriously, you'll only ever find looks like this in fashion mags. It's an Eagle Union thing, according to Kongou...

drop_descrip.line: Being in front of my sisters in this outfit is one thing, but it really is embarrassing to be wearing it in front of you, Commander. Um... ahem! What do you think? Since you're here, want to walk down to the beach together?

home.line: Geesh, just standing around in this outfit draws a ton of attention... Maybe I should just change back into my regular clothes...

login.line: C-Commander... awfully convenient timing there...

main1.line: Hey, Commander, could you support me for a sec? ... Phew, it'll take some time to get used to these high heels.

main2.line: A group photo? Sure thing. Hey, you suggested it, don't shy away from the camera. Okay, say "cheese!"

main3.line: Need a break, Commander? All right, then let's head to Hiei's place and ask her to make us some tasty grub.

touch.line: You think it looks good on me? ... Sounds more like you're just poking fun at me for your own amusement.

touch2.line: C-Commander, this outfit really bothers me... so could you p-p-please stop...

unlock.line: Being in front of my sisters in this outfit is one thing, but it really is embarrassing to be wearing it in front of you, Commander. Um... ahem! What do you think? Since you're here, want to walk down to the beach together?

detail.line: Don't bring a knife to a gunfight! ...Well, don't bring a gun to a showdown between main batteries either~

drop_descrip.line: "Commander, bad luck for you, but you're just going to become another notch on my blade." Haha, just kidding, it's a joke! So, what do you think? My New Year's attire is pretty snazzy, isn't it?

headtouch.line: You like my new hairstyle? When'd you notice?

home.line: Glad you're back, Commander. How are you feeling? Want to come with me to the store? I heard there might be a year-end sale going on.

login.line: It's not like every day can be a holiday, so let's reap the rewards of our achievements!

main1.line: South Dakota... is like a rampaging oni when she gets into a brawl... But, I won't lose out to her either~

main2.line: Ninja? Nah, I was just doing that because I thought it looked cool. We have actual ninjas in the fleet, and I wouldn't want to get on their bad side, y'know.

main3.line: See, there's no issue with me showing my face here. After all, I'm with this commander here who is even more popular than me. Ahaha!

touch.line: Naww, I'm not like Hyuuga and Ise. I won't ask you to spar with me. Hahaha!

touch2.line: Oho~? So, what are you going to do next? If you're all out of moves, then it's my turn to counterattack.

unlock.line: "Commander, bad luck for you, but you're just going to become another notch on my blade." Haha, just kidding, it's a joke! So, what do you think? My New Year's attire is pretty snazzy, isn't it?

detail.line: Aren't you bored, sitting by the side and only watching? You can join me if you want. I've got spare brushes and paper.

drop_descrip.line: The Lunar New Year is known for its hustle and bustle, but it's nice to just sit down with a brush and take in the smell of ink. Hey Commander, got any words you'd want to see rendered in calligraphy?

login.line: Oh, Commander! Great timing! I just finished my latest piece. Care to give it a look?

main1.line: I think Hiei used to paint... I should ask her for some good drawing tips.

main2.line: These ones I'm painting now are for my sisters. Do you wanna tag along with me when I hand them over later?

main3.line: Dang, I'm almost out of ink... Do you reckon Akashi sells ink at her store?

touch.line: Hmm... What should I paint next...

touch2.line: Would you knock it off? I can't paint like this! We'll have time later, so just have a cup of tea and be patient.

unlock.line: The Lunar New Year is known for its hustle and bustle, but it's nice to just sit down with a brush and take in the smell of ink. Hey Commander, got any words you want to see rendered in calligraphy?

battle.line: All right, let's proceed as planned.

detail.line: Don't let anyone get injured? Commander, that's quite the tall order, but I'm up for the challenge.

drop_descrip.line: 1st Ship of the Amagi-class Battlecruisers, Amagi

expedition.line: Commander, a commission has been completed. Also, I have some suggestions for potential candidates to send on the next-

feeling1.line: Swineherds like you are quite hard to find these days.

feeling2.line: Information is a tactician's most valuable asset. Knowing more than your enemy is already half the battle.

feeling3.line: Superior tactics can only make up for differences in strength to a limited extent... *cough* *cough* ...That is why becoming stronger is still of paramount importance, Commander.

feeling4.line: *cough* *cough*... Commander, you've already earned my acknowledgment. Why not have a little more confidence in yourself?

feeling5.line: Commander, if you truly care about me, *cough* then please keep moving forward with all your might. Your gallant victories and smiling face are the best medicine for me.

home.line: Commander, were you able to make use of my strategic plans?

hp_warning.line: Perhaps a change of plans is in order...

login.line: Commander, I've left today's combat operation plans on the table. Please take a look.

lose.line: Did I... make a miscalculation...?

mail.line: Commander, you have new mail. Might it be new intel?

main1.line: The road ahead of us is perilous, but I believe that is also what makes the journey worthwhile.

main2.line: Commander, there is no need to fear failure. As long as I am here, all setbacks are but fodder for our victories.

main3.line: Akagi turned out... a bit differently from what I expected.

mission.line: The next mission is...

mission_complete.line: Mission rewards... we should think of the most efficient way to utilize them.

profile.line: I am the nameship of the Amagi-class battlecruisers, Amagi. Along with Akagi, I was originally supposed to be converted into an aircraft carrier, but that plan was scrapped after a certain natural disaster. *cough* *cough* ... As you can see, my body is not in a great condition, but please do not worry about me too much.

propose.line: Commander... so you've chosen me, then? Hehe... From the beginning, I was prepared to lay my life down for your ambitions. But with this being the case, perhaps I should take better care of my body.

touch.line: Ehehe... Oh, Commander, I was just thinking about what snacks I'd like to eat.

touch2.line: Oh, Commander... I was contemplating some other things...

unlock.line: *cough* *cough* Battlecruiser Amagi, reporting in. It looks like I should be able to fully utilize my abilities here. Commander, would you please brief me on our enemies?

upgrade.line: My health... seems to have improved a bit.

win_mvp.line: Now then, how can we make further use of this victory?

battle.line: First, let us assemble our formation.

detail.line: Is there anything I would like to tell Akagi? Of course, I have many things I would like to impart with her, but perhaps it would be more appropriate that she hears those words from you, Commander. And perhaps, that would be the more interesting way of doing things... Don't you agree? Hehe~

drop_descrip.line: Commander, are you here to pay me a visit? ...Ah, there is no need to be concerned about me. I made a promise to both you and Akagi that I would be mindful of my health.

expedition.line: Commander, a commission has been completed. Shall I summon the returnees here once they are finished with their preparations?

headtouch.line: Oh my, what's this...?

home.line: Thank goodness you're back. Everyone here at port was waiting for your safe return, Commander.

login.line: Commander, are you not going to head down to the ocean? There is no need to worry about me, so please enjoy your time with the others.

lose.line: *cough* *cough*... I wonder if I am coming down with a cold...

mail.line: New mail has arrived — yes, it's good news. You need not be concerned.

main1.line: Kaga's younger sister is quite skilled at drawing... As for my sister, well... Akagi has her own charming points~

main2.line: I'm sorry for the trouble I've caused you due to my less than ideal health, but I would like to say... Commander, you have my deepest gratitude for looking after me all this time.

main3.line: Would a light meal be to your liking, Commander? Kaga, Akagi, and I worked together to make this. We chose our dishes assuming that you would also be here to partake in our cooking. Hehe~

mission.line: Please entrust this assignment to Amagi.

mission_complete.line: The mission rewards have arrived. Please look over them.

touch.line: I'm not going anywhere, Commander. That's what you and Akagi wished for, after all.

touch2.line: Commander, I would advise you to pay closer attention to your surroundings before doing things like this...

unlock.line: Commander, are you here to pay me a visit? ...Ah, there is no need to be concerned about me. I made a promise to both you and Akagi that I would be mindful of my health.

detail.line: Have you already seen Akagi? Heehee, good. She can never settle down unless you're around... No, it's not that she overthinks. I think she's a lot like Nagato, in that she tries to carry all of Sakura Empire on her back. Commander... Make sure you correct her course when she does.

drop_descrip.line: *munch*... Ah. Commander, the banquet isn't over yet. What brings you here? When a host sneaks out, that causes trouble for the person cleaning up after them... Heehee, I didn't say NOT to, now, did I?

expedition.line: The commission is complete. Take it easy and relax, Commander.

feeling5.line: *cough* *cough*... Ah. Commander, I'm just fine. It's not what you think—Oh, thank you. That you've given me tea rather than medicine is proof that you know me well, hehehe.

home.line: You returned right on time. How punctual of you, Commander. Hahaha, I'm just happy that my strategies could help.

login.line: Care for some Sakura confections, Commander? Hiei and the others made a whole bunch, and I just can't stop myself... Heehee, I'm sure Akagi will be worried about me again.

main1.line: I've heard that in Sardegna, they have banquets where you eat lying down. Why don't you try it out, Commander? Heehee!

main2.line: Katsuragi, prattling on for too long will only bother the Commander. At least divide your monologue into two... No, four or five segments would be better...

main3.line: Commander, I know the feast is bountiful, but try not to eat too much, okay? Call it... advice from an expert. Hahaha!

mission.line: Commander, may I accompany you on your next mission?

mission_complete.line: Your mission rewards are here. Yes, I think the fruits of our efforts ought to be reflected in the coming banquet.

touch2.line: Mm... I already know what you're thinking and feeling, Commander. Heehee!

unlock.line: *munch*... Ah. Commander, the banquet isn't over yet. What brings you here? When a host sneaks out, that causes trouble for the person cleaning up after them... Heehee, I didn't say NOT to, now, did I?

win_mvp.line: I'd love to hold a banquet to celebrate everyone's victory. Your thoughts, Commander?

battle.line: Hmph! I shan't lose to the likes of you!

detail.line: Why are you staring at me? ...is my sword too heavy? I- I can take care of myself! It's none of your business!

drop_descrip.line: Fast Battleship, second ship of the Kongou-class Hiei.

expedition.line: Commission complete. I shall go to receive them.

feeling1.line: Kongou! I- I never want to see this Commander again in my life!

feeling2.line: I can do it myself. You go do something else, Commander.

feeling3.line: Hrm... that's not right... Um.... Umm.... Commander? Can you help me with the parts I don't understand?

feeling4.line: Can I prepare the next party? Really!? I won't let you down!

feeling5.line: What did you think of my party, Commander? Did you have fun? Hehe, well, the next one is going to be even better, so you definitely have to come, okay?

home.line: That was a hard-fought sortie... Now then, I didn't make any mistakes, did I?

hp_warning.line: Hiei never leaves a job unfinished!

login.line: Good da- agh! Wahh... I hit myself with my sword.

lose.line: ....urk.... 'tis- 'tis but a trifle! A single defeat! Doesn't bother me at all...

mail.line: New mail... don't tell me... it's a summons!?

main1.line: Make merry? I'd love to! Where are we- oh, no. Now isn't the time for such things!

main2.line: My sisters went to a place called "Royal" to study aboard... abroad? Study abroad. Hmph! I bet you don't even know what abroad is!

main3.line: If you keep staring at me, I'm going to hit you with this! And it's going to hurt!

mission.line: Completing a mission is a glorious thing.

mission_complete.line: Puff out your chest when receiving such honors!

profile.line: Once my big sister Kongou comes back, we're going to shock the world! Until then, I need to work hard to become a leader worthy of her! But.... courtly etiquette is really hard.....

propose.line: Surprised, aren't you? Hiei prepared this party just for you! After all, today is a very important day for me, because... welll... you're very important to me! There, I said it...

touch.line: Do you have anything that needs doing? I must test myself yet!

touch2.line: Shameless pig!

unlock.line: Commander? When I grow up, I’m going to serve the strongest lord in the world! Oh... but for now, I don’t mind if you help me sharpen my skills.

upgrade.line: Hiei won't let you down!

win_mvp.line: Such a victory goes without saying, 'tis but a trifle.

battle.line: Let's proceed as planned.

detail.line: *cough*... *sniffle*... Ugh... I, I'm okay... I just ate too many sweets, and now I'm not feeling so good... *cough* *cough*... *sniffle*...

drop_descrip.line: 1st Ship of the Amagi-class Battlecruisers, Amagi

expedition.line: Commander, a commission has been completed. Should you be willing, may I propose a suggestion for our next task?

feeling1.line: Commander, are you going insane because of my recent poor health...?

feeling2.line: I shall do anything to protect Akagi, the Sakura Empire, and my friends here at this port. Commander, please give me your orders.

feeling3.line: You want to see me grow up healthy and strong? Umm... I understand the importance of this as your subordinate and ship, but... should I be doing anything special?

feeling4.line: *Nom*... Shoooo yummy... Oh, Commander, my apologies, I was just eating this bit of mochi... Hm, it's okay to finish it first? If, if you say so...

feeling5.line: Commander, it's time to take a break. Though you're always looking out for my health, your words wouldn't be persuasive if you didn't also take care of yourself. Here, I've prepared the bed for you~

headtouch.line: Nngh... Commander, p-please stop...

home.line: Welcome back, Commander. Would you like to try some of our traditional sweets? ...If you'd like, I could also eat them with you.

hp_warning.line: Was there an error in my calculations...?

login.line: Commander, I've put today's itinerary here as well as all the documents that need to be looked over. Hm...? I'm perfectly capable of handling this kind of workload by myself.

lose.line: *cough* *cough*... I can't show something so unsightly to Akagi and the others...

mail.line: I wonder if there's any candy inside... Oh, it's just a regular letter...

main1.line: As expected of the head of the Royal Maids... Even I must stop to admire such an excellent cup of black tea... Mm~ hmm~

main2.line: Akagi, Commander is your superior, not your subordinate. ...Jeez, if you end up causing even more trouble, you're going to get an earful!

main3.line: Oops, I mistook the manjuus for dango again... It must be because I'm so hungry...

mission.line: Unfinished missions still remain. We must make efficient use of our earnings...

mission_complete.line: Mission complete, Commander. When can I confirm our next mission?

profile.line: I am Amagi, battlecruiser from the Sakura Empire. Commander, I hope to grow up big and strong here at this port so that I may protect you and Akagi. In other words... I'll do my best to eat properly and sleep properly.

propose.line: You musn't, Commander... If you give this ring to me, then Akagi will... Huh, she's fine with it? ...I see, Akagi is all grown up as well... Wait, sorry, I should be focusing on giving you an answer first... But yes, it'd be an honor to accept this!

touch.line: It's not that my clothes are slipping off, but... Oh, you don't want me catching a cold? Yes, I shall be mindful of that.

touch2.line: Hm? Commander, I am currently busy thinking.

unlock.line: Battlecruiser Amagi offers you her humble greetings, Commander. *cough* *cough* ...Ah, I'm fine, I just seem to have caught a little cold... *achoo!* Aww...

upgrade.line: I must also become stronger, so that I can protect Akagi.

win_mvp.line: Now then... how shall we press the advantage? Hehehe...

battle.line: Milord, those who stand in your way shall find no mercy by my hand.

detail.line: Milord, shall we have tea together?

drop_descrip.line: First ship of the {namecode:78}-class battleships, {namecode:78}.

expedition.line: Milord, your girls have returned from commission. Shall we welcome them back together?

feeling1.line: Milord, might you be the reincarnation of a god of calamity?

feeling2.line: Milord, are you interested in the eight million gods of the Sakura Empire? It is fine if you aren't... I shall offer them your share of prayers.

feeling3.line: Milord, you seem exhausted as of late. Too much work is bad for your health. Please come with me, and allow me to purify you of your fatigue.

feeling4.line: Kagura? That is a dance dedicated to the gods... Ah, why don't I perform just for you, milord? I would be embarrassed if others found out, so please keep it a secret between us, all right?

feeling5.line: Milord, did you know that although a miko of the Sakura Empire must dedicate herself to the gods, she is not actually forbidden from romance? As a matter of fact, she is encouraged to find a husband in order to pass down traditions. Milord, what do you think about me?

home.line: You've worked hard, Milord. Why don't you come to me and take a rest?

hp_warning.line: Gods, please protect us…!

login.line: Welcome back, Milord. Would you like to have your fortune told?

lose.line: Oh no... has my ammunition storage been cursed again?

mail.line: You have a new letter, milord. Please give it a look.

main1.line: I believe that we can change our misfortunes, as long as we work hard and pray...

main2.line: I'll be happy as long as {namecode:79} has a chance to grow up.

main3.line: My main gun specializes in heavy firepower, but is enough to shake my entire body! It can cause me some trouble, every now and then...

mission.line: Milord, a new mission is available. Please take a look.

mission_complete.line: Milord, not claiming your rewards is a bad habit.

profile.line: I am the Sakura Empire's first super-dreadnought, {namecode:78}. In order to cleanse ourselves of the misfortune we were born with, my sister and I offer prayers to the gods every day. We will do whatever it takes to prevent another tragedy like Leyte Gulf from befalling us again. Milord, we would be most grateful should you lend us your aid.

propose.line: May our love last as long as the Great Pines in Takasago and the eternal Tsubaki. May we bring glory to our family, our name heard across the land. These words are said with my highest respect. With this, Milord, you and I become one. Though I may be inexperienced, let us care for and love each other for the rest of eternity.

touch.line: Milord, please rest your head here and allow me to clean your ears.

touch2.line: M-milord... this is improper...

unlock.line: It is an honor to meet you. Milord, you must be the commander. I, {namecode:78}, have been waiting a long time for you. Surely, this is also the guidance of the gods. From now on, please allow me to serve youI

upgrade.line: Now, I can be of greater service to Milord.

win_mvp.line: May thy lost souls return home in peace.

detail.line: Commander, would you like to accompany me for a stroll?

drop_descrip.line: Yamashiro's always saying that I would look better in more trendy clothing, so she went out of her way to pick this out for me. Jeez, that girl... Oh, Commander? Does this outfit... suit me?

login.line: Commander, your luck has been very good recently. Surely, it must be because the gods are also happy.

main1.line: Commander, if it begins to snow, please take cover under my umbrella~

main2.line: Perhaps I should return the favor and make something for Yamashiro to wear... Commander, what kind of outfit do you think is best?

main3.line: The happiness we can enjoy right now is surely a blessing from the gods... No, it's because of your hard work, Commander.

touch.line: Commander, please accept this present. It was prepared specially for you.

touch2.line: Commander? Even though it's a holiday, this kind of thing is...!

unlock.line: Yamashiro's always saying that I would look better in more trendy clothing, so she went out of her way to pick this out for me. Jeez, that girl... Oh, Commander? Does this outfit... suit me?

detail.line: Milord, I feel my bad luck melting away when I am with you... Thank you very much.

drop_descrip.line: Being able to wait for my beloved in this homely attire... Milord, my life has changed so much since meeting you. *giggles*

feeling1.line: Milord, have you grown tired of me...?

feeling2.line: "Dating" is such an incredible word. Milord, even though I've become accustomed to living with you, my heart skips a beat every time I hear that word...

feeling4.line: Milord, I have a small request... but please promise not to laugh. I've always been jealous of the way Akashi jumps into your arms like a spoiled child, but... it's a bit embarrassing to ask... so, um...

feeling5.line: Milord, being able to spend every day with you like this makes it almost feel like we're a married couple... Ah, um, please forget I said anything!

home.line: Milord, the last battle must have been very strenuous, yes? In that case, please come lie down and rest for a while.

login.line: Milord, I just made some snacks. Would you like to try some?

mail.line: Milord, I have brought the mail.

main1.line: Ah... oh no, look at the time... Milord, time passes so quickly when I'm with you. I forgot that I was supposed to take Yamashiro shopping...

main2.line: Milord, do you know how to play Hanafuda cards? Ah, was it Souryuu who taught you how to play? Um, in that case... shall we play together?

main3.line: Milord, the freshly washed blankets sure smell nice. Surely, they'll also be very comfortable to sleep on.

mission.line: Milord, I believe it's time to complete your missions. I shall accompany you.

touch.line: You'd like to take me out? Are you sure? Um, in that case... there are a lot of places I'd like to go with you. Ehehe~

touch2.line: M-Milord...

unlock.line: Being able to wait for my beloved in this homely attire... Milord, my life has changed so much since meeting you. *giggle*

win_mvp.line: Milord, I treasure the time I spend with you above all else.

detail.line: I actually got a lot of things that I want to try, such as be as lively as {namecode:79}... hmm, is that too much?

drop_descrip.line: Milord! Thank you~ Not just for the retrofit, but for many many things. Hehe, it was the greatest of fortune for me and {namecode:79} to meet you.

home.line: Milord, please wait, I’ve made really delicious treats meant especially for you.

login.line: Milord, welcome back~ The profits show that today good things will happen~

lose.line: Oh... no, we can’t blame all failures on our curse.

main1.line: Becoming more… lively? Hehe, that must be merrited by Milord.

main2.line: I feel… that bad luck still exists, but being together with you, Milord, has washed away all my bad luck.

main3.line: {namecode:79} always tells me to look for my own happiness, and I think I’ve finally found it~

mission.line: Milord, can I also join you on this new mission?

touch.line: Milord, do you like the dignified {namecode:78} or the livelier {namecode:78}?

unlock.line: Milord! Thank you~ Not just for the retrofit, but for many many things. Hehe, it was the greatest of fortune for me and {namecode:79} to meet you.

battle.line: Everyone, go~! Waaah?! My guns fired on accident!

detail.line: Milord, you smell really nice~

drop_descrip.line: Second ship of the {namecode:78}-class battleships, {namecode:79}.

expedition.line: Milord, the girls have returned from commissions!

feeling1.line: You're so boring, Milord. I don't want to play with you anymore.

feeling2.line: Milord, come play with me! Ah... I forgot to bring stuff to play with... what should we do?

feeling3.line: I love my sister, but she's a bit too quiet sometimes. Milord, I like spending time with you more because you'll play with me!

feeling4.line: Your Majesty, do you know this mask? It's a fox mask used in Kagura. Hehe, I'm actually about to practice my Kagura dance now. Do you want to watch?

feeling5.line: I know how hard my big sister works, so for her sake, I know that I should allow myself to be happy. That way, I can share my happiness with her. Now that you are here, Milord, I think I'll finally be able to do that. I feel so happy every time I see you!

home.line: Welcome back, Milord, I made you some tea... Woah! Watch out!

login.line: Milord, milord! What shall we do today?

lose.line: Uu... Sister... where are you? *sobs*

mail.line: Milord! Milord! Your mail is here!

main1.line: Milord, Milord! Waah~! ...Thank you, milord. I have always tipped over easily, but I am used to it now.

main2.line: Milord, do you want to jog with me? I want to become a little faster.

main3.line: The vase in the hallway broke... It wasn't me, I swear! It just jumped off right as I walked past it...

mission.line: Milord! New missions!

mission_complete.line: Milord, milord! I've brought the rewards... Oops!

profile.line: Um... I'm big sister {namecode:78}'s little sister, {namecode:79}! Neither of us have really had good fortune since we were born, but I've grown up well thanks to big sis! Please don't judge me by my looks... I was once the flagship of the Combined Fleet! Planes...? What are those? Can I eat them?

propose.line: Milord? You're going to give this to me? ...Even though I am slow-footed and far from perfect? Milord, you are far too kind. I love you too.

touch.line: Milord... that tickles!

touch2.line: Woah! Watch out, Milord! I'm about to fire my main gun!

unlock.line: Woah! It's Milord! Milord in person! Um... I'm Yamahi-, {namecode:79}! I am pleased to make your acquaintance.

upgrade.line: I've gotten stronger... I think!

win_mvp.line: Milord, did you see that? Did you?

detail.line: Milord, I heard that koi streamers can bring good fortune, so I brought some with me~

drop_descrip.line: It’s just not summer without beach volleyball! Ah... Milord, you’re not playing? But I went through all this effort to pick out a swimsuit...

home.line: Milord is back! Ugh... it’s so hot! The fan is even blowing hot air!

login.line: Milord, Milord! Would you help me practice volleyball? It’d be too embarrassing if I let Cygnet beat me...

main1.line: Hawawa! The volleyball is coming my yay! When I stand next to {namecode:17}, I always seem to get hit by things...

main2.line: Ugh... I still can’t light this fire. Stand back, Milord, I’m going to try using my cannons!

main3.line: {namecode:78} tied this bell to my tail so I don’t have to worry about getting bitten by fish when I’m napping at sea... She’s so nice!

touch.line: Ah, Milord! I’m trying to find the best spot to watch fireworks! Want to join me?

touch2.line: Woah...! Milord, next time, say "hi" to me first! I almost rammed my main gun right into you!

unlock.line: It’s just not summer without beach volleyball! Ah... Milord, you’re not playing? But I went through all this effort to pick out a swimsuit...

drop_descrip.line: Merry Christmas! Milord, milord, how do I look? Is my Christmas outfit pretty? Ehehe~ Big sis also praised me today!

main1.line: I sprained my ankle on accident... Uuu... Milord, can you help me massage it?

main2.line: Milord, milord, when it's New Years... will you come see my sister and me perform Kagura?

main3.line: Woah... Milord, milord, it's a snowy Christmas!

touch.line: Merry Christmas! I've already wrapped up a lot of presents! Milord, would you like to pick one out?

touch2.line: Milord... that's not the spot I sprained!

unlock.line: Merry Christmas! Milord, milord, how do I look? Is my Christmas outfit pretty? Ehehe~ Big sis also praised me today!

detail.line: Banquets are a lot of fun! Next time, we should have a Sakura-style banquet and invite everyone from the other camps!

drop_descrip.line: Fusou told me that I have to wear a Western-style dress to the banquet, so she got one for me! Milord, Milord, isn't this dress pretty?

feeling5.line: Milord, Milord, you've done so much for me, so is there anything I can do for you...? Whatever you want, I-I'll do it!

login.line: Heheh~♪ Going to a banquet with Milord... Hawawa?! Milord, how long have you been standing there?

main1.line: Milord, Milord, what's this? And this? There are so many things I haven't experienced before, my head's spinning!

main2.line: Milord, are you sure you'd like to take someone like me to the banquet...? I won't make you look bad, right?

main3.line: Shigure, don't do anything weird at the banquet. You'll bother the others!

touch.line: Milord, Milord, I hear that there will be dancing at the banquet! Would it be okay for me to dance with you?

touch2.line: M-Milord! It's going to be troublesome if everyone sees us!

unlock.line: Fusou told me that I have to wear a Western-style dress to the banquet, so she got one for me! Milord, Milord, isn't this dress pretty?

battle.line: Combat clerk, sortieing! Th-that's what I'm supposed to say, right?!

detail.line: I asked Fusou to prepare this outfit for me! Ehehe, Fubuki and I are going to work hard together!

drop_descrip.line: Milord, Milord, welcome to the store! Yamashiro is a sales clerk today! Mhm, I'll do my best!

home.line: Thank you for your patronage! Awawa... I forgot to give back the change! I, I'm so sorry...

login.line: Milord! Akashi told me to help her out by being a sales clerk today! What do you think about my outfit? Err, huh? It looks funny...?

main1.line: Milord, we have new goodies! Want to take a look? ~☆

main2.line: Fubuki, why are you wearing that... I mean, it's cute, but... Maybe it's best not to think too much about it! Mhm!

main3.line: Shigure, are you shopping with Yuudachi and the others today? Jeez, you should bring Nowaki with you once in a while...

touch.line: Um, Milord, I can't give you a discount on that.

touch2.line: Milord, you also think this outfit is super cute, right?

unlock.line: Milord, Milord, welcome to the store! Yamashiro is a sales clerk today! Mhm, I'll do my best!

detail.line: Ehehe... If I bottle up some of the fresh air here, everyone back at port will get to experience the atmosphere here as well!

drop_descrip.line: Woah, even the air tastes totally different at this vacation spot! Milord, Milord, um, Akashi asked me to bottle up some of the air here for her! Want to give me a hand?

home.line: Milord, Milord, if you're tired, why not take a little break under that umbrella?

login.line: The beach here isn't quite like the one back at the port, but it's totally beautiful! Ehehe, I'm so glad I got to go on a vacation with you, Milord!

main1.line: Look, Milord, someone's surfing over there!

main2.line: How are we supposed to bring all these bottles back to port? ...Milord, I'm sure you'll think up an idea!

main3.line: There are tons of fun places other than the beach? Mmhmm, I'll gladly accompany you, Milord!

touch2.line: Waah! ...I'm so sorry, Milord, I just swung a bottle at you, didn't I...?

unlock.line: Woah, even the air tastes totally different at this vacation spot! Milord, Milord, um, Akashi asked me to bottle up some of the air here for her! Want to give me a hand?

detail.line: Milord, Milord, my friends from the other camps taught me all kinds of neat stuff! To thank them, I also taught them about some of our traditional games!

drop_descrip.line: Uwaah! M-Milord?! I'm so, so sorry... You didn't get hurt, did you? Um... This is my school uniform. Fusou tailored it for me, hehe~ ... Awawa! I should head off to class now! See you later!

home.line: Good work, Milord! Let's go up to the roof to eat lunch together~

login.line: Milord, here's your bento~ I made it myself!

main1.line: Milord, Milord! I want to start a Miko Club at school to help people better understand the work that Fusou and I do! Um, but right now, we still haven't recruited enough members...

main2.line: Milord, I only learned this recently, but ship magazines are really complex... Um, I'll study harder, so that nothing bad will happen to mine again! School is so much fun! I wish Fusou could be here with us as well... But, um, wouldn't it make more sense for her to be a teacher?

touch.line: It was so romantic when I bumped into Commander when I turned around the corner... Maybe next time, I'll wait there on purpose... Eek! Ah, um, you didn't hear anything!

unlock.line: Uwaah! M-Milord?! I'm so, so sorry... You didn't get hurt, did you? Um... This is my school uniform. Fusou tailored it for me, hehe~ ... Awawa! I should head off to class now! See you later!

detail.line: Milord, how was my Kaguya dance? Fusou taught me this dance to help get rid of bad luck!

drop_descrip.line: Milord, Milord, I've finished changing! What do you think? Do you like Yamashiro's new outfit?

feeling5.line: Milord, I love you more than anything else! Being with you is so fun and joyous! I want to stay together with you forever and ever, Milord!

home.line: Milord, Milord, come rest here for a while! Yamashiro will give you a massage... hup!

login.line: Milord, welcome back... Wooooah! Ehehe... I've lost track of the number of times you've had to catch me~

main1.line: Milord, let me help clean your ears!

main2.line: Milord, when spring comes around, let's go view the cherry blossoms!

main3.line: Milord, want to take a nap in Yamashiro's lap?

touch.line: Milord, I want to touch you as well! *Rub rub~ pat pat~*!

touch2.line: Milord, you can get lovey-dovey with Yamashiro all you want! Mmhmm!

unlock.line: Milord, Milord, I've finished changing! What do you think? Do you like Yamashiro's new outfit?

detail.line: Milord~ Was I able to be of use to you?

drop_descrip.line: Milord! I can do anything now~ bombardment or aerial strikes! So, the thing is, you can totally count on me, much much more, Milord! Milord~!

hp_warning.line: Milord... Milord... please save me!

main1.line: If I can be of use to you, Milord, I'll do anything...

main2.line: Milord! Milord! I think I've gotten faster! Did you notice? Uu... I'll... try harder...

main3.line: With my flying friends around, I won't need to light fires with my main cannons to cook anymore~!

touch.line: Milord! Milord! Did you know? I used new bath salts last night~!

touch2.line: Ahh!! Milord, watch out! My seaplanes are going to run into you!!

unlock.line: Milord! I can do anything now~ bombardment or aerial strikes! So, the thing is, you can totally count on me, much much more, Milord! Milord~!

battle.line: Finally! My turn to make some noise.

detail.line: Commander, allow me to show you what real bullet hell looks like!

drop_descrip.line: First ship of the {namecode:76}-class battleships, {namecode:76}.

expedition.line: Operation Kita was more fun that this!

feeling1.line: Are you from the Army?

feeling2.line: It'd be wonderful to be able to go stargazing with {namecode:77} again.

feeling3.line: Compared to that time, life is a lot more vivid and entertaining now. Cheers, Commander!

feeling4.line: Commander, I brought some snacks. Why don't we have some drinks tonight?

feeling5.line: I could have any number of friends stronger than me, but you Commander... Ahaha! You're an idiot, I'm an idiot! Cheers~!

home.line: Tsk... I haven't had a chance to play- Ahem... Commander, I've been guarding our rear just as you asked!

login.line: Let's go have a swell time on the seas, Commander!

lose.line: One... final... bombardment!

mail.line: Whoo! Just the thing to prop up the corner of the table!

main1.line: We're fine without fuel. All you need out on the seas is some good food and booze!

main2.line: What should I call {namecode:78}? Big sister? Senpai?

main3.line: Ise Shrine? I've seen it from a distance, but they won't let me go in...

mission.line: I... I'm coming too! Wait for me!

mission_complete.line: Mmhmmm~! All I need is a beer and a raw egg to wake up. Do you want some too?

profile.line: {namecode:76}, first ship of the {namecode:76}-class battleships! I was on perimeter guard when Pearl Harbor was attacked. I was then recalled and remodeled as an aviation battleship. Then I was recalled again... Tsk! Some ships have a long list of battles, but no one was patient enough to wait for me to join in! We're super dreadnought ships... You would think they'd want our help! *Sigh* Anyways, it's great to finally catch up with the main fleet!

propose.line: Thank you~! I'm going to stay by your side until the end of the end. Why? Because I hate drinking alone!

touch.line: What? W-What do you mean an aviation battleship can't fly? Lame!

touch2.line: Commander, you really want to know what it feels like to fly, don't you? Please feel free to climb into my cannon.

unlock.line: I'm the Sakura Empire battleship who fired the last full volley during the war: Ise-Class battleship, Ise!

upgrade.line: A flight deck, eh? I wish I could fly...

win_mvp.line: Ahaha! As a super dreadnought, it's only natural!

drop_descrip.line: Planes: check! Main guns: check! Nobody can stop me now! Let's sortie right now, Commander! I'm fired up and wanna wreak some havoc on the battlefield!

home.line: Keep an eye out? My aircraft can do that, easy peasy. I tell ya, these beauts are really handy~

login.line: Commander, my guns are gonna rust up if you keep me in port forever.

main1.line: Damn... Guess aviation battleships can't fly, after all. Kinda let down, honestly...

main2.line: What? I can't let my aircraft fly around the port whenever I want? Why not?!

main3.line: Phew... What a nice day! Maybe I'll call over Hyuuga later so we can all go for some drinks. Whaddya say, Commander?

touch.line: You interested in my flight deck?

touch2.line: Aviation battleships can't fly, but if you want me to send you flying, then I'll grant your wish.

unlock.line: Planes: check! Main guns: check! Nobody can stop me now! Let's sortie right now, Commander! I'm fired up and wanna wreak some havoc on the battlefield!

battle.line: Speak your name! I'm not going to cut down some nameless rat!

detail.line: Want to practice combat techniques with me, Commander?

drop_descrip.line: Second ship of the {namecode:76}-class battleships, {namecode:77}.

expedition.line: Mmm, well done!

feeling1.line: My sword has no eyes, Commander. Watch yourself.

feeling2.line: B-big sis... do you have to cling to me every time you drink?

feeling3.line: Ehehe... Commander, you look so cute after a few drinks~

feeling4.line: Neither Ise nor I have any problems with exploding turrets.

feeling5.line: Commander, let's have a duel! Don't worry, I won't use my weapon this time... You might actually stand a chance that way, right?

home.line: Done with warmups? Alright...

login.line: Phew... Wouldn't you agree that it's better to train from dusk until dawn instead of from dawn to dusk?

lose.line: {namecode:76}... Sister...

mail.line: Is this your stuff? Make sure to keep it in a safe place next time.

main1.line: Ise, please clean your room every now and then...

main2.line: It sure would be nice to meet Hatsushimo here.

main3.line: Though the Age of Aviation has come, it still isn't the Age of Aviation Battleships.

mission.line: Commander, we'd be better off just not doing any pointless missions.

mission_complete.line: Commander, drinking a beer with a raw egg is just wrong... All you need is beer. Pure beer!

profile.line: Hyuuga, second ship of the Ise-class, reporting in. Like my sister, I don't have many actual achievements. Then again, the same goes for most of us Sakura Empire battleships. That includes Na-whatever and Ya-whatever. It has nothing to do with our designs or capabilities! ...Hmph. Make fun of me all you want, Commander, but I'll show you what I'm made of.

propose.line: You should keep this kind of thing in your mind only... Seriously... how will people look at me if I wear this... Hehe... hehe... hehe!

touch.line: A veteran swordsman should be able to detect her opponent's energy before they get too close... I still have a long way to go...

touch2.line: Commander, let's spar. If you win, I'll let you touch me as much as you'd like.

unlock.line: I'm the little sister of my stupid big sister... Ah! That doesn't mean that I'm a stupid little sister, alright?! Anyways, I'm {namecode:77}. Nice to meet you.

upgrade.line: Now my main gun sounds even better when it fires!

win_mvp.line: Phew... Let's work a bit harder!
